msgstr "Academia"

#. [unit], id=Charmian, type=Novice Mage, gender=female
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:60
msgid "Charmian"
msgstr "Charmian"

#. [unit], id=Student, type=Thunder Mage MK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:80
msgid "Hotep"
msgstr "Hotep"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:153
msgid "Healing Wing"
msgstr "Ala de Sanación"

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Um, I wonder where Miss Merwe is... Maybe I misunderstood the place she told "
"me to meet her...?"
msgstr ""
"Um, me pregunto dónde estará la señorita Merwe... ¿Quizás entendí mal el "
"lugar donde me dijo que nos encontráramos...?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:210
msgid ""
"(panting) Wait... Here am I... You're the freshman Charmian, right? I am "
"Merwe, and I'm going to show you the Academy today, and also explain "
"everything you need to know about it."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Espera... Aquí estoy... Tú eres la nueva Charmian, ¿verdad? Soy "
"Merwe y hoy te voy a mostrar la Academia y también explicarte todo lo que "
"necesitas saber sobre ella."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Oh, thanks very much, Miss Merwe! You know, this very city is totally "
"unknown to me, so I'm completely lost here..."
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, muchas gracias, señorita Merwe! Sabes, esta ciudad me es totalmente "
"desconocida, así que estoy completamente perdida aquí..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:218
msgid ""
"I understand, I felt the same when I came here from my village for the first "
"time. But you get used to everything quite quickly, just you wait and..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo, me sentí igual cuando vine aquí por primera vez desde mi aldea. "
"Pero te acostumbras a todo bastante rápido, solo espera y..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:225
msgid "Er, Merwe..."
msgstr "Eh, Merwe..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:229
msgid "Hi, Akhen! Charmian, this is Akhen Wadjet..."
msgstr "¡Hola, Akhen! Charmian, este es Akhen Wadjet..."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:233
msgid ""
"You're a Wadjet?! Then you're a descendant of Myra and Aldrik! By the gods, "
"I'm so honoured to meet you! The folks back home won't even believe it when "
"I tell them..."
msgstr ""
"¿¡Eres un Wadjet!? ¡Entonces eres descendiente de Myra y Aldrik! ¡Por los "
"dioses, es un honor conocerte! La gente de mi aldea no se lo va a creer "
"cuando se lo cuente..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:237
msgid "(embarrassed) Well, it's no big deal, really, I'm not like them..."
msgstr ""
"(avergonzado) Bueno, no es para tanto, de verdad, yo no soy como ellos..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:241
msgid "Ahem! So, Akhen, what's the deal?"
msgstr "¡Ejem! Entonces, Akhen, ¿qué pasa?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:245
msgid "Ah, yes... See, I need your help for something..."
msgstr "Ah, sí... Verás, necesito tu ayuda para algo..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:249
msgid "(smiling) You really give me no rest, do you? All right, say it."
msgstr "(sonriendo) De verdad no me das descanso, ¿eh? Está bien, dime."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:253
msgid ""
"I need to train for a duel today, but I haven't fought in ages, so I barely "
"remember any fighting strategy..."
msgstr ""
"Necesito entrenar para un duelo hoy, pero hace mucho que no lucho, así que "
"apenas recuerdo alguna estrategia de combate..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:257
msgid ""
"Actually, in my record you have never fought a duel... And who's challenged "
"you anyway?"
msgstr ""
"En realidad, en mi registro nunca has luchado en un duelo... ¿Y quién te ha "
"desafiado, por cierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:261
msgid "Um, it was Mahyus Meritane..."
msgstr "Um, fue Mahyus Meritane..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:265
msgid "Mahyus?! My goodness, Akhen, what have you done to get him mad at you?"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Mahyus?! Por Dios, Akhen, ¿qué le has hecho para que se enfade contigo?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:269
msgid ""
"I really have no idea, he just came out of nowhere and challenged me to a "
"duel; and, of course, I didn't refuse."
msgstr ""
"De verdad no tengo idea, simplemente apareció de la nada y me desafió a un "
"duelo; y, por supuesto, no me negué."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:273
msgid ""
"Erm, excuse me, but what is happening? Who's this Mahyus, and what is this "
"duel?"
msgstr ""
"Disculpen, ¿qué está pasando? ¿Quién es este Mahyus y qué es este duelo?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:277
msgid ""
"Duels are part of this Academy's curriculum; it is meant to give the "
"students some battle experience, for we veterans are often called to help in "
"military missions. As for Mahyus… Well, he’s one of the best veterans, and "
"has even been to a battle against the orcs already. He studies the Umbra "
"Arts, but is able to summon strong elemental creatures as well."
msgstr ""
"Los duelos forman parte del plan de estudios de esta Academia; sirven para "
"dar a los estudiantes algo de experiencia en batalla, ya que nosotros los "
"veteranos a menudo somos llamados a ayudar en misiones militares. En cuanto "
"a Mahyus… Bueno, es uno de los mejores veteranos y ya ha participado en una "
"batalla contra los orcos. Estudia las Artes Umbra, pero también es capaz de "
"invocar fuertes criaturas elementales."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:281
msgid ""
"Ah, but I doubt he will stand a chance against the heir of the first and "
"most powerful of all elementalists!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ah, pero dudo que tenga alguna posibilidad contra el heredero del primero y "
"más poderoso de todos los elementalistas!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:285
msgid ""
"Well... All right, Akhen, I will help you... Charmian, do you mind coming "
"along? You will see much of the Academy as you follow us anyway."
msgstr ""
"Bueno... Está bien, Akhen, te ayudaré... Charmian, ¿te importa venir con "
"nosotros? De todos modos verás gran parte de la Academia mientras nos sigues."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:289
msgid "Of course! I'm eager to see Akhen in action!"
msgstr "¡Por supuesto! ¡Estoy ansiosa por ver a Akhen en acción!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Right... So, Akhen, let's go to a simulator chamber first, so that you may "
"strengthen your elementals."
msgstr ""
"Bien... Entonces, Akhen, vayamos primero a una cámara de simulación para que "
"puedas fortalecer a tus elementales."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:309
msgid "Hey, is this a statue of Myra?"
msgstr "Oye, ¿esta es una estatua de Myra?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:313
msgid ""
"No, that's Maat of Hiera'Shirsha, Myra's foster-mother. She was a legend "
"long before Myra became one, an Ascendant of the Windsong who was respected "
"and admired by everyone in the Old Home. So admired she was that, when our "
"Aragwaithi and Hannuk ancestors founded our city, rather than name it after "
"either people's language, it was named after Maat. In the old ceremonial "
"language of the Windsong, Maat'Kare means 'Maat's Haven'."
msgstr ""
"No, esa es Maat de Hiera'Shirsha, la madre adoptiva de Myra. Fue una leyenda "
"mucho antes de que Myra lo fuera, una Ascendente de las Hijas del Viento que "
"era respetada y admirada por todos en el Viejo Hogar. Tan admirada era que, "
"cuando nuestros ancestros aragwaithi y hannuk fundaron nuestra ciudad, en "
"lugar de nombrarla según el idioma de alguno de los pueblos, la nombraron en "
"honor a Maat. En el antiguo idioma ceremonial de las Hijas del Viento, "
"Maat'Kare significa «Refugio de Maat»."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:317
msgid ""
"She looks so cool! I knew her story, of course, but I'd never seen a statue "
"of her before. Also, I didn't know our city's name came from the language of "
"the Windsong!"
msgstr ""
"¡Se ve increíble! Conocía su historia, por supuesto, pero nunca había visto "
"una estatua suya. Además, ¡no sabía que el nombre de nuestra ciudad venía "
"del idioma de las Hijas del Viento!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:321
msgid ""
"Not just the city's, though. What we now call our 'high speech', with which "
"we write official documents, name our cities and ourselves, is entirely the "
"Windsong ceremonial language. But you're forgiven for not knowing that; "
"after Hashira's Betrayal, there was a lot of effort to erase their "
"contributions to our society."
msgstr ""
"No solo el de la ciudad. Lo que ahora llamamos nuestro «habla elevada», con "
"la que escribimos documentos oficiales, nombramos nuestras ciudades y a "
"nosotros mismos, es completamente el idioma ceremonial de las Hijas del "
"Viento. Pero te perdono por no saberlo; después de la Traición de Hashira "
"hubo mucho esfuerzo por borrar sus contribuciones a nuestra sociedad."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:325
msgid ""
"And my teachers back in the village used to say our high speech came from a "
"very ancient, very great civilisation..."
msgstr ""
"Y mis maestros en la aldea solían decir que nuestro habla elevada provenía "
"de una civilización muy antigua y muy grande..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:329
msgid ""
"Oh, they weren't lying. The Windsong's ceremonial speech is itself borrowed "
"from the language of an ancient empire known as Sekhem. Even the Windsong "
"knew little about them, though, so ancient Sekhem is. Historians don't even "
"agree on <i>where</i> it was; it's generally agreed such a grand human "
"civilisation would've influenced all others that came later, but of all "
"known human cultures of the Old Home, none bear the slightest trace of "
"Sekhem's language. Some even theorise the empire rose in an island that was "
"swallowed by the seas aeons ago."
msgstr ""
"Oh, no mentían. El habla ceremonial de las Hijas del Viento está tomada del "
"idioma de un antiguo imperio conocido como Sekhem. Sin embargo, incluso las "
"Hijas del Viento sabían poco sobre ellos, tan antiguo es Sekhem. Los "
"historiadores ni siquiera se ponen de acuerdo en <i>dónde</i> estaba; "
"generalmente se acepta que una civilización humana tan grandiosa habría "
"influido en todas las que vinieron después, pero de todas las culturas "
"humanas conocidas del Viejo Hogar, ninguna muestra el más mínimo rastro del "
"idioma de Sekhem. Algunos incluso teorizan que el imperio surgió en una isla "
"que fue tragada por los mares hace eones."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:333
msgid "Ohhh..."
msgstr "Ohhh..."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:349
msgid "Hey Merwe, Akhen, what is that monument for?"
msgstr "Oye Merwe, Akhen, ¿para qué es ese monumento?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:361
msgid ""
"It celebrates this Academy's thousandth anniversary; we could go see it, it "
"tells a little about this place's History and about the magic paths."
msgstr ""
"Celebra el milésimo aniversario de esta Academia; podríamos ir a verlo, "
"cuenta un poco sobre la historia de este lugar y sobre las sendas de la "
"magia."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:377
msgid ""
"'The ancient Academy of Maat'Kare was founded alongside its home city by "
"Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, the greatest heroine of our people, and by former "
"Windsong who wished to develop new paths of magic.'"
msgstr ""
"«La antigua Academia de Maat'Kare fue fundada junto a su ciudad natal por "
"Myra de Hiera'Shirsha, la mayor heroína de nuestro pueblo, y por antiguas "
"Hijas del Viento que deseaban desarrollar nuevas sendas de la magia.»"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:382
msgid ""
"'After years of studies, and with the invaluable aid of Windsong and of "
"allied Celestials, four different paths were established. Each of these "
"paths is symbolically represented by an orb of light of a particular colour: "
"when a mage masters any of them, he is given a magical gem with the colour "
"associated with the completed path. It is not uncommon to see mages wearing "
"two luminous gemstones; less common is the sight of mages wielding three "
"gemstones. And in all of our history, only two individuals have been graced "
"with four gemstones: one was Aldrik the Wise, and the other is Menon Hekare. "
"For this reason, they are popularly known as Masters of Four Lights.' "
msgstr ""
"«Tras años de estudios, y con la inestimable ayuda de las Hijas del Viento y "
"de Celestiales aliados, se establecieron cuatro sendas diferentes. Cada una "
"de estas sendas está representada simbólicamente por un orbe de luz de un "
"color particular: cuando un mago domina alguna de ellas, se le entrega una "
"gema mágica con el color asociado a la senda completada. No es raro ver "
"magos que portan dos gemas luminosas; menos común es ver magos que portan "
"tres gemas. Y en toda nuestra historia, solo dos individuos han sido "
"agraciados con cuatro gemas: uno fue Aldrik el Sabio y el otro es Menon "
"Hekare. Por esta razón, son conocidos popularmente como Maestros de las "
"Cuatro Luces.» "

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:387
msgid ""
"'Aquamarine Arts: They comprise the secrets of the elemental magic created "
"by Myra and perfected by Aldrik; they allow the mage not only to control the "
"elements and the weather, but also to communicate with and even summon "
"spirits of Nature - though not like Myra did, or so it is believed. Those "
"who walk this path are known for caring deeply about Nature; they stand as "
"guardians of the natural world.'"
msgstr ""
"«Artes Aguamarinas: Comprenden los secretos de la magia elemental creada por "
"Myra y perfeccionada por Aldrik; permiten al mago no solo controlar los "
"elementos y el clima, sino también comunicarse e incluso invocar espíritus "
"de la Naturaleza, aunque no como lo hacía Myra, o eso se cree. Quienes "
"siguen esta senda son conocidos por preocuparse profundamente por la "
"Naturaleza; se erigen como guardianes del mundo natural.»"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:392
msgid ""
"'Lucent Arts: Inherited from the mysterious lore of the Celestials, beings "
"who have dwelt on Netjer-Ta ages ago, and who are said to be the descendants "
"of gods. Their arts focus on the powers of the light and of the arcane: as "
"such, they are exceedingly effective in healing and in dispelling unnatural "
"phenomena. Those who walk this path are known for their selflessness, and "
"tirelessly dedicate themselves to the cause of those in need.'"
msgstr ""
"«Artes Lucientes: Heredadas del misterioso saber de los Celestiales, seres "
"que habitaron Netjer-Ta hace eras y que se dice son descendientes de dioses. "
"Sus artes se centran en los poderes de la luz y lo arcano: por ello, son "
"extremadamente efectivas en sanar y disipar fenómenos antinaturales. Quienes "
"siguen esta senda son conocidos por su altruismo y se dedican "
"incansablemente a la causa de quienes lo necesitan.»"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:397
msgid ""
"'Crimson Arts: The original art of our people, on which our very "
"civilisation was founded. Established by former Windsong who had deserted "
"their order, those who walk this path have inherited their eagerness for "
"learning and storing any knowledge that is within human reach. Also from the "
"Windsong's legacy comes its adepts' mastery of fire magic.'"
msgstr ""
"«Artes Carmesíes: El arte original de nuestro pueblo, sobre el cual se fundó "
"nuestra propia civilización. Establecidas por antiguas Hijas del Viento que "
"desertaron de su orden, quienes siguen esta senda han heredado su afán por "
"aprender y almacenar cualquier conocimiento que esté al alcance humano. "
"También del legado de las Hijas del Viento proviene el dominio de la magia "
"del fuego de sus adeptos.»"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:402
msgid ""
"'Umbra Arts: Inheritors of the darkest legacy of the Windsong, the teachings "
"of the ancient Book of the Dead, commit themselves to the secrets of the "
"Spirit World. Those who walk this path are ever on the twilight realm "
"between Life and Death, Light and Darkness. Yet, as there is no light "
"without shadow, so are the Umbra Arts invaluable to our people, who have "
"time and again been protected by the sages who brave this dangerous path.'"
msgstr ""
"«Artes Umbra: Herederas del legado más oscuro de las Hijas del Viento, las "
"enseñanzas del antiguo Libro de los Muertos, se consagran a los secretos del "
"Mundo Espiritual. Quienes siguen esta senda se encuentran siempre en el "
"reino crepuscular entre la Vida y la Muerte, la Luz y la Oscuridad. Sin "
"embargo, como no hay luz sin sombra, las Artes Umbra son invaluables para "
"nuestro pueblo, que una y otra vez ha sido protegido por los sabios que se "
"atreven a transitar esta senda peligrosa.»"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:436
msgid "There goes the Academy's bottom couple, the misfit and the bookworm!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahí va la pareja más baja de la Academia, el inadaptado y la ratón de "
"biblioteca!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:440
msgid "(sarcastic) And there goes the Academy's bottom comedian..."
msgstr "(sarcástica) Y ahí va el comediante más bajo de la Academia..."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:456
msgid ""
"You may get angry at us for pairing you up, but the two of you do look cute "
"together..."
msgstr ""
"Puede que se enojen con nosotros por emparejarlos, pero los dos se ven muy "
"lindos juntos..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:460
msgid "(blushing) Shut up, you idiot..."
msgstr "(sonrojándose) Cállate, idiota..."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:478
msgid ""
"You know, you're very clever and skilled, but you really should work on your "
"looks and your attitude..."
msgstr ""
"Sabes, eres muy inteligente y hábil, pero realmente deberías trabajar en tu "
"apariencia y tu actitud..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:482
msgid "What I should do is send you to the Healing Wing! Now, out of my way!"
msgstr ""
"¡Lo que debería hacer es enviarte al Ala de Sanación! ¡Ahora, quítate de mi "
"camino!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:515
msgid ""
"You know, I'm pretty sure that, wherever she is, Myra must be looking at "
"Maat'Kare now and shaking her head in disgust at how useless her last heir "
"is."
msgstr ""
"Sabes, estoy bastante seguro de que, dondequiera que esté, Myra debe estar "
"mirando Maat'Kare ahora y negando con la cabeza con disgusto por lo inútil "
"que es su último heredero."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:519
msgid "Yes, right..."
msgstr "Sí, claro..."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:536
msgid ""
"You see, he grew up in this Academy, always surrounded by thousands of books "
"and dozens of masters of magic, and still he can't even summon a mere "
"elemental... That's what I call being really useless."
msgstr ""
"Verás, creció en esta Academia, siempre rodeado de miles de libros y decenas "
"de maestros de magia, y aun así ni siquiera puede invocar un simple "
"elemental... A eso le llamo yo ser realmente inútil."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:553
msgid ""
"Um, suddenly I felt this area's average skill level decrease some points..."
msgstr ""
"Um, de repente sentí que el nivel promedio de habilidad de esta zona bajó "
"unos puntos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:557
msgid "You're not funny..."
msgstr "No eres gracioso..."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:574
msgid "Say, Akhen, doesn't your family have any cool secret magic?"
msgstr "Oye, Akhen, ¿tu familia no tiene alguna magia secreta genial?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:578
msgid ""
"No, not really... The Trident of the Seas officially belongs to the Wadjets, "
"though."
msgstr ""
"No, la verdad que no... Aunque el Tridente de los Mares pertenece "
"oficialmente a los Wadjet."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:582
msgid "Cool! Do you wield it outside the Academy?"
msgstr "¡Genial! ¿Lo usas fuera de la Academia?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:586
msgid ""
"Actually, I've never even touched it; Master Menon says it has a huge amount "
"of power within itself, and that I could get hurt if I wielded it right now."
msgstr ""
"En realidad, ni siquiera lo he tocado nunca; el Maestro Menon dice que "
"contiene una enorme cantidad de poder y que podría hacerme daño si lo usara "
"ahora."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:590
msgid "Um, that's a shame... Well, see you at Tothes' class!"
msgstr "Um, qué lástima... Bueno, ¡nos vemos en la clase de Tothes!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:607
msgid ""
"Hey, Akhen, is it true that you have already met Master Menon in person?"
msgstr ""
"Oye, Akhen, ¿es verdad que ya has conocido al Maestro Menon en persona?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:611
msgid "Of course, I mean, he was the one who raised me."
msgstr "Por supuesto, quiero decir, él fue quien me crió."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:615
msgid ""
"So, tell me... How does he look like? I mean, he surely doesn't actually "
"look like he does in the communication crystals, right?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, dime... ¿Cómo es su apariencia? Quiero decir, seguramente no se ve "
"realmente como en los cristales de comunicación, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:619
msgid ""
"(angry) If he doesn't reveal his true appearance, it's because he doesn't "
"want to! Now, mind your own business, please."
msgstr ""
"(enojado) ¡Si no revela su verdadera apariencia es porque no quiere! Ahora, "
"ocúpate de tus asuntos, por favor."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:623
msgid "Pff, useless as always..."
msgstr "Pff, inútil como siempre..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:638
msgid ""
"Seems like these chambers aren't currently working... Well, it's not like "
"you really had time to spare playing in them anyway."
msgstr ""
"Parece que estas cámaras no están funcionando en este momento... Bueno, de "
"todos modos no es que tuvieras mucho tiempo libre para jugar en ellas."

#. [unit], id=Training Orb, type=Training Orb
#. [unit_type], id=Training Orb, race=mechanical
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:653
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Training_Orb.cfg:5
msgid "Training Orb"
msgstr "Orbe de Entrenamiento"

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:673
msgid "Whoa, what a cool place! It's like entering another world..."
msgstr "¡Vaya, qué lugar tan genial! Es como entrar en otro mundo..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:677
msgid ""
"But this abyss is just an illusion spell; actually we're in a simple room. "
"Now, Akhen, get yourself ready, the Orb is going to start sending wisps at "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Pero este abismo es solo un hechizo de ilusión; en realidad estamos en una "
"habitación simple. Ahora, Akhen, prepárate, el Orbe va a empezar a enviarte "
"fuegos fatuos."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:695
msgid ""
"(whisper) Why is he summoning wisps? Shouldn't he be giving his best at the "
"training?"
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) ¿Por qué está invocando fuegos fatuos? ¿No debería estar dando "
"lo mejor de sí en el entrenamiento?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:699
msgid ""
"(awkward) See, Charmian, the thing is, he isn't good at the Aquamarine "
"Arts..."
msgstr ""
"(incómoda) Verás, Charmian, el asunto es que no es bueno en las Artes "
"Aguamarinas..."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:703
msgid ""
"Really? That's weird, I thought he had some special talent for elemental "
"magic... What's his forte, then?"
msgstr ""
"¿En serio? Qué raro, pensaba que tenía algún talento especial para la magia "
"elemental... ¿Entonces cuál es su fuerte?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:707
msgid "<i>(embarrassed silence)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(silencio avergonzado)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:711
msgid "Wait... Are you saying that he isn't good at anything?"
msgstr "Espera... ¿Estás diciendo que no es bueno en nada?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:715
msgid ""
"Well, I like to think that he has some special skill that will blossom in "
"the right time; in fact, he has a very cool Cross of Life which he once "
"imbued with powerful arcane energy; he's never used it in a fight, but I'm "
"sure that it's a bane to any magical creature!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, me gusta pensar que tiene alguna habilidad especial que florecerá en "
"el momento adecuado; de hecho, tiene una Cruz de la Vida muy genial que una "
"vez imbuyó con poderosa energía arcana; nunca la ha usado en una pelea, "
"¡pero estoy segura de que es una perdición para cualquier criatura mágica!"

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:719
msgid ""
"But... But he's a Wadjet! (turning to Akhen) Say, Mr. Wadjet, can't you "
"really summon a single high-level elemental?"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero... pero es un Wadjet! (volviéndose hacia Akhen) Dime, señor Wadjet, "
"¿realmente no puedes invocar ni un solo elemental de alto nivel?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:723
msgid ""
"Please, just call me Akhen... And, well, I do have some difficulty summoning "
"higher-level elementals, but I do have an Ethereal Orb, see..."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, solo llámame Akhen... Y, bueno, sí tengo cierta dificultad para "
"invocar elementales de nivel superior, pero tengo un Orbe Etéreo, mira..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:738
msgid ""
"Right, so now let's focus on the training. See, some crystals are about to "
"be created!"
msgstr ""
"Bien, entonces ahora centrémonos en el entrenamiento. ¡Mira, están a punto "
"de crearse algunos cristales!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:750
msgid "Good, you managed to develop some of your wisps!"
msgstr "Bien, ¡lograste desarrollar algunos de tus fuegos fatuos!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:755
msgid "Do you think I'm ready for the duel with only these?"
msgstr "¿Crees que estoy listo para el duelo solo con estos?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:759
msgid ""
"Well, in the time you have available, I don't think you can train much "
"more... But you could practice some attack spells with the training orbs. "
"Mind the time, though, you don't want to be late for the duel... Is there "
"anything wrong, Charmian?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, en el tiempo que tienes disponible, no creo que puedas entrenar mucho "
"más... Pero podrías practicar algunos hechizos de ataque con los orbes de "
"entrenamiento. Cuida el tiempo, no querrás llegar tarde al duelo... ¿Pasa "
"algo, Charmian?"

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:763
msgid "(looking disillusioned) No, not really..."
msgstr "(con aspecto desilusionado) No, la verdad que no..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:812
msgid ""
"At long last you have come! I was beginning to think that you had given up "
"on the duel!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin has venido! Ya empezaba a pensar que te habías rendido en el duelo!"

#. [message], speaker=Student
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:816
msgid ""
"Oh, look, folks, there is going to be a duel now! Who are you going to maul "
"today, Mahyus?"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, mirad, gente, va a haber un duelo ahora! ¿A quién vas a destrozar hoy, "
"Mahyus?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:820
msgid "I would never flee from a challenge, Mahyus! I would rather-"
msgstr "¡Nunca huiría de un desafío, Mahyus! Preferiría-"

#. [message], speaker=Student
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:824
msgid ""
"(laughing) Are you fighting Akhen?! Oh my, I foresee a long night of work "
"for the healers..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¡¿Vas a luchar contra Akhen?! Dios mío, preveo una larga noche de "
"trabajo para los sanadores..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:828
msgid "(looks upset)"
msgstr "(parece molesto)"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:832
msgid ""
"Oh, shut up, all of you! And you, Mahyus, I want to know why you've even "
"challenged him for a duel?"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, callaos todos! Y tú, Mahyus, quiero saber por qué lo has desafiado a un "
"duelo."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:836
msgid ""
"That's not of your concern, girl from Meroites; and don't you start "
"lecturing me, I'm not doing anything against the rules."
msgstr ""
"Eso no es asunto tuyo, chica de Meroites; y no empieces a sermonearme, no "
"estoy haciendo nada contra las reglas."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:840
msgid ""
"Indeed you're not; after all, there's no rule against being a stupid bully..."
msgstr ""
"Claro que no; después de todo, no hay ninguna regla contra ser un matón "
"estúpido..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:844
msgid ""
"Merwe, it's all right, we're just going to duel, like everyone else does."
msgstr "Merwe, está bien, solo vamos a duelar, como hace todo el mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:848
msgid ""
"...All right, then... I'll be right here, rooting for you; now, keep your "
"mind cool, mind your training, don't take your eyes off him and his "
"creatures, and good luck..."
msgstr ""
"...Está bien, entonces... Estaré aquí mismo, animándote; ahora, mantén la "
"mente fría, recuerda tu entrenamiento, no le quites los ojos de encima a él "
"ni a sus criaturas, y buena suerte..."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:852
msgid "Go, Akhen! Make your ancestors proud!"
msgstr "¡Vamos, Akhen! ¡Haz que tus ancestros se sientan orgullosos!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:871
msgid ""
"So these are the rules of this duel: each of us may summon up to ten "
"creatures at the same time to help us; we may only summon creatures of a "
"particular kind, in other words, if you summon an elemental, you can't "
"summon an undead - not that you are going to summon anything other than "
"wisps, of course..."
msgstr ""
"Estas son las reglas de este duelo: cada uno de nosotros puede invocar hasta "
"diez criaturas al mismo tiempo para que nos ayuden; solo podemos invocar "
"criaturas de un tipo particular, es decir, si invocas un elemental, no "
"puedes invocar un no-muerto... no es que vayas a invocar otra cosa que no "
"sean fuegos fatuos, claro..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:875
msgid "Crowd: *<i>giggles</i>*"
msgstr "Multitud: *<i>risitas</i>*"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:879
msgid "I have nothing against these rules..."
msgstr "No tengo nada en contra de estas reglas..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:883
msgid "Good; so, let us begin!"
msgstr "Bien; ¡entonces, empecemos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:889
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1009
msgid "Defeat Mahyus Meritane"
msgstr "Derrota a Mahyus Meritane"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:902
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1026
msgid ""
"Akhen may recruit in the hexes adjacent to the one where he starts the duel, "
"except for the Great Tree hex."
msgstr ""
"Akhen puede reclutar en los hexágonos adyacentes a aquel donde inicia el "
"duelo, excepto en el hexágono del Gran Árbol."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:915
msgid ""
"I know that Master Menon and the Chamber of Sages have allowed the use of "
"Necromancy, to compensate our low numbers in the wars against our enemies, "
"but I still find it horrible to use a corpse like this, even if it's an orc, "
"minotaur or vampire one."
msgstr ""
"Sé que el Maestro Menon y la Cámara de los Sabios han permitido el uso de la "
"Nigromancia para compensar nuestro bajo número en las guerras contra "
"nuestros enemigos, pero sigo encontrando horrible usar un cadáver como este, "
"aunque sea de un orco, minotauro o vampiro."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:919
msgid "I agree..."
msgstr "Estoy de acuerdo..."

#. [message], speaker=Student
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:962
msgid ""
"Whoa, look! Seems like our little Akhen has skills after all! What are you "
"going to do, Mahyus? He's about to kick your ass!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vaya, mirad! ¡Parece que nuestro pequeño Akhen sí tiene habilidades después "
"de todo! ¿Qué vas a hacer, Mahyus? ¡Está a punto de darte una paliza!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:966
msgid ""
"(furious) Like I'd let that happen... Rise, Furnace Beast, fiery embodiment "
"of nature's wrath, and consume your foes in your undying fire!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) Como si fuera a permitir que eso ocurra... ¡Levántate, Bestia del "
"Horno, encarnación ardiente de la ira de la naturaleza, y consume a tus "
"enemigos en tu fuego eterno!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:984
msgid ""
"Wait a minute, you can't summon an elemental if you've already summoned an "
"undead, it's against the-"
msgstr ""
"Espera un momento, no puedes invocar un elemental si ya has invocado un no-"
"muerto, va en contra de las-"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:988
msgid ""
"To hell with the rules! Duels are supposed to prepare us for battle, and "
"there are no rules on a battlefield, little Wadjet!"
msgstr ""
"¡Al diablo con las reglas! Los duelos se supone que nos preparan para la "
"batalla, ¡y en un campo de batalla no hay reglas, pequeño Wadjet"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:992
msgid ""
"You cheating bastard, how can you summon such a dangerous monster inside the "
"Academy?! Wait for me, Akhen, let me kick his treacherous ass too!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldito tramposo, cómo puedes invocar un monstruo tan peligroso dentro de "
"la Academia! ¡Espérame, Akhen, déjame patearle el trasero traicionero "
"también a él"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:999
msgid "(troubled) Stay out of this, girl, or you will get seriously hurt!"
msgstr ""
"(preocupado) Quédate fuera de esto, chica, ¡o te vas a lastimar de verdad"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1003
msgid ""
"I'm not as clumsy as you may deem me, right? And besides, having your enemy "
"receive unexpected reinforcements is common on a battlefield too, have you "
"forgotten?"
msgstr ""
"No soy tan torpe como crees, ¿verdad? Además, que tu enemigo reciba "
"refuerzos inesperados es algo común en un campo de batalla también, ¿lo "
"olvidaste"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1017
msgid "Defeat of Merwe"
msgstr "Derrota de Merwe"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1057
msgid "Now you shall get what you deserve, 'Meritane boy'..."
msgstr "Ahora vas a recibir lo que mereces, «chico Meritane»..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1061
msgid "No, please wait...!"
msgstr "¡No, por favor espera..."

#. [message], speaker=Student
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1078
msgid "By the Gods of Light, it's a Revenant! How did you raise him?"
msgstr "¡Por los Dioses de la Luz, es un Revenant! ¿Cómo lo levantaste"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1082
msgid ""
"(frightened) How <i>could</i> you raise him?! Ah, I bet it was just another "
"of your tricks..."
msgstr ""
"(asustada) ¡¿Cómo <i>pudiste</i> levantarlo?! Ah, apuesto a que fue solo "
"otro de tus trucos.."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1086
msgid ""
"It was never supposed to be raised here! I... I think I lost control of it "
"with the imminence of your attack..."
msgstr ""
"¡Nunca debió ser levantado aquí! Yo... creo que perdí el control de él con "
"la inminencia de tu ataque.."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1090
msgid "Oh, don't you dare blame us for your own mistakes, you..."
msgstr "Oh, no te atrevas a culparnos por tus propios errores, tú.."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1094
msgid "Wait, guys, I think I can take it down with my ankh..."
msgstr "Esperen, chicos, creo que puedo derribarlo con mi ankh..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1104
msgid "AKHEN, WATCH OUT!!!"
msgstr "¡AKHEN, CUIDADO!!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1108
msgid "Ouch! Damn it, I shouldn't have gotten so close..."
msgstr "¡Ay! Maldición, no debí acercarme tanto..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1129
msgid "H-headmistress...?"
msgstr "¿S-señora directora..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1134
msgid ""
"Your power has increased considerably in the last months, Mahyus Meritane, "
"but such a high-level creature is still far above you to control; because "
"you failed to notice that, your colleagues nearly got seriously hurt."
msgstr ""
"Tu poder ha aumentado considerablemente en los últimos meses, Mahyus "
"Meritane, pero una criatura de tan alto nivel todavía está muy por encima de "
"tu capacidad para controlarla; porque no te diste cuenta de eso, tus "
"compañeros casi resultan gravemente heridos."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1138
msgid ""
"Not only that, headmistress, but he also cheated at this duel! I hope that "
"he will be severely..."
msgstr ""
"No solo eso, señora directora, ¡además hizo trampa en este duelo! Espero que "
"sea severamente..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1142
msgid ""
"I know very well what he deserves, Merwe. Now, I want you, Akhen and Mahyus "
"to follow me to the Elder Headmaster's office..."
msgstr ""
"Sé muy bien lo que merece, Merwe. Ahora, quiero que tú, Akhen y Mahyus me "
"sigan a la oficina del Director Mayor..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1146
msgid "Wait, Headmistress, Akhen and I have done nothing wrong, we just..."
msgstr "Espere, señora directora, Akhen y yo no hemos hecho nada malo, solo..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1150
msgid ""
"(impatient) He just wishes to see you both, for the Light's sake, calm down!"
msgstr ""
"(impaciente) Solo desea verlos a los dos, ¡por el amor de la Luz, cálmate"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1154
msgid ""
"Er, apologies, Headmistress, I'm still too angry at Mahyus and his "
"treachery... Sorry, Charmian, I'll show you the Academy later."
msgstr ""
"Eh, disculpas, señora directora, todavía estoy muy enojada con Mahyus y su "
"traición... Lo siento, Charmian, te mostraré la Academia más tarde."

#. [message], speaker=Charmian
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1158
msgid "(excited) Don't worry, I've seen a lot of it already for a day!"
msgstr "(emocionada) ¡No te preocupes, ya he visto bastante por un día"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1203
msgid ""
"The Elder Headmaster is coming, wait here - and behave yourselves! I have "
"more business to attend now."
msgstr ""
"El Director Mayor viene en camino, esperen aquí, ¡y compórtense! Tengo más "
"asuntos que atender ahora"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1219
msgid ""
"(whispers) See, Merwe... I have been thinking about the duel... About the "
"reason he challenged me so out of a sudden, and about the fact that his "
"creatures didn't hit you a single time... Don't you think that he, you know, "
"likes you?"
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Mira, Merwe... He estado pensando en el duelo... Sobre la razón "
"por la que me desafió tan de repente, y sobre el hecho de que sus criaturas "
"no te golpearon ni una sola vez... ¿No crees que él, ya sabes, te gusta"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1223
msgid ""
"(whispers) What?! Come on, the precious heir of the Meritanes would never "
"fall for a 'girl from Meroites'... Oh, look, the communication crystal is "
"activating!"
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) ¡¿Qué?! Vamos, el precioso heredero de los Meritane nunca se "
"fijaría en una «chica de Meroites»... ¡Oh, mira, el cristal de comunicación "
"se está activando"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1235
msgid ""
"Good evening, students. I'm already aware of the events of this night..."
msgstr ""
"Buenas noches, estudiantes. Ya estoy al tanto de los eventos de esta noche..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1239
msgid "Elder Headmaster, I'd like to say that I'm truly sorry that..."
msgstr "Director Mayor, me gustaría decir que realmente lamento que..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1243
msgid "...that was a very exciting duel indeed..."
msgstr "...fue un duelo realmente muy emocionante..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1247
msgid "(surprised) Oh, really...?"
msgstr "(sorprendido) ¿Oh, en serio..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1251
msgid ""
"...But to be honest, your conduct was most disapproving, Mahyus. Not only "
"did you violate your own rules, but you also jeopardized your own colleagues "
"with that Revenant."
msgstr ""
"...Pero para ser honesto, tu conducta fue muy reprobable, Mahyus. No solo "
"violaste tus propias reglas, sino que también pusiste en peligro a tus "
"compañeros con ese Revenant."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1255
msgid ""
"Well, I am truly sorry for what happened there, and I will humbly accept any "
"punishment you have for me - but please, I beg you, allow me to join Lord "
"Suryen's army in the attack on the Windswept Cliffs; I have been preparing "
"for that since last winter..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, realmente lamento lo que pasó allí, y aceptaré humildemente cualquier "
"castigo que tengas para mí, pero por favor, te ruego que me permitas unirme "
"al ejército del señor Suryen en el ataque a los Acantilados Barridos por el "
"Viento; he estado preparándome para eso desde el invierno pasado..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1259
msgid ""
"I'm glad to hear that you are so eager to help Maat'Kare, and for this "
"reason I shall change the punishment I had in mind for you - which brings us "
"to the reason I wished to talk with Akhen and Merwe. I have commended you to "
"a mission on behalf of Lord Smenkhare Sekhet."
msgstr ""
"Me alegra oír que estás tan ansioso por ayudar a Maat'Kare, y por esa razón "
"cambiaré el castigo que tenía pensado para ti, lo que nos lleva a la razón "
"por la que quería hablar con Akhen y Merwe. Los he encomendado a una misión "
"en nombre del señor Smenkhare Sekhet."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1263
msgid "Smenkhare, the Bane of the Vampires?!"
msgstr "¡¿Smenkhare, el Azote de los Vampiros?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1267
msgid ""
"But that's great! We're extremely honoured to be part of this mission, "
"Master Menon, and we promise you that we shall not disappoint. But, if I may "
"ask, what is this mission about?"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero eso es genial! Estamos extremadamente honrados de formar parte de esta "
"misión, Maestro Menon, y te prometemos que no te defraudaremos. Pero, si "
"puedo preguntar, ¿de qué se trata esta misión"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1271
msgid ""
"Around three weeks ago, Maat'Kare lost contact with the Migdol of Desret, "
"our southernmost outpost, in the middle of the Silent Desert; razorbird "
"scouts have detected no movement inside it, and so Smenkhare is preparing an "
"expedition to go there and investigate what may have happened."
msgstr ""
"Hace unas tres semanas, Maat'Kare perdió contacto con el Migdol de Desret, "
"nuestro puesto avanzado más al sur, en medio del Desierto Silencioso; los "
"exploradores con pájaros navaja no detectaron movimiento dentro de él, por "
"lo que Smenkhare está preparando una expedición para ir allí e investigar "
"qué pudo haber pasado."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1275
msgid "But will we really be of any aid to Lord Smenkhare's soldiers?"
msgstr ""
"¿Pero realmente seremos de alguna ayuda para los soldados del señor "
"Smenkhare?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1279
msgid ""
"Your main task will be to detect any possible trace of magic in whatever was "
"left of Desret, because there is a possibility - and this is highly "
"confidential information - that the Lich-Lords of Skiron may have something "
"to do with that fortress' fate."
msgstr ""
"Su tarea principal será detectar cualquier posible rastro de magia en lo que "
"quede de Desret, porque existe la posibilidad —y esta es información "
"altamente confidencial— de que los Señores Liche de Skiron tengan algo que "
"ver con el destino de esa fortaleza."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1283
msgid ""
"I see; the Lich-Lords are said to always use dark magi in their armies, so "
"if they have indeed attacked Desret, we will certainly find traces of magic "
"energy there."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo; se dice que los Señores Liche siempre usan magos oscuros en sus "
"ejércitos, así que si realmente atacaron Desret, seguramente encontraremos "
"rastros de energía mágica allí."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1287
msgid ""
"Precisely. Besides, even if you find no such trace there, you will still be "
"valuable assets to Smenkhare's men."
msgstr ""
"Exactamente. Además, incluso si no encuentran tal rastro allí, seguirán "
"siendo activos valiosos para los hombres de Smenkhare."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1291
msgid "But, Elder Headmaster, I don't understand… Oh, wait, will you..."
msgstr "Pero, Director Mayor, no entiendo… Oh, espera, ¿usted..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1295
msgid ""
"As you have already smartly guessed, young Mahyus, I'm sending you alongside "
"these two in this mission. Yours will also be an invaluable aid, since you "
"will easily notice any vestige of dark magic that may be there. Besides, you "
"will learn to peacefully coexist and work as a team with your colleagues "
"and, at the same time, serve our beloved Maat'Kare."
msgstr ""
"Como ya has adivinado inteligentemente, joven Mahyus, te estoy enviando "
"junto a estos dos en esta misión. Tu ayuda también será invaluable, ya que "
"notarás fácilmente cualquier vestigio de magia oscura que pueda haber allí. "
"Además, aprenderás a coexistir pacíficamente y trabajar en equipo con tus "
"compañeros y, al mismo tiempo, servir a nuestra querida Maat'Kare."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1299
msgid ""
"(annoyed) A-as you wish, Elder Headmaster... I promise I will do my best to "
"help Akhen in whatever dire situation he gets himself in..."
msgstr ""
"(molesto) C-como usted diga, Director Mayor... Prometo que haré lo mejor "
"posible para ayudar a Akhen en cualquier situación difícil en la que se "
"meta..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1303
msgid ""
"(smiling) As I'm certain that he will help you if you find yourself in a "
"similar situation - just as he delayed that Revenant for you tonight..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Como estoy seguro de que él te ayudará si te encuentras en una "
"situación similar, tal como retrasó ese Revenant por ti esta noche..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1307
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:732
msgid "(giggles)"
msgstr "(ríe)"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1311
msgid ""
"Now, my students, you may go. You shall soon receive more instructions about "
"the mission, but I can say in advance that Smenkhare's retinue's departure "
"is schedule for the day after tomorrow."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, mis estudiantes, pueden irse. Pronto recibirán más instrucciones "
"sobre la misión, pero puedo adelantarles que la partida del séquito de "
"Smenkhare está programada para pasado mañana."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1315
msgid "Good night, Master Menon."
msgstr "Buenas noches, Maestro Menon."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1330
msgid "Master..."
msgstr "Maestro..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1334
msgid ""
"Say no more, Akhen. I'm certain that you will perform exceedingly well in "
"this mission, if you just stop undermining yourself."
msgstr ""
"No digas más, Akhen. Estoy seguro de que te desempeñarás extremadamente bien "
"en esta misión, si simplemente dejas de menospreciarte."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1338
msgid ""
"But if I fail even at the Academy, which is such a peaceful and safe "
"environment..."
msgstr ""
"Pero si fallo incluso en la Academia, que es un ambiente tan pacífico y "
"seguro..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1342
msgid ""
"Doing bad in a classroom is no guarantee that you will do likewise in a "
"practical situation, just as excelling as a student does not mean that one "
"will have a similar performance in the real world. Trust yourself and your "
"power, learn from the world around you and count on your friends, and show "
"everyone your true potential. I sense a great future ahead of you, Akhen; do "
"not let anyone make you believe differently."
msgstr ""
"Hacerlo mal en un aula no es garantía de que lo hagas igual en una situación "
"práctica, así como destacar como estudiante no significa que uno tendrá un "
"desempeño similar en el mundo real. Confía en ti mismo y en tu poder, "
"aprende del mundo que te rodea, cuenta con tus amigos y muestra a todos tu "
"verdadero potencial. Percibo un gran futuro por delante para ti, Akhen; no "
"permitas que nadie te haga creer lo contrario."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1346
msgid "Thank you, Master..."
msgstr "Gracias, Maestro..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1371
msgid ""
"Is this the best your creatures can do, Mahyus? They haven't even scratched "
"me, and I'm on vulnerable terrain!"
msgstr ""
"¿Esto es lo mejor que pueden hacer tus criaturas, Mahyus? Ni siquiera me han "
"rozado, ¡y estoy en terreno vulnerable"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1375
msgid "(still looking troubled) Tsc!"
msgstr "(todavía con aspecto preocupado) ¡Tsc"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/01_Heir_Of_The_Elements.cfg:1386
msgid "No! I shouldn't have lost... I think I really am no use, after all..."
msgstr ""
"¡No! No debí perder... Creo que realmente no sirvo para nada, después de "
"todo..."

#. [scenario], id=02_Children_Of_Darkness
