#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:227
msgid ""
"Um, are you sure that this is the place where we're supposed to meet Lord "
"Smenkhare's retinue? I see no soldier around, let alone the lord himself..."
msgstr ""
"Um, ¿estás segura de que este es el lugar donde se supone que debemos "
"encontrar al séquito del señor Smenkhare? No veo ningún soldado por aquí, "
"mucho menos al señor mismo..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:231
msgid ""
"But the scroll told us to be here, in front of the Barracks, at this exact "
"time... Look, there's a girl coming from inside, let's ask her whether Lord "
"Smenkhare is there..."
msgstr ""
"Pero el pergamino nos dijo que estuviéramos aquí, frente a los Cuarteles, a "
"esta hora exacta... Mira, hay una chica saliendo de adentro, preguntémosle "
"si el señor Smenkhare está allí..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:238
msgid ""
"I assume you are Akhen Wadjet, Mahyus Meritane and Merwe, from the Academy?"
msgstr ""
"Supongo que ustedes son Akhen Wadjet, Mahyus Meritane y Merwe, de la "
"Academia, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:242
msgid "Exactly. Has Lord Smenkhare sent you?"
msgstr "Exacto. ¿El señor Smenkhare te envió?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:246
msgid ""
"Not exactly. My name is Atenak Aracyne, niece to Admiral Lord Tewarin "
"Aracyne; unexpected and highly important affairs have demanded General "
"Smenkhare’s closer attention; to relieve him of too many duties, my uncle "
"has offered to undertake the mission to Desret. However, since he has "
"important business at Maat'Kare as well, he's named me to lead his men."
msgstr ""
"No exactamente. Mi nombre es Atenak Aracyne, sobrina del Almirante Señor "
"Tewarin Aracyne; asuntos inesperados y de gran importancia han requerido la "
"atención más cercana del General Smenkhare; para aliviarlo de tantas "
"obligaciones, mi tío se ha ofrecido a llevar a cabo la misión a Desret. Sin "
"embargo, como también tiene asuntos importantes en Maat'Kare, me ha nombrado "
"a mí para liderar a sus hombres."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:250
msgid "So... you're going to lead us?"
msgstr "Entonces... ¿vas a liderarnos tú?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:254
msgid "Yes. Do you have any issue with that?"
msgstr "Sí. ¿Tienes algún problema con eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:258
msgid ""
"No, I mean... You look so young, and yet you lead official expeditions..."
msgstr ""
"No, quiero decir... Te ves tan joven, y sin embargo lideras expediciones "
"oficiales..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:262
msgid "(giggles) Tactless idiot..."
msgstr "(riendo por lo bajo) Idiota sin tacto..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:266
msgid ""
"(stung) I may have seen only sixteen springs, Mr. Wadjet, but I have a "
"somewhat extensive experience: I've already fought vampires, minotaurs and "
"orcs alongside my uncle, I have survived a shipwreck in the open sea, I have "
"even been to Argea already. As for you, Mr. Wadjet... According to Professor "
"Sadjet, you barely even leave the island..."
msgstr ""
"(ofendida) Puede que solo haya visto dieciséis primaveras, señor Wadjet, "
"pero tengo una experiencia bastante extensa: ya he luchado contra vampiros, "
"minotauros y orcos junto a mi tío, he sobrevivido a un naufragio en mar "
"abierto, incluso ya he estado en Argea. En cuanto a ti, señor Wadjet... "
"Según el profesor Sadjet, apenas sales de la isla..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:270
msgid "Er, well, I don't need to leave it very often, so..."
msgstr "Eh, bueno, no necesito salir muy a menudo, así que..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:274
msgid ""
"(smiling sardonically) Of course you don't. Now, please follow me into the "
"Barracks; the soldiers are just finishing preparations for the travel, and "
"we shall depart as soon as we can."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo sarcásticamente) Por supuesto que no. Ahora, por favor síganme al "
"interior de los Cuarteles; los soldados están terminando los preparativos "
"para el viaje, y partiremos tan pronto como podamos."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:281
msgid ""
"(whispers) By the Gods, what an insufferable girl! How can she treat "
"companions she's just met like this?"
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) ¡Por los Dioses, qué chica tan insufrible! ¿Cómo puede tratar "
"así a compañeros que acaba de conocer?"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:285
msgid ""
"So you say, but she has no choice but to be harsh and firm, otherwise no one "
"would take her seriously."
msgstr ""
"Tú lo dices, pero no tiene más remedio que ser dura y firme, de lo contrario "
"nadie la tomaría en serio."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:289
msgid "Bah, you're only defending her because she has picked on Akhen..."
msgstr "Bah, solo la defiendes porque se metió con Akhen..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:293
msgid "Yes, that too."
msgstr "Sí, eso también."

#. [unit], id=Svartol, type=Pack Leader
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:338
msgid "Svartol"
msgstr "Svartol"

#. [unit], id=Rhadanthus, type=Minotaur Rouser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:347
msgid "Rhadanthus"
msgstr "Rhadanthus"

#. [unit], id=Sepate, type=Imeyer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:356
msgid "Sepate"
msgstr "Sepate"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:414
msgid ""
"We've managed to leave the Land's End Peninsula and cross most of Tarkyn's "
"Meadows; for a day's march, that is excellent! Now, soldiers, let us rest, "
"for we are resuming our march in the next sunrise."
msgstr ""
"Hemos logrado salir de la Península del Fin de la Tierra y cruzar la mayor "
"parte de los Prados de Tarkyn; ¡para una jornada de marcha, eso es "
"excelente! Ahora, soldados, descansemos, porque reanudaremos la marcha al "
"amanecer."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:418
msgid ""
"I've been around here before, there is a village called Khaset nearby; we "
"could go there and see if the villagers can supply us with water and food."
msgstr ""
"He estado por aquí antes, hay una aldea llamada Khaset cerca; podríamos ir "
"allí y ver si los aldeanos pueden suministrarnos agua y comida."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:422
msgid ""
"Good idea; thus our own provisions will last longer, and we don't know how "
"long the crossing of the Silent Desert will..."
msgstr ""
"Buena idea; así nuestras propias provisiones durarán más, y no sabemos "
"cuánto durará el cruce del Desierto Silencioso..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:434
msgid "(frightened) Eeek!!!"
msgstr "(asustada) ¡Eeeek!!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:438
msgid ""
"Uh-oh, there are wolves in this region; we better go to that village in "
"groups..."
msgstr ""
"Oh-oh, hay lobos en esta región; mejor vayamos a esa aldea en grupos..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:442
msgid ""
"This howl, o inexperienced youth, doesn't belong to a wolf, but to something "
"far worse: a being with man-like body and wit, and lupine features and "
"ferocity; a creature born from twisted Windsong experiments in the Old Home, "
"unleashed upon Netjer-Ta before the arrival of our forefathers..."
msgstr ""
"Este aullido, oh juventud inexperta, no pertenece a un lobo, sino a algo "
"mucho peor: un ser con cuerpo y inteligencia parecidos a los humanos, y "
"rasgos y ferocidad lupinos; una criatura nacida de experimentos retorcidos "
"de las Hijas del Viento en el Viejo Hogar, desatada sobre Netjer-Ta antes de "
"la llegada de nuestros antepasados..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:446
msgid "(tired) In other words, a warg."
msgstr "(cansada) En otras palabras, un huargo."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:450
msgid "Then we need not worry, for the wargs are friendly to us humans."
msgstr ""
"Entonces no tenemos que preocuparnos, porque los huargos son amistosos con "
"los humanos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:454
msgid ""
"Not all of them are: a newly risen faction, the Warglanders, is hostile. "
"They claim that Maat'Kare's lands were not given to us, but forcefully taken "
"from them by our ancestors. It's likely that a Warglander pack leader is "
"currently attacking the village, which makes our little visit even more "
"urgent. Ah, and Akhen, don't go around boasting that you're Myra's heir; "
"rumours say that these Warglanders blame her more than anyone else for this "
"'treachery'."
msgstr ""
"No todos lo son: una facción recién surgida, los Warglanders, es hostil. "
"Afirman que las tierras de Maat'Kare no nos fueron dadas, sino tomadas por "
"la fuerza por nuestros ancestros. Es probable que un líder de manada "
"warglander esté atacando la aldea en este momento, lo que hace nuestra "
"pequeña visita aún más urgente. Ah, y Akhen, no vayas presumiendo por ahí "
"que eres el heredero de Myra; los rumores dicen que estos warglanders la "
"culpan a ella más que a nadie por esta «traición»."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:476
msgid ""
"Don't you even think of saying out loud that Akhen descends of Myra, Mahyus!"
msgstr "¡Ni se te ocurra decir en voz alta que Akhen desciende de Myra, Mahyus"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:480
msgid "(smirking) But I'd <i>never</i> do such thing..."
msgstr "(sonriendo burlonamente) Pero yo <i>nunca</i> haría tal cosa..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:484
msgid ""
"By the way, you could show some usefulness and invoke some elementals, or "
"even your undead pets, to avoid the loss of human lives."
msgstr ""
"Por cierto, podrías mostrar algo de utilidad e invocar algunos elementales, "
"o incluso tus mascotas no-muertas, para evitar la pérdida de vidas humanas."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:488
msgid ""
"I'm not that versed in the Aquamarine Arts yet, I'm man enough to admit. As "
"for my undead, I was going to summon them, but..."
msgstr ""
"Aún no estoy tan versado en las Artes Aguamarinas, soy lo suficientemente "
"hombre para admitirlo. En cuanto a mis no-muertos, iba a invocarlos, pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:492
msgid "...I don't want those aberrations marching under the Aracynes' banner."
msgstr ""
"...no quiero que esas aberraciones marchen bajo el estandarte de los Aracyne."

#. [message], speaker=Sepate
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:514
msgid ""
"Oh, blessed be the Gods of Light for bringing a Maat'Karian battalion to our "
"village! Hurry, soldiers, or we will succumb to these barbarians!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, benditos sean los Dioses de la Luz por traer un batallón maat'kariano a "
"nuestra aldea! ¡Apúrense, soldados, o sucumbiremos ante estos bárbaros"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:518
msgid "Worry not, lord, for we shall help you repel them."
msgstr "No se preocupe, señor, porque los ayudaremos a repelerlos."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:522
msgid ""
"I see we have minotaurs as foes, in addition to the wargs. Is their presence "
"common in this region?"
msgstr ""
"Veo que tenemos minotauros como enemigos, además de los huargos. ¿Su "
"presencia es común en esta región?"

#. [message], speaker=Sepate
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:526
msgid ""
"Sadly, it isn't. Lately, we’ve been plagued by foes that we haven't seen in "
"many years, even though we're a frontier village. For instance, our "
"cattle... (shudders)"
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, no. Últimamente hemos sido plagados por enemigos que no "
"veíamos desde hace muchos años, aunque somos una aldea fronteriza. Por "
"ejemplo, nuestro ganado... (estremeciéndose)"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:530
msgid "What is wrong with your cattle?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con su ganado?"

#. [message], speaker=Sepate
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:534
msgid ""
"They have been appearing dead in the outskirts of our fields, completely "
"bloodless, their throats ripped open; we have no doubt that it's a vampire's "
"work, but we haven't located him yet, even with the hard effort of our best "
"hunters!"
msgstr ""
"Han aparecido muertos en las afueras de nuestros campos, completamente "
"desangrados, con la garganta desgarrada; no tenemos duda de que es obra de "
"un vampiro, ¡pero todavía no lo hemos localizado, a pesar del gran esfuerzo "
"de nuestros mejores cazadores"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:538
msgid ""
"I see... Well, when we're done with the enemies at hand, we may plan "
"something to catch this vampire; I'm certain that the scent of this "
"bloodshed is watering his mouth as we speak, so he may expose himself to get "
"a taste of blood this very night."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Bueno, cuando terminemos con los enemigos que tenemos delante, "
"podemos planear algo para atrapar a este vampiro; estoy segura de que el "
"olor de esta matanza le está haciendo agua la boca mientras hablamos, así "
"que puede que se exponga para probar sangre esta misma noche."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:544
msgid "Defeat the minotaurs and the wargs"
msgstr "Derrota a los minotauros y a los huargos"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:548
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:641
msgid "Capture the vampire"
msgstr "Captura al vampiro"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:593
msgid ""
"There! Our vampire has finally revealed himself - better, herself. Akhen, "
"Merwe and Mahyus, your arcane attacks are powerful against these blood-"
"suckers, so you're in charge of taking her down."
msgstr ""
"¡Allí! Nuestro vampiro finalmente se reveló, mejor dicho, ella misma. Akhen, "
"Merwe y Mahyus, sus ataques arcanos son poderosos contra estos chupasangre, "
"así que están a cargo de derribarla."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:597
msgid ""
"You send these upstarts to catch Nyx, Maat'Karian? Nyx knows your kind does "
"not love hers, but you could at least show her some respect and send true "
"fighters after her!"
msgstr ""
"¿Envías a estos novatos a atrapar a Nyx, maat'kariano? Nyx sabe que tu gente "
"no ama a la suya, ¡pero al menos podrías mostrarle algo de respeto y enviar "
"verdaderos luchadores tras ella"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:601
msgid ""
"Akhen, Merwe, leave her to me; I've seen these vampire duelists in action "
"before, their blades are capable of finding breaches even in the best-built "
"defences."
msgstr ""
"Akhen, Merwe, déjenmela a mí; ya he visto a estos duelistas vampiros en "
"acción antes, sus espadas son capaces de encontrar brechas incluso en las "
"mejores defensas."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:605
msgid ""
"Yes, you should do as your senior is telling you, babies, Nyx really doesn't "
"want to slash this beautiful, soft skin of yours..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, deberían hacer lo que les dice su mayor, bebés, Nyx realmente no quiere "
"cortar esta hermosa y suave piel de ustedes..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:609
msgid ""
"(angry) Right, I've had enough of it; I know I’m not the brightest of the "
"Academy, and that I'm not what one would expect from a descendant of Myra, "
"but..."
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Bien, ya tuve suficiente; sé que no soy el más brillante de la "
"Academia, y que no soy lo que uno esperaría de un descendiente de Myra, "
"pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Svartol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:613
msgid ""
"(snarling) Did I hear it well? Is there really a member of the Wadjet clan, "
"the heirs of the despicable Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, amongst our foes tonight? "
"Ah, I shall not let this prey escape my claws; wargs, I want all of you "
"searching for this boy!"
msgstr ""
"(gruñendo) ¿Escuché bien? ¿Realmente hay un miembro del clan Wadjet, los "
"herederos de la despreciable Myra de Hiera'Shirsha, entre nuestros enemigos "
"esta noche? Ah, no dejaré que esta presa escape de mis garras; ¡huargos, "
"quiero que todos busquen a este chico"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:617
msgid "(rolls eyes) Great, Akhen, that was really clever of you..."
msgstr ""
"(poniendo los ojos en blanco) Genial, Akhen, eso fue realmente inteligente "
"de tu parte..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:635
msgid ""
"We have finally gotten ridden of the Warglanders and the minotaurs; now, "
"let's focus on capturing that blood-sucker."
msgstr ""
"Finalmente nos hemos librado de los Warglanders y los minotauros; ahora, "
"centrémonos en capturar a esa chupasangre."

#. [message], speaker=Sepate
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:676
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:808
msgid ""
"At last, our dear Khaset is saved. We owe you our very lives, young masters."
msgstr ""
"Por fin, nuestro querido Khaset está a salvo. Os debemos literalmente la "
"vida, jóvenes señores."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:680
msgid ""
"We did nothing but our duty, which is to serve the Maat'Karian people. "
"However, we would welcome food and water, for we have a long path ahead of "
"us."
msgstr ""
"No hicimos más que cumplir con nuestro deber, que es servir al pueblo "
"maat'kariano. Sin embargo, agradeceríamos algo de comida y agua, pues "
"tenemos un largo camino por delante."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:684
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:816
msgid "Um, won't you ask them to let us rest under their roofs as well...?"
msgstr ""
"Um, ¿no les pedirás que nos dejen descansar también bajo sus techos...?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:688
msgid ""
"No. We shall sleep in our camp, with the sky as roof, as soldiers ought to "
"do. You Academy mages would do well to take this as an opportunity to get "
"used to military life."
msgstr ""
"No. Dormiremos en nuestro campamento, con el cielo como techo, como deben "
"hacer los soldados. Vosotros, magos de la Academia, haríais bien en "
"aprovechar esta oportunidad para acostumbraros a la vida militar."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:692
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:824
msgid "As you say, commander... (sigh)"
msgstr "Como digas, comandante... (suspiro)"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:711
msgid ""
"Aaarrghh!!! Let go of Nyx, you vermin! She just wants to live calmly in the "
"forest, why do you keep pestering her?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aaarrghh!!! ¡Soltad a Nyx, alimañas! Solo quiere vivir tranquila en el "
"bosque, ¿por qué seguís molestándola?"

#. [message], speaker=Sepate
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:715
msgid ""
"How can we coexist peacefully with a vampire, specially one who steals our "
"cattle? Prepare yourself, blood-sucker, for you're about to meet your "
"rightful punishment..."
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo podemos convivir en paz con una vampira, especialmente una que roba "
"nuestro ganado? Prepárate, chupasangre, porque estás a punto de recibir tu "
"justo castigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:719
msgid ""
"Wait a minute, Sepate, there’s something I don't understand: you said she "
"preyed on your cattle, but not on your fellow villagers, is that right?"
msgstr ""
"Espera un momento, Sepate, hay algo que no entiendo: dijiste que atacó "
"vuestro ganado, pero no a vuestros vecinos, ¿es correcto?"

#. [message], speaker=Sepate
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:723
msgid "Well, yes, but that's just a matter of time until she does that, right?"
msgstr "Bueno, sí, pero solo es cuestión de tiempo hasta que lo haga, ¿no?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:727
msgid ""
"I find it very unusual that this vampiress has attacked cattle, but not "
"humans; who knows, maybe she really doesn't want to harm the good people of "
"Khaset, and just wants to live calmly in her own turf."
msgstr ""
"Me parece muy extraño que esta vampira haya atacado ganado pero no humanos. "
"Quién sabe, quizá realmente no quiere hacer daño a la buena gente de Khaset "
"y solo desea vivir tranquila en su territorio."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:731
msgid ""
"You... (after a while) Hrumph! Nyx just did that because even an animal's "
"blood tastes better than that of you Maat'Karians..."
msgstr ""
"Tú... (después de un rato) ¡Hrumph! Nyx solo hizo eso porque incluso la "
"sangre de un animal sabe mejor que la de vosotros, los maat'karianos..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:735
msgid ""
"What do you have in mind, Akhen? Do you think it would be better to let her "
"free?"
msgstr "¿Qué tienes en mente, Akhen? ¿Crees que sería mejor dejarla libre?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:739
msgid ""
"Well, I just don't think it would be fair to execute someone who hasn't "
"preyed on Maat'Karian lives..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, simplemente no creo que sea justo ejecutar a alguien que no ha "
"atacado vidas maat'karianas..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:743
msgid ""
"Let's arrest her, then; that's the standard punishment for damaging one's "
"property anyway."
msgstr ""
"Entonces arrestémosla; de todos modos, ese es el castigo estándar por dañar "
"la propiedad ajena."

#. [message], speaker=Sepate
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:747
msgid ""
"We have no dungeon in our village, and even if we did I doubt that any of us "
"would accept feeding her! But, if you wish to take her into your custody, "
"noble masters, I can do nothing but to comply with your will."
msgstr ""
"No tenemos mazmorra en nuestra aldea, y aunque la tuviéramos dudo que alguno "
"de nosotros aceptara alimentarla. Pero si deseáis llevarla bajo vuestra "
"custodia, nobles señores, no puedo más que cumplir con vuestra voluntad."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:751
msgid ""
"I'm not wasting my men's provisions with such a dead weight; if you care so "
"much about being just, Akhen, you may take care of her yourself - but make "
"sure that she doesn't threaten anyone else's safety."
msgstr ""
"No voy a desperdiciar las provisiones de mis hombres con semejante peso "
"muerto. Si tanto te importa ser justo, Akhen, puedes encargarte tú mismo de "
"ella, pero asegúrate de que no amenace la seguridad de nadie más."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:755
msgid ""
"Nyx won't be a human boy's pet! She'd rather be butchered than suffer such..."
msgstr ""
"¡Nyx no será la mascota de un chico humano! Preferiría ser destrozada antes "
"que sufrir algo así..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:782
msgid ""
"Now bind her and take her to our camp, we have no time to waste arguing with "
"her."
msgstr ""
"Ahora atadla y llevadla a nuestro campamento, no tenemos tiempo que perder "
"discutiendo con ella."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:786
msgid ""
"I bet you're hoping that this vampiress will rip Akhen's neck open in his "
"sleep... But I do admire your decision, Akhen; unlike certain individuals, "
"you're a kind person."
msgstr ""
"Apuesto a que esperas que esta vampira le abra el cuello a Akhen mientras "
"duerme... Pero admiro tu decisión, Akhen; a diferencia de ciertas personas, "
"tú eres una persona amable."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:790
msgid "Who wouldn't be kind to such an attractive lady, am I right?"
msgstr "¿Quién no sería amable con una dama tan atractiva, verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:794
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:276
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:413
msgid "(blushes)"
msgstr "(se sonroja)"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:798
msgid "(sulks) Hrumph!"
msgstr "(refunfuña) ¡Hrumph!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:812
msgid ""
"We did nothing but our duty, which is to serve the Maat'Karian people. "
"However, if you wish to show us your gratitude, I ask you some food and "
"water, for we have a long path ahead of us, and our provisions are quite "
"limited."
msgstr ""
"No hicimos más que cumplir con nuestro deber, que es servir al pueblo "
"maat'kariano. Sin embargo, si deseáis mostrarnos vuestra gratitud, os pido "
"algo de comida y agua, pues tenemos un largo camino por delante y nuestras "
"provisiones son bastante limitadas."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:820
msgid ""
"No. We shall sleep in our camp, with the sky as roof, as soldiers ought to "
"do; as for you mages, enjoy this chance to get used to rough life."
msgstr ""
"No. Dormiremos en nuestro campamento, con el cielo como techo, como deben "
"hacer los soldados; en cuanto a vosotros, magos, aprovechad esta oportunidad "
"para acostumbraros a la vida dura."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/02_Children_Of_Darkness.cfg:841
msgid ""
"We had to save this town, but we shouldn't have wasted so much time here, we "
"have an urgent mission to accomplish!"
msgstr ""
"Tuvimos que salvar esta ciudad, pero no deberíamos haber perdido tanto "
"tiempo aquí. ¡Tenemos una misión urgente que cumplir!"

#. [scenario], id=03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:4
msgid "Between the Mountains and the Woods"
msgstr "Entre las Montañas y los Bosques"

