#. [side], type=Direwolf Rider
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:92
msgid "Ergarak"
msgstr "Ergarak"

#. [side], type=Direwolf Rider
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:97
msgid "Varag's Vanguard"
msgstr "Vanguardia de Varag"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:117
msgid "Aigathol Clan"
msgstr "Clan Aigathol"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:142
msgid "Faeries"
msgstr "Hadas"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:199
msgid ""
"So this is the famed valley where Alenya and Dvalin lived their forbidden "
"love? Such a beautiful and idyllic landscape, even in this weather... I know "
"this region is under the Aigathol dwarves' jurisdiction; is it possible that "
"they will let us rest here for a while, before we enter the desert...?"
msgstr ""
"¿Así que este es el famoso valle donde Alenya y Dvalin vivieron su amor "
"prohibido? Qué paisaje tan hermoso e idílico, incluso con este clima... Sé "
"que esta región está bajo la jurisdicción de los enanos de Aigathol. ¿Es "
"posible que nos dejen descansar aquí un rato antes de entrar en el "
"desierto...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Well, certainly they would, for Lord Vindalf is very hospitable and friendly "
"to us humans; the problem is that this valley is, in fact, ruled by the "
"fairies, and they may be more troublesome..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, seguramente sí, porque el señor Vindalf es muy hospitalario y amable "
"con los humanos. El problema es que este valle, en realidad, está gobernado "
"por las hadas, y ellas podrían ser más problemáticas..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:207
msgid ""
"(surprised) Fairies? But I thought they were merely a folk tale... And how "
"do you know so much about this valley?"
msgstr ""
"(sorprendida) ¿Hadas? Pero pensaba que solo eran un cuento popular... ¿Y "
"cómo sabes tanto sobre este valle?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:211
msgid ""
"My mother, Amunet Wadjet, brought me here once when I was a child. She was "
"Lord Vindalf's friend - after all, both our families descend of Dvalin and "
"Alenya. Back then, the lord's sister, Sigdral, showed me the region, and "
"even introduced me to Violindë, the leader of the fairies."
msgstr ""
"Mi madre, Amunet Wadjet, me trajo aquí una vez cuando era niño. Ella era "
"amiga del señor Vindalf; después de todo, ambas familias descienden de "
"Dvalin y Alenya. En aquel entonces, la hermana del señor, Sigdral, me mostró "
"la región e incluso me presentó a Violindë, la líder de las hadas."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:215
msgid ""
"(triumphant) See? He may not leave the Academy very often, but he still "
"knows some precious things about our continent!"
msgstr ""
"(triunfante) ¿Ves? Puede que no salga mucho de la Academia, pero aún sabe "
"cosas valiosas sobre nuestro continente."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:219
msgid ""
"Well, I'm impressed indeed; maybe you could try and talk with the Fairy "
"Queen, so that she may allow us to camp here for a night."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, estoy realmente impresionada. Tal vez podrías intentar hablar con la "
"Reina de las Hadas para que nos permita acampar aquí una noche."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:223
msgid "Um, I don't think it is gonna work, though..."
msgstr "Um, no creo que vaya a funcionar, sin embargo..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:227
msgid "Whoa! Who said that?!"
msgstr "¡Whoa! ¿Quién dijo eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:238
msgid ""
"It's me, Sigdral. Sorry, I was passing by and couldn't resist seeing you "
"more closely, but I hid myself in the mountains not to frighten you..."
msgstr ""
"Soy yo, Sigdral. Lo siento, pasaba por aquí y no pude resistirme a veros más "
"de cerca, pero me escondí en las montañas para no asustaros..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:242
msgid "Which you ultimately did!"
msgstr "¡Lo que al final conseguiste!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:246
msgid ""
"Er, sorry 'bout that... So, Akhen, I see that you have kept your promise, "
"and become big enough to carry me on your shoulders, just like I used to do "
"with you back then!"
msgstr ""
"Er, lo siento por eso... Así que, Akhen, veo que cumpliste tu promesa y te "
"has hecho lo suficientemente grande como para llevarme sobre tus hombros, "
"¡igual que yo solía hacer contigo en aquel entonces!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:250
msgid ""
"(smiling) But you remain exactly as I remembered you... Don't you female "
"dwarves age at all?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Pero sigues exactamente como te recordaba... ¿Las enanas no "
"envejecen en absoluto?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:254
msgid ""
"A female dwarf? Impressive! Oh, I mean... Oh Gods, I'm sorry, I didn't mean "
"to offend..."
msgstr ""
"¿Una enana? ¡Impresionante! Oh, quiero decir... ¡Oh dioses, lo siento, no "
"quise ofender..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:258
msgid ""
"(giggling) Nay, it's fine, I'm used to that already. As a saying of ours "
"goes, 'if males are plentiful and tough like granite, females are rare and "
"delicate like crystals'. So, Akhen, will you introduce me to your friends?"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) No, está bien, ya estoy acostumbrada. Como dice un refrán nuestro: "
"«si los machos son abundantes y duros como el granito, las hembras son raras "
"y delicadas como cristales». Entonces, Akhen, ¿me presentarás a tus amigos?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:262
msgid ""
"Of course! Well, these are Merwe and Mahyus, my friends from the Academy; "
"and this is Atenak Aracyne, Lord Tewarin's niece and leader of our retinue..."
msgstr ""
"¡Por supuesto! Bueno, estos son Merwe y Mahyus, mis amigos de la Academia; y "
"esta es Atenak Aracyne, sobrina del señor Tewarin y líder de nuestra "
"comitiva..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:274
msgid ""
"(sleepy) Blood and gore, you Maat'Karians sure are noisy... Have we arrived "
"at the damn... I mean, doomed..."
msgstr ""
"(somnolienta) Sangre y vísceras, vosotros los maat'karianos sí que sois "
"ruidosos... ¿Hemos llegado al maldito... quiero decir, condenado..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:278
msgid "NYX, YOU'RE BACK!!!"
msgstr "¡NYX, HAS VUELTO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:282
msgid ""
"Wha- (smiles) But if it isn't the rune-midget... Come here and give Nyx a "
"hug, you little troublemaker, for she's currently bound and unable to hug "
"you myself!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué...? (sonríe) Pero si es la enana de las runas... Ven aquí y dale un "
"abrazo a Nyx, pequeña alborotadora, ¡porque ahora mismo está atada y no "
"puede abrazarte ella misma!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:286
msgid "Wait a minute, do you know each other?!"
msgstr "¡Espera un momento, ¿os conocéis?!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:290
msgid ""
"Of course, we grew up together in this valley! But why is she tied up- Ah, "
"has she tried to bite any of you? Bad girl, Nyx, bad girl!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por supuesto, crecimos juntas en este valle! Pero ¿por qué está atada? Ah, "
"¿ha intentado morder a alguno de vosotros? ¡Niña mala, Nyx, niña mala!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:294
msgid ""
"Shut up, Tiny One, Nyx hasn't laid a finger on them, it's them who insist "
"that she's going to rip their throats open!"
msgstr ""
"Cállate, Enana, Nyx no les ha puesto un dedo encima, ¡son ellos los que "
"insisten en que va a arrancarles la garganta!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:298
msgid ""
"If that's the case, then I give you my word, Captain Atenak, that Nyx is not "
"dangerous - not to humans anyway. She has her reasons not to attack your "
"kind, even if she doesn't reveal them."
msgstr ""
"Si ese es el caso, entonces te doy mi palabra, capitana Atenak, de que Nyx "
"no es peligrosa, al menos no para los humanos. Tiene sus razones para no "
"atacar a tu gente, aunque no las revele."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:302
msgid ""
"Well, if you say so... then I see no reason not to let her free. Akhen, you "
"may untie her..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, si tú lo dices... entonces no veo razón para no dejarla libre. Akhen, "
"puedes desatarla..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:306
msgid "(sarcastic) <i>Most grateful</i>."
msgstr "(sarcástica) <i>Muy agradecida</i>."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:310
msgid ""
"Lady Sigdral, we are heading to Desret, from which we have received no "
"report in months, and so we have been commissioned to..."
msgstr ""
"Señora Sigdral, nos dirigimos a Desret, del que no hemos recibido ningún "
"informe en meses, y por eso se nos ha encomendado..."

#. [message], speaker=Ergarak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:322
msgid ""
"Puny fire-breathers, stinking midgets, we bring message of your impending "
"doom! I am Ergarak, and I lead the vanguard of a monumental horde under the "
"banner of Varag the Great! Tremble, lowly creatures, tremble before our "
"wrath!"
msgstr ""
"¡Insignificantes escupidores de fuego, apestosos enanos, os traemos mensaje "
"de vuestra inminente perdición! ¡Soy Ergarak y lidero la vanguardia de una "
"horda monumental bajo el estandarte de Varag el Grande! ¡Temblad, criaturas "
"inferiores, temblad ante nuestra ira!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:326
msgid ""
"Awww, such a lofty speech from one so small... See, Siggy, it seems like he "
"was trying to impress us."
msgstr ""
"Awww, qué discurso tan grandilocuente de alguien tan pequeño... Mira, Siggy, "
"parece que intentaba impresionarnos."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:330
msgid "Aye. I'm sure that he spent many nights practicing this speech..."
msgstr ""
"Sí. Estoy segura de que pasó muchas noches practicando este discurso..."

#. [message], speaker=Ergarak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:334
msgid "(upset) You... you... I'm going to feed you to my wolves for that!"
msgstr ""
"(enfadado) Vosotros... vosotros... ¡Os voy a dar de comer a mis lobos por "
"eso!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:338
msgid ""
"That goblin may look somewhat goofy, but the force he leads is large! Even "
"if the fairies help us, this will be one difficult battle."
msgstr ""
"Ese trasgo puede parecer un poco torpe, pero la fuerza que lidera es grande. "
"Incluso si las hadas nos ayudan, esta será una batalla difícil."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:342
msgid ""
"I will talk to Violindë, so that the fairies may help us; they may not like "
"humans, but defending this valley is in their interests as well. However, "
"you Maat'Karians must shield them, for they're quite frail."
msgstr ""
"Hablaré con Violindë para que las hadas nos ayuden. Puede que no les gusten "
"los humanos, pero defender este valle también está en su interés. Sin "
"embargo, vosotros, maat'karianos, debéis protegerlas, porque son bastante "
"frágiles."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:382
msgid "But how have you ended up here, so far from vampire lands?"
msgstr ""
"Pero ¿cómo has terminado aquí, tan lejos de las tierras de los vampiros?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:386
msgid ""
"Life has taken Nyx through many meandering ways, boy - none of which "
"concerns you."
msgstr ""
"La vida ha llevado a Nyx por muchos caminos sinuosos, chico; ninguno de los "
"cuales te concierne."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:390
msgid "Come on, don't be so mean, there's nothing wrong with that question!"
msgstr "Vamos, no seas tan mala, ¡no hay nada malo en esa pregunta!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:394
msgid ""
"(snorts) All right, then... Well, after Nyx was exiled, she was forced to go "
"as far from the vampires' lands as she could; she decided to go to Argea, "
"but she couldn't even make it to the Silent Desert. Nyx remembers that she "
"fainted, and when she next woke up, Sigdral and Violindë were by her side. "
"The fairy decided to adopt her, and thus she lived here for many years."
msgstr ""
"(bufa) Está bien, entonces... Bueno, después de que Nyx fuera exiliada, se "
"vio obligada a alejarse lo máximo posible de las tierras de los vampiros. "
"Decidió ir a Argea, pero ni siquiera llegó al Desierto Silencioso. Nyx "
"recuerda que se desmayó, y cuando despertó, Sigdral y Violindë estaban a su "
"lado. La hada decidió adoptarla y así vivió aquí durante muchos años."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:398
msgid "Why were you searching for another home, then?"
msgstr "¿Por qué buscabas otro hogar entonces?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:402
msgid "Nyx only talks to the ones who care about her..."
msgstr "Nyx solo habla con aquellos que se preocupan por ella..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:406
msgid ""
"(sigh) Then why did you leave this valley, if you were well-received here?"
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Entonces ¿por qué dejaste este valle si aquí te recibieron bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:410
msgid ""
"Who said I was well-received here? Violindë may have adopted Nyx, but the "
"other fairies never liked having an unnatural being such as herself amongst "
"them; one day, she grew tired of their bullying, and decided to move again; "
"that was over seventeen years ago."
msgstr ""
"¿Quién dijo que me recibieron bien aquí? Violindë puede que adoptara a Nyx, "
"pero las otras hadas nunca les gustó tener un ser antinatural como ella "
"entre ellas. Un día se cansó de sus burlas y decidió mudarse de nuevo; eso "
"fue hace más de diecisiete años."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:414
msgid ""
"Now, Akhen, please ask her why she keeps referring to herself in the third "
"person."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, Akhen, por favor pregúntale por qué sigue refiriéndose a sí misma en "
"tercera persona."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:418
msgid ""
"Nyx speaks like that because she loves how her name sounds, that's why. You "
"would do that too, if your name was as melodious as mine."
msgstr ""
"Nyx habla así porque le encanta cómo suena su nombre, por eso. Tú también lo "
"harías si tu nombre fuera tan melodioso como el mío."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:422
msgid "(rolls eyes)"
msgstr "(pone los ojos en blanco)"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:448
msgid ""
"(panting) Sigdral...! At last I... have found you... By Moradin, stop "
"frightening me like this, or my old heart will not last another couple of "
"years!"
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) ¡Sigdral...! Por fin te... he encontrado... ¡Por Moradin, deja de "
"asustarme así o mi viejo corazón no aguantará otro par de años!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:452
msgid ""
"C'mon, Professor, I told you I was going to play with my sisters - with the "
"faerie ones, anyway."
msgstr ""
"Vamos, profesor, te dije que iba a jugar con mis hermanas, con las hadas en "
"este caso."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:456
msgid ""
"(sigh) You should think more about your brother, he bears with a lot of "
"criticism already, even within our own clan, for his friendship with the elf-"
"likes..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Deberías pensar más en tu hermano, ya soporta muchas críticas, "
"incluso dentro de nuestro propio clan, por su amistad con los elfos..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:460
msgid ""
"They're called fairies, Professor, and we shouldn't bother with the judgment "
"of dwarves stupid enough to hate a people they've never even met. Now, "
"please over with the lecture, 'cause we have to concentrate in the fighting!"
msgstr ""
"Se llaman hadas, profesor, y no deberíamos preocuparnos por el juicio de "
"enanos lo suficientemente estúpidos como para odiar a un pueblo que ni "
"siquiera han conocido. Ahora, por favor, termina la lección, porque tenemos "
"que concentrarnos en la lucha."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:464
msgid ""
"(angry) These cursed orcs, they never tire of tasting our steel! Worry not, "
"human friends, we shall not let any orcish victory song echo in our precious "
"valley!"
msgstr ""
"(enfadado) ¡Estos orcos malditos nunca se cansan de probar nuestro acero! No "
"os preocupéis, amigos humanos, no permitiremos que ninguna canción de "
"victoria orca resuene en nuestro precioso valle."

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:503
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:619
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:55
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:983
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:56
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:644
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:707
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:906
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:64
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:717
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:819
msgid "Death of allied leaders"
msgstr "Muerte de líderes aliados"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:526
msgid "Violindë? Please, wake up at once..."
msgstr "¿Violindë? Por favor, despierta de una vez..."

#. [unit], id=Violinde, type=Faerie Dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:536
msgid "Violindë"
msgstr "Violindë"

#. [message], speaker=Violinde
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:552
msgid ""
"(sleepy) Uwaaahhh...! Who is the cruel creature who disturbed such a good "
"sleep...? Ah, it's you, Sigdral... By the First's sake, is that revenge for "
"the last prank I played on you?"
msgstr ""
"(somnolienta) ¡Uwaaahhh...! ¿Quién es la criatura cruel que interrumpió un "
"sueño tan bueno...? Ah, eres tú, Sigdral... Por el Primer, ¿es esa tu "
"venganza por la última broma que te hice?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:556
msgid "I'm really sorry to disturb you, but you must help us..."
msgstr "Lamento mucho molestarte, pero debes ayudarnos..."

#. [message], speaker=Violinde
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:560
msgid ""
"No! I care not about your problems, so leave me at once; if I go back to my "
"bed now, I may still return to that sweet dream I was dreaming..."
msgstr ""
"¡No! No me importan vuestros problemas, así que dejadme de una vez. Si "
"vuelvo a mi cama ahora, tal vez aún pueda regresar a ese dulce sueño que "
"estaba teniendo..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:564
msgid ""
"Get your wings off your bed at once, you lazy fairy, can't you see that your "
"valley is being invaded by orcs?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Saca tus alas de la cama de una vez, hada perezosa! ¿No ves que tu valle "
"está siendo invadido por orcos?"

#. [message], speaker=Violinde
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:568
msgid "Nyx, is that really you...?"
msgstr "Nyx, ¿realmente eres tú...?"

#. [message], speaker=Violinde
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:577
msgid ""
"You go away without even leaving a note, how dare you come back like this, "
"you darn... (looks south) Oh, orcs, lots of orcs pouring into our valley... "
"And lots of humans as well... Why did you take so long to wake me up, "
"Sigdral? Now I'll have to call every single fairy to save your dwarves!"
msgstr ""
"Te vas sin dejar ni una nota, ¿cómo te atreves a volver así, maldita...? "
"(mira al sur) Oh, orcos, montones de orcos entrando en nuestro valle... Y "
"también montones de humanos... ¿Por qué tardaste tanto en despertarme, "
"Sigdral? ¡Ahora tendré que llamar a todas las hadas para salvar a vuestros "
"enanos!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:581
msgid ""
"Ahem, leaving the last comment aside, the humans are our friends, and will "
"protect your fairies from the brunt of the enemy assault."
msgstr ""
"Ahem, dejando de lado el último comentario, los humanos son nuestros amigos "
"y protegerán a vuestras hadas del grueso del asalto enemigo."

#. [message], speaker=Violinde
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:585
msgid "Hrumph, if that is so..."
msgstr "Hrumph, si es así..."

#. [message], speaker=Ergarak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:640
msgid ""
"Yes, my assassins, this is finally your chance to shine! Sneak through the "
"enemy ranks and strike the stronger opponents down with poison!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sí, mis asesinos, esta es finalmente vuestra oportunidad de brillar! "
"Infiltraos entre las filas enemigas y abatid a los oponentes más fuertes con "
"veneno."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:644
msgid ""
"So the orcs have developed a new unit... They may look frail in build, but I "
"bet they're quite hard to hit - and, if the goblin is to be trusted, they "
"employ poison in their tactics, so beware, all of you."
msgstr ""
"Así que los orcos han desarrollado una nueva unidad... Pueden parecer "
"frágiles de complexión, pero apuesto a que son bastante difíciles de "
"alcanzar. Y si hay que creer al trasgo, emplean veneno en sus tácticas, así "
"que tened cuidado, todos vosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:666
msgid ""
"Interesting... You do look like the elves as they're described in our "
"scrolls; are you cousin races?"
msgstr ""
"Interesante... Os parecéis a los elfos tal como se describen en nuestros "
"pergaminos. ¿Sois razas primas?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:670
msgid "(faces the other way) Hrumph!"
msgstr "(se da la vuelta) ¡Hrumph!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:674
msgid ""
"Um, sorry for that, they're normally so sweet with those they like, but they "
"can be a bit difficult... And yes, they are indeed related to each other."
msgstr ""
"Um, lo siento por eso, normalmente son muy dulces con aquellos que les "
"gustan, pero pueden ser un poco difíciles... Y sí, efectivamente están "
"emparentadas entre sí."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:678
msgid ""
"Still, there is no evidence of these fairies being sighted in the Old Home, "
"as there is no evidence of elvish presence in Netjer-Ta - other than Alenya "
"herself -, so how can they be related?"
msgstr ""
"Aun así, no hay evidencia de que estas hadas hayan sido vistas en la Antigua "
"Patria, como tampoco hay evidencia de presencia élfica en Netjer-Ta (aparte "
"de la propia Alenya), así que ¿cómo pueden estar emparentadas?"

#. [message], speaker=Violinde
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:682
msgid ""
"There are things about this universe that you and your allegedly 'wise' "
"sages utterly ignore, young human."
msgstr ""
"Hay cosas sobre este universo que tú y tus supuestamente «sabios» sabios "
"ignoráis por completo, joven humano."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:686
msgid "(rolls eyes) All right, <i>Majesty</i>..."
msgstr "(pone los ojos en blanco) Está bien, <i>Majestad</i>..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:701
msgid ""
"'Like the earth needs the trees' roots\n"
"    Not to dissolve in the rainfall,\n"
"\tI need you, my fair Alenya,\n"
"\tSo that my world won't fall apart\n"
"\tAnd as the trees need the fertile earth\n"
"\tTo remain always green and lush,\n"
"\tI need you, beloved Dvalin,\n"
"\tOtherwise I would have no life."
msgstr ""
"«Como la tierra necesita las raíces de los árboles\n"
"    para no disolverse en la lluvia,\n"
"\tte necesito a ti, mi bella Alenya,\n"
"\tpara que mi mundo no se desmorone.\n"
"\tY como los árboles necesitan la tierra fértil\n"
"\tpara permanecer siempre verdes y frondosos,\n"
"\tte necesito a ti, amado Dvalin,\n"
"\tde lo contrario no tendría vida."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:712
msgid ""
"(tear-eyed) Such warm and loving verses...! And to think that their love "
"lived on against all odds, like a flower that blossoms amidst arid, "
"windswept rocks..."
msgstr ""
"(con lágrimas en los ojos) ¡Qué versos tan cálidos y amorosos...! Y pensar "
"que su amor perduró contra todo pronóstico, como una flor que florece en "
"medio de rocas áridas y azotadas por el viento..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:716
msgid "They've got neither rhyme nor rhythm, though."
msgstr "Sin embargo, no tienen ni rima ni ritmo."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:720
msgid ""
"Shut up, you brute! It's the message that matters the most, not the cold, "
"systematic aesthetics!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cállate, bruto! Lo que más importa es el mensaje, ¡no la fría estética "
"sistemática!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:724
msgid ""
"(whispers) And so it turns out that our tough captain actually has got a "
"'soft' side to herself..."
msgstr ""
"(susurra) Así que resulta que nuestra dura capitana en realidad tiene un "
"lado «suave»..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:728
msgid "(blushes) Tsc..."
msgstr "(se sonroja) Tsc..."

#. [message], speaker=Ergarak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:744
msgid ""
"Argh! Wolf rider, go back to Chief Varag's base and tell them that the enemy "
"is stronger than we thought..."
msgstr ""
"¡Argh! Jinete de lobo, regresa a la base del jefe Varag y diles que el "
"enemigo es más fuerte de lo que pensábamos..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:756
msgid ""
"I don't like the sound of that: first, he claims to be the vanguard of an "
"army, and now he talks of a base... Seems like this Varag is about to launch "
"a massive attack on the Sun Path."
msgstr ""
"No me gusta cómo suena eso: primero afirma ser la vanguardia de un ejército, "
"y ahora habla de una base... Parece que este Varag está a punto de lanzar un "
"ataque masivo contra el Camino del Sol."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:760
msgid ""
"So it seems, but you Maat'Karians need not to worry: I shall send word to "
"Lord Vindalf, and soon this valley will be so strongly defended that not "
"even ten thousand orcs shall be able to cross it."
msgstr ""
"Así parece, pero vosotros, maat'karianos, no tenéis por qué preocuparos: "
"enviaré un mensaje al señor Vindalf y pronto este valle estará tan bien "
"defendido que ni siquiera diez mil orcos podrán cruzarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:764
msgid ""
"Still, it's going to be troublesome, to cross the Silent Desert with all "
"these orcs roaming around it..."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, va a ser complicado cruzar el Desierto Silencioso con todos estos "
"orcos rondando por allí..."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:768
msgid ""
"You said that you were heading to the fortress of Desret; if I recall it "
"well, it stands in the seaside, so why don't you go by the sea?"
msgstr ""
"Dijiste que se dirigían a la fortaleza de Desret. Si recuerdo bien, está "
"junto al mar, ¿por qué no van por el mar?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:772
msgid ""
"Because the waters between Netjer-Ta and Argea are no longer safe; ships "
"from Skiron are often spotted patrolling the strait, and unfortunately they "
"largely surpass us in naval power. No, we have no choice but to go by the "
"desert."
msgstr ""
"Porque las aguas entre Netjer-Ta y Argea ya no son seguras. A menudo se "
"avistan barcos de Skiron patrullando el estrecho, y lamentablemente nos "
"superan ampliamente en poder naval. No, no tenemos más remedio que ir por el "
"desierto."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:776
msgid ""
"Well, even if the orcs have higher numbers, they are slow and defenceless on "
"sandy terrain, while you Maat'Karians fare quite well there. Who knows, we "
"could even catch this Varag off guard and strike him down, thus disbanding "
"his army. And this is in us dwarves' interests, so I shall go along with you."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, aunque los orcos tengan más números, son lentos y vulnerables en "
"terreno arenoso, mientras que ustedes los maat'karianos se desenvuelven "
"bastante bien allí. Quién sabe, podríamos incluso sorprender a este Varag y "
"derribarlo, disolviendo así su ejército. Y esto también conviene a los "
"enanos, por eso iré con ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:780
msgid ""
"Oh, no, no, no, milady, you are definitely not going there! It is bad enough "
"already that you leave the caves so often; if you keep wandering about so "
"much no other dwarf will want to marry you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, no, no, no, milady, definitivamente no vas a ir allí! Ya es bastante "
"malo que salgas tan a menudo de las cuevas. Si sigues vagando tanto, ningún "
"otro enano querrá casarse contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:784
msgid ""
"Oh, no dwarf will wish to marry me if I keep going out? So now I'm "
"<i>definitely</i> not staying another single second inside a cave!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, ¿ningún enano querrá casarse conmigo si sigo saliendo? Entonces ahora "
"<i>definitivamente</i> no me quedo ni un segundo más dentro de una cueva!"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:788
msgid "My girl, please think of your brother...!"
msgstr "¡Mi niña, por favor piensa en tu hermano...!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:792
msgid ""
"As I said, it's in our people's interests that this orc chieftain is "
"defeated, so he'll surely understand it if I help our allies bring about "
"Varag's demise. If he doesn't, well, I'm sure that you will be able to "
"convince him otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Como dije, está en interés de nuestro pueblo que este jefe orco sea "
"derrotado, así que seguramente lo entenderá si ayudo a nuestros aliados a "
"acabar con Varag. Si no lo entiende, bueno, estoy segura de que tú podrás "
"convencerlo de lo contrario."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:796
msgid "(sigh) By Moradin's Hammers, you will be my doom, Lady Sigdral..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Por los Martillos de Moradin, vas a ser mi perdición, Lady "
"Sigdral..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:800
msgid ""
"That's why I love you, Professor! Now, folks, let's hurry before we're "
"caught by another orc battalion!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por eso te quiero, profesor! Ahora, gente, ¡apúrense antes de que nos "
"alcance otro batallón de orcos!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:809
msgid "See you, little fairy..."
msgstr "Nos vemos, pequeña hada..."

#. [message], speaker=Violinde
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:813
msgid ""
"(enraged) STOP MAKING FUN OF MY HEIGHT, YOU CLUMSY GIRAFFE! By the Great "
"Mother, that's why I didn't miss you in the least during all these years..."
msgstr ""
"(enojada) ¡DEJA DE BURLARTE DE MI ESTATURA, JIRAFA TORPE! Por la Gran Madre, "
"por eso no te extrañé ni un poco durante todos estos años..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:817
msgid "(amused) My, my, life here sure is lively..."
msgstr "(divertida) Vaya, vaya, la vida aquí sí que es animada..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/03_Between_The_Mountains_And_The_Wood.cfg:821
msgid "(chuckling) I know, right? "
msgstr "(riendo entre dientes) Lo sé, ¿verdad?"

#. [scenario], id=04_Sea_Of_Fire
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:4
msgid "Sea of Fire"
msgstr "Mar de Fuego"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:28
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:366
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:503
msgid "Find the Migdol of Desret"
msgstr "Encuentra el Migdol de Desret"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:58
msgid ""
"It would be wise to recruit/recall a good contingent to follow you through "
"the desert from the start"
msgstr ""
"Sería prudente reclutar o reincorporar un buen contingente para que te "
"acompañe a través del desierto desde el principio"

#. [side], type=Minotaur Elder
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:86
msgid "Labrys"
msgstr "Labrys"

#. [side], type=Minotaur Elder
#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:91
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:133
msgid "Varag's Army"
msgstr "Ejército de Varag"

#. [side], type=Giant Scorpion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:117
msgid "Desert Beasts"
msgstr "Bestias del Desierto"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=General SK
#. [side], type=Necromancer
#. [side], type=Banebow
#. [side], type=Lich Lord WotJ
#. [side], type=Death Knight
#. [modify_side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:152
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:46
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:147
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:83
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:101
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:103
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:186
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:210
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:91
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:133
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:155
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:123
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:143
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:167
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:236
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:257
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:110
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:137
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:161
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:362
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:87
msgid "Skiron"
msgstr "Skiron"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:228
msgid ""
"Damn these winds that keep throwing sand in my eyes! I knew this desert had "
"nothing of 'silent', but this is just too much!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos vientos que no dejan de tirarme arena a los ojos! Sabía que este "
"desierto no tenía nada de «silencioso», ¡pero esto es demasiado!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:232
msgid ""
"Nyx cannot complain, though; there's no way she'd be able to walk under this "
"scorching sun without at least a nice breeze to comfort her."
msgstr ""
"Nyx no puede quejarse, sin embargo. No hay forma de que pudiera caminar bajo "
"este sol abrasador sin al menos una buena brisa que la reconforte."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:236
msgid "Well, if you want to go away, you won't be missed, you know..."
msgstr "Bueno, si quieres irte, no te extrañaremos, sabes..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:240
msgid ""
"(sighing tiredly) Girl, I've told you already, you don't need to be hostile "
"towards me, Nyx is not stealing your man..."
msgstr ""
"(suspirando cansada) Chica, ya te lo dije, no necesitas ser hostil conmigo, "
"Nyx no te está robando a tu hombre..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:244
msgid "(blushing violently) Shut up, you stupid vampiress!!!"
msgstr "(sonrojándose violentamente) ¡Cállate, estúpida vampira!!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:248
msgid "Stop messing with her, Nyx..."
msgstr "Deja de molestarla, Nyx..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Less talking and more marching, please. We're almost reaching Desret now, "
"and so we will certainly find more than simple scorpions and Gnolls... Or so "
"I hope..."
msgstr ""
"Menos hablar y más caminar, por favor. Ya casi llegamos a Desret, así que "
"seguramente encontraremos más que simples escorpiones y gnolls... O eso "
"espero..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:256
msgid ""
"You <i>hope</i> to find worse enemies here? I didn't know you were so "
"bloodthirsty, milady."
msgstr ""
"¿Esperas encontrar enemigos peores aquí? No sabía que fueras tan sedienta de "
"sangre, milady."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:260
msgid ""
"That's not it, I was just thinking out loud. And I've already warned you to "
"stop calling me that; I'm not a noblewoman, but your commander. Now, let us "
"find out once and for all what has befallen Desret!"
msgstr ""
"No es eso, solo estaba pensando en voz alta. Y ya te he advertido que dejes "
"de llamarme así; no soy una noble, sino tu comandante. Ahora, ¡averigüemos "
"de una vez por todas qué le ha pasado a Desret!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:276
msgid "Watch out, there are minotaurs that way!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, hay minotauros por allá!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:280
msgid ""
"They must mercenaries from Varag's army; as much as I'd like to put an end "
"to his threat here and now, we have too few men and a more urgent mission, "
"so let us just avoid them for now."
msgstr ""
"Deben ser mercenarios del ejército de Varag. Por mucho que me gustaría poner "
"fin a su amenaza aquí y ahora, tenemos muy pocos hombres y una misión más "
"urgente, así que evitémoslos por ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:284
msgid ""
"On the other hand, if we are forced to retreat quickly, we'll find our way "
"blocked by the minotaurs. Maybe we should kill them while we can; Nyx senses "
"no orcish stench around here anyway, so these minotaurs must be far from the "
"main army."
msgstr ""
"Por otro lado, si nos vemos obligados a retirarnos rápidamente, "
"encontraremos el camino bloqueado por los minotauros. Tal vez deberíamos "
"matarlos mientras podamos. Nyx no percibe olor orco por aquí de todos modos, "
"así que estos minotauros deben estar lejos del ejército principal."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:288
msgid "You've got a keen nose indeed, just like a dog..."
msgstr "Tienes un olfato muy fino, la verdad, como un perro..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:292
msgid "(mumbling) And they scold Nyx for picking on her.."
msgstr "(murmurando) Y luego regañan a Nyx por burlarse de ella..."

#. [message], speaker=Labrys
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:304
msgid ""
"Ack! Monsters down the desert, monsters up the desert, monsters "
"everywhere...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ack! Monstruos abajo en el desierto, monstruos arriba en el desierto, "
"¡monstruos por todas partes...!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:316
msgid "What a weird last breath message... What do you think that he meant?"
msgstr ""
"Qué mensaje tan raro para su último aliento... ¿Qué crees que quiso decir?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:320
msgid "I have absolutely no idea..."
msgstr "No tengo ni la menor idea..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:335
msgid "Commander, look! There are some ruins over here..."
msgstr "¡Comandante, miren! Hay unas ruinas por aquí..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:339
msgid "But we are still too far from Desret... Let me investigate it."
msgstr "Pero todavía estamos muy lejos de Desret... Déjenme investigarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:346
msgid "Could it be a camp set up by the soldiers of the Migdol?"
msgstr "¿Podría ser un campamento levantado por los soldados del Migdol?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:350
msgid ""
"Why would they build a village when they had a whole Migdol for them? "
"Besides, these ruins don't seem quite recent..."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué construirían una aldea cuando tenían todo un Migdol para ellos? "
"Además, estas ruinas no parecen muy recientes..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:354
msgid ""
"Well, I can discover the age of these wrecks with my runes if you wish, but "
"it may take a while..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, puedo descubrir la antigüedad de estos restos con mis runas si lo "
"deseas, pero puede llevar un tiempo..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:358
msgid ""
"Please, do it; I want to learn more about this village. In the meanwhile, we "
"can regroup and rest for a while."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, hazlo. Quiero saber más sobre esta aldea. Mientras tanto, podemos "
"reagruparnos y descansar un rato."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:370
msgid "Leave Sigdral at the ruined village's keep for 2 turns"
msgstr "Deja a Sigdral en el torreón de la aldea en ruinas durante 2 turnos"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:450
msgid ""
"Hey, Atenak, I've managed to detect the approximate age of these ruins... "
"They've been here for at least six hundred years."
msgstr ""
"Oye, Atenak, he logrado detectar la edad aproximada de estas ruinas... Han "
"estado aquí durante al menos seiscientos años."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:454
msgid ""
"Then they are older than Desret itself... And that's weird, since Desret "
"was, at least officially, the first Maat'Karian settlement in this desert."
msgstr ""
"Entonces son más antiguas que el propio Desret... Y eso es extraño, ya que "
"Desret fue, al menos oficialmente, el primer asentamiento maat'kariano en "
"este desierto."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:458
msgid ""
"Additionally, I've noticed many signs of non-natural damage over the "
"buildings, as if it had been attacked by someone or something."
msgstr ""
"Además, he notado muchas señales de daño no natural en los edificios, como "
"si hubieran sido atacados por alguien o algo."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:462
msgid "Maybe it wasn't built by Maat'Karians, but by orcs or minotaurs..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez no fue construido por maat'karianos, sino por orcos o minotauros..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:466
msgid ""
"I don't think so. This architectonic style is clearly Maat'Karian, and I "
"doubt that anything built by orcs or minotaurs would have survived erosion "
"for so many centuries."
msgstr ""
"No lo creo. Este estilo arquitectónico es claramente maat'kariano, y dudo "
"que algo construido por orcos o minotauros hubiera sobrevivido a la erosión "
"durante tantos siglos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:470
msgid ""
"So we have a Maat'Karian village that is older than the officially oldest "
"Maat'Karian settlement is this region, and which bears marks of unnatural "
"damage...? (looks agape) This..."
msgstr ""
"¿Así que tenemos una aldea maat'kariana que es más antigua que el "
"asentamiento maat'kariano oficialmente más antiguo de esta región y que "
"presenta marcas de daño antinatural...? (mira boquiabierta) Esto..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:474
msgid "What's going on, Atenak?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa, Atenak?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:478
msgid ""
"I...! (shakes head) No, I... we... we must now focus on investigating what "
"has happened to Desret; I can worry about this village later..."
msgstr ""
"¡Yo...! (niega con la cabeza) No, yo... nosotros... ahora debemos centrarnos "
"en investigar qué le ha pasado a Desret; ya me preocuparé por esta aldea más "
"tarde..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:482
msgid ""
"Still, why do you look so astonished? What does this village possibly mean?"
msgstr ""
"Aun así, ¿por qué te ves tan asombrada? ¿Qué puede significar esta aldea?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:486
msgid ""
"(angry) Would you please stop worrying about useless things and remember why "
"we are here in the first place?"
msgstr ""
"(enojada) ¿Podrías dejar de preocuparte por cosas inútiles y recordar por "
"qué estamos aquí en primer lugar?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:490
msgid "(offended) As you say, <i>commander</i>!"
msgstr "(ofendida) ¡Como digas, <i>comandante</i>!"

#. [unit], id=Bashed Orc, type=Orcish Warrior
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:563
msgid "Bashed Orc"
msgstr "Orco golpeado"

#. [message], speaker=Bashed Orc
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:570
msgid "Ugh...! Damn these... monsters...!"
msgstr "¡Ugh...! ¡Malditos... monstruos...!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:580
msgid ""
"That orc sure took one harsh beating... And, to make matters worse... "
"(sniffs the air) There is a strong scent of blood nearby. Beware, everyone..."
msgstr ""
"Ese orco sin duda recibió una buena paliza... Y, para empeorar las cosas... "
"(olfatea el aire) Hay un fuerte olor a sangre cerca. Tened cuidado, todos..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:584
msgid ""
"I think we are about to meet the 'monsters' who attacked that orc and those "
"minotaurs from before. Ready your weapons, Maat'Karians!"
msgstr ""
"Creo que estamos a punto de conocer a los «monstruos» que atacaron a ese "
"orco y a aquellos minotauros de antes. ¡Preparad vuestras armas, "
"maat'karianos!"

#. [unit], id=Ragdur, type=Orcish Slurbow
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:608
msgid "Ragdur"
msgstr "Ragdur"

#. [unit], id=Alectas, type=Necromancer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:623
msgid "Summoner Alectas"
msgstr "Invocador Alectas"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:642
msgid ""
"So Master Menon and the Chamber of Sages were right, after all; Desret was "
"really attacked by forces from Skiron!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces el maestro Menon y la Cámara de los Sabios tenían razón después de "
"todo. ¡Desret realmente fue atacado por fuerzas de Skiron!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:646
msgid ""
"But they don't seem to be very strong right now; fighting Desret's "
"defenders, and now the orcs, has visibly taken its toll on them."
msgstr ""
"Pero no parecen estar muy fuertes ahora. Luchar contra los defensores de "
"Desret y ahora contra los orcos claramente les ha pasado factura."

#. [message], speaker=Ragdur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:650
msgid ""
"More despicable humans come from the north! That's good, I won't be "
"satisfied with crushing only these stinking southerners and their "
"aberrations! Smite them, orcs! Our campaign is over, but we can at least "
"take some human skulls to adorn our huts!"
msgstr ""
"¡Más humanos despreciables vienen del norte! Eso está bien, no me conformaré "
"con aplastar solo a estos sureños apestosos y sus aberraciones. "
"¡Aplastadlos, orcos! Nuestra campaña ha terminado, pero al menos podemos "
"llevar algunos cráneos humanos para adornar nuestras chozas."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:654
msgid ""
"So Varag's army has stumbled on the Skironians too... We couldn't have been "
"luckier; men, let us crush the orcish threat and repel the Skironian "
"vanguard with a single blow! If we secure Desret again, we'll have a "
"precious tactical advantage against any battalion that comes from the sea!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces el ejército de Varag también se ha topado con los skironianos... No "
"podríamos haber tenido más suerte. ¡Hombres, aplastemos la amenaza orca y "
"repitamos la vanguardia skironian con un solo golpe! Si aseguramos Desret de "
"nuevo, tendremos una valiosa ventaja táctica contra cualquier batallón que "
"venga del mar."

#. [message], speaker=Alectas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:658
msgid ""
"At last we get to face the lowly Maat'Karians... Warriors of Skiron, I'm "
"counting on you: fight to the death and beyond!"
msgstr ""
"Por fin nos enfrentamos a los humildes maat'karianos... Guerreros de Skiron, "
"cuento con ustedes: ¡luchen hasta la muerte y más allá!"

#. [unit]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:677
msgid "Revived Soldier"
msgstr "Soldado revivido"

#. [message], speaker=Alectas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:703
msgid ""
"Worry not, brave soldier, I shall give you another chance to fight for our "
"homeland!"
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, valiente soldado, te daré otra oportunidad de luchar por "
"nuestra patria."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:707
msgid ""
"How disgusting... In their eagerness to achieve victory, they go to the "
"extreme of defiling their own comrades!"
msgstr ""
"Qué asco... En su afán por lograr la victoria, llegan al extremo de profanar "
"a sus propios compañeros."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:711
msgid ""
"This is what that once bright civilization has become: they've traded "
"morality for power, and now, though their wealth and military might are "
"great, their people live under the rule of twisted monsters."
msgstr ""
"Esto es en lo que se ha convertido aquella civilización que alguna vez fue "
"brillante: han cambiado la moralidad por el poder y ahora, aunque su riqueza "
"y poder militar son grandes, su pueblo vive bajo el dominio de monstruos "
"retorcidos."

#. [message], speaker=Ragdur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:723
msgid "Ugh! Damn you, monsters...!"
msgstr "¡Ugh! ¡Malditos monstruos...!"

#. [message], speaker=Alectas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:735
msgid "A prayer... for life immortal...!"
msgstr "¡Una oración... por la vida inmortal...!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:743
msgid ""
"Excellent fight, men! Now that we've retaken Desret, we must repair its "
"defences as well as we can, and prepare ourselves for any further Skironian "
"aggression; I'm certain that this was just a vanguard to secure a beachhead "
"for the rest of the army..."
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente combate, hombres! Ahora que hemos recuperado Desret, debemos "
"reparar sus defensas lo mejor posible y prepararnos para cualquier agresión "
"skironian futura. Estoy segura de que esto solo fue una vanguardia para "
"asegurar una cabeza de playa para el resto del ejército..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:747
msgid ""
"(sniffs the air) No... (suddenly frightened) Folks, watch out, it's an "
"ambush!"
msgstr ""
"(olfatea el aire) No... (de repente asustada) Gente, ¡cuidado, es una "
"emboscada!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:751
msgid "Wha..."
msgstr "Qué..."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:772
msgid ""
"(clapping hands) Bravo, bravo indeed! To be able to vanquish two larger "
"forces with such a small troop... Verily, Maat'Karians <i>are</i> as "
"powerful as they are rumoured to be! Nevertheless, I strongly recommend you "
"not to defy me, especially because I have no intention of killing you right "
"now..."
msgstr ""
"(aplaudiendo) ¡Bravo, bravo de verdad! Poder vencer a dos fuerzas mayores "
"con una tropa tan pequeña... En verdad, los maat'karianos <i>son</i> tan "
"poderosos como se rumorea. Sin embargo, les recomiendo encarecidamente que "
"no me desafíen, especialmente porque no tengo intención de matarlos ahora "
"mismo..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:776
msgid ""
"What Lich-Lord are you? Why are you Skironians breaking the ancient treaty "
"and attacking us?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué Señor-Liche eres tú? ¿Por qué ustedes, los skironianos, rompen el "
"antiguo tratado y nos atacan?"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:780
msgid ""
"We are attacking you basically for the same reason every country attacks "
"another, you see. As for my identity... I am Lich-Lady Stygia of Thalassia, "
"pleased to meet you."
msgstr ""
"Los atacamos básicamente por la misma razón por la que cualquier país ataca "
"a otro, ya sabes. En cuanto a mi identidad... Soy la Liche-Lady Stygia de "
"Thalassia, encantada de conocerlos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:784
msgid "(appalled) Stygia, the Monster of the Abyss…?!"
msgstr "(horrorizada) ¡¿Stygia, el Monstruo del Abismo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:788
msgid ""
"(chuckling) Um, it flatters me, to know that I'm so famous outside my own "
"land! Now that I have introduced myself, fair commander, I want you to lead "
"me to the glorious City of the Sun, for I wish to have and audience with the "
"Sages and the Lords - and especially with the Immortal..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo entre dientes) Um, me halaga saber que soy tan famosa fuera de mi "
"propia tierra. Ahora que me he presentado, justa comandante, quiero que me "
"lleves a la gloriosa Ciudad del Sol, porque deseo tener una audiencia con "
"los Sabios y los Señores, y especialmente con el Inmortal..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:792
msgid "You want me to take you and your monsters to my city?!"
msgstr "¡¿Quieres que te lleve a ti y a tus monstruos a mi ciudad?!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:801
msgid "You..."
msgstr "Tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:808
msgid ""
"...<i>Never</i> talk about my creations like this again, do you understand?"
msgstr ""
"...<i>Nunca</i> vuelvas a hablar de mis creaciones de esa forma, ¿entiendes?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:812
msgid "Atenak!!!"
msgstr "¡Atenak!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:816
msgid ""
"(coldly) I am but an ambassadress, so I only wish to talk - as you can see, "
"if I wished your death, you would have been mine already. Now, I will sail "
"to Maat'Kare with you by my side; after all, a newcomer is always more "
"welcome if accompanied by natives."
msgstr ""
"(fríamente) Solo soy una embajadora, así que solo deseo hablar. Como pueden "
"ver, si quisiera su muerte, ya serían míos. Ahora navegaré hacia Maat'Kare "
"con ustedes a mi lado; después de todo, un recién llegado siempre es más "
"bienvenido si va acompañado de nativos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/04_Sea_Of_Fire.cfg:877
msgid ""
"We should have accomplished this mission sooner! Our provisions are over, "
"and in this desert we'll find no way to replenish them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Deberíamos haber cumplido esta misión antes! Nuestras provisiones se han "
"terminado y en este desierto no encontraremos forma de reponerlas."

#. [scenario], id=05_Shadows_Of_The_Past
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:4
msgid "Shadows of the Past"
msgstr "Sombras del Pasado"

#. [unit], id=Imethep, type=MaatKarian Elder Sage
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:113
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:159
msgid "Imethep"
msgstr "Imethep"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:134
msgid ""
"I, Menon Hekare, Elder Sage of this Chamber, declare this emergency council "
"opened. This was a most unexpected visit, Lady Stygia; in Netjer-Ta, when a "
"faction wishes to talk to another, it sends a message warning of the coming "
"of an ambassador."
msgstr ""
"Yo, Menon Hekare, Sabio Anciano de esta Cámara, declaro abierto este consejo "
"de emergencia. Esta fue una visita muy inesperada, Lady Stygia. En Netjer-"
"Ta, cuando una facción desea hablar con otra, envía un mensaje advirtiendo "
"de la llegada de un embajador."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:138
msgid ""
"Apologies, Menon Hekare, but Lord Aegaion was afraid that the exchange of "
"messages would take too long, and he was anxious for this meeting to "
"happen..."
msgstr ""
"Disculpas, Menon Hekare, pero Lord Aegaion temía que el intercambio de "
"mensajes tomara demasiado tiempo y estaba ansioso porque esta reunión "
"ocurriera..."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:142
msgid ""
"Why didn't he come here himself, then? Is his skeleton too worn up for such "
"a long travel?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué no vino él mismo entonces? ¿Su esqueleto está demasiado desgastado "
"para un viaje tan largo?"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:146
msgid ""
"Why such sharp words, good lord? I've always believed Maat'Karians to be "
"flawless in their codes of conduct - after all, you're the ones from which "
"we Skironians descend..."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué palabras tan afiladas, buen señor? Siempre creí que los "
"maat'karianos eran impecables en sus códigos de conducta. Después de todo, "
"ustedes son de quienes descendemos nosotros, los skironianos..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:150
msgid ""
"Straight to the point, Lich-Lady; state your business and explain why you "
"bring my niece and my soldiers as prisoners."
msgstr ""
"Directo al punto, Liche-Lady. Exponga su asunto y explique por qué trae a mi "
"sobrina y a mis soldados como prisioneros."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:154
msgid ""
"Well, I have found this lovely lady and her companions as they dug the ruins "
"of Desret, and so, being a kind noblewoman, I decided to bring them to their "
"city along with me..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, encontré a esta encantadora dama y a sus compañeros mientras "
"excavaban las ruinas de Desret y, siendo una noble bondadosa, decidí "
"traerlos a su ciudad junto conmigo..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:158
msgid "<i>(shocked exclamations amongst Sages and Lords)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(exclamaciones de shock entre los Sabios y los Señores)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:162
msgid ""
"Oh, you didn't know about Desret yet, did you? See, I did not seek its "
"destruction, I was there, simply disembarking my soldiers on the pleasant "
"southern beaches of Netjer-Ta, but then your countrymen charged at me as "
"mindlessly as undead - which they eventually became..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, ¿todavía no sabían de Desret? Verán, yo no busqué su destrucción. Estaba "
"allí simplemente desembarcando a mis soldados en las agradables playas del "
"sur de Netjer-Ta, pero entonces sus compatriotas me atacaron tan sin sentido "
"como no-muertos, en los que eventualmente se convirtieron..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:166
msgid "<i>(Indignant uproar in the assembly)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(Indignado alboroto en la asamblea)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:170
msgid ""
"You sure are bold to butcher our brothers and walk into our city scorning "
"their valour! I say we put the laws of hospitality and diplomacy aside and "
"reduce her bones to dust!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sin duda eres muy audaz para masacrar a nuestros hermanos y entrar en "
"nuestra ciudad despreciando su valor! Digo que dejemos de lado las leyes de "
"hospitalidad y diplomacia y reduzcamos sus huesos a polvo."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:174
msgid ""
"Destroy my body and I shall use the last of my power to open a portal to the "
"heart of our land. Trust me, we Skironians can do that; and Lord Aegaion, "
"foreseeing Maat'Karian treachery, has carefully prepared an army to avenge "
"me, should I fall..."
msgstr ""
"Destruyan mi cuerpo y usaré el último de mis poderes para abrir un portal al "
"corazón de nuestra tierra. Créanme, nosotros los skironianos podemos "
"hacerlo. Y Lord Aegaion, previendo la traición maat'kariana, ha preparado "
"cuidadosamente un ejército para vengarme si caigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:178
msgid ""
"Friends, please calm yourselves. Now, Stygia, tell us the reason of this "
"sudden attack on our domains. We had a truce with your nation; why is "
"Aegaion throwing it away now?"
msgstr ""
"Amigos, por favor cálmense. Ahora, Stygia, díganos la razón de este "
"repentino ataque a nuestros dominios. Teníamos una tregua con su nación. "
"¿Por qué Aegaion la está desechando ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Right, to business: Menon, we know that you and your mage colleagues have "
"always wondered how a nation without magic lore such as Skiron suddenly "
"started raising entire armies of undead. The answer lies in the depths of a "
"very interesting jewel which we call the Ruby of Fire, and which Lord "
"Aegaion discovered after finding it amidst the long-dead remains of a dragon."
msgstr ""
"Bien, al asunto: Menon, sabemos que tú y tus colegas magos siempre se han "
"preguntado cómo una nación sin conocimiento mágico como Skiron comenzó de "
"repente a levantar ejércitos enteros de no-muertos. La respuesta se "
"encuentra en las profundidades de una joya muy interesante que llamamos el "
"Rubí de Fuego, y que Lord Aegaion descubrió tras encontrarlo entre los "
"restos hace tiempo muertos de un dragón."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:186
msgid "(disturbed) A dragon...? Then..."
msgstr "(perturbado) ¿Un dragón...? Entonces..."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:190
msgid ""
"(grinning) Ah, methinks you have already understood everything, right, "
"Immortal? Indeed, nothing escapes your knowledge..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Ah, creo que ya lo has entendido todo, ¿verdad, Inmortal? En "
"efecto, nada escapa a tu conocimiento..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:194
msgid ""
"Nonetheless, I fear the rest of us are ignorant on this matter. Do you know "
"what she is talking about, Master Menon?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, temo que el resto de nosotros ignoramos este asunto. ¿Sabes de "
"qué está hablando, maestro Menon?"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:198
msgid ""
"The Ruby of Fire, good lords, is a magical jewel crafted out of another "
"one..."
msgstr ""
"El Rubí de Fuego, buenos señores, es una joya mágica elaborada a partir de "
"otra..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:202
msgid "Stygia, silence from you!"
msgstr "¡Stygia, silencio!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:206
msgid ""
"...One that was created by the legendary Maat of Hiera'Shirsha, and which is "
"known as the Sky Soul - or, if you prefer, the Garnet of Cursed Souls."
msgstr ""
"...una que fue creada por la legendaria Maat de Hiera'Shirsha, y que se "
"conoce como el Alma del Cielo, o, si lo prefieren, el Granate de las Almas "
"Malditas."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:210
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:318
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/16_Burning_Ice.cfg:652
msgid "<i>(silence)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(silencio)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:214
msgid "(amused) Yes, I thought this would be your reaction..."
msgstr "(divertida) Sí, pensé que esta sería su reacción..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:218
msgid ""
"(sigh) The Garnet is no mere myth, friends - better, it is a myth forged by "
"the Founders to protect us from a terrible truth: that the Sky Dragon, who "
"once terrorized Irdya, still lives inside a magic cell; a gem they dubbed "
"the Sky Soul. It was lost after the Battle of the Crystal Tower, but "
"rediscovered by Hashira the Vile, and split into two different jewels: one "
"contains the souls of three Fire Dragons, and was hidden inside the dragon "
"Isfet, whilst the other one, containing the Sky Dragon's soul, has been "
"entrusted to my keeping since the Treason."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) El Granate no es un mero mito, amigos. Mejor dicho, es un mito "
"forjado por los Fundadores para protegernos de una terrible verdad: que el "
"Dragón del Cielo, que una vez aterrorizó Irdya, aún vive dentro de una celda "
"mágica; una gema que llamaron Alma del Cielo. Se perdió después de la "
"Batalla de la Torre de Cristal, pero fue redescubierta por Hashira la Vil y "
"dividida en dos joyas diferentes: una contiene las almas de tres Dragones de "
"Fuego y fue escondida dentro del dragón Isfet, mientras que la otra, que "
"contiene el alma del Dragón del Cielo, me ha sido confiada desde la Traición."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:222
msgid ""
"(shocked) But... but... How come that the Lords have never heard of such "
"thing?!"
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) ¡Pero... pero... cómo es posible que los Señores nunca hayan "
"oído de algo así?!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:226
msgid ""
"It was known only to the Chamber of Sages; it has always pained us, to keep "
"it a secret from everyone else, but we didn't wish to cause unnecessary "
"panic. At the same time, we had to keep it as safe as we could - and that "
"meant keeping the Soul with us at Maat'Kare..."
msgstr ""
"Solo era conocido por la Cámara de los Sabios. Siempre nos ha dolido "
"mantenerlo en secreto para todos los demás, pero no queríamos causar pánico "
"innecesario. Al mismo tiempo, teníamos que mantenerlo lo más seguro posible, "
"y eso significaba conservar el Alma con nosotros en Maat'Kare..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:230
msgid ""
"(enraged) So you've put the citizens of Maat'Kare under the shadow of the "
"Bane of Irdya without even telling them?!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) ¡¿Entonces pusieron a los ciudadanos de Maat'Kare bajo la sombra "
"del Azote de Irdya sin siquiera decírselo?!"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:234
msgid ""
"Wait, Tewarin... I share your indignation, but we must not quarrel amongst "
"ourselves, not now, not here. And you, Lich, tell us how did your people "
"find out about a secret so well-hidden by us?"
msgstr ""
"Espera, Tewarin... Comparto tu indignación, pero no debemos pelear entre "
"nosotros, no ahora, no aquí. Y tú, Liche, dinos cómo tu gente se enteró de "
"un secreto tan bien oculto por nosotros"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:238
msgid ""
"See, as Lord Aegaion peered into the Ruby of Fire, he managed to contact the "
"souls of the Fire Dragons, and they told him not only about the Sky Soul, "
"but also about the knowledge of the Dark Arts, which they had learned from "
"the famous Book of the Dead. This was how we mastered magic - because our "
"northern neighbours were never willing to share their own lore with us..."
msgstr ""
"Verán, cuando el Señor Aegaion miró dentro del Rubí de Fuego, logró "
"contactar las almas de los Dragones de Fuego, y ellas le contaron no solo "
"sobre el Alma del Cielo, sino también sobre el conocimiento de las Artes "
"Oscuras, que habían aprendido del famoso Libro de los Muertos. Así fue como "
"dominamos la magia, porque nuestros vecinos del norte nunca quisieron "
"compartir su propio saber con nosotros..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:242
msgid ""
"I see, I see: Aegaion has learned about the Soul's existence, and now seeks "
"to obtain it for himself, right? (chuckles)"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo, entiendo: Aegaion se enteró de la existencia del Alma y ahora "
"busca obtenerla para sí mismo, ¿verdad? (ríe entre dientes)"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:246
msgid "Does the prospect of your nation's ruin amuse you, Menon?"
msgstr "¿La perspectiva de la ruina de tu nación te divierte, Menon?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:250
msgid ""
"Aegaion has indeed seen many things, but never could he have seen, probably "
"not even guessed, how the Sky Soul works. He wishes to have it so that his "
"power would reach unimaginable heights, but even if he holds that jewel in "
"his hands, he'll never own it; it's the Soul that will own him, and "
"eventually cause his own destruction and that of his empire."
msgstr ""
"Aegaion ha visto muchas cosas, pero nunca pudo haber visto, probablemente ni "
"siquiera adivinado, cómo funciona el Alma del Cielo. Desea tenerla para que "
"su poder alcance alturas inimaginables, pero aunque sostenga esa joya en sus "
"manos, nunca la poseerá. Será el Alma la que lo posea a él y, eventualmente, "
"cause su propia destrucción y la de su imperio."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:254
msgid ""
"(menacingly) You look down on Lord Aegaion's abilities, Menon, just as your "
"countrymen have always looked down on us, but this shall soon end: our power "
"has grown exponentially in the last decades, as we now command Death itself!"
msgstr ""
"(amenazante) Desprecias las habilidades del Señor Aegaion, Menon, tal como "
"tus compatriotas siempre nos han despreciado a nosotros, pero esto terminará "
"pronto: nuestro poder ha crecido exponencialmente en las últimas décadas, "
"¡ya que ahora comandamos a la Muerte misma"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:258
msgid ""
"So this is why you have come here, Lich, to invite us to war. Very well, "
"then, consider your message delivered, and tell your Aegaion this: your "
"skeletons shall burn and your wraiths shall vanish before the blaze of the "
"City of the Sun!"
msgstr ""
"Así que por eso has venido aquí, Liche, a invitarnos a la guerra. Muy bien, "
"entonces considera tu mensaje entregado, y dile a tu Aegaion esto: tus "
"esqueletos arderán y tus espectros desaparecerán ante el resplandor de la "
"Ciudad del Sol"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:262
msgid ""
"(grinning) Thus begins the War of the Jewel... I shall give you seven days "
"to prepare your forces and alliances, Maat'Karians. During this time, I "
"promise you that Skiron shall not attack, if you promise not to attack us "
"either; we shall also use this period to build our base on what was left of "
"your poor fortress..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Así comienza la Guerra de la Joya... Les daré siete días para "
"preparar sus fuerzas y alianzas, maat'karianos. Durante este tiempo, les "
"prometo que Skiron no atacará, si ustedes prometen no atacarnos tampoco. "
"También usaremos este período para construir nuestra base sobre lo que quedó "
"de su pobre fortaleza..."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:266
msgid "You...!"
msgstr "¡Tú…!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:270
msgid ""
"These are the end days for you, Maat'Karians. Soon your precious sun shall "
"bleach your bones as they march under Skiron's banner! As for you, Menon the "
"Immortal... I look forward to meeting you on the battlefield."
msgstr ""
"Estos son los últimos días para ustedes, maat'karianos. Pronto su precioso "
"sol blanqueará sus huesos mientras marchan bajo el estandarte de Skiron. En "
"cuanto a ti, Menon el Inmortal... Espero con ansias encontrarte en el campo "
"de batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Imethep
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:286
msgid ""
"Alas, our city shall go to full-scale war for the first time in centuries..."
msgstr ""
"Lamentablemente, nuestra ciudad irá a una guerra a gran escala por primera "
"vez en siglos..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:290
msgid ""
"Yes, we will, and for a weapon kept in secret by the Chamber of Sages for "
"centuries!!! I have always spoken against Master Menon's and his Academy's "
"monopoly over our civilization's lore, and now you see how right I was!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sí, lo haremos, y por un arma que la Cámara de los Sabios mantuvo en "
"secreto durante siglos!!! Siempre hablé en contra del monopolio del Maestro "
"Menon y su Academia sobre el saber de nuestra civilización, ¡y ahora ven "
"cómo tenía razón"

#. [message], speaker=Imethep
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:294
msgid ""
"Lord Tewarin, I beg you to try and understand us! If the Soul's existence "
"was revealed to everyone, how long do you think it would take until, say, "
"vampires or orcs knew of its existence and began attempts to steal it? Even "
"the Founders knew the dangers of exposing it to everyone, hence they "
"enshrouded it in myth!"
msgstr ""
"Señor Tewarin, te ruego que intentes entendernos. Si la existencia del Alma "
"se revelaba a todos, ¿cuánto crees que tardarían, por ejemplo, vampiros u "
"orcos en enterarse de su existencia y comenzar intentos de robarla? ¡Incluso "
"los Fundadores conocían los peligros de exponerla a todos, por eso la "
"envolvieron en mito"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:298
msgid ""
"Tewarin, I too feel consternated that this truth has been kept from us for "
"so long, but I see Imethep's point. Until now, never have we been attacked "
"by factions seeking this artefact, and never has this city been damaged by "
"its alleged power."
msgstr ""
"Tewarin, yo también me siento consternado porque esta verdad se nos haya "
"ocultado por tanto tiempo, pero veo el punto de Imethep. Hasta ahora, nunca "
"hemos sido atacados por facciones que busquen este artefacto, y nunca esta "
"ciudad ha sido dañada por su supuesto poder."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:302
msgid "<i>(Disagreeing murmurs amongst the Lords)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(murmullos de desacuerdo entre los Señores)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:306
msgid ""
"I'm afraid that not all of us think like you, my friend. Furthermore, I "
"can't help but wonder how the weapon has found its way to Master Menon's "
"hands; certainly he insisted on keeping it, claiming that none other was as "
"capable of protecting it?"
msgstr ""
"Me temo que no todos pensamos como tú, amigo mío. Además, no puedo evitar "
"preguntarme cómo el arma llegó a las manos del Maestro Menon. Seguramente él "
"insistió en conservarla, alegando que nadie más era tan capaz de protegerla, "
"¿verdad"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:310
msgid ""
"For a long time I refused to keep it, as much as the Sages of old insisted "
"on the contrary, because - I confess - I feared the Soul. However, I "
"ultimately decided that I shouldn't turn away from my duty, and accepted it, "
"but not without taking the best measures I could think of to avoid being "
"affected by it. In fact, I've never touched it since I collected it from "
"Hashira's scorched hands."
msgstr ""
"Durante mucho tiempo me negué a conservarla, por más que los Sabios antiguos "
"insistieran en lo contrario, porque —lo confieso— temía al Alma. Sin "
"embargo, finalmente decidí que no debía dar la espalda a mi deber y la "
"acepté, pero no sin tomar las mejores medidas que se me ocurrieron para "
"evitar ser afectado por ella. De hecho, nunca la he tocado desde que la "
"recogí de las manos quemadas de Hashira."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:314
msgid ""
"You've said it yourself that this gem is impregnated with a massive evil "
"energy - which is understandable, since it shelters the soul of the Bane of "
"Irdya. Thus, how can we be sure that you haven't fallen prey to its "
"corruption already?"
msgstr ""
"Tú mismo dijiste que esta gema está impregnada de una energía maligna "
"masiva, lo cual es comprensible, ya que alberga el alma del Azote de Irdya. "
"Entonces, ¿cómo podemos estar seguros de que tú no has caído ya presa de su "
"corrupción?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:322
msgid ""
"(serious) For seven centuries, I have used the full extent of my knowledge "
"and skill - which, modesty aside, are not to be disdained - to suppress the "
"Soul's aura; still, I can safely say that, for seven centuries, I have "
"risked myself to protect Maat'Kare from that evil. Thus, I will not tolerate "
"any accusation against my commitment to our civilization's welfare. That "
"said, should the Lords deem me untrustworthy, then I shall retire myself to "
"Hiera'Laksha, and remain there until no doubt of my honesty remains."
msgstr ""
"(serio) Durante siete siglos he usado todo el alcance de mi conocimiento y "
"habilidad —que, sin modestia, no son despreciables— para suprimir el aura "
"del Alma. Aun así, puedo decir con seguridad que, durante siete siglos, me "
"he arriesgado para proteger a Maat'Kare de ese mal. Por lo tanto, no "
"toleraré ninguna acusación contra mi compromiso con el bienestar de nuestra "
"civilización. Dicho esto, si los Señores me consideran indigno de confianza, "
"entonces me retiraré a Hiera'Laksha y permaneceré allí hasta que no quede "
"ninguna duda sobre mi honestidad."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:326
msgid "No! Master Menon, please don't..."
msgstr "¡No! Maestro Menon, por favor no..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:330
msgid ""
"Now, my fellow Maat'Karians, we must prepare ourselves for the looming war, "
"and send ambassadors to our dwarf and warg allies. Furthermore, I strongly "
"recommend parleying with the orcs, the vampires and the Warglanders, and "
"convince them that Skiron is their enemy as well. But it's no longer in my "
"power to decide our people's next course of action; as my last act before my "
"self-exile, I declare this emergency council over."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, mis compañeros maat'karianos, debemos prepararnos para la guerra que "
"se avecina y enviar embajadores a nuestros aliados enanos y huargos. Además, "
"recomiendo encarecidamente negociar con los orcos, los vampiros y los "
"Warglanders, y convencerlos de que Skiron también es su enemigo. Pero ya no "
"está en mi poder decidir el siguiente curso de acción de nuestro pueblo. "
"Como mi último acto antes de mi autoexilio, declaro terminado este consejo "
"de emergencia."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:334
msgid ""
"Master Menon, I promise you that this exile will not last long; I will talk "
"to the other Lords, and make them see how insane it is, to send our best "
"citizen away in this time of utmost need."
msgstr ""
"Maestro Menon, te prometo que este exilio no durará mucho. Hablaré con los "
"otros Señores y les haré ver lo insensato que es enviar a nuestro mejor "
"ciudadano lejos en este momento de máxima necesidad."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:341
msgid ""
"(kindly) Akhen, I am relieved to see that you, Merwe and Mahyus are safe and "
"sound, and glad to see you again, fair Sigdral. But I wonder who this "
"vampiress by your side might be..."
msgstr ""
"(amablemente) Akhen, me alivia ver que tú, Merwe y Mahyus están sanos y "
"salvos, y me alegra verte de nuevo, bella Sigdral. Pero me pregunto quién "
"podría ser esta vampira que está a tu lado..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:345
msgid ""
"Wha... I mean, this is Nyx; albeit being a vampire, she's Sigdral's old "
"friend, and has already proved not to be hostile to humans, so we let her "
"follow us..."
msgstr ""
"Qué... Quiero decir, esta es Nyx. Aunque es una vampira, es una vieja amiga "
"de Sigdral y ya ha demostrado que no es hostil hacia los humanos, por eso le "
"permitimos que nos siguiera..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:349
msgid ""
"(whisper) That was one gross understatement, Akhen; you actually <i>forced</"
"i> me to come with you."
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Eso fue una gran subestimación, Akhen. En realidad <i>me "
"obligaste</i> a venir contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:353
msgid "Master, how can they do this to you...!"
msgstr "¡Maestro, cómo pueden hacerte esto...!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:357
msgid ""
"(smiling) Don't worry, my dear Akhen; Hiera'Laksha is no prison, so I will "
"be just fine. As for the Soul, it shall remain exactly as it is right now: "
"inside a strong barrier of ciphers and other spells. I will also leave my "
"most trusted professors to watch over it."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) No te preocupes, mi querido Akhen. Hiera'Laksha no es una "
"prisión, así que estaré bien. En cuanto al Alma, permanecerá exactamente "
"como está ahora: dentro de una fuerte barrera de cifrados y otros hechizos. "
"También dejaré a mis profesores más confiables vigilándola."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:361
msgid "Still, what will be of me...? I mean, what will I do?"
msgstr "Aun así, ¿qué será de mí...? Quiero decir, ¿qué haré?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:365
msgid ""
"If you wish to do something for your nation, I will talk to Atseger, and she "
"will see that you are placed in a mage battalion; you have already gained "
"enough experience to join one, and the Gods know how desperately Maat'Kare "
"will need the mages’ power in this war."
msgstr ""
"Si deseas hacer algo por tu nación, hablaré con Atseger y ella se encargará "
"de que te coloquen en un batallón de magos. Ya has ganado suficiente "
"experiencia para unirte a uno, y los Dioses saben lo desesperadamente que "
"Maat'Kare necesitará el poder de los magos en esta guerra."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:369
msgid ""
"Er, Master, do you think it is possible for me to join Akhen's mage "
"battalion... (blushing) I mean, to join a mage battalion like Akhen..."
msgstr ""
"Eh, Maestro, ¿crees que sea posible que me una al batallón de magos de "
"Akhen...? (sonrojándose) Quiero decir, unirme a un batallón de magos como "
"Akhen..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:373
msgid ""
"Master, I'd like to join one as well, but alongside Akhen and Merwe; you "
"know, our powers kind of… complete each other..."
msgstr ""
"Maestro, a mí también me gustaría unirme a uno, pero junto a Akhen y Merwe. "
"Sabes, nuestros poderes como que... se complementan..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:377
msgid ""
"(laughing) I'm pleased to see that you have finally learned to get along! "
"Don't worry, I'll leave Master Atseger an express order that you must be "
"enrolled in the same battalion."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¡Me alegra ver que finalmente aprendieron a llevarse bien! No se "
"preocupen, le dejaré al Maestro Atseger una orden expresa de que deben ser "
"inscritos en el mismo batallón."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:381
msgid ""
"Thank you, Master! (whispering to Mahyus) 'Our powers complete each other', "
"uh? We'll see..."
msgstr ""
"¡Gracias, Maestro! (susurrando a Mahyus) «Nuestros poderes se complementan», "
"¿eh? Ya veremos..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:385
msgid ""
"Akhen, I must return to my home and tell my brother what has happened "
"here... That is, if he lets me talk at all, for I sense an epic lecture "
"looming before me... And you, Nyx, you'll be coming with me; I won't let you "
"wander around this continent alone anymore, not until this war is over."
msgstr ""
"Akhen, debo regresar a mi hogar y contarle a mi hermano lo que ha pasado "
"aquí... Es decir, si me deja hablar, porque presiento una lección épica "
"acercándose... Y tú, Nyx, vendrás conmigo. No te dejaré vagar sola por este "
"continente nunca más, no hasta que esta guerra termine."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:389
msgid "Nyx hears and obeys, mistress..."
msgstr "Nyx escucha y obedece, ama..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:393
msgid "Till next time, friends! And do not get yourself killed!"
msgstr "¡Hasta la próxima, amigos! ¡Y no se dejen matar!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/05_Shadows_Of_The_Past.cfg:397
msgid "(smiling) I tell you the same..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) Les digo lo mismo..."

#. [scenario], id=06_Spark_Of_Violence
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:4
msgid "Spark of Violence"
msgstr "Chispa de Violencia"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:23
msgid "Repel Erynia's attack"
msgstr "Repele el ataque de Erynia"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:51
msgid "Death of any allied leader"
msgstr "Muerte de cualquier líder aliado"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Sire
#. [side], type=Vampiric Dread Bat
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:89
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:95
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:110
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:127
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:180
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:125
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:141
msgid "Vampires"
msgstr "Vampiros"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:114
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:136
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:181
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:79
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:100
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:95
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:53
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:36
msgid "Aigathol Dwarves"
msgstr "Enanos Aigathol"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Garou
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:158
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:105
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:114
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:109
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:62
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:46
msgid "Wargs"
msgstr "Huargos"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Lord Tewarin, allow me to accompany you to the Hall of Auroghar, where he "
"awaits you alongside the representatives of our allies."
msgstr ""
"Señor Tewarin, permíteme acompañarte al Salón de Auroghar, donde te espera "
"junto a los representantes de nuestros aliados."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Thanks, Master Anduril. Come, Atenak, we must not let our friends await us "
"for long."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, Maestro Anduril. Ven, Atenak, no debemos hacer esperar mucho a "
"nuestros amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:233
msgid "(puzzled) *...What is this noise...?*"
msgstr "(desconcertada) *...¿Qué es ese ruido...?*"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:237
msgid "Atenak, did you hear me?"
msgstr "Atenak, ¿me escuchaste?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:241
msgid "<span size='large'>scratch scratch*</span>"
msgstr "<span size='large'>ras ras*</span>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:245
msgid "<span size='large'>Blam!*</span>"
msgstr "<span size='large'>¡Blam!*</span>"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:260
msgid "Ouch! Damn you, Mahyus, I told you to stop waddling!"
msgstr "¡Ay! ¡Maldito seas, Mahyus, te dije que dejaras de tambalearte!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:264
msgid ""
"I wasn't waddling, I was just trying to get my face away from this idiot's "
"foot, because he was too dumb to move it a couple of inches!"
msgstr ""
"¡No me estaba tambaleando, solo intentaba alejar mi cara del pie de este "
"idiota, porque era demasiado tonto para moverlo un par de centímetros!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:268
msgid ""
"(astonished) What shamelessness is this? You are students of the Academy - "
"and <i>you</i> are the Wadjet boy, Menon's own pupil!!!"
msgstr ""
"(asombrado) ¿Qué descaro es este? ¡Ustedes son estudiantes de la Academia, y "
"<i>tú</i> eres el chico Wadjet, el propio pupilo de Menon!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:272
msgid ""
"Erm, Lord Tewarin, I apologise for the inconvenience; we heard that you were "
"partaking of a council with representatives of the dwarves and the wargs, "
"and we, well, we just couldn't sit quietly at the Academy any longer, and so "
"we thought we could, well..."
msgstr ""
"Eh, Señor Tewarin, me disculpo por la molestia. Escuchamos que estabas "
"participando en un consejo con representantes de los enanos y los huargos, y "
"nosotros, bueno, simplemente no pudimos quedarnos tranquilos en la Academia "
"por más tiempo, así que pensamos que podíamos, bueno..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:276
msgid ""
"So you sneaked into my caravan, hid in my carriages like assassins and the "
"like, and shamed me in front of our allies?! I should send you back to "
"Maat'Kare in chains for this affront!"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Entonces se colaron en mi caravana, se escondieron en mis carruajes como "
"asesinos y cosas por el estilo, y me avergonzaron frente a nuestros "
"aliados?! ¡Debería enviarlos de regreso a Maat'Kare encadenados por esta "
"afrenta"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:280
msgid ""
"(amused) My good Lord Tewarin, please forgive their brashness. Certainly "
"they should have asked you permission to accompany you, but they're just "
"youths who are eager to do something for their beloved nation."
msgstr ""
"(divertido) Mi buen Señor Tewarin, por favor perdona su atrevimiento. "
"Seguramente deberían haberte pedido permiso para acompañarte, pero solo son "
"jóvenes que están ansiosos por hacer algo por su querida nación."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:284
msgid ""
"Please, uncle, let them stay with us as companions; I will take "
"responsibility for them."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, tío, déjalos quedarse con nosotros como acompañantes. Yo me haré "
"responsable de ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:288
msgid ""
"So be it. Out of respect for Master Anduril, I shall allow you to stay - but "
"you two (points to Merwe and Mahyus) are to remain at my chariot; Wadjet "
"boy, you shall accompany me to the meeting as a representative of the "
"Academy."
msgstr ""
"Que así sea. Por respeto al Maestro Anduril, permitiré que se queden, pero "
"ustedes dos (señala a Merwe y Mahyus) deben permanecer en mi carro. Chico "
"Wadjet, tú me acompañarás a la reunión como representante de la Academia."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:292
msgid "(sigh) To stay here all alone with this dark adept..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Quedarme aquí sola con este adepto oscuro..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:296
msgid ""
"(angry whisper) You owe me one, Akhen Wadjet. Never forget that, understood?"
msgstr ""
"(susurro enojado) Me debes una, Akhen Wadjet. Nunca lo olvides, ¿entendido?"

#. [unit], id=Romlur, type=Garou
#. [side], type=Garou
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:383
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1243
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:200
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:289
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:108
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:103
msgid "Romlur"
msgstr "Romlur"

#. [unit], id=Skorr, type=Night Eye
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:393
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:338
msgid "Skorr"
msgstr "Skorr"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:415
msgid ""
"Worthy lords, I welcome you to the hall of my ancestors. I'm glad to see "
"that most of the invited leaders are present; although not all of us are "
"friendly to each other, we are currently at the mercy of the same evil: the "
"twisted Empire of Skiron has invaded Netjer-Ta. Make no mistake: though it "
"has officially declared war on Maat'Kare only, it'd be very unwise of us not "
"to expect them to try and turn all of us into mindless undead slaves."
msgstr ""
"Dignos señores, les doy la bienvenida al salón de mis ancestros. Me alegra "
"ver que la mayoría de los líderes invitados están presentes. Aunque no todos "
"somos amistosos entre nosotros, actualmente estamos a merced del mismo mal: "
"el retorcido Imperio de Skiron ha invadido Netjer-Ta. No se equivoquen: "
"aunque ha declarado oficialmente la guerra solo a Maat'Kare, sería muy "
"imprudente de nuestra parte no esperar que intenten convertirnos a todos en "
"esclavos no-muertos sin mente."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:419
msgid ""
"I've made my stance clear to our Maat'Karian friends already: the Warg packs "
"have already pledged themselves to the aid of humans and dwarves against "
"those foul violators of Nature."
msgstr ""
"Ya le he dejado clara mi postura a nuestros amigos maat'karianos: las "
"manadas de huargos ya se han comprometido a ayudar a humanos y enanos contra "
"esos repugnantes violadores de la Naturaleza."

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:423
msgid ""
"Mind your words, Romlur, for not all Warg packs are dirty traitors of their "
"own kind. In the name of all Warglanders, I declare that we shall not raise "
"a claw to help the treacherous humans, neither Myra's folk nor the ones from "
"Argea."
msgstr ""
"Cuida tus palabras, Romlur, porque no todas las manadas de huargos son "
"sucios traidores de su propia especie. En nombre de todos los Warglanders, "
"declaro que no levantaremos una garra para ayudar a los humanos "
"traicioneros, ni al pueblo de Myra ni a los de Argea."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:427
msgid ""
"Friends, please let us not be hostile to each other. Chief Skorr, I deeply "
"lament that you are unwilling to leave your divergences aside to deal with a "
"common foe, but if that's your final decision, we must all respect it. Now, "
"I wish to ask you, Gomatol, why has Lord Argatyr not honoured us with his "
"presence?"
msgstr ""
"Amigos, por favor no seamos hostiles entre nosotros. Jefe Skorr, lamento "
"profundamente que no estés dispuesto a dejar de lado tus diferencias para "
"enfrentar a un enemigo común, pero si esa es tu decisión final, todos "
"debemos respetarla. Ahora, quisiera preguntarte, Gomatol, ¿por qué el Señor "
"Argatyr no nos ha honrado con su presencia?"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:431
msgid ""
"My lord asked me to transmit his apologies, but he didn't feel it was the "
"best time for meeting again certain individuals..."
msgstr ""
"Mi señor me pidió que transmitiera sus disculpas, pero no sintió que fuera "
"el mejor momento para volver a reunirse con ciertas personas..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:435
msgid "(rolls eyes) By Moradin's sake, he hasn't overcome that yet..."
msgstr ""
"(pone los ojos en blanco) Por el amor de Moradin, todavía no lo ha "
"superado..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:439
msgid ""
"(whispers) He's a male after all, his wounded pride won't heal so quickly..."
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Es un varón después de todo, su orgullo herido no sanará tan "
"rápido..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:443
msgid ""
"...However, he authorized me to pledge the forces of the Motsoghnir to the "
"aid of our Aigathol friends and of our Maat'Karian allies."
msgstr ""
"...Sin embargo, me autorizó a comprometer las fuerzas de los Motsoghnir para "
"ayudar a nuestros amigos Aigathol y a nuestros aliados maat'karianos."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:447
msgid ""
"This is great news! I'm glad to hear that Lord Argatyr shall join us in this "
"war; after all, the Motsoghnir's knowledge of the tunnels of both Netjer-Ta "
"and Argea is..."
msgstr ""
"¡Esta es una gran noticia! Me alegra oír que el Señor Argatyr se unirá a "
"nosotros en esta guerra. Después de todo, el conocimiento de los Motsoghnir "
"sobre los túneles tanto de Netjer-Ta como de Argea es..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:454
msgid "W-was that an earthquake?!"
msgstr "¡¿F-fue eso un terremoto?!"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:458
msgid ""
"(alarmed) No, it came from above, from the outside... Can it be a surprise "
"attack by Skiron?"
msgstr ""
"(alarmado) No, vino de arriba, desde afuera... ¿Podría ser un ataque "
"sorpresa de Skiron?"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:462
msgid ""
"But they promised not to attack until the end of this week! Have they lost "
"their honour in addition to their humanity?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero prometieron no atacar hasta el final de esta semana! ¿Acaso perdieron "
"su honor además de su humanidad?"

#. [message], speaker=Guard
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:470
msgid ""
"(panting) Lord Vindalf... Vampires are attacking us from the north... And "
"it's no mere raid: I received word that Grand Duchess Erynia herself is "
"leading this attack..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Señor Vindalf... Vampiros nos están atacando desde el norte... Y "
"no es solo una incursión: recibí noticia de que la mismísima Gran Duquesa "
"Erynia está liderando este ataque..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:474
msgid "(suddenly enraged) Erynia's here?!"
msgstr "(repentinamente enfurecida) ¡¿Erynia está aquí?!"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:478
msgid ""
"Her timing sure is impeccable... Friends, we must call off today's meeting; "
"hopefully we shall continue it tomorrow, but now I must deal with this "
"unexpected attack."
msgstr ""
"Su momento es impecable... Amigos, debemos cancelar la reunión de hoy. Con "
"suerte la continuaremos mañana, pero ahora debo ocuparme de este ataque "
"inesperado."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:482
msgid ""
"Lord Vindalf, allow me to help you; though my retinue is not large, it "
"counts with many seasoned fighters who are used to fighting vampires."
msgstr ""
"Señor Vindalf, permíteme ayudarte. Aunque mi séquito no es grande, cuenta "
"con muchos luchadores experimentados que están acostumbrados a combatir "
"vampiros."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:486
msgid ""
"We too wish to join the fray, but I fear I've brought too few warriors with "
"me; maybe if Skorr accepts joining forces with me..."
msgstr ""
"Nosotros también deseamos unirnos a la pelea, pero me temo que traje muy "
"pocos guerreros conmigo. Tal vez si Skorr acepta unir fuerzas conmigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:490
msgid ""
"Hrumph! I hate to admit it, but I too came here with few warriors; let's "
"unite then - but make no mistake; I just want to kill some blood-suckers, "
"not to be friends with you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! Odio admitirlo, pero yo también vine aquí con pocos guerreros. "
"Unámonos entonces, pero que no haya error: solo quiero matar a algunos "
"chupasangre, ¡no ser amigo de ustedes"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Alas, I shall not be able to help you, friends, for I've brought no soldiers "
"with me."
msgstr ""
"Lamentablemente, no podré ayudarlos, amigos, porque no traje soldados "
"conmigo."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:498
msgid ""
"Worry not, good Gomatol, you couldn't have foreseen such attack. As for you, "
"friends, I thank and welcome your aid. Sigdral, you stay here preparing the "
"reserves for when and if they're needed, and don't even try to convince me "
"otherwise! But I cannot command you, Nyx, so, if you wish to fight as well, "
"you’re free to follow us."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, buen Gomatol, no podías prever un ataque así. En cuanto a "
"ustedes, amigos, agradezco y acepto su ayuda. Sigdral, tú quédate aquí "
"preparando las reservas para cuando y si se necesitan, ¡y ni siquiera "
"intentes convencerme de lo contrario! Pero a ti no puedo ordenarte, Nyx, así "
"que si deseas luchar también, eres libre de seguirnos."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:502
msgid "(ferocious) With pleasure..."
msgstr "(feroz) Con gusto..."

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:626
msgid ""
"Just as I told you, my vassals: poke at the insects' hive and they'll all "
"come out in a hurry to be killed. Lowly vermin like them are so "
"predictable..."
msgstr ""
"Como les dije, mis vasallos: piquen el nido de los insectos y todos saldrán "
"corriendo para ser asesinados. Alimañas inferiores como ellos son tan "
"predecibles..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:630
msgid ""
"Lord Vindalf, yours is the largest force, but I ask you to leave the centre "
"for us Maat'Karians and the wargs, for we fare better on flat and woody "
"terrain."
msgstr ""
"Señor Vindalf, la tuya es la fuerza más grande, pero te pido que dejes el "
"centro para nosotros los maat'karianos y los huargos, porque nos "
"desenvolvemos mejor en terreno plano y boscoso."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:634
msgid ""
"You speak wisely, Lord Tewarin; I shall split my forces in two and attack "
"across the mountains flanking the valley. Anduril, you lead the western "
"offensive, whilst I shall lead from the east."
msgstr ""
"Hablas con sabiduría, Señor Tewarin. Dividiré mis fuerzas en dos y atacaré a "
"través de las montañas que flanquean el valle. Anduril, tú liderarás la "
"ofensiva occidental, mientras que yo lideraré desde el este."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#. [message], speaker=Noxes
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:638
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:605
msgid "As you wish, milord."
msgstr "Como desees, milord."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:648
msgid ""
"Atenak, I want you to lead the soldiers in the front lines; Wadjet boy, I "
"told you and your friends to stay in the caves, but you insisted on coming "
"along, so you shall fight as well."
msgstr ""
"Atenak, quiero que lideres a los soldados en las líneas del frente. Chico "
"Wadjet, te dije a ti y a tus amigos que se quedaran en las cuevas, pero "
"insistieron en venir, así que ustedes también lucharán."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:652
msgid "Understood, Lord Tewarin."
msgstr "Entendido, Señor Tewarin."

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:674
msgid ""
"A vampiress fighting her own kind? Now there's something I'd never seen "
"before..."
msgstr ""
"¿Una vampira luchando contra los de su propia especie? Ahora eso es algo que "
"nunca había visto antes..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:678
msgid ""
"Nyx will fight and kill anyone who stands on her way, be it vampire or not - "
"and especially stinking furries who put their noses in what is not of their "
"concern!"
msgstr ""
"Nyx luchará y matará a cualquiera que se interponga en su camino, sea "
"vampiro o no, ¡y especialmente a peludos apestosos que meten las narices en "
"lo que no les concierne"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Hey, Nyx, save your anger for our foes! We shouldn't quarrel with friends!"
msgstr ""
"Oye, Nyx, guarda tu enojo para nuestros enemigos. ¡No deberíamos pelear con "
"amigos"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:693
msgid ""
"ERYNIA, YOU WRETCHED TRAITOR!!! TODAY YOU SHALL FINALLY MEET YOUR FATE BY MY "
"BLADE!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡ERYNIA, MALDITA TRAIDORA!!! ¡HOY FINALMENTE ENCONTRARÁS TU DESTINO POR MI "
"ESPADA!!"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:697
msgid ""
"Um, who is that fool that's challenging me... No... can it be really her...? "
"(thrilled) Ah, Nyx, my dear, it's you! Sorry for not recognizing you sooner; "
"I remembered you as a fine and elegant young vampiress, but now you wear "
"rags and smell to dwarves and other similarly malodorous scum... You're a "
"daughter of Aryen Devellian, and so you should behave as such!"
msgstr ""
"Um, ¿quién es esa tonta que me desafía...? No... ¿podría ser realmente "
"ella...? (emocionada) ¡Ah, Nyx, querida, eres tú! Lamento no haberte "
"reconocido antes. Te recordaba como una joven vampira fina y elegante, pero "
"ahora llevas harapos y hueles a enanos y a otra escoria igualmente "
"maloliente... Eres hija de Aryen Devellian, y por eso deberías comportarte "
"como tal."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:701
msgid ""
"(seething in anger) Don't you dare pronounce my father's name with your "
"sordid mouth, you disgusting animal!"
msgstr ""
"(hirviendo de rabia) ¡No te atrevas a pronunciar el nombre de mi padre con "
"tu boca asquerosa, animal repugnante"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:705
msgid "Wait a minute, your father was Aryen Devellian?!"
msgstr "¡Un momento, tu padre era Aryen Devellian?!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:709
msgid "Why such surprise? Do you know him?"
msgstr "¿Por qué tanta sorpresa? ¿Lo conoces?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:713
msgid ""
"Aryen was a powerful vampire lord, a descendant of Vrykos himself; but, "
"unlike his kin, he was friendly to humans, because he was in love with a "
"human woman..."
msgstr ""
"Aryen era un poderoso señor vampiro, descendiente del propio Vrykos. Pero, a "
"diferencia de su linaje, era amistoso con los humanos porque estaba "
"enamorado de una mujer humana..."

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:717
msgid ""
"...A scandalous affair indeed, don't you think? An heir of the great Vrykos, "
"staining the honour of the Devellians like this... I warned that fool that "
"such union would cause the downfall of our House, but he refused to heed me, "
"and so I had to act to save our clan's dignity. Unfortunately, I couldn't "
"risk suffering the vengeance of his offspring, and thus I was forced to send "
"them all to meet their father - except for a little batty bat who somehow "
"managed to escape my fangs..."
msgstr ""
"...Un asunto escandaloso, ¿no creen? Un heredero del gran Vrykos, manchando "
"el honor de los Devellian de esta manera... Le advertí a ese tonto que esa "
"unión causaría la caída de nuestra Casa, pero se negó a escucharme, y por "
"eso tuve que actuar para salvar la dignidad de nuestro clan. "
"Lamentablemente, no podía arriesgarme a sufrir la venganza de su "
"descendencia, y por eso me vi obligada a enviarlos a todos a reunirse con su "
"padre, excepto por un pequeño murciélago que de alguna manera logró escapar "
"de mis colmillos..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:721
msgid ""
"(enraged) ...One who now returns to exact revenge on her who murdered her "
"own kin!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecida) ...¡Una que ahora regresa para vengarse de quien asesinó a su "
"propia familia!"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:725
msgid ""
"How sweet, she calls me a kin-slayer while calmly slitting the throat of a "
"fellow vampire..."
msgstr ""
"Qué dulce, me llama asesina de familia mientras tranquilamente le corta la "
"garganta a un vampiro compañero..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:729
msgid "I'm no kin to scum who serves and bows down to one such as you!"
msgstr ""
"¡No soy familia de escoria que sirve y se inclina ante alguien como tú!"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:733
msgid ""
"Still, my dear niece, vampires have no one else to count on in this world "
"that hates our kind. See: (shouting) Dwarves, wargs and humans, heed me! I "
"am willing to withdraw my forces and sign a year-long truce if you simply "
"deliver me my niece!"
msgstr ""
"Aun así, mi querida sobrina, los vampiros no tienen a nadie más en quien "
"apoyarse en este mundo que odia a nuestra especie. Miren: (gritando) "
"¡Enanos, huargos y humanos, escúchenme! Estoy dispuesta a retirar mis "
"fuerzas y firmar una tregua de un año si simplemente me entregan a mi "
"sobrina."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:737
msgid "Damn you, Erynia...!"
msgstr "¡Maldita seas, Erynia...!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:741
msgid ""
"Lord Vindalf, I've noticed that this vampiress is a good friend of your "
"sister, but I beg you to consider this offer. With Skiron's full power at "
"our doorstep, engaging the vampire hordes too would be extremely troublesome."
msgstr ""
"Señor Vindalf, he notado que esta vampira es una buena amiga de tu hermana, "
"pero te ruego que consideres esta oferta. Con todo el poder de Skiron a "
"nuestras puertas, enfrentarnos también a las hordas de vampiros sería "
"extremadamente complicado"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:745
msgid ""
"I... acknowledge your reasoning, Lord Tewarin; Sigdral would hate me for "
"this, but the lives of thousands of dwarves and humans outweigh a vampire "
"life and a dwarf's happiness by far..."
msgstr ""
"Reconozco tu razonamiento, Señor Tewarin. Sigdral me odiaría por esto, pero "
"las vidas de miles de enanos y humanos pesan mucho más que la vida de una "
"vampira y la felicidad de una enana..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:749
msgid ""
"Wait, you can't hand Nyx over like this, she's our ally! And besides, who "
"can tell whether Erynia will really be true to her word?"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen, no pueden entregar a Nyx así, ella es nuestra aliada! Además, "
"¿quién puede asegurar que Erynia cumplirá realmente su palabra?"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:753
msgid "You insignificant vermin, how dare you question my honour?!"
msgstr "¡Insignificante alimaña, cómo te atreves a cuestionar mi honor!"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:757
msgid ""
"The boy has a point, my lords. Moreover, even if Erynia actually withdraws "
"her army, with what face will we return to our homes? Dwarves win their "
"battles with blood and sweat, not by delivering innocents to the hands of "
"monsters!"
msgstr ""
"El chico tiene razón, mis señores. Además, aunque Erynia realmente retire su "
"ejército, ¿con qué cara regresaremos a nuestros hogares? Los enanos ganan "
"sus batallas con sangre y sudor, ¡no entregando inocentes en manos de "
"monstruos"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:761
msgid ""
"The problem, my loyal Anduril, is that we may not have a home to return to, "
"should we have have too many enemies to fight..."
msgstr ""
"El problema, mi leal Anduril, es que tal vez no tengamos un hogar al que "
"regresar si tenemos demasiados enemigos a los que enfrentar.."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:765
msgid ""
"Boy, stand aside! I commend your chivalry, but you must learn that there are "
"times when we must be cold and practical for the greater good."
msgstr ""
"Chico, apártate. Alabo tu caballerosidad, pero debes aprender que hay "
"momentos en que debemos ser fríos y prácticos por el bien mayor."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:769
msgid ""
"With all due respect, Lord Tewarin, if we're going to doom innocents to save "
"ourselves, then we don't even have a right to be saved at all! If you’re "
"going to deliver Nyx to the vampires, then you'll have to kill me first, for "
"I will not let you lay a finger on her - and if you do, I'll go and take her "
"back, from Duchess Erynia's own camp if needed be!"
msgstr ""
"Con todo respeto, Señor Tewarin, si vamos a condenar a inocentes para "
"salvarnos, entonces ni siquiera tenemos derecho a ser salvados. Si van a "
"entregar a Nyx a los vampiros, tendrán que matarme primero, porque no "
"permitiré que le pongan un dedo encima, y si lo hacen, iré y la recuperaré, "
"¡incluso del campamento de la Duquesa Erynia si es necesario"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:773
msgid "Human, why...!"
msgstr "¡Humano, por qué...!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:777
msgid ""
"(angry) You fool of a boy... Lord Vindalf, care not about his youthful "
"antics; if we simply knock him down, he'll be unable to do anything..."
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Eres un tonto, chico... Señor Vindalf, no hagas caso a sus "
"travesuras juveniles. Si simplemente lo derribamos, no podrá hacer nada..."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:781
msgid ""
"No, Lord Tewarin... I sense that he really means what he's saying: he would "
"venture into the beast's mouth to rescue an innocent. As expected from a son "
"of Amunet and a heir of Myra... No, I shall not have him risk his precious "
"life; instead, I shall draw strength from his example, and win this battle "
"and the ones that follow with honour and courage!"
msgstr ""
"No, Señor Tewarin... Siento que realmente dice lo que piensa: se aventuraría "
"en la boca de la bestia para rescatar a un inocente. Como era de esperarse "
"de un hijo de Amunet y heredero de Myra... No, no permitiré que arriesgue su "
"preciosa vida. En cambio, tomaré fuerza de su ejemplo y ganaré esta batalla "
"y las que sigan con honor y coraje"

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:785
msgid ""
"Well, whatever; if this battle continues, we'll be able to butcher more "
"vampires anyway..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, lo que sea. Si esta batalla continúa, de todos modos podremos "
"masacrar más vampiros..."

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:789
msgid ""
"(furious) I too have no objection, for I now want to fight more than ever "
"before - and capture both the heiress of Aryen and the heir of the "
"despicable Myra!"
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) Yo tampoco tengo objeción, porque ahora quiero luchar más que "
"nunca, ¡y capturar tanto a la heredera de Aryen como al heredero de la "
"despreciable Myra"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:793
msgid ""
"Frankly, human, you're hard to understand, but Nyx promises that she won't "
"forget how you saved her today. Please, fight alongside me: being a mage, "
"you're vulnerable to melee attacks, so Nyx shall make anyone think twice "
"before approaching you."
msgstr ""
"Francamente, humano, eres difícil de entender, pero Nyx promete que no "
"olvidará cómo la salvaste hoy. Por favor, lucha a mi lado: siendo mago, eres "
"vulnerable a ataques cuerpo a cuerpo, así que Nyx hará que cualquiera piense "
"dos veces antes de acercarse a ti."

#. [leadership], id=nyx_protection
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:811
msgid "protected"
msgstr "protegido"

#. [leadership], id=nyx_protection
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:812
msgid "female^protection"
msgstr "protección"

#. [leadership], id=nyx_protection
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:813
msgid ""
"Akhen is now being protected by Nyx, who will fight harder when near him, "
"becoming 25% stronger."
msgstr ""
"Akhen ahora está siendo protegido por Nyx, quien luchará con más fuerza "
"cuando esté cerca de él, volviéndose 25% más fuerte."

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:835
msgid ""
"Curse you all, wretched scum! I will withdraw now, but know that your days "
"are counted; with me attacking from the north and our Skironian allies "
"attacking from the south, you shall be crushed like a beetle and vanish from "
"existence!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos sean todos, escoria miserable! Me retiraré ahora, pero sepan que "
"sus días están contados. Conmigo atacando desde el norte y nuestros aliados "
"skironianos atacando desde el sur, serán aplastados como un escarabajo y "
"desaparecerán de la existencia"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:846
msgid "No! When did the vampires ally with the Lich-Lords?"
msgstr "¡No! ¿Cuándo se aliaron los vampiros con los Señores Liche?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:850
msgid ""
"As far as we know, Stygia could have gone to Maat'Kare with Erynia as her "
"new friend already. I did find it very suspicious when she said that 'Skiron "
"would not attack'; indeed, Skiron did not attack, their allies did."
msgstr ""
"Hasta donde sabemos, Stygia podría haber ido ya a Maat'Kare con Erynia como "
"su nueva amiga. Me pareció muy sospechoso cuando dijo que «Skiron no "
"atacaría». En efecto, Skiron no atacó, fueron sus aliados"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:854
msgid "So delivering Nyx to the Duchess wouldn't have helped us in the least?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces entregar a Nyx a la Duquesa no nos habría ayudado en absoluto?"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#. [unit_type], id=Menon_Projection, race=maatkarian
#. [unit_type], id=MaatKarian Chariot, race=mechanical
#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Champion, race=washraha
#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Jackal Warrior, race=washraha
#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Lightning Striker, race=washraha, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Smiter, race=washraha, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Warrior, race=washraha
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:858
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:862
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:532
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1039
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:428
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Menon_Projection.cfg:21
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Caravan.cfg:19
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Champion.cfg:17
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Jackal_Warrior.cfg:18
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Lightning_Striker.cfg:19
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Smiter.cfg:18
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Warrior.cfg:17
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:866
msgid ""
"(sigh) Well, let's just pretend this didn't happen; Nyx is used to being "
"treated like this already."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Bueno, hagamos como si esto no hubiera pasado. Nyx ya está "
"acostumbrada a que la traten así."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:870
msgid ""
"Still, I want you to know that I am deeply ashamed for having ever "
"considered delivering you to our enemy, Nyx, and that I will do anything to "
"compensate you for that..."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, quiero que sepas que estoy profundamente avergonzado por haber "
"considerado siquiera entregarte a nuestro enemigo, Nyx, y que haré cualquier "
"cosa para compensarte por eso..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:874
msgid ""
"Then give your word that you'll let your sister go out a bit more often, and "
"I'll call it quits."
msgstr ""
"Entonces dame tu palabra de que dejarás que tu hermana salga un poco más a "
"menudo, y lo daré por terminado."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:878
msgid ""
"I... Well, I give you my word that I will. Now, I'd like to invite you back "
"to my caves, where my healers shall tend to your wounds and serve you food; "
"afterwards, we must resume our meeting."
msgstr ""
"Yo... Bueno, te doy mi palabra de que lo haré. Ahora, me gustaría invitarte "
"de regreso a mis cuevas, donde mis sanadores atenderán tus heridas y te "
"servirán comida. Después, debemos reanudar nuestra reunión."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:882
msgid "So, human, about Nyx's very special needs..."
msgstr "Entonces, humano, sobre las necesidades muy especiales de Nyx..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:886
msgid "Uh, what...?"
msgstr "Eh, ¿qué...?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:890
msgid ""
"Well, since you've saved Nyx, you should take responsibility for her, as a "
"man ought to do. For a start, she needs sustenance in the form of copious "
"amount of raw, bloody, fresh meat."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, como salvaste a Nyx, deberías tomar responsabilidad por ella, como "
"debe hacer un hombre. Para empezar, necesita sustento en forma de una "
"cantidad copiosa de carne cruda, sangrienta y fresca."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:894
msgid "So now you want to follow him indefinitely? Over my dead body you will!"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces ahora quieres seguirlo indefinidamente? ¡Sobre mi cadáver lo harás!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:898
msgid ""
"Worry not, missy, as Nyx has already told you, she's not stealing your man; "
"even if she wanted to, it wouldn't work. Humans and vampires can't even have "
"babies together, after all, and I'm sure a vigorous young scion such as him "
"wishes to sire many new scions of his noble bloodline."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, señorita, como Nyx ya te dijo, no te está robando a tu "
"hombre. Aunque quisiera, no funcionaría. Los humanos y los vampiros ni "
"siquiera pueden tener bebés juntos, después de todo, y estoy segura de que "
"un vigoroso joven vástago como él desea engendrar muchos nuevos vástagos de "
"su noble linaje."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:902
msgid "(red) W-what are you babbling about, it has nothing to do with that..."
msgstr "(roja) ¿Q-qué estás balbuceando, eso no tiene nada que ver con eso..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:906
msgid ""
"Well, I see no problem in her coming with us; maybe the folks back home "
"won't like having a vampiress near them, but they can't complain if she "
"stays at my house."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no veo problema en que venga con nosotros. Tal vez a la gente de casa "
"no le guste tener una vampira cerca, pero no pueden quejarse si se queda en "
"mi casa."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:910
msgid ""
"Good! Now, since Nyx has nothing to offer but her blade, she also needs the "
"finest dwarf-crafted swords and the supplest enchanted leather armour. She "
"also needs good rest; contrary to what you may believe, our undeath does not "
"come with endless stamina. An ample bedroom sheltered from the sun, with a "
"lord's bed cushioned with swan feathers, will suffice."
msgstr ""
"¡Bien! Ahora, como Nyx no tiene nada que ofrecer más que su espada, también "
"necesita las mejores espadas forjadas por enanos y la armadura de cuero "
"encantada más suave. También necesita buen descanso. Contrario a lo que "
"puedan creer, nuestra no-muerte no viene con resistencia infinita. Una "
"habitación amplia protegida del sol, con una cama de señor acolchada con "
"plumas de cisne, será suficiente."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:914
msgid "(shaking head) Oh my..."
msgstr "(sacudiendo la cabeza) Dios mío..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:918
msgid ""
"(smiling) Akhen, I want to tell you that I'm truly impressed for what you "
"did today, and not to worry about my uncle; he may look sullen, but in "
"reality he is approving of what you did."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Akhen, quiero decirte que estoy realmente impresionada por lo "
"que hiciste hoy, y no te preocupes por mi tío. Puede verse malhumorado, pero "
"en realidad aprueba lo que hiciste."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:922
msgid ""
"Well, he just wanted to do what he deemed best for us all, so it's fine. "
"Now, let's follow the others into the caves."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, solo quería hacer lo que consideraba mejor para todos, así que está "
"bien. Ahora, sigamos a los demás a las cuevas."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:945
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1277
msgid "Uncle, NO!"
msgstr "¡Tío, NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:949
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1281
msgid "Ack! How could I have fallen like this...?"
msgstr "¡Ack! ¿Cómo pude caer así...?"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:963
msgid "Alas, I have fallen... Anduril, please help Sigdral lead our people..."
msgstr ""
"Lamentablemente, he caído... Anduril, por favor ayuda a Sigdral a liderar a "
"nuestro pueblo..."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:967
msgid "Milord, you can't die now, only you can lead us!"
msgstr "¡Milord, no puedes morir ahora, solo tú puedes liderarnos!"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:981
msgid "Apologies, Lord Vindalf, but I may continue no longer..."
msgstr "Disculpas, Señor Vindalf, pero no puedo continuar más..."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:985
msgid "Anduril, no! The Aigathol need your advice in this war!"
msgstr "¡Anduril, no! ¡Los Aigathol necesitan tu consejo en esta guerra!"

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:999
msgid "Curse these vampires! Friends, fight on without me..."
msgstr "¡Malditos vampiros! Amigos, continúen luchando sin mí..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:1003
msgid ""
"This is a disaster! Because we let him die, I doubt that the wargs will "
"remain on our side!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es un desastre! Porque lo dejamos morir, dudo que los huargos se "
"mantengan de nuestro lado"

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:1017
msgid "Aaarrgghhh! To die alongside humans and dirty traitors..."
msgstr "¡Aaarrgghhh! Morir junto a humanos y sucios traidores..."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:1021
msgid ""
"He might have been an insufferable warg, but with his fall here the "
"Warglanders will suspect treachery, and will certainly wage war on us and "
"and the Maat'karians!"
msgstr ""
"Puede que haya sido un huargo insufrible, pero con su caída aquí los "
"Warglanders sospecharán traición y sin duda declararán la guerra contra "
"nosotros y los maat'karianos"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/06_Spark_Of_Violence.cfg:1032
msgid ""
"We're taking far too much time to defeat Erynia! Now, her forces grow larger "
"with reinforcements, while ours get increasingly depleted!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estamos tardando demasiado en derrotar a Erynia! Ahora sus fuerzas crecen "
"más con refuerzos, mientras que las nuestras se debilitan cada vez más"

#. [scenario], id=07_Foundation_Stone
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:4
msgid "Foundation Stone"
msgstr "Piedra Fundacional"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:22
msgid "Find the fortress of Grimbek"
msgstr "Encuentra la fortaleza de Grimbek"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:52
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:419
msgid "HINT: Time is of the essence; go west as quickly as you can!"
msgstr "PISTA: El tiempo es esencial. ¡Ve al oeste lo más rápido posible!"

#. [side], type=Orcish Sorcerer
#. [unit], id=Varag, type=Orcish Sorcerer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:90
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:69
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:778
msgid "Varag"
msgstr "Varag"

#. [side], type=Orcish Sorcerer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:95
msgid "Varag's Orcs"
msgstr "Orcos de Varag"

#. [side], type=Orcish Slurbow
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:114
msgid "Gigor"
msgstr "Gigor"

#. [side], type=Orcish Slurbow
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:119
msgid "Gigor's Orcs"
msgstr "Orcos de Gigor"

#. [side], type=General SK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:142
msgid "General Skotas"
msgstr "General Skotas"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:227
msgid ""
"So these are the Orc's Lands... When I was a child, I used to hear tales "
"that described this region as a barren wasteland, but in reality it seems "
"quite pleasant."
msgstr ""
"Entonces estas son las Tierras de los Orcos... Cuando era niña solía "
"escuchar cuentos que describían esta región como un páramo estéril, pero en "
"realidad parece bastante agradable."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:231
msgid ""
"The tales we usually hear about the orcs are often exaggerated; they're "
"belligerent and ruthless, but they also have some sort of very interesting "
"warrior's code."
msgstr ""
"Los cuentos que solemos oír sobre los orcos suelen estar exagerados. Son "
"belicosos y despiadados, pero también tienen una especie de código de "
"guerrero muy interesante."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:235
msgid ""
"I've read that, if you defeat them in battle, they'll actually respect you "
"very much, and may even become your allies. Well, at least that was how Myra "
"got many of them to ally with Maat'Kare, in the past."
msgstr ""
"He leído que si los derrotas en batalla, en realidad te respetarán mucho y "
"hasta pueden convertirse en tus aliados. Bueno, al menos así fue como Myra "
"logró que muchos de ellos se aliaran con Maat'Kare en el pasado."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:239
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, we better not expect any friendship from them, especially from "
"Varag. He has many reasons to hate humans, in case you have forgotten."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, es mejor que no esperemos amistad de ellos, especialmente de "
"Varag. Tiene muchas razones para odiar a los humanos, por si lo olvidaron."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:243
msgid ""
"Indeed; after all, we and the Skironians mercilessly crushed the army he'd "
"prepared with such love and care..."
msgstr ""
"En efecto. Después de todo, nosotros y los skironianos aplastamos sin piedad "
"el ejército que él había preparado con tanto amor y cuidado..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:247
msgid ""
"(sniffing the air) Watch out, folks, I smell orcs nearby... and also "
"something far more stinking, like corpses..."
msgstr ""
"(olfateando el aire) Cuidado, gente, huelo orcos cerca... y también algo "
"mucho más apestoso, como cadáveres..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:251
msgid ""
"So Skiron has reached this region already... Onwards, soldiers! We must take "
"Grimbek and secure it!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces Skiron ya ha llegado a esta región... ¡Adelante, soldados! ¡Debemos "
"tomar Grimbek y asegurarla!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:276
msgid ""
"Um, Sigdral, there's something I wanted to ask you since the meeting at the "
"Hall of Auroghar..."
msgstr ""
"Um, Sigdral, hay algo que quería preguntarte desde la reunión en el Salón de "
"Auroghar..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:280
msgid "Ask away."
msgstr "Pregunta."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:284
msgid ""
"Back then, I noticed that, when Argatyr's representative said that his lord "
"had decided not to come, you said something about him 'not overcoming' "
"something..."
msgstr ""
"En ese entonces noté que cuando el representante de Argatyr dijo que su "
"señor había decidido no venir, dijiste algo sobre que él «no había superado» "
"algo..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:288
msgid ""
"Ah, that. (giggles) Well, the truth is that he's still mad at me because I "
"forced him to dissolve our marriage; he wanted me to be a good, traditional "
"dwarf wife, but you know me, I'm incapable of living like that."
msgstr ""
"Ah, eso. (ríe) Bueno, la verdad es que todavía está enojado conmigo porque "
"lo obligué a disolver nuestro matrimonio. Él quería que fuera una buena "
"esposa enana tradicional, pero ya me conoces, soy incapaz de vivir así."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:292
msgid ""
"(astonished) Y-you were married to Lord Argatyr?! But... I heard he's quite "
"aged already!"
msgstr ""
"(asombrada) ¡¿Tú estabas casada con el Señor Argatyr?! Pero... ¡escuché que "
"ya está bastante mayor!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:296
msgid "He is, but I'm not a young dwarf any more either..."
msgstr "Lo está, pero yo tampoco soy una enana joven ya..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:300
msgid "Come on, you can't be that old!"
msgstr "Vamos, ¡no puedes ser tan vieja!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:304
msgid ""
"Female dwarves age a little differently than males; they develop beards and "
"get craggy skin quite early, while we look youthful for far longer. "
"Something to do with our different lifestyles, most likely."
msgstr ""
"Las enanas envejecen un poco diferente que los varones. Desarrollan barba y "
"piel rugosa bastante temprano, mientras que nosotras lucimos juveniles por "
"mucho más tiempo. Probablemente algo relacionado con nuestros diferentes "
"estilos de vida."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:308
msgid "So, what's your real age?"
msgstr "¿Entonces cuál es tu edad real?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:312
msgid "(giggling) I'm fifty-winters-old."
msgstr "(riendo) Tengo cincuenta inviernos."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:316
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/16_Burning_Ice.cfg:386
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:860
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:352
msgid "!!!"
msgstr "!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:325
msgid "So, if you're fifty, then Nyx is...?"
msgstr "Entonces, si tú tienes cincuenta, ¿Nyx tiene...?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:329
msgid ""
"If you wish to know her age so much, know that Nyx has graced the world with "
"her existence for forty-three winters already."
msgstr ""
"Si tanto deseas saber su edad, sepan que Nyx ha honrado al mundo con su "
"existencia durante cuarenta y tres inviernos ya."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:333
msgid ""
"(raising eyebrows) I see, I really thought you had a more... 'seasoned' air "
"about you."
msgstr ""
"(levantando las cejas) Ya veo, realmente pensaba que tenías un aire más... "
"«experimentado»."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:337
msgid "But, you know, some lads do prefer seasoned women..."
msgstr "Pero, sabes, algunos muchachos prefieren mujeres experimentadas..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:341
msgid "(angry) And what is that supposed to mean?"
msgstr "(enojada) ¿Y eso qué se supone que significa?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:355
msgid ""
"So this is the fortress of Grimbek? It's an outstanding fortification "
"indeed... Was it really built by the orcs?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces esta es la fortaleza de Grimbek? Es una fortificación realmente "
"impresionante... ¿Realmente fue construida por los orcos?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:359
msgid ""
"Actually, it was designed and built by dwarves who were being held captives "
"by them, and, although it has been conquered by other nations in the past "
"countless times, it has never been used by anyone other than orcs for long."
msgstr ""
"En realidad, fue diseñada y construida por enanos que eran mantenidos como "
"cautivos por ellos, y aunque ha sido conquistada por otras naciones "
"innumerables veces en el pasado, nunca ha sido usada por nadie más que orcos "
"por mucho tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:363
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:544
msgid "Why?"
msgstr "¿Por qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:367
msgid ""
"(smiling) See, we dwarves are a people who never yields to slavery, and so "
"we'd never meekly obey any would-be master. While those captives were "
"building this fortress, they made sure that it would have many disguised "
"weaknesses that any keen commander would notice. Everyone in Netjer-Ta knows "
"that, as do some cleverer orcish chieftains, but most orcs still see Grimbek "
"as an invincible fortress, even though it's been conquered dozens of times "
"already."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Verán, nosotros los enanos somos un pueblo que nunca se somete a "
"la esclavitud, por eso nunca obedeceríamos mansamente a ningún supuesto amo. "
"Mientras esos cautivos construían esta fortaleza, se aseguraron de que "
"tuviera muchas debilidades disfrazadas que cualquier comandante astuto "
"notaría. Todos en Netjer-Ta lo saben, al igual que algunos jefes orcos más "
"listos, pero la mayoría de los orcos todavía ven a Grimbek como una "
"fortaleza invencible, aunque ha sido conquistada docenas de veces ya."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:371
msgid ""
"And this is the fortress we're supposed to use to control western Netjer-Ta?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y esta es la fortaleza que se supone que debemos usar para controlar el "
"oeste de Netjer-Ta?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:375
msgid ""
"Obviously we will repair its weaknesses, to make it truly powerful; I've "
"read the reports of past missions about Grimbek's flaws, correcting them "
"won't be a hard task."
msgstr ""
"Obviamente repararemos sus debilidades para hacerla realmente poderosa. He "
"leído los informes de misiones pasadas sobre las fallas de Grimbek, "
"corregirlas no será una tarea difícil."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:379
msgid ""
"By the way, didn't you say that there was an orcish chieftain sitting on it? "
"Because this fortress is completely empty..."
msgstr ""
"Por cierto, ¿no dijiste que había un jefe orco sentado en ella? Porque esta "
"fortaleza está completamente vacía..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:383
msgid ""
"I think the orcs, or maybe the Skironians, have scared Varag out of it, but "
"our mission is still far from over: we must now vanquish any enemy around "
"this region, to truly secure Grimbek; if the enemy is too strong, we could "
"attract them here and use these fortifications to our advantage."
msgstr ""
"Creo que los orcos, o tal vez los skironianos, asustaron a Varag y lo "
"sacaron de allí, pero nuestra misión todavía está lejos de terminar: ahora "
"debemos vencer a cualquier enemigo alrededor de esta región para asegurar "
"realmente Grimbek. Si el enemigo es demasiado fuerte, podríamos atraerlos "
"aquí y usar estas fortificaciones a nuestro favor."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:389
msgid "Investigate further westwards for possible Skironian enemies"
msgstr "Investiga más al oeste en busca de posibles enemigos skironianos"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:468
msgid ""
"At long last! I thought we would never find them; today Nyx shall finally "
"have some fresh blood..."
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin! Pensaba que nunca los encontraríamos. Hoy Nyx por fin tendrá "
"sangre fresca..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:472
msgid ""
"Um, I may be wrong, but the banner of the chieftain that's near the river is "
"the same as the one that belonged to the orcs we fought in the Silent "
"Desert..."
msgstr ""
"Um, puede que me equivoque, pero el estandarte del jefe que está cerca del "
"río es el mismo que pertenecía a los orcos con los que luchamos en el "
"Desierto Silencioso..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:476
msgid "No, you're right, those are Varag's orcs."
msgstr "No, tienes razón, esos son los orcos de Varag."

#. [message], speaker=Gigor
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:480
msgid ""
"Ha! We got you now, you puny old coot! Don't even try using your tricks on "
"us, they will only get you a bloodier death!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Ahora te tenemos, viejo enclenque! Ni siquiera intentes usar tus "
"trucos con nosotros, solo te conseguirán una muerte más sangrienta."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:484
msgid ""
"Damn you, bunch of morons! Can't you see that, if we keep brawling amongst "
"ourselves, we'll all be butchered by those stupid southerners?! It's because "
"of dung-headed animals like you that orc-kind has always been everyone "
"else's punching bag!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos sean, pandilla de idiotas! ¿No ven que si seguimos peleando entre "
"nosotros, todos seremos masacrados por esos estúpidos sureños? ¡Es por "
"animales de cabeza de estiércol como ustedes que la raza orca siempre ha "
"sido el saco de golpes de todos los demás!"

#. [message], speaker=Skotas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:488
msgid ""
"It doesn't matter how many swords you raise, all who dare defy the might of "
"Skiron shall be crushed - and make no mistake: you shall not receive the "
"blessing of un-death from me!"
msgstr ""
"No importa cuántas espadas levanten, todos los que se atrevan a desafiar el "
"poder de Skiron serán aplastados, y que no haya error: ¡no recibirán la "
"bendición de la no-muerte de mí!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:492
msgid "'Blessing', he says... No kidding, is there no end to their insanity?"
msgstr "«Bendición», dice... Sin broma, ¿no hay fin a su locura?"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:496
msgid ""
"(noticing the Maat'Karians) Oh, damn you, stinking Maat'Karians! What the "
"hell is wrong with you, for you to always show up at the worst possible "
"time?!"
msgstr ""
"(notando a los maat'karianos) ¡Oh, malditos sean, apestosos maat'karianos! "
"¿Qué demonios les pasa para que siempre aparezcan en el peor momento posible?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:500
msgid ""
"(licking her lips) Nyx has no interest in that wrecked old orc, but she "
"wants the larger warriors; their blood is surprisingly tasty..."
msgstr ""
"(lamiéndose los labios) Nyx no tiene interés en ese viejo orco destrozado, "
"pero quiere a los guerreros más grandes. Su sangre es sorprendentemente "
"sabrosa..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:504
msgid ""
"Chief Varag, why such sharp words? We come here not to fight you, but to "
"help defending our precious Netjer-Ta from these Argean invaders!"
msgstr ""
"Jefe Varag, ¿por qué palabras tan afiladas? No venimos aquí a luchar contra "
"ti, sino a ayudar a defender nuestro precioso Netjer-Ta de estos invasores "
"argeanos."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:508
msgid ""
"If that's true, then you can have them as you wish; do not attack my "
"warriors, and I will not attack yours."
msgstr ""
"Si eso es cierto, entonces puedes tenerlos como desees. No ataques a mis "
"guerreros y yo no atacaré a los tuyos."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:512
msgid "(sullen) Atenak, you did that on purpose, didn't you?"
msgstr "(malhumorada) Atenak, lo hiciste a propósito, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:516
msgid ""
"I have an idea, but I need Varag alive for that... And don't be upset, Nyx, "
"you still have that other orcish clan and the living Skironian soldiers to "
"feast yourself on."
msgstr ""
"Tengo una idea, pero necesito a Varag vivo para eso... Y no te molestes, "
"Nyx, todavía tienes ese otro clan orco y a los soldados skironianos vivos "
"para darte un festín."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:527
msgid "Defeat Gigor and Skotas"
msgstr "Derrota a Gigor y Skotas"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:555
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:934
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1074
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1189
msgid "Death of Varag"
msgstr "Muerte de Varag"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:583
msgid ""
"Say, Chief Varag, you seem to be in quite a pinch there, even though we've "
"relieved you from the brunt of the attack; if you wish, we could help you..."
msgstr ""
"Dime, Jefe Varag, pareces estar en un buen aprieto allí, aunque te hemos "
"aliviado del grueso del ataque. Si lo deseas, podríamos ayudarte..."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:587
msgid ""
"...In exchange for my loyalty, right? You humans always do that, thinking us "
"to be all like that ancient idiot, Ogesh, but this won't work with this orc "
"here, so give up!"
msgstr ""
"...A cambio de mi lealtad, ¿verdad? Ustedes los humanos siempre hacen eso, "
"pensando que todos somos como ese antiguo idiota, Ogesh, pero esto no "
"funcionará con este orco aquí, ¡así que rindanse!"

#. [message], speaker=Gigor
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:591
msgid ""
"Damn, that puny old coot is more stubborn than I thought... Blood and gore, "
"send in the hell-damned reinforcements!"
msgstr ""
"Maldición, ese viejo enclenque es más terco de lo que pensaba... Sangre y "
"vísceras, ¡enviad los malditos refuerzos!"

#. [message], speaker=Skotas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:601
msgid ""
"Oh, really? Well then, if it's violence that you want, that violence you "
"shall have: Noxes, summon the Elite Four!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, ¿en serio? Bueno, si es violencia lo que quieren, violencia tendrán: "
"Noxes, ¡invoca a los Cuatro de Élite!"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:615
msgid ""
"What the hell...?! Argh... All right, all right, with a thousand curses, "
"please help me, and I'll do whatever the hell you want!"
msgstr ""
"¡Qué demonios...?! Argh... Está bien, está bien, con mil maldiciones, por "
"favor ayúdenme y haré lo que demonios quieran."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:619
msgid ""
"Really? But you were so categorical in your refusal, I'm not sure whether I "
"have enough men to spare now..."
msgstr ""
"En serio? Pero estabas tan categórico en tu rechazo, no estoy segura de si "
"tengo suficientes hombres para destinar ahora..."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:623
msgid "Damn you, brat! Will you really make me beg on my knees?!"
msgstr "¡Maldita seas, mocosa! ¿De verdad me vas a hacer rogar de rodillas?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:627
msgid ""
"Pardon me, I just wanted to make sure that you truly wanted our aid. "
"Maat'Karians, the plans are still the same: let us clear this region of "
"Skironians and orcs, and make sure that Varag is alive at the end of this "
"battle!"
msgstr ""
"Disculpen, solo quería asegurarme de que realmente querías nuestra ayuda. "
"Maat'karianos, los planes siguen siendo los mismos: limpiemos esta región de "
"skironianos y orcos, y asegurémonos de que Varag esté vivo al final de esta "
"batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Noxes
#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:646
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:563
msgid "No...!"
msgstr "¡No...!"

#. [message], speaker=Skotas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:650
msgid "The undead!"
msgstr "¡Los no-muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Skotas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:661
msgid "You'll pay for that, Maat'Karians!"
msgstr "¡La pagarán por eso, maat'karianos!"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:670
msgid "Argh, as much as it displeases me, I must thank your aid..."
msgstr "Argh, por más que me desagrade, debo agradecer su ayuda..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:674
msgid ""
"Chief Varag, there's no need for such hostility, for we truly stand here as "
"friends. Come, we haven't been properly introduced to each other: I am "
"Atenak Aracyne, and I command this expedition on behalf of Lord Tewarin "
"Aracyne."
msgstr ""
"Jefe Varag, no hay necesidad de tanta hostilidad, porque realmente estamos "
"aquí como amigos. Ven, no nos hemos presentado correctamente: soy Atenak "
"Aracyne y comando esta expedición en nombre del Señor Tewarin Aracyne."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:678
msgid ""
"And I am Varag, son of Eragor, chieftain of the Burning Fang clan, the main "
"keepers of Orc-kind's lore, responsible for recording our people’s History, "
"and the only authority that can unite all the clans in times of crisis... Or "
"so it used to be, before every chieftain decided to piss on our traditions "
"and look after their own arses alone."
msgstr ""
"Y yo soy Varag, hijo de Eragor, jefe del clan Colmillo Ardiente, los "
"principales guardianes del saber de la raza orca, responsables de registrar "
"la Historia de nuestro pueblo y la única autoridad que puede unir a todos "
"los clanes en tiempos de crisis... O al menos eso era antes de que cada jefe "
"decidiera orinar sobre nuestras tradiciones y cuidar solo su propio trasero."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Still, you had managed to amass quite a large army some time ago, didn't you?"
msgstr ""
"Aun así, lograste reunir un ejército bastante grande hace algún tiempo, "
"¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:686
msgid ""
"Those were the last remaining clans that were loyal to us, but an unexpected "
"attack by the cursed southern humans destroyed our great army..."
msgstr ""
"Esos eran los últimos clanes que nos eran leales, pero un ataque inesperado "
"de los malditos humanos del sur destruyó nuestro gran ejército..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:690
msgid "Erm, well... That's lamentable, really..."
msgstr "Eh, bueno... Eso es lamentable, de verdad..."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:694
msgid ""
"Right, we have introduced ourselves, now tell me: why exactly have you come "
"here?"
msgstr ""
"Bien, nos hemos presentado, ahora dime: ¿exactamente por qué han venido aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:698
msgid ""
"I'll speak frankly, Chief Varag: originally, our mission was to conquer "
"Grimbek and wipe out any enemy faction around this area, including yours. "
"However, I now think that it'd be far more advantageous for us both if we "
"became allies. You have already seen by yourself that Skiron shall not spare "
"anyone in Netjer-Ta; if your clan joins our alliance, we may be able to help "
"you again, and we would have an ally protecting western Netjer-Ta."
msgstr ""
"Hablaré con franqueza, Jefe Varag: originalmente nuestra misión era "
"conquistar Grimbek y eliminar cualquier facción enemiga alrededor de esta "
"zona, incluida la tuya. Sin embargo, ahora pienso que sería mucho más "
"ventajoso para ambos si nos convertimos en aliados. Ya has visto por ti "
"mismo que Skiron no perdonará a nadie en Netjer-Ta. Si tu clan se une a "
"nuestra alianza, podremos ayudarte de nuevo y tendríamos un aliado "
"protegiendo el oeste de Netjer-Ta."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:702
msgid ""
"Your proposal is very interesting in theory, but, firstly, I'm not sure "
"whether my clan, or any of our remaining allies, will like the idea of being "
"friends with humans; and secondly, we can't be sure ourselves that Maat'Kare "
"will really help us if we need it."
msgstr ""
"Tu propuesta es muy interesante en teoría, pero primero no estoy seguro de "
"si a mi clan o a alguno de nuestros aliados restantes les gustará la idea de "
"ser amigos de los humanos. Y segundo, nosotros mismos no podemos estar "
"seguros de que Maat'Kare realmente nos ayude si lo necesitamos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:706
msgid ""
"We're aware of the mutual distrust between our peoples, but I ask you to "
"remember how our Founder and my ancestor, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, was "
"friendly to Emperor Ogesh and his people. It's truly unfortunate that we "
"couldn't remain as friends after their deaths."
msgstr ""
"Somos conscientes de la desconfianza mutua entre nuestros pueblos, pero te "
"pido que recuerdes cómo nuestra Fundadora y mi ancestra, Myra de "
"Hiera'Shirsha, fue amistosa con el Emperador Ogesh y su pueblo. Es realmente "
"lamentable que no pudiéramos permanecer como amigos después de sus muertes."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:710
msgid ""
"(impressed) So you're a descendant of that woman? Interesting... You may "
"ignore it, Maat'Karians, but, human as she was, Myra is remembered as a "
"great heroine by many orcish clans: she's the Friend-of-Orcs, who bashed the "
"skulls of Hagash the Treacherous and of that bird-lord who tried to control "
"this continent..."
msgstr ""
"(impresionado) ¿Entonces eres descendiente de esa mujer? Interesante... "
"Pueden ignorarlo, maat'karianos, pero, humana como era, Myra es recordada "
"como una gran heroína por muchos clanes orcos: es la Amiga-de-los-Orcos, que "
"aplastó los cráneos de Hagash el Traidor y de ese señor de los pájaros que "
"intentó controlar este continente..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:714
msgid "(whisper) They've really adapted her tale to their style, after all..."
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Realmente adaptaron su historia a su estilo, después de todo..."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:718
msgid ""
"Well, Maat'Karians, after better reflecting on the subject, I've decided "
"that the Burning Fang shall join your alliance. Don't worry about my people, "
"they'll do as I tell them; but I can't assure you that other clans will "
"accept being your allies too."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, maat'karianos, después de reflexionar mejor sobre el asunto, he "
"decidido que el Colmillo Ardiente se unirá a su alianza. No se preocupen por "
"mi gente, harán lo que yo les diga. Pero no puedo asegurarles que otros "
"clanes acepten ser sus aliados también."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:722
msgid ""
"Chief Varag, I'd like to add that I don't wish this alliance to be only as "
"long-lived as this war; rather, I hope this is the foundation stone of a "
"solid friendship between humans and orcs."
msgstr ""
"Jefe Varag, me gustaría agregar que no deseo que esta alianza dure solo lo "
"que dure esta guerra. Más bien, espero que esta sea la piedra fundacional de "
"una amistad sólida entre humanos y orcos."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:726
msgid ""
"Well spoken, girl. Now, over with the chatter; the enemy can attack again at "
"any time, and so we must repair and reequip Grimbek."
msgstr ""
"Bien dicho, chica. Ahora, basta de charla. El enemigo puede atacar de nuevo "
"en cualquier momento, así que debemos reparar y reequipar Grimbek."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:730
msgid ""
"(in private) That was a great idea, Atenak, to get them to be our friends "
"instead of just killing them all."
msgstr ""
"(en privado) Esa fue una gran idea, Atenak, hacer que sean nuestros amigos "
"en lugar de simplemente matarlos a todos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:734
msgid ""
"(smiling) Well, I just remembered how your sparing of that vampiress in "
"Khaset and then again in the battle against Erynia won us a strong ally, and "
"so I decided to try it myself."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Bueno, solo recordé cómo tu decisión de perdonar a esa vampira "
"en Khaset y luego de nuevo en la batalla contra Erynia nos ganó una fuerte "
"aliada, así que decidí intentarlo yo misma."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:738
msgid "(sigh) And in the end Nyx could barely get a single sip of blood..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Y al final Nyx apenas pudo tomar un sorbo de sangre..."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:753
msgid "Argh! Curse all these imbeciles..."
msgstr "¡Argh! Malditos todos estos imbéciles..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:757
msgid "That's not good, he would have been a precious ally for us!"
msgstr "Eso no es bueno, ¡él habría sido un aliado precioso para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/07_Foundation_Stone.cfg:768
msgid ""
"We should have finished these enemies earlier, now that they're getting "
"reinforcements it will be much harder to vanquish them!"
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos haber terminado con estos enemigos antes. Ahora que están "
"recibiendo refuerzos será mucho más difícil vencerlos."

#. [scenario], id=08_Crimson_Ice
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:4
msgid "Crimson Ice"
msgstr "Hielo Carmesí"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:23
msgid "Find the entrance to the caves in the northeast"
msgstr "Encuentra la entrada a las cuevas en el noreste"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:51
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:539
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:51
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:330
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:393
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:598
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:687
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:779
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:946
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:52
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:670
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:488
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:56
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:534
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:930
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1070
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1185
msgid "Death of Gomatol"
msgstr "Muerte de Gomatol"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:55
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:543
msgid ""
"Sighting of Maat'Karians and dwarves by the vampires of the southeastern town"
msgstr ""
"Avistamiento de maat'karianos y enanos por los vampiros de la ciudad del "
"sureste"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:61
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:549
msgid ""
"You may recruit dwarvish units for this scenario and the next; afterwards "
"they'll only be available to you in certain scenarios"
msgstr ""
"Puedes reclutar unidades enanas para este escenario y el siguiente; después "
"solo estarán disponibles para ti en ciertos escenarios"

#. [side], type=Sire
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:90
msgid "Lord Damien"
msgstr "Señor Damien"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:160
msgid "Wilderness"
msgstr "Tierras salvajes"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:267
msgid ""
"(trembling in cold) Hey guys, how far are we from the Red Pinnacle? I mean, "
"we've been wandering these mountains for nearly a month already, and still "
"we haven't even spotted that city..."
msgstr ""
"(temblando de frío) Oigan chicos, ¿qué tan lejos estamos del Pináculo Rojo? "
"Quiero decir, hemos estado vagando por estas montañas durante casi un mes y "
"todavía ni siquiera hemos avistado esa ciudad..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:271
msgid ""
"We wouldn't be taking so long if you hadn't slowed us down, but I mustn't "
"complain, for you and this vampiress of yours have been of  great aid to us "
"so far..."
msgstr ""
"No estaríamos tardando tanto si no nos hubieran retrasado, pero no debo "
"quejarme, porque tú y esta vampira tuya nos han sido de gran ayuda hasta "
"ahora..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:275
msgid ""
"(whispers) Now Nyx understands why you couldn't live with the Motsoghnir for "
"long, Sigdral, they're simply obnoxious..."
msgstr ""
"(susurra) Ahora Nyx entiende por qué no pudiste vivir mucho tiempo con los "
"Motsoghnir, Sigdral, simplemente son odiosos..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:279
msgid ""
"...According to our maps, the Red Pinnacle is just beyond those huge "
"mountains to the east; unfortunately, the caves known to us end here, so "
"we'll have to risk ourselves on the surface again. But if we go through that "
"valley to the southeast..."
msgstr ""
"...Según nuestros mapas, el Pináculo Rojo está justo más allá de esas "
"enormes montañas al este. Desafortunadamente, las cuevas que conocemos "
"terminan aquí, así que tendremos que arriesgarnos en la superficie de nuevo. "
"Pero si vamos por ese valle al sureste..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:283
msgid ""
"Forget about going that way, there's a vampire town there. We should go "
"northeast; it will cost us more time, but Nyx knows an entrance to a natural "
"cave system that goes beneath those huge mountains to the north and the "
"northeast."
msgstr ""
"Olviden ir por ese camino, hay una ciudad de vampiros allí. Deberíamos ir al "
"noreste. Nos costará más tiempo, pero Nyx conoce una entrada a un sistema de "
"cuevas naturales que pasa por debajo de esas enormes montañas al norte y al "
"noreste."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:287
msgid "And will those tunnels take us nearer the Red Pinnacle?"
msgstr "¿Y esos túneles nos llevarán más cerca del Pináculo Rojo?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:291
msgid ""
"Better, it'll take us to the Red Pinnacle's own undergrounds. See, when Nyx "
"was a child, she used to play with the Malborn - or newly-infected - youths "
"of that city. Because they are considered a lower class in vampire society, "
"they got used to living underground, and so, by hanging out with them, Nyx "
"explored the Pinnacle's sewers, which happen to be connected to the caves "
"she's just mentioned."
msgstr ""
"Mejor aún, nos llevará a los subterráneos del propio Pináculo Rojo. Verán, "
"cuando Nyx era niña, solía jugar con los Malborn (o recién infectados) "
"jóvenes de esa ciudad. Como se les considera una clase inferior en la "
"sociedad vampírica, se acostumbraron a vivir bajo tierra y, al pasar tiempo "
"con ellos, Nyx exploró las alcantarillas del Pináculo, que casualmente están "
"conectadas con las cuevas que acabo de mencionar."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:295
msgid ""
"I see; but won't the Malborns who live in the sewers find us and alert the "
"others?"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo, pero ¿los Malborn que viven en las alcantarillas no nos "
"encontrarán y alertarán a los demás?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:299
msgid ""
"No, because they no longer dwell there; they were all banished from the Red "
"Pinnacle by Erynia, who saw them as too unworthy of living even in the "
"sewers of her precious city."
msgstr ""
"No, porque ya no viven allí. Todos fueron desterrados del Pináculo Rojo por "
"Erynia, quien los consideraba demasiado indignos incluso para vivir en las "
"alcantarillas de su preciosa ciudad."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:303
msgid ""
"I see... And, if we're caught and attacked, we'll be able to use the sewers' "
"narrowness to compensate our lesser numbers. I just hope that we're not "
"sighted before we reach those caves..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Y si nos descubren y atacan, podremos usar la estrechez de las "
"alcantarillas para compensar nuestro menor número. Solo espero que no nos "
"avisten antes de llegar a esas cuevas..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:307
msgid ""
"Keep your senses alert, for there may be hunting parties, wolves and "
"minotaurs around this region."
msgstr ""
"Mantengan sus sentidos alerta, porque puede haber partidas de caza, lobos y "
"minotauros en esta región."

#. [unit], id=Arion, type=Twilight Walker
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:326
msgid "Arion"
msgstr "Arion"

#. [message], speaker=Arion
#. [message], speaker=Tainn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:348
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:424
msgid ""
"What the hell is happening here... How did this enemy troop manage to reach "
"this region?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué demonios está pasando aquí...? ¿Cómo logró esta tropa enemiga llegar a "
"esta región?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:352
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:428
msgid "Damn it, when did they build this outpost...?"
msgstr "Maldición, ¿cuándo construyeron este puesto avanzado...?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:356
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:432
msgid ""
"We must kill them all before they have the chance to go alert their comrades!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debemos matarlos a todos antes de que tengan la oportunidad de alertar a "
"sus compañeros!"

#. [message], speaker=Arion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:362
msgid ""
"I was right to suspect some enemy treachery when I heard all that noise from "
"Tainn's outpost... Armand, go quickly to Lord Damien and warn him of this "
"surprise attack!"
msgstr ""
"Tenía razón al sospechar alguna traición enemiga cuando escuché todo ese "
"ruido desde el puesto de Tainn... ¡Armand, ve rápido al Señor Damien y "
"avísale de este ataque sorpresa!"

#. [unit], id=Armand, type=Day Hunter
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:368
msgid "Armand"
msgstr "Armand"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:379
msgid "Damn it... Someone get that vampire before he reaches the damned city!"
msgstr ""
"Maldición... ¡Que alguien atrape a ese vampiro antes de que llegue a la "
"maldita ciudad!"

#. [unit], id=Tainn, type=Sword Dancer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:402
msgid "Tainn"
msgstr "Tainn"

#. [message], speaker=Tainn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:438
msgid ""
"I was right to suspect some enemy treachery when I heard all that noise from "
"Arion's outpost... Aislinn, go quickly to Lord Damien and warn him of this "
"surprise attack!"
msgstr ""
"Tenía razón al sospechar alguna traición enemiga cuando escuché todo ese "
"ruido desde el puesto de Arion... ¡Aislinn, ve rápido al Señor Damien y "
"avísale de este ataque sorpresa!"

#. [unit], id=Aislinn, type=Day Hunter
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:444
msgid "Aislinn"
msgstr "Aislinn"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:455
msgid "We must get that vampiress before she alerts the rest of her friends!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debemos atrapar a esa vampira antes de que alerte al resto de sus amigos!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:471
msgid "Whoa, who is that big guy over there?!"
msgstr "¡Whoa, ¿quién es ese tipo grande de allá?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:475
msgid ""
"That's a Yeti. They were thought to have gone extinct many years ago, after "
"being hunted for centuries; Nyx is genuinely surprised to see one around "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Eso es un Yeti. Se pensaba que se habían extinguido hace muchos años después "
"de ser cazados durante siglos. Nyx está realmente sorprendida de ver uno por "
"aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:479
msgid ""
"Hrumph! If vampires managed to prey on them, I don't think that they're so "
"powerful. Still, let's try not to kill it, after all we are the ones "
"invading their territory."
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! Si los vampiros lograron cazarlos, no creo que sean tan poderosos. "
"Aun así, intentemos no matarlo, después de todo somos nosotros los que "
"invadimos su territorio."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:483
msgid ""
"You know, I don't fell much kinship to other vampires, but when you speak "
"like this I can't avoid the feeling a bit offended..."
msgstr ""
"Sabes, no siento mucho parentesco con otros vampiros, pero cuando hablas así "
"no puedo evitar sentirme un poco ofendida..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:491
msgid "All right then, leave Nyx speaking to the winds..."
msgstr "Está bien entonces, deja que Nyx hable con el viento..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:505
msgid ""
"That's the entrance! Hurry inside, but keep cautious, for some minotaurs may "
"have hidden there; in the past, many Malborns were killed by them in these "
"tunnels."
msgstr ""
"¡Esa es la entrada! Apúrense a entrar, pero mantengan la cautela, porque "
"puede haber algunos minotauros escondidos allí. En el pasado, muchos Malborn "
"fueron asesinados por ellos en estos túneles."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:511
msgid "Proceed to the end of the tunnel"
msgstr "Avanza hasta el final del túnel"

#. [unit], id=Cretos, type=Minotaur Executioner
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:573
msgid "Cretos"
msgstr "Cretos"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:585
msgid ""
"Stench of vampire sewers mixed with the stench of wet minotaur fur... Ah, my "
"poor nose..."
msgstr ""
"Hedor de alcantarillas de vampiros mezclado con el hedor de pelaje húmedo de "
"minotauro... Ah, mi pobre nariz..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:599
msgid ""
"So far, so good. From now on, we should have a nice cave crawling until the "
"undergrounds beneath the Red Pinnacle."
msgstr ""
"Hasta ahora todo bien. De ahora en adelante deberíamos tener un agradable "
"avance por las cuevas hasta los subterráneos debajo del Pináculo Rojo."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:603
msgid ""
"Still, do not lower your guard for a single second; who knows what may lurk "
"in these tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, no bajen la guardia ni por un segundo. Quién sabe qué puede acechar "
"en estos túneles."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:624
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1387
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1155
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:847
msgid "Arrrgh! Curse them..."
msgstr "¡Arrrgh! Malditos sean..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:628
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1391
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1159
msgid ""
"We needed him to move through the northern tunnels, now we won't be able to "
"escape back through the caves!"
msgstr ""
"Lo necesitábamos para movernos por los túneles del norte, ¡ahora no podremos "
"escapar de vuelta a través de las cuevas!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:645
msgid ""
"Lord... Damien... There is a... human-dwarvish battalion here... and it's a "
"large one..."
msgstr ""
"Señor... Damien... Hay un... batallón humano-enano aquí... y es uno grande..."

#. [message], speaker=Damien
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:649
msgid ""
"How did an enemy force manage to sneak through so much of the Northern "
"Mountains unseen?! Well, it doesn't matter, I shall take care of them "
"presently - but, just in case, I shall warn the Duchess and ask for "
"reinforcements."
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo logró una fuerza enemiga infiltrarse a través de tantas Montañas del "
"Norte sin ser vista? Bueno, no importa, me ocuparé de ellos ahora mismo, "
"pero por si acaso advertiré a la Duquesa y pediré refuerzos."

#. [message], speaker=Damien
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:666
msgid ""
"Are those... dwarves and Maat'Karians?! Curses upon them, they're just too "
"numerous for me! I'll have to send a bat to the Duchess asking for "
"reinforcements..."
msgstr ""
"¿Son esos... enanos y maat'karianos? ¡Malditos sean, son simplemente "
"demasiados para mí! Tendré que enviar un murciélago a la Duquesa pidiendo "
"refuerzos..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:670
msgid ""
"Damn it, we should have avoided this town at any cost! Now, we will be "
"overwhelmed before we can escape back through the tunnels!"
msgstr ""
"Maldición, ¡deberíamos haber evitado esta ciudad a toda costa! Ahora seremos "
"abrumados antes de poder escapar de vuelta a través de los túneles."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice.cfg:681
msgid ""
"Folks, I know this region is covered in snow, but we really should have been "
"quicker! With the snowfall diminishing, this fog will soon vanish, and we "
"will be seen by farther vampire outposts!"
msgstr ""
"Gente, sé que esta región está cubierta de nieve, pero realmente deberíamos "
"haber sido más rápidos. Con la nevada disminuyendo, esta niebla pronto "
"desaparecerá y seremos vistos por puestos avanzados de vampiros más lejanos."

#. [scenario], id=08_Crimson_Ice_b
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:4
msgid "Crimson Ice - Part II"
msgstr "Hielo Carmesí - Parte II"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:23
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:298
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:361
msgid "Advance into the caves"
msgstr "Avanza hacia las cuevas"

#. [side], type=Vampiric Dread Bat
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:120
msgid "Chiroptus"
msgstr "Chiroptus"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:202
msgid ""
"Nyx remembers this area... We're very close to our goal, folks. He, this "
"brings back memories..."
msgstr ""
"Nyx recuerda esta área... Estamos muy cerca de nuestra meta, gente. Je, esto "
"trae recuerdos..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:206
msgid "Well, if you say that this dismaying stench makes you nostalgic..."
msgstr "Bueno, si dices que este hedor espantoso te pone nostálgica..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:210
msgid "(tired) Merwe, please, at least <i>try</i> to be friendly with her..."
msgstr ""
"(cansado) Merwe, por favor, al menos <i>intenta</i> ser amable con ella..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:214
msgid "Oh my, getting scolded by your man because of another woman..."
msgstr "Oh cielos, siendo regañada por tu hombre por culpa de otra mujer..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:218
msgid "(sigh) Don't you provoke her either, Nyx..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Tú tampoco la provoques, Nyx..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:222
msgid ""
"Jests aside, there should be a couple keeps further down this tunnel, if you "
"don't want to deploy too many soldiers so soon."
msgstr ""
"Bromas aparte, debería haber un par de torreones más adelante en este túnel, "
"si no quieren desplegar demasiados soldados tan pronto."

#. [unit], id=Heron, type=Necromancer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:241
msgid "Heron"
msgstr "Heron"

#. [unit], id=Taxos, type=Necromancer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:250
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:526
msgid "Taxos"
msgstr "Taxos"

#. [message], speaker=Taxos
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:261
msgid ""
"How annoying... We're almost out of these stinking caves and we haven't "
"found a single bone that could be used..."
msgstr ""
"Qué molesto... Ya casi salimos de estas apestosas cuevas y no hemos "
"encontrado ni un solo hueso que pueda usarse..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:265
msgid "Oh, damn..."
msgstr "Oh, maldición..."

#. [message], speaker=Heron
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:269
msgid ""
"What are you talking about, Taxos? I see plenty of healthy bones happily "
"dancing all the way towards us!"
msgstr ""
"¿De qué estás hablando, Taxos? ¡Veo un montón de huesos sanos bailando "
"alegremente hacia nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Taxos
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:273
msgid ""
"Wait, that blood-sucker said nothing about enemies coming this way! Theirs "
"is not a large force, but they have many veterans; I think we should go back "
"and alert..."
msgstr ""
"Espera, ¡ese chupasangre no dijo nada sobre enemigos viniendo por este "
"camino! Su fuerza no es grande, pero tienen muchos veteranos. Creo que "
"deberíamos regresar y alertar..."

#. [message], speaker=Heron
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:277
msgid ""
"If you're too insecure to fight them, you may go back to our master - but "
"know that I will not share any of their bones with you."
msgstr ""
"Si te sientes demasiado inseguro para luchar contra ellos, puedes regresar "
"con nuestro amo, pero sabe que no compartiré ninguno de sus huesos contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:288
msgid "Well, that was not in the plan..."
msgstr "Bueno, eso no estaba en el plan..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:292
msgid ""
"Och, you can't be blamed, though; never could you have known that there were "
"Skironians even here..."
msgstr ""
"Och, no se te puede culpar; nunca podrías haber sabido que había skironianos "
"incluso aquí..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:302
msgid "Defeat Heron"
msgstr "Derrota a Heron"

#. [message], speaker=Heron
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:351
msgid "Damn you, Maat'Karians...!"
msgstr "¡Malditos sean, maat'karianos...!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:355
msgid "Now, let us hurry and get the other summoner!"
msgstr "Ahora, apurémonos y atrapemos al otro invocador."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:365
msgid "Find the second Necromancer"
msgstr "Encuentra al segundo nigromante"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:416
msgid ""
"Watch out, people, there's a very steep tunnel going downwards here, if "
"anyone falls in it we'll have trouble rescuing them!"
msgstr ""
"Cuidado, gente, hay un túnel muy empinado que baja aquí. Si alguien cae en "
"él tendremos problemas para rescatarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:420
msgid "It seems bottomless... I wonder where it ends..."
msgstr "Parece sin fondo... Me pregunto dónde termina..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:424
msgid ""
"Maybe that monolith has the answer to that question; Nyx, could you read "
"it..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez ese monolito tenga la respuesta a esa pregunta. Nyx, ¿podrías "
"leerlo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:431
msgid "No, wait, I know this writing... Can it be...?!"
msgstr "No, espera, conozco esta escritura... ¡¿Puede ser...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:435
msgid ""
"Have you managed to translate it? I couldn't decipher it even though I "
"searched for those symbols in my father's old library."
msgstr ""
"¿Lograste traducirlo? No pude descifrarlo aunque busqué esos símbolos en la "
"antigua biblioteca de mi padre."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:439
msgid ""
"Yes, I know this alphabet, I've learned it in a book from the Academy's "
"Library, it's the old cursive writing used by old Windsong!"
msgstr ""
"Sí, conozco este alfabeto, lo aprendí en un libro de la Biblioteca de la "
"Academia. ¡Es la antigua escritura cursiva usada por las antiguas Hijas del "
"Viento!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:443
msgid ""
"(surprised) They've entered vampire land after being expelled from "
"Hiera'Laksha, then?"
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) ¿Entonces entraron en tierras de vampiros después de ser "
"expulsados de Hiera'Laksha?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:447
msgid ""
"Yes, and, apparently, they plunged into this tunnel, or so these "
"inscriptions seem to tell. I'm not an expert in their language, so I can "
"only understand some fragments..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, y aparentemente se lanzaron a este túnel, o eso parece contar estas "
"inscripciones. No soy un experto en su idioma, así que solo puedo entender "
"algunos fragmentos..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:451
msgid "Does this monolith say anything else?"
msgstr "¿Este monolito dice algo más?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:455
msgid ""
"Well, here they say... that they are 'leaving the continent that has "
"betrayed them behind'... 'to revive the Hiera' - that is, their 'Holy "
"Foundation' - at... 'Kirya Yukuya'..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, aquí dicen... que están «dejando atrás el continente que los "
"traicionó»... «para revivir la Hiera», es decir, su «Fundación Sagrada», "
"en... «Kirya Yukuya»..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:459
msgid "Kirya Yukuya... I've never seen this name on any map."
msgstr "Kirya Yukuya... Nunca he visto este nombre en ningún mapa."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:463
msgid ""
"That doesn't sound like a region's name... Wait, I remember it now! Kirya "
"means 'utmost', 'polar', and Yukuya means 'snowy', so Kirya Yukuya should "
"mean..."
msgstr ""
"Eso no suena como el nombre de una región... Espera, ¡ahora lo recuerdo! "
"Kirya significa «extremo», «polar», y Yukuya significa «nevado», así que "
"Kirya Yukuya debería significar..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:467
msgid ""
"'Snowy pole'... Akhen, do you think the Windsong have gone to the Blue Realm?"
msgstr ""
"«Polo nevado»... Akhen, ¿crees que las Hijas del Viento se fueron al Reino "
"Azul?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:471
msgid "A region beyond Netjer-Ta, I assume?"
msgstr "¿Una región más allá de Netjer-Ta, supongo?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:475
msgid ""
"Yes. 'Blue Realm' is how we call the seas and lands beyond the utmost north, "
"a realm completely covered in ice that Aldrik discovered during his "
"lifetime. He didn't explore that region, due to its 'extreme "
"inhospitableness'; can it be that the Windsong have settled there...?"
msgstr ""
"Sí. «Reino Azul» es como llamamos a los mares y tierras más allá del extremo "
"norte, un reino completamente cubierto de hielo que Aldrik descubrió durante "
"su vida. No exploró esa región debido a su «extrema inhospitalidad». ¿Será "
"posible que las Hijas del Viento se hayan establecido allí...?"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:479
msgid ""
"Listen, I understand that this must be a very interesting story for you "
"humans, but we should concentrate on our original mission."
msgstr ""
"Escuchen, entiendo que esta debe ser una historia muy interesante para "
"ustedes los humanos, pero deberíamos concentrarnos en nuestra misión "
"original."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:483
msgid "You're right, I apologise for our distraction..."
msgstr "Tienes razón, me disculpo por nuestra distracción..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:497
msgid ""
"Blast it, at this height we can't possibly catch that Necromancer! What will "
"we do now?"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, a esta altura no podemos alcanzar a ese nigromante! ¿Qué haremos "
"ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:501
msgid ""
"Listen, we're currently very close to the Red Pinnacle; if we hurry, we may "
"still invade it before the guards or the Skironians are able to mount a "
"proper defence!"
msgstr ""
"Escuchen, estamos muy cerca del Pináculo Rojo en este momento. Si nos "
"apuramos, aún podemos invadirlo antes de que los guardias o los skironianos "
"puedan montar una defensa adecuada."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:505
msgid ""
"Then let's run for it; please, try not to lag behind so much, we'll need "
"your strength if we have to fight too many of those bloodsuckers."
msgstr ""
"Entonces corramos hacia allá. Por favor, intenten no quedarse tan atrás, "
"necesitaremos su fuerza si tenemos que luchar contra demasiados de esos "
"chupasangre."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:509
msgid ""
"I’m really not sure whether I should feel offended or flattered by this "
"comment..."
msgstr ""
"Realmente no estoy seguro de si debería sentirme ofendido o halagado por "
"este comentario..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:536
msgid "Nyx, is something the..."
msgstr "Nyx, ¿pasa algo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:540
msgid "Hush! I hear something..."
msgstr "¡Silencio! Escucho algo..."

#. [message], speaker=Taxos
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:544
msgid "...And so I ran back here, to warn you of their presence..."
msgstr "...Y por eso corrí de vuelta aquí, para advertirte de su presencia..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:548
msgid ""
"(raspy voice) You did well, my disciple, much better than that foolish, "
"greedy Heron. These Maat'Karians, who managed to sneak through vampire "
"territory unnoticed, could have plotted something to destroy our portal, "
"which is still far too vulnerable to suffer even the slightest damage."
msgstr ""
"(voz ronca) Lo hiciste bien, mi discípulo, mucho mejor que ese tonto y "
"codicioso Heron. Estos maat'karianos, que lograron infiltrarse por "
"territorio vampírico sin ser notados, podrían haber planeado algo para "
"destruir nuestro portal, que aún es demasiado vulnerable para sufrir incluso "
"el más mínimo daño."

#. [message], speaker=Taxos
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:552
msgid "Um, shouldn't we warn the Duchess of the enemy's presence here as well?"
msgstr ""
"Um, ¿no deberíamos advertir también a la Duquesa de la presencia del enemigo "
"aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:556
msgid ""
"We need not bother her with such insignificant matter; I, Caror, shall "
"quickly smite these Maat'Karians and give barrels with their blood as a gift "
"to our new ally; their bones, however, shall be ours."
msgstr ""
"No es necesario molestarla con un asunto tan insignificante. Yo, Caror, "
"aplastaré rápidamente a estos maat'karianos y entregaré barriles con su "
"sangre como regalo a nuestro nuevo aliado. Sus huesos, sin embargo, serán "
"nuestros."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:560
msgid ""
"I see... Well, folks, we need not hurry, for the Skironians are not going to "
"warn the vampires. On the other hand, there is a Lich-Lord ahead of us, and "
"he's summoning some sort of portal, which doesn't sound good however you "
"look at it."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Bueno, gente, no necesitamos apurarnos, porque los skironianos "
"no van a advertir a los vampiros. Por otro lado, hay un Señor-Liche delante "
"de nosotros y está invocando algún tipo de portal, lo cual no suena nada "
"bien por más que lo mires."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:564
msgid ""
"Oh no, it must one of those portals Stygia mentioned in the Chamber of Sages "
"- the ones that are connected to Skiron! We must destroy it, otherwise "
"they'll bring more armies from Argea through it!"
msgstr ""
"Oh no, debe ser uno de esos portales que mencionó Stygia en la Cámara de los "
"Sabios, ¡los que están conectados con Skiron! Debemos destruirlo, ¡de lo "
"contrario traerán más ejércitos de Argea a través de él!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:570
msgid "Confront the Lich-Lord of Skiron"
msgstr "Enfrenta al Señor-Liche de Skiron"

#. [unit], id=Caror, type=Lich Lord WotJ
#. [side], type=Lich Lord WotJ
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:630
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:90
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/characters.cfg:400
msgid "Lich-Lord Caror"
msgstr "Señor-Liche Caror"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:645
msgid "So, which of the Lich-Lords are you?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿cuál de los Señores-Liches eres tú?"

#. [message], speaker=Caror
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:649
msgid ""
"Would you know me, scum? Then listen well: I am Caror, Lord of Aionian and a "
"favourite of the great Aegaion, the Eternal Emperor!"
msgstr ""
"¿Me conocerías, escoria? Entonces escucha bien: soy Caror, Señor de Aionian "
"y favorito del gran Aegaion, ¡el Emperador Eterno!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:653
msgid ""
"Oh, really? Well, pardon our ignorance, we couldn't have known a Lich-Lord "
"whose feats haven't echoed outside his own land..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, ¿en serio? Bueno, disculpa nuestra ignorancia, no podíamos conocer a un "
"Señor-Liche cuyos logros no han resonado fuera de su propia tierra..."

#. [message], speaker=Caror
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:657
msgid ""
"You...! How dare you mock me, my power?! I will turn your companions into my "
"slaves, but you, little vampiress, will become my personal toy; I was after "
"a non-human creature to perform experiments anyway..."
msgstr ""
"¡Tú...! ¿Cómo te atreves a burlarte de mí, de mi poder? Convertiré a tus "
"compañeros en mis esclavos, pero tú, pequeña vampira, te convertirás en mi "
"juguete personal. De todos modos estaba buscando una criatura no humana para "
"realizar experimentos..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:663
msgid "Destroy Lich-Lord Caror"
msgstr "Destruye al Señor-Liche Caror"

#. [message], speaker=Caror
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:708
msgid ""
"AAARRRGH!!! Curse these bloody Maat'Karians! Fortunately, the portal is "
"nearly complete already, so I may withdraw - but I must make sure that "
"they're not able to follow me... Ack! Curses on you, disgusting brats, Lord "
"Aegaion will be furious at me for destroying this portal..."
msgstr ""
"¡AAARRRGH!!! ¡Malditos maat'karianos sangrientos! Afortunadamente el portal "
"ya está casi completo, así que puedo retirarme, pero debo asegurarme de que "
"no puedan seguirme... ¡Ack! ¡Malditos sean, niños asquerosos! Lord Aegaion "
"se enfurecerá conmigo por destruir este portal..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:729
msgid "Damn it, the portal is going to explode! Retreat, everyone!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, el portal va a explotar! ¡Retírense, todos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:751
msgid ""
"At the end of the next turn, the cave's roof above Caror's keep will fall; "
"remove all units from there!"
msgstr ""
"Al final del siguiente turno, el techo de la cueva sobre el torreón de Caror "
"se derrumbará. ¡Retiren todas las unidades de allí!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:804
msgid "People, HURRY UP!"
msgstr "¡Gente, apúrense!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:883
msgid "(stunned) W-what the hell has just happened..."
msgstr "(aturdido) ¿Qué demonios acaba de pasar...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:887
msgid "The portal's explosion has brought down part of the Red Pinnacle!"
msgstr "¡La explosión del portal ha derribado parte del Pináculo Rojo!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:891
msgid ""
"And not just any part; I recognize those ruins, they belong to Castle "
"Drakonian!"
msgstr ""
"Y no cualquier parte. Reconozco esas ruinas, ¡pertenecen al Castillo "
"Drakoniano!"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:895
msgid ""
"(furious) I refuse to believe my eyes... Where the hell did those "
"Maat'Karians come from?!"
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) Me niego a creer lo que ven mis ojos... ¡¿De dónde demonios "
"salieron esos maat'karianos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:899
msgid "And that is... ERYNIA!!!"
msgstr "¡Y esa es... ERYNIA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:903
msgid ""
"Oh, that was all that I needed right now... Vampires, worry not about your "
"wounds, for the enemy is worn out as well!"
msgstr ""
"Oh, eso era justo lo que necesitaba ahora... Vampiros, no se preocupen por "
"sus heridas, ¡porque el enemigo también está agotado!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:907
msgid ""
"Don't you dare lay a paw on Erynia, she's mine, understood?! Now, let's "
"crush them!"
msgstr ""
"¡No te atrevas a ponerle una pata encima a Erynia, ella es mía, ¿entendido?! "
"¡Ahora, aplastémoslos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:918
msgid "Kill Grand Duchess Erynia with Nyx"
msgstr "Mata a la Gran Duquesa Erynia con Nyx"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:974
msgid "DIE, ERYNIA!!!"
msgstr "¡MUERE, ERYNIA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:989
msgid "'AAAARRRRR!!! YOU DAMN BRAT-"
msgstr "¡AAAARRRRR!!! MALDITA NIÑA-"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:993
msgid ""
"I told you that I'd make you pay for your treachery; now, Erynia Devellian, "
"in the name of Aryen Devellian, I condemn your rotten soul to the lowest "
"pits of..."
msgstr ""
"Te dije que te haría pagar por tu traición. Ahora, Erynia Devellian, en "
"nombre de Aryen Devellian, condeno tu alma podrida a los pozos más bajos "
"de..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1002
msgid "W-what...?!"
msgstr "¡Q-qué...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1006
msgid ""
"Let's... have a family meeting... with your father and siblings... in "
"hell...!"
msgstr ""
"Vamos a tener... una reunión familiar... con tu padre y tus hermanos... en "
"el infierno...!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1017
msgid "NYX!"
msgstr "¡NYX!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1021
msgid "Oh no... Hold on, Nyx, we're going to heal you soon enough..."
msgstr "Oh no... Aguanta, Nyx, vamos a sanarte muy pronto..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1038
msgid ""
"(weakly) Damn that bastard, even at death's gates she managed to trouble "
"me... But at least I have completed my revenge, so now I may go in peace..."
msgstr ""
"(débilmente) Maldita bastarda, incluso en las puertas de la muerte logró "
"molestarme... Pero al menos he completado mi venganza, así que ahora puedo "
"irme en paz..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1042
msgid "Stop talking nonsense, who said that you must die now?!"
msgstr "Deja de decir tonterías, ¡¿quién dijo que tienes que morir ahora?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1046
msgid ""
"I have nothing else in my life, I... have lost everyone and everything... I "
"don't want to live decades and decades of a miserable, lonely life..."
msgstr ""
"No tengo nada más en mi vida, yo... he perdido a todos y todo... No quiero "
"vivir décadas y décadas de una vida miserable y solitaria..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1050
msgid ""
"Then don't live such a life! Who said that you're alone in this world? You "
"have Sigdral, Violindë, and now you have me, Merwe, Mahyus and Atenak! Don't "
"let your life be a mere quest for vengeance!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces no vivas esa vida! ¿Quién dijo que estás sola en este mundo? "
"Tienes a Sigdral, a Violindë, y ahora me tienes a mí, a Merwe, a Mahyus y a "
"Atenak. ¡No dejes que tu vida sea solo una búsqueda de venganza!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1054
msgid "And why... the hell... do you worry so much... about me...?!"
msgstr "¿Y por qué demonios... te preocupas tanto... por mí...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1058
msgid ""
"Because you're my friend and because you're a good person, that's why! Now, "
"open your mouth, for I won't let you die like this!"
msgstr ""
"¡Porque eres mi amiga y porque eres una buena persona, por eso! Ahora abre "
"la boca, ¡porque no voy a dejarte morir así!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1062
msgid "Akhen, what are you..."
msgstr "Akhen, ¿qué estás...?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1079
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:248
msgid "Akhen...!"
msgstr "¡Akhen...!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1083
msgid ""
"Be careful, you! If she bites you even by accident, you could turn into a "
"vampire too!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ten cuidado! Si te muerde aunque sea por accidente, ¡podrías convertirte en "
"vampiro también!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1087
msgid ""
"(calmly) Hey, Akhen... Please, just keep your wrist above Nyx's mouth; "
"she'll drink your blood as it spills..."
msgstr ""
"(con calma) Oye, Akhen... Por favor, solo mantén tu muñeca sobre la boca de "
"Nyx. Ella beberá tu sangre mientras se derrama..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1125
msgid "That's one nauseating sight, but she's clearly recovering..."
msgstr "Esa es una vista nauseabunda, pero claramente se está recuperando..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1129
msgid "Enough, now please close this wound, you can't lose too much blood..."
msgstr ""
"Suficiente, ahora por favor cierra esta herida, no puedes perder tanta "
"sangre..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1133
msgid "(hugging Akhen) Thank you, my friend... Thank you..."
msgstr "(abrazando a Akhen) Gracias, mi amigo... Gracias..."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1291
msgid ""
"Ah, at long last... After being delayed by that cursed blizzard for days, "
"we've finally reached the Crimson Valley!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, por fin... Después de ser retrasados por esa maldita ventisca durante "
"días, ¡finalmente hemos llegado al Valle Carmesí!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1295
msgid ""
"Indeed, but... Don't you find it odd that we have been unopposed thus far? "
"And besides, look at those outposts, they're completely empty; could it be "
"that the vampires are preparing an ambush?"
msgstr ""
"En efecto, pero... ¿no les parece extraño que no hayamos encontrado "
"oposición hasta ahora? Además, miren esos puestos avanzados, están "
"completamente vacíos. ¿Será que los vampiros están preparando una emboscada?"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1299
msgid "No, I don't think so..."
msgstr "No, no lo creo..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1303
msgid "And what makes you so sure of that?"
msgstr "¿Y qué te hace estar tan seguro de eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1307
msgid ""
"(pointing to the northwest) Because they are no longer in conditions to "
"fight us."
msgstr ""
"(señalando al noroeste) Porque ya no están en condiciones de luchar contra "
"nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1319
msgid ""
"General Smenkhare, Master Sadjet, Chief Romlur, it's a pleasure to see you. "
"Apologies for making you come here in vain, but, as you can see, we've "
"already collected the Duchess' head and rendered the vampires powerless. "
"Changing the subject, we were lucky to find some barrels of mead in what was "
"left of Erynia's castle, and it's surprisingly fine; do you accept some?"
msgstr ""
"General Smenkhare, maestro Sadjet, jefe Romlur, es un placer verlos. "
"Disculpen por hacerlos venir aquí en vano, pero como pueden ver, ya hemos "
"tomado la cabeza de la Duquesa y dejado a los vampiros impotentes. Cambiando "
"de tema, tuvimos suerte de encontrar algunos barriles de hidromiel en lo que "
"quedó del castillo de Erynia, y está sorprendentemente bueno. ¿Aceptan un "
"poco?"

#. [message], speaker=Erynia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1369
msgid ""
"Insufferable vermin...! You win this time, but I shall have my revenge..."
msgstr "¡Alimañas insufribles...! Ganan esta vez, pero tendré mi venganza..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1373
msgid ""
"She's turning into nightmist...! I told you, I had to be the one killing "
"her! Now she'll rally her dukes while we're stranded at the very heart of "
"her territory..."
msgstr ""
"¡Se está convirtiendo en niebla nocturna...! ¡Te lo dije, tenía que ser yo "
"quien la matara! Ahora reunirá a sus duques mientras estamos varados en el "
"mismo corazón de su territorio..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/08_Crimson_Ice_b.cfg:1402
msgid ""
"We should have been quicker; now, Erynia will certainly be warned of our "
"presence here!"
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos haber sido más rápidos. ¡Ahora Erynia sin duda será advertida de "
"nuestra presencia aquí!"

#. [scenario], id=09_Dark_Eclipse
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:4
msgid "Dark Eclipse"
msgstr "Eclipse Oscuro"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:23
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:947
msgid "Counter Skiron's attack and defeat Lich-Lord Jevyan"
msgstr "Contrarresta el ataque de Skiron y derrota al Señor-Liche Jevyan"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:51
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:975
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:60
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:713
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:815
msgid "Death of Sadjet"
msgstr "Muerte de Sadjet"

#. [side], type=Necromancer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:180
msgid "Summoner Eria"
msgstr "Invocadora Eria"

#. [side], type=General SK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:205
msgid "General Telos"
msgstr "General Telos"

#. [unit], id=Tothes, type=Mage of Storms MK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:287
msgid "Professor Tothes"
msgstr "Profesor Tothes"

#. [unit], id=Khamaat, type=Mage of Nature MK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:297
msgid "Professor Khama'at"
msgstr "Profesor Khama'at"

#. [unit], id=Sitamun, type=Mage of Nature MK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:307
msgid "Professor Sitamun"
msgstr "Profesor Sitamun"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:342
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:319
msgid "The Academy"
msgstr "La Academia"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:346
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:323
msgid "Veela's Garden"
msgstr "El Jardín de Veela"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:350
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:327
msgid "Wadjet Manor"
msgstr "Mansión Wadjet"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:354
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:331
msgid "Aracynes Manor"
msgstr "Mansión Aracynes"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:358
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:335
msgid "The Docks"
msgstr "Los Muelles"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:362
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:339
msgid "Thalia Migdol"
msgstr "Migdol Thalia"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:366
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:343
msgid "Isle of Deianira"
msgstr "Isla de Deianira"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:375
msgid "W-what on Irdya is happening here...?"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios está pasando aquí en Irdya...?"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:401
msgid ""
"Cursed be these Skironians, they must have broken through the Nitiballi Wall!"
msgstr "¡Malditos sean estos skironianos, deben haber roto el Muro Nitiballi!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:405
msgid "I thought it was supposed to be impenetrable?!"
msgstr "¡Pensé que se suponía que era impenetrable!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:409
msgid ""
"No wall is impenetrable, Maat'Karian, especially if I'm on the attacking "
"side, leading the Fleet of Skiron!"
msgstr ""
"Ningún muro es impenetrable, maat'kariano, especialmente si yo estoy del "
"lado atacante, ¡liderando la Flota de Skiron!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:413
msgid "My, my, these southerners sure talk a lot..."
msgstr "Vaya, vaya, estos sureños sí que hablan mucho..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:417
msgid ""
"As much as I hate to admit, his bragging is no mere arrogance. He's Lich-"
"Lord Jevyan, the monster who besmirches our Founder's name, and rumoured to "
"be the third most powerful Lich-Lord of Skiron, surpassed only by Stygia and "
"by Aegaion himself. It's said he single-handedly laid waste to an entire "
"orcish host in Argea; friends, prepare for what promises to be a long and "
"vicious battle..."
msgstr ""
"Por más que odie admitirlo, su fanfarronería no es mera arrogancia. Es el "
"Señor-Liche Jevyan, el monstruo que mancha el nombre de nuestro Fundador y "
"se rumorea que es el tercer Señor-Liche más poderoso de Skiron, solo "
"superado por Stygia y por el propio Aegaion. Se dice que él solo destruyó a "
"todo un ejército orco en Argea. Amigos, prepárense para lo que promete ser "
"una batalla larga y feroz..."

#. [unit]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:445
msgid "Undead Soldier"
msgstr "Soldado no-muerto"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:516
msgid "They've managed to disembark soldiers on M'lena Island! I need aid!"
msgstr "¡Han logrado desembarcar soldados en la Isla M'lena! ¡Necesito ayuda!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:544
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:564
msgid "More Skironians are being disembarked on the southern beaches!"
msgstr "¡Están desembarcando más skironianos en las playas del sur!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:581
msgid ""
"At long last, reinforcements have come! With most of our army doing battle "
"in faraway regions, I feared that the sun would fade on this day before the "
"darkness of Skiron! But I'm surprised that you've returned so soon, general; "
"were the vampires so weak, to have fallen so quickly?"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin han llegado refuerzos! Con la mayor parte de nuestro ejército "
"luchando en regiones lejanas, temía que el sol se apagara en este día antes "
"que la oscuridad de Skiron. Pero me sorprende que hayas regresado tan "
"pronto, general. ¿Eran los vampiros tan débiles como para caer tan rápido?"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:585
msgid ""
"They weren't, and we'd certainly still be fighting them if your niece's "
"troop hadn't sneaked into the Red Pinnacle alongside some of the Motsoghnir "
"and slain the Grand Duchess, thus disbanding the vampire hosts."
msgstr ""
"No lo eran, y seguramente aún estaríamos luchando contra ellos si la tropa "
"de tu sobrina no se hubiera infiltrado en el Pináculo Rojo junto con algunos "
"Motsoghnir y hubiera matado a la Gran Duquesa, disolviendo así a los "
"ejércitos vampíricos."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:589
msgid ""
"(impressed) Really? I see... Well done, Atenak; your decisions, albeit "
"almost stupidly reckless, may have helped save our city."
msgstr ""
"(impresionado) ¿En serio? Entiendo... Bien hecho, Atenak. Tus decisiones, "
"aunque casi estúpidamente imprudentes, pueden haber ayudado a salvar nuestra "
"ciudad."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:593
msgid ""
"(whisper) Was that a praise or what? Nyx really couldn't tell the difference."
msgstr ""
"(susurro) ¿Eso fue un elogio o qué? Nyx realmente no pudo notar la "
"diferencia."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:597
msgid "Tewarin, Atseger, when did this sudden attack begin?"
msgstr "Tewarin, Atseger, ¿cuándo comenzó este ataque repentino?"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:601
msgid ""
"It started in the morning of the day before you arrived, little after a "
"scouting boat reported that the Nitiballi Wall had been breached. We've "
"defeated two attack waves already; Jevyan himself has appeared only a few "
"hours ago, so the brunt of their attack hasn't reached us yet."
msgstr ""
"Comenzó en la mañana del día antes de que llegaran, poco después de que un "
"barco de exploración reportara que el Muro Nitiballi había sido roto. Ya "
"hemos derrotado dos oleadas de ataque. El propio Jevyan apareció solo hace "
"unas horas, así que el grueso de su ataque aún no nos ha alcanzado."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:605
msgid ""
"We've gathered the sages at the City Heart; Lord Tewarin has rallied every "
"able-bodied citizen here to help defending the city, and I've gathered all "
"of the Academy's professors and every veteran student I could find. Still, "
"we barely managed to hold our ground against the Skironians."
msgstr ""
"Hemos reunido a los sabios en el Corazón de la Ciudad. Lord Tewarin ha "
"convocado a todos los ciudadanos aptos aquí para ayudar a defender la "
"ciudad, y yo he reunido a todos los profesores de la Academia y a todos los "
"estudiantes veteranos que pude encontrar. Aun así, apenas logramos mantener "
"nuestra posición contra los skironianos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:609
msgid "If only Master Menon was here..."
msgstr "Si tan solo el maestro Menon estuviera aquí..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:618
msgid ""
"Indeed, if he was here everything would be different; his mere sight would "
"be enough to make even the senseless undead tremble in fear!"
msgstr ""
"En efecto, si estuviera aquí todo sería diferente. Su mera presencia sería "
"suficiente para hacer temblar de miedo incluso a los no-muertos sin sentido."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:622
msgid ""
"I'm afraid that Suryen was right; it was madness to exile the strongest "
"Maat'Karian in a war like this..."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que Suryen tenía razón. Fue una locura exiliar al maat'kariano más "
"fuerte en una guerra como esta..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:626
msgid ""
"(impatient) I acknowledge that Menon's presence here would have changed the "
"course of this battle, but the decision to exile him in itself was not "
"erroneous, at least not at that time..."
msgstr ""
"(impaciente) Reconozco que la presencia de Menon aquí habría cambiado el "
"curso de esta batalla, pero la decisión de exiliarlo en sí misma no fue "
"errónea, al menos no en ese momento..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:630
msgid ""
"There's no use arguing over it right now! And besides, we can't just always "
"rely on Master Menon for everything; he would want us to know how to deal "
"with our own problems."
msgstr ""
"¡No sirve de nada discutir eso ahora! Además, no podemos depender siempre "
"del maestro Menon para todo. Él querría que supiéramos cómo resolver "
"nuestros propios problemas."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:634
msgid ""
"And Sadjet, Akhen, I must ask you to help me defend the Academy at all "
"costs. I'm certain that Master Menon has told you about what he has left "
"here..."
msgstr ""
"Y Sadjet, Akhen, debo pedirles que me ayuden a defender la Academia a toda "
"costa. Estoy segura de que el maestro Menon les ha hablado de lo que dejó "
"aquí..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:638
msgid ""
"(astonished) Darn it, how could I have forgotten that?! Wadjet, Meritane and "
"Merwe, we must protect the Academy even if it costs us our lives!"
msgstr ""
"(asombrado) ¡Maldición, cómo pude olvidarlo! Wadjet, Meritane y Merwe, "
"¡debemos proteger la Academia aunque nos cueste la vida!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:642
msgid "Understood, professor!"
msgstr "¡Entendido, profesora!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:661
msgid ""
"At last, the preparations for that spell are completed... Behold, "
"Maat'Karians, my new enchantment, which I have prepared especially for you..."
msgstr ""
"Por fin, los preparativos para ese hechizo están completos... Contemplen, "
"maat'karianos, mi nuevo encantamiento, que he preparado especialmente para "
"ustedes..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:665
msgid "Uh-oh, I really don't like the sound of it..."
msgstr "Uh-oh, realmente no me gusta cómo suena eso..."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:669
msgid ""
"'Children of the Primeval Chaos, hearken my call... Shadows of Umbra, crawl "
"forth from the abyss... Cover skies, earth, seas and all... Seal the World "
"in invincible Darkness!'"
msgstr ""
"«Hijos del Caos Primigenio, escuchen mi llamado... Sombras de Umbra, "
"arrastrense desde el abismo... Cubran cielos, tierra, mares y todo... "
"¡Sellen el Mundo en una Oscuridad invencible!»"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Damn it! What kind of spell is this? It's so dark that I can barely see "
"across the street!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición! ¿Qué clase de hechizo es este? Está tan oscuro que apenas puedo "
"ver al otro lado de la calle."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:686
msgid ""
"No way... How can someone who has been learning magic for a mere four "
"decades know such spells?! Is <i>this</i> the power of the Ruby of Fire...?"
msgstr ""
"No puede ser... ¿Cómo puede alguien que ha estado aprendiendo magia por "
"apenas cuatro décadas conocer tales hechizos? ¿Es <i>este</i> el poder del "
"Rubí de Fuego...?"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:690
msgid ""
"Atenak, Lord Tewarin, I suggest that you reconsider the ban on the use of "
"undead by me; this unnatural darkness weakens our soldiers very much, but "
"also strengthens undead creatures considerably."
msgstr ""
"Atenak, Lord Tewarin, sugiero que reconsideren la prohibición del uso de no-"
"muertos por mi parte. Esta oscuridad antinatural debilita mucho a nuestros "
"soldados, pero también fortalece considerablemente a las criaturas no-"
"muertas."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:694
msgid ""
"I understand that the situation is dire, but we must not let it overcome our "
"principles; I <i>shall not</i> allow any of those aberrations to march under "
"Ravyan's banner!"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo que la situación es grave, pero no debemos permitir que supere "
"nuestros principios. ¡<i>No</i> permitiré que ninguna de esas aberraciones "
"marche bajo el estandarte de Ravyan!"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:698
msgid ""
"(enraged) Mahyus Meritane, how can you forget your loyalty?! I am the one "
"you should ask permission for raising undead, and <i>I</i> say raise them at "
"once!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecida) Mahyus Meritane, ¿cómo puedes olvidar tu lealtad? ¡Yo soy a "
"quien debes pedir permiso para levantar no-muertos, y <i>yo</i> digo que los "
"levantes de inmediato!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:702
msgid "(affronted) Atseger, how can you...?!"
msgstr "(ofendido) ¡Atseger, ¿cómo puedes...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:706
msgid ""
"Apologies, my friend, but I'm with her; after all, our law allows the "
"practice of Necromancy if it is to protect our city and our people in times "
"of greatest need, which is undoubtedly the case."
msgstr ""
"Disculpas, amigo mío, pero estoy con ella. Después de todo, nuestra ley "
"permite la práctica de la nigromancia si es para proteger nuestra ciudad y a "
"nuestra gente en tiempos de mayor necesidad, que sin duda es este caso."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:710
msgid ""
"Well, Atenak, sorry, but before being your soldier, I'm a student of the "
"Academy, so..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, Atenak, lo siento, pero antes de ser tu soldado soy un estudiante de "
"la Academia, así que..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:714
msgid "Don't worry, I understand..."
msgstr "No te preocupes, entiendo…"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:718
msgid ""
"Let darkness engulf this peninsula, Skiron is not alone in who revels in it!"
msgstr ""
"¡Que la oscuridad engulla esta península, Skiron no es el único que se "
"deleita en ella!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:735
msgid "Mahyus may now recruit undead units"
msgstr "Mahyus ahora puede reclutar unidades no-muertas"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:766
msgid ""
"I must confess that I'm vexed by the fortitude of these Maat'Karians; they "
"truly deserve all their renown and fame... But alas, no star is so shining "
"that it'll never fade one day. Behold, People of the Sun, the final wave "
"that shall ultimately ravage your city!"
msgstr ""
"Debo confesar que estoy molesto por la fortaleza de estos maat'karianos. "
"Realmente merecen toda su fama y renombre... Pero ay, ninguna estrella "
"brilla tanto que no se apague algún día. Contemplen, Pueblo del Sol, ¡la "
"oleada final que finalmente arrasará su ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:815
msgid "Oh no, no, no, no!!!"
msgstr "¡Oh no, no, no, no!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:819
msgid ""
"(desperate) Oh, a thousand curses upon them! We won't be able to fight such "
"a huge offensive, not worn out as we are right now..."
msgstr ""
"(desesperada) ¡Oh, mil maldiciones sobre ellos! No podremos enfrentar una "
"ofensiva tan enorme, no agotados como estamos ahora..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:823
msgid ""
"M-maybe we should evacuate the city; we may be able to cover them and fight "
"off the enemy as we retreat..."
msgstr ""
"T-tal vez deberíamos evacuar la ciudad. Podríamos cubrirlos y combatir al "
"enemigo mientras nos retiramos..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:827
msgid ""
"So we're going to flee and abandon our city, which has been the home of our "
"people for sixteen centuries?! I simply refuse to flee before those unworthy "
"monsters! We should stay and fight!"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces vamos a huir y abandonar nuestra ciudad, que ha sido el hogar de "
"nuestro pueblo durante dieciséis siglos? ¡Simplemente me niego a huir ante "
"esos monstruos indignos! ¡Debemos quedarnos y luchar!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:831
msgid "Agreed!"
msgstr "¡De acuerdo!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:835
msgid "Well spoken, Merwe!"
msgstr "¡Bien dicho, Merwe!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:839
msgid ""
"Gallant words, youths, but my niece is right; we should do as the Windsong "
"did when Hiera'Shirsha was destroyed, and sacrifice our city for the sake of "
"our people!"
msgstr ""
"Palabras valientes, jóvenes, pero mi sobrina tiene razón. Deberíamos hacer "
"como hicieron las Hijas del Viento cuando destruyeron Hiera'Shirsha, y "
"sacrificar nuestra ciudad por el bien de nuestro pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:843
msgid ""
"(crying in rage) Stupid Tewarin, shut up at once this mouth that has doomed "
"us! Were it not for your senseless enmity towards Master Menon, there would "
"still be hope for us!"
msgstr ""
"(llorando de rabia) ¡Estúpido Tewarin, cállate de una vez esa boca que nos "
"ha condenado! ¡De no ser por tu enemistad insensata hacia el maestro Menon, "
"todavía habría esperanza para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:854
msgid ""
"(alarmed) What was this flash of light?! My veil of darkness should be able "
"to block even the sun!"
msgstr ""
"(alarmado) ¿Qué fue ese destello de luz? ¡Mi velo de oscuridad debería poder "
"bloquear incluso al sol!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:858
msgid ""
"This power...! I sense no hostility towards us, so why am I feeling so "
"overwhelmed...?"
msgstr ""
"¡Este poder...! No siento hostilidad hacia nosotros, entonces ¿por qué me "
"siento tan abrumada...?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:862
msgid ""
"(Booming voice) Atseger, my dear, why do you forget everything I have taught "
"you? Why do you fight your friends when you should be uniting to face the "
"enemy? Why are you losing your hope so easily?"
msgstr ""
"(voz atronadora) Atseger, querida, ¿por qué olvidas todo lo que te he "
"enseñado? ¿Por qué luchas contra tus amigos cuando deberías unirte para "
"enfrentar al enemigo? ¿Por qué pierdes la esperanza tan fácilmente?"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:866
msgid "(astonished) This voice...!"
msgstr "(asombrada) ¡Esta voz...!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:870
msgid "Master, is that really you?!"
msgstr "¡Maestro, ¿realmente eres tú?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:897
msgid "MASTER!!!"
msgstr "¡MAESTRO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:901
msgid "Master Menon! But... But..."
msgstr "¡Maestro Menon! Pero... Pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:905
msgid ""
"I understand your shock, and that's why I hardly showed my face to anyone "
"before; I didn't want to shock any of you... But this is how I was able to "
"remain alive for so long, and so I ask you to forgive me for becoming a "
"monster, and for hiding my face for so long..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo su conmoción, y por eso apenas mostré mi rostro a nadie antes. No "
"quería conmocionarlos... Pero así es como pude permanecer vivo tanto tiempo, "
"y por eso les pido que me perdonen por convertirme en un monstruo y por "
"ocultar mi rostro durante tanto tiempo..."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:909
msgid ""
"Great Menon, it is us who should beg you for forgiveness; never should we "
"have sent you away, and because of our foolishness our precious city "
"nearly..."
msgstr ""
"Gran Menon, somos nosotros quienes deberíamos pedirte perdón. Nunca "
"deberíamos haberte enviado lejos, y por nuestra estupidez nuestra preciosa "
"ciudad casi..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:913
msgid ""
"Good Smenkhare, if you wish to ask me for forgiveness, then we may call it "
"quits, right? Now, let us leave the past behind, and strengthen our union "
"more than ever before..."
msgstr ""
"Buen Smenkhare, si deseas pedirme perdón, entonces podemos considerarlo "
"saldado, ¿verdad? Ahora, dejemos el pasado atrás y fortalezcamos nuestra "
"unión más que nunca..."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:917
msgid ""
"Menon, also known as the Immortal... I deeply lamented your exiling when I "
"heard about it; like so many other Lich-Lords, I had great expectations "
"about meeting you on the battlefield. It's a pity that it took so long to "
"happen, but now we finally meet!"
msgstr ""
"Menon, también conocido como el Inmortal... Lamenté profundamente tu exilio "
"cuando me enteré. Como tantos otros Señor-Liches, tenía grandes expectativas "
"de encontrarte en el campo de batalla. Es una lástima que haya tardado tanto "
"en suceder, ¡pero ahora finalmente nos encontramos!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:921
msgid ""
"Indeed, our meeting today is a fortunate event; had I not felt so strongly "
"that my precious city, which I have defended for so long, was in desperate "
"need of aid, I wouldn't have left Hiera'Laksha and hurried here... "
"Nevertheless, Jevyan, I'm afraid that you shall soon regret meeting me on "
"the battlefield..."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, nuestro encuentro de hoy es un evento afortunado. Si no hubiera "
"sentido tan fuertemente que mi preciosa ciudad, que he defendido durante "
"tanto tiempo, necesitaba ayuda desesperadamente, no habría dejado "
"Hiera'Laksha y me habría apresurado aquí... Sin embargo, Jevyan, me temo que "
"pronto lamentarás haberme encontrado en el campo de batalla..."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:925
msgid "(grinning) We shall see about that."
msgstr "(sonriendo) Ya veremos eso."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:941
msgid ""
"Men, the Immortal is on our side now! Victory is once again within our "
"reach! Now, CHARGE!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hombres, el Inmortal está ahora de nuestro lado! ¡La victoria está una vez "
"más a nuestro alcance! ¡Ahora, ¡AL ATAQUE!"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:979
msgid "Destruction of Menon Hekare"
msgstr "Destrucción de Menon Hekare"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1003
msgid ""
"My... powers have failed me...!? But... I shall not fall, not here, not "
"today..."
msgstr ""
"¡Mis... poderes me han fallado...!? Pero... no caeré, no aquí, no hoy..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1023
msgid ""
"(echoing voice) Curses upon you, Maat'Karians... You may have prevailed "
"today, but you shall not be so lucky forever; all life is finite, every fire "
"fades, but death and darkness are eternal!"
msgstr ""
"(voz resonante) ¡Malditos sean, maat'karianos...! Pueden haber prevalecido "
"hoy, pero no tendrán tanta suerte para siempre. Toda vida es finita, todo "
"fuego se apaga, ¡pero la muerte y la oscuridad son eternas!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1027
msgid "Shame on me, I was unable to capture him..."
msgstr "Qué vergüenza, no pude capturarlo..."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1031
msgid ""
"Still, Jevyan has been far too weakened to fight any further in this war. "
"Besides, were it not for your intervention, Master, we wouldn't be alive now."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, Jevyan ha quedado demasiado debilitado para seguir luchando en esta "
"guerra. Además, si no hubiera sido por tu intervención, maestro, ahora no "
"estaríamos vivos."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1035
msgid ""
"I hope that this stands as a lesson for anyone who thinks that Master Menon "
"should stay out of Maat'Kare."
msgstr ""
"Espero que esto sirva de lección para cualquiera que piense que el maestro "
"Menon debería mantenerse fuera de Maat'Kare."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1043
msgid ""
"I thank your admiration and support. I've been away from this city for far "
"too long; but, now that I have returned, I wish to dedicate all of my power "
"and knowledge to help our civilization drive away these aggressors."
msgstr ""
"Agradezco su admiración y apoyo. He estado lejos de esta ciudad durante "
"demasiado tiempo. Pero ahora que he regresado, deseo dedicar todo mi poder y "
"conocimiento para ayudar a nuestra civilización a expulsar a estos agresores."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1047
msgid ""
"As you well know, Master, you have my full support - and not only that: I "
"want to officially vote for Menon Hekare as Maat'Kare's Great Seer!"
msgstr ""
"Como bien sabes, maestro, cuentas con todo mi apoyo. Y no solo eso: quiero "
"votar oficialmente por Menon Hekare como el Gran Vidente de Maat'Kare."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1051
msgid ""
"What?! Please, friends, let us not be taken by the enthusiasm of this great "
"victory; a Great Seer has absolute military and political powers over all of "
"the Maat'Karian civilization, and thus it isn't a title that may be "
"conferred without careful and extensive..."
msgstr ""
"¡¿Qué?! Por favor, amigos, no nos dejemos llevar por el entusiasmo de esta "
"gran victoria. Un Gran Vidente tiene poderes militares y políticos absolutos "
"sobre toda la civilización maat'kariana, y por eso no es un título que se "
"pueda otorgar sin cuidado y de manera extensa..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1055
msgid ""
"This title was created because our ancestors knew that, in times of great "
"turmoil, our land would need a single, strong and absolute leadership to "
"survive; you are right when you say that this isn't a power for anyone, but "
"I cannot see anyone as fitting for this position as Menon Hekare, who has "
"served our civilization well for seven centuries."
msgstr ""
"Este título fue creado porque nuestros ancestros sabían que, en tiempos de "
"gran agitación, nuestra tierra necesitaría un liderazgo único, fuerte y "
"absoluto para sobrevivir. Tienes razón al decir que no es un poder para "
"cualquiera, pero no veo a nadie más adecuado para este puesto que Menon "
"Hekare, quien ha servido bien a nuestra civilización durante siete siglos."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1059
msgid ""
"This title can only be entrusted by whichever ruling body is present at the "
"capital, which happens to be the Chamber of Sages. We shall hold an "
"emergency council to see what they have to say about this, but firstly we "
"must tend to the wounded and repair the damages suffered by our city."
msgstr ""
"Este título solo puede ser otorgado por el órgano gobernante que se "
"encuentre en la capital, que en este caso es la Cámara de los Sabios. "
"Celebraremos un consejo de emergencia para ver qué opinan al respecto, pero "
"primero debemos atender a los heridos y reparar los daños sufridos por "
"nuestra ciudad."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1212
msgid ""
"I anticipated so much seeing the glorious sun of Maat'Kare once again after "
"so many days in the dark tunnels of Hiera'Laksha, only to see a landscape "
"shrouded in such a thick veil of darkness... I have to do something about "
"that..."
msgstr ""
"Esperaba con tantas ganas volver a ver el glorioso sol de Maat'Kare después "
"de tantos días en los túneles oscuros de Hiera'Laksha, solo para encontrar "
"un paisaje envuelto en un velo tan espeso de oscuridad... Tengo que hacer "
"algo al respecto..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1216
msgid ""
"Saying that, the ancient, but imposing undead master raised his skeletal "
"left hand to the heavens: his hollow eyes were filled with a pitch-black "
"aura, and in his raised hand a vortex of dark energy gathered. It took some "
"seconds for the Maat'Karians to understand what was happening, but then the "
"sky became increasingly clearer, and soon the sun shone again over the "
"world: Menon had absorbed Jevyan's darkness within himself."
msgstr ""
"Dicho esto, el antiguo pero imponente maestro no-muerto levantó su mano "
"esquelética izquierda hacia los cielos: sus ojos huecos se llenaron de un "
"aura completamente negra y en su mano alzada se formó un vórtice de energía "
"oscura. Pasaron algunos segundos antes de que los maat'karianos entendieran "
"lo que ocurría, pero entonces el cielo se volvió cada vez más claro y pronto "
"el sol brilló de nuevo sobre el mundo: Menon había absorbido la oscuridad de "
"Jevyan dentro de sí mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1229
msgid ""
"(shocked) But... How... You shouldn't have been able to suck all that "
"darkness and remain standing!"
msgstr ""
"(impactado) Pero... ¿Cómo...? ¡No deberías haber podido absorber toda esa "
"oscuridad y seguir en pie!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1233
msgid ""
"I am a Master of Four Lights; I have fathomed the secrets of all paths of "
"magic to the point that neither fire, nor arcane, nor elemental, nor dark "
"powers have any effect over me - for I am both Light and Darkness, and "
"Nature is my ally. This is why I could absorb all of your darkness without "
"any side effect; but you, being a mere Lich-Lord, shall not escape my power "
"unscathed."
msgstr ""
"Soy un Maestro de las Cuatro Luces. He comprendido los secretos de todos los "
"caminos de la magia hasta el punto de que ni el fuego, ni lo arcano, ni lo "
"elemental, ni los poderes oscuros tienen efecto sobre mí, porque soy tanto "
"Luz como Oscuridad, y la Naturaleza es mi aliada. Por eso pude absorber toda "
"tu oscuridad sin ningún efecto secundario. Pero tú, siendo solo un Liche-"
"Lord, no escaparás ileso de mi poder."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1260
msgid ""
"Astounding... He raised an earthen path out of the seabed itself in order to "
"reach Jevyan!"
msgstr ""
"Asombroso... ¡Levantó un camino de tierra directamente del fondo del mar "
"para alcanzar a Jevyan!"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1295
msgid "I have failed my city and my students..."
msgstr "He fallado a mi ciudad y a mis estudiantes..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1299
msgid "Atseger, NO!"
msgstr "¡Atseger, NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1303
msgid ""
"Without Professor Atseger protecting the Academy, nothing will prevent "
"Jevyan from taking the Soul! This is a disaster!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sin la profesora Atseger protegiendo la Academia, nada impedirá que Jevyan "
"tome el Alma! ¡Esto es un desastre!"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1317
msgid "Argh! I shouldn't have died like this..."
msgstr "¡Argh! No debería haber muerto así..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1331
msgid "Sadjet, my friend, please don't die!"
msgstr "¡Sadjet, amiga mía, por favor no mueras!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1335
msgid "Apologies, girl, but I can continue no longer..."
msgstr "Disculpa, muchacha, pero ya no puedo continuar..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1339
msgid ""
"I can't believe it... even the Fire Empress couldn't stand Jevyan's power! "
"Do we have the slightest hope to defeat him...?"
msgstr ""
"No puedo creerlo... ¡ni siquiera la Emperatriz del Fuego pudo resistir el "
"poder de Jevyan! ¿Tenemos la más mínima esperanza de derrotarlo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1353
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:912
msgid "I have... failed...?!"
msgstr "¿He… fallado…?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1357
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:916
msgid "MASTER, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡MAESTRO, NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1361
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:920
msgid ""
"I can't believe it... No, I <i>refuse</i> to believe it... Master is... "
"dead?!"
msgstr ""
"No puedo creerlo... No, <i>me niego</i> a creerlo... ¡¿El maestro está... "
"muerto?!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1365
msgid ""
"So the Immortal has finally met his fate... Now, Skironians, charge and "
"destroy what is left of their pathetic city!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces el Inmortal finalmente ha encontrado su destino... ¡Ahora, "
"skironianos, carguen y destruyan lo que queda de su patética ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/09_Dark_Eclipse.cfg:1369
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:928
msgid ""
"No, this... This is the end... We have no more hopes of winning this war...!"
msgstr ""
"No, esto... Esto es el fin... ¡Ya no tenemos esperanzas de ganar esta "
"guerra...!"

#. [scenario], id=10_Waters_Of_Light
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:4
msgid "Waters of Light"
msgstr "Aguas de Luz"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:23
msgid "Defeat Lich-Lord Maurias"
msgstr "Derrota al Señor-Liche Maurias"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:51
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:492
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:632
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:918
msgid "Death of Suryen"
msgstr "Muerte de Suryen"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:270
msgid "General Suryen, I am Atenak Aracyne, captain of the... erm..."
msgstr "General Suryen, soy Atenak Aracyne, capitana del... eh..."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:274
msgid ""
"(laughing) I see, so you are the Myra Battalion of which the recruits talk "
"so much: the group of youths who not only managed to get orcs on our side, "
"but also sneaked into the Red Pinnacle and killed Erynia herself... Don't be "
"abashed, you do deserve this nickname; the Founders too were a group of "
"young and daring fighters from various backgrounds, after all."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Entiendo, así que ustedes son el Batallón Myra del que tanto hablan "
"los reclutas: el grupo de jóvenes que no solo logró poner a los orcos de "
"nuestro lado, sino que también se infiltró en el Pináculo Rojo y mató a la "
"propia Erynia... No se avergüencen, realmente merecen este apodo. Después de "
"todo, los Fundadores también fueron un grupo de jóvenes y audaces luchadores "
"de diversos orígenes."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:278
msgid ""
"General, Master... I mean, the Great Seer informed us that you were fighting "
"a Lich-Lord in these swamps, is that true?"
msgstr ""
"General, maestro... Quiero decir, el Gran Vidente nos informó que estabas "
"luchando contra un Señor-Liche en estos pantanos, ¿es cierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:282
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, it is. So far, we had only seen lesser summoners and "
"generals, but now Skiron has finally decided to send their full might. He "
"introduced himself as Lich-Lord Maurias."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, sí. Hasta ahora solo habíamos visto invocadores y "
"generales menores, pero ahora Skiron finalmente decidió enviar todo su "
"poder. Se presentó como Señor-Liche Maurias."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:286
msgid ""
"I've heard of him; he isn't known for his magical power, but he’s considered "
"the brightest mind in all of Skiron when it comes to the study of the "
"undead. It's said that he was the one who discovered a way to summon and "
"control the dark ghosts known as the Shadows."
msgstr ""
"He oído hablar de él. No es conocido por su poder mágico, pero se le "
"considera la mente más brillante de todo Skiron en el estudio de los no-"
"muertos. Se dice que fue él quien descubrió la forma de invocar y controlar "
"a los fantasmas oscuros conocidos como las Sombras."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:290
msgid "What about the gnolls who dwell here?"
msgstr "¿Y qué hay de los gnolls que viven aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:294
msgid "All dead; their bows now serve Maurias."
msgstr "Todos muertos. Sus arcos ahora sirven a Maurias."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:298
msgid ""
"Poor creatures! They may be constantly harassing us at the service of the "
"minotaurs, but they didn't deserve such fate!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pobres criaturas! Puede que nos hostiguen constantemente al servicio de los "
"minotauros, ¡pero no merecían ese destino!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:302
msgid ""
"Nobody does. So, let us waste no more time talking, and give the gnolls "
"their deserved rest."
msgstr ""
"Nadie lo merece. Así que no perdamos más tiempo hablando y demos a los "
"gnolls el descanso que merecen."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:306
msgid ""
"Ah, I almost forgot to tell: the Lich seems to have placed Shadows over the "
"swamp to strike by surprise, so beware of them. Last but not least, my "
"soldiers have recently encountered some humanoid abominations that are "
"unknown even to our mages. Albeit not very strong, they're hard to destroy, "
"can make you fall ill with a single scratch from their foul claws, and "
"are... extremely unpleasant to the sight, or so the soldiers claim."
msgstr ""
"Ah, casi olvido decirlo: parece que el Liche ha colocado Sombras sobre el "
"pantano para atacar por sorpresa, así que tengan cuidado con ellas. Por "
"último, pero no menos importante, mis soldados se han encontrado "
"recientemente con algunas abominaciones humanoides desconocidas incluso para "
"nuestros magos. Aunque no son muy fuertes, son difíciles de destruir, pueden "
"enfermarte con un solo rasguño de sus asquerosas garras y son... "
"extremadamente desagradables a la vista, según afirman los soldados."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:310
msgid "Come on, what kind of soldier lets an enemy's bad looks affect him?"
msgstr ""
"Vamos, ¿qué clase de soldado deja que la mala apariencia de un enemigo lo "
"afecte?"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:314
msgid ""
"Hush! If it was bad enough to shake even Lord Suryen's soldiers, then we "
"must be careful with those aberrations!"
msgstr ""
"¡Silencio! Si fue lo suficientemente malo como para sacudir incluso a los "
"soldados del señor Suryen, ¡entonces debemos tener cuidado con esas "
"aberraciones!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:318
msgid "As you say, Mr. Meritane..."
msgstr "Como digas, señor Meritane..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:343
msgid ""
"You know, I've been thinking about all this comparing us to Maat'Kare's "
"Founders, and I've been wondering: if our team as a whole is like Myra's, "
"which of the Founders each of us represents?"
msgstr ""
"Saben, he estado pensando en toda esta comparación con los Fundadores de "
"Maat'Kare y me he preguntado: si nuestro equipo en conjunto es como el de "
"Myra, ¿a cuál de los Fundadores representa cada uno de nosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:347
msgid ""
"Certainly you're our 'Dvalin', being the only representative of the dwarves "
"here; whilst Nyx, being the prettiest and most refined, is our 'Alenya'..."
msgstr ""
"Seguramente tú eres nuestra «Dvalin», al ser la única representante de los "
"enanos aquí. Mientras que Nyx, siendo la más bonita y refinada, es nuestra "
"«Alenya»..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:351
msgid "So that means we're going to marry?"
msgstr "¿Entonces eso significa que nos vamos a casar?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:355
msgid "Well, we do make a great pair, don't we?"
msgstr "Bueno, hacemos una gran pareja, ¿no?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:359
msgid ""
"Mahyus is our 'Akashia': antisocial, ill-tempered, but with a heart of "
"gold..."
msgstr ""
"Mahyus es nuestro «Akashia»: antisocial, de mal genio, pero con un corazón "
"de oro..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:363
msgid "(sullen) I'm our <i>what</i>?"
msgstr "(malhumorado) ¿Soy su <i>qué</i>?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:367
msgid ""
"Atenak is our 'Ravyan', for being our field commander; it does make sense "
"after all, since she's his descendant..."
msgstr ""
"Atenak es nuestra «Ravyan», por ser nuestra comandante en el campo. Después "
"de todo, tiene sentido, ya que es su descendiente..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:371
msgid "Akhen is our 'Myra', since he’s our other leader and her descendant..."
msgstr ""
"Akhen es nuestro «Myra», ya que es nuestro otro líder y su descendiente..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:375
msgid "...And, since he's 'Myra', naturally Merwe is our 'Jevyan'!"
msgstr "...Y como él es «Myra», ¡naturalmente Merwe es nuestro «Jevyan»!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:379
msgid "(sigh) I won't even bother getting angry at you any more..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Ya ni siquiera me molestaré en enojarme contigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:383
msgid ""
"Wait, since when I'm a leader? I have no leadership skills, Atenak has them.."
msgstr ""
"Espera, ¿desde cuándo soy un líder? No tengo habilidades de liderazgo, "
"Atenak las tiene..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:387
msgid ""
"It may be so, but you're the one who united us all. In case you haven't "
"noticed, neither Nyx, nor Sigdral would be here if it wasn't for you, and "
"the same goes for Merwe and Mahyus."
msgstr ""
"Puede ser así, pero tú eres quien nos unió a todos. Por si no lo has notado, "
"ni Nyx ni Sigdral estarían aquí si no fuera por ti, y lo mismo aplica para "
"Merwe y Mahyus."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:391
msgid "Well, when you put it that way..."
msgstr "Bueno, cuando lo pones de esa manera..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:406
msgid "(shocked) By the Gods of Light, what is that thing?"
msgstr "(impactada) ¡Por los Dioses de la Luz, ¿qué es esa cosa?!"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:410
msgid "That's one of the abominations I told you about."
msgstr "Esa es una de las abominaciones de las que les hablé."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:414
msgid ""
"Nyx takes back what she said earlier... Nyx has seen many gross things in "
"her life, but that thing beats all of them with ease."
msgstr ""
"Nyx se retracta de lo que dijo antes... Nyx ha visto muchas cosas asquerosas "
"en su vida, pero esa cosa las supera a todas con facilidad."

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:418
msgid ""
"(voice echoing in the distance) He he, seems like my creations are becoming "
"popular amongst you, aren't they? I bet that even you Maat'Karians, with all "
"your knowledge, have never created such a thing, have you?"
msgstr ""
"(voz resonando a lo lejos) Je je, parece que mis creaciones se están "
"volviendo populares entre ustedes, ¿verdad? Apuesto a que ni siquiera "
"ustedes, los maat'karianos, con todo su conocimiento, han creado nunca algo "
"así, ¿o sí?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:422
msgid ""
"Nor would we ever want to! Unlike you Skironians, we have limits to what we "
"do with our own power!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y nunca querríamos hacerlo! A diferencia de ustedes, los skironianos, "
"nosotros tenemos límites en lo que hacemos con nuestro propio poder."

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:426
msgid ""
"(laughing) Oh, come on, don't tell me that your mages have never thought "
"about how <i>great</i> it would be, to create an undead that is resilient to "
"holy magic! Because this is what I've done here: a moving dead body which "
"still keeps its own soul!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Oh, vamos, no me digan que sus magos nunca han pensado en lo "
"<i>grandioso</i> que sería crear un no-muerto resistente a la magia sagrada. "
"¡Porque eso es lo que he hecho aquí: un cuerpo muerto en movimiento que aún "
"conserva su propia alma!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:430
msgid ""
"I see... Normal undead have their bodies filled with dark magic, which keeps "
"them moving, but which can also be easily dispelled by holy magic. However, "
"this... thing's body is moved by its original soul, which can't be easily "
"purged from a body by arcane beams."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Los no-muertos normales tienen sus cuerpos llenos de magia "
"oscura que los mantiene en movimiento, pero que también puede ser disipada "
"fácilmente por la magia sagrada. Sin embargo, el cuerpo de esta... cosa se "
"mueve por su alma original, que no puede ser purgada fácilmente de un cuerpo "
"mediante rayos arcanos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:434
msgid ""
"So the person that monster once was still lives inside that bloated ruin...?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces la persona que ese monstruo fue alguna vez todavía vive dentro de "
"esa ruina hinchada...?"

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:438
msgid ""
"Oh, no, no, no, none of my ghouls was made out of a human; the ones you see "
"before you were mere, ah... How do you call them again? Ah, that’s it, "
"they're gnolls, right? Eh, they were a very easy prey, but the downside is "
"that their bodies are quite frail..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, no, no, no, ninguno de mis necrófagos fue hecho a partir de un humano. "
"Los que ven delante de ustedes eran simples, ah... ¿Cómo los llaman de "
"nuevo? Ah, eso es, ¿son gnolls, verdad? Eh, fueron una presa muy fácil, pero "
"el inconveniente es que sus cuerpos son bastante frágiles..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:442
msgid ""
"(crying in fury) You... How dare you do this... No living being should be "
"used as a toy..."
msgstr ""
"(llorando de furia) Tú... ¿Cómo te atreves a hacer esto...? Ningún ser vivo "
"debería ser usado como un juguete..."

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:446
msgid ""
"But if the weak weren't made to serve the interests of the strong, what is "
"their purpose in existence?"
msgstr ""
"Pero si los débiles no fueron hechos para servir a los intereses de los "
"fuertes, ¿cuál es su propósito en la existencia?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:450
msgid ""
"(clenching fists) You disgusting monster... By the Gods of Light, I will not "
"let you live beyond this battle...!"
msgstr ""
"(apretando los puños) Tú, monstruo asqueroso... Por los Dioses de la Luz, "
"¡no te dejaré vivir más allá de esta batalla...!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:454
msgid ""
"Merwe... Let's destroy this monster together, all right? Just please, get a "
"hold of yourself, and don't do anything stupid, for this is exactly what he "
"wants you to do..."
msgstr ""
"Merwe... Destruyamos a este monstruo juntos, ¿de acuerdo? Solo por favor, "
"contrólate y no hagas nada estúpido, porque eso es exactamente lo que él "
"quiere que hagas..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:458
msgid ""
"All right... Leave him to me, though; if we are not careful, he'll escape "
"just like Jevyan and Stygia did, but I shall not let that happen..."
msgstr ""
"Está bien... Déjenmelo a mí, sin embargo. Si no tenemos cuidado, escapará "
"igual que Jevyan y Stygia, pero no permitiré que eso ocurra..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:464
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:599
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:890
msgid "Defeat Lich-Lord Maurias with Merwe"
msgstr "Derrota al Señor-Liche Maurias con Merwe"

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:516
msgid ""
"Oh, ho-ho, behold, my children, the Maat'Karians are managing to get closer "
"to me! Ah, I see, I see, you don't want me to get harmed, and wish to join "
"the fray as well... Oh, you're such lovely kids, I wish I didn't have to "
"risk losing you, but I have no choice... Rise, my elite warriors! Make these "
"Maat'Karians taste the same terror once felt by the strong people of "
"Thalassia!"
msgstr ""
"Oh, jo jo, miren, mis hijos, ¡los maat'karianos están logrando acercarse a "
"mí! Ah, ya veo, ya veo, no quieren que me lastimen y desean unirse también a "
"la refriega... Oh, son unos niños tan adorables, desearía no tener que "
"arriesgarme a perderlos, pero no tengo opción... ¡Levántense, mis guerreros "
"de élite! ¡Hagan que estos maat'karianos prueben el mismo terror que una vez "
"sintieron los fuertes pueblos de Thalassia!"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:529
msgid ""
"(sigh) Great, more undead are rising from the water. And I thought we'd be "
"done with it before breakfast..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Genial, más no-muertos se levantan del agua. Y yo que pensaba que "
"terminaríamos antes del desayuno..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:533
msgid ""
"*This water... It spreads all over this region, reaching nearly every undead "
"here... But, would it work...?*"
msgstr ""
"*Esta agua... Se extiende por toda esta región, alcanzando a casi todos los "
"no-muertos aquí... Pero, ¿funcionaría...?*"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:540
msgid "Hey Mahyus, I suggest you to take your undead out of the water..."
msgstr "Oye Mahyus, te sugiero que saques a tus no-muertos del agua..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:548
msgid ""
"I think I've never told you how I imbued my ankh with such strong arcane "
"magic, have I?"
msgstr ""
"Creo que nunca les conté cómo imbui mi ankh con una magia arcana tan fuerte, "
"¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:552
msgid "Didn't you once say that you simply didn't know how you had done that?"
msgstr "¿No dijiste una vez que simplemente no sabías cómo lo habías hecho?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:556
msgid ""
"At the time, I really didn't, but lately I've been giving it a second "
"thought, and I think I've found the answer. When I first learned magic, I "
"was so excited that I often played with it; amongst other things, I used to "
"invoke some weak arcane light on my Cross of Life, just to see its crystals "
"glittering..."
msgstr ""
"En ese momento realmente no lo sabía, pero últimamente le he dado una "
"segunda vuelta y creo que he encontrado la respuesta. Cuando aprendí magia "
"por primera vez, estaba tan emocionado que a menudo jugaba con ella. Entre "
"otras cosas, solía invocar una luz arcana débil sobre mi Cruz de la Vida, "
"solo para ver cómo brillaban sus cristales..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:560
msgid ""
"(giggling) Nyx can picture a tiny Akhen, smiling from ear to ear and "
"giggling with delight as he blew the cross with arcane energy..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Nyx puede imaginar a un pequeño Akhen sonriendo de oreja a oreja y "
"riendo de alegría mientras soplaba la cruz con energía arcana..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:564
msgid ""
"(blushing slightly) Well, anyway, the thing is that my cross is made of "
"magically-conductive wood and crystals, just like a mage's staff, and which "
"absorbs magical energy. It's true that my arcane light was very weak, but "
"the tiny amounts of arcane energy showered on the cross accumulated inside "
"it until it became an actually huge amount of energy; you see, I did play "
"with it for a long time."
msgstr ""
"(sonrojándose ligeramente) Bueno, de todos modos, el asunto es que mi cruz "
"está hecha de madera y cristales conductores de magia, igual que el bastón "
"de un mago, y que absorbe energía mágica. Es cierto que mi luz arcana era "
"muy débil, pero las pequeñas cantidades de energía arcana que llovían sobre "
"la cruz se acumularon dentro de ella hasta convertirse en una cantidad "
"realmente enorme de energía. Verán, jugué con ella durante mucho tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:568
msgid "And how does this information helps us win this battle?"
msgstr "¿Y cómo nos ayuda esta información a ganar esta batalla?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:572
msgid ""
"What I'm thinking about is: if the exposition to arcane energy has caused "
"the Cross of Life to get 'arcanized', wouldn't the same happen with water, "
"which is magically-conductive as well?"
msgstr ""
"Lo que estoy pensando es: si la exposición a la energía arcana ha hecho que "
"la Cruz de la Vida se «arcanice», ¿no ocurriría lo mismo con el agua, que "
"también es conductora de magia?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:576
msgid ""
"I see what you're planning to do... But, even if it works, will the cross be "
"able to 'arcanize' this entire swamp?"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo lo que planeas hacer... Pero, aunque funcione, ¿la cruz podrá "
"«arcanizar» todo este pantano?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:580
msgid ""
"I'm not sure; maybe I will only imbue the water with arcane energy within a "
"short radius only, but I should still try it, right?"
msgstr ""
"No estoy seguro. Tal vez solo imbuya el agua con energía arcana en un radio "
"corto, pero igual debería intentarlo, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:584
msgid ""
"Indeed you should. The undead keep growing in numbers, and so a trick like "
"this would be extremely welcome."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que deberías. Los no-muertos siguen aumentando en número, así "
"que un truco como este sería muy bienvenido."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:588
msgid ""
"Then concentrate on making that work, Akhen; Nyx and the others shall "
"protect you while you're busy."
msgstr ""
"Entonces concéntrate en hacer que eso funcione, Akhen. Nyx y los demás te "
"protegerán mientras estás ocupado."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:604
msgid "Keep Akhen at 20,24 for 1 turn so that he may arcanize the waters"
msgstr ""
"Mantén a Akhen en 20,24 durante 1 turno para que pueda arcanizar las aguas"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:638
msgid ""
"WARN: Keep Nyx and Mahyus' undead out of the water, or they will be hit as "
"well!"
msgstr ""
"ADVERTENCIA: Mantén a los no-muertos de Nyx y Mahyus fuera del agua, ¡o "
"ellos también serán afectados!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:663
msgid ""
"I think this is a good place from which to spread the cross' holy energy... "
"Please, cover me as I make it work!"
msgstr ""
"Creo que este es un buen lugar desde donde extender la energía sagrada de la "
"cruz... ¡Por favor, cúbranme mientras lo hago funcionar!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:719
msgid ""
"I... I think it's working! Nyx, Mahyus, I hope you're out of the water, for "
"I can't hold back the cross' power any longer...!"
msgstr ""
"Yo... ¡Creo que está funcionando! Nyx, Mahyus, espero que estén fuera del "
"agua, ¡porque ya no puedo contener más el poder de la cruz...!"

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:850
msgid "NO!!! By the Gods of Darkness, what have you done to my children?"
msgstr "¡NO!!! Por los Dioses de la Oscuridad, ¿qué le has hecho a mis hijos?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:854
msgid ""
"They're being freed from your tyranny, you mad lich, that's all! Now, "
"friends, this is our chance to finish off this monster!"
msgstr ""
"¡Están siendo liberados de tu tiranía, loco liche, eso es todo! ¡Ahora, "
"amigos, esta es nuestra oportunidad de acabar con este monstruo!"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:858
msgid ""
"As expected from Menon's foster-son! However, the holy waters don't seem to "
"be affecting the undead any more..."
msgstr ""
"¡Tal como se esperaba del hijo adoptivo de Menon! Sin embargo, las aguas "
"sagradas ya no parecen afectar a los no-muertos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:862
msgid ""
"I think that the water's holy energy has dissipated already; it has been "
"exposed to arcane energy for too short a period of time, after all. "
"Besides... I don't sense any energy from my Cross of Life either."
msgstr ""
"Creo que la energía sagrada del agua ya se ha disipado. Después de todo, ha "
"estado expuesta a la energía arcana durante un período demasiado corto. "
"Además... tampoco siento energía de mi Cruz de la Vida."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:866
msgid ""
"Well, after such an outburst, it's to be expected that it would completely "
"run out of energy. At least now you know how to make more of those."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, después de un estallido así, era de esperarse que se quedara "
"completamente sin energía. Al menos ahora sabes cómo hacer más de esas."

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:944
msgid ""
"Oh, to be defeated by a mere Maat'Karian girl! But I will not forget your "
"face, light mage; I withdraw now, but I will find you again in the future, "
"and when that happens, you will not-"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, ser derrotado por una simple muchacha maat'kariana! Pero no olvidaré tu "
"rostro, maga de la luz. Me retiro ahora, pero te encontraré de nuevo en el "
"futuro, y cuando eso ocurra, tú no-"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:948
msgid ""
"No, you bastard, this is the first and last time we ever meet - and <i>I</i> "
"will be the last thing you'll ever see!"
msgstr ""
"No, bastardo, esta es la primera y última vez que nos encontramos, ¡y <i>yo</"
"i> seré lo último que verás!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:952
msgid ""
"'O Stars of Arcane Light, breakers of the Primeval Darkness, show me your "
"glorious might, burst in all your brightness'!"
msgstr ""
"«¡Oh Estrellas de Luz Arcana, rompedoras de la Oscuridad Primigenia, "
"muéstrenme su glorioso poder, estallen en todo su brillo!»"

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:965
msgid ""
"AARRGHH!!! Damn you, Maat'Karian! Dispel this damned wall of light at once, "
"I can't cross it in this state!"
msgstr ""
"¡AARRGHH!!! ¡Maldita maat'kariana! ¡Disipa esta maldita muralla de luz de "
"inmediato, no puedo cruzarla en este estado!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:969
msgid ""
"Disappear from this world, your cursed lich! SCOURGE OF THE FIVE STARS!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡Desaparece de este mundo, liche maldito! ¡AZOTE DE LAS CINCO ESTRELLAS!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:991
msgid "NNOOOOO!!!"
msgstr "¡NNOOOOO!!!"

#. [effect], apply_to=new_attack, type=arcane, range=ranged
#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1017
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Menon.cfg:110
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Menon_Dark.cfg:110
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Menon_Young.cfg:82
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Silver_Master_Atseger.cfg:57
msgid "Tie-Seba Hedjay"
msgstr "Tie-Seba Hedjay"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1058
msgid "(astonished) Merwe, this..."
msgstr "(asombrado) Merwe, esto..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1062
msgid ""
"(smiling) This is what I call kicking an arse! Why didn't you tell us that "
"you were so amazing before?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) ¡Esto es lo que yo llamo dar una patada en el trasero! ¿Por qué "
"no nos dijiste antes que eras tan increíble?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1066
msgid ""
"(panting) I, well... I've just recently learned this spell... Master Menon "
"taught me himself, after I queried him about how he had absorbed Jevyan's "
"darkness… He said he had used the Supreme Umbra Spell... And then he taught "
"me this spell, 'Tie-Seba Hedjay', which is the Supreme Lucent Spell... I'm "
"glad that I was able to successfully cast it, but it's certainly taken a "
"toll on me..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Yo, bueno... Acabo de aprender este hechizo hace poco... El "
"maestro Menon me lo enseñó él mismo después de que le preguntara cómo había "
"absorbido la oscuridad de Jevyan... Dijo que había usado el Hechizo Umbra "
"Supremo... Y luego me enseñó este hechizo, «Tie-Seba Hedjay», que es el "
"Hechizo Luciente Supremo... Me alegra haber podido lanzarlo con éxito, pero "
"sin duda me ha pasado factura..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1070
msgid ""
"Merwe, you were wonderful! Please, take a rest, you certainly deserve it!"
msgstr ""
"¡Merwe, estuviste maravillosa! Por favor, descansa, ¡sin duda lo mereces!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1074
msgid "Indeed, Nyx thinks it's time for her to actually stop picking on you..."
msgstr "En efecto, Nyx cree que es hora de que realmente deje de molestarte..."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1078
msgid ""
"Ah, Myra Battalion, I haven't had so much fun fighting alongside an ally in "
"ages... Come, I want you and your soldiers to feast alongside me and my men; "
"our mission here in the Gnoll Swamps is not over yet, and so we need to "
"restore our energies for the next challenge!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, Batallón Myra, hace años que no me divertía tanto luchando junto a un "
"aliado... Vengan, quiero que ustedes y sus soldados celebren un festín junto "
"a mí y mis hombres. Nuestra misión aquí en los Pantanos de los Gnolls aún no "
"ha terminado, así que necesitamos restaurar nuestras energías para el "
"próximo desafío."

#. [message], speaker=Maurias
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1106
msgid ""
"Oh, to be defeated by a mere Maat'Karian girl! But I will not forget your "
"face, light mage; I will withdraw now, but I will find you again in the "
"future, and when that happens, you will not be so lucky any more, little "
"girl..."
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, ser derrotado por una simple muchacha maat'kariana! Pero no olvidaré tu "
"rostro, maga de la luz. Me retiraré ahora, pero te encontraré de nuevo en el "
"futuro, y cuando eso ocurra, ya no tendrás tanta suerte, niñita..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1122
msgid "No! I would have been able to prevent him from fleeing!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Habría podido evitar que escapara!"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1136
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:898
msgid "Damn these... monsters...!"
msgstr "¡Malditos... monstruos...!"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/10_Waters_Of_Light.cfg:1147
msgid ""
"Damn it, we should have ended this earlier! Maurias should get "
"reinforcements at any time now!"
msgstr ""
"Maldición, ¡deberíamos haber terminado esto antes! Maurias debería recibir "
"refuerzos en cualquier momento ahora."

#. [scenario], id=11_True_Darkness
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:4
msgid "True Darkness"
msgstr "Oscuridad Verdadera"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:24
msgid "Find Argatyr"
msgstr "Encuentra a Argatyr"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:60
msgid ""
"You may recall and use your old dwarvish units for a while in this scenario. "
"Also, keep an eye on your orcish allies; you might not want to leave your "
"units near them for long..."
msgstr ""
"Puedes reincorporar y usar tus antiguas unidades enanas durante un tiempo en "
"este escenario. Además, mantén un ojo en tus aliados orcos; es posible que "
"no quieras dejar tus unidades cerca de ellos por mucho tiempo..."

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Lord
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Dragonguard
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Sentinel
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Runemaster
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:98
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:102
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:77
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:94
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:113
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:92
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:129
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:151
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:174
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:196
msgid "Motsoghnir Dwarves"
msgstr "Enanos Motsoghnir"

#. [side], type=Orcish Warlord
#. [side], type=Orcish Sorcerer
#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:192
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:74
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:108
msgid "Burning Fang Clan"
msgstr "Clan Colmillo Ardiente"

#. [side], type=Moon Blade
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:213
msgid "Silver Claw Clan"
msgstr "Clan Garra Plateada"

#. [side], type=General SK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:252
msgid "General Thaneos"
msgstr "General Thaneos"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:354
msgid ""
"What?! How did orcs manage to come so deep into the tunnels of the "
"Motsoghnir?! Quick, boys, chop their heads off where they..."
msgstr ""
"¡¿Qué?! ¿Cómo lograron los orcos llegar tan profundo en los túneles de los "
"Motsoghnir? ¡Rápido, muchachos, córteles la cabeza donde..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:358
msgid ""
"Gomatol, please wait! These orcs are loyal to our ally, Varag, and have come "
"here at the request of Lord Vindalf!"
msgstr ""
"¡Gomatol, por favor espera! Estos orcos son leales a nuestro aliado Varag y "
"han venido aquí a petición del señor Vindalf."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Och, so he has asked orcs for aid?! Now I understand why Lord Argatyr "
"doesn't like him very much: first he befriends those elves, and now he "
"befriends orcs..."
msgstr ""
"Och, ¿así que pidió ayuda a los orcos? ¡Ahora entiendo por qué al señor "
"Argatyr no le cae muy bien: primero se hace amigo de esos elfos y ahora se "
"hace amigo de orcos..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:366
msgid "You watch out how you talk of my brother, you stupid Motsoghnir!"
msgstr "¡Cuida cómo hablas de mi hermano, estúpido Motsoghnir!"

#. [message], speaker=Vigdash
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Yeah, dwarf, we've come here to save your tiny asses, so you should be more "
"grateful to us..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, enano, hemos venido aquí a salvar sus pequeños traseros, así que "
"deberían estar más agradecidos con nosotros..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:374
msgid ""
"(sullen) Well, be it then... Your aid is more than welcome, indeed, even "
"though Lord Argatyr won't be glad for being helped by orcs, humans or "
"wargs..."
msgstr ""
"(malhumorado) Bueno, que así sea entonces... Su ayuda es más que bienvenida, "
"en efecto, aunque al señor Argatyr no le agradará ser ayudado por orcos, "
"humanos o huargos..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:378
msgid ""
"I'm sure he won't, but he’ll have to swallow his pride if he wishes to be "
"victorious today! And where is he, anyway?"
msgstr ""
"Estoy segura de que no le agradará, ¡pero tendrá que tragarse su orgullo si "
"quiere ser victorioso hoy! ¿Y dónde está él, de todos modos?"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:382
msgid ""
"He, well... Once he heard that reinforcements were coming, he said that he "
"'didn't need any help at all', and then he took the warriors and rushed "
"against the enemy..."
msgstr ""
"Él, bueno... Una vez que escuchó que venían refuerzos, dijo que «no "
"necesitaba ninguna ayuda en absoluto» y luego tomó a los guerreros y se "
"lanzó contra el enemigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:386
msgid "(snorting) Oh damn, that's so <i>typical</i> of him..."
msgstr "(resoplando) Oh maldición, eso es tan <i>típico</i> de él..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:390
msgid ""
"So he's fighting the Skironian hordes on his own?! We must go help him at "
"once!"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Así que está luchando solo contra las hordas skironianas?! ¡Debemos ir a "
"ayudarlo de inmediato!"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:394
msgid ""
"Och, we must really hurry; it's been a while since I last heard of Lord "
"Argatyr, and I'm starting to worry about him..."
msgstr ""
"Och, realmente debemos apurarnos. Hace rato que no sé nada del señor Argatyr "
"y estoy empezando a preocuparme por él..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Damn, it's so humid in these caves... It seems like we’re already in the "
"tunnels beneath the Strait of the Continents."
msgstr ""
"Maldición, qué humedad hay en estas cuevas... Parece que ya estamos en los "
"túneles debajo del Estrecho de los Continentes."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:416
msgid ""
"(shivers) To think that we have such a colossal water mass just above our "
"heads..."
msgstr ""
"(estremeciéndose) Pensar que tenemos una masa de agua tan colosal justo "
"encima de nuestras cabezas..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:420
msgid ""
"Worry not, friends, these tunnels were built by us Motsoghnir; we've managed "
"to cross the vast Stormy Ocean in such tunnels, after all!"
msgstr ""
"No se preocupen, amigos, estos túneles fueron construidos por nosotros los "
"Motsoghnir. ¡Después de todo, logramos cruzar el vasto Océano Tormentoso en "
"túneles como estos!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:424
msgid ""
"But the tunnels you've built beneath that ocean ended up crushed by the "
"sea's weight, didn't they?"
msgstr ""
"Pero los túneles que construyeron debajo de ese océano terminaron aplastados "
"por el peso del mar, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:448
msgid ""
"Lord Argatyr! It's relieving to see that you and our brothers are faring "
"well against these monsters!"
msgstr ""
"¡Señor Argatyr! Es un alivio ver que tú y nuestros hermanos se están "
"defendiendo bien contra estos monstruos."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:452
msgid ""
"On the other hand, I don't find it relieving to see you out of the post I "
"designed you to be, nor to see meddlesome humans, lowly orcs and... Is that "
"a blood-sucker?"
msgstr ""
"Por otro lado, no me alivia verte fuera del puesto para el que te designé, "
"ni ver a humanos entrometidos, orcos inferiores y... ¿Eso es una chupasangre?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:456
msgid ""
"Cut it out already, Argatyr! You know full well that you cannot hold off so "
"many enemies alone, so drop your damn arrogance and be grateful we all came "
"in time to help you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ya basta, Argatyr! Sabes muy bien que no puedes contener a tantos enemigos "
"solo, así que deja tu maldita arrogancia y agradece que todos llegamos a "
"tiempo para ayudarte."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:460
msgid ""
"So even you have come... I see: probably that soft, friend-of-elf Vindalf "
"got all scared because of the violence of the Skironians' offensive and "
"cried out for help... Well, I don’t know what he's told you, but your aid is "
"not needed here - though it'd be helpful of you to get out of our way..."
msgstr ""
"Así que hasta tú has venido... Entiendo: probablemente ese blando amigo de "
"los elfos, Vindalf, se asustó por la violencia de la ofensiva skironian y "
"pidió ayuda a gritos... Bueno, no sé qué les ha dicho, pero su ayuda no es "
"necesaria aquí, aunque sería útil que se quitaran de nuestro camino..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:464
msgid ""
"You really don't change, do you? Fine, then, if you wish to die alone, we'll "
"let you; we'll be right behind your keep, preparing for when the Skironians "
"cut through your ranks and advance towards Netjer-Ta..."
msgstr ""
"Realmente no cambias, ¿verdad? Está bien, entonces, si quieres morir solo, "
"te dejaremos. Estaremos justo detrás de tu torreón, preparándonos para "
"cuando los skironianos atraviesen tus filas y avancen hacia Netjer-Ta..."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:468
msgid ""
"(chuckling) Make yourselves comfortable back there - and make sure to get a "
"good view of me, so that you may have a chance to witness the power of the "
"Motsoghnir's greatest relic."
msgstr ""
"(riendo entre dientes) Pónganse cómodos allá atrás, y asegúrense de tener "
"una buena vista de mí, para que tengan la oportunidad de presenciar el poder "
"de la mayor reliquia de los Motsoghnir."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:472
msgid "Wait a minute, this hammer you're wielding... Is it the..."
msgstr "Espera un momento, ese martillo que estás empuñando... ¿Es el...?"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:476
msgid ""
"...Hammer of Ymer, one of the two artefacts used by Moradin himself to craft "
"our people out of the hardest rocks in the deepest abyss, brought by our "
"forefathers from the Great Continent; a marvel of power and craftsmanship "
"that would make even Myra's fabled Trident look like a fisherman's tool."
msgstr ""
"...Martillo de Ymer, uno de los dos artefactos usados por el propio Moradin "
"para forjar a nuestro pueblo a partir de las rocas más duras del abismo más "
"profundo, traído por nuestros antepasados desde el Gran Continente. Una "
"maravilla de poder y artesanía que haría que incluso el legendario Tridente "
"de Myra parezca una herramienta de pescador."

#. [message], speaker=Vigdash
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:480
msgid ""
"Hrumph! Let the little dwarf get himself butchered by the southerners, if "
"that's what he wants; I'll enjoy seeing him squeal like the pig he is..."
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! Que el enano pequeño se deje masacrar por los sureños si eso es lo "
"que quiere. Disfrutaré viéndolo chillar como el cerdo que es..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:492
msgid "(shocked) What..."
msgstr "(impactada) ¿Qué...?"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:500
msgid ""
"Chief...! YOU BLOODY, TREACHEROUS DWARF, YOU'LL PAY FOR KILLING OUR CHIEF!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jefe...! ¡ENANO SANGRIENTO Y TRAIDOR, PAGARÁS POR HABER MATADO A NUESTRO "
"JEFE!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:504
msgid "Argatyr, you idiot, what have you..."
msgstr "Argatyr, idiota, ¿qué has...?"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:508
msgid ""
"(threatening) This is what happens to scum who dares to insult me - and you "
"better watch your own mouth, Sigdral! I will no longer tolerate your "
"disrespectfulness! Now, gather your mongrel lackeys and remove yourself from "
"this cave!"
msgstr ""
"(amenazante) Esto es lo que les pasa a la escoria que se atreve a "
"insultarme, ¡y más te vale cuidar tu boca, Sigdral! ¡Ya no toleraré más tu "
"falta de respeto! Ahora, reúne a tus lacayos mestizos y salgan de esta cueva."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:518
msgid "(appalled) But... what on Irdya is he thinking..."
msgstr "(horrorizada) Pero... ¿en qué demonios está pensando...?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:522
msgid ""
"Give up, Atenak, he's... Honestly, I knew that he was a difficult dwarf, but "
"this..."
msgstr ""
"Déjalo, Atenak, él es... Sinceramente, sabía que era un enano difícil, pero "
"esto..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:526
msgid ""
"We get it, Sigdral. Now, let us avoid his fighters, before he decides to "
"strike any of us as well..."
msgstr ""
"Entendemos, Sigdral. Ahora evitemos a sus luchadores, antes de que decida "
"atacarnos también a nosotros..."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Retreat if you want, we won't give a single step backwards before we have "
"that stinking dwarf's head! And you, humans, you better stay out of our way, "
"or you may get yourself hurt too!"
msgstr ""
"Retírense si quieren, ¡no daremos ni un solo paso atrás antes de tener la "
"cabeza de ese enano apestoso! Y ustedes, humanos, mejor manténganse fuera de "
"nuestro camino, o podrían salir lastimados también."

#. [message], speaker=Garuro
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:540
msgid ""
"As I thought, we can never trust these barbarians... Come, human friends, we "
"shall help you defend against orcs, dwarves and Skironians alike!"
msgstr ""
"Como pensaba, nunca podemos confiar en estos bárbaros... Vengan, amigos "
"humanos, los ayudaremos a defenderse contra orcos, enanos y skironianos por "
"igual."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:544
msgid "(horrified) By the Gods, this will be a bloodbath!"
msgstr "(horrorizada) ¡Por los Dioses, esto va a ser una masacre!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:548
msgid ""
"I fear so, but we must not leave these caves; we must make sure that no "
"Skironian advances towards our continent. I don’t think we should worry "
"about Argatyr; he's focused in fighting the orcs and the Skironians, so, if "
"we just stay away from him, he won't attack us."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que sí, pero no debemos abandonar estas cuevas. Debemos asegurarnos "
"de que ningún skironian avance hacia nuestro continente. No creo que debamos "
"preocuparnos por Argatyr. Está concentrado en luchar contra los orcos y los "
"skironianos, así que si nos mantenemos alejados de él, no nos atacará."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:552
msgid "(puzzled) I... I must..."
msgstr "(desconcertado) Yo... debo..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:556
msgid "Sorry, buddy..."
msgstr "Lo siento, amigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:581
msgid ""
"You, dwarves, you better take him out of this battle, or he'll end up "
"seriously hurt."
msgstr ""
"Ustedes, enanos, mejor sáquenlo de esta batalla o terminará gravemente "
"herido."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:590
msgid ""
"One of us will do that, but the others will stay and fight; even if Lord "
"Argatyr tries to kill us, we can't flee while the Skironians are attacking!"
msgstr ""
"Uno de nosotros lo hará, pero los demás nos quedaremos y lucharemos. ¡Aunque "
"el señor Argatyr intente matarnos, no podemos huir mientras los skironianos "
"nos atacan!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:594
msgid "(sigh) How did it all come down to this madness...?"
msgstr "(suspiro) ¿Cómo llegamos a esta locura...?"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:612
msgid "Clean the caves of enemies"
msgstr "Limpia las cuevas de enemigos"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:640
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:703
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:902
msgid "Death of Argatyr"
msgstr "Muerte de Argatyr"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:648
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:711
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:910
msgid ""
"You may no longer recall your old dwarvish units. Furthermore, even though "
"Argatyr is now your enemy, you must not let him die, or the enemy will be "
"able to advance into Netjer-Ta."
msgstr ""
"Ya no puedes reincorporar tus antiguas unidades enanas. Además, aunque "
"Argatyr ahora es tu enemigo, no debes dejar que muera, o el enemigo podrá "
"avanzar hacia Netjer-Ta."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:675
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:874
msgid "Defeat at least one of the Lich-Lords in the southern tunnels"
msgstr "Derrota al menos a uno de los Señores-Liches en los túneles del sur"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:766
msgid "This presence...!"
msgstr "¡Esta presencia…!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:770
msgid "Oh, no, that's not good..."
msgstr "Oh no, eso no es bueno..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:774
msgid "Hey, stop scaring Nyx! What's going on here?"
msgstr "¡Oye, deja de asustar a Nyx! ¿Qué está pasando aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:778
msgid "Stygia... She is here!"
msgstr "Stygia... ¡Ella está aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:782
msgid ""
"Oh, my, my, my... You sure are lovely foes, greeting me with the gift of "
"such wonderful sight: orcs, dwarves, undead, humans and wargs all butchering "
"each other, what a grand bloodshed!"
msgstr ""
"Oh, cielos, cielos, cielos... Sin duda son unos enemigos encantadores, "
"recibiéndome con el regalo de una vista tan maravillosa: orcos, enanos, no-"
"muertos, humanos y huargos masacrándose entre sí. ¡Qué gran derramamiento de "
"sangre!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:786
msgid "You... Are you the witch in command of the lowly southerners' invasion?"
msgstr ""
"Tú... ¿Eres la bruja al mando de la invasión de los sureños inferiores?"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:790
msgid ""
"(amused) To hear one so small calling us 'lowly'... Yes, little lord, I am "
"Stygia, and I have come here to see for myself why my subordinates were "
"having so much trouble waving you aside."
msgstr ""
"(divertida) Escuchar a alguien tan pequeño llamarnos «inferiores»... Sí, "
"pequeño señor, soy Stygia y he venido aquí para ver por mí misma por qué mis "
"subordinados tenían tanta dificultad para apartarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:794
msgid ""
"Blame them not; they're simply puny weaklings who are being thrown against "
"the might of the Motsoghnir by their incompetent commanders. However, if you "
"want to see your goal reached, you should come here and try it yourself - "
"not that you'll succeed, though..."
msgstr ""
"No los culpes. Son simplemente debiluchos insignificantes que sus "
"comandantes incompetentes están lanzando contra el poder de los Motsoghnir. "
"Sin embargo, si quieres ver tu objetivo cumplido, deberías venir aquí e "
"intentarlo tú misma, aunque no creo que lo logres..."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:798
msgid ""
"Ah, midget, be certain that I will go there and spill your blood myself soon "
"enough. However, I want to let you, and those behind you, experience the "
"terror of death to the fullest..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, enano, ten por seguro que iré allí y derramaré tu sangre yo misma muy "
"pronto. Sin embargo, quiero que tú y los que están detrás de ti experimenten "
"el terror de la muerte en su máxima expresión..."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:813
msgid "...Witness true darkness..."
msgstr "...Contemplen la verdadera oscuridad..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:817
msgid "Damn it, even my light can barely shine in this darkness!"
msgstr "Maldición, ¡ni siquiera mi luz logra brillar en esta oscuridad!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:827
msgid ""
"Everyone, do not lose control! We can still hear each other, so let us stay "
"close together! Keep closed formations, protect the man next to you, and "
"let's march slowly and carefully!"
msgstr ""
"¡Todos, no pierdan el control! Todavía podemos escucharnos, así que "
"mantengámonos juntos. Mantengan formaciones cerradas, protejan al compañero "
"de al lado y avancemos lentamente y con cuidado."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:831
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:861
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:925
msgid "Are you insane?! Do you want us to rush even deeper into this mayhem?!"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Estás loca?! ¡¿Quieres que nos lancemos aún más profundo en este caos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:835
msgid ""
"Argatyr's fighting the Skironian hordes on his own! We must go help him!"
msgstr ""
"¡Argatyr está luchando solo contra las hordas skironianas! ¡Debemos ir a "
"ayudarlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:839
msgid "Och, we must really hurry; I'm worried about him..."
msgstr "Och, realmente debemos apurarnos. Estoy preocupado por él..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:843
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:869
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:933
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:929
msgid "Let's do it, then..."
msgstr "Entonces hagámoslo..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:857
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:921
msgid ""
"Everyone, do not lose control! We can still hear each other, so let us stay "
"close together! Keep closed formations, protect the man next to you, and "
"let's march slowly and carefully to the south!"
msgstr ""
"¡Todos, no pierdan el control! Todavía podemos escucharnos, así que "
"mantengámonos juntos. Mantengan formaciones cerradas, protejan al compañero "
"de al lado y avancemos lentamente y con cuidado hacia el sur."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:865
msgid ""
"That's not it; I just think that it's within our power, to kill at least one "
"of the summoners that are flanking Argatyr; thus we would relieve his "
"warriors a little..."
msgstr ""
"No es eso. Solo creo que está en nuestro poder matar al menos a uno de los "
"invocadores que flanquean a Argatyr. Así aliviaríamos un poco a sus "
"guerreros..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:929
msgid ""
"That's not it; I just think that it's within our power, to kill Stygia; thus "
"we would relieve Argatyr's warriors a little..."
msgstr ""
"No es eso. Solo creo que está en nuestro poder matar a Stygia. Así "
"aliviaríamos un poco a los guerreros de Argatyr..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:963
msgid ""
"Great! We've managed to defeat one of the summoners against all odds! I hope "
"this is enough to relieve Lord Argatyr and his warriors..."
msgstr ""
"¡Genial! ¡Logramos derrotar a uno de los invocadores contra todo pronóstico! "
"Espero que esto sea suficiente para aliviar al señor Argatyr y a sus "
"guerreros..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:993
msgid "Great! We've managed to defeat the summoners against all odds!"
msgstr "¡Genial! ¡Logramos derrotar a los invocadores contra todo pronóstico!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1006
msgid ""
"(chuckling) Poor, naïve mortals... So you still believe that you stand a "
"chance against me? I thought you had understood that I was just playing with "
"you, but, if you need a more concrete proof..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo entre dientes) Pobres mortales ingenuos... ¿Todavía creen que tienen "
"alguna oportunidad contra mí? Pensé que habían entendido que solo estaba "
"jugando con ustedes, pero si necesitan una prueba más concreta..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1013
msgid "<i>(scream in the distance)</i> AAAAUURRRGGGHHH!!!"
msgstr "<i>(grito a lo lejos)</i> ¡AAAAUURRRGGGHHH!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1017
msgid "Argatyr?! Damn you, Stygia, what have you done to him?!"
msgstr "¡¿Argatyr?! ¡Maldita seas, Stygia, ¿qué le has hecho?!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1021
msgid ""
"See how easily I crushed your strong lord? (menacing) Now, children, "
"playtime is over... You, little dwarf girl, who mourned your dwarf friend’s "
"death, shall be next..."
msgstr ""
"¿Ven con qué facilidad aplasté a su fuerte señor? (amenazante) Ahora, niños, "
"el tiempo de jugar ha terminado... Tú, pequeña enana que lloraste la muerte "
"de tu amigo enano, serás la siguiente..."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1025
msgid "YOU... DAMN... WITCH!!!"
msgstr "¡TÚ... MALDITA... BRUJA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1045
msgid ""
"(frightened) What is this power...? You puny dwarf, so you still had a "
"little trick up your sleeve, hadn't you?"
msgstr ""
"(asustada) ¿Qué es este poder...? Pequeño enano, así que todavía tenías un "
"pequeño truco bajo la manga, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1052
msgid "(alarmed) Oh my, what's this splashing noise...?!"
msgstr "(alarmada) ¡Oh cielos, ¿qué es ese ruido de salpicaduras...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1056
msgid "Argatyr... He brought down the cave's roof!"
msgstr "Argatyr... ¡Derrumbó el techo de la cueva!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1060
msgid "Then what are we waiting for?! Let's get out of here at once!"
msgstr "¡Entonces, ¿a qué esperamos?! ¡Salgamos de aquí de inmediato!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1064
msgid ""
"I must congratulate you for managing to stop me, little dwarf, but this will "
"have little effect on the outcome of this war: I will go back to the surface "
"and lead Skiron's full might against Netjer-Ta's petty denizens, while you "
"will die here and now, buried beneath the rubble and the sea..."
msgstr ""
"Debo felicitarte por lograr detenerme, pequeño enano, pero esto tendrá poco "
"efecto en el resultado de esta guerra. Volveré a la superficie y lideraré "
"todo el poder de Skiron contra los insignificantes habitantes de Netjer-Ta, "
"mientras que ustedes morirán aquí y ahora, enterrados bajo los escombros y "
"el mar..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1068
msgid "Argatyr...!"
msgstr "¡Argatyr...!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1072
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, Sigdral, but there's nothing we can do now other than saving "
"ourselves to avenge him later!"
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, Sigdral, pero ahora no podemos hacer nada más que salvarnos para "
"vengarlo después."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1076
msgid ""
"He won't die... If the legend of Ymer's Hammer is true, Argatyr will remain "
"alive as long as he's holding it..."
msgstr ""
"No morirá... Si la leyenda del Martillo de Ymer es cierta, Argatyr "
"permanecerá vivo mientras lo tenga en sus manos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1080
msgid "We shall ask Master Menon to rescue him then, now we must HURRY!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces le pediremos al maestro Menon que lo rescate. ¡Ahora debemos "
"APURARNOS!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1084
msgid ""
"*Please, hold on, Argatyr... I won't let you die like this... In spite of "
"everything, I still...*"
msgstr ""
"*Por favor, resiste, Argatyr... No dejaré que mueras así... A pesar de todo, "
"todavía...*"

#. [message], speaker=Garuro
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1118
msgid "Apologies, friends, but you'll have to fight on without me..."
msgstr "Disculpen, amigos, pero tendrán que seguir luchando sin mí..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1122
msgid "We shouldn't have let him die; now we're hopelessly outnumbered!"
msgstr ""
"No deberíamos haberlo dejado morir. ¡Ahora estamos irremediablemente "
"superados en número!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1137
msgid ""
"To fall like this, at the hands of disgusting monsters and surrounded by "
"humans and orcs..."
msgstr ""
"Caer así, a manos de monstruos asquerosos y rodeado de humanos y orcos..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1141
msgid "Argatyr, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡Argatyr, NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1175
msgid ""
"(chuckling) Poor, naïve mortals... So you still believe that you stand a "
"chance against me? I thought you had understood that I was just playing with "
"you."
msgstr ""
"(riendo entre dientes) Pobres mortales ingenuos... ¿Todavía creen que tienen "
"alguna oportunidad contra mí? Pensé que habían entendido que solo estaba "
"jugando con ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/11_True_Darkness.cfg:1185
msgid ""
"We've fought for too long, and our forces are worn out, while the enemy's "
"grow steadily! At this pace, we'll never seize victory!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos luchado demasiado tiempo y nuestras fuerzas están agotadas, mientras "
"que las del enemigo crecen constantemente. ¡A este ritmo nunca lograremos la "
"victoria!"

#. [scenario], id=12_Immortal_Fire
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:4
msgid "Immortal Fire"
msgstr "Fuego Inmortal"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:24
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:681
msgid "Destroy Lich-Lady Stygia"
msgstr "Destruye a la Liche-Lady Stygia"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:28
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:783
msgid "Destroy the Portal to Skiron by moving a unit onto it"
msgstr "Destruye el Portal a Skiron moviendo una unidad sobre él"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:56
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:709
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:811
msgid "Death of Menon"
msgstr "Muerte de Menon"

#. [side], type=Garou
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:205
msgid "Howling Wind Clan"
msgstr "Clan Viento Aullante"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:222
msgid "Satellite Bases"
msgstr "Bases Satélite"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:361
msgid ""
"At last, we've reached the Skironians' main and only remaining base on "
"Netjer-Ta. According to the razorbird scouts, their portal functions only "
"once a day, but each time it opens hundreds of Skironians pour through it."
msgstr ""
"Por fin hemos llegado a la base principal y única que queda de los "
"skironianos en Netjer-Ta. Según los exploradores de pájaros navaja, su "
"portal funciona solo una vez al día, pero cada vez que se abre cientos de "
"skironianos salen a través de él."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:365
msgid ""
"I thought that they had only repaired Desret, but in fact they built an "
"entirely new fortress on top of it - and a very strong one!"
msgstr ""
"Pensaba que solo habían reparado Desret, pero en realidad construyeron una "
"fortaleza completamente nueva encima de él, ¡y muy fuerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:369
msgid ""
"In truth, their defensive strength relies not on fortifications, but on the "
"living and un-living defenders around their base. Thus, we must charge at "
"them three or four at a time, and take them down before they can make full "
"use of their terrain advantage."
msgstr ""
"En verdad, su fuerza defensiva no se basa en fortificaciones, sino en los "
"defensores vivos y no-muertos alrededor de su base. Por eso debemos "
"atacarlos de tres o cuatro en cuatro y derribarlos antes de que puedan "
"aprovechar completamente su ventaja de terreno."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:373
msgid "Furthermore, we must destroy that portal before more enemies may come."
msgstr "Además, debemos destruir ese portal antes de que lleguen más enemigos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:377
msgid ""
"And, thanks to that portal, the enemy needs not leave the comfort and "
"protection of their walls."
msgstr ""
"Y gracias a ese portal, el enemigo no necesita salir de la comodidad y "
"protección de sus murallas."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:381
msgid ""
"Ah, but it would be no fun, to simply sit here and wait for you to make a "
"move! No, we'll get you on the sands, denizens of Netjer-Ta, and turn them "
"forever red with your blood; after this battle, this will no longer be known "
"as the Silent Desert, but as the Crimson Wasteland!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, pero no sería divertido simplemente sentarnos aquí y esperar a que "
"ustedes hagan un movimiento. No, los atraparemos en las arenas, habitantes "
"de Netjer-Ta, y las teñiremos para siempre de rojo con su sangre. Después de "
"esta batalla, esto ya no se conocerá como el Desierto Silencioso, ¡sino como "
"el Yermo Carmesí!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:385
msgid ""
"You wish to fight us on our element? Well, I suppose you are free to at the "
"very least try..."
msgstr ""
"¿Quieren luchar contra nosotros en nuestro elemento? Bueno, supongo que al "
"menos son libres de intentarlo..."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:389
msgid ""
"Your terrain advantage is irrelevant here; we can afford losing four, even "
"five fighters to each of you, for our numbers are endless, and no matter how "
"hard you fight, you shall be crushed beneath them! But you, Menon Hekare, I "
"pray that you live long enough for me to crush your bones and disintegrate "
"your soul... Now, legions of Skiron, charge, and make our foes join us in "
"death!"
msgstr ""
"Su ventaja de terreno es irrelevante aquí. Podemos permitirnos perder "
"cuatro, incluso cinco luchadores por cada uno de ustedes, porque nuestros "
"números son infinitos y, sin importar cuánto luchen, serán aplastados debajo "
"de ellos. Pero tú, Menon Hekare, ruego que vivas lo suficiente para que yo "
"aplaste tus huesos y desintegre tu alma... ¡Ahora, legiones de Skiron, "
"carguen y hagan que nuestros enemigos se unan a nosotros en la muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:393
msgid ""
"Maat'Karians, wargs and dwarves, follow me! The time has come for us to free "
"Netjer-Ta from Skironian greed!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maat'karianos, huargos y enanos, síganme! ¡Ha llegado el momento de liberar "
"a Netjer-Ta de la codicia skironian!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Folks, it may be just my impression, but... Are those streams sprouting from "
"the outer forts into the main fortress made of <i>blood</i>?"
msgstr ""
"Gente, puede que sea solo mi impresión, pero... ¿esos arroyos que brotan de "
"las fortalezas exteriores hacia la fortaleza principal están hechos de "
"<i>sangre</i>?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:406
msgid ""
"You're not wrong, that's really blood: tens of thousands of gallons of it, "
"enough to put the Red Pinnacle itself to shame."
msgstr ""
"No te equivocas, eso es realmente sangre: decenas de miles de galones, "
"suficiente para avergonzar al propio Pináculo Rojo."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:410
msgid ""
"(shocked) By the Gods... How many beings must have been killed in order to "
"gather so much blood?! And why are they making rivers with it? Really, their "
"madness has no limit at all..."
msgstr ""
"(impactado) ¡Por los Dioses...! ¿Cuántos seres deben haber sido asesinados "
"para reunir tanta sangre? ¿Y por qué están haciendo ríos con ella? Realmente "
"su locura no tiene límites..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:414
msgid ""
"In fact, I think there's a practical reason for it. If you pay attention, "
"that blood flows towards those outer bases; most likely it serves to feed "
"the undead guarding them - after all, fresh blood contains some energy in "
"itself."
msgstr ""
"De hecho, creo que hay una razón práctica. Si prestan atención, esa sangre "
"fluye hacia esas bases exteriores. Lo más probable es que sirva para "
"alimentar a los no-muertos que las custodian. Después de todo, la sangre "
"fresca contiene algo de energía en sí misma."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:418
msgid ""
"And it's no normal blood; see, the surplus that escapes to the ocean has "
"already tainted the nearby waters. If it keeps spreading, all sea life will "
"eventually be contaminated."
msgstr ""
"Y no es sangre normal. Miren, el exceso que escapa al océano ya ha "
"contaminado las aguas cercanas. Si sigue extendiéndose, toda la vida marina "
"terminará contaminada."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:434
msgid "Earth God, sweep away these violators of Nature! GEB NESHNY!"
msgstr ""
"¡Dios de la Tierra, barre a estos violadores de la Naturaleza! ¡GEB NESHNY!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:448
msgid ""
"Fire God, burn these unworthy beings to a cinder and purify this land! "
"SEDJET NETJER!"
msgstr ""
"¡Dios del Fuego, reduce a cenizas a estos seres indignos y purifica esta "
"tierra! ¡SEDJET NETJER!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:462
msgid "Receive the punishment of the Sky Goddess' five stars! TIE-SEBA HEDJAY!"
msgstr ""
"¡Reciban el castigo de las cinco estrellas de la Diosa del Cielo! ¡TIE-SEBA "
"HEDJAY!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:476
msgid ""
"You, who worship Death as your ally, receive the embrace of the Death "
"Goddess... NEFTHYS HEPET!"
msgstr ""
"Ustedes, que adoran a la Muerte como aliada, reciban el abrazo de la Diosa "
"de la Muerte... ¡NEFTHYS HEPET!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:490
msgid ""
"Ah, new troops! You've arrived just in time, the vermin still stand, so you "
"may yet have the pleasure of cutting them down!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, ¡nuevas tropas! Llegaron justo a tiempo, la alimaña todavía resiste, así "
"que aún pueden tener el placer de cortarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:494
msgid ""
"We must destroy that portal as soon as we can, or she'll keep receiving "
"massive reinforcements!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debemos destruir ese portal lo antes posible, o ella seguirá recibiendo "
"refuerzos masivos!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:505
msgid "Keep coming, my fellow Skironians!"
msgstr "¡Sigan llegando, compañeros skironianos!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:538
msgid ""
"What... What is happening here...? How did they manage to get so close to "
"me...?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué... qué está pasando aquí...? ¿Cómo lograron acercarse tanto a mí...?"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:545
msgid ""
"No... There's no way you will prevail against me, Lord Aegaion's own "
"apprentice!"
msgstr ""
"No... No hay forma de que prevalezcan contra mí, ¡la propia aprendiz de Lord "
"Aegaion!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:549
msgid "Oh, great, here we go, plunging into darkness again..."
msgstr "Oh genial, aquí vamos, sumergiéndonos en la oscuridad otra vez..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:556
msgid "Useless, Stygia, just as when Jevyan used it..."
msgstr "Inútil, Stygia, igual que cuando Jevyan lo usó..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:567
msgid "We're almost there, men! Be not afraid, for Master Menon is with us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ya casi llegamos, hombres! ¡No tengan miedo, porque el maestro Menon está "
"con nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:579
msgid ""
"It's... It's over! We have defeated the hosts of Skiron and saved Netjer-Ta!"
msgstr ""
"¡Se... se acabó! ¡Hemos derrotado a los ejércitos de Skiron y salvado Netjer-"
"Ta!"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:583
msgid "Hail Master Menon Hekare, the Master of Four Lights!"
msgstr "¡Salve al maestro Menon Hekare, el Maestro de las Cuatro Luces!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:587
msgid "<i>(thunderous roar)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(rugido atronador)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:591
msgid ""
"Your praise honours me, but this is still not the time to celebrate, for "
"Skiron's threat is not over yet; though we have repelled them now, they "
"still have vast armies at their disposal, and many Lich-Lords to command "
"them. It's very unwise to assume that they won’t try and attack us again. As "
"the Great Seer of Maat'Kare, I declare that now it's the Maat'Karians who "
"shall wage war on Skiron, to destroy Aegaion and his Liches and seize the "
"Ruby of Fire, to prevent it from falling into the wrong hands ever again!"
msgstr ""
"Su elogio me honra, pero aún no es momento de celebrar, porque la amenaza de "
"Skiron no ha terminado. Aunque los hemos repelido ahora, todavía tienen "
"vastos ejércitos a su disposición y muchos Señores-Liches para comandarlos. "
"Es muy imprudente asumir que no intentarán atacarnos de nuevo. Como Gran "
"Vidente de Maat'Kare, declaro que ahora son los maat'karianos quienes "
"declararán la guerra a Skiron, para destruir a Aegaion y a sus Liches y "
"tomar el Rubí de Fuego, para evitar que caiga en manos equivocadas nunca más."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:595
msgid "*Oh, no...*"
msgstr "*Oh no...*"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:599
msgid ""
"If that is so, then allow me to be one the generals to lead our armies into "
"Argea! I pledge myself to collect at least six Lich skulls!"
msgstr ""
"Si es así, ¡permítanme ser uno de los generales que lidere nuestros "
"ejércitos hacia Argea! ¡Me comprometo a recolectar al menos seis cráneos de "
"Liche!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:603
msgid "And I shall burn whatever legion I come across to a cinder!"
msgstr "¡Y yo reduciré a cenizas cualquier legión que me cruce!"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:607
msgid ""
"As for the Aigathol, I regret to say that we can't afford to send fighters "
"to Argea; after fighting vampires and Skironians, we have lost too many "
"soldiers. But we shall guard our continent against any further incursion "
"from the south, so your armies may march with the confidence that their home "
"is safe!"
msgstr ""
"En cuanto a los Aigathol, lamento decir que no podemos permitirnos enviar "
"luchadores a Argea. Después de luchar contra vampiros y skironianos, hemos "
"perdido demasiados soldados. Pero protegeremos nuestro continente contra "
"cualquier incursión futura desde el sur, para que sus ejércitos puedan "
"marchar con la confianza de que su hogar está seguro."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:611
msgid ""
"It heartens me, to know that our friends shall remain by our side. Now, let "
"us gather at our base on the Peaks of Meditation, and then return to "
"Maat'Kare; our people deserve to hear good news after enduring such "
"hardships!"
msgstr ""
"Me alegra saber que nuestros amigos permanecerán a nuestro lado. Ahora "
"reunámonos en nuestra base en las Cumbres de la Meditación y luego "
"regresemos a Maat'Kare. Nuestro pueblo merece escuchar buenas noticias "
"después de soportar tantas dificultades."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:615
msgid "Atenak, why does it seem that you're the only one who isn't happy here?"
msgstr "Atenak, ¿por qué parece que eres la única que no está feliz aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:619
msgid ""
"I am happy, I'm just too tired to scream or jump in celebration... *Would "
"that it was really that... Now that Netjer-Ta is safe, uncle will not hold "
"himself any longer, especially after this decision to attack Skiron... "
"Akhen, Merwe, Mahyus, I fear that we are soon going to be on opposite "
"sides...!*"
msgstr ""
"Estoy feliz, solo estoy demasiado cansada para gritar o saltar de "
"celebración... *Ojalá fuera realmente eso... Ahora que Netjer-Ta está a "
"salvo, mi tío no se contendrá más, especialmente después de esta decisión de "
"atacar Skiron... Akhen, Merwe, Mahyus, temo que pronto estaremos en bandos "
"opuestos...*"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:671
msgid ""
"The portal is no longer! Now, we only have to destroy the witch herself!"
msgstr ""
"¡El portal ya no existe! ¡Ahora solo tenemos que destruir a la bruja misma!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:675
msgid "(trembling) You... You cursed...!"
msgstr "(temblando) ¡Tú... maldita...!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:744
msgid ""
"(trembling) N-no... I c-can't be d-destroyed, I... I am a Lich-Lady of Sk-"
"kiron... Lord Aegaion p-promised that I'd n-never be d-destroyed..."
msgstr ""
"(temblando) N-no... No puedo ser d-destruid, yo... soy una Liche-Lady de "
"Skiron... Lord Aegaion p-prometió que nunca sería d-destruid..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:748
msgid ""
"It does not matter how strong you are, there'll always be a way to bring you "
"down - especially if you ignore this simple truth. And this is why your Lord "
"Aegaion has his days numbered; for he has dared to fly too close to the sun, "
"and now the sun shall turn him and all his might into ashes."
msgstr ""
"No importa cuán fuerte seas, siempre habrá una forma de derribarte, "
"especialmente si ignoras esta simple verdad. Y por eso los días de tu Lord "
"Aegaion están contados, porque se atrevió a volar demasiado cerca del sol y "
"ahora el sol lo convertirá a él y a todo su poder en cenizas."

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:752
msgid ""
"(trembling in rage) You... You think yourself b-better than us, Menon "
"Hekare, but you're no different. We have peered into the Ruby of Fire, b-but "
"you have peered into the Sky Soul; and, just as we were taken by the Ruby's "
"d-darkness, you will be destroyed by the Sky Dragon's malice. I know it, I "
"know how the lure of power c-can bend even the b-brightest spirit..."
msgstr ""
"(temblando de rabia) Tú... Te crees m-mejor que nosotros, Menon Hekare, pero "
"no eres diferente. Nosotros hemos mirado dentro del Rubí de Fuego, p-pero tú "
"has mirado dentro del Alma del Cielo. Y así como nosotros fuimos atrapados "
"por la o-oscuridad del Rubí, tú serás destruido por la malicia del Dragón "
"del Cielo. Lo sé, sé cómo el señuelo del poder puede torcer incluso al "
"espíritu más b-brillante..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:756
msgid ""
"The darkness lives inside everyone; these two cursed jewels only bring it to "
"the surface. However, one who has accepted one's own darkness can master it "
"instead of being mastered by it; and this is where you and all the other "
"Lich-Lords have failed. Now, Stygia of Thalassia... VANISH FROM EXISTENCE!"
msgstr ""
"La oscuridad vive dentro de todos. Estas dos joyas malditas solo la traen a "
"la superficie. Sin embargo, quien ha aceptado su propia oscuridad puede "
"dominarla en lugar de ser dominado por ella. Y ahí es donde tú y todos los "
"demás Señores-Liches han fallado. Ahora, Stygia de Thalassia... ¡DESAPARECE "
"DE LA EXISTENCIA!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:760
msgid ""
"You really do deserve your title... Immortal... At least I shall now be..."
msgstr "Realmente mereces tu título... Inmortal... Al menos ahora yo seré..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:777
msgid "Now we must only destroy the portal to end Skiron's invasion!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora solo debemos destruir el portal para acabar con la invasión de Skiron!"

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:843
msgid "Darn it! Apologies, my friends, but I can fight no longer..."
msgstr "¡Maldición! Lo siento, amigos, pero ya no puedo seguir luchando..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:847
msgid ""
"We needed his wargs in order to win this battle! Now, we'll be hopelessly "
"outnumbered!"
msgstr ""
"¡Necesitábamos sus huargos para ganar esta batalla! ¡Ahora estaremos en "
"desventaja numérica!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:862
msgid "Brother, NO!"
msgstr "¡Hermano, NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:866
msgid "Sorry, sister, my allies... I have... fallen..."
msgstr "Lo siento, hermana, mis aliados... He... caído..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:880
msgid "How can I die like this...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo puedo morir así...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:884
msgid "Sadjet, no! We need your power in order to win!"
msgstr "¡Sadjet, no! ¡Necesitamos tu poder para ganar!"

#. [message], speaker=Stygia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/12_Immortal_Fire.cfg:924
msgid ""
"So the Immortal wasn't as immortal as we've always thought... Now, "
"Skironians, charge and destroy what is left of their morale!"
msgstr ""
"Así que el Inmortal no era tan inmortal como siempre pensabamos... ¡Ahora, "
"skironianos, carguen y destruyan lo que queda de su moral!"

#. [scenario], id=13_The_Shadows_Within
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:4
msgid "The Shadows Within: Black Light"
msgstr "Las Sombras Internas: Luz Negra"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:20
msgid "Follow the Orb to the Central Tower, and pick the item that lies there"
msgstr ""
"Sigue el Orbe hasta la Torre Central y recoge el objeto que se encuentra allí"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:66
msgid "Rebels"
msgstr "Rebeldes"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Seraph
#. [side], type=Eternal Night
#. [side], type=Lich Lord WotJ
#. [side], type=Priest SK
#. [unit_type], id=Dream Avatar, race=monster
#. [unit_type], id=Nature Orb, race=elemental
#. [unit_type], id=Shadow Avatar, race=monster
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:78
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:158
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:69
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:91
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:96
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:118
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:136
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:107
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Dream_Avatar.cfg:5
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Nature_Orb.cfg:5
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Shadow_Avatar.cfg:6
msgid "???"
msgstr "???"

#. [message], speaker=Imethep
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:183
msgid ""
"Lord Tewarin, as Law dictates the petition you have handed us has enough "
"signatures to force us to strip Master Menon of his powers as Great Seer, "
"even if only temporarily. Nevertheless, we wish to speak with you, so that "
"we may reach a decision that pleases all sides. Would you mind explaining to "
"us why you're against him even now? Hasn't Master Menon satisfactorily led "
"our nation so far in this war?"
msgstr ""
"Señor Tewarin, según dicta la Ley, la petición que nos han entregado tiene "
"suficientes firmas para obligarnos a despojar al maestro Menon de sus "
"poderes como Gran Vidente, aunque sea solo temporalmente. Sin embargo, "
"deseamos hablar contigo para llegar a una decisión que agrade a todas las "
"partes. ¿Te importaría explicarnos por qué estás en su contra incluso ahora? "
"¿No ha liderado el maestro Menon satisfactoriamente a nuestra nación hasta "
"ahora en esta guerra?"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:187
msgid ""
"Certainly, good Imethep. As you all know, I have my reasons to believe that "
"Menon Hekare isn't as good-natured as he may seem. However, I have recently "
"found the evidence I needed - better, my niece has. Atenak, please step "
"forward."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, buen Imethep. Como todos saben, tengo mis razones para creer "
"que Menon Hekare no es tan bondadoso como parece. Sin embargo, recientemente "
"he encontrado la evidencia que necesitaba; mejor dicho, mi sobrina la ha "
"encontrado. Atenak, por favor, da un paso adelante."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:191
msgid "(whispers) Atenak? But... What on Irdya is going on here?"
msgstr "(susurros) ¿Atenak? Pero... ¿Qué demonios está pasando aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:195
msgid ""
"Well... During the expedition I led to Desret, months ago, I found a ruined "
"village in the middle of the Silent Desert. By its architectonic style, it "
"was undoubtedly Maat'Karian; however, after a careful examination by the "
"rune-crafter Sigdral, sister of Lord Vindalf of the Aigathol, we found out "
"that it was older than Desret itself, the allegedly oldest human settlement "
"in that desert. Furthermore, we found signs that it was destroyed by some "
"unnatural event, possibly an attack."
msgstr ""
"Bueno... Durante la expedición que lideré a Desret hace meses, encontré una "
"aldea en ruinas en medio del Desierto Silencioso. Por su estilo "
"arquitectónico, era sin duda maat'kariana; sin embargo, después de un examen "
"cuidadoso por parte de la forjadora de runas Sigdral, hermana del señor "
"Vindalf de los Aigathol, descubrimos que era más antigua que el propio "
"Desret, el supuesto asentamiento humano más antiguo de ese desierto. Además, "
"encontramos señales de que fue destruida por algún evento antinatural, "
"posiblemente un ataque."

#. [message], speaker=Imethep
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:199
msgid "Do you confirm that, Lady Sigdral?"
msgstr "¿Lo confirmas, lady Sigdral?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:203
msgid "(puzzled) Yes, I do, but..."
msgstr "(desconcertada) Sí, lo confirmo, pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:207
msgid ""
"This village, Lords and Sages, is the ultimate proof of the existence of the "
"Desert Ghosts, the sentinels rumoured to have been set up by the Founder "
"Jevyan to protect the Garnet of Cursed Souls - or, as we're calling it now, "
"the Sky Soul. I, for one, needed no such evidence, for their existence has "
"always been known to my family: one of my ancestors was a member of that "
"noble faction. She moved to Maat'Kare after the Ghosts' destruction at the "
"hands of Menon Hekare..."
msgstr ""
"Esta aldea, señores y sabios, es la prueba definitiva de la existencia de "
"los Fantasmas del Desierto, los centinelas que se rumorea fueron "
"establecidos por el Fundador Jevyan para proteger el Granate de las Almas "
"Malditas, o como lo llamamos ahora, el Alma del Cielo. Yo, por mi parte, no "
"necesitaba tal evidencia, porque su existencia siempre ha sido conocida por "
"mi familia: una de mis antepasadas fue miembro de esa noble facción. Ella se "
"mudó a Maat'Kare después de la destrucción de los Fantasmas a manos de Menon "
"Hekare..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:211
msgid "<i>(astonished murmurs)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(murmullos de asombro)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:215
msgid ""
"She is remembered by my family for her hatred of Menon; when questioned, she "
"only said that he'd stolen something from her tribe, without ever explaining "
"what; and she died with a madwoman's reputation. However, I've always "
"believed that she spoke the truth; when I learned about the Soul at this "
"very hall, I connected the facts, and finally realised who our 'Master' "
"truly is: a two-faced, ambitious mage who did all in his power to have the "
"Soul for himself!"
msgstr ""
"Mi familia la recuerda por su odio hacia Menon; cuando la interrogaban, solo "
"decía que él le había robado algo a su tribu, sin explicar nunca qué; y "
"murió con reputación de loca. Sin embargo, siempre he creído que decía la "
"verdad; cuando supe del Alma en este mismo salón, conecté los hechos y "
"finalmente me di cuenta de quién es realmente nuestro «maestro»: un mago de "
"dos caras y ambicioso que hizo todo lo posible por tener el Alma para sí "
"mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:219
msgid ""
"Enough! Lord Tewarin, I have told you already that I will not admit any "
"false accusation against my honesty and commitment to our civilization; if "
"you are going to accuse me of something, then at least put some solid "
"evidence forward, instead of faint confabulations and theories!"
msgstr ""
"¡Basta! Señor Tewarin, ya te he dicho que no admitiré ninguna acusación "
"falsa contra mi honestidad y mi compromiso con nuestra civilización; si vas "
"a acusarme de algo, al menos presenta evidencia sólida, en lugar de vagas "
"invenciones y teorías."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:223
msgid ""
"So you deny that you killed Leivyan and all the Desert Ghosts just so that "
"there would be no one left who stood witness of your crimes?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces niegas que mataste a Leivyan y a todos los Fantasmas del Desierto "
"para que no quedara nadie que fuera testigo de tus crímenes?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:227
msgid "*How does he know that name...?!*"
msgstr "*¡¿Cómo conoce ese nombre...?!*"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:231
msgid ""
"You knew, Menon Hekare, that the Chamber of Sages would have never accepted "
"keeping the Soul here, in Maat'Kare, and under your custody, if they could "
"have left it safely away from this city, and with those who had faithfully "
"guarded it for centuries!"
msgstr ""
"Sabías, Menon Hekare, que la Cámara de Sabios nunca habría aceptado mantener "
"el Alma aquí, en Maat'Kare, y bajo tu custodia, si hubieran podido dejarla a "
"salvo lejos de esta ciudad y con aquellos que la habían custodiado fielmente "
"durante siglos."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:235
msgid ""
"Stop, stop all this nonsense! By the Gods of Light, Tewarin, what do you "
"seek with your relentless persecution of Master Menon? Haven't you nearly "
"ruined Maat'Kare already because of this? And you, Smenkhare, how can you "
"support him?"
msgstr ""
"¡Detente, detén todo este sinsentido! Por los Dioses de la Luz, Tewarin, "
"¿qué buscas con tu persecución implacable contra el maestro Menon? ¿No has "
"estado a punto de arruinar Maat'Kare ya por esto? Y tú, Smenkhare, ¿cómo "
"puedes apoyarlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:239
msgid ""
"I acknowledge that Master Menon has served Maat'Kare well, but I'm with "
"Tewarin when he says that no one should keep so much power alone. Right now, "
"on top of being the Chief Elder of the Chamber of Sages and keeper of the "
"Sky Soul, he's also the Great Seer. Giving him this title was necessary "
"during Skiron's siege on Netjer-Ta, but now I see no reason for him to keep "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Reconozco que el maestro Menon ha servido bien a Maat'Kare, pero estoy con "
"Tewarin cuando dice que nadie debe conservar tanto poder solo. Ahora mismo, "
"además de ser el Anciano Principal de la Cámara de Sabios y custodio del "
"Alma del Cielo, también es el Gran Vidente. Darle este título fue necesario "
"durante el asedio de Skiron a Netjer-Ta, pero ahora no veo razón para que lo "
"conserve."

#. [message], speaker=Imethep
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:243
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, Lord Tewarin is not merely requesting Master Menon to step "
"down as a Great Seer, but he's also accusing him of an extremely grave "
"crime, and the only evidences he's presenting are family legends and some "
"obscure ruins! Frankly, Lord Tewarin, never would I have expected such "
"childishness from you, especially as we are in the middle of such a grave "
"war!"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, el señor Tewarin no solo está pidiendo que el maestro Menon "
"renuncie como Gran Vidente, sino que también lo acusa de un crimen "
"extremadamente grave, y las únicas evidencias que presenta son leyendas "
"familiares y unas ruinas oscuras. Francamente, señor Tewarin, nunca habría "
"esperado tal infantilismo de ti, especialmente cuando estamos en medio de "
"una guerra tan grave."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:247
msgid ""
"Yes, so many acts have been excused by this war. Quite convenient, don't you "
"think? It almost makes me wonder whether someone inside our own country has "
"somehow started it..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, muchos actos han sido excusados por esta guerra. Bastante conveniente, "
"¿no crees? Casi me hace preguntarme si alguien dentro de nuestro propio país "
"la ha iniciado de alguna forma..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:251
msgid "THAT IS ENOUGH!!!"
msgstr "¡YA ES SUFICIENTE!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:258
msgid ""
"Tewarin Aracyne, I've always tolerated your distaste for me, for it was "
"always in your right to feel that way. I've even given up my position as an "
"authority when I was considered too unreliable for that. However, you've now "
"crossed all boundaries; you throw weak, calumnious arguments against me, and "
"by doing this you cause internal rifts in a country at war! The way <i>I</i> "
"see it, you're simply trying to wave me aside so that your influence in our "
"city may grow, and thus <i>you</i> are the one consumed by ambition, not I!"
msgstr ""
"Tewarin Aracyne, siempre he tolerado tu antipatía hacia mí, porque siempre "
"estuvo en tu derecho sentirte así. Incluso renuncié a mi posición de "
"autoridad cuando se me consideró demasiado poco confiable para ello. Sin "
"embargo, ahora has cruzado todos los límites; lanzas argumentos débiles y "
"calumniosos contra mí, y al hacer esto causas divisiones internas en un país "
"en guerra. La forma en que <i>yo</i> lo veo es que simplemente intentas "
"apartarme para que tu influencia en nuestra ciudad crezca, y por lo tanto "
"<i>tú</i> eres el que está consumido por la ambición, ¡no yo!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:262
msgid "<i>(approving murmurs amongst Sages)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(murmullos de aprobación entre los Sabios)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:266
msgid "You... How dare you..."
msgstr "Tú... ¿Cómo te atreves...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:273
msgid ""
"Tewarin Aracyne, I deem you a threat to Maat'Kare's safety, and so I am "
"stripping you of your authority as a Lord and as an Admiral, and condemning "
"you to imprisonment in the Duat! Sages and Lords, how many amongst you are "
"approving of this?"
msgstr ""
"Tewarin Aracyne, te considero una amenaza para la seguridad de Maat'Kare, "
"por lo que te despojo de tu autoridad como Señor y como Almirante, y te "
"condeno al encarcelamiento en el Duat. ¡Sabios y Señores, cuántos de ustedes "
"aprueban esto?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:277
msgid "<i>(unanimous support amongst Sages; some support amongst Lords)</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>(apoyo unánime entre los Sabios; algo de apoyo entre los Señores)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:281
msgid ""
"Apologies, Tewarin, but I won't stand for you causing such petty schisms "
"amongst us."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, Tewarin, pero no voy a tolerar que causes divisiones tan "
"mezquinas entre nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:285
msgid "No... Wait, it... can't be..."
msgstr "No... Espera, esto... no puede ser..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:289
msgid "Guards, you may arrest them."
msgstr "Guardias, pueden arrestarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:293
msgid ""
"No! I will not go to prison and let you do as you wish, Menon Hekare! Men, I "
"need aid!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡No iré a prisión y te dejaré hacer lo que quieras, Menon Hekare! "
"¡Hombres, necesito ayuda!"

#. [message], speaker=Tewarin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:307
msgid ""
"Now, my friends, leave this building and go as fast as you can to Ineb-Hedj, "
"as combined! My men shall cover you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora, amigos míos, salgan de este edificio y vayan lo más rápido posible a "
"Ineb-Hedj, todos juntos! ¡Mis hombres los cubrirán!"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:311
msgid "To think that the worst-case scenario would actually happen...!"
msgstr "¡Pensar que el peor escenario posible realmente ocurriría...!"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:318
msgid "Come, Atenak, we must flee!"
msgstr "¡Ven, Atenak, debemos huir!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:322
msgid "(confused) But, uncle...!"
msgstr "(confundida) ¡Pero, tío...!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:326
msgid "You truly leave me no choice..."
msgstr "Realmente no me dejas otra opción..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:333
msgid "UNCLE!!!"
msgstr "¡TÍO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:337
msgid "(shocked) What on Irdya...?!"
msgstr "(impactada) ¡¿Qué demonios en Irdya...?! "

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:341
msgid "Lords, we must flee now! Atenak, please..."
msgstr "Señores, ¡debemos huir ahora! Atenak, por favor..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:345
msgid "(in shock) Unc-cle, you..."
msgstr "(en shock) Tí-tío, tú..."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:349
msgid "Damn it, Atenak! Apologies, but we can't waste any more time here..."
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, Atenak! Lo siento, pero no podemos perder más tiempo aquí..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:358
msgid ""
"I hereby declare that all the Lords that have signed this malicious petition "
"against me, as well as anyone who shows them any kind of support, are "
"traitors and enemies of Maat'Kare!"
msgstr ""
"Por la presente declaro que todos los Señores que han firmado esta maliciosa "
"petición contra mí, así como cualquiera que les muestre algún tipo de apoyo, "
"son traidores y enemigos de Maat'Kare."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:362
msgid "(trembling) By the Gods, what madness is this...?!"
msgstr "(temblando) ¡Por los Dioses, qué locura es esta...?! "

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:366
msgid ""
"(bitter) Simply put, we're now fighting Maat'Karians as well as Skironians. "
"Akhen, Merwe, Sigdral, let's follow the Sages out of this place, before more "
"of Tewarin's soldiers appear!"
msgstr ""
"(amargado) En pocas palabras, ahora estamos luchando contra maat'karianos "
"además de skironianos. Akhen, Merwe, Sigdral, sigamos a los Sabios fuera de "
"este lugar, ¡antes de que aparezcan más soldados de Tewarin!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:370
msgid "A-all right..."
msgstr "S-sí, está bien…"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:455
msgid "Master, I wish to talk to you..."
msgstr "Maestro, deseo hablar contigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:459
msgid ""
"(sigh) If it's about Atenak again, Akhen, my answer hasn't changed: she will "
"remain detained until this rebellion is dealt with. You may insist that she "
"won't do anything that troubles Maat'Kare, and that she's your friend, but "
"she's picked her side, and that's not ours."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Si se trata de Atenak otra vez, Akhen, mi respuesta no ha "
"cambiado: ella permanecerá detenida hasta que esta rebelión sea resuelta. "
"Puedes insistir en que no hará nada que perjudique a Maat'Kare y que es tu "
"amiga, pero ella ha elegido su bando, y ese no es el nuestro."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:463
msgid ""
"But isn't it only natural that she stood by her only living relative? I'm "
"sure that she simply trusted her uncle because she liked him, not because "
"she agreed with his ideas..."
msgstr ""
"Pero ¿no es natural que se haya mantenido al lado de su único familiar vivo? "
"Estoy seguro de que simplemente confiaba en su tío porque le caía bien, no "
"porque estuviera de acuerdo con sus ideas..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:467
msgid ""
"So, according to you, she went as far as to help ignite a civil war amongst "
"our people because of her uncle; how do you think she will react when she "
"next sees the one who ended his life?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, según tú, llegó al punto de ayudar a encender una guerra civil "
"entre nuestro pueblo por su tío; ¿cómo crees que reaccionará la próxima vez "
"que vea a quien terminó con su vida?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:474
msgid ""
"Then, what will be of her? She won't remain imprisoned forever, will she?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ¿qué será de ella? No permanecerá encarcelada para siempre, "
"¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:478
msgid ""
"I'd rather not have it so; I don't want to punish her who's now the only "
"living descendant of Ravyan too harshly - and that's exactly why I'm keeping "
"her under house arrest: if she's freed, she'll certainly join the other "
"rebels, and then I fear I won't be able to show her any mercy."
msgstr ""
"Preferiría que no fuera así; no quiero castigarla demasiado severamente, ya "
"que ahora es la única descendiente viva de Ravyan también, y esa es "
"exactamente la razón por la que la mantengo bajo arresto domiciliario: si es "
"liberada, sin duda se unirá a los otros rebeldes, y entonces temo que no "
"podré mostrarle ninguna misericordia."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:482
msgid "What do you mean? Wait, are you going to..."
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir? Espera, ¿vas a...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:486
msgid ""
"Smenkhare and the other rebel Lords will not accept me as their leader; "
"worse still, they won't rest while I'm the Great Seer, and so they will work "
"to overthrow me, even if that means fighting their own country. But I will "
"not let any harm afflict my city; I will kill all the rebel leaders, and any "
"soldier that chooses to stand against me, before they trouble Maat'Kare even "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Smenkhare y los otros Señores rebeldes no me aceptarán como su líder; peor "
"aún, no descansarán mientras yo sea el Gran Vidente, y por eso trabajarán "
"para derrocarme, incluso si eso significa luchar contra su propio país. Pero "
"no permitiré que ningún daño afecte a mi ciudad; mataré a todos los líderes "
"rebeldes y a cualquier soldado que elija oponerse a mí, antes de que causen "
"aún más problemas a Maat'Kare."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:490
msgid ""
"But... But... Master, what are you saying? Are you really going to kill our "
"fellow Maat'Karians?"
msgstr ""
"Pero... Pero... Maestro, ¿qué estás diciendo? ¿Realmente vas a matar a "
"nuestros compañeros maat'karianos?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:494
msgid ""
"What choice do I have? Should I simply step down and let them guide our "
"country to the ruin?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué opción tengo? ¿Debo simplemente renunciar y dejar que ellos guíen a "
"nuestro país a la ruina?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:498
msgid ""
"I don't think that they would lead us to destruction, but if you have to "
"give up your authority to avoid the loss of life, then you should do it! "
"Didn't you say it yourself that sacrificing one's own power and life for "
"other people is always worthwhile?"
msgstr ""
"No creo que ellos nos lleven a la destrucción, pero si tienes que renunciar "
"a tu autoridad para evitar la pérdida de vidas, ¡entonces deberías hacerlo! "
"¿No dijiste tú mismo que sacrificar el propio poder y la vida por otras "
"personas siempre vale la pena?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:502
msgid ""
"And it's even more worthwhile to become as powerful as you can be for the "
"sake of those you love. For them, anything is just, even it means the death "
"of a few individuals. That's why bringing such war upon ourselves is just: "
"now we shall destroy Skiron, the greatest threat to Maat'Kare, seize the "
"Ruby of Fire and keep the two cursed jewels safely under our custody."
msgstr ""
"Y es aún más valioso volverse tan poderoso como se pueda por el bien de "
"aquellos a quienes amas. Para ellos, cualquier cosa es justa, incluso si "
"significa la muerte de unos pocos individuos. Por eso traer esta guerra "
"sobre nosotros mismos es justo: ahora destruiremos Skiron, la mayor amenaza "
"para Maat'Kare, tomaremos el Rubí de Fuego y mantendremos las dos joyas "
"malditas a salvo bajo nuestra custodia."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:509
msgid ""
"Master... What do you mean when you say... 'bringing such war upon "
"ourselves'...?"
msgstr ""
"Maestro... ¿Qué quieres decir cuando dices... «traer esta guerra sobre "
"nosotros mismos»...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:516
msgid ""
"(sigh) I trust you so much that I spoke what I shouldn't... Listen, Akhen, "
"this world is not for the fainthearted; it's ruthless and cruel, and "
"sometimes we have to be ruthless and cruel as well, for our own sake and "
"those we hold dear."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Confío tanto en ti que dije lo que no debía... Escucha, Akhen, "
"este mundo no es para los pusilánimes; es despiadado y cruel, y a veces "
"nosotros también tenemos que ser despiadados y crueles, por nuestro propio "
"bien y el de aquellos que nos importan."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:520
msgid ""
"Since the Lich-Lords rose to power in Skiron, over forty years ago, I have "
"tirelessly tried to convince the two Chambers to attack that empire while it "
"was still weakened by Aegaion's civil war. However, they wouldn't "
"acknowledge the danger posed by the Lich-Lords, not unless this danger "
"creeped to our very doorstep. Thus, I plotted a way to make Skiron declare "
"war on us, so that we'd have a reason to wipe them out."
msgstr ""
"Desde que los Señores Liche subieron al poder en Skiron hace más de cuarenta "
"años, he intentado incansablemente convencer a las dos Cámaras de atacar ese "
"imperio mientras aún estaba debilitado por la guerra civil de Aegaion. Sin "
"embargo, no querían reconocer el peligro que representaban los Señores "
"Liche, a menos que este peligro llegara hasta nuestra misma puerta. Por eso, "
"tramé una forma de hacer que Skiron nos declarara la guerra, para que "
"tuviéramos una razón para aniquilarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:527
msgid "No... Imp... Impossible..."
msgstr "No... Imp... Imposible..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:531
msgid ""
"You see, there's a strange connection between the World of the Dead and "
"Dreamland; they're like twin dimensions separated by a thin veil - that's "
"why, for instance, spirits of deceased people may appear in one's dreams. "
"Thus, through the World of the Dead I visited Aegaion's mind in his dreams "
"and, disguised as a Fire Dragon, I told him of the Soul's existence."
msgstr ""
"Verás, existe una extraña conexión entre el Mundo de los Muertos y el Reino "
"de los Sueños; son como dimensiones gemelas separadas por un velo fino, por "
"eso, por ejemplo, los espíritus de personas fallecidas pueden aparecer en "
"los sueños de alguien. Así, a través del Mundo de los Muertos visité la "
"mente de Aegaion en sus sueños y, disfrazado como un Dragón de Fuego, le "
"hablé de la existencia del Alma."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:535
msgid ""
"(trembling) N-no... Master, you shouldn't jest with such imp-portant "
"matters... No way would you ever... Not the Master I know..."
msgstr ""
"(temblando) N-no... Maestro, no deberías bromear con asuntos tan imp-"
"ortantes... De ninguna manera tú harías... No el Maestro que conozco..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:539
msgid ""
"I understand that you must be shocked, but you will comprehend my logic if "
"you..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo que debes estar impactado, pero comprenderás mi lógica si tú..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:543
msgid ""
"I know! The barrier you put around the Soul has weakened, and so the jewel's "
"influence is causing you to have these horrible thoughts! Master you should "
"be more careful with that thing! Tell me where it is, I will take it as far "
"as..."
msgstr ""
"¡Lo sé! ¡La barrera que pusiste alrededor del Alma se ha debilitado, y por "
"eso la influencia de la joya te está causando estos pensamientos horribles! "
"¡Maestro, deberías tener más cuidado con esa cosa! Dime dónde está, la "
"llevaré tan lejos como..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:547
msgid "DO NOT TOUCH THAT JEWEL!"
msgstr "¡NO TOQUES ESA JOYA!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:554
msgid "Akhen, I'm sorry, I didn't mean to scream at you..."
msgstr "Akhen, lo siento, no quise gritarte..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:558
msgid ""
"No... No... Master Menon would never have done such things... It's the Soul "
"that has affected you... Quick, Master, we have to get rid of that thing "
"before it causes you any more problems!"
msgstr ""
"No... No... El maestro Menon nunca habría hecho tales cosas... Es el Alma la "
"que te ha afectado... ¡Rápido, Maestro, tenemos que deshacernos de esa cosa "
"antes de que te cause más problemas!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:562
msgid ""
"If it could be destroyed, your ancestor would have done it already, Akhen..."
msgstr "Si pudiera ser destruida, tu ancestro ya lo habría hecho, Akhen..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:566
msgid "(falling to his knees) No… T-this... can't b-be happening...!"
msgstr "(cayendo de rodillas) ¡No… E-esto... no p-puede estar pasando...!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:570
msgid ""
"(sigh) I understand your pain, Akhen, but don't worry, I will spare you from "
"seeing the horrors of this war any further."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Entiendo tu dolor, Akhen, pero no te preocupes, te ahorraré ver "
"los horrores de esta guerra por más tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:584
msgid ""
" Sleep, my boy, and take your time to digest all these things; I will "
"patiently wait for you to understand my motives..."
msgstr ""
" Duerme, muchacho, y tómate tu tiempo para digerir todas estas cosas; "
"esperaré pacientemente a que entiendas mis motivos..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:638
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/16_Burning_Ice.cfg:345
msgid "<i>Akhen...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Akhen...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:642
msgid "<i>Akhen, my child, please wake up...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Akhen, hijo mío, por favor despierta...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:646
msgid "<i>You have to wake up, or everything will be lost...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Tienes que despertar, o todo se perderá...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:664
msgid "What... Where am I... What has... (alarmed) Oh, no... Master...!"
msgstr "¿Qué... Dónde estoy... Qué ha... (alarmado) Oh, no... ¡Maestro...!"

#. [message], speaker=Orb
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:668
msgid ""
"<i>Unfortunately, my child, that wasn't a bad dream. But you mustn't muse "
"about that now; you must leave this place immediately.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Desafortunadamente, hijo mío, eso no fue una pesadilla. Pero no debes "
"pensar en eso ahora; debes abandonar este lugar inmediatamente.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:672
msgid ""
"...Who are you? You look like an Ethereal Orb, but you feel much different..."
msgstr ""
"...¿Quién eres? Te ves como un Orbe Etéreo, pero te sientes muy diferente..."

#. [message], speaker=Orb
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:676
msgid "<i>(sounding frustrated) Seriously, can't you feel who I am?</i>"
msgstr "<i>(con frustración) En serio, ¿no puedes sentir quién soy?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:680
msgid ""
"Well, sorry, but... (suddenly annoyed) Wait, I'm not letting an Ethereal Orb "
"mock me, it's bad enough that everyone at the Academy does that..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, lo siento, pero... (de repente molesto) Espera, no voy a permitir que "
"un Orbe Etéreo se burle de mí, ya es bastante malo que todos en la Academia "
"hagan eso..."

#. [message], speaker=Orb
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:684
msgid ""
"<i>Whatever... Just follow what I say without questioning; I'm certain that "
"even my dense great-great-great-grandson can feel that I'm friendly, or am I "
"wrong?</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Lo que sea... Solo sigue lo que digo sin cuestionar; estoy segura de que "
"incluso mi denso bis-bis-bis-nieto puede sentir que soy amigable, ¿o me "
"equivoco?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:688
msgid ""
"You're my great... Well, anyway, I get that, so tell me: what should I do?"
msgstr ""
"Eres mi bis... Bueno, de todos modos, entiendo, así que dime: ¿qué debo "
"hacer?"

#. [message], speaker=Orb
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:692
msgid ""
"<i>I sense that the Academy is nearly empty now but for a few elemental "
"guards, so you must take advantage of that and flee. However, you must first "
"go to the Central Tower; there's something for you there.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Siento que la Academia está casi vacía ahora, salvo por unos pocos "
"guardias elementales, así que debes aprovechar eso y huir. Sin embargo, "
"primero debes ir a la Torre Central; hay algo para ti allí.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:696
msgid ""
"Of course there is, that's the place where the monsters we study in Animal "
"Anatomy classes are raised!"
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí, ¡ese es el lugar donde crían a los monstruos que "
"estudiamos en las clases de Anatomía Animal!"

#. [message], speaker=Orb
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:700
msgid ""
"<i>There's no monster there, this I can assure you. Now, go! I have unlocked "
"the door already, and I'll guide you out of here, just be quick, please!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>No hay ningún monstruo allí, de eso puedo asegurarte. ¡Ahora, ve! Ya he "
"desbloqueado la puerta y te guiaré fuera de aquí, solo sé rápido, por favor."
"</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Orb
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:726
msgid ""
"<i>All right, the door's unlocked already. Now, hurry inside, I'll be "
"waiting for you there; I won't resist much longer in this form if I remain "
"far from it...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>De acuerdo, la puerta ya está desbloqueada. Ahora, apresúrate a entrar, "
"te estaré esperando allí; no resistiré mucho más en esta forma si me "
"mantengo lejos de ella...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:737
msgid "Hey, wait! Damn... My ancestors sure were crazy..."
msgstr "¡Oye, espera! Maldición... Mis ancestros sí que estaban locos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:751
msgid ""
"(astonished) *This is... the Trident of the Seas!? But I thought... I mean, "
"I was told... (sigh) So that was a lie too... Then, it must also be a lie "
"that I can't wield it with my current power level...*"
msgstr ""
"(asombrado) *¡Esto es... el Tridente de los Mares!? Pero pensé... Quiero "
"decir, me dijeron... (suspiro) Así que eso también era una mentira... "
"Entonces, también debe ser mentira que no puedo empuñarlo con mi nivel de "
"poder actual...*"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:761
msgid ""
"*Such tremendous power... still, it emanates such a warm, heartening energy; "
"the energy of the Water Dragon... Wait, could it be that that Orb just "
"now... (after a while) No, it can't be, Nitiballi isn't an ancestor of "
"mine...*"
msgstr ""
"*¡Qué poder tan tremendo...! Sin embargo, emana una energía tan cálida y "
"reconfortante; la energía del Dragón de Agua... Espera, ¿podría ser que ese "
"Orbe de hace un momento... (después de un rato) No, no puede ser, Nitiballi "
"no es un ancestro mío...*"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:765
msgid "So, Mrs. Voice, I've taken the Trident, where should I go now?"
msgstr "Entonces, señora Voz, he tomado el Tridente, ¿adónde debo ir ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:769
msgid ""
"<i>Do I even need to say it? You get out of this Academy, of course!</i>"
msgstr "<i>¿Acaso necesito decirlo? ¡Sal de esta Academia, por supuesto!</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:773
msgid ""
"Um, all right... But first I must find my friends; where could they be...?"
msgstr ""
"Um, de acuerdo... Pero primero debo encontrar a mis amigos; ¿dónde podrían "
"estar...?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:777
msgid ""
"<i>Don't worry, it's unlikely that they'll suffer any harm; you, on the "
"other hand...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>No te preocupes, es poco probable que ellos sufran algún daño; tú, en "
"cambio...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:781
msgid ""
"Wait a minute, there's no way I'm going anywhere without my friends! "
"Besides, I won't let them stay under the threat of the Sky Soul's influence."
msgstr ""
"Espera un momento, ¡de ninguna manera me iré a ningún lado sin mis amigos! "
"Además, no los dejaré quedarse bajo la amenaza de la influencia del Alma del "
"Cielo."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:785
msgid ""
"<i>...So be it... I sense their auras, let me see... around the Great Hall..."
"</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>...Que así sea... Siento sus auras, déjame ver... alrededor del Gran "
"Salón...</i>"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:791
msgid "Go to the statue of Aldrik in the Great Hall"
msgstr "Ve a la estatua de Aldrik en el Gran Salón"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:815
msgid ""
"Say, Mrs. Voice, who are you, after all? It doesn't matter how much I think, "
"I can't figure out who you are with certainty."
msgstr ""
"Dime, señora Voz, ¿quién eres, después de todo? No importa cuánto piense, no "
"puedo averiguar con certeza quién eres."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:819
msgid ""
"<i>Keep trying, then, it'll be good for you to develop your soul's senses. "
"I'll give you a hint, though: I'm related to the Water Dragon.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Sigue intentándolo entonces, te vendrá bien para desarrollar los sentidos "
"de tu alma. Aunque te daré una pista: estoy relacionada con el Dragón de "
"Agua.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:833
msgid ""
"Er, Mrs. Voice, I'm sorry, but I really have no idea who you could be... I "
"mean, the Water Dragon had no relatives, right?"
msgstr ""
"Eh, señora Voz, lo siento, pero realmente no tengo idea de quién podrías "
"ser... Quiero decir, el Dragón de Agua no tenía familiares, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:837
msgid ""
"<i>(sounding impatient) Holy Heavens, my lineage ended in an idiot...!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>(con impaciencia) Santos Cielos, ¡mi linaje terminó en un idiota...!</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:841
msgid ""
"Your lineage... Oh... (astonished) Wait, don't tell me... You can't be...!"
msgstr ""
"Tu linaje... Oh... (asombrado) Espera, no me digas... ¡No puedes ser...!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:845
msgid ""
"<i>Oh, at long last! Yes, I am Myra, but further explanation shall wait; "
"now, obey your great-great-Grandma and hurry up, for the Gods' sake!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>¡Oh, por fin! Sí, soy Myra, pero la explicación más detallada tendrá que "
"esperar; ahora, obedece a tu bis-bis-abuela y date prisa, ¡por el amor de "
"los Dioses!</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:882
msgid "Akhen! Where have you... Wait a minute, what is that trident?"
msgstr "¡Akhen! ¿Dónde has... Espera un minuto, ¿qué es ese tridente?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:886
msgid ""
"(panting) I... can't explain now... Just, please, trust me... Master... "
"Tewarin was right... He isn't..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Yo... no puedo explicarlo ahora... Solo, por favor, confíen en "
"mí... Maestro... Tewarin tenía razón... Él no es..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:893
msgid ""
"Master Menon was the one who caused this war. He somehow found a way to let "
"Aegaion know of the Soul's existence..."
msgstr ""
"El maestro Menon fue quien causó esta guerra. De alguna forma encontró la "
"manera de que Aegaion supiera de la existencia del Alma..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:897
msgid "He <i>what</i>?! Akhen, what the hell are you..."
msgstr "¡¿Él <i>qué</i>?! Akhen, qué demonios estás..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:901
msgid ""
"Just listen! He wanted to wage war on Skiron, but the Chambers wouldn't "
"accept it unless they attacked us first."
msgstr ""
"¡Solo escuchen! Quería declarar la guerra a Skiron, pero las Cámaras no lo "
"aceptarían a menos que ellos nos atacaran primero."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:905
msgid "(shocked) But... Why would he do such a thing?"
msgstr "(impactada) Pero... ¿Por qué haría algo así?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:909
msgid ""
"I'm not sure... By the Gods, I can't even say whether there's anything I'm "
"sure of right now... But it seems like he wants to have the Ruby of Fire for "
"himself... I mean, it's not him, it's the Sky Dragon's soul who is "
"manipulating him, in order to have his dragon vassals near him again, or "
"something like this..."
msgstr ""
"No estoy seguro... Por los Dioses, ni siquiera puedo decir si hay algo de lo "
"que esté seguro en este momento... Pero parece que quiere tener el Rubí de "
"Fuego para sí mismo... Quiero decir, no es él, es el alma del Dragón del "
"Cielo quien lo está manipulando, para tener a sus vasallos dragones cerca de "
"él otra vez, o algo así..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:913
msgid ""
"I-I see... But, if what you're saying is true, then we really must leave "
"this place, and go... well... I know! Let's go to the home of the Aigathol, "
"I'm sure they'll grant us asylum!"
msgstr ""
"Ya... ya veo... Pero, si lo que dices es verdad, entonces realmente debemos "
"abandonar este lugar e ir... bueno... ¡Ya sé! ¡Vayamos a la casa de los "
"Aigathol, estoy segura de que nos darán asilo!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:917
msgid ""
"You're right, but there's something else we must do before leaving "
"Maat'Kare..."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón, pero hay algo más que debemos hacer antes de abandonar "
"Maat'Kare..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:921
msgid ""
"Rescue Atenak, I know. Grim Gods of Darkness, and we were thinking about a "
"way to get her out of there just now; I just had no damn idea that we were "
"going to do that literally..."
msgstr ""
"Rescatar a Atenak, lo sé. Dioses Oscuros Sombríos, y justo ahora estábamos "
"pensando en una forma de sacarla de allí; simplemente no tenía ni idea de "
"que íbamos a hacerlo literalmente..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:925
msgid ""
"And don't forget that we have to get Sigdral and Nyx; they're still at your "
"mansion, Akhen."
msgstr ""
"Y no olviden que tenemos que ir por Sigdral y Nyx; todavía están en tu "
"mansión, Akhen."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:933
msgid ""
"Um, I know we shouldn't waste a single second talking, but... could that "
"possibly be the Trident of the Seas?"
msgstr ""
"Um, sé que no deberíamos perder ni un segundo hablando, pero... ¿podría ser "
"ese el Tridente de los Mares?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:937
msgid "You guessed it right, but, as I said, I'll explain everything later."
msgstr "Adivinaste bien, pero como dije, explicaré todo más tarde."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within.cfg:968
msgid "Damn it, I'm taking too much time to leave this place!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, estoy tardando demasiado en salir de este lugar!"

#. [scenario], id=13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:4
msgid "The Shadows Within: Dark Pride"
msgstr "Las Sombras Internas: Orgullo Oscuro"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:24
msgid "Go south to investigate what may be happening"
msgstr "Ve al sur para investigar qué puede estar pasando"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:68
msgid "Fugitives"
msgstr "Fugitivos"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:195
msgid "Hello! Is anyone there?"
msgstr "¡Hola! ¿Hay alguien ahí?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:202
msgid ""
"That's weird; last time we came here, there were tons of sentinels at the "
"gates, weren't there?"
msgstr ""
"Qué raro; la última vez que vinimos aquí había montones de centinelas en las "
"puertas, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:206
msgid ""
"Weird indeed; I shouldn't even have needed to open the gates myself, the "
"guards should have done it as soon as they sighted me. Could it be that "
"we're being attacked by someone, and because of that the guards have been "
"relocated...?"
msgstr ""
"Raro, sí; ni siquiera debería haber tenido que abrir las puertas yo misma, "
"los guardias deberían haberlo hecho en cuanto me vieran. ¿Será que nos están "
"atacando y por eso han reubicado a los guardias...?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:210
msgid ""
"Maybe Skiron has found a way to invade Netjer-Ta again during these days "
"we've been travelling."
msgstr ""
"Quizá Skiron encontró la forma de invadir Netjer-Ta otra vez durante estos "
"días que hemos estado viajando."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Nyx wouldn't bet on that... She senses the smell of dwarvish blood in the "
"air, but there's no trace of undead stench..."
msgstr ""
"Nyx no apostaría por eso... Ella percibe olor a sangre enana en el aire, "
"pero no hay rastro de hedor de no-muertos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:219
msgid ""
"Discussing what could be happening won't take us anywhere; we must hurry up "
"and see what's actually going on here."
msgstr ""
"Discutir qué podría estar pasando no nos llevará a ningún lado; debemos "
"apresurarnos y ver qué está ocurriendo realmente aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:223
msgid ""
"Right... Let's get moving; if we go straight south, we'll inevitably reach "
"the Great Northern Hall, and there we'll surely find someone able to inform "
"us."
msgstr ""
"Correcto... Pongámonos en marcha; si vamos directo al sur, llegaremos sin "
"falta al Gran Salón del Norte, y allí seguro encontraremos a alguien que "
"pueda informarnos."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Thanks Moradin, it's the Motsoghnir! Hey friends, please tell me, what is "
"happening..."
msgstr ""
"Gracias Moradin, ¡son los Motsoghnir! Oigan amigos, por favor díganme, ¿qué "
"está pasando...?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:256
msgid "Sigdral, wait, don't go near them!"
msgstr "¡Sigdral, espera, no te acerques a ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Anthaus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:260
msgid ""
"My, my, look at what we've got here... Isn't that the unworthy sister of the "
"unworthy Vindalf?"
msgstr ""
"Vaya, vaya, miren lo que tenemos aquí... ¿No es esa la hermana indigna del "
"indigno Vindalf?"

#. [message], speaker=Peldursol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:264
msgid ""
"Och, you're right, I've seen her before! So, if that's Sigdral, then those "
"humans must be the outlaws wanted by Lord Menon! Quick, if we get them we'll "
"be showered with rewards by Lord Argatyr!"
msgstr ""
"¡Och, tienes razón, la he visto antes! Así que si esa es Sigdral, entonces "
"esos humanos deben ser los forajidos que busca el señor Menon. ¡Rápido, si "
"los atrapamos nos lloverán recompensas del señor Argatyr!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:268
msgid "B-but w-what is..."
msgstr "P-pero q-qué es..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:272
msgid "I don't believe it... Has Argatyr betrayed the Aigathol?!"
msgstr "No lo puedo creer... ¡¿Argatyr ha traicionado a los Aigathol?!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:276
msgid "And it seems like he's in cahoots with Menon..."
msgstr "Y parece que está confabulado con Menon..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:280
msgid ""
"(enraged) You disgusting Motsoghnir, you'll never lay a finger on Sigdral "
"while I'm still alive! Come, folks, Lord Vindalf needs our aid!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecida) ¡Asquerosos Motsoghnir, nunca pondrán un dedo sobre Sigdral "
"mientras yo esté viva! ¡Vamos, gente, el señor Vindalf necesita nuestra "
"ayuda!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:348
msgid "No..."
msgstr "No…"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:366
msgid ""
"(enraged) ARGATYR!!! I DEMAND YOU TO EXPLAIN WHAT THE MEANING OF THIS "
"BETRAYAL IS!!!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecida) ¡ARGATYR!!! ¡EXIJO QUE EXPLIQUES EL SIGNIFICADO DE ESTA "
"TRAICIÓN!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:370
msgid ""
"This is not a betrayal, my little Sigdral: I'm simply correcting the mistake "
"my ancestors committed by allowing this impure, bastardized clan of dwarves "
"in our continent - a weak clan that shames all of dwarf-kind by mingling "
"with elves and befriending orcs!"
msgstr ""
"Esto no es una traición, mi pequeña Sigdral: simplemente estoy corrigiendo "
"el error que cometieron mis ancestros al permitir que este clan impuro y "
"bastardo de enanos entrara en nuestro continente, un clan débil que "
"avergüenza a toda la raza enana al mezclarse con elfos y hacerse amigo de "
"orcos."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:374
msgid ""
"You disgusting monster, it's you who brings shame to the dwarves of the "
"entire Irdya with your foolishness! Come on, Sigdral, someone must put an "
"end to his madness!"
msgstr ""
"¡Monstruo asqueroso, eres tú quien avergüenza a los enanos de toda Irdya con "
"tu estupidez! ¡Vamos, Sigdral, alguien debe poner fin a su locura!"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:378
msgid ""
"Wait...! Sigdral, Nyx, please run away... You are no match for Argatyr now, "
"he's... he's become a monster..."
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen...! Sigdral, Nyx, por favor huyan... No son rivales para Argatyr "
"ahora, él... se ha convertido en un monstruo..."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:382
msgid ""
"So you think that becoming stronger is turning into a monster? Truly words "
"worthy of a weakling."
msgstr ""
"¿Así que crees que volverse más fuerte es convertirse en un monstruo? "
"Palabras dignas de un débil."

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:386
msgid ""
"Become stronger, you said? No, Argatyr, the truth is that you've become "
"weaker; you could have died a warrior's death in the fight against Stygia, "
"sacrificing yourself to save us all, but you were too fearful of dying, "
"weren't you? Now, look at yourself: you’ve become a puppet to Menon, "
"Argatyr..."
msgstr ""
"¿Volverse más fuerte, dijiste? No, Argatyr, la verdad es que te has vuelto "
"más débil; podrías haber muerto con la muerte de un guerrero en la lucha "
"contra Stygia, sacrificándote para salvarnos a todos, pero tenías demasiado "
"miedo de morir, ¿verdad? Ahora mírate: te has convertido en un títere de "
"Menon, Argatyr..."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:390
msgid ""
"(laughing) You would think that he's controlling me, just as he probably "
"does himself, but you're both mistaken. I've merely used him for my own "
"ends; now that my body's restored, I will crush him and his stinking human "
"vermin, and afterwards I'll cleanse Netjer-Ta of whatever lowly race remains "
"- and I shall begin this cleansing with these bastard elvish dwarves..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Pensarían que él me está controlando, igual que probablemente se "
"controla a sí mismo, pero ambos se equivocan. Solo lo he usado para mis "
"propios fines; ahora que mi cuerpo está restaurado, lo aplastaré a él y a su "
"apestosa basura humana, y después limpiaré Netjer-Ta de cualquier raza "
"inferior que quede, y comenzaré esta limpieza con estos enanos bastardos "
"élficos..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:397
msgid "Brother, watch out!"
msgstr "¡Hermano, cuidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Vindalf
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:401
msgid ""
"(coughing) Sigdral, search for Anduril, he's evacuating our people to "
"Dvalin's Haven; please, lead our people for me..."
msgstr ""
"(tos) Sigdral, busca a Anduril, está evacuando a nuestra gente hacia el "
"Refugio de Dvalin; por favor, lidera a nuestra gente por mí..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:405
msgid "BROTHER!!!"
msgstr "¡HERMANO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:443
msgid "He blocked our path to prevent the Motsoghnir from catching us!"
msgstr "¡Bloqueó nuestro camino para impedir que los Motsoghnir nos atraparan!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:447
msgid "(crying) No... DAMN YOU, ARGATYR, HOU COULD YOU DO THIS?!"
msgstr "(llorando) No... ¡MALDITO SEAS, ARGATYR, ¿CÓMO PUDISTE HACER ESTO?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:451
msgid ""
"Sigdral, please, be strong, we must escape the Motsoghnir, or his sacrifice "
"will have been in vain!"
msgstr ""
"Sigdral, por favor, sé fuerte, debemos escapar de los Motsoghnir, ¡o su "
"sacrificio habrá sido en vano!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:455
msgid ""
"Sigdral, I understand how you feel; I too have just lost the person who was "
"dearest to me, though in a different way... Still, here I am, doing what I "
"can for those who can still be saved, am I not?"
msgstr ""
"Sigdral, entiendo cómo te sientes; yo también acabo de perder a la persona "
"que más quería, aunque de forma diferente... Aun así, aquí estoy, haciendo "
"lo que puedo por quienes todavía pueden salvarse, ¿no es así?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:459
msgid ""
"Y-you are right... Let's... Let's go this way; I know a secret passage in "
"this tunnel that leads to Dvalin's Haven..."
msgstr ""
"T-tienes razón... Vamos... Vamos por este camino; conozco un pasaje secreto "
"en este túnel que lleva al Refugio de Dvalin..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:465
msgid "Go east and rendezvous with Anduril"
msgstr "Ve al este y reúnete con Anduril"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:495
msgid ""
"While you go to Dvalin's Haven, Argatyr's forces are going there as well. "
"The Aigathol will delay them for a while only, so hurry up!"
msgstr ""
"Mientras tú vas al Refugio de Dvalin, las fuerzas de Argatyr también se "
"dirigen allí. Los Aigathol solo los retrasarán por un tiempo, ¡así que "
"apúrense!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:534
msgid ""
"*If only I could invoke the Trident's power... Damn you, Myra, why haven't "
"you appeared again since our flight from Maat'Kare...?*"
msgstr ""
"*Si tan solo pudiera invocar el poder del Tridente... Maldita seas, Myra, "
"¿por qué no has aparecido de nuevo desde nuestra huida de Maat'Kare...?*"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:588
msgid ""
"Sigdral! Thank goodness that you've managed to reach our home safe and "
"sound; your brother was fighting the Motsoghnir in the Citadel, to cover our "
"evacuation, but..."
msgstr ""
"¡Sigdral! Gracias a los dioses que lograste llegar a salvo a nuestro hogar; "
"tu hermano estaba luchando contra los Motsoghnir en la Ciudadela para cubrir "
"nuestra evacuación, pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:592
msgid "Brother's dead, Anduril. Argatyr killed him."
msgstr "Mi hermano está muerto, Anduril. Argatyr lo mató."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:596
msgid "(shocked) Lord Vindalf... is dead...?"
msgstr "(impactado) ¿El señor Vindalf... está muerto...?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:600
msgid "Anduril, tell me: how did this invasion begin?"
msgstr "Anduril, dime: ¿cómo comenzó esta invasión?"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:604
msgid ""
"Well... Mind you, milady, everything was well until yesterday; this attack "
"was completely unexpected, and thus we were practically defenceless against "
"it - in fact, we'd probably be no more, hadn't this brave dwarf warned us of "
"Argatyr's attack."
msgstr ""
"Bueno... Tenga en cuenta, milady, que todo estaba bien hasta ayer; este "
"ataque fue completamente inesperado y por eso estábamos prácticamente "
"indefensos ante él. De hecho, probablemente ya no estaríamos aquí si este "
"valiente enano no nos hubiera advertido del ataque de Argatyr."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:608
msgid "Hey, aren't you Gomatol, Argatyr's second-in-command?"
msgstr "Oye, ¿no eres Gomatol, el segundo al mando de Argatyr?"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:612
msgid ""
"No longer, not after I've seen what he's become; he isn't a dwarf anymore, "
"he's... I don't even know a word to describe what he's become."
msgstr ""
"Ya no, después de ver en qué se ha convertido; ya no es un enano, es... ni "
"siquiera tengo una palabra para describir en qué se ha convertido."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:616
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_b.cfg:767
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:308
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir?"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:620
msgid ""
"He... He said that Menon had asked him to search for some traitors in the "
"caves of the Aigathol, and that he was indebted to the Maat'Karian for "
"saving his life..."
msgstr ""
"Él... Dijo que Menon le había pedido buscar a algunos traidores en las "
"cuevas de los Aigathol, y que estaba en deuda con el maat'kariano por "
"haberle salvado la vida..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:624
msgid ""
"Professor, we've recently discovered that Menon is not who we always thought "
"him to be. He's caused the war against Skiron in order to have an excuse to "
"attack it."
msgstr ""
"Profesor, recientemente descubrimos que Menon no es quien siempre creímos "
"que era. Él provocó la guerra contra Skiron para tener una excusa para "
"atacarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:628
msgid ""
"But... Oh, my, this is all too confusing for an old dwarf like me... "
"However, I'll do what I can; I've understood that Argatyr is destroying our "
"home at the request of Menon, who wants to capture Akhen and his friends. "
"This we shall not allow! Humans, I will order a dwarf scout to take you away "
"from here; in the meanwhile, we'll hold back the Motsoghnir!"
msgstr ""
"Pero... Dios mío, todo esto es demasiado confuso para un viejo enano como "
"yo... Sin embargo, haré lo que pueda; entendí que Argatyr está destruyendo "
"nuestro hogar a pedido de Menon, quien quiere capturar a Akhen y a sus "
"amigos. ¡Esto no lo permitiremos! Humanos, ordenaré a un explorador enano "
"que los lleve lejos de aquí; mientras tanto, ¡contendremos a los Motsoghnir!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:632
msgid ""
"Thanks, Master Anduril, but we won't simply flee and leave you behind; we'll "
"help you hold back the Motsoghnir's attack for as long as we can!"
msgstr ""
"Gracias, maestro Anduril, pero no huiremos simplemente y los dejaremos "
"atrás; ¡los ayudaremos a contener el ataque de los Motsoghnir todo el tiempo "
"que podamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:636
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, we won't stand a chance if Argatyr himself attacks with Ymer's "
"Hammer in his hands. I will cause a rockslide to block the tunnels leading "
"here; please, protect me as I get to them."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, no tendremos ninguna oportunidad si el propio Argatyr ataca con "
"el Martillo de Ymer en sus manos. Provocaré un derrumbe para bloquear los "
"túneles que llevan aquí; por favor, protéjanme mientras llego a ellos."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:642
msgid ""
"Move Sigdral to 60,36 or 60,37 so that she may block the path of the "
"Motsoghnir"
msgstr ""
"Mueve a Sigdral a 60,36 o 60,37 para que pueda bloquear el camino de los "
"Motsoghnir"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:674
msgid "Death of Anduril"
msgstr "Muerte de Anduril"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:680
msgid ""
"Since Atenak hasn't brought her troops, you may only recruit/recall undead "
"and elemental units, and also recall Gomatol's dwarves"
msgstr ""
"Como Atenak no trajo sus tropas, solo puedes reclutar o reincorporar "
"unidades no-muertas y elementales, y también reincorporar a los enanos de "
"Gomatol"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:699
msgid "You shall advance no further into our caves, treacherous Motsoghnir!"
msgstr "¡No avanzarán más en nuestras cuevas, traicioneros Motsoghnir!"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:726
msgid ""
"At long last... This is far from being an actual victory, but at least the "
"worst has been averted."
msgstr ""
"Por fin... Esto está lejos de ser una victoria real, pero al menos se evitó "
"lo peor."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:730
msgid ""
"Now, we must meet Smenkhare in the Windswept Cliffs; I just hope that Menon "
"hasn't attacked him already..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora debemos reunirnos con Smenkhare en los Acantilados Azotados por el "
"Viento; solo espero que Menon no lo haya atacado ya..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:734
msgid ""
"And what will we do once we get there? Are we really going to fight our "
"countrymen?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y qué haremos una vez que lleguemos allí? ¿Realmente vamos a luchar contra "
"nuestros compatriotas?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:738
msgid ""
"I'm afraid that we have no other choice, Akhen - but I have other plans for "
"you. You do remember that Windsong monolith that we found in the Frozen "
"Mountains, and also the conclusion that we took from that, don't you?"
msgstr ""
"Me temo que no tenemos otra opción, Akhen, pero tengo otros planes para ti. "
"¿Recuerdas ese monolito de las Hijas del Viento que encontramos en las "
"Montañas Congeladas, y también la conclusión a la que llegamos con eso, "
"verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:742
msgid ""
"Yes... We concluded that the Windsong must have gone to the Blue Realms; but "
"what does this have to do with anything?"
msgstr ""
"Sí... Concluimos que las Hijas del Viento debían haber ido a los Reinos "
"Azules; pero ¿qué tiene que ver esto con nada?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:746
msgid ""
"See, as we are right now, we have no hope of standing against Menon and "
"Argatyr. But if we get the Windsong to help us..."
msgstr ""
"Verás, tal como estamos ahora, no tenemos esperanza de enfrentarnos a Menon "
"y Argatyr. Pero si logramos que las Hijas del Viento nos ayuden..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:750
msgid ""
"Wait a minute, do you want us to wander the Blue Realm, a region so cold "
"that even the air is said to freeze your lungs if you breathe it for too "
"long, after people we're not even sure to be really there? And besides, even "
"if we do find them, I doubt that they'll accept helping the people who "
"expelled them from this continent!"
msgstr ""
"Espera un momento, ¿quieres que vaguemos por el Reino Azul, una región tan "
"fría que dicen que el aire congela los pulmones si lo respiras por demasiado "
"tiempo, buscando a gente de la que ni siquiera estamos seguros de que esté "
"realmente allí? Y además, aunque los encontremos, dudo que acepten ayudar a "
"la gente que los expulsó de este continente."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:754
msgid ""
"It was Menon who did that, not Maat'Kare, and I'm sure that they'll "
"seriously consider helping us if that means having their revenge on him. And "
"yes, I know that I'm asking you to undergo an insanely dangerous enterprise, "
"but what other option do we have? If there's any, please tell me!"
msgstr ""
"Fue Menon quien hizo eso, no Maat'Kare, y estoy segura de que considerarán "
"seriamente ayudarnos si eso significa vengarse de él. Y sí, sé que les estoy "
"pidiendo que emprendan una empresa increíblemente peligrosa, pero ¿qué otra "
"opción tenemos? ¡Si hay alguna, por favor díganmela!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:758
msgid ""
"No, you're right… Especially with the Academy on his side, I see no hope of "
"surviving unless we have a faction like the Windsong on our side."
msgstr ""
"No, tienes razón… Especialmente con la Academia de su lado, no veo esperanza "
"de sobrevivir a menos que tengamos una facción como las Hijas del Viento de "
"nuestro lado."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:762
msgid "Well, if you're going there, then I'm following you."
msgstr "Bueno, si vas allí, entonces yo te sigo."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:766
msgid "So am I."
msgstr "Yo también."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:770
msgid ""
"Sorry, friends, but this time I won't be able to accompany you; I must stay "
"and help my people, lest we'll really be eradicated by Argatyr... But you "
"should go with them, Nyx."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, amigos, pero esta vez no podré acompañarlos; debo quedarme y "
"ayudar a mi gente, o realmente seremos erradicados por Argatyr... Pero tú "
"deberías ir con ellos, Nyx."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:774
msgid "And leave you alone? No way Nyx will..."
msgstr "¿Y dejarte sola? De ninguna manera Nyx va a..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:778
msgid ""
"I'll be fine, Anduril is with me; and, by helping Akhen find the Windsong, "
"you'll be doing us a great service as well. Besides, you still have that "
"debt to him, have you forgotten that?"
msgstr ""
"Estaré bien, Anduril está conmigo; y al ayudar a Akhen a encontrar a las "
"Hijas del Viento, también nos harás un gran servicio. Además, todavía tienes "
"esa deuda con él, ¿lo olvidaste?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:782
msgid ""
"But... (sigh) Well, Nyx won't discuss with you. Please, stay safe, all "
"right? Otherwise Nyx will put you on top of one of the library's bookshelves "
"and leave you there; you know she can really do that."
msgstr ""
"Pero... (suspiro) Bueno, Nyx no discutirá contigo. Por favor, mantente a "
"salvo, ¿de acuerdo? De lo contrario Nyx te pondrá encima de uno de los "
"estantes de la biblioteca y te dejará allí; sabes que realmente puede "
"hacerlo."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:786
msgid "Stay safe you too, sis - and the same goes to all of you."
msgstr "Tú también mantente a salvo, hermana, y lo mismo para todos ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:790
msgid "Good luck, Sigdral; I'll be back as soon as I can."
msgstr "Buena suerte, Sigdral; regresaré lo antes posible."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:829
msgid "I'm sorry, Lady Sigdral, I've failed you..."
msgstr "Lo siento, lady Sigdral, te he fallado..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:833
msgid "Anduril, not you too! I won't manage to lead our people without you!"
msgstr "¡Anduril, tú también no! ¡No podré liderar a nuestra gente sin ti!"

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:851
msgid "No! He and his veterans would have been an invaluable ally for us!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Él y sus veteranos habrían sido un aliado invaluable para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:862
msgid ""
"Seems like my fighters are failing to crush the vermin Aigathol... I think "
"I'll have to do it myself, then..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que mis guerreros no logran aplastar a la plaga Aigathol... Creo que "
"tendré que hacerlo yo mismo, entonces..."

#. [message], speaker=Anduril
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/13_The_Shadows_Within_Part_II.cfg:866
msgid ""
"No! We should have blocked the caves sooner! Now that Argatyr is on his way "
"here, we're doomed!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Deberíamos haber bloqueado las cuevas antes! ¡Ahora que Argatyr viene "
"hacia aquí, estamos perdidos!"

#. [scenario], id=14_Frozen_Earth_a
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:4
msgid "The Departure"
msgstr "La Partida"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:20
msgid "Recall six Maat'Karian veterans to accompany you on your journey"
msgstr ""
"Reincorpora a seis veteranos maat'karianos para que te acompañen en tu viaje"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:38
msgid "Rebel Maat'Karians"
msgstr "Rebeldes Maat'Karianos"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:100
msgid ""
"I really wish I could go with you all, but, as the only remaining heiress of "
"both the Aracynes and the Mewates, it is my duty to..."
msgstr ""
"Realmente desearía poder ir con todos ustedes, pero como la única heredera "
"restante tanto de los Aracyne como de los Mewate, es mi deber..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:104
msgid ""
"And we've already told you that we understand it, and that you need not "
"worry."
msgstr "Y ya te hemos dicho que lo entendemos y que no debes preocuparte."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:108
msgid "Exactly, mom, we will be fine on our own..."
msgstr "Exacto, mamá, estaremos bien por nuestra cuenta..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:112
msgid ""
"(smiling faintly) You silly folks, I'm just worried about you... Well, "
"anyway, I may not be following you, but I'll let you choose six of my "
"soldiers to accompany you on your journey."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo débilmente) Tontos, solo estoy preocupada por ustedes... Bueno, "
"de todos modos, aunque no los acompañe, les permitiré elegir a seis de mis "
"soldados para que los acompañen en su viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:116
msgid "Thank you, Atenak."
msgstr "Gracias, Atenak."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:125
msgid "Goodbye then, and good luck, and be careful..."
msgstr "Adiós entonces, y buena suerte, y tengan cuidado..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:129
msgid "<i>Bye</i>, mom..."
msgstr "<i>Adiós</i>, mamá..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_a.cfg:133
msgid ""
"I promise we will be back as soon as we can with strong reinforcements - be "
"they Windsong or anyone else who may wish to help us..."
msgstr ""
"Prometo que regresaremos lo antes posible con refuerzos fuertes, sean las "
"Hijas del Viento o cualquier otro que quiera ayudarnos..."

#. [scenario], id=14_Frozen_Earth_b
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_b.cfg:4
msgid "Frozen Earth"
msgstr "Tierra Congelada"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_b.cfg:24
msgid "Explore the Blue Realm"
msgstr "Explora el Reino Azul"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_b.cfg:44
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_b.cfg:626
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/16_Burning_Ice.cfg:51
msgid ""
"In this scenario, living units without the Flameheart Amulet will suffer the "
"effects of the land's cold, losing 2 HP per turn if not treated by healers. "
"Staying inside a castle, village or keep will nullify the freezing's effects."
msgstr ""
"En este escenario, las unidades vivas sin el Amuleto de Corazón de Llama "
"sufrirán los efectos del frío de la tierra, perdiendo 2 PV por turno si no "
"son tratadas por sanadores. Permanecer dentro de un castillo, aldea o "
"torreón anulará los efectos de la congelación."

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/14_Frozen_Earth_b.cfg:64
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/16_Burning_Ice.cfg:73
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:59
