#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:641
msgid "Death of Branwyn"
msgstr "Muerte de Branwyn"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:70
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:82
msgid "Outlaws"
msgstr "Forajidos"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:93
msgid "Rockvale"
msgstr "Rockvale"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:117
msgid "Woses"
msgstr "Woses"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:179
msgid ""
"Oh, sleeping beauty has finally awakened! You seem to have suffered a true "
"trashing by Thalassa, haven't you?"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, la bella durmiente por fin despertó! Parece que sufriste una verdadera "
"paliza de Thalassa, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:183
msgid "Ugh... Who... Where..."
msgstr "Ugh... ¿Quién... Dónde..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:187
msgid ""
"I knew it, you're not from this island! Though you don't look that Chomi to "
"me, especially with such fine clothing... Where are you from, and what "
"brings you to our humble Green Isle?"
msgstr ""
"Lo sabía, ¡no eres de esta isla! Aunque no me pareces tan chomi, "
"especialmente con ropa tan fina... ¿De dónde vienes y qué te trae a nuestra "
"humilde Isla Verde?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:191
msgid ""
"(suddenly agitated) Wait, is this the Green Isle...?! Listen, did you see "
"anyone with features and clothing like my own around?"
msgstr ""
"(repentinamente agitado) Espera, ¿esta es la Isla Verde...?! Escucha, ¿has "
"visto a alguien con rasgos y vestimenta como la mía por aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:195
msgid "Alas, I've just found you all alone on this beach..."
msgstr "Lamentablemente, te encontré completamente solo en esta playa..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:204
msgid ""
"He isn't alone. Now, step back slowly and carefully, or Nyx may accidentally "
"slash your throat."
msgstr ""
"Él no está solo. Ahora, retrocede lentamente y con cuidado, o Nyx podría "
"cortarte la garganta por accidente."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:208
msgid ""
"Whoa, there's no need for that, my fair lady, I don't steal from strangers "
"who've just stranded on our shores, we Aeserians do know our hospitality... "
"Um, you don't resemble him, though... And you're so pale, are you sick or "
"anything?"
msgstr ""
"Vaya, no hace falta eso, mi bella dama, no robo a extraños que acaban de "
"varar en nuestras costas, los aeserianos sí sabemos de hospitalidad... Eh, "
"no te pareces a él, sin embargo... Y estás tan pálida, ¿estás enferma o algo?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:212
msgid "(angry) Who the hell is this wench...?"
msgstr "(enojada) ¿Quién demonios es esta mujer...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:216
msgid ""
"Listen, friend, my name is Akhen Wadjet, and this is Nyx Devellian; we came "
"from Netjer-Ta, a continent far to the west, but we've suffered a shipwreck "
"and we got separated from our friends..."
msgstr ""
"Escucha, amiga, mi nombre es Akhen Wadjet, y esta es Nyx Devellian; venimos "
"de Netjer-Ta, un continente muy al oeste, pero sufrimos un naufragio y nos "
"separamos de nuestros amigos..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:220
msgid ""
"Netjer-Ta? Never knew this name before... In fact, I thought that the only "
"other lands beside this were Arajunna and the Aeserians' old homeland beyond "
"the seas, but I'm only a poor poetess who lives in the wilderness, I have "
"little contact with the outside world."
msgstr ""
"¿Netjer-Ta? Nunca había oído ese nombre antes... De hecho, pensaba que las "
"únicas otras tierras además de esta eran Arajunna y la antigua patria de las "
"aeserianas más allá de los mares, pero solo soy una pobre poetisa que vive "
"en la naturaleza, tengo poco contacto con el mundo exterior."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:224
msgid "All right... Listen, uh..."
msgstr "De acuerdo... Escucha, uh..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:228
msgid "You may call me Branwyn, Branwyn the Bard."
msgstr "Puedes llamarme Branwyn, Branwyn la Barda."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:232
msgid ""
"Branwyn, we come here as friends; we knew of this island's existence, but we "
"know nothing of its inhabitants. If you could tell us more about your people "
"and take us to one of your kingdoms or cities, we will reward you generously."
msgstr ""
"Branwyn, venimos aquí como amigos; conocíamos la existencia de esta isla, "
"pero no sabemos nada de sus habitantes. Si pudieras contarnos más sobre tu "
"gente y llevarnos a uno de sus reinos o ciudades, te recompensaremos "
"generosamente."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:236
msgid "You don't look like you have a hoard with you, though..."
msgstr "Aunque no pareces tener un tesoro contigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:241
msgid "(sigh) Take this armlet of Nyx in advance, then..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Toma este brazalete de Nyx por adelantado, entonces..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:245
msgid ""
"No worries, judging by your garments you do seem to come from a realm of "
"plenty. For now, I'll just stick with you until you find your fellows again, "
"I think."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, a juzgar por tus ropas sí pareces venir de un reino de "
"abundancia. Por ahora, solo me quedaré contigo hasta que encuentres de nuevo "
"a tus compañeros, creo."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:249
msgid "Fine. So, where in this island are we?"
msgstr "Bien. Entonces, ¿en qué parte de la isla estamos?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:253
msgid ""
"In the north-eastern reaches of our realm, a region we Aeserians gave the "
"suggestive name of Outlaw Land. The closest lawful settlement is Rockvale, "
"but we'll have to cross some extension of land to reach it."
msgstr ""
"En las regiones noreste de nuestro reino, una zona que nosotros las "
"Aeserianos llamamos con el sugerente nombre de Tierra de Forajidos. El "
"asentamiento legal más cercano es Rockvale, pero tendremos que cruzar un "
"tramo de tierra para llegar allí."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:257
msgid ""
"Lead us there, then; if we find any band of outlaws or wild beasts, we may "
"be able to vanquish them with some ease."
msgstr ""
"Llévanos allí entonces; si encontramos alguna banda de forajidos o bestias "
"salvajes, podremos derrotarlos con relativa facilidad."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:279
msgid "And Nyx... Thank you for saving my life."
msgstr "Y Nyx... Gracias por salvarme la vida."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:283
msgid ""
"You're welcome! It does feel good to be the one doing the saving for a "
"change."
msgstr "¡De nada! Se siente bien ser quien salva a alguien para variar."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:290
msgid ""
"You know, with the amount of mutual saving we've done so far, you are "
"allowed to be frank with me."
msgstr ""
"Sabes, con la cantidad de salvadas mutuas que hemos hecho hasta ahora, "
"puedes ser franco conmigo."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:294
msgid ""
"(blushes) Oh well... There is something I've been meaning to ask for a "
"while. Mind you, I searched about it the Academy's Library before, but our "
"knowledge on vampires is shamefully limited..."
msgstr ""
"(se sonroja) Bueno... Hay algo que he querido preguntar desde hace un "
"tiempo. Ten en cuenta que busqué sobre eso en la biblioteca de la Academia "
"antes, pero nuestro conocimiento sobre vampiros es vergonzosamente "
"limitado..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:298
msgid ""
"(chuckles) Leave it to you to read an entire library rather than ask people "
"directly..."
msgstr ""
"(ríe) Típico de ti leer una biblioteca entera en vez de preguntar "
"directamente a la gente..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:302
msgid ""
"(blushes even more) Anyway... What I meant to ask is: how do vampire "
"families work? I recall you mentioning that vampires can't have children, "
"and yet you had... well, a pretty large family."
msgstr ""
"(se sonroja aún más) De todos modos... Lo que quería preguntar es: ¿cómo "
"funcionan las familias de vampiros? Recuerdo que mencionaste que los "
"vampiros no pueden tener hijos, y sin embargo tú tenías... bueno, una "
"familia bastante grande."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:306
msgid ""
"Ah, yes. You would never find the answer to that in your scrolls, as it's "
"perhaps our closest-guarded secret..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, sí. Nunca encontrarías la respuesta a eso en tus pergaminos, porque es "
"quizás nuestro secreto mejor guardado..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:310
msgid "You don't have to say anything if you don't want to..."
msgstr "No tienes que decir nada si no quieres..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:314
msgid ""
"I know. But perhaps it's for the best that we have this conversation now. "
"What you see of vampire society is the façade we allow you to see; what we "
"don't allow you to see is that most of it is made up of uninfected people."
msgstr ""
"Lo sé. Pero quizás sea mejor que tengamos esta conversación ahora. Lo que "
"ves de la sociedad vampírica es la fachada que permitimos que vean; lo que "
"no permitimos que vean es que la mayoría está compuesta por personas no "
"infectadas."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:318
msgid "Hold on, then..."
msgstr "Espera entonces..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:322
msgid ""
"Yes, we turn them once they reach certain age, after they've birthed an "
"adequate number of people to replenish our numbers as we wither or as we are "
"killed in battle. Noble clans function much the same way: whoever is chosen "
"to suceed the previous patriarch or matriarch sires or births a certain "
"number of children, and only then are they turned - usually by their "
"predecessor. Traditionally, you see, whoever turns us becomes a sort of "
"parent as well."
msgstr ""
"Sí, los convertimos una vez que alcanzan cierta edad, después de que hayan "
"dado a luz a un número adecuado de personas para reponer nuestros números "
"cuando nos debilitamos o cuando nos matan en batalla. Los clanes nobles "
"funcionan de forma muy similar: quien es elegido para suceder al patriarca o "
"matriarca anterior engendra o da a luz a cierto número de hijos, y solo "
"entonces son convertidos, usualmente por su predecesor. Tradicionalmente, "
"quien nos convierte se vuelve una especie de padre también."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:326
msgid ""
"That's... So right now, there are hundreds, perhaps thousands of uninfected "
"people-"
msgstr ""
"Eso es... Entonces ahora mismo hay cientos, quizá miles de personas no "
"infectadas..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:330
msgid ""
"Allow me to say this in my people's defence: the uninfected, or the unreborn "
"as we call them, aren't mere cattle... well, to a few clans they may be, but "
"these are the exception. Traditionally, our relationship is one of "
"symbiosis: we who have been 'reborn' as vampires use the strength the curse "
"gives us to protect the unreborn from the dangers of that continent where "
"the old Windsong left us."
msgstr ""
"Permíteme decir esto en defensa de mi gente: los no infectados, o los no "
"renacidos como los llamamos, no son mera ganado... bueno, para algunos "
"clanes pueden serlo, pero son la excepción. Tradicionalmente, nuestra "
"relación es de simbiosis: nosotros que hemos sido «renacidos» como vampiros "
"usamos la fuerza que nos da la maldición para proteger a los no renacidos de "
"los peligros de ese continente donde las antiguas Hijas del Viento nos "
"dejaron."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:334
msgid ""
"But these unreborn aren't even aware that there is another human "
"civilisation on Netjer-Ta, are they?"
msgstr ""
"Pero estos no renacidos ni siquiera saben que existe otra civilización "
"humana en Netjer-Ta, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:338
msgid ""
"Oh, of course they are. They're also aware that this other civilisation is "
"so bent on destroying vampire-kind, it'll kill even the unreborn to make "
"sure our curse isn't passed on."
msgstr ""
"Oh, claro que lo saben. También saben que esa otra civilización está tan "
"empeñada en destruir a los vampiros que matará incluso a los no renacidos "
"para asegurarse de que nuestra maldición no se transmita."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:342
msgid ""
"That seems... You know what? I'm not in a position to judge, not when my "
"people has never put a lot of effort in understanding yours-"
msgstr ""
"Eso parece... ¿Sabes qué? No estoy en posición de juzgar, no cuando mi gente "
"nunca ha puesto mucho esfuerzo en entender a la tuya..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:346
msgid ""
"You're allowed to disagree with our ways too, Akhen. Especially ways my own "
"father disagreed with. He wanted to allow the unreborn the choice to join "
"Maat'Karian society, should they not desire to become vampires. That was why "
"his vassals turned on him when Erynia attacked: they were too afraid that, "
"if given the choice, most unreborn would join their fellow 'warmlings', "
"condemning our entire society to slowly die out."
msgstr ""
"También puedes estar en desacuerdo con nuestras costumbres, Akhen. "
"Especialmente con las que mi propio padre no estaba de acuerdo. Él quería "
"permitir que los no renacidos tuvieran la opción de unirse a la sociedad "
"maat'kariana si no deseaban convertirse en vampiros. Por eso sus vasallos se "
"volvieron contra él cuando Erynia atacó: tenían demasiado miedo de que, si "
"se les daba la opción, la mayoría de los no renacidos se unieran a sus "
"compañeros «calientitos», condenando a toda nuestra sociedad a morir "
"lentamente."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:350
msgid ""
"I see... Well, who knows, perhaps we could renew your father's dream? He was "
"a powerful lord, one who stood to lose the most if the unreborn deserted; "
"surely some vampires from lesser castes share his opinions?"
msgstr ""
"Ya veo... Bueno, quién sabe, ¿quizá podríamos renovar el sueño de tu padre? "
"Él era un señor poderoso, uno que tenía más que perder si los no renacidos "
"desertaban; seguro que algunos vampiros de castas inferiores comparten su "
"opinión."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:354
msgid ""
"Perhaps... But that would be a work of generations, and it'd take the "
"leadership of a duke or duchess. Vampire society is too hierarchical for "
"such a great change to be achieved without the leadership of powerful "
"individuals. Perhaps if I'd fought for my birthright; father did publicly "
"chose me as his scion... (shakes head) No, I would never have ruled over "
"those people who let my father die. Let change be done by someone else; I "
"regret nothing. Much more preferable to walk among people who actually care "
"for Nyx... 'Warmling' as they may be."
msgstr ""
"Quizá... Pero eso sería trabajo de generaciones y requeriría el liderazgo de "
"un duque o duquesa. La sociedad vampírica es demasiado jerárquica para que "
"un cambio tan grande se logre sin el liderazgo de individuos poderosos. "
"Quizá si hubiera luchado por mi derecho de nacimiento; mi padre me eligió "
"públicamente como su sucesora... (sacude la cabeza) No, nunca habría "
"gobernado sobre esas personas que dejaron morir a mi padre. Que el cambio lo "
"haga otro; no me arrepiento de nada. Es mucho más preferible caminar entre "
"personas que realmente se preocupan por Nyx... aunque sean «calientitos»."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:358
msgid "(smiling) And I'm glad you feel that way."
msgstr "(sonriendo) Y me alegra que te sientas así."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:365
msgid "But... hold on... if you were your father's chosen successor..."
msgstr "Pero... espera... si eras la sucesora elegida de tu padre..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:369
msgid ""
"(chuckles) No, I've birthed no scion of my own. I said father chose me as "
"his scion, but I actually refused. The idea of ruling sounded nice, but the "
"idea of birthing child after child, and by someone I felt no affection "
"for... *shudders*"
msgstr ""
"(ríe) No, no he dado a luz a ningún sucesor propio. Dije que mi padre me "
"eligió como su sucesora, pero en realidad me negué. La idea de gobernar "
"sonaba bien, pero la idea de dar a luz hijo tras hijo, y con alguien por "
"quien no sentía afecto... *estremecimiento*"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Of course, it would've been a different matter if I'd known a <i>certain</i> "
"someone then. With <i>his</i> children, I might have gladly filled the Red "
"Pinnacle's court..."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, habría sido diferente si hubiera conocido a <i>cierta</i> "
"persona en ese entonces. Con <i>sus</i> hijos, quizá habría llenado "
"gustosamente la corte de la Cumbre Roja..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:380
msgid "(blushes violently)"
msgstr "(se sonroja violentamente)"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:401
msgid ""
"Branwyn, a while ago you mentioned names such as 'Aeserians', 'Chomi' and "
"'Arajunna'. Could you please tell us more about these?"
msgstr ""
"Branwyn, hace un rato mencionaste nombres como «aeserianas», «chomi» y "
"«Arajunna». ¿Podrías contarnos más sobre ellos?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:405
msgid ""
"Ah, sure! (starts playing harp) 'From setting sun our 'cestors sailed / Our "
"land lost to lowly looters / Brutes who 'bibed the blood of our brothers / "
"Here they had a haven / In this isle the Aeserians settled / Living 'lone "
"for long... (stops playing harp) Until the Chomi came from a continent "
"beyond the southern seas, which they call Arajunna."
msgstr ""
"¡Ah, claro! (empieza a tocar el arpa) «Del sol poniente navegaron nuestros "
"ancestros / Nuestra tierra perdida ante viles saqueadores / Brutos que "
"bebieron la sangre de nuestros hermanos / Aquí encontraron refugio / En esta "
"isla se establecieron las aeserianas / Viviendo solas por mucho tiempo...» "
"(deja de tocar el arpa) Hasta que los chomi vinieron de un continente más "
"allá de los mares del sur, al que llaman Arajunna."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:409
msgid "What an abrupt break of rhythm..."
msgstr "Qué ruptura tan abrupta del ritmo..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Well, I've just recently started composing it, so it's not really fine yet. "
"Anyway, these Chomi came from Arajunna in many boats and built some bases "
"here, but only in lands uninhabited by us Aeserians. You see, they don't "
"want to fight us, and that is a fortunate thing, for they have tools and "
"talents that we don't."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, recién empecé a componerla, así que todavía no está muy bien. De "
"todos modos, estos chomi vinieron de Arajunna en muchos barcos y "
"construyeron algunas bases aquí, pero solo en tierras no habitadas por "
"nosotras las aeserianas. Verán, no quieren pelear con nosotras, y eso es una "
"suerte, porque tienen herramientas y talentos que nosotras no tenemos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:417
msgid ""
"That's interesting indeed... These Chomi must be the people Yukia told us "
"about; the fierce warriors who live side by side with giants in a land to "
"the south of this island..."
msgstr ""
"Eso es realmente interesante... Estos chomi deben ser la gente de la que nos "
"habló Yukia; los fieros guerreros que viven junto a gigantes en una tierra "
"al sur de esta isla..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:421
msgid "Um, I'm eager to visit this land of Arajunna..."
msgstr "Um, tengo muchas ganas de visitar esta tierra de Arajunna..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:425
msgid ""
"Me too; having an army of giants on our side would certainly compensate the "
"loss of the Windsong..."
msgstr ""
"Yo también; tener un ejército de gigantes de nuestro lado sin duda "
"compensaría la pérdida de las Hijas del Viento..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:429
msgid "...and also because they must have plenty of blood..."
msgstr "...y también porque deben tener mucha sangre..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:433
msgid "(chuckling) Nyx, Nyx..."
msgstr "(riendo) Nyx, Nyx..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:437
msgid "(looks puzzled)"
msgstr "(parece confundida)"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:454
msgid ""
"(suddenly alert) Uh-oh... Folks, I think we've walked right into a trap..."
msgstr ""
"(de repente alerta) Uh-oh... Gente, creo que hemos caído directamente en una "
"trampa..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:458
msgid "What d-"
msgstr "¿Qué d-?"

#. [unit], id=Lyr, type=Highwayman
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:472
msgid "Mac Lyr"
msgstr "Mac Lyr"

#. [unit], id=Caullon, type=Fugitive
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:481
msgid "Mac Caullon"
msgstr "Mac Caullon"

#. [unit], id=Keiran, type=Ranger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:490
msgid "Mac Keiran"
msgstr "Mac Keiran"

#. [message], speaker=Lyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:504
msgid ""
"See, brothers? I told you that the Chomi were using this region as a new "
"trading route!"
msgstr ""
"¿Ven, hermanos? ¡Les dije que los chomi estaban usando esta región como una "
"nueva ruta comercial!"

#. [message], speaker=Caullon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:508
msgid ""
"Eh, I don't see any caravan with them though, not even a merchant cart, but "
"that fine-looking trident the boy is carrying must be quite expensive... But "
"let's not be so merciless with our visitors from the south: if they calmly "
"yield us their belongings, there's no reason to kill them."
msgstr ""
"Eh, no veo ninguna caravana con ellos, ni siquiera un carro de mercader, "
"pero ese tridente tan bonito que lleva el muchacho debe ser bastante caro... "
"Pero no seamos tan despiadados con nuestros visitantes del sur: si nos "
"entregan tranquilamente sus pertenencias, no hay razón para matarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:512
msgid ""
"No way I'm giving you anything! I'll say it only once: you can let us go in "
"peace or, if you want to fight that much, get yourselves ready."
msgstr ""
"¡De ninguna manera les voy a dar nada! Lo diré solo una vez: pueden dejarnos "
"ir en paz o, si tanto quieren pelear, prepárense."

#. [message], speaker=Keiran
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:516
msgid ""
"(angry) These damn Chomi, they think themselves so great just because "
"they're good at sailing and at doing tricks! C'mon, brothers, let's give "
"them a lesson on respect!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Estos malditos chomi, ¡se creen tan grandes solo porque son buenos "
"navegando y haciendo trucos! ¡Vamos, hermanos, démosles una lección de "
"respeto!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:520
msgid ""
"Listen, you better have some trick up your sleeve, 'cause I'm not going to "
"die for your bravado!"
msgstr ""
"Escuchen, más les vale tener algún truco bajo la manga, ¡porque no voy a "
"morir por su valentía!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:524
msgid ""
"(smirking) Don't worry, bard girl, just stay behind that we will protect you."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo burlonamente) No te preocupes, chica barda, solo quédate atrás "
"que nosotros te protegeremos."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:544
msgid "Defeat the Mac Brothers"
msgstr "Derrota a los hermanos Mac"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:560
msgid "NOTE: Akhen can recruit from 35,27 in the adjoining hexes."
msgstr "NOTA: Akhen puede reclutar desde 35,27 en los hexágonos adyacentes."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:578
msgid "WHOA! What on this wide green world is that thing?!"
msgstr "¡WHOA! ¿Qué demonios en este vasto mundo verde es esa cosa?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:582
msgid ""
"That's an elemental creature I've summoned through magic. Probably that's "
"not something the Chomi can do, but in my homeland we have many mages "
"capable of that."
msgstr ""
"Esa es una criatura elemental que he invocado mediante magia. Probablemente "
"eso no sea algo que los chomi puedan hacer, pero en mi tierra natal tenemos "
"muchos magos capaces de hacerlo."

#. [message], speaker=Caullon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:586
msgid ""
"Don't be afraid, men, if it is solid it can be either killed or destroyed!"
msgstr "No tengan miedo, hombres, ¡si es sólido se puede matar o destruir!"

#. [message], speaker=Caullon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:600
msgid ""
"See! They fall to pieces just like anything else if you hit them hard enough!"
msgstr ""
"¡Miren! Se hacen pedazos igual que cualquier otra cosa si los golpeas lo "
"suficientemente fuerte."

#. [message], speaker=Lyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:617
msgid "Is that wench... drinking blood?! What kind of perversion is that?!"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Esa mujer... está bebiendo sangre?! ¡¿Qué clase de perversión es esa?!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:621
msgid "I'm with them on that, folks, that's just <i>gross</i>..."
msgstr ""
"Estoy de acuerdo con ellos en eso, gente, eso es simplemente <i>asqueroso</"
"i>..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:625
msgid ""
"See, Branwyn, Nyx is a vampiress, a creature that feeds on blood - but don't "
"worry, she won't do that to you."
msgstr ""
"Mira, Branwyn, Nyx es una vampiresa, una criatura que se alimenta de sangre, "
"pero no te preocupes, no te hará eso a ti."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:629
msgid "(scared) If you say so..."
msgstr "(asustada) Si tú lo dices..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:646
msgid ""
"(frightened) Aaaiieeee!!! With a thousand curses, what was that just now?!"
msgstr ""
"(aterrorizada) ¡Aaaiieeee!!! ¡Con mil maldiciones, qué fue eso que acaba de "
"pasar?!"

#. [message], speaker=Keiran
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:650
msgid ""
"(scared) What the hell...? I didn't know there was such kind of monster in "
"Arajunna...!"
msgstr ""
"(asustado) ¿Qué demonios...? ¡No sabía que había ese tipo de monstruo en "
"Arajunna...!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:654
msgid "(blinking) Just a little spell from my homeland's lore, you see..."
msgstr ""
"(parpadeando) Solo un pequeño hechizo del conocimiento de mi tierra natal, "
"ya ves..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:658
msgid ""
"(rolls eyes) Don't be so impressed, bard girl, we have two other friends who "
"can do just as much as he does."
msgstr ""
"(pone los ojos en blanco) No te impresiones tanto, chica barda, tenemos "
"otros dos amigos que pueden hacer tanto como él."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:662
msgid "(sulks)"
msgstr "(hace pucheros)"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:681
msgid ""
"(sigh) Why couldn't they just let us pass...? I'm sorry for causing such "
"bloodshed on your land, Branwyn, but this Trident is an extremely important "
"item..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) ¿Por qué no pudieron simplemente dejarnos pasar...? Lo siento por "
"causar tal derramamiento de sangre en tu tierra, Branwyn, pero este Tridente "
"es un objeto extremadamente importante..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:685
msgid ""
"Ah, don't worry, you've actually done a worthy deed. The Mac Brothers were a "
"grave threat to peasant and pilgrim alike; without them, north-eastern Green "
"Isle will be much safer. Now, onwards to Rockvale: down this road to the "
"east and through the Wailing Valley, our destination will unfold before our "
"eyes."
msgstr ""
"Ah, no te preocupes, en realidad has hecho una buena acción. Los hermanos "
"Mac eran una grave amenaza tanto para campesinos como para peregrinos; sin "
"ellos, el noreste de la Isla Verde estará mucho más seguro. Ahora, en marcha "
"hacia Rockvale: por este camino hacia el este y a través del Valle de los "
"Lamentos, nuestro destino se revelará ante nuestros ojos."

#. [unit], id=Blude, type=Ancient Dark Wose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:739
msgid "Bludebalmen"
msgstr "Bludebalmen"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:766
msgid ""
"Halt, you! State your name and business in... Wait, is that you, Branwyn?"
msgstr ""
"¡Alto ahí! Digan su nombre y qué asunto les trae... Espera, ¿eres tú, "
"Branwyn?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:770
msgid "She seems to be quite well know, doesn't she?"
msgstr "Parece que es bastante conocida, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:774
msgid ""
"Course I am, I'm the best bard 'bout... (to the sentry) I'm simply seeing to "
"these foreign friends, who wished to reach the nearest of our cities."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que lo soy, soy la mejor barda de por aquí... (al centinela) "
"Solo estoy acompañando a estos amigos extranjeros que deseaban llegar a la "
"ciudad más cercana de las nuestras."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:778
msgid ""
"It is so; in fact, we wish to talk to your ruler, or rulers, do you think "
"that's possible?"
msgstr ""
"Así es; de hecho, deseamos hablar con su gobernante o gobernantes, ¿crees "
"que eso sea posible?"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:782
msgid ""
"Elder Afallon is always welcoming of outsiders, and accepts speaking with "
"anyone who wishes to have a word with him, but right now I fear he won't be "
"receiving anyone - actually, staying at Rockvale right now is not a good "
"idea... Mind you, we're under attack by the woses. They just came out of "
"nowhere, crushing our walls, claiming that they're going to wipe us out..."
msgstr ""
"El anciano Afallon siempre recibe bien a los forasteros y acepta hablar con "
"cualquiera que desee tener una palabra con él, pero ahora temo que no "
"recibirá a nadie. De hecho, quedarse en Rockvale ahora no es una buena "
"idea... Ten en cuenta que estamos bajo ataque de los woses. Salieron de la "
"nada, aplastando nuestras murallas, diciendo que van a exterminarnos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:786
msgid "Sorry, but what are woses?"
msgstr "Lo siento, pero ¿qué son los woses?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:790
msgid ""
"The folk of the forest; they're trees who talk and are as much smart as men "
"and women."
msgstr ""
"El pueblo del bosque; son árboles que hablan y son tan inteligentes como los "
"hombres y las mujeres."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:794
msgid ""
"Did you just say <i>talking trees</i>? Now that's something Nyx would like "
"to see for herself..."
msgstr ""
"¿Acabas de decir <i>árboles que hablan</i>? Ahora eso es algo que Nyx "
"quisiera ver por sí misma..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:798
msgid "Worry not, though, for my friends shall finish these fiends with ease!"
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, porque mis amigos terminarán con estos demonios con "
"facilidad."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:802
msgid ""
"If that is so, then please hurry to our city, for I'm afraid that things are "
"boding badly for our side!"
msgstr ""
"Si es así, entonces por favor apúrense a nuestra ciudad, porque me temo que "
"las cosas se ven mal para nuestro bando."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:825
msgid ""
"And so we finally reach fair Rockvale! My, 'twas truth that poured out of "
"that sentry's mouth, the woses are truly waging total war on the locals..."
msgstr ""
"¡Y así finalmente llegamos a la bella Rockvale! Vaya, era verdad lo que "
"salió de la boca de ese centinela, los woses realmente están librando una "
"guerra total contra los locales..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:829
msgid ""
"Hail, good people of Rockvale! I am Akhen Wadjet, and I have come to your "
"island from a distant continent; may I rest at your town for a while?"
msgstr ""
"¡Saludos, buena gente de Rockvale! Soy Akhen Wadjet y he venido a su isla "
"desde un continente lejano; ¿puedo descansar en su ciudad por un tiempo?"

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:833
msgid ""
"Greetings, foreigner; I am Afallon, called 'the Wise' by the folk, and I say "
"come and enjoy our hospitality - or so I would in a normal situation. "
"Nevertheless, right now we're at risk of being uprooted from our town by the "
"tree-folk!"
msgstr ""
"Saludos, forastero; soy Afallon, llamado «el Sabio» por la gente, y digo que "
"vengan y disfruten de nuestra hospitalidad, o eso diría en una situación "
"normal. Sin embargo, ahora mismo estamos en riesgo de ser arrancados de "
"nuestra ciudad por el pueblo de los árboles."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:837
msgid ""
"So those are woses... Interesting, they do look like trees; it must be truly "
"hard to fight them in such a woody region, you never know which is an actual "
"tree, and which is a foe..."
msgstr ""
"Así que esos son los woses... Interesante, sí parecen árboles; debe ser "
"realmente difícil luchar contra ellos en una región tan boscosa, nunca sabes "
"cuál es un árbol real y cuál es un enemigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:841
msgid ""
"Weird... I feel a great malice from them, something that's not typical of "
"any living being... Elder, these woses haven't always behaved so violently, "
"have they?"
msgstr ""
"Qué raro... Siento una gran malicia de ellos, algo que no es típico de "
"ningún ser vivo... Anciano, estos woses no siempre se han comportado tan "
"violentamente, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:845
msgid ""
"(surprised) You're right, my boy; though they're not always happy with us "
"human-folk for our cutting of trees, they've never been so vicious before."
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) Tienes razón, muchacho; aunque no siempre están contentos con "
"nosotros los humanos por cortar árboles, nunca habían sido tan feroces antes."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:850
msgid ""
"<i>*These woses have been corrupted, Akhen; they may look like mere walking "
"trees, but they have keen magical senses, and share a deep connection to "
"nature. However, even nature has got a dark side to itself, and that's "
"specially true of woses*</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>*Estos woses han sido corrompidos, Akhen; pueden parecer simples árboles "
"que caminan, pero tienen sentidos mágicos agudos y comparten una conexión "
"profunda con la naturaleza. Sin embargo, incluso la naturaleza tiene un lado "
"oscuro, y eso es especialmente cierto para los woses.*</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:854
msgid ""
"I see... Elder, what you said just now has made me think... Probably the "
"woses have grown resentful of humans chopping down their forests, and this "
"hatred has corrupted one of them, which by its turn corrupted its offspring. "
"I think I can solve this problem: I'll make it to their leader, and try to "
"purge his darkness out of him."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo... Anciano, lo que acabas de decir me ha hecho pensar... "
"Probablemente los woses se han vuelto resentidos porque los humanos cortan "
"sus bosques, y este odio ha corrompido a uno de ellos, que a su vez "
"corrompió a su descendencia. Creo que puedo resolver este problema: llegaré "
"hasta su líder e intentaré purgar la oscuridad de él."

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:858
msgid ""
"If you think that you can do this, young man, we shall protect you as you "
"reach the Elder Wose; we don't have other alternatives anyway..."
msgstr ""
"Si crees que puedes hacer esto, joven, te protegeremos mientras llegas hasta "
"el Anciano Wose; de todos modos no tenemos otras alternativas..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:864
msgid "Defeat Bludebalmen with Akhen"
msgstr "Derrota a Bludebalmen con Akhen"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:880
msgid "Death of Afallon"
msgstr "Muerte de Afallon"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:906
msgid ""
"(disgusted) Ack! Their sap tastes horribly! No, there's no way I'll become "
"vegetarian if I have to drink such horrible blood..."
msgstr ""
"(asqueada) ¡Ack! ¡Su savia sabe horrible! No, de ninguna manera me haré "
"vegetariana si tengo que beber una sangre tan horrible..."

#. [message], speaker=Blude
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:921
msgid ""
"You puny human, we receive your kind on our island with open branches, you "
"promise never to lay a finger on our precious forests, and a few generations "
"later you forget all that and start felling our homes with your accursed "
"axes, by the First I shall not let you remain on our island anymore!"
msgstr ""
"Pequeño humano, recibimos a tu clase en nuestra isla con ramas abiertas, "
"prometes nunca poner un dedo en nuestros preciosos bosques, y unas pocas "
"generaciones después olvidas todo eso y comienzas a talar nuestros hogares "
"con tus hachas malditas. ¡Por el Primero, no permitiré que permanezcas más "
"en nuestra isla!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:926
msgid ""
"*By the First... Funny, I remember hearing the fairy Violindë saying exactly "
"the same thing...* Noble woses, I fear you are accusing my kind of too great "
"a crime. It's true that humans cut some trees, but we do that to build our "
"homes and lit bonfires to take shelter from the cold and the wild beasts, "
"not for cruelty. It's not unlike a wolf that eats a hare in order to "
"survive; unless the humans don't exceed themselves in cutting the trees, "
"it's part of the cycle of life..."
msgstr ""
"*Por el Primero... Qué curioso, recuerdo haber oído a la hada Violindë decir "
"exactamente lo mismo...* Nobles woses, me temo que están acusando a mi gente "
"de un crimen demasiado grande. Es cierto que los humanos cortamos algunos "
"árboles, pero lo hacemos para construir nuestros hogares y encender fogatas "
"para refugiarnos del frío y de las bestias salvajes, no por crueldad. No es "
"diferente a un lobo que come una liebre para sobrevivir; siempre y cuando "
"los humanos no se excedan cortando árboles, es parte del ciclo de la vida..."

#. [message], speaker=Blude
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:930
msgid "SILENCE!!! I will bear the sight of treacherous human no longer!!!"
msgstr "¡SILENCIO!!! ¡No soportaré más la vista de un humano traicionero!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:934
msgid ""
"Killing an entire species is nothing more than a cruel genocide that goes "
"against the balance of nature, Elder Wose. You disappoint the spirits of "
"Irdya with such violence, but that's only because you've been taken by your "
"anger; worry not, for I shall chase away your darkness..."
msgstr ""
"Matar a una especie entera no es más que un cruel genocidio que va en contra "
"del equilibrio de la naturaleza, Anciano Wose. Desilusionas a los espíritus "
"de Irdya con tal violencia, pero eso es solo porque te has dejado llevar por "
"tu ira; no te preocupes, porque expulsaré la oscuridad de tu alma..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:938
msgid ""
"Saying that, Akhen laid the Trident of the Seas by his side, and boldly "
"walked closer to the towering wose, whose branches and roots crackled "
"menacingly, but strangely not hitting the young human, who touched the noble "
"creature between his eyes and where should be his chest. Then, to everyone's "
"astonishment, Akhen's eyes shone like aquamarine stars, and light flowed "
"from his hand into the wose, whose bellow echoed in the entire valley... And "
"then, as suddenly as it had begun, it was over."
msgstr ""
"Diciendo eso, Akhen dejó el Tridente de los Mares a su lado y caminó "
"audazmente más cerca del imponente wose, cuyas ramas y raíces crujían "
"amenazadoramente, pero curiosamente sin golpear al joven humano, quien tocó "
"a la noble criatura entre sus ojos y donde debería estar su pecho. Entonces, "
"para asombro de todos, los ojos de Akhen brillaron como estrellas de "
"aguamarina y la luz fluyó de su mano hacia el wose, cuyo rugido resonó en "
"todo el valle... Y luego, tan repentinamente como había comenzado, todo "
"terminó."

#. [message], speaker=Blude
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:948
msgid ""
"(blinking) What... Where... Why am I... (seems shocked) No, I... What was I "
"trying to accomplish...?"
msgstr ""
"(parpadeando) ¿Qué... Dónde... Por qué estoy...? (parece impactado) No, "
"yo... ¿Qué estaba intentando lograr...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:952
msgid ""
"(exhausted) Your hatred, born from your resentment towards humans, had "
"corrupted your soul; it may happen to every sensitive being, even the best "
"ones... But I have purged the greatest darkness out of your soul. Still, "
"your ability to hate remains inside you, and so it's up to you to prevent it "
"from corrupting your heart ever again."
msgstr ""
"(agotado) Tu odio, nacido de tu resentimiento hacia los humanos, había "
"corrompido tu alma; eso puede pasarle a todo ser sensible, incluso a los "
"mejores... Pero he purgado la mayor oscuridad de tu alma. Aun así, tu "
"capacidad de odiar permanece dentro de ti, y por eso depende de ti evitar "
"que corrompa tu corazón otra vez."

#. [message], speaker=Blude
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:956
msgid ""
"You... In all my long life, never had I thought that I'd ever meet an animal "
"being with such sensibility and such connection to the heart of nature "
"itself... I thank you for saving me, young one; you have my word that I "
"shall not allow myself to be corrupted again. Furthermore, I'll make sure "
"that my kind never takes the offensive on yours ever again, and even help "
"rebuild this town."
msgstr ""
"Tú... En toda mi larga vida, nunca pensé que conocería a un ser animal con "
"tanta sensibilidad y una conexión tan profunda con el corazón de la "
"naturaleza misma... Te agradezco por salvarme, joven; tienes mi palabra de "
"que no permitiré que me corrompa de nuevo. Además, me aseguraré de que mi "
"gente nunca vuelva a tomar la ofensiva contra la tuya, e incluso ayudaré a "
"reconstruir esta ciudad."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:960
msgid "Thank you, Elder Wose... (falls down)"
msgstr "Gracias, Anciano Wose... (cae)"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:964
msgid "AKHEN!"
msgstr "¡AKHEN!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:981
msgid ""
"Damn you, boy, stop pushing yourself so hard and worrying Nyx like this!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldito seas, muchacho, deja de esforzarte tanto y de preocupar a Nyx de "
"esta forma!"

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:985
msgid ""
"(astonished) Impressive... I've wandered both the Green Isle and Arajunna, "
"and even learned some magic from the wisest Chomi priests, but never have I "
"seen such prodigies being performed before my eyes…! Tell me, friend, where "
"do you come from, and how did you know the way to stop the woses? Are you "
"gifted in prophecy and clairvoyance?"
msgstr ""
"(asombrado) Impresionante... He vagado tanto por la Isla Verde como por "
"Arajunna, e incluso aprendí algo de magia de los sacerdotes chomi más "
"sabios, pero nunca había visto tales prodigios realizarse ante mis ojos… "
"¡Dime, amigo, de dónde vienes y cómo supiste la forma de detener a los "
"woses? ¿Estás dotado de profecía y clarividencia?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:989
msgid ""
"No, I'm simply a mage from the city of Maat'Kare, far to the west... I can "
"explain everything to you, but now, if that's not asking too much, I'd "
"really appreciate a bed and some food and drinking; I haven't eaten or "
"rested since the shipwreck..."
msgstr ""
"No, simplemente soy un mago de la ciudad de Maat'Kare, muy al oeste... Puedo "
"explicártelo todo, pero ahora, si no es pedir demasiado, realmente "
"agradecería una cama, algo de comida y bebida; no he comido ni descansado "
"desde el naufragio..."

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:993
msgid ""
"And I shall provide everything that you ask - after all, that's the least we "
"can do for our saviour!"
msgstr ""
"Y yo te proporcionaré todo lo que pidas, ¡después de todo, es lo menos que "
"podemos hacer por nuestro salvador!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:997
msgid ""
"'And thus the valiant, virile hero had his first victory / On the foreign "
"soil of fair Flora's Island / To the wose threat an end he put, for the "
"people and his belle so pale...'"
msgstr ""
"«Y así el valiente y viril héroe tuvo su primera victoria / En suelo "
"extranjero de la bella Isla de Flora / Al peligro de los woses puso fin, por "
"el pueblo y por su pálida bella...»"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1001
msgid "(blushing) Stop it, Branwyn..."
msgstr "(sonrojándose) Basta, Branwyn..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1005
msgid "(smiling) ..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) ..."

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1024
msgid "I die... Please, protect my villagers from these monsters..."
msgstr "Muero... Por favor, protejan a mis aldeanos de estos monstruos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1028
msgid "That's bad! He would have been an invaluable ally for us!"
msgstr "¡Eso es malo! ¡Él habría sido un aliado invaluable para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1042
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:540
msgid "I can't fall now, there's still so many songs to learn...!"
msgstr "¡No puedo caer ahora, todavía hay tantas canciones por aprender...!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1046
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:544
msgid "No! How could we have let her die?"
msgstr "¡No! ¿Cómo pudimos dejarla morir?"

#. [message], speaker=Blude
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1065
msgid ""
"I may have fallen, but my offspring shall fight on without me, and they "
"shall not rest until our island is pure again!"
msgstr ""
"Puede que haya caído, pero mi descendencia luchará sin mí y no descansará "
"hasta que nuestra isla esté pura otra vez."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1069
msgid ""
"No! I could have purified him and all of his offspring, but now who knows "
"how many more corrupted woses we'll have to fight!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! Podría haberlo purificado a él y a toda su descendencia, ¡pero ahora "
"quién sabe cuántos woses corrompidos más tendremos que enfrentar!"

#. [message], speaker=Blude
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1080
msgid ""
"You pesky humans, you won't even have the decency of dying without fighting "
"back, then? Let it not be a problem, I shall summon my offspring all over "
"the Green Isle to crush you once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Humanos molestos, ¿ni siquiera tendrán la decencia de morir sin pelear? Que "
"no sea problema, ¡invocaré a toda mi descendencia por toda la Isla Verde "
"para aplastarlos de una vez por todas!"

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/17_Flora_Island.cfg:1084
msgid ""
"This is hopeless! We cannot fight all of the Green Isle's woses... we're "
"doomed!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es desesperado! No podemos luchar contra todos los woses de la Isla "
"Verde... ¡estamos condenados!"

#. [scenario], id=18_Rekindled_Fire
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:4
msgid "Rekindled Fire"
msgstr "Fuego Reavivado"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:22
msgid "Investigate what's happening at Forstsea"
msgstr "Investiga qué está pasando en Forstsea"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:38
msgid ""
"In this scenario, Akhen may recruit Aeserians. Also, he may recruit at the "
"hexes adjacent to 3,22"
msgstr ""
"En este escenario, Akhen puede reclutar aeserianos. Además, puede reclutar "
"en los hexágonos adyacentes a 3,22"

#. [side], type=Huntsman_Peasant
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:69
msgid "Llyr"
msgstr "Llyr"

#. [side], type=Huntsman_Peasant
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:74
msgid "Forstsea"
msgstr "Forstsea"

#. [side], type=Drake Flameheart
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:89
msgid "Grelnit"
msgstr "Grelnit"

#. [side], type=Drake Flameheart
#. [side], type=Armageddon Drake
#. [side], type=Drake Enforcer
#. [side], type=Fire Dragon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:94
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:95
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:145
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:167
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:109
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:135
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:217
msgid "Morogor"
msgstr "Morogor"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:224
msgid ""
"So, tell me more about these creatures: are they truly so terrible that not "
"even your cool tricks can easily take them down?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, cuéntame más sobre estas criaturas: ¿realmente son tan terribles "
"que ni siquiera tus trucos geniales pueden derrotarlas fácilmente?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:228
msgid ""
"Ages ago, there were two women whose power far exceeded my own; one of them "
"could actually control the weather and the seas at will. Still, they were "
"unable to completely defeat the creatures I'm talking about. However, they "
"might not be coming in great numbers, so we may at least be able to stop a "
"first wave, specially if our friends are really around here..."
msgstr ""
"Hace mucho tiempo hubo dos mujeres cuyo poder superaba con creces el mío; "
"una de ellas podía controlar el clima y los mares a voluntad. Aun así, no "
"lograron derrotar por completo a las criaturas de las que hablo. Sin "
"embargo, es posible que no vengan en grandes números, así que al menos "
"podremos detener una primera oleada, especialmente si nuestros amigos "
"realmente están por aquí..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:232
msgid ""
"Let's make haste then, and meet your mates at once! If we follow this road, "
"we'll quickly reach the shores where your razor creature saw them; on the "
"way, we may even find the folks of the town of Forstsea, where I was born, "
"they'd certainly help us."
msgstr ""
"Entonces apurémonos y encontremos a tus compañeros de una vez. Si seguimos "
"este camino, llegaremos rápido a las costas donde tu criatura afilada los "
"vio; en el camino, quizás incluso encontremos a la gente de la ciudad de "
"Forstsea, donde nací, y seguro que nos ayudarán."

#. [unit], id=Bashed Peasant, type=Trapper_Peasant
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:259
msgid "Bashed Peasant"
msgstr "Campesino Golpeado"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:266
msgid "Look, there goes a... Wait... What..."
msgstr "Miren, ahí va un... Esperen... ¿Qué...?"

#. [message], speaker=Bashed Peasant
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:270
msgid ""
"(gasping) You... Don't... go... east... monsters... burning... devouring..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Ustedes... No... vayan... al este... monstruos... quemando... "
"devorando..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:274
msgid "Hold on there, friend, I'm going to heal you!"
msgstr "¡Aguanta, amigo, voy a sanarte!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:284
msgid "It's no good, Akhen, his heartbeats have stopped..."
msgstr "No sirve de nada, Akhen, sus latidos se detuvieron..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:288
msgid "Damn... Hurry, folks, situation is getting critical already!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición... Apúrense, muchahos, la situación ya se está poniendo crítica!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:332
msgid "(frightened) W-what are t-those things...?"
msgstr "(asustada) ¿Q-qué son e-esas cosas...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:336
msgid "Those are drakes: the bane of my people's ancestors."
msgstr "Esos son dracos: la perdición de los ancestros de mi pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:340
msgid ""
"AKHEN! And you too, Nyx... By the Gods of Light, look, Mahyus, it's really "
"them!"
msgstr ""
"¡AKHEN! Y tú también, Nyx... Por los Dioses de la Luz, miren, Mahyus, "
"¡realmente son ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:344
msgid ""
"That's really great! I'd go there myself and give you a pat on the shoulder, "
"but busy as I am right now..."
msgstr ""
"¡Eso es genial! Yo mismo iría allí a darte una palmada en el hombro, pero "
"estoy ocupado en este momento..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:348
msgid ""
"Stand strong, guys, we're coming to your aid! And you, Branwyn, you should "
"stay back, these drakes are way worse than anything you must have already "
"fought against."
msgstr ""
"Resistan con fuerza, muchachos, ¡vamos en su ayuda! Y tú, Branwyn, deberías "
"quedarte atrás, estos dracos son mucho peores que cualquier cosa contra la "
"que hayas luchado antes."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:352
msgid ""
"No... No, I won't just take cover while my people are attacked, not when "
"even you foreigners are fighting for them! I may be a bard, but I know how "
"to fight too!"
msgstr ""
"No... No, no me voy a quedar escondida mientras atacan a mi gente, ¡no "
"cuando hasta ustedes extranjeros están luchando por ellos! Puede que sea una "
"barda, pero también sé pelear."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:361
msgid "Defeat the Drake Vanguard"
msgstr "Derrota a la Vanguardia Draco"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:385
msgid "Death of Llyr"
msgstr "Muerte de Llyr"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:409
msgid ""
"(despairing) Damn... Why... can't... I... hit... these... damn... monsters?!"
msgstr ""
"(desesperada) Maldición... ¿Por qué... no puedo... golpear... a estos... "
"malditos... monstruos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Branwyn, calm down and aim for their head or their wings! If you hit their "
"flanks, their scales will render your blows harmless!"
msgstr ""
"Branwyn, cálmate y apunta a su cabeza o a sus alas. Si les golpeas los "
"costados, sus escamas harán que tus golpes sean inofensivos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:431
msgid ""
"Curse them! I never thought I'd ever face an enemy against whom my Supreme "
"Spells would be so ineffective... Only my arcane beams seem to damage them, "
"but it's not that strong..."
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos sean! Nunca pensé que enfrentaría a un enemigo contra el que mis "
"Hechizos Supremos serían tan ineficaces... Solo mis rayos arcanos parecen "
"dañarlos, pero no son tan fuertes..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:435
msgid ""
"On the other hand, they fall like rotten fruits before my Nefthys Hepet... "
"Seems like they're extremely vulnerable to cold."
msgstr ""
"En cambio, caen como frutas podridas ante mi Nefthys Hepet... Parece que son "
"extremadamente vulnerables al frío."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:439
msgid ""
"Then you shall lead the attack, Mahyus; I'll stay behind summoning "
"elementals, I've finally got full control over them!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces tú liderarás el ataque, Mahyus; yo me quedaré atrás invocando "
"elementales, ¡finalmente tengo control total sobre ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Grelnit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:451
msgid ""
"Argh, these puny apes seem stronger than we thought... But no matter how "
"strong you are, you can't hope to defeat Lord Vitras..."
msgstr ""
"Argh, estos monos insignificantes parecen más fuertes de lo que "
"pensábamos... Pero no importa cuán fuertes sean, no pueden esperar derrotar "
"al señor Vitras..."

#. [message], speaker=Llyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:463
msgid "What did he mean? Is there more of them coming to attack us?"
msgstr "¿Qué quiso decir? ¿Vienen más de ellos a atacarnos?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:467
msgid ""
"Seems so; the drakes of Morogor are preparing to conquer this island, as "
"they did with our ancestors' homelands..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que sí; los dracos de Morogor se están preparando para conquistar "
"esta isla, como hicieron con las tierras natales de nuestros ancestros..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:471
msgid ""
"That's pessim; even our ancestors, with Myra, Maat and King Abhai on their "
"side, could not stop them when they attacked with all their might. Who "
"knows, we might even have to evacuate this island..."
msgstr ""
"Eso es pesimismo; ni siquiera nuestros ancestros, con Myra, Maat y el rey "
"Abhai de su lado, pudieron detenerlos cuando atacaron con toda su fuerza. "
"Quién sabe, quizá hasta tengamos que evacuar esta isla..."

#. [message], speaker=Llyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:475
msgid ""
"What, leave the land where we've been living for so long? Is there really no "
"other way to avoid certain death?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué, abandonar la tierra donde hemos vivido por tanto tiempo? ¿Realmente no "
"hay otra forma de evitar una muerte segura?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:479
msgid ""
"Don't worry, we shall help you with whatever strength and knowledge on the "
"enemy that we have. However, we’ll need the aid of all Aeserians on this "
"island, and probably the Chomi as well, if they choose to fight for this "
"island too. I've talked to Elder Afallon already, and he must be sending "
"messages to other towns as we speak."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, los ayudaremos con toda la fuerza y el conocimiento sobre "
"el enemigo que tenemos. Sin embargo, necesitaremos la ayuda de todas las "
"aeserianas de esta isla, y probablemente también de los chomi, si deciden "
"luchar por esta isla. Ya hablé con el anciano Afallon, y debe estar enviando "
"mensajes a otras ciudades mientras hablamos."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:483
msgid ""
"Eh, it's quite ironic that we came here seeking aid for our war, and we're "
"about to help others instead."
msgstr ""
"Eh, es bastante irónico que hayamos venido aquí buscando ayuda para nuestra "
"guerra y ahora estemos a punto de ayudar a otros en su lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:487
msgid ""
"(in private) To be honest, since Afallon told me Rockvale is one of the "
"Aeserians' biggest and strongest towns, I’m doubtful about the worth of "
"their aid in a war against Skironians, Motsoghnir and Maat'Kare. These "
"Chomi, on the other hand, might be good allies, and they may be convinced to "
"aid us if we aid them and their friends first."
msgstr ""
"(en privado) Para ser honesto, como Afallon me dijo que Rockvale es una de "
"las ciudades más grandes y fuertes de las aeserianas, dudo del valor de su "
"ayuda en una guerra contra skironianos, motsoghnir y maat'karianos. Estos "
"chomi, en cambio, podrían ser buenos aliados, y quizás se convenzan de "
"ayudarnos si primero los ayudamos a ellos y a sus amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:491
msgid ""
"Branwyn, it's good that you're well. Don't worry about today's battle, you "
"couldn't have possibly been prepared to fight such a strong and unknown foe."
msgstr ""
"Branwyn, qué bueno que estés bien. No te preocupes por la batalla de hoy, no "
"podías estar preparada para enfrentar a un enemigo tan fuerte y desconocido."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:495
msgid ""
"Right... *I know we Aeserians aren't great thing next to the Chomi and to "
"you, but you don't need to disregard us so much either...*"
msgstr ""
"Correcto... *Sé que nosotras las aeserianas no somos gran cosa al lado de "
"los chomi y de ustedes, pero tampoco necesitan despreciarnos tanto...*"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:499
msgid "And you, friends... I'm so glad to see you alive and well..."
msgstr "Y ustedes, amigos... Me alegra tanto verlos vivos y bien..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:503
msgid ""
"As we are. The Gods know how worried we were when we lost sight of you and "
"Nyx; never thought I'd say that, but blessed be Mahyus' undead minions, they "
"were the ones who saved us, since they could neither get tired nor drown..."
msgstr ""
"Como nosotros. Los Dioses saben lo preocupados que estábamos cuando los "
"perdimos de vista a ti y a Nyx; nunca pensé que diría esto, pero benditos "
"sean los minions no-muertos de Mahyus, fueron ellos quienes nos salvaron, ya "
"que ni se cansaban ni se ahogaban..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:507
msgid ""
"Now, to business. We must send more razorbirds to watch out for more drake "
"attacks, and then meet the leaders of the Aeserians and of the Chomi in a "
"council to tell them all that we know about the drakes, and help them "
"counter their attack. Luckily, we may stop them by killing this Lord Vitras, "
"who seems to be the one leading their invasion; but we must also have plans "
"for the worst-case scenario..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, al grano. Debemos enviar más pájaros navaja para vigilar posibles "
"ataques de dracos, y luego reunirnos con los líderes de las aeserianas y de "
"los chomi en un consejo para contarles todo lo que sabemos sobre los dracos "
"y ayudarlos a contrarrestar su ataque. Por suerte, podemos detenerlos "
"matando a este señor Vitras, que parece ser quien lidera su invasión; pero "
"también debemos tener planes para el peor escenario..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:526
msgid ""
"No! With Forstsea's Elder dead, it won't be able to stand the drakes' attack!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! Con el anciano de Forstsea muerto, ¡no podrá resistir el ataque de los "
"dracos!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/18_Rekindled_Fire.cfg:555
msgid ""
"We should have vanquished this vanguard sooner, now the main army is coming! "
"We're doomed!"
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos haber derrotado antes a esta vanguardia, ¡ahora viene el ejército "
"principal! ¡Estamos condenados!"

#. [scenario], id=19_Stone_Of_Destiny
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:4
msgid "Stone of Destiny"
msgstr "Piedra del Destino"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:22
msgid "Defeat Garlin Ohn"
msgstr "Derrota a Garlin Ohn"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:46
msgid "Death of Owain"
msgstr "Muerte de Owain"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:50
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:512
msgid "Death of Adapa"
msgstr "Muerte de Adapa"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:54
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:52
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:434
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:516
msgid "In this scenario, Akhen may recruit Aeserians."
msgstr "En este escenario, Akhen puede reclutar aeserianos."

#. [side], type=Armageddon Drake
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:90
msgid "Garlin Ohn"
msgstr "Garlin Ohn"

#. [side], type=Highwayman_Peasant
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:110
msgid "Owain"
msgstr "Owain"

#. [side], type=Highwayman_Peasant
#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:115
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:170
msgid "Aeserians"
msgstr "Aeserianas"

#. [side], type=Chomi Ranger
#. [unit], id=Adapa, type=Chomi Ranger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:125
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:457
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/characters.cfg:499
msgid "Adapa"
msgstr "Adapa"

#. [side], type=Chomi Ranger
#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:130
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:193
msgid "Green Isle Chomi"
msgstr "Chomi de la Isla Verde"

#. [side], type=Drake Flameheart
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:140
msgid "Gravlan"
msgstr "Gravlan"

#. [side], type=Drake Enforcer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:162
msgid "Verlinn"
msgstr "Verlinn"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Stay still and behold, friends, the Stone of Destiny with its unreachable "
"pinnacles! Here is the place where, in the past, countless heroes perished, "
"attempting to get to its highest peak and, as our tradition promises, be "
"given power over all of the Green Isle!"
msgstr ""
"Quédense quietos y contemplen, amigos, ¡la Piedra del Destino con sus "
"cumbres inalcanzables! Aquí es donde, en el pasado, innumerables héroes "
"perecieron intentando llegar a su cima más alta y, como promete nuestra "
"tradición, recibir el poder sobre toda la Isla Verde."

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:218
msgid ""
"You didn't exaggerate at all when you described these monsters' power, Seer; "
"the Aeserians and us have made this mountain into a fortress far stronger "
"than even that of the Washraha, and still we're barely managing to halt the "
"enemy advance!"
msgstr ""
"No exageraste en absoluto cuando describiste el poder de estos monstruos, "
"Vidente; nosotras las aeserianas y nosotros hemos convertido esta montaña en "
"una fortaleza mucho más fuerte incluso que la de los Washraha, y aun así "
"apenas logramos detener el avance del enemigo."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:222
msgid ""
"I'll ask you later about these Washraha, but now we must hurry to Owain's "
"aid and repel the drakes!"
msgstr ""
"Te preguntaré después sobre esos Washraha, pero ahora debemos apresurarnos a "
"ayudar a Owain y repeler a los dracos."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:244
msgid ""
"Don't get too close to me, bard girl, my body is taken by a dark energy that "
"may seriously damage you who are not used to it..."
msgstr ""
"No te acerques demasiado a mí, chica barda, mi cuerpo está impregnado de una "
"energía oscura que podría dañarte seriamente a ti que no estás acostumbrada "
"a ella..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:248
msgid ""
"Please, call me Branwyn, and don't worry, I'm not afraid of your power; in "
"fact, I enjoy darkness."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, llámame Branwyn, y no te preocupes, no le tengo miedo a tu poder; "
"de hecho, disfruto de la oscuridad."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Is that so? Most humans would cower in fear before the powers of the dark..."
msgstr ""
"¿En serio? La mayoría de los humanos se encogerían de miedo ante los poderes "
"de la oscuridad..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Well, I don't. Darkness can be a gentle companion, immersing us in soothing "
"loneliness and shielding us in its black veil; on the other hand, the "
"scorching and blinding light may bare us to the world, making us more "
"vulnerable. It's true that it can also be an enemy; but in your hands, I "
"know it's used for good."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, yo no. La oscuridad puede ser una compañera gentil, sumergiéndonos en "
"una soledad reconfortante y protegiéndonos con su velo negro; en cambio, la "
"luz abrasadora y cegadora puede exponernos al mundo, volviéndonos más "
"vulnerables. Es cierto que también puede ser un enemigo; pero en tus manos "
"sé que se usa para el bien."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:260
msgid "And how can you be sure of that?"
msgstr "¿Y cómo puedes estar segura de eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:264
msgid ""
"You fight for your friends, and are now fighting for my people, even though "
"you barely know them. Besides, you've saved my town, Forstsea, and for this "
"I wish to thank you from the bottom of my heart."
msgstr ""
"Luchas por tus amigos y ahora estás luchando por mi gente, aunque apenas los "
"conoces. Además, salvaste mi ciudad, Forstsea, y por eso quiero agradecerte "
"desde el fondo de mi corazón."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:268
msgid ""
"Well, I've got to admit that I've never seen darkness so... poetically. And "
"no need to thank me, I mean, it's only natural that I help those who are "
"being attacked without reason, right?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, tengo que admitir que nunca había visto la oscuridad de forma tan... "
"poética. Y no hace falta que me agradezcas, quiero decir, es natural que "
"ayude a quienes son atacados sin razón, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:272
msgid ""
"There is nothing banal about risking life and limb for those who are in "
"desperate need. 'Tis the stuff heroes of legend are made of."
msgstr ""
"No hay nada banal en arriesgar la vida y el cuerpo por quienes están en "
"necesidad desesperada. Eso es de lo que están hechos los héroes de leyenda."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:280
msgid "(whisper) I think she's taken a liking for our darkly friend..."
msgstr "(susurro) Creo que le ha tomado cariño a nuestro amigo oscuro..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:284
msgid "(whisper) I'm certain of that, though."
msgstr "(susurro) Estoy seguro de eso."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:288
msgid "(whisper) Why?"
msgstr "(susurro) ¿Por qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:292
msgid ""
"(whisper) The way she addresses him. She speaks in a much more natural, "
"intimate tone... just as you do when speaking to me. You only refer to "
"yourself in first person when you're talking to me."
msgstr ""
"(susurro) La forma en que se dirige a él. Habla en un tono mucho más natural "
"e íntimo... justo como tú lo haces cuando hablas conmigo. Solo te refieres a "
"ti misma en primera persona cuando hablas conmigo."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:296
msgid ""
"(blushing, if that's even possible) The impudence on this human boy! Nyx "
"shall be more mindful of her speech from now on, lest he thinks he has any "
"hold over her heart!"
msgstr ""
"(sonrojándose, si eso es posible) ¡La insolencia de este muchacho humano! "
"Nyx será más cuidadosa con su forma de hablar de ahora en adelante, ¡no sea "
"que piense que tiene algún control sobre su corazón!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:303
msgid "*Which he does... Gods of Night does he do...*"
msgstr "*Lo cual tiene... Por los Dioses de la Noche, sí que lo tiene...*"

#. [message], speaker=Owain
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:318
msgid ""
"By the Gods of Light, the rumours I heard about these foreigners' power was "
"no exaggeration... Even our Chomi allies are having a hard time dealing with "
"those fire-breathing bastards, and yet they're falling in the dozens before "
"the Seer's people - and especially before that darkly one!"
msgstr ""
"Por los Dioses de la Luz, los rumores que escuché sobre el poder de estos "
"extranjeros no eran exagerados... Incluso nuestros aliados chomi tienen "
"dificultades para lidiar con esos bastardos que escupen fuego, ¡y sin "
"embargo caen por docenas ante la gente del Vidente, y especialmente ante ese "
"tipo oscuro!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:322
msgid ""
"Indeed, his cold-based Umbra spells are a bane to the drakes! Keep going "
"like this, Mahyus; my elementals and the soldiers shall guard you from their "
"claws and blades!"
msgstr ""
"Así es, ¡sus hechizos de Umbra basados en el frío son la perdición de los "
"dracos! Sigue así, Mahyus; mis elementales y los soldados te protegerán de "
"sus garras y espadas."

#. [message], speaker=Garlin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:326
msgid ""
"These pesky humans... It was said that their most dangerous mages had been "
"wiped out during Shek'har's reign, but they still seem to have some tricks "
"up their sleeve! I must think of a trick of my own, then..."
msgstr ""
"Estos molestos humanos... Se decía que sus magos más peligrosos habían sido "
"eliminados durante el reinado de Shek'har, ¡pero todavía parecen tener "
"algunos trucos bajo la manga! Entonces tendré que pensar en un truco "
"propio..."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:343
msgid ""
"Lord Garlin Ohn has fallen! Drakes, we must withdraw and regroup, there's no "
"possibility of victory for us today!"
msgstr ""
"¡El señor Garlin Ohn ha caído! Dracos, debemos retirarnos y reagruparnos, "
"¡hoy no hay posibilidad de victoria para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Garlin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:353
msgid ""
"How shameful to fall like this to these lowly, hairless apes! However..."
msgstr ""
"Qué vergonzoso caer así ante estos monos pelados y viles. Sin embargo..."

#. [unit], id=Murr, type=Hurricane Drake
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:367
msgid "Murr"
msgstr "Murr"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:380
msgid "What..."
msgstr "Qué…"

#. [message], speaker=Garlin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:384
msgid "...I'll make sure that you remember me after my death..."
msgstr "...me aseguraré de que me recuerden después de mi muerte..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:392
msgid "Branwyn!!!"
msgstr "¡Branwyn!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:396
msgid "Mahy-"
msgstr "Mahy-"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:416
msgid ""
"Damn it, how could we let them snatch her from right under our nose?! We "
"have to-"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, cómo pudimos dejar que se la llevaran justo bajo nuestras "
"narices! Tenemos que-"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:420
msgid ""
"Wait, Mahyus, do not go after that drake now, it'll only lure you to their "
"base! Branwyn has been but abducted, we may still save her!"
msgstr ""
"Espera, Mahyus, no vayas tras ese draco ahora, solo te atraerá a su base. "
"Branwyn solo ha sido secuestrada, ¡todavía podemos salvarla!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:424
msgid ""
"But not by sitting here idly! We must hurry before anything bad happens to "
"her!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero no quedándonos aquí sin hacer nada! ¡Debemos apurarnos antes de que le "
"pase algo malo!"

#. [message], speaker=Owain
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:428
msgid ""
"Darkly one, rest assured that, when you go rescue Branwyn, we Aeserians "
"shall help you; she is one of us, after all."
msgstr ""
"Amigo oscuro, ten por seguro que cuando vayas a rescatar a Branwyn, nosotras "
"las aeserianas te ayudaremos; después de todo, ella es una de nosotras."

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Now that we've secured our main fortress and halted their momentum, we must "
"counter-attack, enjoying that their morale must be low after their recent "
"defeats and corner them."
msgstr ""
"Ahora que hemos asegurado nuestra fortaleza principal y detenido su impulso, "
"debemos contraatacar, aprovechando que su moral debe estar baja después de "
"sus recientes derrotas y acorralarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:436
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, I don't think that they be truly cornered; not when they can "
"fly across the ocean whenever they feel like it..."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, no creo que estén realmente acorralados; no cuando pueden volar "
"a través del océano cuando quieran..."

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:440
msgid ""
"They're not the only ones who can move across the seas. When we attack their "
"main base, we Chomi will use all of our Green Isle fleet to surround the "
"drakes completely, preventing any of them from escaping. If we manage to "
"kill all of them, their kin back at their own home may feel discouraged to "
"further advance in their campaign."
msgstr ""
"No son los únicos que pueden moverse por los mares. Cuando ataquemos su base "
"principal, nosotros los chomi usaremos toda nuestra flota de la Isla Verde "
"para rodear completamente a los dracos, impidiendo que ninguno escape. Si "
"logramos matarlos a todos, sus parientes en su tierra natal quizás se "
"desanimen de seguir avanzando en su campaña."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:444
msgid ""
"I see... Well, this is a plan we must share with the other leaders; I'll "
"send razorbirds to summon them to Rockvale, and there we shall decide our "
"next course of action."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo... Bueno, este es un plan que debemos compartir con los otros "
"líderes; enviaré pájaros navaja para convocarlos a Rockvale, y allí "
"decidiremos nuestro próximo curso de acción."

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:465
msgid ""
"No! Without Owain to command the defence of the Stone, it'll inevitably fall "
"to the lizards!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin Owain para comandar la defensa de la Piedra, inevitablemente caerá "
"ante los lagartos!"

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:479
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:1007
msgid "How can I die like this...?!"
msgstr "¡¿Cómo puedo morir así...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Owain
#. [message], speaker=Affalon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:483
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:1011
msgid ""
"That's a disaster! Without the Chomi, we'll be too outnumbered to possibly "
"prevail!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eso es un desastre! ¡Sin los chomi, estaremos demasiado superados en número "
"para poder prevalecer!"

#. [message], speaker=Garlin
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Seems like these humans are actually stronger than I thought... It will make "
"no difference, though: bring in reinforcements!"
msgstr ""
"Parece que estos humanos son en realidad más fuertes de lo que pensaba... "
"Aunque eso no hará ninguna diferencia: ¡traigan refuerzos!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/19_Stone_Of_Destiny.cfg:498
msgid "Oh, damn it! There is no way we can defeat them now!"
msgstr "¡Oh, maldición! ¡Ahora no hay forma de que podamos derrotarlos!"

#. [scenario], id=20_Ancient_Fire
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:4
msgid "Ancient Fire"
msgstr "Fuego Ancestral"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:24
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:410
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:488
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:659
msgid "Defeat the Army of Morogor"
msgstr "Derrota al Ejército de Morogor"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:28
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:65
msgid "Rescue Branwyn"
msgstr "Rescata a Branwyn"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:48
msgid "Death of Lord Vitras before Branwyn's rescue"
msgstr "Muerte del señor Vitras antes de rescatar a Branwyn"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:69
msgid "Sighting of Mahyus"
msgstr "Avistamiento de Mahyus"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:73
msgid ""
"In order not to be seen, you must neither attack nor be attacked, and also "
"refrain from recruiting/recalling"
msgstr ""
"Para no ser visto, no debes atacar ni ser atacado, y también debes "
"abstenerte de reclutar o reincorporar"

#. [side], type=Fire Dragon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:104
msgid "Lord Vitras"
msgstr "Señor Vitras"

#. [side], type=Armageddon Drake
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:130
msgid "Veralon"
msgstr "Veralon"

#. [side], type=Armageddon Drake
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:212
msgid "Markinos"
msgstr "Markinos"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:276
msgid ""
"So much for stealth... Nyx really hates these lizards, as if their fire-"
"breathing wasn't harmful enough, she can't even smell them."
msgstr ""
"Adiós al sigilo... Nyx realmente odia a estos lagartos, como si escupir "
"fuego no fuera lo suficientemente dañino, ni siquiera puede olerlos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:280
msgid ""
"(sigh) Now we have no choice but to attack; I just hope that our allies "
"don't take much more time to reach this place as well..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Ahora no tenemos más opción que atacar; solo espero que nuestros "
"aliados no tarden mucho más en llegar también a este lugar..."

#. [message], speaker=Veralon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:284
msgid ""
"And so the sneaky little bastards have come... Lord Vitras, look, the humans "
"have come – and not the common ones, but the mages you wanted to meet!"
msgstr ""
"Y así vinieron los pequeños bastardos sigilosos... Señor Vitras, mira, han "
"venido los humanos, ¡y no los comunes, sino los magos que querías conocer!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:288
msgid ""
"(distant roar) Is that so? Interesting... in this case, I shall attend to "
"the battle myself..."
msgstr ""
"(rugido lejano) ¿Es así? Interesante... en ese caso, yo mismo atenderé la "
"batalla..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:303
msgid ""
"(frightened) By the Gods of Light, is <i>that</i> what our ancestors "
"fought...?!"
msgstr ""
"(asustada) ¡Por los Dioses de la Luz, ¿eso es lo que enfrentaron nuestros "
"ancestros...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:307
msgid ""
"I see... They look just like the rest of their kind, but I can feel their "
"magical power. That's quite nostalgic indeed; the last time I felt such "
"energy coming from a human was ages ago, when I was but an Inferno drake "
"fighting under Lord Shek'har the Great..."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo... Se ven igual que el resto de su especie, pero puedo sentir su "
"poder mágico. Eso es bastante nostálgico; la última vez que sentí esa "
"energía provenir de un humano fue hace mucho tiempo, cuando yo era solo un "
"draco Inferno luchando bajo el señor Shek'har el Grande..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:311
msgid ""
"I know who you're talking about, dragon; my people are aware of the Dragon "
"War of ancient times, as well as of how your people devastated much of the "
"Great Continent. Let me ask you then, why do you seek to conquer this island "
"if you already have such vast lands? Why won't you give other peoples the "
"right to live freely in their own land?"
msgstr ""
"Sé de quién hablas, dragón; mi pueblo conoce la Guerra de los Dragones de la "
"antigüedad, así como cómo tu gente devastó gran parte del Gran Continente. "
"Entonces déjame preguntarte, ¿por qué buscas conquistar esta isla si ya "
"tienes tierras tan vastas? ¿Por qué no les das a otros pueblos el derecho a "
"vivir libremente en su propia tierra?"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Your people may be aware of that war, but not of its aftermath. We did not "
"rule the Great Continent for long, boy, thanks to those fools, Shek'kahan "
"and Khrakrahs, who fought each other for the right to become the sovereign "
"of Dragons' Land! Divided and weakened by the battles in the east, we were "
"pushed back into the sea by the elves, and so we were limited to Morogor. "
"However, our island can no longer sustain our great population, and so we "
"must find new land for ourselves."
msgstr ""
"Tu pueblo puede estar al tanto de esa guerra, pero no de su secuela. No "
"gobernamos el Gran Continente por mucho tiempo, muchacho, gracias a esos "
"tontos, Shek'kahan y Khrakrahs, que lucharon entre sí por el derecho a "
"convertirse en el soberano de la Tierra de los Dragones. Divididos y "
"debilitados por las batallas en el este, fuimos empujados de vuelta al mar "
"por los elfos, y así quedamos limitados a Morogor. Sin embargo, nuestra isla "
"ya no puede sostener a nuestra gran población, por lo que debemos encontrar "
"nuevas tierras para nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:319
msgid ""
"But why do you have to take it from others? Why don't you try and coexist "
"peacefully with the humans of this island?"
msgstr ""
"Pero ¿por qué tienen que quitársela a otros? ¿Por qué no intentan coexistir "
"pacíficamente con los humanos de esta isla?"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:323
msgid ""
"Who can coexist peacefully with belligerent apes such as you? I know your "
"kind well, boy; you may think us tyrants, but we're no worse than you, or "
"the elves, or the dwarves, or any other intelligent race on this world!"
msgstr ""
"¿Quién puede coexistir pacíficamente con monos belicosos como ustedes? "
"Conozco bien a tu especie, muchacho; pueden pensar que somos tiranos, ¡pero "
"no somos peores que ustedes, o los elfos, o los enanos, o cualquier otra "
"raza inteligente en este mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Not everyone is like that, Vitras; the natives of this island have "
"peacefully accepted the presence of foreign humans here, and my own people "
"was given their current homeland by another race. Your mistake was believing "
"that the behaviour of a few gave you the right to regard all their ilk as "
"equals!"
msgstr ""
"No todos son así, Vitras; los nativos de esta isla han aceptado "
"pacíficamente la presencia de humanos extranjeros aquí, y a mi propio pueblo "
"le fue dada su tierra actual por otra raza. Tu error fue creer que el "
"comportamiento de unos pocos te daba el derecho a considerar a todos los de "
"su clase como iguales."

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:331
msgid ""
"(roaring) Who cares if we kill a few puny apes to take their land? It is the "
"law of nature that the strong wipe out the weak to grant their survival, boy!"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) ¿A quién le importa si matamos a unos cuantos monos "
"insignificantes para tomar su tierra? ¡Es la ley de la naturaleza que los "
"fuertes eliminen a los débiles para asegurar su supervivencia, muchacho!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:335
msgid ""
"It's also the law of nature that we must evolve, dragon, and by behaving as "
"mindless beasts that can only fight over land and food we remain the same as "
"we've always been. Now, if you crave battle so much, then we shall battle "
"for our own goals as warriors; this means that you don't need to keep that "
"human girl with you anymore."
msgstr ""
"También es ley de la naturaleza que debemos evolucionar, dragón, y "
"comportándonos como bestias sin mente que solo pueden pelear por tierra y "
"comida seguimos siendo los mismos de siempre. Ahora, si tanto anhelas la "
"batalla, entonces lucharemos por nuestros propios objetivos como guerreros; "
"eso significa que ya no necesitas mantener a esa chica humana contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:339
msgid ""
"Ah, you mean the red-haired singer... I disagree with you, boy, I do need "
"her in order to keep that dark mage of yours at bay. Besides, I have really "
"taken a liking for her skills; I think I will keep her as my pet..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, te refieres a la cantante pelirroja... Discrepo contigo, muchacho, sí la "
"necesito para mantener a raya a ese mago oscuro tuyo. Además, realmente me "
"han gustado sus habilidades; creo que la mantendré como mi mascota..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:343
msgid ""
"There's really no use arguing with him... Let's do it then, folks; we must "
"hold them off while our allies don't come, and also keep them busy while Nyx "
"sneaks through their camp and gets Branwyn. I fear that, if we win, Vitras "
"will get so angry that he'll kill her in revenge."
msgstr ""
"Realmente no sirve de nada discutir con él... Hagámoslo entonces, gente; "
"debemos contenerlos mientras no llegan nuestros aliados, y también "
"mantenerlos ocupados mientras Nyx se infiltra en su campamento y rescata a "
"Branwyn. Temo que, si ganamos, Vitras se enoje tanto que la mate por "
"venganza."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:347
msgid "Understood."
msgstr "Entendido."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:356
msgid ""
"*That's it, then; I must sneak into their camp without either summoning "
"undead nor attacking nor being attacked, or I else will be seen... And I "
"should wait until the drakes' forces are reduced... Oh yeah, this will be "
"hard...*"
msgstr ""
"*Eso es entonces; debo infiltrarme en su campamento sin invocar no-muertos, "
"sin atacar ni ser atacado, o de lo contrario me verán... Y debo esperar "
"hasta que las fuerzas de los dracos se reduzcan... Oh sí, esto será "
"difícil...*"

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:400
msgid ""
"Seems like I'm late... Sorry for that, we had some trouble fighting them on "
"Calwyn's Fields... Oh... (looks terrified) What on the wide green world is "
"that beast...?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que llego tarde... Lo siento por eso, tuvimos algunos problemas "
"luchando contra ellos en los Campos de Calwyn... Oh... (mira aterrorizado) "
"¿Qué demonios en este vasto mundo verde es esa bestia...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:404
msgid ""
"That, my friend, is a dragon. Worry not, though, they fall just like any "
"living being, as my ancestors' history can tell."
msgstr ""
"Eso, amigo mío, es un dragón. No te preocupes, caen igual que cualquier ser "
"vivo, como puede contar la historia de mis ancestros."

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:430
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:508
msgid "Death of Affalon"
msgstr "Muerte de Afallon"

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:482
msgid ""
"Damn it, because of those pesky drakes we were the last ones to arrive! Come "
"on, fighters, let's hurry before our friends finish the... (sees Vitras) So "
"that is their leader, uh? Well, he may be big, but he's only one, so I'm "
"sure that he'll fall as well if we just rain enough javelins on him."
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, por culpa de esos molestos dracos fuimos los últimos en llegar! "
"¡Vamos, guerreros, apurémonos antes de que nuestros amigos terminen con "
"el... (ve a Vitras) ¿Así que ese es su líder, eh? Bueno, puede ser grande, "
"pero es solo uno, así que estoy seguro de que también caerá si le llovemos "
"suficientes jabalinas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:541
msgid "Why is it so dark around here...?"
msgstr "¿Por qué está tan oscuro por aquí...?"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:545
msgid ""
"<span size='large'>Damn it, I forgot that my friends can recognize my "
"shadows!*</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span size='large'>¡Maldición, olvidé que mis amigos pueden reconocer mis "
"sombras!*</span>"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:549
msgid ""
"(casually) A pity Mahyus isn't here, I'm sure these drakes would provide "
"interesting undead for him..."
msgstr ""
"(con naturalidad) Lástima que Mahyus no esté aquí, estoy seguro de que estos "
"dracos le proporcionarían no-muertos interesantes..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:553
msgid "<span size='large'>...Thank you, friend...*</span>"
msgstr "<span size='large'>...Gracias, amigo...*</span>"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:583
msgid "Y-you...!"
msgstr "¡T-tú...!"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:587
msgid ""
"(astonished) You treacherous ape, how did you manage to sneak so deep into "
"my base?!"
msgstr ""
"(asombrado) ¡Mono traicionero, cómo lograste infiltrarte tan profundo en mi "
"base?!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:591
msgid ""
"The shadows are both my ally and part of my being, and so they hid me in "
"their veil. And please, don't call me treacherous, I don't want to hear that "
"from a dragon who relies on using weak, defenceless girls as safeguards..."
msgstr ""
"Las sombras son tanto mi aliada como parte de mi ser, y por eso me ocultaron "
"en su velo. Y por favor, no me llames traicionero, no quiero oír eso de un "
"dragón que depende de usar chicas débiles e indefensas como escudos..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:595
msgid "(slap!)"
msgstr "(¡bofetada!)"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:599
msgid "(shocked) Branwyn...? W-why did you do that?!"
msgstr "(impactado) ¿Branwyn...? ¿P-por qué hiciste eso?!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:603
msgid ""
"This was to show you that I'm no 'weak, defenceless girl', and for you to "
"never patronise me like this again, understand?"
msgstr ""
"Esto fue para mostrarte que no soy una «chica débil e indefensa», y para que "
"nunca más me trates con condescendencia de esta forma, ¿entendido?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:607
msgid ""
"(laughing) Friends, we no longer need to worry about Branwyn; now, charge "
"all at once, and let's rid the Green Isle of dragon tyranny!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Amigos, ya no necesitamos preocuparnos por Branwyn; ahora, ¡ataquen "
"todos a la vez y liberemos a la Isla Verde de la tiranía de los dragones!"

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:611
msgid ""
"Now is the time... Ibejis, sail forth and surround the enemy camp by sea, "
"and let no drake pass through you!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora es el momento... Ibejis, naveguen y rodeen el campamento enemigo por "
"mar, ¡y que ningún draco pase a través de ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:632
msgid ""
"(furious) Accursed apes, even after sixteen centuries you haven't learned "
"how to DIE!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) ¡Malditos simios, incluso después de dieciséis siglos todavía no "
"han aprendido a MORIR!"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:639
msgid "Drakes, you take care of the other apes; this one is mine...!"
msgstr "¡Dracos, encárguense de los otros monos; este es mío...!"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:679
msgid ""
"Mahyus may recruit anywhere inside the circle of fire. In this scenario, "
"Akhen may recruit Aeserians."
msgstr ""
"Mahyus puede reclutar en cualquier lugar dentro del círculo de fuego. En "
"este escenario, Akhen puede reclutar aeserianos."

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:701
msgid ""
"I can't believe it... I, Vitras, the last Dragon Lord of Morogor... "
"defeated... by a puny ape girl...?!"
msgstr ""
"No lo puedo creer... Yo, Vitras, el último Señor Dragón de Morogor... "
"¡¿derrotado... por una chica mono insignificante...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:705
msgid ""
"Your mistake was to underestimate the Islefolk, lizard; we may not be mighty "
"and wise as the Chomi or the Seer's folk, but we have our pride and our "
"valour too! Now, in the name of all the Aeserians you've killed, GO TO "
"HELL!!!"
msgstr ""
"Tu error fue subestimar al pueblo de la Isla, lagarto; puede que no seamos "
"tan poderosos y sabios como los chomi o la gente del Vidente, ¡pero también "
"tenemos nuestro orgullo y nuestro valor! ¡Ahora, en nombre de todas las "
"aeserianas que has matado, ¡VETE AL INFIERNO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:720
msgid ""
"I can't believe it... I, Vitras, the last Dragon Lord of Morogor... "
"defeated... by a puny ape...?!"
msgstr ""
"No lo puedo creer... Yo, Vitras, el último Señor Dragón de Morogor... "
"¡¿derrotado... por un mono insignificante...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:724
msgid ""
"You should have known better than underestimating us, dragon; after all, I'm "
"a descendant of the people who thwarted you at Garet-Desh and at the Great "
"Continent's Far East, the people of Maat and Myra of Hiera'Shirsha! Now, "
"Dragon Lord Vitras, die, and leave us in peace once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Deberías haber sabido mejor que subestimarnos, dragón; después de todo, soy "
"descendiente del pueblo que te frustró en Garet-Desh y en el Lejano Oriente "
"del Gran Continente, ¡el pueblo de Maat y Myra de Hiera'Shirsha! ¡Ahora, "
"Señor Dragón Vitras, muere y déjanos en paz de una vez por todas!"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:742
msgid ""
"I may have fallen today, puny apes, but I shall not go alone... Drakes, now "
"you may butcher the singer ape as you wish!"
msgstr ""
"Puede que hoy haya caído, monos insignificantes, pero no me iré solo... "
"¡Dracos, ahora pueden destazar a la cantante mono como quieran!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:746
msgid "NO!!! I said that we had to rescue Branwyn before killing Vitras!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡NO!!! ¡Dije que teníamos que rescatar a Branwyn antes de matar a Vitras!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Vitras
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:770
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:798
msgid ""
"Ha! I should have expected lowly apes to resort to such treachery; first "
"they promise they won't send out their dark mage, and then they send him "
"under a disguise! But that is not  major problem, we'll kill you anyway - "
"the only difference is that you'll see your precious singer die!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! Debería haber esperado que los monos viles recurrieran a tal traición; "
"primero prometen que no enviarán a su mago oscuro, ¡y luego lo envían "
"disfrazado! Pero eso no es un problema mayor, de todos modos los mataremos, "
"la única diferencia es que verán morir a su preciosa cantante."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:774
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:802
msgid "NO!!! How could I have exposed myself before rescuing her?!!"
msgstr "¡NO!!! ¡¿Cómo pude exponerme antes de rescatarla?!!"

#. [message], speaker=Affalon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:816
msgid "We... we've done it! We've beaten those monsters, and saved our island!"
msgstr ""
"¡Lo... lo logramos! ¡Hemos derrotado a esos monstruos y salvado nuestra isla!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:824
msgid "All hail the Seer and his people, who led us to victory!"
msgstr "¡Todos alaben al Vidente y a su gente, que nos llevaron a la victoria!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:828
msgid ""
"Thanks, friends, but it's us who should thank you; after all, you helped me "
"and my friends after we had suffered a shipwreck..."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, amigos, pero somos nosotros quienes deberíamos agradecerles; "
"después de todo, nos ayudaron a mí y a mis amigos después de que sufriéramos "
"un naufragio..."

#. [message], speaker=Afallon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:832
msgid ""
"No, young friend, you'd have reunited even if we hadn't aided you; on the "
"other hand, without you we really wouldn't have stood a chance against those "
"drakes. It's true that, even without their lord, they may still attack us "
"again, but that's our problem now; you should return to your land and save "
"it from the evil you told me about."
msgstr ""
"No, joven amigo, se habrían reunido incluso si no los hubiéramos ayudado; en "
"cambio, sin ustedes realmente no habríamos tenido ninguna oportunidad contra "
"esos dracos. Es cierto que, incluso sin su señor, todavía pueden atacarnos "
"de nuevo, pero ese es nuestro problema ahora; ustedes deberían regresar a su "
"tierra y salvarla del mal del que me hablaron."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:836
msgid ""
"Indeed it is so; but I must find willing allies to help me in my own war. "
"That was, in fact, the reason I came here, though, after having so many of "
"you killed by drakes, I can't ask you to fight another war on another "
"continent."
msgstr ""
"Así es; pero debo encontrar aliados dispuestos a ayudarme en mi propia "
"guerra. De hecho, esa era la razón por la que vine aquí, aunque, después de "
"que tantos de ustedes murieran por los dracos, no puedo pedirles que luchen "
"en otra guerra en otro continente."

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:840
msgid ""
"In this I can help you: my people's colonies on this island are few and "
"weak, but in our homeland of Arajunna we have many cities and countless "
"soldiers. I, as the Great Commander of the Green Isle's Chomi, will send a "
"message to my lord, Holy Father Orun, telling him of how you saved us and "
"this entire island, and he'll help you however he can."
msgstr ""
"En esto puedo ayudarte: las colonias de mi pueblo en esta isla son pocas y "
"débiles, pero en nuestra tierra natal de Arajunna tenemos muchas ciudades y "
"soldados incontables. Yo, como Gran Comandante de los chomi de la Isla "
"Verde, enviaré un mensaje a mi señor, el Santo Padre Orun, contándole cómo "
"nos salvaste a nosotros y a toda esta isla, y él te ayudará como pueda."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:844
msgid ""
"Thanks very much, friend. Your soldiers, with their skill on forested and "
"swampy terrain, would be invaluable allies for us."
msgstr ""
"Muchas gracias, amigo. Tus soldados, con su habilidad en terreno boscoso y "
"pantanoso, serían aliados invaluables para nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:848
msgid ""
"And you, 'darkly one', I have to admit that you looked quite cool, coming "
"all alone to save me from the claws of a dragon. In fact, I'm planning on "
"making a song about it: a hero that comes from a foreign land to help a "
"princess defeat the king of beasts, such a theme could yield so many "
"stories..."
msgstr ""
"Y tú, «amigo oscuro», tengo que admitir que te veías bastante genial, "
"viniendo solo a salvarme de las garras de un dragón. De hecho, estoy "
"planeando hacer una canción sobre eso: un héroe que viene de una tierra "
"extranjera a ayudar a una princesa a derrotar al rey de las bestias, un tema "
"así podría dar muchas historias..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:852
msgid "Indeed, you owe me one for that..."
msgstr "Ciertamente, me debes una por eso..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:856
msgid "Um, yes, you're right... So here is your reward... (kisses him)"
msgstr "Um, sí, tienes razón... Entonces aquí está tu recompensa... (lo besa)"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:864
msgid "(raises eyebrows) My, my..."
msgstr "(levanta las cejas) Vaya, vaya..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:868
msgid ""
"(smiling) You know, Branwyn, if you want to come along with us, there'll "
"certainly be a vacant place on our ship..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Sabes, Branwyn, si quieres venir con nosotros, seguro habrá un "
"lugar vacante en nuestro barco..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:872
msgid ""
"'Course I'm coming along, you still have to pay me for helping you when you "
"arrived on our shores!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por supuesto que voy con ustedes, todavía tienes que pagarme por ayudarlos "
"cuando llegaron a nuestras costas!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:876
msgid "(snaps fingers) Mahyus, awaken! We're moving already!"
msgstr "(chasquea los dedos) ¡Mahyus, despierta! ¡Ya nos vamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:880
msgid "(surprised) Oh, well, right, I see, I'm coming..."
msgstr "(sorprendido) Oh, bueno, sí, entiendo, ya voy..."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:912
msgid ""
"Lord Vitras may have fallen, but we still stand, and so we must fight! Stand "
"strong, Children of Morogor, we still have to take this island for our "
"people!"
msgstr ""
"Puede que el señor Vitras haya caído, ¡pero nosotros todavía estamos de pie "
"y por eso debemos luchar! ¡Resistan con fuerza, Hijos de Morogor, todavía "
"tenemos que tomar esta isla para nuestra gente!"

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:916
msgid ""
"Persistent bastards, aren't they... Do not lose heart, fighters, with their "
"leader dead we only have to defeat the weak ones!"
msgstr ""
"Qué bastardos persistentes, ¿verdad...? No pierdan el ánimo, guerreros, con "
"su líder muerto solo tenemos que derrotar a los débiles."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:928
msgid "Finish off the remaining warriors of Morogor"
msgstr "Termina con los guerreros restantes de Morogor"

#. [message], speaker=Affalon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:989
msgid "I have fallen... Please, continue fighting without me..."
msgstr "He caído... Por favor, continúen luchando sin mí..."

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:993
msgid ""
"No! Without Affalon, the Aeserians are panicking and fleeing the "
"battlefield! We're too outnumbered to win now!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin Afallon, las aeserianas están entrando en pánico y huyendo del "
"campo de batalla! ¡Ahora estamos demasiado superados en número para ganar!"

#. [message], speaker=Adapa
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/20_Ancient_Fire.cfg:1022
msgid ""
"No... There are more lizard armies coming from the east! Now we're surely "
"doomed!"
msgstr ""
"No... ¡Hay más ejércitos de lagartos viniendo del este! ¡Ahora sí estamos "
"condenados!"

#. [scenario], id=21_The_Windy_Plains
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:4
msgid "The Windy Plains"
msgstr "Las Llanuras Ventosas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:27
msgid "Go southwards through the Windy Plains"
msgstr "Ve hacia el sur a través de las Llanuras Ventosas"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:51
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:575
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:49
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:468
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:113
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:562
msgid "Death of Olufemi"
msgstr "Muerte de Olufemi"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:55
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:579
msgid "NOTE: In this scenario and the next four, Akhen may recruit Chomi units"
msgstr ""
"NOTA: En este escenario y en los próximos cuatro, Akhen puede reclutar "
"unidades chomi"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:86
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:151
msgid "Deshrai"
msgstr "Deshrai"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:104
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:127
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:105
msgid "Washraha"
msgstr "Washraha"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:229
msgid ""
"(sigh) I am sorry to tell you this, Seer, but the storm blew us way off "
"course; and, to make matters worse, the ship is damaged, and there is no "
"tree in this region that we may use to repair it. We'll have to cross miles "
"of land on foot."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Lamento decirte esto, Vidente, pero la tormenta nos desvió mucho "
"del rumbo; y, para empeorar las cosas, el barco está dañado y no hay ningún "
"árbol en esta región que podamos usar para repararlo. Tendremos que cruzar "
"millas de tierra a pie."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Let's do it then, I have no problem with that; thus we'll be able to see "
"more of this continent."
msgstr ""
"Hagámoslo entonces, no tengo problema con eso; así podremos ver más de este "
"continente."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:237
msgid ""
"(panting) Nyx, by her turn, sees lots of problems with that; she doesn't "
"think she'll survive walking through this scorching inferno..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Nyx, por su parte, ve muchos problemas con eso; no cree que "
"sobreviva caminando a través de este infierno abrasador..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:241
msgid ""
"You can stay close to me, my shadow aura will diminish the sun's heat and "
"light."
msgstr ""
"Puedes quedarte cerca de mí, mi aura de sombra reducirá el calor y la luz "
"del sol."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:245
msgid ""
"I too wouldn't have a problem travelling on foot, lord, if we just weren't "
"going to cross this region in particular. You see, the lands unfolding "
"before your eyes are the Windy Plains, a very hot, dry and open region that "
"is inhabited not only by the Washraha, but also by Deshrai."
msgstr ""
"Yo tampoco tendría problema en viajar a pie, señor, si no fuera que vamos a "
"cruzar precisamente esta región. Verán, las tierras que se extienden ante "
"sus ojos son las Llanuras Ventosas, una región muy caliente, seca y abierta "
"que está habitada no solo por los Washraha, sino también por los Deshrai."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:249
msgid ""
"Then let us proceed very carefully. We should send scouts ahead of us, so "
"that we won't be caught by surprise, and, most importantly, keep close "
"together; I'm certain that we can defeat even the strongest of these giants "
"if we attack all at once, but if we fight individually we'll be an easy prey."
msgstr ""
"Entonces avancemos con mucho cuidado. Deberíamos enviar exploradores por "
"delante para no ser sorprendidos, y, lo más importante, mantenernos juntos; "
"estoy seguro de que podemos derrotar incluso al más fuerte de estos gigantes "
"si atacamos todos a la vez, pero si luchamos individualmente seremos una "
"presa fácil."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:270
msgid ""
"I've never thought I'd ever really reach the realm of Arajunna... Though now "
"I may as well miss my Green Isle: the home of the Chomi's so horribly hot... "
"Mahyus, don't you dare stay away from me, I want your shadows..."
msgstr ""
"Nunca pensé que realmente llegaría al reino de Arajunna... Aunque ahora bien "
"podría extrañar mi Isla Verde: la tierra de los chomi es tan horriblemente "
"caliente... Mahyus, no te atrevas a alejarte de mí, quiero tus sombras..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:274
msgid ""
"(laughs) Mahyus being the most popular guy to hang out with, it's kind of "
"nostalgic really."
msgstr ""
"(ríe) Mahyus siendo el chico más popular para andar juntos, es algo "
"nostálgico realmente."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:278
msgid ""
"Don't be jealous, Akhen, you're still Nyx's favourite. Now, if you just "
"manage to invoke a shadow aura like Mahyus', I'll be all yours..."
msgstr ""
"No estés celoso, Akhen, todavía eres el favorito de Nyx. Ahora, si logras "
"invocar un aura de sombra como la de Mahyus, seré toda tuya..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:282
msgid ""
"(annoyed) Geesh, folks, behave yourselves properly! What will the Chomi "
"think of us if they hear such dirty talk?"
msgstr ""
"(molesta) Geesh, gente, ¡compórtense como se debe! ¿Qué pensarán los chomi "
"de nosotros si escuchan semejante charla sucia?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:286
msgid ""
"Nothing bad in a bit of bawdy banter, sis. Why don't you try it yourself? "
"Merryment is never too much, more so as we march through danger."
msgstr ""
"No hay nada malo en un poco de broma picante, hermana. ¿Por qué no lo "
"intentas tú misma? La diversión nunca es demasiada, más aún cuando marchamos "
"a través del peligro."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:290
msgid "She'd first need someone to flirt with, but that one's a lost cause..."
msgstr ""
"Primero necesitaría a alguien con quien coquetear, pero ese es un caso "
"perdido..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:294
msgid ""
"No soul is a lost cause in matters of love! Come, Merwe the Unmerry, I shall "
"be your match-maker! Do you like strapping lads, beastly fierce? Or perhaps "
"you prefer gentler gents, willowy and suave? Or maybe it is in a fair lady "
"that you are fated to find love? The Aeserian folk loves freely, and I know "
"some of our followers fancy their own sex too. Give the command, and I shall "
"cause your paths to converge!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ninguna alma es un caso perdido en asuntos de amor! Ven, Merwe la "
"Desanimada, ¡yo seré tu casamentera! ¿Te gustan los muchachos fornidos y "
"ferozmente bestiales? ¿O tal vez prefieres caballeros más gentiles, delgados "
"y suaves? ¿O quizás es en una bella dama donde estás destinada a encontrar "
"el amor? El pueblo aeseriano ama libremente, y sé que algunas de nuestras "
"seguidoras también prefieren su propio sexo. ¡Da la orden y haré que tus "
"caminos se crucen!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:298
msgid "(sighs)"
msgstr "(suspira)"

#. [unit], id=Trakkon, type=Deshra Chieftain
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:318
msgid "Trakkon"
msgstr "Trakkon"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:343
msgid ""
"(suddenly alert) Darn it...! Friends, stand ready, for I fear we've entered "
"territory of the..."
msgstr ""
"(de repente alerta) ¡Maldición...! Amigos, prepárense, porque me temo que "
"hemos entrado en territorio de los..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:367
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "Oh…"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:371
msgid "...my..."
msgstr "...mi..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:375
msgid "...FOOD!!!"
msgstr "¡...COMIDA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:379
msgid "By the Gods, they're even larger than the drakes...!"
msgstr "¡Por los Dioses, son incluso más grandes que los dracos...!"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:383
msgid ""
"And what's worse, they look extremely angry and agitated; I wouldn't be "
"surprised if they're fleeing a Washraha group..."
msgstr ""
"Y lo peor es que se ven extremadamente enojados y agitados; no me "
"sorprendería que estén huyendo de un grupo de Washraha..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:387
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, our path goes through exactly that area, and these plains "
"really have nowhere to hide... I think we have no choice but to fight."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, nuestro camino pasa exactamente por esa área, y estas llanuras "
"realmente no tienen dónde esconderse... Creo que no tenemos otra opción que "
"luchar."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:404
msgid ""
"Well, their blood tastes is rich, but their skin is so hard and so filthy... "
"Don't they clean themselves every once in a while?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, su sangre tiene un sabor rico, pero su piel es tan dura y tan "
"sucia... ¿No se limpian de vez en cuando?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:422
msgid ""
"Whew, they're tough indeed! I find it hard to believe that such beings can "
"be afraid of anyone... Are the Washraha this fearsome?"
msgstr ""
"Uf, ¡son realmente duros! Me cuesta creer que seres así puedan tenerle miedo "
"a alguien... ¿Los Washraha son tan temibles?"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:426
msgid ""
"They're a nation that loves battle more than anything else, friend. Their "
"social positions are defined by one's number of kills, they measure one's "
"worth by their strength, their rituals of initiation into manhood involves "
"killing enemies; summing it up, they breath, eat, drink and transpire war."
msgstr ""
"Son una nación que ama la batalla más que cualquier otra cosa, amigo. Sus "
"posiciones sociales se definen por la cantidad de muertes de cada uno, miden "
"el valor de una persona por su fuerza, sus rituales de iniciación a la "
"adultez involucran matar enemigos; en resumen, respiran, comen, beben y "
"transpiran guerra."

#. [unit], id=Mitunnu, type=Washraha Jackal Warrior
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:450
msgid "Mitunnu"
msgstr "Mitunnu"

#. [unit], id=Kemosh, type=Washraja
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:465
msgid "Kemosh"
msgstr "Kemosh"

#. [unit], id=Kramak, type=Deshra Chieftain
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:480
msgid "Kramak"
msgstr "Kramak"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:521
msgid ""
"Just as I thought... The Washraha have attacked this small Deshra village to "
"capture their younglings for their army; the ones we've just fought were "
"mere refugees..."
msgstr ""
"Justo como pensaba... Los Washraha han atacado esta pequeña aldea Deshra "
"para capturar a sus jóvenes para su ejército; los que acabamos de combatir "
"eran solo refugiados..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:527
msgid ""
"It looks like the Washraha have attacked this small Deshra village to "
"capture their younglings for their army."
msgstr ""
"Parece que los Washraha han atacado esta pequeña aldea Deshra para capturar "
"a sus jóvenes para su ejército."

#. [message], speaker=Mitunnu
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:533
msgid "Oh, look, captain, more preys coming from the hills, and human prey!"
msgstr ""
"Oh, miren, capitán, más presas vienen de las colinas, ¡y presas humanas!"

#. [message], speaker=Kemosh
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:537
msgid ""
"(laughing) What a pleasant surprise... We come for Deshra and, as bonus, we "
"get a bunch of those soft weaklings - and they seem to have brought some "
"fine goods from wherever they sail to! Quick, warriors, get them before they "
"flee or get devoured along with their items by a Deshra!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Qué agradable sorpresa... Venimos por los Deshra y, como bono, "
"conseguimos un montón de esos blandos debiluchos, ¡y parece que trajeron "
"algunas mercancías finas de dondequiera que naveguen! ¡Rápido, guerreros, "
"atrápenlos antes de que huyan o sean devorados junto con sus objetos por un "
"Deshra!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:541
msgid "And he didn't even tell us his name... Talk about a truculent fellow."
msgstr "Y ni siquiera nos dijo su nombre... Hablando de un tipo truculento."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:545
msgid ""
"Well, I'd have preferred to settle this peacefully, but if you attack us, "
"Washraha, then we shall answer in kind."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, habría preferido resolver esto pacíficamente, pero si nos atacan, "
"Washraha, entonces responderemos de la misma forma."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:551
msgid ""
"Defeat every enemy standing in order to continue through the Windy Plains"
msgstr ""
"Derrota a todos los enemigos que queden de pie para continuar a través de "
"las Llanuras Ventosas"

#. [message], speaker=Kemosh
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:606
msgid ""
"Tsc! Damn you and your cheap tricks, Chomi, we'll get you as real warriors, "
"relying only on our strength and skill!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tsc! Malditos sean ustedes y sus trucos baratos, chomi, ¡los enfrentaremos "
"como verdaderos guerreros, confiando solo en nuestra fuerza y habilidad!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:610
msgid ""
"You know, I'm not the kind of person who likes showing off, but I really "
"expected them to be impressed..."
msgstr ""
"Saben, no soy el tipo de persona que le gusta presumir, pero realmente "
"esperaba que se impresionaran..."

#. [unit], id=Eren, type=Deshra
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:630
msgid "Wounded Deshra"
msgstr "Deshra Herido"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:644
msgid "Watch out! Curses, we should have kept it in the cage!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado! ¡Maldición, deberíamos haberlo mantenido en la jaula!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:648
msgid "Gods, he's so wounded..."
msgstr "Dioses, está tan herido..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:665
msgid ""
"Let me heal him, then he might even be friendly tow... (the giant seizes and "
"lifts her) Aaaiieeee!!!"
msgstr ""
"Déjenme sanarlo, entonces quizás hasta sea amistoso ha... (el gigante la "
"agarra y la levanta) ¡Aaaiieeee!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:669
msgid "Damn it... Release her at once, you stinking giant!"
msgstr "¡Maldición... Suéltala de inmediato, gigante apestoso!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:673
msgid ""
"Wait, let me deal with him! (points finger at the giant) You! Bad boy, "
"really bad boy! I'm a friend, they are bad guys! I help you, we crush them! "
"Now, put me on the ground, and slowly!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen, déjenme encargarme de él! (señala con el dedo al gigante) ¡Tú! "
"¡Mal chico, muy mal chico! ¡Soy una amiga, ellos son los malos! ¡Yo te "
"ayudo, aplastamos a ellos! ¡Ahora, bájame al suelo, y despacio!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:677
msgid "Is she truly trying to talk to that giant...?"
msgstr "¿Realmente está intentando hablar con ese gigante...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:681
msgid "It seems like it's working, though: see, he's actually lowering her!"
msgstr ""
"Parece que está funcionando, sin embargo: ¡miren, realmente la está bajando!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:685
msgid "Good, good boy! Now, come, we crush Washraha together!"
msgstr "¡Bien, buen chico! ¡Ahora, ven, aplastamos a los Washraha juntos!"

#. [message], speaker=Eren
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:689
msgid "(angry) Vashraha, gumbamgalba baldungar!!!"
msgstr "(enojado) ¡Vashraha, gumbamgalba baldungar!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:693
msgid ""
"Merwe, you sure are amazing; now we have a giant on our side! Let's keep him "
"well, he may unbalance many battles for us!"
msgstr ""
"Merwe, realmente eres increíble; ¡ahora tenemos un gigante de nuestro lado! "
"Mantengámoslo bien, ¡puede desequilibrar muchas batallas a nuestro favor!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:697
msgid "Indeed, let's keep him well, thus Nyx will never starve again..."
msgstr ""
"Ciertamente, mantengámoslo bien, así Nyx nunca volverá a pasar hambre..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:701
msgid "Keep your fangs away from Eren, you maniac vampiress!"
msgstr "¡Mantén tus colmillos lejos de Eren, vampiresa maniática!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:705
msgid "'Eren'? Where the hell did you take this name from?"
msgstr "¿«Eren»? ¿De dónde demonios sacaste ese nombre?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:709
msgid ""
"Well, it's the name of a character from a picture book I used to read..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, es el nombre de un personaje de un libro ilustrado que solía leer..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:738
msgid ""
"Seer, I never tire of watching your folk fighting. Are you sure that you "
"need the aid of anyone?"
msgstr ""
"Vidente, nunca me canso de ver a tu gente luchando. ¿Estás seguro de que "
"necesitas la ayuda de alguien?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:742
msgid ""
"We may be powerful, friend, but our enemy knows just as much as we do, or "
"even more, to be honest. But you and your fighting techniques are unknown to "
"them, and so your aid would still be invaluable."
msgstr ""
"Podemos ser poderosos, amigo, pero nuestro enemigo sabe tanto como nosotros, "
"o incluso más, para ser honesto. Pero tú y tus técnicas de combate les son "
"desconocidas, y por eso tu ayuda seguiría siendo invaluable."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:746
msgid ""
"I see... Well, after killing so many Deshrai, I believe that the path ahead "
"will be relatively safe. We'll only have to cross the swamps surrounding "
"River Oshune, and we'll enter the lands of Ifeh, so we need not worry about "
"more Washraha, for they don't venture into swampy lands."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo... Bueno, después de matar a tantos Deshrai, creo que el camino por "
"delante será relativamente seguro. Solo tendremos que cruzar los pantanos "
"que rodean el Río Oshune, y entraremos a las tierras de Ifeh, así que no "
"necesitamos preocuparnos por más Washraha, porque ellos no se aventuran en "
"tierras pantanosas."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:750
msgid ""
"A sun-scorched plain, and now a mosquito-infested swamp... How Nyx misses "
"her cold home mountains..."
msgstr ""
"Una llanura quemada por el sol, y ahora un pantano infestado de mosquitos... "
"Cómo extraña Nyx sus frías montañas natales..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:771
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:602
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:678
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:472
msgid "Apologies, friends... I have failed you..."
msgstr "Lo siento, amigos... Les he fallado..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:775
msgid "No! Without Olufemi, we will never find Ifeh!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Sin Olufemi, nunca encontraremos Ifeh!"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/21_The_Windy_Plains.cfg:786
msgid ""
"We're taking too much time to cross the Windy Plains! At this pace, we'll be "
"caught and overwhelmed by Washraha or Deshrai!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estamos tardando demasiado en cruzar las Llanuras Ventosas! ¡A este ritmo, "
"seremos atrapados y abrumados por Washraha o Deshrai!"

#. [scenario], id=22_Path_Of_Stones
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:4
msgid "Path of Stones"
msgstr "Camino de Piedras"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:25
msgid "Reach the Deshrai Mountains to the south"
msgstr "Llega a las Montañas Deshrai al sur"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:161
msgid ""
"Behold, friends: this is Lake Deva, the largest one in all of Arajunna. "
"Those green peaks you see past the lake are the Deshra Mountains; that's "
"where the path to Shray Tahl, the Washrahan capital, lies."
msgstr ""
"Miren, amigos: este es el Lago Deva, el más grande de toda Arajunna. Esas "
"cumbres verdes que ven más allá del lago son las Montañas Deshra; allí es "
"donde se encuentra el camino a Shray Tahl, la capital washrahana."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:165
msgid ""
"Deshra Mountains, you say? Eh, maybe it'd have been safer for us to simply "
"hack our way through the Washrahan lands..."
msgstr ""
"¿Montañas Deshra, dices? Eh, quizás habría sido más seguro para nosotros "
"simplemente abrirnos paso a través de las tierras washrahanas..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:169
msgid ""
"Worry not, those mountains only bear this name because they used to be a "
"home for the giants, but they've long left them. Now, as I was saying, our "
"secret path goes through the jungle that covers and surrounds the Deshra "
"Mountains; it's so thick and full of wild animals that the Washraha don't "
"dare venture into them, but the Chomi feel at home there, and so we can "
"easily cross it."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, esas montañas solo llevan este nombre porque antes eran "
"hogar de los gigantes, pero hace mucho que los dejaron. Ahora, como decía, "
"nuestro camino secreto pasa por la selva que cubre y rodea las Montañas "
"Deshra; es tan espesa y llena de animales salvajes que los Washraha no se "
"atreven a aventurarse en ella, pero los chomi se sienten como en casa allí, "
"y por eso podemos cruzarla fácilmente."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:173
msgid ""
"I see... But, if you Chomi use to wander about those mountains, won't there "
"be Washrahan outposts built outside of the jungle, maybe even on the other "
"side of this lake? There seems to be some human presence in this region, "
"judging by this bridge I see crossing the lake..."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo... Pero, si ustedes los chomi suelen vagar por esas montañas, ¿no "
"habrá puestos de avanzada Washrahanos construidos fuera de la selva, quizás "
"incluso al otro lado de este lago? Parece haber cierta presencia humana en "
"esta región, a juzgar por este puente que veo cruzando el lago..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:177
msgid ""
"Oh, no, this bridge isn't human-made. This is the Giants' Causeway, built by "
"the Deshrai long ago; I think that they didn't want to go all the way around "
"Lake Deva in order to reach our lands. As for the Washrahan outposts, don't "
"worry, recent scouting shows that there are none around – on the other hand, "
"we may come across nomad Chomi; it's known that they sometimes use the "
"islands in the middle of this lake as a hiding place."
msgstr ""
"Oh, no, este puente no fue hecho por humanos. Esta es la Calzada de los "
"Gigantes, construida por los Deshrai hace mucho tiempo; creo que no querían "
"dar toda la vuelta al Lago Deva para llegar a nuestras tierras. En cuanto a "
"los puestos de avanzada Washrahanos, no se preocupen, los reconocimientos "
"recientes muestran que no hay ninguno alrededor; en cambio, podemos "
"encontrarnos con chomi nómadas; se sabe que a veces usan las islas en medio "
"de este lago como escondite."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:181
msgid ""
"Hiding haven? The way you say it, they sound like some sort of bandit "
"group..."
msgstr ""
"¿Escondite? Por la forma en que lo dices, suenan como algún tipo de grupo de "
"bandidos..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:186
msgid ""
"Indeed, they're a group of Chomi outcasts. Forbidden to settle on any of our "
"cities, they wander the realm, preying on unaware Chomi travellers and even "
"Washraha retinues."
msgstr ""
"Así es, son un grupo de chomi proscritos. Prohibidos de establecerse en "
"cualquiera de nuestras ciudades, vagan por el reino, acechando a viajeros "
"chomi desprevenidos e incluso a comitivas washrahanas."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:190
msgid ""
"So now we have a good notion of what we may find; let's get moving and reach "
"those mountains as soon as we can; the scouts may not have seen Washraha "
"outposts around, but they may still have their own scouts in the area, and "
"until we enter that jungle we'll be way too exposed."
msgstr ""
"Así que ahora tenemos una buena idea de lo que podemos encontrar; pongámonos "
"en marcha y lleguemos a esas montañas lo antes posible; los exploradores "
"pueden no haber visto puestos de avanzada Washrahanos alrededor, pero "
"todavía pueden tener sus propios exploradores en la zona, y hasta que "
"entremos en esa selva estaremos demasiado expuestos."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:217
msgid ""
"Akhen, Mahyus, I've been thinking about the name of this lake, I'm certain "
"I've read it in some scroll at the Academy..."
msgstr ""
"Akhen, Mahyus, he estado pensando en el nombre de este lago, estoy segura de "
"haberlo leído en algún pergamino en la Academia..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:221
msgid ""
"You're right; Deva was the name of Akashia's famous magic sword. Considering "
"that the Windsong at her time filled their ranks with orphan girls from "
"various countries, it's very likely that Akashia was a native of Arajunna."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón; Deva era el nombre de la famosa espada mágica de Akashia. "
"Considerando que las Hijas del Viento en su época llenaban sus filas con "
"niñas huérfanas de varios países, es muy probable que Akashia fuera nativa "
"de Arajunna."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Then she must have been a Washraha, for 'Deva' is a word of their tongue, I "
"think it means 'holy'. They've probably named this lake like this due to the "
"stories regarding it. It's said that the islands amidst it were once used "
"for sacred rituals by the Asherah, the men who walked on Arajunna in the "
"dawn of time."
msgstr ""
"Entonces debe haber sido una Washraha, porque «Deva» es una palabra de su "
"lengua, creo que significa «santo». Probablemente nombraron este lago así "
"debido a las historias sobre él. Se dice que las islas en medio de él fueron "
"usadas una vez para rituales sagrados por los Asherah, los hombres que "
"caminaron por Arajunna en el amanecer de los tiempos."

#. [unit], id=Akia, type=Chomi Ranger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:242
msgid "Akia"
msgstr "Akia"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:262
msgid "And, as expected..."
msgstr "Y, como era de esperar..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:266
msgid ""
"Chomi brothers, we seek no quarrel with you; rather, we're bound to the land "
"of the Washraha, our common foe! In the name of the high gods, I ask you to "
"let us go in peace, and we shall repay your generosity by making this region "
"free of Washrahan menace!"
msgstr ""
"Hermanos chomi, no buscamos pelea con ustedes; más bien, estamos destinados "
"a la tierra de los Washraha, ¡nuestro enemigo común! En nombre de los altos "
"dioses, les pido que nos dejen ir en paz, y les recompensaremos su "
"generosidad liberando esta región de la amenaza washrahana."

#. [message], speaker=Akia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:270
msgid ""
"Pfff, these city Chomi, always thinking that we'll take easy on them because "
"of our kinship... You call us brothers now, but no one treated us so when we "
"were expelled from your cities! As for the Washraha, we can deal with them "
"ourselves, thanks very much. Now, if you're done talking, grab your sword "
"and spears, and at least have a decent death!"
msgstr ""
"Pfff, estos chomi de ciudad, siempre pensando que los trataremos con "
"suavidad por nuestro parentesco... ¡Ahora nos llaman hermanos, pero nadie "
"nos trató así cuando nos expulsaron de sus ciudades! En cuanto a los "
"Washraha, podemos encargarnos de ellos nosotros mismos, muchas gracias. "
"Ahora, si ya terminaron de hablar, tomen su espada y lanzas, ¡y al menos "
"tengan una muerte decente!"

#. [message], speaker=Akia
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:282
msgid ""
"Damn city Chomi and even more damn foreigners! This is not a fight worth "
"dying for, men, we must flee!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos chomi de ciudad y extranjeros aún más malditos! Esta no es una "
"pelea por la que valga la pena morir, hombres, ¡debemos huir!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:292
msgid ""
"Oh-oh, look, guys, seems like those bandits were going the Washrahan way and "
"training some young Deshrai themselves..."
msgstr ""
"Oh-oh, miren, muchachos, parece que esos bandidos iban por el camino "
"washrahano y ellos mismos estaban entrenando a algunos jóvenes Deshrai..."

#. [unit], id=Goghi, type=Deshra
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:298
msgid "Goghi"
msgstr "Goghi"

#. [unit], id=Megoghi, type=Deshra
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:312
msgid "Megoghi"
msgstr "Megoghi"

#. [message], speaker=Eren
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:341
msgid ""
"Damba Deshrai, garsha dombahr bangalba dhar! Eren ghor bangradhar Mervi "
"shagradhan!"
msgstr ""
"Damba Deshrai, garsha dombahr bangalba dhar! Eren ghor bangradhar Mervi "
"shagradhan!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:345
msgid "Nyx thinks your sweet giant is talking about you, 'Mervi'..."
msgstr "Nyx cree que tu dulce gigante está hablando de ti, «Mervi»..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:349
msgid "Oh, shut u- Hey, look, the three Deshrai are... greeting me?"
msgstr "Oh, cállate- Oye, miren, ¿los tres Deshrai me están... saludando?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:353
msgid ""
"And yet again Merwe the Motherly manages to conquer new allies for our army!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y una vez más Merwe la Maternal logra conquistar nuevos aliados para "
"nuestro ejército!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:357
msgid ""
"'Merwe the Motherly'... I like it, but I'd rather be called, let me see... "
"What about Mother of Giants?"
msgstr ""
"«Merwe la Maternal»... Me gusta, pero preferiría que me llamaran, déjenme "
"ver... ¿Qué tal Madre de Gigantes?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:361
msgid "I still think that 'Mervi' sounds better..."
msgstr "Sigo pensando que «Mervi» suena mejor..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:365
msgid ""
"(laughing) You better mind the words you drive at her, Nyx, or else she may "
"send her children to avenge their wronged mother. Now, to business: we "
"shouldn't have any obstacle on the way to the Deshra Mountains, so let's go "
"on."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Mejor cuida las palabras que le diriges, Nyx, o ella podría enviar "
"a sus hijos a vengar a su madre agraviada. Ahora, al grano: no deberíamos "
"tener ningún obstáculo en el camino a las Montañas Deshra, así que sigamos."

#. [message], speaker=Goghi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:371
msgid "(looking frightened) Dhorba, dhorba Goghi ba Megoghi!"
msgstr "(mirando asustado) ¡Dhorba, dhorba Goghi ba Megoghi!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:375
msgid ""
"By the Gods, what have those bandits done to make such strong creatures so "
"fragile...? Don't worry, Deshrai, we won't hurt you. Now, go and find your "
"kin!"
msgstr ""
"Por los Dioses, ¿qué les habrán hecho esos bandidos a criaturas tan fuertes "
"para volverlas tan frágiles...? No se preocupen, Deshrai, no les haremos "
"daño. ¡Ahora, vayan y encuentren a su gente!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:389
msgid ""
"A pity that that giant Eren is not here, he could have convinced those two "
"to join us..."
msgstr ""
"Lástima que ese gigante Eren no esté aquí, él podría haber convencido a esos "
"dos de unirse a nosotros..."

#. [unit], id=Anshar, type=Washraja
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:416
msgid "Anshar"
msgstr "Anshar"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:430
msgid "Damn, what are so many cursed Washraha doing here...?"
msgstr "¡Maldición, qué hacen tantos Washraha malditos aquí...?"

#. [message], speaker=Anshar
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:434
msgid ""
"(grinning) See, boys? What did I tell you about sneaky Chomi vermin "
"wallowing about in this jungle? I'd like to see those stupid higher-ups "
"saying that building outposts 'round these mountains is a waste now!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) ¿Ven, muchachos? ¿Qué les dije sobre los asquerosos chomi "
"sigilosos que se revuelcan en esta selva? Me gustaría ver a esos estúpidos "
"superiores diciendo ahora que construir puestos de avanzada alrededor de "
"estas montañas es un desperdicio."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:438
msgid ""
"I really don't like this... We may even have to redraw our plans – but for "
"now, we must defeat these Washraha!"
msgstr ""
"Realmente no me gusta esto... Es posible que tengamos que replantear "
"nuestros planes, pero por ahora debemos derrotar a estos Washraha."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:444
msgid "Defeat the Washraha Captain"
msgstr "Derrota al capitán Washraha"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:492
msgid ""
"I have to acknowledge that I committed a great mistake, friends, and for "
"this I'm sorry; never would I have thought that they had decided to "
"establish outposts here now out of all months."
msgstr ""
"Tengo que reconocer que cometí un gran error, amigos, y por eso lo siento; "
"nunca habría pensado que decidirían establecer puestos de avanzada aquí "
"precisamente ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:496
msgid ""
"Worry not, we understand – but we must now consider that there will be more "
"Washraha in this forest, especially when these ones we've just defeated "
"don't report back. It's true that you Chomi can easily move and hide in the "
"jungle, but the same cannot be said of us Maat'Karians... Is there really no "
"other way to reach Shray Tahl?"
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, entendemos, pero ahora debemos considerar que habrá más "
"Washraha en este bosque, especialmente cuando estos que acabamos de derrotar "
"no regresen a informar. Es cierto que ustedes los chomi pueden moverse y "
"esconderse fácilmente en la selva, pero no se puede decir lo mismo de "
"nosotros los maat'karianos... ¿Realmente no hay otra forma de llegar a Shray "
"Tahl?"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:500
msgid ""
"Well, there is one alternative path; however, I didn't even mention it "
"before because that's not something we should even consider..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, hay un camino alternativo; sin embargo, ni siquiera lo mencioné antes "
"porque es algo que ni siquiera deberíamos considerar..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:504
msgid "Well, try explaining what it's like, maybe we could go through it."
msgstr "Bueno, intenta explicar cómo es, quizás podríamos pasar por allí."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:508
msgid ""
"If you insist... Remember what I told you earlier about Lake Deva's islands, "
"that they were once inhabited by the ancient Asherah tribe? Well, amidst "
"this jungle lies the entrance to a deep network of tunnels known as the "
"Caves of the Asherah, or Caves of Light. Even our greatest sages know very "
"little about them, because of all Chomi scouts sent there, none returned. It "
"is known, however, thanks to old Babalawo Kayode, that there is a fearsome "
"power lying on those depths, a power that made even Kayode himself quake in "
"fear, or so the tale claims."
msgstr ""
"Si insisten... ¿Recuerdan lo que les conté antes sobre las islas del Lago "
"Deva, que una vez fueron habitadas por la antigua tribu Asherah? Bueno, en "
"medio de esta selva se encuentra la entrada a una profunda red de túneles "
"conocida como las Cuevas de los Asherah, o Cuevas de la Luz. Incluso "
"nuestros sabios más grandes saben muy poco sobre ellas, porque de todos los "
"exploradores chomi enviados allí, ninguno regresó. Sin embargo, se sabe, "
"gracias al viejo Babalawo Kayode, que hay un poder temible en esas "
"profundidades, un poder que hizo temblar incluso al propio Kayode de miedo, "
"o eso dice el relato."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:512
msgid ""
"I don't want to belittle your High Priest, but I think we could try and "
"identify both the type and the intensity of this power; and, if it's "
"something that we can handle, we could use these caves to reach Shray Tahl – "
"that is, if there is an exit to those caves?"
msgstr ""
"No quiero menospreciar a tu Sumo Sacerdote, pero creo que podríamos intentar "
"identificar tanto el tipo como la intensidad de este poder; y si es algo que "
"podemos manejar, podríamos usar estas cuevas para llegar a Shray Tahl, es "
"decir, si hay una salida de esas cuevas."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:516
msgid ""
"There is such exit; scouts have found it already, though it's not so close "
"to Shray Tahl."
msgstr ""
"Hay tal salida; los exploradores ya la encontraron, aunque no está tan cerca "
"de Shray Tahl."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:520
msgid ""
"Then, please, lead us to the entrance to these Caves of Light; I'm starting "
"to get curious about them..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, por favor, llévanos a la entrada de estas Cuevas de la Luz; estoy "
"empezando a sentir curiosidad por ellas..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/22_Path_Of_Stones.cfg:613
msgid ""
"We should've been quicker, at this pace we will probably be sighted by "
"Washraha before we reach the mountains!"
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos haber sido más rápidos, ¡a este ritmo probablemente seremos "
"avistados por los Washraha antes de llegar a las montañas!"

#. [scenario], id=23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:4
msgid "A Glimpse of the Light"
msgstr "Un Vistazo de la Luz"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:23
msgid "Investigate the Caves of Light, and clear it of any foe you find"
msgstr ""
"Investiga las Cuevas de la Luz y límpialas de cualquier enemigo que "
"encuentres"

#. [side], type=Seraph
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:64
msgid "Eriel"
msgstr "Eriel"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:150
msgid ""
"We're now close to the source of this power, whatever it is; I just pray "
"that it's really something we can deal with..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora estamos cerca de la fuente de este poder, sea lo que sea; solo rezo "
"para que realmente sea algo con lo que podamos lidiar..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:154
msgid ""
"The problem is, the energy we've been feeling since we entered these caves "
"is not the only one I can sense right now..."
msgstr ""
"El problema es que la energía que hemos estado sintiendo desde que entramos "
"en estas cuevas no es la única que puedo percibir ahora..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:158
msgid ""
"You're right... It's a power that is akin to your own, Merwe: a Lucent-like "
"energy... Let's proceed carefully from now on, I've got a bad feeling about "
"this new power."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón... Es un poder similar al tuyo, Merwe: una energía similar a la "
"Luciente... Procedamos con cuidado de ahora en adelante, tengo un mal "
"presentimiento sobre este nuevo poder."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:162
msgid "So do I..."
msgstr "Yo también..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:183
msgid ""
"(smiling) Now that I think of it, this is probably the first time we're "
"alone together since all this began, that day at the Academy, when Mahyus "
"challenged me."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Ahora que lo pienso, probablemente esta es la primera vez que "
"estamos solos juntos desde que todo esto comenzó, ese día en la Academia, "
"cuando Mahyus me desafió."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:187
msgid "Indeed... But what does it have to do with anything?"
msgstr "Ciertamente... ¿Pero qué tiene que ver con algo?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:191
msgid ""
"Well, nothing really, it's just that until that day you were the only one I "
"used to hang with..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, realmente nada, es solo que hasta ese día tú eras la única con quien "
"solía pasar el tiempo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:198
msgid "See, Merwe, about Nyx and I..."
msgstr "Mira, Merwe, sobre Nyx y yo..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:202
msgid ""
"(suddenly angry) No, please, don't, just don't! I'm no fool, Akhen, I've "
"long understood what you feel for each other – and know it, I have accepted "
"it already, and wish you all the happiness that can exist between a human "
"and a vampire, I just... Well, I just wish you had noticed how <i>I</i> felt "
"about you sooner..."
msgstr ""
"(de repente enojada) ¡No, por favor, no, simplemente no! No soy tonta, "
"Akhen, hace mucho que entendí lo que sienten el uno por el otro, y lo sé, ya "
"lo he aceptado y les deseo toda la felicidad que pueda existir entre un "
"humano y una vampiresa, solo que... Bueno, solo desearía que hubieras notado "
"antes cómo <i>yo</i> me sentía por ti..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:206
msgid ""
"I too am no fool, Merwe, I've known what you felt for me since those Academy "
"days... At the time, I just didn't know how to return your feelings; I liked "
"you very much, as I still do, but I felt my kind of love was not the one "
"your own kind deserved. And then I met..."
msgstr ""
"Yo tampoco soy tonto, Merwe, he sabido lo que sentías por mí desde aquellos "
"días en la Academia... En ese momento simplemente no sabía cómo corresponder "
"a tus sentimientos; me gustabas mucho, como todavía me gustas, pero sentía "
"que mi tipo de amor no era el que tu propia clase merecía. Y luego conocí..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:210
msgid ""
"I see... (smiling sadly) Well, we can't force one to love another, I "
"suppose... (energetically) Still, I must find someone myself, I don't want "
"to be the only single in our group!"
msgstr ""
"Ya veo... (sonriendo con tristeza) Bueno, supongo que no se puede obligar a "
"alguien a amar a otro... (con energía) Aun así, yo también debo encontrar a "
"alguien, ¡no quiero ser la única soltera en nuestro grupo!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Look, one of the denizens of this cave has finally appeared. Its power does "
"resemble that of a lucent mage... Do you recognize it, Akhen?"
msgstr ""
"Mira, uno de los habitantes de esta cueva finalmente apareció. Su poder sí "
"se parece al de un mago luciente... ¿Lo reconoces, Akhen?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:229
msgid ""
"It does resemble, and quite alarmingly, the descriptions given by "
"Maat'Karian scrolls of a kind of light fairy used by Celestials in their "
"armies..."
msgstr ""
"Sí se parece, y de manera bastante alarmante, a las descripciones dadas por "
"los pergaminos maat'karianos de un tipo de hada de la luz usada por los "
"Celestiales en sus ejércitos..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Does that mean that this is the place the Celestials came after fleeing "
"Netjer-Ta?"
msgstr ""
"¿Eso significa que este es el lugar al que llegaron los Celestiales después "
"de huir de Netjer-Ta?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:237
msgid ""
"I'd think so, but the Chomi didn't mention anything that could be related to "
"them... Unless the Celestials remained all their time here hiding in caves "
"like this..."
msgstr ""
"Yo pensaría que sí, pero los chomi no mencionaron nada que pudiera estar "
"relacionado con ellos... A menos que los Celestiales se hayan quedado todo "
"este tiempo aquí escondidos en cuevas como esta..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:252
msgid "By the Gods of Light, what kind of creature is that?!"
msgstr "¡Por los Dioses de la Luz, qué clase de criatura es esa!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:256
msgid ""
"I have no idea, but it's a magical creature whose energy is akin to that "
"which impregnates these caves."
msgstr ""
"No tengo idea, pero es una criatura mágica cuya energía es similar a la que "
"impregna estas cuevas."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:260
msgid ""
"I see... The source of this energy is probably the same thing spawning these "
"creatures; I don't like the idea of destroying everything standing on our "
"path, but I'm afraid that they won't let us in peace unless we stop them."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo... La fuente de esta energía probablemente sea la misma cosa que "
"genera a estas criaturas; no me gusta la idea de destruir todo lo que se "
"interponga en nuestro camino, pero me temo que no nos dejarán en paz a menos "
"que los detengamos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:272
msgid ""
"I knew it! So this is where your people came after you were expelled from "
"Netjer-Ta, Celestial; but why do you keep attacking us, even though you're "
"also fighting these cave creatures?"
msgstr ""
"¡Lo sabía! Así que este es el lugar al que llegó tu gente después de ser "
"expulsada de Netjer-Ta, Celestial; pero ¿por qué sigues atacándonos, aunque "
"también estás luchando contra estas criaturas de las cuevas?"

#. [message], speaker=Eriel
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:276
msgid ""
"Why, you ask...? Don't your scrolls tell you what your people have done in "
"the past, Maat'Karian? Let me tell you, then, for I was there when your folk "
"started killing us, even though we were kind enough to let you live on that "
"continent! You destroyed our Crystal Tower, killed our Lords and then swept "
"away all of our settlements, and then your forced us out of our age-old home!"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué, preguntas...? ¿Tus pergaminos no te cuentan lo que tu gente hizo "
"en el pasado, maat'kariano? Déjame contarte entonces, porque yo estaba allí "
"cuando tu gente empezó a matarnos, ¡aunque fuimos lo suficientemente amables "
"como para dejarlos vivir en ese continente! Destruyeron nuestra Torre de "
"Cristal, mataron a nuestros Señores y luego arrasaron todos nuestros "
"asentamientos, ¡y luego nos obligaron a salir de nuestro hogar ancestral!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:280
msgid ""
"This we all know, Celestial; you, however, seem to ignore that it were you "
"who started that war!"
msgstr ""
"Esto lo sabemos todos, Celestial; tú, sin embargo, pareces ignorar que "
"fueron ustedes quienes iniciaron esa guerra."

#. [message], speaker=Eriel
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:284
msgid ""
"But now, ah, now the High Ones have finally given me the chance to fulfil my "
"vengeance; even if I can't destroy all of Maat'Kare, I will at least bring "
"doom upon some of its children!"
msgstr ""
"Pero ahora, ah, ahora los Altos me han dado finalmente la oportunidad de "
"cumplir mi venganza; aunque no pueda destruir toda Maat'Kare, al menos "
"traeré la perdición sobre algunos de sus hijos."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:288
msgid ""
"It's no use trying to argue, Akhen; he's been feeding a deep hatred for us "
"since sixteen centuries ago, he won't change his mind now."
msgstr ""
"No sirve de nada intentar discutir, Akhen; ha estado alimentando un odio "
"profundo hacia nosotros desde hace dieciséis siglos, no cambiará de opinión "
"ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:300
msgid ""
"Now, Celestial, I want to prove to you that we're not the ruthless monsters "
"you deem us to be. If you promise not to pester us again, we shall let you "
"go in peace..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, Celestial, quiero demostrarte que no somos los monstruos despiadados "
"que crees que somos. Si prometes no molestarnos de nuevo, te dejaremos ir en "
"paz..."

#. [message], speaker=Eriel
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:304
msgid ""
"Go in peace, you say? Foolish human, you have no idea where you have set "
"your foot..."
msgstr ""
"¿Ir en paz, dices? Humano tonto, no tienes idea de dónde has puesto el pie..."

#. [message], speaker=Eriel
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:312
msgid ""
"These, humans, are the caves my people chose to settle ages ago; we thought "
"it the perfect place for us, we thought this was where we could meet the "
"Ancient Ones themselves once again, but... We were so terribly mistaken... "
"We did meet one of them, but she was not what we expected, she... she "
"butchered us all with her spawns... And now, it is your time to suffer, "
"Maat'Karians, for Vanadya will not let you out of her tomb..."
msgstr ""
"Estas, humanos, son las cuevas que mi gente eligió para establecerse hace "
"mucho tiempo; pensamos que era el lugar perfecto para nosotros, pensamos que "
"aquí podríamos volver a encontrarnos con los Antiguos, pero... Estábamos tan "
"terriblemente equivocados... Conocimos a una de ellas, pero no era lo que "
"esperábamos, ella... ella nos masacró a todos con sus engendros... Y ahora "
"es su turno de sufrir, maat'karianos, porque Vanadya no los dejará salir de "
"su tumba..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:324
msgid ""
"Merwe, what he's just said... The Ancient Ones, weren't they the gods who "
"created the High Dragons, the Celestials, the world itself...?"
msgstr ""
"Merwe, lo que acaba de decir... ¿Los Antiguos no eran los dioses que crearon "
"a los Dragones Superiores, a los Celestiales, al mundo mismo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:328
msgid ""
"Or so the old Hiera'Laksha scrolls claim... And, if we can trust this "
"Celestial's words, one of them was buried here, where her power still "
"lingers... Akhen, are you sure that you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"O eso afirman los antiguos pergaminos de Hiera'Laksha... Y si podemos "
"confiar en las palabras de este Celestial, uno de ellos fue enterrado aquí, "
"donde su poder todavía perdura... Akhen, ¿estás seguro de que quieres "
"continuar?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:332
msgid ""
"We've been able to fight her creatures so far, haven't we? Besides, if this "
"is her tomb, she must be dead; maybe her power lingers here just as the "
"Water Dragon's power lingered in his tomb, and in this case we only have to "
"fight her remaining creations, not the goddess herself."
msgstr ""
"Hasta ahora hemos podido luchar contra sus criaturas, ¿verdad? Además, si "
"esta es su tumba, debe estar muerta; quizás su poder perdura aquí igual que "
"el poder del Dragón de Agua perduraba en su tumba, y en ese caso solo "
"tenemos que luchar contra sus creaciones restantes, no contra la diosa misma."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:336
msgid ""
"Tell the truth, you're just dying of curiosity to learn more, aren't you?"
msgstr ""
"Dime la verdad, te estás muriendo de curiosidad por aprender más, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:340
msgid ""
"Erm, well... Yes, I am, but this is really something worth learning, don't "
"you think? This may be the first concrete evidence of an Ancient One's "
"identity we've ever found!"
msgstr ""
"Erm, bueno... Sí, lo estoy, pero esto es realmente algo que vale la pena "
"aprender, ¿no crees? ¡Esta puede ser la primera evidencia concreta de la "
"identidad de un Antiguo que hayamos encontrado!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:344
msgid ""
"(smiling) I'd be lying if I told you I didn't feel the same about this "
"matter, so let's go on and find Vanadya's tomb or whatever may lie ahead..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Mentiría si te dijera que no siento lo mismo sobre este asunto, "
"así que sigamos y encontremos la tumba de Vanadya o lo que sea que haya más "
"adelante..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:348
msgid ""
"<i>You speak as if Vanadya is dead, humans... But how would something that "
"can't disappear ever perish...?</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Hablan como si Vanadya estuviera muerta, humanos... Pero ¿cómo podría "
"perecer algo que no puede desaparecer...?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:356
msgid "Akhen, is something the matter?"
msgstr "Akhen, ¿pasa algo?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:360
msgid "Didn't you just hear it?"
msgstr "¿No lo acabas de oír?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:364
msgid "Hear what?"
msgstr "¿Oír qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:368
msgid ""
"A... Well, I think these caves have just played a trick on me... Let's go "
"on; if the situation becomes too bad, we'll go back and venture into the "
"jungle, but for now, let's try and get to the end of these caves..."
msgstr ""
"Un... Bueno, creo que estas cuevas acaban de jugarme una mala pasada... "
"Sigamos; si la situación se pone demasiado mala, regresaremos y nos "
"aventuraremos en la selva, pero por ahora intentemos llegar al final de "
"estas cuevas..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:372
msgid ""
"Wait, look at all these books the Celestial left behind... I wonder whether "
"it has some arcane spells unknown to the Lucent Arts..."
msgstr ""
"Espera, mira todos estos libros que dejó el Celestial... Me pregunto si "
"tiene algunos hechizos arcanos desconocidos para las Artes Lucientes..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:379
msgid "*Myra, can you hear me? Do you have any idea of what is going on here*"
msgstr "*Myra, ¿puedes oírme? ¿Tienes alguna idea de qué está pasando aquí?*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:384
msgid ""
"*<i>I don't know, grandson, and that's what's puzzling me; the energy "
"lingering in these caves, I can't identify it, and I should be able to. It "
"may not even be of this world...*</i>"
msgstr ""
"*<i>No lo sé, nieto, y eso es lo que me intriga; la energía que perdura en "
"estas cuevas no puedo identificarla, y debería poder hacerlo. Puede que ni "
"siquiera sea de este mundo...*</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:388
msgid "*So should I turn back and cross these mountains through the jungle?*>"
msgstr ""
"*¿Entonces debería dar la vuelta y cruzar estas montañas a través de la "
"selva?*>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:393
msgid ""
"<i>*Don't worry. Strange as it is, this energy doesn't feel malicious, even "
"though the creatures originated from it will attempt on your life... I won't "
"leave you alone, Akhen; if I notice anything else, I'll inform you, but for "
"now you may go ahead and investigate it further.*</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>*No te preocupes. Por extraño que sea, esta energía no se siente "
"maliciosa, aunque las criaturas que se originan de ella intentarán atentar "
"contra tu vida... No te dejaré solo, Akhen; si noto algo más, te informaré, "
"pero por ahora puedes continuar e investigarlo más a fondo.*</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:415
msgid ""
"And so we've reached the point where that energy is strongest – and also the "
"place those creatures come from... They seem to be spawning from those dark "
"clouds surrounding that statue in the middle."
msgstr ""
"Y así hemos llegado al punto donde esa energía es más fuerte, y también al "
"lugar del que provienen esas criaturas... Parece que están surgiendo de esas "
"nubes oscuras que rodean esa estatua en el centro."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:419
msgid "Akhen, could that statue be..."
msgstr "Akhen, ¿podría esa estatua ser...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:423
msgid ""
"I bet that represents Vanadya; an Ancient One herself... But why was she "
"buried here, and how did she die, if she was a goddess...?"
msgstr ""
"Apuesto a que representa a Vanadya; una Antigua ella misma... Pero ¿por qué "
"fue enterrada aquí y cómo murió, si era una diosa...?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:427
msgid ""
"There may be some inscriptions over that statue, though I doubt they'll be "
"in a language we can understand. Anyway, let's dispel those shadows and rid "
"these caves of these creatures."
msgstr ""
"Puede que haya algunas inscripciones sobre esa estatua, aunque dudo que "
"estén en un idioma que podamos entender. De todos modos, disipemos esas "
"sombras y liberemos estas cuevas de estas criaturas."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:444
msgid ""
"The others just vanished when the shadows disappeared... And yes, there are "
"inscriptions beneath this statue, but they're in a completely unknown "
"language. I wonder whether it was built by the Asherah people, and whether "
"they had any direct contact with this goddess..."
msgstr ""
"Los otros simplemente desaparecieron cuando las sombras se disiparon... Y "
"sí, hay inscripciones debajo de esta estatua, pero están en un idioma "
"completamente desconocido. Me pregunto si fue construida por el pueblo "
"Asherah y si tuvieron algún contacto directo con esta diosa..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:448
msgid ""
"It's so frustrating to stumble on such a finding and not be able to learn "
"more about it! There must be a world of stories surrounding this place, and "
"yet... (sigh) Well, maybe it is better to just leave Vanadya alone, after "
"all; she must have been a cruel goddess, judging by the creations of her "
"lingering power. Who knows, maybe she isn't even dead, but in a dormant "
"state, waiting to be unleashed upon Irdya once more..."
msgstr ""
"Es tan frustrante tropezar con un hallazgo así y no poder aprender más sobre "
"él. Debe haber un mundo de historias rodeando este lugar, y sin embargo... "
"(suspiro) Bueno, quizás sea mejor dejar a Vanadya en paz después de todo; "
"debe haber sido una diosa cruel, a juzgar por las creaciones de su poder "
"perdurable. Quién sabe, quizás ni siquiera esté muerta, sino en un estado "
"latente, esperando ser liberada sobre Irdya una vez más..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:452
msgid ""
"Yeah, and we all know that we've already got our hands full with destructive "
"god-like beings to wake another one... *So you haven't noticed anything?*"
msgstr ""
"Sí, y todos sabemos que ya tenemos las manos llenas con seres destructivos "
"similares a dioses como para despertar a otro... *¿Entonces no has notado "
"nada?*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:457
msgid ""
"<i>*No... Well, probably these caves are merely impregnated with Vanadya's "
"energy and nothing else. There are no more Ancient Ones remaining, after "
"all...*</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>*No... Bueno, probablemente estas cuevas solo están impregnadas con la "
"energía de Vanadya y nada más. Después de todo, ya no quedan más "
"Antiguos...*</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:466
msgid ""
"I think there's no more threat left in these caves; now, let's find our "
"friends..."
msgstr ""
"Creo que ya no queda más amenaza en estas cuevas; ahora, busquemos a "
"nuestros amigos..."

#. [message], speaker=Shadowavatar
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:511
msgid ""
"See you another aeon, heiress... Take your time, I am in no hurry; after "
"all, what cannot disappear shall never perish..."
msgstr ""
"Nos vemos en otro eón, heredera... Tómate tu tiempo, no tengo prisa; después "
"de todo, lo que no puede desaparecer nunca perecerá..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/23_A_Glimpse_Of_The_Light.cfg:533
msgid ""
"If we continue at this pace, we'll end up overwhelmed by the creatures "
"dwelling in these caves!"
msgstr ""
"Si continuamos a este ritmo, terminaremos abrumados por las criaturas que "
"habitan en estas cuevas."

#. [scenario], id=24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:4
msgid "The Fires of Shray Tahl"
msgstr "Los Fuegos de Shray Tahl"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:89
msgid "Infiltrate Shray Tahl and kill Emperor Tarva Ghar"
msgstr "Infiltra Shray Tahl y mata al Emperador Tarva Ghar"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:117
msgid ""
"NOTE: If any unit enters the line of sight of an enemy unit, it will be "
"caught"
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Si alguna unidad entra en el campo de visión de una unidad enemiga, "
"será atrapada"

#. [side], type=Washraja
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:145
msgid "Emperor Tarva Ghar"
msgstr "Emperador Tarva Ghar"

#. [side], type=Washraja
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:150
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:105
msgid "Shray Tahl"
msgstr "Shray Tahl"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:323
msgid "You're late, you know..."
msgstr "Llegas tarde, sabes..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Sorry, we had some trouble in the caves... Did you have any problems in the "
"forest?"
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, tuvimos algunos problemas en las cuevas... ¿Tuvieron algún "
"problema en el bosque?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:331
msgid ""
"Other than our blood-drinker's blabbering about what the both of you could "
"be doing in the caves that delayed you so, it was quite a tranquil trip..."
msgstr ""
"Además de la charla de nuestra bebedora de sangre sobre lo que ustedes dos "
"podrían estar haciendo en las cuevas que los retrasó tanto, fue un viaje "
"bastante tranquilo..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:335
msgid "(blushing) You... Shut up, you...!"
msgstr "(sonrojándose) ¡Tú... Cállate, tú...!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:339
msgid ""
"Leaving that aside, I take it that the city we see down the valley is Shray "
"Tahl?"
msgstr ""
"Dejando eso de lado, supongo que la ciudad que vemos abajo en el valle es "
"Shray Tahl."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:343
msgid ""
"Yes; before you arrived, we were discussing ways of sneaking into the city. "
"It will be harder than I anticipated, I didn't think there'd be so many "
"guards around it with the Washraha sending armies all over Arajunna..."
msgstr ""
"Sí; antes de que llegaran, estábamos discutiendo formas de infiltrarnos en "
"la ciudad. Será más difícil de lo que anticipaba, no pensaba que habría "
"tantos guardias alrededor con los Washraha enviando ejércitos por toda "
"Arajunna..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:347
msgid ""
"And did you agree on a plan to do it? As far as I can see, it's completely "
"surrounded with well-guarded walls, there seems to be absolutely no breach "
"in their defences."
msgstr ""
"¿Y acordaron un plan para hacerlo? Hasta donde puedo ver, está completamente "
"rodeada por murallas bien custodiadas, parece que no hay absolutamente "
"ninguna brecha en sus defensas."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:351
msgid ""
"See those water ducts entering the city? That water comes from this mountain "
"in streams deep enough for our rangers to hide. Besides, those ducts go "
"through the whole city, including the Emperor's Fortress."
msgstr ""
"¿Ven esos conductos de agua que entran a la ciudad? Esa agua viene de esta "
"montaña en corrientes lo suficientemente profundas como para que nuestros "
"exploradores se escondan. Además, esos conductos atraviesan toda la ciudad, "
"incluyendo la Fortaleza del Emperador."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:355
msgid ""
"Furthermore, Nyx and I could sneak in wherever we wish, as long as she "
"remains hidden in my shadows."
msgstr ""
"Además, Nyx y yo podríamos infiltrarnos donde queramos, siempre y cuando "
"ella permanezca oculta en mis sombras."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:359
msgid ""
"Still, even if you take care, one of the patrolling guards may stumble on "
"you, or hear you. We must have a plan for the case one of us is caught."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, aunque tengan cuidado, uno de los guardias patrulleros podría "
"tropezar con ustedes o oírlos. Debemos tener un plan para el caso de que uno "
"de nosotros sea atrapado."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:363
msgid ""
"If that happens, we'll have to attack the city with our full force, thus "
"they'd hopefully be distracted long enough for the rangers, Mahyus and Nyx "
"to escape. In this case, you'd have to hurry and kill Emperor Tarva Ghar; "
"his death will stun the Washraha so much that they won't be able to mount a "
"coordinated counter-offensive."
msgstr ""
"Si eso sucede, tendremos que atacar la ciudad con toda nuestra fuerza, así "
"ellos hopefully se distraerán el tiempo suficiente para que los "
"exploradores, Mahyus y Nyx escapen. En ese caso, tendrían que apresurarse y "
"matar al Emperador Tarva Ghar; su muerte dejará tan aturdidos a los Washraha "
"que no podrán montar una contraofensiva coordinada."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:367
msgid ""
"I know we've discussed it before, but are you sure that killing their "
"emperor will really work?"
msgstr ""
"Sé que lo discutimos antes, pero ¿estás seguro de que matar a su emperador "
"realmente funcionará?"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:371
msgid ""
"The Washraha are extremely proud warriors, and so, without a leader whom "
"they see as superior enough to be obeyed, they won't follow anyone's orders. "
"Without their paramount leader, it's very likely that the lesser generals "
"will fall into disagreement over the next courses of action."
msgstr ""
"Los Washraha son guerreros extremadamente orgullosos y, por lo tanto, sin un "
"líder al que vean como lo suficientemente superior para obedecer, no "
"seguirán las órdenes de nadie. Sin su líder supremo, es muy probable que los "
"generales menores caigan en desacuerdo sobre los próximos cursos de acción."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:375
msgid ""
"Let's do it then... Mahyus, Nyx, you and the rangers go ahead, the rest of "
"us will remain hidden in the jungle watching everything."
msgstr ""
"Hagámoslo entonces... Mahyus, Nyx, tú y los exploradores vayan adelante, el "
"resto de nosotros permaneceremos escondidos en la selva observando todo."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:379
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:197
msgid "Got it..."
msgstr "Entendido…"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:403
msgid ""
"Bloody fang, what is going on here...? Warriors, there are intruders in the "
"city!"
msgstr ""
"¡Colmillo sangriento, qué está pasando aquí...?! ¡Guerreros, hay intrusos en "
"la ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Tarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:407
msgid ""
"Well, we have to praise their boldness for entering our city like this; most "
"weaklings of this continent would give their wives to stay far from it... "
"Quick, warriors, we can't let the intruders escape!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, tenemos que elogiar su audacia por entrar a nuestra ciudad de esta "
"forma; la mayoría de los debiluchos de este continente darían a sus esposas "
"para mantenerse lejos de ella... ¡Rápido, guerreros, no podemos dejar que "
"los intrusos escapen!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:411
msgid "Damn it, they're screaming something... I think someone was caught!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, están gritando algo... Creo que alguien fue atrapado!"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:415
msgid ""
"Then we have no choice but to attack them head on! I just hope they're able "
"to reach the emperor now..."
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces no tenemos otra opción que atacarlos de frente! Solo espero que "
"ahora puedan llegar hasta el emperador..."

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Father, I've got a bad feeling... Maybe you should summon more guards to "
"protect you this night..."
msgstr ""
"Padre, tengo un mal presentimiento... Quizás deberías convocar más guardias "
"para protegerte esta noche..."

#. [message], speaker=Tarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:453
msgid ""
"You behave like a puny Chomi, daughter; what are you afraid of? Could it be "
"the shadows of the night?"
msgstr ""
"Te comportas como un chomi insignificante, hija; ¿de qué tienes miedo? "
"¿Podrían ser las sombras de la noche?"

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:457
msgid ""
"Of course not, as I said, I've just got a bad feeling. For some reason, this "
"city doesn't feel safe tonight..."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que no, como dije, solo tengo un mal presentimiento. Por alguna "
"razón, esta ciudad no se siente segura esta noche..."

#. [message], speaker=Tarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:461
msgid ""
"And I say there's no reason to be like that. We're in the heart of the "
"Washrahan nation, surrounded by obedient warriors; it's not like we're going "
"to be invaded here, our Arajunnan neighbours don't have the guts to do that. "
"Now, calm yourself and behave like a proper Washrahan; it's bad enough that "
"you were born a female, keep shivering before shadows and not even the "
"children will respect you."
msgstr ""
"Y yo digo que no hay razón para ser así. Estamos en el corazón de la nación "
"washrahana, rodeados de guerreros obedientes; no es como si fuéramos a ser "
"invadidos aquí, nuestros vecinos de Arajunna no tienen el coraje para hacer "
"eso. Ahora, cálmate y compórtate como una washrahana adecuada; ya es "
"bastante malo que hayas nacido mujer, sigue temblando ante las sombras y ni "
"siquiera los niños te respetarán."

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:465
msgid "As you wish, father... (sigh)"
msgstr "Como desees, padre... (suspiro)"

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:479
msgid "FATHER!!!"
msgstr "¡PADRE!!!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:487
msgid ""
"How can it be... Emperor Tarva Ghar, killed at the very heart of our "
"greatest city?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo puede ser... El Emperador Tarva Ghar, asesinado en el mismo corazón de "
"nuestra ciudad más grande?!"

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:491
msgid ""
"(enraged) Curses on these treacherous weaklings...!!! Washraha, do not let "
"our emperor's death dishearten you! I have seen the assassin, it was one of "
"those disgusting Chomi who somehow sneaked into our city! Follow me, "
"warriors, and we shall descend the axe of vengeance upon all of the Chomi!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecida) ¡Maldición sobre estos traicioneros debiluchos...!!! ¡Washraha, "
"no dejen que la muerte de nuestro emperador los desanime! He visto al "
"asesino, ¡fue uno de esos asquerosos chomi que de alguna forma se infiltró "
"en nuestra ciudad! ¡Síganme, guerreros, y haremos descender el hacha de la "
"venganza sobre todos los chomi!"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:515
msgid ""
"Oh, that damn Sa-Tarva... That is bad, friends, the Washraha are rallying "
"around the emperor's daughter!"
msgstr ""
"Oh, esa maldita Sa-Tarva... Eso es malo, amigos, ¡los Washraha se están "
"reuniendo alrededor de la hija del emperador!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:519
msgid ""
"He had a daughter?! You knew that from the start and still you thought that "
"killing him would disorganize the Washraha?!"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Tenía una hija?! ¿Lo sabías desde el principio y aun así pensaste que "
"matarlo desorganizaría a los Washraha?"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:523
msgid ""
"Yes, I mean, Sa-Tarva is a woman, and the Washraha are not known for being "
"commanded by women! Never would I have thought that they'd ever rally to her!"
msgstr ""
"Sí, quiero decir, Sa-Tarva es una mujer, ¡y los Washraha no son conocidos "
"por ser comandados por mujeres! ¡Nunca habría pensado que alguna vez se "
"unirían a ella!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:527
msgid "It's no use to discuss that now, we must focus on rescuing our friends!"
msgstr ""
"No sirve de nada discutir eso ahora, ¡debemos enfocarnos en rescatar a "
"nuestros amigos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:538
msgid "Have all heroes at the initial camp"
msgstr "Reúne a todos los héroes en el campamento inicial"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:639
msgid "Well, that's what I call one astounding failure..."
msgstr "Bueno, eso es lo que yo llamo un fracaso asombroso..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:643
msgid ""
"There may still be hope that the emperor's death will divide their forces, "
"though; the warriors at Shray Tahl may have accepted Sa-Tarva as their "
"leader, but it's extremely unlikely that the leaders of the other cities "
"will do the same."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, puede que todavía haya esperanza de que la muerte del emperador "
"divida sus fuerzas; los guerreros en Shray Tahl pueden haber aceptado a Sa-"
"Tarva como su líder, pero es extremadamente improbable que los líderes de "
"las otras ciudades hagan lo mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:647
msgid "And what if they do?"
msgstr "¿Y si lo hacen?"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:651
msgid ""
"In this case, we'll be attacked by the Washrahan hordes just like we were "
"going to be from the beginning. Don't worry, though; the Seer and his people "
"have fulfilled their part on our agreement, which was killing the emperor, "
"and so they won't be requested to fight in any other battle."
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, seremos atacados por las hordas washrahanas tal como íbamos a "
"serlo desde el principio. No se preocupen, sin embargo; el Vidente y su "
"gente han cumplido su parte en nuestro acuerdo, que era matar al emperador, "
"y por eso no se les pedirá que luchen en ninguna otra batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:655
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, I'll feel bad if I go away with a fraction of your army when "
"you're about to suffer a massive enemy attack. Let's discuss it in Ifeh, "
"though, now we must go as far from Shray Tahl as we can!"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, me sentiré mal si me voy con una fracción de su ejército cuando "
"están a punto de sufrir un ataque masivo del enemigo. Discutámoslo en Ifeh, "
"aunque ahora debemos alejarnos lo más posible de Shray Tahl."

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:689
msgid ""
"Excellent! Our vassals of the east have answered our call, and come to our "
"aid! Now, we shall crush these sneaky, treacherous vermin where they stand!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente! ¡Nuestros vasallos del este han respondido a nuestro llamado y "
"han venido en nuestra ayuda! ¡Ahora aplastaremos a estos sigilosos y "
"traicioneros verminos donde se encuentran!"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/24_The_Fires_Of_Shray_Tahl.cfg:693
msgid ""
"Oh, damn it, they've received massive reinforcements! Even if we flee "
"through the jungle, we won't be able to escape them now!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, maldición, han recibido refuerzos masivos! ¡Incluso si huimos a través "
"de la selva, no podremos escapar de ellos ahora!"

#. [scenario], id=25_Blazing_Hatred
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:4
msgid "Blazing Hatred"
msgstr "Odio Ardiente"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:36
msgid "Kill $units_to_slay Washrahan warriors to repel Sa-Tarva's army"
msgstr ""
"Mata a $units_to_slay guerreros Washrahanos para repeler al ejército de Sa-"
"Tarva"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:40
msgid ""
"NOTE: During daytime in this scenario, living units will suffer the effects "
"of the land's heat, suffering dehydration and losing 1 HP per turn unless "
"treated by healers. Staying inside a castle, village, keep or in water will "
"nullify the dehydration's effects."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Durante el día en este escenario, las unidades vivas sufrirán los "
"efectos del calor de la tierra, padeciendo deshidratación y perdiendo 1 PV "
"por turno a menos que sean tratadas por sanadores. Permanecer dentro de un "
"castillo, aldea, torreón o en el agua anulará los efectos de la "
"deshidratación."

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:64
msgid "Death of Father Orun"
msgstr "Muerte del Padre Orun"

#. [side], type=Washraja
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:100
msgid "Humri"
msgstr "Humri"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:128
msgid "Ifeh"
msgstr "Ifeh"

#. [side], type=Washraha Jackal Warrior
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:146
msgid "Accalu"
msgstr "Accalu"

#. [side], type=Washraha Jackal Warrior
#. [side], type=Washraha Lightning Striker
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:151
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:177
msgid "Sa-Tarva's Armies"
msgstr "Ejércitos de Sa-Tarva"

#. [side], type=Washraha Lightning Striker
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:172
msgid "Badari"
msgstr "Badari"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:260
msgid ""
"What did you say about her not managing to unite the Washrahan generals "
"under her lead, Olufemi?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué dijiste sobre que ella no lograría unir a los generales Washrahanos "
"bajo su mando, Olufemi?"

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:264
msgid ""
"I am frankly disappointed, Chomi; I expected you to have prepared a stronger "
"force, so that this fight would be minimally exciting, but you seem to have "
"underestimated me, just as all those foolish generals of mine did... Get a "
"hold of your weapons, weaklings, for I shall teach you what a grave mistake "
"you've committed!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy francamente decepcionada, chomi; esperaba que hubieran preparado una "
"fuerza más fuerte, para que esta pelea fuera mínimamente emocionante, pero "
"parece que me han subestimado, igual que todos esos generales tontos míos... "
"¡Tomen sus armas, debiluchos, porque les enseñaré qué grave error han "
"cometido!"

#. [message], speaker=Orun
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:268
msgid ""
"She truly knew the right moment to attack us; because of this heat wave, the "
"swamps surrounding Ifeh have mostly dried out and become solid ground, which "
"the Washraha favour and where we're at disadvantage..."
msgstr ""
"Ella realmente supo el momento exacto para atacarnos; por esta ola de calor, "
"los pantanos que rodean Ifeh se han secado casi por completo y se han "
"convertido en terreno sólido, que los Washraha prefieren y donde estamos en "
"desventaja..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:272
msgid ""
"Worry not, Father Orun, though this is no longer our fight, my people and I "
"shall stay and help you defend your city. We would never forgive ourselves "
"if we abandoned you in a moment of such need."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, Padre Orun, aunque esta ya no sea nuestra lucha, mi gente y "
"yo nos quedaremos y te ayudaremos a defender tu ciudad. Nunca nos "
"perdonaríamos si te abandonáramos en un momento de tanta necesidad."

#. [message], speaker=Orun
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:276
msgid ""
"I am profoundly grateful for your assistance, Seer; with you and your "
"warriors by our side, we may stand a chance against Sa-Tarva's armies!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy profundamente agradecido por su ayuda, Vidente; con ustedes y sus "
"guerreros a nuestro lado, podemos tener una oportunidad contra los ejércitos "
"de Sa-Tarva."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:280
msgid "(smirking) Oh, yeah, this is going to be fun..."
msgstr "(sonriendo burlonamente) Oh, sí, esto va a ser divertido..."

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:284
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:230
msgid ""
"That's the spirit, friends! Now, let us honour Sa-Tarva by sending her "
"forces back to whence they came with all we've got!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ese es el espíritu, amigos! ¡Ahora honremos a Sa-Tarva enviando sus fuerzas "
"de regreso de donde vinieron con todo lo que tenemos!"

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Humri, you stay and organize the warriors as they prepare to battle; I shall "
"fight at the forefront of our armies!"
msgstr ""
"Humri, tú quédate y organiza a los guerreros mientras se preparan para la "
"batalla; ¡yo lucharé en la vanguardia de nuestros ejércitos!"

#. [message], speaker=Humri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:306
msgid "Our empress is badly wounded! Men, cover her as she retreats!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nuestra emperatriz está gravemente herida! ¡Hombres, cúbranla mientras se "
"retira!"

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:310
msgid "Damn it...! Keep on fighting, warriors, I shall return soon!"
msgstr "¡Maldición...! ¡Sigan luchando, guerreros, regresaré pronto!"

#. [message], speaker=Humri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:340
msgid ""
"My Empress, these Chomi and their foreign allies are proving to be much "
"tougher than we expected! If we continue this battle any further, our forces "
"will be too depleted for another campaign!"
msgstr ""
"Mi Emperatriz, ¡estos chomi y sus aliados extranjeros están resultando mucho "
"más duros de lo que esperábamos! ¡Si continuamos esta batalla por más "
"tiempo, nuestras fuerzas quedarán demasiado debilitadas para otra campaña!"

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:344
msgid ""
"You're right... Washraha, this battle is not faring in our favour, so let's "
"retreat for now!"
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón... Washraha, esta batalla no nos está favoreciendo, ¡así que "
"retirémonos por ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Satarva
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:348
msgid ""
"Mark my words, Chomi, this is not the last time you will see me; you've only "
"managed to survive because of your new friends, but when they're no longer "
"by your side, you shall fall before our blades as easily as you've always "
"fallen!"
msgstr ""
"Recuerden mis palabras, chomi, esta no es la última vez que me verán; solo "
"han logrado sobrevivir gracias a sus nuevos amigos, pero cuando ya no estén "
"a su lado, ¡caerán ante nuestras espadas tan fácilmente como siempre han "
"caído!"

#. [message], speaker=Orun
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:355
msgid ""
"We owe you an even greater debt now, Seer. It doesn't please me to admit "
"this, but Sa-Tarva spoke the truth – but do not worry about us any further; "
"you have your own war to fight and your own homeland to defend, and so I "
"would not delay you any more. Take our men and ship and return safely to "
"your country; I hope you are victorious in your future battles just as you "
"were in those you fought on our continent."
msgstr ""
"Ahora te debemos una deuda aún mayor, Vidente. No me agrada admitir esto, "
"pero Sa-Tarva dijo la verdad, pero no se preocupen más por nosotros; ustedes "
"tienen su propia guerra que luchar y su propia patria que defender, y por "
"eso no los retrasaré más. Tomen a nuestros hombres y el barco y regresen a "
"salvo a su país; espero que sean victoriosos en sus futuras batallas tal "
"como lo fueron en las que lucharon en nuestro continente."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:359
msgid ""
"And I promise you that we shall not forget how you aided us, Master Orun. "
"When we rid Maat'Kare of the evil threatening it, we shall send heralds "
"here, so that our countries may be friends. I also promise to lead your "
"Chomi as well as I can, and to take them safely back home when our war is "
"over."
msgstr ""
"Y te prometo que no olvidaremos cómo nos ayudaste, Maestro Orun. Cuando "
"liberemos a Maat'Kare del mal que la amenaza, enviaremos heraldos aquí para "
"que nuestros países puedan ser amigos. También prometo liderar a tus chomi "
"lo mejor que pueda y llevarlos de regreso a salvo a casa cuando nuestra "
"guerra termine."

#. [unit], id=Akinsanya, type=Chomi Priest
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:369
msgid "Akinsanya"
msgstr "Akinsanya"

#. [message], speaker=Akinsanya
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:382
msgid ""
"High Priest, apologies for my boldness, but I want to follow the Seer as "
"well. He did us a great service today, and we can't repay him as we should, "
"so I'd like to go and pay our people's debt with my own powers."
msgstr ""
"Sumo Sacerdote, disculpa mi audacia, pero yo también quiero seguir al "
"Vidente. Hoy nos prestó un gran servicio y no podemos pagárselo como "
"deberíamos, así que me gustaría ir y pagar la deuda de nuestro pueblo con "
"mis propios poderes."

#. [message], speaker=Orun
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:386
msgid ""
"You're an honourable priest, Akinsanya; I allow you to go – and not only "
"that: I wish you to take your pupils with you. Our magic may not be as grand "
"as that of the Seer and his people, but it may still be of use to him."
msgstr ""
"Eres un sacerdote honorable, Akinsanya; te permito ir, y no solo eso: deseo "
"que lleves a tus alumnos contigo. Nuestra magia puede que no sea tan "
"grandiosa como la del Vidente y su gente, pero aún puede serle útil."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:390
msgid ""
"Certainly it will, Master Orun. I'm grateful to you and to noble Akinsanya "
"for such aid."
msgstr ""
"Seguro que sí lo será, Maestro Orun. Estoy agradecido contigo y con el noble "
"Akinsanya por tal ayuda."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:394
msgid "Now Akhen may also recruit Chomi Adepts"
msgstr "Ahora Akhen también puede reclutar Adeptos Chomi"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:404
msgid ""
"At long last we're leaving this scorching realm! I can barely wait to see my "
"precious snowy mountains again..."
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin estamos dejando este reino abrasador! Apenas puedo esperar a ver de "
"nuevo mis preciosas montañas nevadas..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:409
msgid ""
"I'm also anxious to finally meet your fair homeland and all its fabulous "
"mysteries – along with Mahyus, of course!"
msgstr ""
"También estoy ansiosa por conocer finalmente tu hermosa patria y todos sus "
"fabulosos misterios, ¡junto con Mahyus, por supuesto!"

#. [message], speaker=Olufemi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:422
msgid "Farewell, friends! It was an honour to fight alongside you!"
msgstr "¡Adiós, amigos! ¡Fue un honor luchar junto a ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:426
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:436
msgid ""
"The honour was ours, friend. Now, all aboard! We've remained away from our "
"homeland for far too long!"
msgstr ""
"El honor fue nuestro, amigo. ¡Ahora, todos a bordo! ¡Hemos estado lejos de "
"nuestra patria por demasiado tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Orun
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:432
msgid "Farewell, young friends! It was an honour to fight alongside you!"
msgstr "¡Adiós, jóvenes amigos! ¡Fue un honor luchar junto a ustedes!"

#. [print]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:455
msgid "Still $units_to_slay Washraha warriors to defeat!"
msgstr "¡Todavía quedan $units_to_slay guerreros Washraha por derrotar!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:476
msgid ""
"Rest in peace, friend, for we shall not let your city fall today. Come on, "
"friends, we have to avenge Olufemi!"
msgstr ""
"Descansa en paz, amigo, porque hoy no dejaremos que tu ciudad caiga. ¡Vamos, "
"amigos, tenemos que vengar a Olufemi!"

#. [message], speaker=Orun
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:487
msgid ""
"I now go join the great gods and our ancestors... Please, do not let our "
"city fall..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora voy a unirme a los grandes dioses y a nuestros ancestros... Por favor, "
"no dejen que nuestra ciudad caiga..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/25_Blazing_Hatred.cfg:491
msgid "Damn it! Without Orun, Ifeh is too defenceless!"
msgstr "¡Maldición! ¡Sin Orun, Ifeh está demasiado indefensa!"

#. [scenario], id=26_Cradle_Of_Darkness
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:4
msgid "Cradle of Darkness"
msgstr "Cuna de la Oscuridad"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:34
msgid "Explore the island"
msgstr "Explorar la isla"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:58
msgid ""
"There's a chance that it may not be a good idea to remain at the keep for "
"long..."
msgstr ""
"Hay una posibilidad de que no sea una buena idea permanecer en el torreón "
"por mucho tiempo..."

#. [side], type=Priest SK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:112
msgid "Aglaia"
msgstr "Aglaia"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:206
msgid ""
"You seemed so eager to see Netjer-Ta again just a few hours ago, only to "
"land on the first beach you find..."
msgstr ""
"Parecías tan ansioso por ver Netjer-Ta de nuevo hace solo unas horas, solo "
"para aterrizar en la primera playa que encuentras..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:210
msgid ""
"I <i>am</i> eager to return home, but the fact is that this ship is not "
"prepared for such a long sea trip; we must repair it and replenish our "
"provisions on this land, else we'll starve before even sighting Cape "
"Atargatis."
msgstr ""
"<i>Sí</i> estoy ansioso por regresar a casa, pero el hecho es que este barco "
"no está preparado para un viaje marítimo tan largo; debemos repararlo y "
"reponer nuestras provisiones en esta tierra, o moriremos de hambre antes de "
"siquiera avistar el Cabo Atargatis."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:214
msgid ""
"You're right... Are you Chomi sure that you've never seen this land before?"
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón... ¿Ustedes los chomi están seguros de que nunca habían visto "
"esta tierra antes?"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:218
msgid ""
"We are, lady. Besides Arajunna and the Green Isle, we only know a few tiny "
"island scattered over the ocean, none of them as large as this one."
msgstr ""
"Lo estamos, señora. Además de Arajunna y la Isla Verde, solo conocemos unas "
"pocas islas diminutas esparcidas por el océano, ninguna tan grande como esta."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:222
msgid "Who knows, we might even have reached Argea by mistake..."
msgstr "Quién sabe, quizás hasta hayamos llegado a Argea por error..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Don't even joke about that, Nyx! Anyway, I think we should explore this "
"island while the Chomi repair the ship; we could even find a new weapon or "
"ally here."
msgstr ""
"Ni siquiera bromees con eso, Nyx! De todos modos, creo que deberíamos "
"explorar esta isla mientras los chomi reparan el barco; incluso podríamos "
"encontrar un arma nueva o un aliado aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:247
msgid "*sniff* Um, watch out, friends, I smell humans nearby..."
msgstr "*olfatea* Um, tengan cuidado, amigos, huelo humanos cerca..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:251
msgid ""
"Good! Now, if I may say, we must send a messenger there, to announce our "
"arrival, else they may deem us demons seeking to conquer them."
msgstr ""
"¡Bien! Ahora, si se me permite decirlo, debemos enviar un mensajero allí "
"para anunciar nuestra llegada, o podrían considerarnos demonios que buscan "
"conquistarlos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:285
msgid ""
"Ahem! People who live on this fair island, please heed me. I come in the "
"name of..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ahem! Gente que vive en esta bella isla, por favor escúchenme. Vengo en "
"nombre de..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:303
msgid "Oh, no... No way, no damn way..."
msgstr "Oh, no... De ninguna manera, de ninguna maldita manera..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:307
msgid "What's wrong?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:311
msgid "Those flags... Please, tell me I'm wrong, but they look awfully like..."
msgstr ""
"Esas banderas... Por favor, dime que estoy equivocado, pero se parecen "
"terriblemente a..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:315
msgid ""
"<i>Skiron's flags</i>!!! By the Gods of Light, have we really come to "
"<i>Skiron</i>, out of all places?!"
msgstr ""
"¡¡¡<i>¡Las banderas de Skiron</i>!!! ¡Por los Dioses de la Luz, ¿realmente "
"hemos llegado a <i>Skiron</i>, de todos los lugares posibles?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:319
msgid ""
"(alarmed) Folks, quietly now... Let's return to our camp, raise the anchor "
"and leave this place before they can notice..."
msgstr ""
"(alarmado) Gente, en silencio ahora... Regresemos a nuestro campamento, "
"levanten el ancla y dejemos este lugar antes de que nos noten..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:323
msgid "Except that they have found us already..."
msgstr "Excepto que ya nos han encontrado..."

#. [unit], id=Odysseis, type=General SK
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:335
msgid "Odysseis"
msgstr "Odysseis"

#. [message], speaker=Acates
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:367
msgid ""
"Look, captain, there's a strange ship docked on the southern beach! Could it "
"be a Maat'Karian vessel?"
msgstr ""
"¡Miren, capitán, hay un barco extraño atracado en la playa sur! ¿Podría ser "
"un barco maat'kariano?"

#. [message], speaker=Odysseis
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:371
msgid ""
"No, their ships are not like this one... Nevertheless, that doesn't change "
"the fact that some foreigner has intruded on our territory, probably not "
"long ago. Quick, search all over the peninsula and find the invaders before "
"they can escape – or worse, before Lord Caror is disturbed by them!"
msgstr ""
"No, sus barcos no son como este... Sin embargo, eso no cambia el hecho de "
"que algún extranjero ha invadido nuestro territorio, probablemente no hace "
"mucho. ¡Rápido, busquen por toda la península y encuentren a los invasores "
"antes de que puedan escapar, o peor, antes de que el señor Caror sea "
"molestado por ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:375
msgid ""
"My, my... Folks, right now there is a ship's crew coming for us, and they've "
"already sent word of our presence here. Also, this region is not an island, "
"but a peninsula. Ah, and it seems like we've arrived on the lands ruled by "
"our old Lich-Lord acquaintance, Caror of Aionian."
msgstr ""
"Vaya, vaya... Gente, justo ahora viene una tripulación de barco hacia "
"nosotros y ya han enviado aviso de nuestra presencia aquí. Además, esta "
"región no es una isla, sino una península. Ah, y parece que hemos llegado a "
"las tierras gobernadas por nuestro viejo conocido Señor Liche, Caror de "
"Aionian."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:379
msgid ""
"(angry) Of all lands on this vast planet, we had to arrive on the only one "
"we shouldn't... Well, we have no time to complain of our bad fortune; since "
"the sea is lost, we have nowhere to go but the north. Let's try to avoid "
"that city, and not be seen by anyone..."
msgstr ""
"(enojado) De todas las tierras en este vasto planeta, teníamos que llegar "
"precisamente a la única que no debíamos... Bueno, no tenemos tiempo para "
"quejarnos de nuestra mala suerte; como el mar está perdido, no tenemos a "
"dónde ir más que al norte. Intentemos evitar esa ciudad y no ser vistos por "
"nadie..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:383
msgid ""
"Akhen, I can see a high mountain in the distance; if we can reach it, we may "
"use the higher ground for our advantage, in the very likely case of us being "
"sighted and attacked. I know it won't help us for long, but..."
msgstr ""
"Akhen, puedo ver una montaña alta a lo lejos; si logramos llegar a ella, "
"podemos usar el terreno elevado a nuestro favor, en el muy probable caso de "
"que seamos avistados y atacados. Sé que no nos ayudará por mucho tiempo, "
"pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:387
msgid ""
"...Still, that's our best option right now, I know. Besides, there's the "
"possibility that there's an entrance to those Motsoghnir tunnels of Argea on "
"that mountain."
msgstr ""
"...Aun así, esa es nuestra mejor opción ahora mismo, lo sé. Además, existe "
"la posibilidad de que haya una entrada a esos túneles Motsoghnir de Argea en "
"esa montaña."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:391
msgid ""
"Or we could convince them to let us pass by simply blasting away as many "
"Skironians as we can; with our current power, I doubt a small city like this "
"one would manage to stand against us..."
msgstr ""
"O podríamos convencerlos de dejarnos pasar simplemente destruyendo a tantos "
"skironianos como podamos; con nuestro poder actual, dudo que una ciudad "
"pequeña como esta logre resistirnos..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:397
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:540
msgid "Kill $units_to_slay Skironian soldiers to be able to escape"
msgstr "Mata a $units_to_slay soldados skironianos para poder escapar"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:402
msgid "Reach the mountain to the north"
msgstr "Llega a la montaña del norte"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:426
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:564
msgid "Akhen may recruit/recall from hex 19,5"
msgstr "Akhen puede reclutar o reincorporar desde el hexágono 19,5"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:459
msgid ""
"Found them! They're not in great numbers, but they seem quite well-armed and "
"battle-hardened; it's probably best to ask for Lord Caror's aid..."
msgstr ""
"¡Los encontramos! No son muchos, pero parecen bastante bien armados y "
"endurecidos en batalla; probablemente sea mejor pedir ayuda al señor Caror..."

#. [message], speaker={LEADER_ID}
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:463
msgid ""
"And let him know that we failed to defend Aionian's shores, you fool?I don't "
"care if they're strong or Maat'Karians, just capture them before..."
msgstr ""
"¿Y dejarle saber que fallamos en defender las costas de Aionian, idiota? No "
"me importa si son fuertes o maat'karianos, solo captúrenlos antes de..."

#. [message], speaker=Caror
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:467
msgid ""
"...Before I learn of what is going on, {LEADER_NAME}? You foolish brat, "
"there's nothing that goes around my land that I'm not aware of, as you "
"should well know!"
msgstr ""
"...¿Antes de que yo me entere de lo que está pasando, {LEADER_NAME}? Eres un "
"mocoso tonto, no hay nada que ocurra en mi tierra de lo que yo no esté al "
"tanto, ¡como deberías saber muy bien!"

#. [message], speaker={LEADER_ID}
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:471
msgid "P-pardon my foolishness, m-milord..."
msgstr "P-perdona mi estupidez, m-mi señor..."

#. [message], speaker=Caror
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:475
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, I'm actually pleased that you have failed to block these "
"invaders; thus I will have the pleasure of having my revenge for the "
"humiliation I suffered in the Red Pinnacle... Or did you think that I would "
"forget that, young Maat'Karians?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, en realidad me alegra que hayan fallado en bloquear a estos "
"invasores; así tendré el placer de vengarme por la humillación que sufrí en "
"la Cumbre Roja... ¿O pensaron que olvidaría eso, jóvenes maat'karianos?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:479
msgid ""
"I have long learned not to doubt the madness and hatefulness of a Skironian "
"Lich Lord, Caror."
msgstr ""
"Hace mucho aprendí a no dudar de la locura y el odio de un Señor Liche "
"skironio, Caror."

#. [message], speaker=Caror
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:483
msgid ""
"(enraged) And you dare mock me still, puny brats? You may have bested me "
"when I was far from my home troops, on foreign and unknown soil and "
"surrounded by treacherous allies, but you're on my domain now! Feel "
"honoured, Maat'Karians, for your grave shall be the fair fields of my noble "
"Aionian!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecido) ¿Y aún te atreves a burlarte de mí, mocosos insignificantes? "
"Pueden haberme vencido cuando estaba lejos de mis tropas natales, en suelo "
"extranjero y desconocido y rodeado de aliados traicioneros, ¡pero ahora "
"están en mi dominio! ¡Siéntanse honrados, maat'karianos, porque su tumba "
"serán los hermosos campos de mi noble Aionian!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:487
msgid ""
"Let's stick to our plan, folks; let's try and get past Aionian and reach the "
"mountain, and then hold off Caror's army. He's powerful, but not a bright "
"tactician, so, if we make him mad enough, he'll probably send his full "
"forces against us even if we have the higher ground."
msgstr ""
"Adhirámonos a nuestro plan, gente; intentemos pasar Aionian y llegar a la "
"montaña, y luego contener al ejército de Caror. Es poderoso, pero no un "
"táctico brillante, así que, si lo enfurecemos lo suficiente, probablemente "
"enviará todas sus fuerzas contra nosotros incluso si tenemos el terreno "
"elevado."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:491
msgid ""
"And, when we destroy the brunt of his forces, we take the chance to flee, is "
"that right?"
msgstr ""
"Y cuando destruyamos la mayor parte de sus fuerzas, aprovechamos la "
"oportunidad para huir, ¿es eso correcto?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:495
msgid ""
"Yes; I still don't know where we should run, but, like in this dense mist, "
"we can only see a few steps at a time."
msgstr ""
"Sí; todavía no sé hacia dónde deberíamos correr, pero, como en esta niebla "
"densa, solo podemos ver unos pocos pasos a la vez."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:499
msgid "(chuckling) Oh yeah, tis' going to be thrilling..."
msgstr "(riendo) Oh sí, esto va a ser emocionante..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:503
msgid "(grinning) Agreed..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) De acuerdo..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:507
msgid "They really were made one for the other, weren't they?"
msgstr "Realmente fueron hechos el uno para el otro, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:534
msgid ""
"Good, now let's build our defences quickly and destroy Caror's minions until "
"he gives up pestering us!"
msgstr ""
"Bien, ahora construyamos nuestras defensas rápido y destruyamos a los "
"minions de Caror hasta que se dé por vencido de molestarnos."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:592
msgid ""
"We're managing to wear out Caror's forces! Are you sure that we must flee, "
"Akhen? If we push forward, we may even be able to destroy the Lich-Lord and "
"take his city!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estamos logrando desgastar las fuerzas de Caror! ¿Estás seguro de que "
"debemos huir, Akhen? Si avanzamos, ¡quizás hasta podamos destruir al Señor "
"Liche y tomar su ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:596
msgid ""
"That's a tempting plan, but there's no advantage in taking Aionian; it'll do "
"us no good to settle in a fortress, since we must reach Netjer-Ta, and it "
"won't protect us against larger Skironian armies. Fighting Caror is one "
"thing, but fighting the likes of Jevyan and Aegaion is a completely "
"different matter..."
msgstr ""
"Ese es un plan tentador, pero no hay ventaja en tomar Aionian; no nos "
"servirá de nada establecernos en una fortaleza, ya que debemos llegar a "
"Netjer-Ta, y no nos protegerá contra ejércitos skironianos más grandes. "
"Luchar contra Caror es una cosa, pero luchar contra gente como Jevyan y "
"Aegaion es un asunto completamente diferente..."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:618
msgid "Wise words, lad."
msgstr "Palabras sabias, muchacho."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:622
msgid "Thanks, frie- Wait, what?!"
msgstr "Gracias, ami- ¡Espera, ¿qué?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:626
msgid "Akhen, stay back! And you, hairy creature, prepare to meet your fate..."
msgstr ""
"¡Akhen, quédate atrás! Y tú, criatura peluda, prepárate para encontrar tu "
"destino..."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:630
msgid ""
"Wait, wait, I'm no foe, I'm your friend! I'd've killed you a thousand times "
"already if I wished so!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, espera, no soy enemigo, soy tu amigo! ¡Ya los habría matado mil "
"veces si así lo quisiera!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:634
msgid ""
"Wait, Nyx, let him speak at least. Tell us, who are you, what people do you "
"belong to, and what do you want with us?"
msgstr ""
"Espera, Nyx, déjalo hablar al menos. Dinos, ¿quién eres, a qué pueblo "
"perteneces y qué quieres con nosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:638
msgid ""
"My name is Volturnus, I'm a faun from Heartwood Valley, and by the First, I "
"swear that I'm a friend! I was just passing by, peeking at the cursed "
"Skironians, when I saw you fighting them so skilfully, and I thought to "
"myself, 'could they be the famed Maat'Karian humans of the Fairy Continent?' "
"Then I decided that I should talk to you, so that together we may find a way "
"to bring down the enemy that we both hate."
msgstr ""
"Mi nombre es Volturnus, soy un fauno del Valle del Bosque Profundo, y por el "
"Primero juro que soy un amigo. Solo pasaba por aquí, espiando a los malditos "
"skironianos, cuando los vi luchando contra ellos con tanta habilidad, y "
"pensé para mí mismo: «¿podrían ser los famosos humanos maat'karianos del "
"Continente de las Hadas?». Entonces decidí que debía hablar con ustedes, "
"para que juntos encontremos una forma de derribar al enemigo que ambos "
"odiamos."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:642
msgid ""
"And can we really trust you? Our people's scrolls never mention the "
"existence of these 'fauns' in Argea; who can guarantee that you're not "
"actually an aberration created by Skironian magic and sent to trick us?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y podemos realmente confiar en ti? Los pergaminos de nuestra gente nunca "
"mencionan la existencia de estos «faunos» en Argea; ¿quién puede garantizar "
"que no seas en realidad una aberración creada por magia skironia y enviada "
"para engañarnos?"

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:646
msgid ""
"Now that's rude, lad; my people is an ancient one, dwellers of this "
"continent since the dawn of time, fond of secrecy and wardens of nature! To "
"think that we're dirty spawns of those lowly humans... No offence intended, "
"though."
msgstr ""
"Eso es grosero, muchacho; mi pueblo es uno antiguo, habitantes de este "
"continente desde el amanecer de los tiempos, aficionados al secreto y "
"guardianes de la naturaleza. Pensar que somos sucios engendros de esos "
"humanos inferiores... Sin ofender, sin embargo."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:650
msgid ""
"You speak of the 'First' and call your folk 'wardens of nature'; in a "
"faraway island, I met a being who also mentioned this 'First', and who also "
"called his folk wardens of nature."
msgstr ""
"Hablas del «Primero» y llamas a tu pueblo «guardianes de la naturaleza»; en "
"una isla lejana conocí a un ser que también mencionó este «Primero» y que "
"también llamó a su pueblo guardianes de la naturaleza."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:654
msgid ""
"Aye, you must have met a wose; they're the only ones I can think of who "
"would've said those things."
msgstr ""
"Sí, debes haber conocido a un wose; son los únicos en los que puedo pensar "
"que habrían dicho esas cosas."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:658
msgid ""
"(surprised) I see... Folks, I think these fauns can be trusted; like the "
"fairies and the woses, they only dislike those who destroy or corrupt the "
"environment, and so I don't think they'll be hostile towards us."
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) Ya veo... Gente, creo que estos faunos pueden ser de "
"confianza; como las hadas y los woses, solo les desagradan aquellos que "
"destruyen o corrompen el medio ambiente, y por eso no creo que sean hostiles "
"hacia nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:662
msgid ""
"And you've arrived at this conclusion because they're like the fairies who "
"hate humans and the woses who tried to purge the Green Isle of them?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y has llegado a esta conclusión porque son como las hadas que odian a los "
"humanos y los woses que intentaron purgar la Isla Verde de ellos?"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:666
msgid ""
"And, in case you've forgotten, my arts are exactly what is widely considered "
"as corruption of nature."
msgstr ""
"Y, en caso de que lo hayas olvidado, mis artes son exactamente lo que se "
"considera ampliamente como corrupción de la naturaleza."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:670
msgid ""
"Aye, I've noticed that you use un-living aberrations to fight for you, just "
"as the Skironians do. However, if a friend-of-nature like this young lad "
"accepts you amongst his comrades, then you must know how to use your evil "
"powers for good goals. See, we fauns are not narrow-minded like woses and "
"fairies, we know that even an evil can be wielded for a worthy end."
msgstr ""
"Sí, he notado que usas aberraciones no vivientes para luchar por ti, igual "
"que los skironianos. Sin embargo, si un amigo de la naturaleza como este "
"joven muchacho te acepta entre sus compañeros, entonces debes saber cómo "
"usar tus poderes malignos para fines dignos. Verán, nosotros los faunos no "
"somos de mente estrecha como los woses y las hadas, sabemos que incluso un "
"mal puede ser utilizado para un fin valioso."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:674
msgid ""
"Well, I don't think we have many alternatives; we're stranded on the land of "
"Skironians and orcs, we shouldn't shun anyone who offers a friendly hand."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no creo que tengamos muchas alternativas; estamos varados en la "
"tierra de skironianos y orcos, no deberíamos rechazar a nadie que ofrezca "
"una mano amiga."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:678
msgid ""
"True... Volturnus, we'll follow you to your people's home and hear what you "
"have to say. However, I must inform you that we can't fight Skiron right "
"now, for we must free our own nation from another foe. However, if you help "
"us, I give you my word that, when we're done with our war, I shall "
"personally meet you again and help you in yours."
msgstr ""
"Cierto... Volturnus, te seguiremos a la casa de tu pueblo y escucharemos lo "
"que tienes que decir. Sin embargo, debo informarte que no podemos luchar "
"contra Skiron ahora mismo, porque debemos liberar a nuestra propia nación de "
"otro enemigo. Sin embargo, si nos ayudas, te doy mi palabra de que, cuando "
"terminemos nuestra guerra, me reuniré personalmente contigo de nuevo y te "
"ayudaré en la tuya."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Fair enough. So, let's leave that foolish Skironian beast with his tantrums "
"and head for the fair Heartwood Valley!"
msgstr ""
"Bastante justo. Entonces, ¡dejemos a esa bestia skironia tonta con sus "
"rabietas y dirijámonos al hermoso Valle del Bosque Profundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Caror
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:686
msgid ""
"(enraged) YOU DAMN MAAT'KARIANS, GET BACK HERE AND FACE ME! I'M NOT DONE "
"WITH YOU YET, COWARDS!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecido) ¡USTEDES MALDITOS MAAT'KARIANOS, REGRESEN AQUÍ Y ENFRÉNTENME! "
"¡AÚN NO HE TERMINADO CON USTEDES, COBARDES!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:690
msgid "Goodbye to you too, lich..."
msgstr "Adiós a ti también, liche..."

#. [print]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:701
msgid "Still $units_to_slay Skironian soldiers to defeat!"
msgstr "¡Todavía quedan $units_to_slay soldados skironianos por derrotar!"

#. [message], speaker=Caror
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:715
msgid ""
"Argh, as much as I hate to admit it, I won't manage to defeat these "
"Maat'Karians, not with my currently depleted army... Aglaia, go north and "
"warn Jevyan that I' in need of aid!"
msgstr ""
"Argh, por más que odie admitirlo, no lograré derrotar a estos maat'karianos, "
"no con mi ejército actualmente debilitado... ¡Aglaia, ve al norte y advierte "
"a Jevyan que necesito ayuda!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/26_Cradle_Of_Darkness.cfg:719
msgid ""
"Oh, no! We won't be able to fight Caror and Jevyan at once! This is our end!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, no! ¡No podremos luchar contra Caror y Jevyan al mismo tiempo! ¡Este es "
"nuestro fin!"

#. [scenario], id=27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:4
msgid "The Folk of the Forest"
msgstr "El Pueblo del Bosque"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:26
msgid "Help Aferius defeat all enemies in the region"
msgstr "Ayuda a Aferius a derrotar a todos los enemigos en la región"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:50
msgid "Death of Volturnus"
msgstr "Muerte de Volturnus"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:54
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:49
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:428
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:639
msgid "Death of Aferius"
msgstr "Muerte de Aferius"

#. [side], type=Orcish Warlord
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:90
msgid "Pragdush"
msgstr "Pragdush"

#. [side], type=Orcish Warlord
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:95
msgid "Orcs"
msgstr "Orcos"

#. [side], type=Minotaur Overlord
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:113
msgid "Rhadathus"
msgstr "Rhadathus"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:136
msgid "Fauns"
msgstr "Faunos"

#. [side], type=Warrior Carapace
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:152
msgid "Krakus"
msgstr "Krakus"

#. [side], type=Warrior Carapace
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:156
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:153
msgid "Carapace"
msgstr "Caparazón"

#. [side], type=Gryphon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:170
msgid "Kzuuu"
msgstr "Kzuuu"

#. [side], type=Gryphon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:174
msgid "Gryphons"
msgstr "Grifos"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Ah, orcs and minotaurs... I never thought I'd ever say that, but I kind of "
"missed them."
msgstr ""
"Ah, orcos y minotauros... Nunca pensé que diría esto, pero en cierto modo "
"los extrañaba."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:256
msgid "So did I, specially as we were fighting those monstrous Deshrai..."
msgstr ""
"Yo también, especialmente cuando luchábamos contra esos monstruosos "
"Deshrai..."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:260
msgid ""
"Don't worry, they're always coming around this region to try and build new "
"settlements for themselves, but they're never much more than a nuisance for "
"us fauns, who have to repel them in order to keep our home a secret haven. "
"Look, there goes Aferius and his warriors..."
msgstr ""
"No se preocupen, siempre vienen a esta región para intentar construir nuevos "
"asentamientos para ellos, pero nunca son mucho más que una molestia para "
"nosotros los faunos, que tenemos que rechazarlos para mantener nuestro hogar "
"como un refugio secreto. Miren, ahí va Aferius y sus guerreros..."

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:264
msgid ""
"C'mon, warriors, time for cleansing this valley once ag... Wait, Volturnus, "
"is that you?"
msgstr ""
"¡Vamos, guerreros, es hora de limpiar este valle una vez más... Espera, "
"Volturnus, ¿eres tú?"

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:268
msgid ""
"Aye, friend, and I come with good news for the Wardens. These humans here "
"are Maat'Karians from the Fairy Continent, enemies to the Skironians just as "
"we are, and so they're willing to help us rid our land from their evil!"
msgstr ""
"Sí, amigo, y vengo con buenas noticias para los Guardianes. Estos humanos de "
"aquí son maat'karianos del Continente de las Hadas, enemigos de los "
"skironianos igual que nosotros, ¡y por eso están dispuestos a ayudarnos a "
"librar nuestra tierra de su mal!"

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:272
msgid ""
"Maat'Karians, uh? I've heard about them from a northern fairy, they're "
"friend-of-nature enough, but... human still. Anyway, maybe you're right, "
"Volturnus, maybe they're really friendly, but this we can discuss later; now "
"we must complete our task here."
msgstr ""
"¿Maat'karianos, eh? He oído sobre ellos de una hada del norte, son lo "
"suficientemente amigos de la naturaleza, pero... todavía humanos. De todos "
"modos, quizás tengas razón, Volturnus, quizás realmente sean amistosos, pero "
"esto podemos discutirlo después; ahora debemos completar nuestra tarea aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:276
msgid ""
"Let us aid you then, faun captain, as a sign of our good will. Come on, "
"folks, we must be done here as soon as possible, or we may be caught by more "
"Skironians; I doubt that our little stroll near Aionian will go unnoticed by "
"Aegaion."
msgstr ""
"Entonces permítenos ayudarte, capitán fauno, como señal de nuestra buena "
"voluntad. ¡Vamos, gente, debemos terminar aquí lo antes posible, o podemos "
"ser atrapados por más skironianos; dudo que nuestro pequeño paseo cerca de "
"Aionian pase desapercibido para Aegaion."

#. [message], speaker=Pragdush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:280
msgid ""
"Gore and steel! As if that bloody pest of the woods, those stinking birds "
"and those disgusting turtle men weren't enough, now there comes a human "
"battalion! You better sharpen your blades again, orcs, they'll work hard "
"today!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sangre y acero! Como si esa maldita plaga del bosque, esos pájaros "
"apestosos y esos asquerosos hombres tortuga no fueran suficientes, ¡ahora "
"viene un batallón humano! Mejor afilen sus espadas otra vez, orcos, ¡hoy "
"trabajarán duro!"

#. [message], speaker=Pragdush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:293
msgid "Ugh! Damn all these freakish monsters...!"
msgstr "¡Ugh! ¡Malditos sean todos estos monstruos freak...!"

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:302
msgid ""
"I must thank your aid, Maat'Karians; without it, more fauns would have died "
"today. I suppose that you want to talk with our leaders now?"
msgstr ""
"Debo agradecer su ayuda, maat'karianos; sin ella, más faunos habrían muerto "
"hoy. Supongo que ahora quieren hablar con nuestros líderes."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:306
msgid ""
"We do, captain. We must return to our continent to save it from a great "
"evil, but we were stranded on this continent; we wanted your help to safely "
"cross Argea into Netjer-Ta."
msgstr ""
"Así es, capitán. Debemos regresar a nuestro continente para salvarlo de un "
"gran mal, pero quedamos varados en este continente; queríamos su ayuda para "
"cruzar Argea de forma segura hacia Netjer-Ta."

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:310
msgid "Volturnus said you were the one wanting to help us, though..."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, Volturnus dijo que ustedes eran los que querían ayudarnos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:314
msgid ""
"And he said no lie. Skiron recently tried to conquer our country, and so "
"it's our enemy as much as it's yours. We just have to end a civil war in our "
"land first, or we won't be in conditions to help you."
msgstr ""
"Y no mintió. Skiron recientemente intentó conquistar nuestro país, y por eso "
"es nuestro enemigo tanto como el de ustedes. Solo tenemos que terminar una "
"guerra civil en nuestra tierra primero, o no estaremos en condiciones de "
"ayudarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:318
msgid ""
"Fair enough, I think; that doesn't mean the Wardens will think likewise, "
"though... Follow me then, Maat'Karians; I'll take you to Heartwood Valley, "
"but only your leader may talk to the Wardens. Be honoured, for you'll be the "
"first non-fauns allowed to enter our lands in many decades."
msgstr ""
"Bastante justo, creo; eso no significa que los Guardianes piensen lo mismo, "
"sin embargo... Síganme entonces, maat'karianos; los llevaré al Valle del "
"Bosque Profundo, pero solo su líder podrá hablar con los Guardianes. "
"Siéntanse honrados, porque serán los primeros no faunos permitidos a entrar "
"en nuestras tierras en muchas décadas."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:322
msgid "We certainly are, captain. Come, folks, let's follow the fauns..."
msgstr "Ciertamente lo somos, capitán. Vengan, gente, sigamos a los faunos..."

#. [message], speaker=Shadow
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:335
msgid ""
"So Caror's message was true after all; and, to make things better, the heir "
"of Myra, the wielder of the Trident of the Seas, is amongst them, and "
"heading for Heartwood Valley... Maybe I should attend to this matter myself; "
"with Stygia gone, Lenvan busy and Jevyan weakened, none of my disciples will "
"be able to defeat such powers..."
msgstr ""
"Así que el mensaje de Caror era cierto después de todo; y, para mejorar las "
"cosas, el heredero de Myra, el portador del Tridente de los Mares, está "
"entre ellos y se dirige al Valle del Bosque Profundo... Quizás debería "
"atender este asunto yo mismo; con Stygia desaparecida, Lenvan ocupado y "
"Jevyan debilitado, ninguno de mis discípulos podrá derrotar tales poderes..."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:356
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:902
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:508
msgid "Ack! I think I was too brash..."
msgstr "¡Ack! Creo que fui demasiado impulsivo..."

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:360
msgid ""
"I knew humans couldn't be trusted! You let one of our own die, irresponsible "
"boy; expect no further aid from us fauns!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sabía que no se podía confiar en los humanos! Dejaste morir a uno de los "
"nuestros, muchacho irresponsable; ¡no esperes más ayuda de nosotros los "
"faunos!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:364
msgid ""
"This is a disaster! Without the fauns, we're completely lost and alone on "
"this continent!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es un desastre! ¡Sin los faunos, estamos completamente perdidos y "
"solos en este continente!"

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:378
msgid "Fauns, return to Heartwood Valley... This battle is lost"
msgstr ""
"Faunos, regresen al Valle del Bosque Profundo... Esta batalla está perdida"

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:382
msgid ""
"That's no good, Aferius was Heartwood Valley's captain of the guard! Without "
"him, our home is too defenceless!"
msgstr ""
"Eso no es bueno, ¡Aferius era el capitán de la guardia del Valle del Bosque "
"Profundo! ¡Sin él, nuestro hogar está demasiado indefenso!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/27_The_Folk_Of_The_Forest.cfg:393
msgid ""
"We shouldn't have spent so much time to win here, now Jevyan and his army "
"will certainly find and overwhelm us!"
msgstr ""
"No deberíamos haber pasado tanto tiempo para ganar aquí, ¡ahora Jevyan y su "
"ejército sin duda nos encontrarán y nos abrumarán!"

#. [scenario], id=28_Rain_Of_Light
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:4
msgid "Rain of Light"
msgstr "Lluvia de Luz"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:25
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:400
msgid "Defeat Emperor Aegaion of Skiron"
msgstr "Derrotar al Emperador Aegaion de Skiron"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:53
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:432
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:643
msgid "Death of Bacus"
msgstr "Muerte de Bacus"

#. [side], type=Faun Lord
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:105
msgid "Warden Bacus"
msgstr "Guardián Bacus"

#. [side], type=Faun Lord
#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:110
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:133
msgid "Heartwood Fauns"
msgstr "Faunos del Bosque Profundo"

#. [side], type=Warrior Carapace
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:149
msgid "Arkur"
msgstr "Arkur"

#. [unit], id=Hadeis, type=Lich Lord WotJ
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:211
msgid "Lich-Lord Hadeis"
msgstr "Señor Liche Hadeis"

#. [unit], id=Hamadryas, type=Faun Lord
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:221
msgid "Warden Hamadryas"
msgstr "Guardián Hamadryas"

#. [unit], id=Turius, type=Faun Lord
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:231
msgid "Warden Turius"
msgstr "Guardián Turius"

#. [message], speaker=Hamadryas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:254
msgid ""
"You sure deserve your nickname, Volturnus, to interrupt the Wardens' meeting "
"so brusquely!"
msgstr ""
"¡Realmente mereces tu apodo, Volturnus, al interrumpir la reunión de los "
"Guardianes de manera tan brusca!"

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:258
msgid ""
"Pardon me, masters, but... The Green Pass' sentries have just sighted a "
"small Skironian retinue coming..."
msgstr ""
"Perdónenme, maestros, pero... Los centinelas del Paso Verde acaban de "
"avistar a una pequeña comitiva skironia que se acerca..."

#. [message], speaker=Turius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:262
msgid ""
"Such a large stirring for such a tiny matter? Surely the Wood Guards are "
"capable of dealing with them?"
msgstr ""
"¿Tanto alboroto por un asunto tan pequeño? ¿Seguramente los Guardias del "
"Bosque son capaces de encargarse de ellos?"

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:266
msgid ""
"You don't understand, this retinue is composed by two Lich-Lords plus the "
"Emperor himself!"
msgstr ""
"No entienden, ¡esta comitiva está compuesta por dos Señores Liche más el "
"Emperador en persona!"

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:270
msgid "(appalled) Aegaion is here...?!"
msgstr "(horrorizado) ¿Aegaion está aquí...?"

#. [message], speaker=Hamadryas
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:274
msgid "But... Would he really dare to attack us now, after all these decades?"
msgstr ""
"Pero... ¿Realmente se atrevería a atacarnos ahora, después de todas estas "
"décadas?"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:278
msgid ""
"(booming voice in the distance) And who said that the Dark Saint has come "
"here to fight, worthy fauns? Do you think he's changed so much as to turn "
"his power against you who once helped him without any provocation?"
msgstr ""
"(voz atronadora en la distancia) ¿Y quién dijo que el Santo Oscuro ha venido "
"aquí a luchar, dignos faunos? ¿Creen que ha cambiado tanto como para volver "
"su poder contra ustedes, que una vez lo ayudaron sin ninguna provocación?"

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:282
msgid ""
"Ah, young one, believe it, you have changed since those times... But this is "
"not what concerns me right now. Tell us, what has made you travel so far "
"from your deathly throne into this remote region?"
msgstr ""
"Ah, joven, créelo, has cambiado desde aquellos tiempos... Pero esto no es lo "
"que me preocupa ahora. Dinos, ¿qué te ha hecho viajar tan lejos desde tu "
"trono mortal hasta esta región remota?"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:286
msgid ""
"You shelter people who invade and harry my land and you still don't "
"understand why I'm here? Frankly, Bacus, you used to be a quicker thinker!"
msgstr ""
"¿Ustedes protegen a gente que invade y hostiga mi tierra y todavía no "
"entienden por qué estoy aquí? Francamente, Bacus, ¡solías pensar más rápido!"

#. [message], speaker=Turius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:290
msgid ""
"Do not insult us, Aegaion! We both know that such matter would never be "
"enough to make you come here yourself!"
msgstr ""
"¡No nos insultes, Aegaion! Ambos sabemos que ese asunto nunca sería "
"suficiente para hacerte venir aquí en persona!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:294
msgid ""
"Seems like I can no longer deceive you... Indeed, old friends, I have come "
"in person because I want to see for myself the power of Myra's heir, and, "
"most importantly... I want to capture the spirit of Myra herself, which is "
"still connected to this plane of existence."
msgstr ""
"Parece que ya no puedo engañarlos... En efecto, viejos amigos, he venido en "
"persona porque quiero ver por mí mismo el poder del heredero de Myra, y, lo "
"más importante... quiero capturar el espíritu de Myra misma, que todavía "
"está conectado a este plano de existencia."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:298
msgid ""
"*Damn it, how does he know these things...?!* If you Skironians don't know "
"it, let me tell you, Aegaion; Myra's body and soul have vanished centuries "
"ago without a trace..."
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, cómo sabe estas cosas...?! Si ustedes los skironianos no lo "
"saben, déjenme decirles, Aegaion; el cuerpo y el alma de Myra desaparecieron "
"hace siglos sin dejar rastro..."

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:302
msgid ""
"Now it's you who insults me, boy, with your futile attempts to deceive me. "
"The moment you stepped on Aionian's beaches, I knew who you were, and who "
"was accompanying you. Sixteen centuries may have passed, but the Three "
"Dragons of the Ruby would never have forgotten the energy of her who blasted "
"away their armies at Garet-Desh with such ease, and who was also the first "
"to peer into the Sky Soul..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora eres tú quien me insulta, muchacho, con tus inútiles intentos de "
"engañarme. En el momento en que pisaste las playas de Aionia, supe quién "
"eras y quién te acompañaba. Pueden haber pasado dieciséis siglos, pero los "
"Tres Dragones del Rubí nunca habrían olvidado la energía de aquella que "
"destruyó sus ejércitos en Garet-Desh con tanta facilidad, y que también fue "
"la primera en mirar dentro del Alma del Cielo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:306
msgid "Do you mean... have those dragons..."
msgstr "¿Quieres decir... que esos dragones...?"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:310
msgid ""
"Oh, no, they haven't awakened, at least not in physical form. But they still "
"live, boy, inside the jewel crafted out of the Sky Soul; and whoever peers "
"into it can talk to them and learn from their vast knowledge, which they "
"obtained from the Sky Dragon himself."
msgstr ""
"Oh, no, no han despertado, al menos no en forma física. Pero todavía viven, "
"muchacho, dentro de la joya creada a partir del Alma del Cielo; y quien mire "
"dentro de ella puede hablar con ellos y aprender de su vasto conocimiento, "
"que obtuvieron del propio Dragón del Cielo."

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:314
msgid ""
"You have harnessed a great power indeed, Aegaion; why do you seek even more, "
"then? Isn't your current power enough to improve your country, as you've "
"always wished?"
msgstr ""
"Realmente has dominado un gran poder, Aegaion; ¿por qué buscas aún más, "
"entonces? ¿No es suficiente tu poder actual para mejorar tu país, como "
"siempre has deseado?"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:318
msgid ""
"Skiron is still far from my vision, Bacus, it's still vulnerable to external "
"threats. It failed to defeat Maat'Kare, and even now it reels under their "
"attacks. I'll even admit that we won't manage to stand against Menon "
"Hekare's fury for long – after all, he possesses the mightier jewel. "
"However, the young mages gathered at this valley can be the key for us to "
"understand the secrets of Maat'Karian magic, and use it against their "
"countrymen. Furthermore, by capturing the spirit of Myra we may have access "
"to the power that defeated the Sky Dragon thrice in the past, and thus even "
"Menon and the Sky Soul will no longer be a threat to us."
msgstr ""
"Skiron todavía está lejos de mi visión, Bacus, todavía es vulnerable a "
"amenazas externas. Falló en derrotar a Maat'Kare, e incluso ahora se "
"tambalea bajo sus ataques. Incluso admitiré que no resistiremos por mucho "
"tiempo la furia de Menon Hekare; después de todo, él posee la joya más "
"poderosa. Sin embargo, los jóvenes magos reunidos en este valle pueden ser "
"la clave para que entendamos los secretos de la magia maat'kariana y la "
"usemos contra sus compatriotas. Además, al capturar el espíritu de Myra "
"podemos tener acceso al poder que derrotó al Dragón del Cielo tres veces en "
"el pasado, y así ni siquiera Menon y el Alma del Cielo serán una amenaza "
"para nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:322
msgid ""
"So you want no less than enough power to control the entire world. (sigh) "
"We've allowed you many things, Aegaion, even to go in peace when you were "
"already being corrupted by that cursed jewel... But this we cannot allow. "
"Akhen Wadjet, rest assured that we shall not yield you to our common enemy. "
"We'll make sure that you go back to your land in safety, even if we have to "
"die for that to happen."
msgstr ""
"Entonces quieres nada menos que suficiente poder para controlar el mundo "
"entero. (suspiro) Te hemos permitido muchas cosas, Aegaion, incluso dejarte "
"ir en paz cuando ya estabas siendo corrompido por esa joya maldita... Pero "
"esto no podemos permitirlo. Akhen Wadjet, ten por seguro que no te "
"entregaremos a nuestro enemigo común. Nos aseguraremos de que regreses a tu "
"tierra a salvo, incluso si tenemos que morir para que eso ocurra."

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:326
msgid ""
"(darkly) What a grave mistake you've made, Bacus... For all these decades, "
"I've refrained from attacking your people, in gratitude for all the aid "
"you've once given me, but that's in the past now. Tomorrow, the fauns shall "
"wake up as part of Skiron's legions, and this valley shall be a dried up, "
"lifeless testament of how foolish it is to oppose the will of the Eternal "
"Emperor!"
msgstr ""
"(con tono sombrío) Qué grave error has cometido, Bacus... Durante todas "
"estas décadas, me he abstenido de atacar a tu pueblo, en gratitud por toda "
"la ayuda que una vez me diste, pero eso ya es pasado. Mañana, los faunos "
"despertarán como parte de las legiones de Skiron, y este valle será un "
"testimonio seco y sin vida de lo estúpido que es oponerse a la voluntad del "
"Emperador Eterno!"

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:330
msgid ""
"Akhen, hurry and come with me to where your friends are, they'll need you to "
"oppose Aegaion's army!"
msgstr ""
"Akhen, ¡apúrate y ven conmigo donde están tus amigos, te necesitarán para "
"oponerte al ejército de Aegaion!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:339
msgid "*Myra, is it true that your spirit can be captured?*"
msgstr "*Myra, ¿es cierto que tu espíritu puede ser capturado?*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:344
msgid ""
"<i>*If even Svarballi's could, then mine can certainly be as well. And, "
"considering that this Aegaion has been taught by those dragons, who were "
"once lieutenants of Svarballi, and that my current form is way too weak to "
"defend itself... Argh, it's so humiliating...*</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>*Si incluso el de Svarballi pudo, entonces el mío seguramente también. Y, "
"considerando que este Aegaion ha sido enseñado por esos dragones, que una "
"vez fueron tenientes de Svarballi, y que mi forma actual es demasiado débil "
"para defenderse... Argh, es tan humillante...*</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:348
msgid ""
"*Don't worry, there's no way I'll let him capture you – this I promise!*"
msgstr ""
"*No te preocupes, de ninguna manera permitiré que te capture; ¡esto te lo "
"prometo!*"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Akhen, at last you're back! What was Aegaion talking about? I heard him "
"talking about Myra, but..."
msgstr ""
"Akhen, ¡por fin has regresado! ¿De qué estaba hablando Aegaion? Lo oí hablar "
"de Myra, pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:366
msgid ""
"I'll tell you everything another time, right now you just have to know that "
"Myra's spirit is accompanying me, as it has been doing since we fled "
"Maat'Kare, and that she must not get captured by Aegaion!"
msgstr ""
"Te contaré todo en otro momento, ahora solo debes saber que el espíritu de "
"Myra me acompaña, como ha estado haciendo desde que huimos de Maat'Kare, ¡y "
"que no debe ser capturado por Aegaion!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Well, that's obvious, isn't it? Come on, Branwyn, let's show the valour of "
"the Aeserians to those Skironian bastards!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, eso es obvio, ¿no? Vamos, Branwyn, ¡mostremos el valor de los "
"aeserianos a esos bastardos skironianos!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:374
msgid ""
"Normally Nyx would agree with you, but look at those undead; we're not "
"fighting mere generals and stupid Lich-Lords anymore, we're facing Aegaion "
"himself – and, in case you haven't noticed, Jevyan, <i>that</i> Jevyan who "
"nearly single-handedly destroyed Maat'Kare, is by his side!"
msgstr ""
"Normalmente Nyx estaría de acuerdo contigo, pero mira a esos no muertos; ya "
"no estamos luchando contra simples generales y estúpidos Señores Liche, "
"estamos enfrentándonos al propio Aegaion; ¡y, por si no lo has notado, "
"Jevyan, <i>ese</i> Jevyan que casi destruyó Maat'Kare él solo, está a su "
"lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:378
msgid ""
"The situation is dire indeed, but we may still have a chance of winning. In "
"the last days, I've been studying those books we found at the Celestial's "
"fortress, back in Arajunna, and I'm sure that one of the spells I've found "
"there could give us victory today. It's called Sacred Heavens, and, if the "
"description is to be believed, it creates a magical dome which increases the "
"intensity of sunlight inside it."
msgstr ""
"La situación es realmente grave, pero todavía podemos tener una oportunidad "
"de ganar. En los últimos días he estado estudiando esos libros que "
"encontramos en la fortaleza del Celestial, allá en Arajunna, y estoy segura "
"de que uno de los hechizos que encontré allí podría darnos la victoria hoy. "
"Se llama Cielos Sagrados y, si la descripción es cierta, crea una cúpula "
"mágica que aumenta la intensidad de la luz del sol en su interior."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:382
msgid ""
"I see, I think I've read about it in a scroll which told of the Battle of "
"the Crystal Tower; the Celestials used it in that occasion... But this must "
"be an extremely complex spell..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo, creo que leí sobre eso en un pergamino que hablaba de la Batalla "
"de la Torre de Cristal; los Celestiales lo usaron en esa ocasión... Pero "
"este debe ser un hechizo extremadamente complejo..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:386
msgid ""
"It is, but it's nothing that we can't do, not with our Lucent powers. It'll "
"take time to be completed, though, so we'll have to stay out of the fight "
"for a while."
msgstr ""
"Lo es, pero no es nada que no podamos hacer, no con nuestros poderes "
"Lucientes. Sin embargo, tomará tiempo completarlo, así que tendremos que "
"quedarnos fuera de la lucha por un rato."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:390
msgid ""
"Just stand back and do your best, that we'll battle them until you're done."
msgstr ""
"Solo quédense atrás y hagan lo mejor que puedan, que nosotros los "
"combatiremos hasta que terminen."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:394
msgid ""
"Thank you, friends... Stand strong, and leave some of them for us, that "
"we'll join you soon..."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, amigos... Resistan con fuerza y déjennos algunos de ellos, que "
"pronto nos uniremos a ustedes..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:404
msgid ""
"Leave Akhen and Merwe idle and next to each other for 8 turns in order to "
"invoke the Sacred Spell"
msgstr ""
"Deja a Akhen y a Merwe inactivos y uno al lado del otro durante 8 turnos "
"para invocar el Hechizo Sagrado"

#. [message], speaker=Hadeis
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:452
msgid ""
"You will not lay a finger on our Eternal Emperor, creature - of this I shall "
"make sure!"
msgstr ""
"¡No pondrás un dedo sobre nuestro Emperador Eterno, criatura; de esto me "
"encargaré!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:461
msgid ""
"This cursed alliance between fauns and Maat'Karians is proving itself a far "
"harder foe than we had anticipated..."
msgstr ""
"Esta maldita alianza entre faunos y maat'karianos se está demostrando un "
"enemigo mucho más difícil de lo que anticipamos..."

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:465
msgid ""
"Indeed, my good Jevyan, they're fighting quite nicely. I even think they're "
"up to a greater challenge..."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, mi buen Jevyan, están luchando bastante bien. Incluso creo que "
"están a la altura de un desafío mayor..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:476
msgid ""
"Oh, damn, damn, damn, they're summoning another horde! Akhen, Merwe, I do "
"hope this spell works, or else we're all doomed!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, maldición, maldición, maldición, están invocando otra horda! Akhen, "
"Merwe, espero que este hechizo funcione, ¡o estamos todos condenados!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:554
msgid "What... What is this blinding, scorching light...?"
msgstr "¿Qué... qué es esta luz cegadora y abrasadora...?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:558
msgid ""
"This is the shine of the Sacred Dawn, which burns away those who cower "
"before the light! Everyone, this spell won't last for long, so we must "
"attack now!"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el resplandor del Amanecer Sagrado, que quema a aquellos que se "
"acobardan ante la luz! ¡Todos, este hechizo no durará mucho, así que debemos "
"atacar ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:562
msgid ""
"The tales of the Maat'Karians' prowess were no overstatement, what a "
"splendid magic... Fauns, the young lady just said everything; charge at "
"those aberrations while they're weakened!"
msgstr ""
"Los relatos sobre la destreza de los maat'karianos no eran exagerados, ¡qué "
"magia tan espléndida...! Faunos, la joven dama acaba de decirlo todo; "
"¡carguen contra esas aberraciones mientras están debilitadas!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:566
msgid "With a thousand curses, not even the Invincible Darkness is working...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Con mil maldiciones, ni siquiera la Oscuridad Invencible está "
"funcionando...!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:570
msgid ""
"Of course it isn't; it may have come from the teachings of the Ruby, but the "
"spell they're using has much higher origins... If anything, it has just made "
"this battle more interesting; I was holding back in order not to be too "
"disloyal, but now it's no longer necessary... Let the Amphyon be unleashed!"
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que no; puede haber venido de las enseñanzas del Rubí, pero el "
"hechizo que están usando tiene orígenes mucho más altos... Si algo, solo ha "
"hecho esta batalla más interesante; me estaba conteniendo para no ser "
"demasiado desleal, pero ahora ya no es necesario... ¡Que se desate el "
"Amphyon!"

#. [message], speaker=Hadeis
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:574
msgid "As you wish, Master."
msgstr "Como desees, Maestro."

#. [unit], id=Amphyon, type=Amphyon
#. [unit_type], id=Amphyon, race=monster
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:580
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Amphyon.cfg:5
msgid "Amphyon"
msgstr "Amphyon"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:592
msgid ""
"Look, I've seen many weird things created out of the Dark Arts, but just "
"what the hell is <i>that</i> thing?!"
msgstr ""
"Mira, he visto muchas cosas extrañas creadas con las Artes Oscuras, ¡pero "
"qué demonios es <i>esa</i> cosa?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:596
msgid ""
"Did you like him? This is the former Emperor of Skiron, who lived a life of "
"abundance at the expense of his own people. He deserved to be obliterated, "
"but I decided to be merciful, and so I gave him greater power, as well as "
"the chance to fight for his homeland."
msgstr ""
"¿Te gustó? Este es el antiguo Emperador de Skiron, que vivió una vida de "
"abundancia a costa de su propio pueblo. Merecía ser obliterado, pero decidí "
"ser misericordioso, y por eso le di un mayor poder, así como la oportunidad "
"de luchar por su patria."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:600
msgid ""
"Now I know who inspired Maurias to be the monster he used to be... How I "
"would love to give him the same fate I gave that Lich-Lord..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora sé quién inspiró a Maurias a ser el monstruo que era... Cómo me "
"gustaría darle el mismo destino que le di a ese Señor Liche..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:604
msgid ""
"He's all yours, then; my Umbra spells will be of little effect against "
"Aegaion, but your Scourge of the Five Stars can severely damage even him."
msgstr ""
"Entonces es todo tuyo; mis hechizos de Umbra tendrán poco efecto contra "
"Aegaion, pero tu Azote de las Cinco Estrellas puede dañarlo gravemente "
"incluso a él."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:615
msgid "Defeat Emperor Aegaion of Skiron with either Akhen or Merwe"
msgstr "Derrotar al Emperador Aegaion de Skiron con Akhen o Merwe"

#. [message], speaker=Amphyon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:668
msgid "RRRUUAAAAARRRGGGHHHHH!!!"
msgstr "¡RRRUUAAAAARRRGGGHHHHH!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:672
msgid ""
"Damn it...! EVERYONE, GET OUT OF HIS WAY! ATTACK HIM ONLY FROM A DISTANCE!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición...! ¡TODOS, APÁRTENSE DE SU CAMINO! ¡ATÁQUENLO SOLO DESDE LA "
"DISTANCIA!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:684
msgid ""
"You may have been a tyrant, but I doubt even you deserved such a horrific "
"fate. May the Gods of Light and Darkness judge your soul as they see fit, "
"Amphyon."
msgstr ""
"Puedes haber sido un tirano, pero dudo que incluso tú merecieras un destino "
"tan horrible. Que los Dioses de la Luz y la Oscuridad juzguen tu alma como "
"mejor les parezca, Amphyon."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:699
msgid ""
"So you've dared come near me... Prepare yourself for the greatest pain "
"you'll ever..."
msgstr ""
"Así que te atreviste a acercarte a mí... Prepárate para el mayor dolor que "
"jamás..."

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:703
msgid ""
"Jevyan, wait! You haven't completely recovered yourself from Menon's attack, "
"you must retreat! I can't afford to lose another of my best disciples!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jevyan, espera! No te has recuperado completamente del ataque de Menon, "
"¡debes retirarte! ¡No puedo permitirme perder a otro de mis mejores "
"discípulos!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:707
msgid "I will do as you say, Master... (sigh)"
msgstr "Haré como dices, Maestro... (suspiro)"

#. [message], speaker=Hadeis
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:722
msgid "Master, please help me...!"
msgstr "¡Maestro, por favor ayúdame...!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:726
msgid ""
"If you couldn't even survive this little skirmish, Hadeis, there's no place "
"for you in the Skiron of my dreams. Rest in peace, though, for your family "
"shall remain safe as I've promised."
msgstr ""
"Si ni siquiera pudiste sobrevivir a esta pequeña escaramuza, Hadeis, no hay "
"lugar para ti en el Skiron de mis sueños. Descansa en paz, sin embargo, "
"porque tu familia permanecerá a salvo como te lo prometí."

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:738
msgid "What a shame, he was such a promising young man..."
msgstr "Qué lástima, era un joven tan prometedor..."

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:753
msgid ""
"I must commend you for managing to reach me, young one. To honour your "
"valour, I, the Eternal Emperor of Skiron, shall send you to the Otherworld "
"with my full power!"
msgstr ""
"Debo felicitarte por haber logrado llegar hasta mí, joven. Para honrar tu "
"valor, yo, el Emperador Eterno de Skiron, te enviaré al Otro Mundo con todo "
"mi poder!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:774
msgid ""
"Pitiful fools, do you truly believe that puny mortals like you could "
"possibly defeat me?"
msgstr ""
"Pobres tontos, ¿realmente creen que mortales insignificantes como ustedes "
"podrían derrotarme?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:781
msgid "Leave him to me and Merwe, he's too powerful for you!"
msgstr "¡Déjenmelo a mí y a Merwe, es demasiado poderoso para ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:799
msgid "NO!!! What... What is happening... I am... being... bested...?!"
msgstr "¡NO!!! ¿Qué... qué está pasando... yo... estoy siendo... derrotado...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:803
msgid ""
"It does not matter how strong you are, there'll always be a way to bring you "
"down – specially if you make the mistake of considering yourself invincible. "
"Now, Aegaion, Emperor of Skiron... VANISH FROM EXISTENCE!!!"
msgstr ""
"No importa cuán fuerte seas, siempre habrá una forma de derribarte, "
"especialmente si cometes el error de considerarte invencible. Ahora, "
"Aegaion, Emperador de Skiron... ¡DESAPARECE DE LA EXISTENCIA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:808
msgid ""
"(enraged) Do you really think that I'll fall like this, alone in this "
"stinking valley, killed by Maat'Karian BRATS?! Do not be full of yourselves, "
"you've simply caught me off guard and far from my armies; but I shall "
"recover, and when I do, I shall send not a fraction of Skiron's legions, but "
"our entire military force to completely obliterate your sorry nation from "
"the face of Irdya!!!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecido) ¿Realmente creen que caeré así, solo en este valle apestoso, "
"asesinado por MOCOSOS maat'karianos?! No se crean tanto, simplemente me "
"tomaron desprevenido y lejos de mis ejércitos; pero me recuperaré, y cuando "
"lo haga, enviaré no una fracción de las legiones de Skiron, sino toda "
"nuestra fuerza militar para obliterar por completo su miserable nación de la "
"faz de Irdya!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:833
msgid "Hey, folks... Did we, you know, just defeat..."
msgstr "Oigan, gente... ¿Acabamos de derrotar...?"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:837
msgid "...the Emperor of Skiron himself, yes, we did..."
msgstr "...al propio Emperador de Skiron, sí, lo hicimos..."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:841
msgid ""
"(laughing) Didn't I tell you all that these folks were pretty strong? Not "
"even the high and mighty Dark Saint could stand them!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¿No les dije a todos que esta gente era bastante fuerte? ¡Ni "
"siquiera el poderoso y altivo Santo Oscuro pudo resistirlos!"

#. [message], speaker=Turius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:845
msgid "Eh, I have to admit that they truly impressed me..."
msgstr "Eh, tengo que admitir que realmente me impresionaron..."

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:849
msgid ""
"Young humans, today you have irrefutably proved your worth. As promised, we "
"shall help you reach the Fairy Continent, and then wait for you to win your "
"war and rebuild your nation from its damages."
msgstr ""
"Jóvenes humanos, hoy han demostrado irrefutablemente su valía. Como "
"prometimos, los ayudaremos a llegar al Continente de las Hadas, y luego "
"esperaremos a que gane su guerra y reconstruya su nación de sus daños."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:853
msgid ""
"Thank you, Warden Bacus. But I confess that even I am surprised that we "
"managed to defeat Aegaion, who's said to be a match for Master Menon "
"himself..."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, Guardián Bacus. Pero confieso que incluso yo estoy sorprendido de "
"que hayamos logrado derrotar a Aegaion, quien se dice que es rival del "
"propio Maestro Menon..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:857
msgid "But, if you wasn't expecting to win, why were you fighting for?"
msgstr "Pero, si no esperabas ganar, ¿por qué estabas luchando?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:861
msgid ""
"I did expect to win, but by destroying his armies and convincing him to "
"withdraw, not by directly defeating him. I hadn't realised we've gotten so "
"strong..."
msgstr ""
"Sí esperaba ganar, pero destruyendo sus ejércitos y convenciéndolo de "
"retirarse, no derrotándolo directamente. No me había dado cuenta de que nos "
"hemos vuelto tan fuertes..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:865
msgid ""
"Anyway, now there shouldn't be any obstacle barring us from reaching Netjer-"
"Ta, so let's hurry, that we have friends there who need us!"
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, ahora no debería haber ningún obstáculo que nos impida "
"llegar a Netjer-Ta, ¡así que apurémonos, que tenemos amigos allí que nos "
"necesitan!"

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:874
msgid ""
"Wait, I won't allow you to go alone; some of our warriors shall follow you "
"and help you in your war – and you shall go with them too, Volturnus, as I'm "
"sure you desire. After saving our valley and severely wounding Aegaion, "
"that's the least we can do."
msgstr ""
"Espera, no permitiré que vayan solos; algunos de nuestros guerreros los "
"seguirán y los ayudarán en su guerra; y tú también irás con ellos, "
"Volturnus, como estoy seguro que deseas. Después de salvar nuestro valle y "
"herir gravemente a Aegaion, eso es lo menos que podemos hacer."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:878
msgid ""
"Thank you once again, Warden Bacus. Now, friends, onwards, to Netjer-Ta and "
"to Maat'Kare!"
msgstr ""
"Gracias una vez más, Guardián Bacus. Ahora, amigos, ¡adelante, hacia Netjer-"
"Ta y hacia Maat'Kare!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:906
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:512
msgid ""
"Were it not for you, Volturnus, we would have surely perished in Argea. Rest "
"in peace, friend."
msgstr ""
"Si no fuera por ti, Volturnus, sin duda habríamos perecido en Argea. "
"Descansa en paz, amigo."

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:917
msgid "Fauns, please don't let our home be overrun by those monsters..."
msgstr ""
"Faunos, por favor no permitan que nuestro hogar sea invadido por esos "
"monstruos..."

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:921
msgid ""
"This is a catastrophe! Aferius was our best strategist, without him our "
"defences will be ineffective!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es una catástrofe! Aferius era nuestro mejor estratega, ¡sin él "
"nuestras defensas serán ineficaces!"

#. [message], speaker=Bacus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:935
msgid ""
"The time has come for my body to return to the Mother's bosom; fight on "
"without me, my people..."
msgstr ""
"Ha llegado el momento de que mi cuerpo regrese al seno de la Madre; "
"continúen luchando sin mí, mi pueblo..."

#. [message], speaker=Aferius
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/28_Rain_Of_Light.cfg:939
msgid "Master, no! There's no way we can win without you!"
msgstr "¡Maestro, no! ¡No hay forma de que podamos ganar sin ti!"

#. [scenario], id=29_From_Darkness
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:4
msgid "From Darkness"
msgstr "Desde la Oscuridad"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:24
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:20
msgid "Explore the caves"
msgstr "Explorar las cuevas"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:171
msgid "So, did you find any sign of Motsoghnir presence around?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces, encontraron alguna señal de la presencia de los Motsoghnir por "
"aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:175
msgid ""
"We've found some settlements carrying Motsoghnir banners, but we've found no "
"dwarf in the nearby tunnels, though Nyx said that she could hear a distant "
"commotion..."
msgstr ""
"Hemos encontrado algunos asentamientos con estandartes de los Motsoghnir, "
"pero no hemos encontrado ningún enano en los túneles cercanos, aunque Nyx "
"dijo que podía oír un alboroto distante..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:179
msgid ""
"I bet that's the Motsoghnir and the Aigathol fighting... Which is good news, "
"for that means that Sigdral still stands."
msgstr ""
"Apuesto a que son los Motsoghnir y los Aigathol luchando... Lo cual es buena "
"noticia, porque eso significa que Sigdral todavía resiste."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:183
msgid ""
"But not for long, if we don't go to her aid as soon as we can. More than a "
"year has passed, who knows how many of her forces still remain."
msgstr ""
"Pero no por mucho tiempo, si no vamos en su ayuda lo antes posible. Ha "
"pasado más de un año, quién sabe cuántas de sus fuerzas todavía quedan."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:208
msgid ""
"Something still bugs me, though. Aegaion said that Skiron was under heavy "
"siege by Menon; that would explain why he attacked us with only a couple "
"Lich-Lords to back him, but then, if Menon is spending time and troops on a "
"campaign against Skiron, does that mean that he's dealt with the rebels "
"already...?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, algo todavía me molesta. Aegaion dijo que Skiron estaba bajo un "
"fuerte asedio por parte de Menon; eso explicaría por qué nos atacó solo con "
"un par de Señores Liche para respaldarlo, pero entonces, si Menon está "
"gastando tiempo y tropas en una campaña contra Skiron, ¿eso significa que ya "
"se ha encargado de los rebeldes...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:212
msgid ""
"That makes sense... Or else they might have been sheltered by Sigdral. Well, "
"let's proceed and find the truth; and Branwyn, be careful with scouting "
"ahead of us. Dwarves are not as huge as drakes or Deshrai, but they can "
"still be brutal enemies."
msgstr ""
"Eso tiene sentido... O tal vez hayan sido protegidos por Sigdral. Bueno, "
"procedamos y encontremos la verdad; y Branwyn, ten cuidado al explorar "
"delante de nosotros. Los enanos no son tan enormes como los dracos o los "
"Deshrai, pero aún pueden ser enemigos brutales."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:216
msgid ""
"(giggling) Sorry, it's just that I'm so thrilled for treading on your land "
"that I got a bit carried away..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Lo siento, es solo que estoy tan emocionada de pisar tu tierra que "
"me dejé llevar un poco..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:237
msgid "Uh-oh... Here we go..."
msgstr "Oh-oh... Allá vamos..."

#. [message], speaker=Augthil
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:241
msgid ""
"(panting) Come, boys, we have to take cover before returning to... (sees "
"Maat'Karians) By the Nine Hells, humans coming from the flooded tunnels...?! "
"Ah, I see it already, you're trying to sneak behind us, aren't you, "
"treacherous apes?"
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Vamos, muchachos, tenemos que ponernos a cubierto antes de "
"regresar a... (ve a los maat'karianos) ¡Por los Nueve Infiernos, humanos "
"saliendo de los túneles inundados...?! Ah, ya lo veo, están tratando de "
"infiltrarse detrás de nosotros, ¿verdad, simios traicioneros?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:245
msgid ""
"We're not sneaking, we're just arriving late for the party. Nyx suggests you "
"to take your leave and run away, for now that we've come this party is going "
"to get bloody!"
msgstr ""
"No nos estamos infiltrando, solo llegamos tarde a la fiesta. Nyx les sugiere "
"que se vayan y huyan, porque ahora que hemos llegado esta fiesta se va a "
"poner sangrienta!"

#. [message], speaker=Augthil
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:249
msgid ""
"Pah! It doesn't matter how wounded we are, puny humans will never be a match "
"for us, specially in our own home! C'mon boys, let's bleed them to make it "
"easier for Lord Argatyr to finish them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pah! No importa cuán heridos estemos, los humanos insignificantes nunca "
"serán rival para nosotros, ¡especialmente en nuestra propia casa! Vamos "
"muchachos, hagámoslos sangrar para que sea más fácil que Lord Argatyr "
"termine con ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:253
msgid ""
"Friends, Sigdral and her people are just behind these dwarves! Let's hurry "
"to her aid!"
msgstr ""
"¡Amigos, Sigdral y su gente están justo detrás de estos enanos! ¡Apurémonos "
"en su ayuda!"

#. [unit], id=Dulcatus, type=Dwarvish Dragonguard
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:351
msgid "Dulcatus"
msgstr "Dulcatus"

#. [unit], id=Gomthril, type=Dwarvish Lord
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:365
msgid "Gomthril"
msgstr "Gomthril"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Why do you fight on, my little Sigdral? Your forces are depleted, your "
"entire kingdom is lost, your precious Anduril is no more, and your only "
"allies are puny humans who currently can't hold their own against even a "
"puny orcish raiding party. Can't you see that it's pointless to resist any "
"further? Give up now, and I will spare your folk and give you a merciful "
"death..."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué sigues luchando, mi pequeña Sigdral? Tus fuerzas están agotadas, "
"todo tu reino está perdido, tu preciado Anduril ya no existe, y tus únicos "
"aliados son humanos insignificantes que actualmente no pueden defenderse ni "
"siquiera contra un pequeño grupo de asalto orco. ¿No ves que es inútil "
"resistir más? Ríndete ahora, y perdonaré a tu gente y te daré una muerte "
"misericordiosa..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:388
msgid ""
"(in furious despair) After all you've done to me, to my brother, to Anduril "
"and to my people? <i>Never</i>, Argatyr, <i>never</i>! If I am to die this "
"day, then be it, but I'll make sure that you follow me to the Ninth Hell!"
msgstr ""
"(en furiosa desesperación) ¿Después de todo lo que me has hecho, a mi "
"hermano, a Anduril y a mi pueblo? <i>Nunca</i>, Argatyr, <i>nunca</i>. Si he "
"de morir este día, que así sea, ¡pero me aseguraré de que tú me sigas al "
"Noveno Infierno!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:392
msgid ""
"If you choose a brutal death by my hands, then I shall fulfil your wish most "
"gleefully..."
msgstr ""
"Si eliges una muerte brutal a mis manos, entonces cumpliré tu deseo con gran "
"alegría..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:396
msgid "Not if we stop you, Argatyr!"
msgstr "¡No si nosotros te detenemos, Argatyr!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:400
msgid "(surprised) You...!"
msgstr "(sorprendido) ¡Tú...!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:404
msgid "It's... It's..."
msgstr "Es... Es..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:408
msgid "(smiling radiantly) AKHEN, YOU'RE...! And Merwe, Mahyus and Nyx...!"
msgstr "(sonriendo radiantemente) ¡AKHEN, ERES...! ¡Y Merwe, Mahyus y Nyx...!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Sorry for taking so long, friends, we had some trouble on our way, but now "
"we're here to help, and we've brought new friends with us!"
msgstr ""
"Perdón por tardar tanto, amigos, tuvimos algunos problemas en el camino, "
"pero ahora estamos aquí para ayudar, ¡y hemos traído nuevos amigos con "
"nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:416
msgid ""
"You humans sure know how to be inconvenient... But nothing has changed, boy, "
"I shall leave this cave in triumph, and you and your sorry friends shall "
"rest here for eternity, crushed by Ymir's Hammer!"
msgstr ""
"Los humanos sí saben cómo ser inconvenientes... Pero nada ha cambiado, "
"muchacho, saldré de esta cueva en triunfo, y tú y tus miserables amigos "
"descansarán aquí por la eternidad, aplastados por el Martillo de Ymir!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:428
msgid "(shocked) AAARRGGHHH!!! You vermin, what have you done...?!"
msgstr "(impactado) ¡AAARRGGHHH!!! ¡Verminosos, qué han hecho...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:432
msgid ""
"You may have the hammer once wielded by Moradin, but I wield the trident "
"forged by the first warden of Irdya, the High Dragon of Water himself! Now, "
"friends, this is what we wandered the world for! Strike them down, for our "
"friends and for peace in Netjer-Ta!"
msgstr ""
"Puedes tener el martillo que una vez empuñó Moradin, ¡pero yo empuño el "
"tridente forjado por el primer guardián de Irdya, el propio Alto Dragón del "
"Agua! Ahora, amigos, ¡esto es por lo que vagamos por el mundo! ¡Derribenlos, "
"por nuestros amigos y por la paz en Netjer-Ta!"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:436
msgid ""
"By Moradin, this is the first time that someone manages to land a severe "
"blow on Argatyr...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por Moradin, esta es la primera vez que alguien logra asestar un golpe "
"severo a Argatyr...!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:440
msgid ""
"See, my soldiers? He can be hit and bled like anyone else! Now, let's give "
"him the payback, for the heir of Myra is with us now!"
msgstr ""
"¿Ven, mis soldados? ¡Puede ser golpeado y hecho sangrar como cualquier otro! "
"Ahora, ¡démosle su merecido, porque el heredero de Myra está con nosotros "
"ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:446
msgid "Sigdral and Atenak have given you 400 gold"
msgstr "Sigdral y Atenak te han dado 400 de oro"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:456
msgid "Break Argatyr's siege by attacking him"
msgstr "Romper el asedio de Argatyr atacándolo"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:492
msgid ""
"Atenak may now recruit level 2 Maat'Karian units. The dwarvish veterans will "
"be available for this scenario and the next; also, Sigdral and Gomatol may "
"now recruit as well."
msgstr ""
"Atenak ahora puede reclutar unidades maat'karianas de nivel 2. Los veteranos "
"enanos estarán disponibles para este escenario y el siguiente; además, "
"Sigdral y Gomatol ahora también pueden reclutar."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:514
msgid ""
"Impressive... You're not sturdily built, and yet you fight with the ferocity "
"of a Wersefet. Who are you, friend?"
msgstr ""
"Impresionante... No eres de complexión robusta, y sin embargo luchas con la "
"ferocidad de un Wersefet. ¿Quién eres, amigo?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:518
msgid ""
"(bowing) I'm flattered to have earned the praise of Atenak of the Fire "
"Fists! I am Branwyn the Bard from the Green Isle, and I have come to battle "
"for my beloved Mahyus' bright Maat'Kare!"
msgstr ""
"(haciendo una reverencia) ¡Me halaga haber recibido el elogio de Atenak de "
"los Puños de Fuego! Soy Branwyn la Barda de la Isla Verde, ¡y he venido a "
"luchar por el brillante Maat'Kare de mi amado Mahyus!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:522
msgid "'Beloved Mahyus'... You <i>were</i> looking for allies, weren't you?"
msgstr "«Amado Mahyus»... Estabas buscando aliados, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:526
msgid "(blushing) Of course we were, but... A lot of things happened..."
msgstr "(sonrojándose) Por supuesto que sí, pero... Han pasado muchas cosas..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:530
msgid "(giggle) And I'll want to hear everything in detail later."
msgstr "(riendo) Y querré escuchar todo con detalle más tarde."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:547
msgid ""
"(enraged) I was so close...! A thousand curses upon you, Sigdral - and a "
"thousand times more upon you, Akhen Wadjet! Think not that you have defeated "
"me, for I shall return soon enough, and with my entire army, to crush you "
"once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecido) ¡Estuve tan cerca...! ¡Mil maldiciones sobre ti, Sigdral, y mil "
"veces más sobre ti, Akhen Wadjet! No creas que me has derrotado, porque "
"regresaré pronto, ¡y con todo mi ejército, para aplastarlos de una vez por "
"todas!"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:565
msgid ""
"Och, boy, you sure came on the nick of time; a few more hours late and "
"we'd've been dead meat..."
msgstr ""
"Och, muchacho, llegaste justo a tiempo; unas horas más tarde y habríamos "
"sido carne muerta..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:569
msgid ""
"(smiling) Indeed! I'll only let it pass because you've brought some good "
"fighters with you..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) ¡Claro! Solo lo dejaré pasar porque has traído algunos buenos "
"luchadores contigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:573
msgid ""
"I'm so glad to see you alive, friends; for a moment we thought that you had "
"been captured and killed. Especially you, Atenak-"
msgstr ""
"Me alegra tanto verlos vivos, amigos; por un momento pensamos que los habían "
"capturado y matado. Especialmente tú, Atenak..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:577
msgid "<i>Slap!</i>"
msgstr "<i>¡Slap!</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:581
msgid "(angry) Hey, what the hell was that for?!"
msgstr "(enojada) ¡Oye, ¿qué demonios fue eso?!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:585
msgid ""
"(hugging Akhen in tears) You idiot, w-why did you t-take so long to ret-"
"turn, we t-thought you d-dead, you irresp-ponsible idiot!"
msgstr ""
"(abrazando a Akhen entre lágrimas) Idiota, ¿p-por qué t-tardaste tanto en "
"regresar, pensamos que estabas m-muerto, ¡idiota irresponsable!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:589
msgid ""
"(smirking) That’s the Atenak we know: harsh and cold on the outside, but a "
"hopeless sentimental at heart."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo burlonamente) Esa es la Atenak que conocemos: dura y fría por "
"fuera, pero una sentimental sin remedio en el fondo."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:593
msgid ""
"(sobbing) That's n-not funny, you d-darkly idiot, I was really w-worried..."
msgstr ""
"(sollozando) Eso n-no tiene gracia, idiota sombrío, estaba realmente "
"preocupada..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:597
msgid ""
"(smiling) I know, because we too were extremely worried about you. Come, "
"let's heal our wounds, and while we're at that we shall talk."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Lo sé, porque nosotros también estábamos extremadamente "
"preocupados por ustedes. Vengan, curemos nuestras heridas, y mientras lo "
"hacemos hablaremos."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:601
msgid ""
"We can't linger here for long, though, else Argatyr will really come back "
"with a far greater army. We must go to the surface, where your soldiers and "
"Atenak's fight better, and where there's still an intact Aigathol fortress. "
"Come, I'll lead the way."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, no podemos quedarnos aquí mucho tiempo, o Argatyr realmente "
"regresará con un ejército mucho mayor. Debemos subir a la superficie, donde "
"tus soldados y los de Atenak luchan mejor, y donde todavía hay una fortaleza "
"Aigathol intacta. Vengan, yo guiaré el camino."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:616
msgid ""
"Damn you, traitors, don't you know when to DIE?! Send in all reserves, I "
"want to see them dead before me as soon as possible!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos traidores, ¿no saben cuándo MORIR?! ¡Envíen todas las reservas, "
"quiero verlos muertos frente a mí lo antes posible!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/29_From_Darkness.cfg:620
msgid ""
"No! We should have repelled him before he had the chance to send out his "
"full army! Now we'll surely perish here!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Deberíamos haberlo repelido antes de que tuviera la oportunidad de "
"enviar todo su ejército! ¡Ahora seguramente moriremos aquí!"

#. [scenario], id=30_Renewing_Winds
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:4
msgid "Renewing Winds"
msgstr "Vientos Renovadores"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:134
msgid ""
"No, let him be, he may have burst into this fortress on a gryphon but he "
"means no harm. And you, boy, I thought you had died already; it's been "
"months since I last heard of you. Not that I cared much, though; I don't "
"bother to think about self-proclaimed friends who backstab you when "
"situation gets dire."
msgstr ""
"No, déjenlo, puede que haya irrumpido en esta fortaleza en un grifo pero no "
"tiene malas intenciones. Y tú, muchacho, pensé que ya habías muerto; han "
"pasado meses desde la última vez que supe de ti. Aunque no me importaba "
"mucho; no me molesto en pensar en amigos autoproclamados que te apuñalan por "
"la espalda cuando la situación se pone difícil."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:138
msgid ""
"Chief Varag, do not blame us for Argatyr's betrayal. My friends and I never "
"wanted to raise a blade against your warriors, but they started attacking us "
"after their betrayal by the Motsoghnir!"
msgstr ""
"Jefe Varag, no nos culpes por la traición de Argatyr. Mis amigos y yo nunca "
"quisimos levantar una espada contra tus guerreros, ¡pero ellos empezaron a "
"atacarnos después de su traición por parte de los Motsoghnir!"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:142
msgid ""
"(looking puzzled) So you say, but my rider came here that day with a "
"different story. He claimed that, as soon as the disgusting dwarf lord went "
"crazy, your people ran to a safe spot and let my warriors on their own!"
msgstr ""
"(mirando desconcertado) Eso dices tú, pero mi jinete llegó ese día con una "
"historia diferente. Afirmó que, tan pronto como el asqueroso señor enano "
"enloqueció, tu gente corrió a un lugar seguro y dejó a mis guerreros solos!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:146
msgid ""
"Of course we did, they started attacking us before we could even explain "
"that we were no longer on Argatyr's side!"
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que lo hicimos, ¡ellos empezaron a atacarnos antes de que "
"pudiéramos explicar que ya no estábamos del lado de Argatyr!"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:150
msgid "(darkly) Rider? What do you have to say about that?"
msgstr "(con tono sombrío) ¿Jinete? ¿Qué tienes que decir sobre eso?"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:158
msgid "Erm, well, maybe I misunderstood things in the heat of battle..."
msgstr ""
"Ejem, bueno, tal vez entendí mal las cosas en el calor de la batalla..."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:162
msgid ""
"(shaking head) Anyway, what did you come here for? Oh, no, let me guess: you "
"want my help to vanquish some foe again, don't you?"
msgstr ""
"(sacudiendo la cabeza) De todos modos, ¿para qué viniste aquí? Oh, no, "
"déjame adivinar: quieres mi ayuda para vencer a algún enemigo otra vez, "
"¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:166
msgid ""
"More than that: I want to give you a chance to have your revenge on the "
"dwarf who killed your warriors that day, and who certainly killed many more "
"in other battles. My friends and I know where Argatyr is, but we can't hope "
"to win against him with our current forces."
msgstr ""
"Más que eso: quiero darte la oportunidad de vengarte del enano que mató a "
"tus guerreros ese día, y que seguramente mató a muchos más en otras "
"batallas. Mis amigos y yo sabemos dónde está Argatyr, pero no podemos "
"esperar ganar contra él con nuestras fuerzas actuales."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:170
msgid ""
"I confess that the idea pleases me… but the truth is, even though I've "
"managed to unite more orcish tribes under the Burning Fang banner, my army "
"is too worn out to engage another campaign so soon."
msgstr ""
"Confieso que la idea me agrada… pero la verdad es que, aunque he logrado "
"unir a más tribus orcas bajo el estandarte del Colmillo Ardiente, mi "
"ejército está demasiado desgastado para iniciar otra campaña tan pronto."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:174
msgid ""
"It won't be a long campaign. Our goal is the Motsoghnir capital; our army, "
"being strong and swift, will be able to break through their defences - which "
"are depleted by the battles against Skiron and the Aigathol - and reach the "
"Thunder Pinnacle before more platoons are sent to stop us. At the same time, "
"you must attack from the west with your best host; if we attack strongly "
"from two fronts, the Motsoghnir will likely concentrate their forces on "
"their capital."
msgstr ""
"No será una campaña larga. Nuestro objetivo es la capital de los Motsoghnir; "
"nuestro ejército, siendo fuerte y veloz, podrá atravesar sus defensas —que "
"están debilitadas por las batallas contra Skiron y los Aigathol— y llegar a "
"la Cumbre del Trueno antes de que envíen más pelotones para detenernos. Al "
"mismo tiempo, tú debes atacar desde el oeste con tu mejor hueste; si "
"atacamos con fuerza desde dos frentes, es probable que los Motsoghnir "
"concentren sus fuerzas en su capital."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:178
msgid ""
"And then we shall crush the Thunder Pinnacle together... Yeah, seems "
"pleasant enough, but we probably would only reach that mountain two or three "
"days after you, at the very least. Are you sure that you'll manage to deal "
"with them until we arrive?"
msgstr ""
"Y entonces aplastaremos juntos la Cumbre del Trueno... Sí, parece bastante "
"agradable, pero probablemente solo llegaremos a esa montaña dos o tres días "
"después de ustedes, como mínimo. ¿Estás seguro de que podrán lidiar con "
"ellos hasta que lleguemos?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:182
msgid ""
"My friends and I have been through many challenges on realms far from Netjer-"
"Ta, chief Varag, and faced worse foes than Argatyr, but we've managed to "
"return stronger than before. We shall not fall now, so close to our home and "
"to our final goal."
msgstr ""
"Mis amigos y yo hemos pasado por muchos desafíos en reinos lejanos a Netjer-"
"Ta, jefe Varag, y enfrentado enemigos peores que Argatyr, pero hemos logrado "
"regresar más fuertes que antes. No caeremos ahora, tan cerca de nuestro "
"hogar y de nuestro objetivo final."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:186
msgid ""
"I see... You know, boy, when you and your friends came here that time, that "
"blonde friend of yours declared that to be the foundation stone of a good "
"and profitable alliance for our peoples. Unfortunately, misunderstandings "
"delayed the building of that friendship, but I say, let this refreshing wind "
"blow away all those memories like it does with that leaf litter, and push us "
"to a future where we can breath the air of victory and stand on the corpses "
"of our enemies!"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Sabes, muchacho, cuando tú y tus amigos vinieron aquí aquella "
"vez, esa amiga rubia tuya declaró que eso sería la piedra fundamental de una "
"buena y provechosa alianza para nuestros pueblos. Desafortunadamente, los "
"malentendidos retrasaron la construcción de esa amistad, pero yo digo: ¡que "
"este viento refrescante se lleve todos esos recuerdos como hace con esa "
"hojarasca, y nos impulse hacia un futuro donde podamos respirar el aire de "
"la victoria y pararnos sobre los cadáveres de nuestros enemigos!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:190
msgid "<i>(thunderous roar from the orcs)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(rugido atronador de los orcos)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:194
msgid ""
"I make your words mine, chief Varag. When the time comes, I shall send you a "
"razorbird; when you receive it, you'll know that it's safe for you to attack."
msgstr ""
"Hago tuyas tus palabras, jefe Varag. Cuando llegue el momento, te enviaré un "
"pájaro navaja; cuando lo recibas, sabrás que es seguro atacar."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/30_Renewing_Winds.cfg:198
msgid ""
"Be it then. Just don’t kill them all before we arrive, or my warriors will "
"vent our bloodlust on your folks!"
msgstr ""
"Que así sea. Solo no los mates a todos antes de que lleguemos, ¡o mis "
"guerreros desahogarán nuestra sed de sangre en tu gente!"

#. [scenario], id=31_Raging_Thunder
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:4
msgid "Raging Thunder"
msgstr "Trueno Furioso"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:24
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:497
msgid "Withstand the Dwarvish attack for 8 turns"
msgstr "Resistir el ataque enano durante 8 turnos"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:276
msgid "Great Dam"
msgstr "Gran Presa"

#. [message], speaker=Nordri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:292
msgid ""
"And so, as Lord Argatyr had expected, the puny elf-friendly kin-slayers and "
"their disgusting human allies have sneaked through our tunnels and reached "
"our capital..."
msgstr ""
"Y así, tal como Lord Argatyr esperaba, los insignificantes asesinos de su "
"propia raza amigos de elfos y sus asquerosos aliados humanos se han "
"infiltrado por nuestros túneles y han llegado a nuestra capital..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:296
msgid ""
"I won't hear that from ones such as you Motsoghnir, followers of a mad, "
"corrupted dwarf who started a war on his fellow dwarves because of his lust "
"for power!"
msgstr ""
"No voy a escuchar eso de gente como ustedes los Motsoghnir, seguidores de un "
"enano loco y corrompido que inició una guerra contra sus propios hermanos "
"enanos por su ambición de poder!"

#. [message], speaker=Nordri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:300
msgid "(furious) How dare you speak of Lord...!"
msgstr "(furioso) ¡Cómo te atreves a hablar del Lord...!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:304
msgid ""
"AND WHAT ABOUT YOU, ARGATYR? WHY ARE YOU HIDING FROM ME NOW? COME, DON'T BE "
"AFRAID OF MY FRIENDS, IT IS I WHOM YOU SHALL FACE!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y TÚ, ARGATYR! ¿POR QUÉ TE ESCONDES DE MÍ AHORA? ¡VEN, NO TENGAS MIEDO DE "
"MIS AMIGOS, A QUIEN DEBES ENFRENTAR ES A MÍ!"

#. [message], speaker=Suthri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:308
msgid ""
"Lord Argatyr has graced you with his presence far too much already; now you "
"must prove your mettle before earning the honour of fighting him personally, "
"and so he's sent us to test you!"
msgstr ""
"Lord Argatyr ya los ha honrado demasiado con su presencia; ahora deben "
"demostrar su valía antes de ganar el honor de luchar contra él "
"personalmente, ¡por eso nos ha enviado a probarlos!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:312
msgid ""
"If I have to crush a thousand of his warriors to make him show his decayed "
"face again, then be it; no matter what, I shall not leave this valley before "
"punishing Argatyr for all the suffering he's brought upon my people and "
"myself!"
msgstr ""
"Si tengo que aplastar a mil de sus guerreros para que muestre su rostro "
"podrido otra vez, que así sea; pase lo que pase, no dejaré este valle antes "
"de castigar a Argatyr por todo el sufrimiento que ha traído sobre mi pueblo "
"y sobre mí misma!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:316
msgid "That's the spirit, Sigdral!"
msgstr "¡Ese es el espíritu, Sigdral!"

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:320
msgid ""
"Boys, the dwarves before us have been led astray by our corrupted old lord; "
"we must strike him down as soon as we can in order to open their eyes to his "
"madness!"
msgstr ""
"Muchachos, los enanos frente a nosotros han sido engañados por nuestro viejo "
"señor corrompido; ¡debemos derribarlo lo antes posible para que abran los "
"ojos a su locura!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:324
msgid ""
"Remember, we don't have to strike at them for now, we can stay on the "
"defensive until Varag's forces arrive."
msgstr ""
"Recuerden, no tenemos que atacarlos por ahora, podemos quedarnos a la "
"defensiva hasta que lleguen las fuerzas de Varag."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:328
msgid ""
"I just hope that Varag isn't too late; we can't face this dwarvish host on "
"our own..."
msgstr ""
"Solo espero que Varag no llegue demasiado tarde; no podemos enfrentar a este "
"ejército enano solos..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:461
msgid ""
"Damn, this region is so montainous... I think it'll be harder to defeat them "
"here than in the caves."
msgstr ""
"Maldición, esta región es tan montañosa... Creo que será más difícil "
"derrotarlos aquí que en las cuevas."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:465
msgid ""
"Maybe there is a way to reduce their terrain advantage; that dam is giving "
"me ideas..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez haya una forma de reducir su ventaja de terreno; esa presa me está "
"dando ideas..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:475
msgid "What do you... No, wait, are you really..."
msgstr "¿Qué estás... No, espera, ¿realmente estás...?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:479
msgid ""
"I see your plan... I've been to that dam once, it wouldn't be hard to break; "
"it's really old, and it hasn't been repaired in centuries."
msgstr ""
"Veo tu plan... He estado en esa presa una vez, no sería difícil romperla; es "
"muy antigua y no ha sido reparada en siglos."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:483
msgid ""
"Then I could swiftly sneak in there, and soon the rivers would flow freely "
"once more."
msgstr ""
"Entonces yo podría infiltrarme rápidamente allí, y pronto los ríos volverían "
"a fluir libremente."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:487
msgid "Don't worry, Gomatol, we'll help you rebuild it after this war is over."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, Gomatol, te ayudaremos a reconstruirla después de que "
"termine esta guerra."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:491
msgid "(sigh) If there's no other way..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Si no hay otra forma..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:502
msgid ""
"Move any unit to 46,29 and leave it there for 2 turns in order to break the "
"dam"
msgstr ""
"Mueve cualquier unidad a 46,29 y déjala allí durante 2 turnos para romper la "
"presa"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:561
msgid ""
"All right, I'm in... Yes, I think I can do it, though it will take a while..."
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo, estoy dentro... Sí, creo que puedo hacerlo, aunque tomará un "
"tiempo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:565
msgid "Focus on opening it then, we shall cover you!"
msgstr "¡Entonces concéntrate en abrirla, nosotros te cubriremos!"

#. [message], speaker=Esthri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:627
msgid ""
"By the Nine Hells, they've destroyed the Great Dam! You sneaky bastards, "
"you'll pay for that!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por los Nueve Infiernos, han destruido la Gran Presa! ¡Bastardos furtivos, "
"pagarán por eso!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:631
msgid ""
"Now we must be careful not to be caught by the flowing waters, or we'll be "
"in trouble!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora debemos tener cuidado de no ser atrapados por las aguas que fluyen, o "
"estaremos en problemas!"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:803
msgid ""
"There you have it, you impatient bastards, plenty of dwarves for you to kill "
"however the hell you wish!"
msgstr ""
"Ahí lo tienen, bastardos impacientes, ¡montones de enanos para que los maten "
"como demonios quieran!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:807
msgid ""
"You sure were eager to have your revenge, Varag, to have arrived so early, "
"and personally leading your warriors!"
msgstr ""
"Realmente estabas ansioso por vengarte, Varag, por haber llegado tan "
"temprano y liderando personalmente a tus guerreros!"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:811
msgid ""
"Did you really think I'd miss the chance of personally crushing those "
"disgusting Motsoghnir at their very turf? If we take his throne to Grimbek, "
"the Burning Fang Clan will be a legend to be feared for the next thousand "
"years! (to his warriors) Did you hear that, dung-heads? Show some worth and "
"make our name known and respected even across the sea!"
msgstr ""
"¿Realmente pensaste que me perdería la oportunidad de aplastar personalmente "
"a esos asquerosos Motsoghnir en su propio territorio? ¡Si llevamos su trono "
"a Grimbek, el Clan del Colmillo Ardiente será una leyenda temida por los "
"próximos mil años! (a sus guerreros) ¿Escucharon eso, cabezas de estiércol? "
"¡Demuestren su valía y hagan que nuestro nombre sea conocido y respetado "
"incluso al otro lado del mar!"

#. [message], speaker=Nordri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:815
msgid "Come in, you bunch of animals, and meet your end by our axes!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vengan, pandilla de animales, y encuentren su fin por nuestras hachas!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:819
msgid ""
"(booming voice in the distance) Well said, Nordri, but even worthy dwarves "
"like you will fall before so many foes; even a rabble can be quite dangerous "
"if they have greater numbers. They've indeed proven their mettle, so now I "
"shall honour them by attending to this battle myself..."
msgstr ""
"(voz atronadora en la distancia) Bien dicho, Nordri, pero incluso enanos "
"dignos como ustedes caerán ante tantos enemigos; incluso una chusma puede "
"ser bastante peligrosa si tienen mayor número. Realmente han demostrado su "
"valía, así que ahora los honraré asistiendo yo mismo a esta batalla..."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:840
msgid ""
"I must commend you, Wadjet boy; before your return your little friends could "
"do nothing but crawl away from my armies, but now, just look at you all, "
"raising your tiny fists before the Thunder Pinnacle itself..."
msgstr ""
"Debo felicitarte, muchacho Wadjet; antes de tu regreso tus pequeños amigos "
"solo podían arrastrarse lejos de mis ejércitos, pero ahora, mírenlos a "
"todos, levantando sus pequeños puños frente a la propia Cumbre del Trueno..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:844
msgid ""
"Only because you had no restraint in using treacherous methods on us "
"whenever you could, Argatyr; after all, dishonourable tactics best those "
"with dignity sometimes - but not forever, and today I shall give you the "
"reward of your treachery!"
msgstr ""
"Solo porque no tuviste ningún reparo en usar métodos traicioneros contra "
"nosotros cuando podías, Argatyr; después de todo, las tácticas deshonrosas a "
"veces vencen a los que tienen dignidad, pero no para siempre, ¡y hoy te daré "
"la recompensa por tu traición!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:848
msgid ""
"How funny to hear a friend-of-elves talking about betrayal... Victory shall "
"define who is right and who is wrong, my little Sigdral, and you have no "
"hope to win against the power of the King-in-the-Earth!"
msgstr ""
"Qué gracioso oír a una amiga de elfos hablando de traición... La victoria "
"definirá quién tiene razón y quién no, mi pequeña Sigdral, ¡y no tienes "
"ninguna esperanza de ganar contra el poder del Rey-en-la-Tierra!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:855
msgid ""
"So now you're even calling yourself such... (chuckles) I was truly a foolish "
"girl, for having ever loved one such as you..."
msgstr ""
"Así que ahora hasta te llamas a ti mismo así... (riendo entre dientes) "
"Realmente fui una chica tonta por haber amado alguna vez a alguien como tú..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:859
msgid "Come on, friends, now is the time to charge with everything we've got!"
msgstr "¡Vamos, amigos, ahora es el momento de cargar con todo lo que tenemos!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:863
msgid ""
"Beware, everyone, do not attack Argatyr without a plan! Master of the runes "
"as he is, I'm certain that he's using our most powerful arts to strengthen "
"both his defence and his attack!"
msgstr ""
"Cuidado, todos, ¡no ataquen a Argatyr sin un plan! Como maestro de las runas "
"que es, estoy segura de que está usando nuestras artes más poderosas para "
"fortalecer tanto su defensa como su ataque!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:867
msgid ""
"Then let us rain our strongest spells on him all at once! I doubt even he "
"can withstand our own arts for long!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces lancemos nuestros hechizos más fuertes sobre él todos a la vez! "
"¡Dudo que incluso él pueda resistir nuestras propias artes por mucho tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:871
msgid ""
"Not long enough: he'd leave us half-dead with his counter-attacks, and then "
"finish us as we recovered for a second attack. Let me land the first blow on "
"him; strong as his defence runes may be, they are no match for the might of "
"the rune Ansuz..."
msgstr ""
"No por mucho tiempo: nos dejaría medio muertos con sus contraataques, y "
"luego nos terminaría mientras nos recuperamos para un segundo ataque. "
"Déjenme asestar el primer golpe sobre él; por fuertes que sean sus runas de "
"defensa, no son rivales para el poder de la runa Ansuz..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:898
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1038
msgid "Destroy Rune-Lord Argatyr"
msgstr "Destruir al Señor de las Runas Argatyr"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:938
msgid ""
"Sigdral has personal scores to settle with Argatyr; allowing her to attack "
"him might be the best course of action..."
msgstr ""
"Sigdral tiene cuentas personales que saldar con Argatyr; permitirle atacarlo "
"podría ser el mejor curso de acción..."

#. [message], speaker=Vestri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:957
msgid ""
"Boys, stop; stop and turn your axes and hammers to the opposite side, for "
"our true enemy lies behind us. Gomatol, my friend, I apologize for taking so "
"long to see the truth you wanted me to see."
msgstr ""
"Muchachos, deténganse; deténganse y giren sus hachas y martillos hacia el "
"lado opuesto, porque nuestro verdadero enemigo está detrás de nosotros. "
"Gomatol, amigo mío, me disculpo por haber tardado tanto en ver la verdad que "
"querías que viera."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:969
msgid ""
"This is part of the past now, brother. Now, let us free our home and clan "
"from this mad lord and his deceived underlings together!"
msgstr ""
"Esto ya es parte del pasado, hermano. ¡Ahora liberemos juntos nuestro hogar "
"y clan de este señor loco y sus subordinados engañados!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:978
msgid "Wait, uh, so now I can't bash this dwarf here anymore?"
msgstr "Espera, eh, ¿entonces ahora ya no puedo golpear a este enano aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:982
msgid "Of course not, you idiot, his leader is now on our side!"
msgstr "¡Por supuesto que no, idiota, su líder ahora está de nuestro lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:986
msgid ""
"So you choose to die beside the lowly traitors of their own kind, Vestri. I "
"shall not allow it, though; elf-friends and lesser races deserve to die, but "
"traitors deserve a fate far worse..."
msgstr ""
"Así que eliges morir junto a los traidores despreciables de su propia raza, "
"Vestri. Sin embargo, no lo permitiré; los amigos de elfos y razas inferiores "
"merecen morir, pero los traidores merecen un destino mucho peor..."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1016
msgid ""
"Pitiful vermin, I have told you already that you stand no chance against "
"Dwarfdom's ultimate power!"
msgstr ""
"Pobres verminosos, ya les dije que no tienen ninguna oportunidad contra el "
"poder supremo de los Enanos!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1020
msgid ""
"How can it be...? I hit him with all my strength, and it barely scratched "
"his armour!"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo puede ser...? Lo golpeé con toda mi fuerza, ¡y apenas rayó su armadura!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1024
msgid ""
"Just as I thought, he's protected by Elder Runes, the mightiest that we have "
"knowledge of; there's no way they'd fail against an earthly power, but I can "
"dispel them if I get close enough."
msgstr ""
"Justo como pensaba, está protegido por Runas Antiguas, las más poderosas que "
"conocemos; no hay forma de que fallen contra un poder terrenal, pero puedo "
"disiparlas si me acerco lo suficiente."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1028
msgid ""
"Then you focus on reaching that fool, that Nyx and the others shall protect "
"you on the way!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces concéntrate en llegar a ese tonto, que Nyx y los demás te "
"protegerán en el camino!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1034
msgid "To break Argatyr's protection, hit him with Sigdral's Ansuz Rune"
msgstr ""
"Para romper la protección de Argatyr, golpéalo con la Runa Ansuz de Sigdral"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1139
msgid "AAARRRRGGHHHH!!! The Elder Runes are faltering...?!"
msgstr "¡AAARRRRGGHHHH!!! ¿Las Runas Antiguas están fallando...?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1143
msgid ""
"For one thing alone I'm thankful to you, Argatyr: the knowledge of Elder "
"Runes you taught me, especially the first and holiest of them all: Ansuz, "
"whispered to Moradin by the gods themselves, and whose power can suppress "
"that of any other rune. So, <i>my dear</i>, how does it feel to have "
"'Dwarfdom's ultimate power' turned against you?"
msgstr ""
"Por una sola cosa te estoy agradecida, Argatyr: el conocimiento de las Runas "
"Antiguas que me enseñaste, especialmente la primera y más sagrada de todas: "
"Ansuz, susurrada a Moradin por los propios dioses, y cuyo poder puede "
"suprimir el de cualquier otra runa. Entonces, <i>querido mío</i>, ¿cómo se "
"siente que el «poder supremo de los Enanos» se vuelva contra ti?"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1147
msgid ""
"(enraged) You cursed woman, I should have put you back to your deserved "
"place long ago! Allowing you to learn our sacred lore to use it in favour of "
"lesser races was my biggest mistake, but I shall correct it soon enough!!!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecido) ¡Mujer maldita, debería haberte puesto en tu lugar merecido "
"hace mucho tiempo! Permitirte aprender nuestro conocimiento sagrado para "
"usarlo a favor de razas inferiores fue mi mayor error, ¡pero lo corregiré "
"muy pronto!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1153
msgid "Destroy the Rune-Lord Argatyr"
msgstr "Destruir al Señor de las Runas Argatyr"

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1211
msgid "What... What is happening to my body...?"
msgstr "¿Qué... qué le está pasando a mi cuerpo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1215
msgid ""
"Your body is long dead, Argatyr; all that kept it moving was Menon's dark "
"magic, but being successively hit by Elder Runes, magical and physical "
"attacks has gradually dispelled it. Now that there's no more dark magic to "
"sustain your body, it will finally fall apart."
msgstr ""
"Tu cuerpo está muerto hace mucho, Argatyr; todo lo que lo mantenía en "
"movimiento era la magia oscura de Menon, pero al ser golpeado sucesivamente "
"por Runas Antiguas, ataques mágicos y físicos la ha disipado gradualmente. "
"Ahora que ya no hay magia oscura para sostener tu cuerpo, finalmente se "
"desmoronará."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1219
msgid ""
"Nonsense, I... I still wield Ymer's Hammer! It will not allow a direct heir "
"of Moradin to die like this!"
msgstr ""
"Tonterías, yo... ¡todavía empuño el Martillo de Ymer! ¡No permitirá que un "
"heredero directo de Moradin muera así!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1223
msgid ""
"You overestimate yourself, Argatyr. Moradin's Hammers were created for "
"dwarves to wield, but do you honestly think yourself a dwarf still? Your "
"runic armour allowed you to wield it for all this time, but now that it's "
"broken, there's nothing about you that the Hammer will recognize as dwarven. "
"After all, Argatyr, just as my brother told you before dying, you've become "
"a monster."
msgstr ""
"Te sobreestimas, Argatyr. Los Martillos de Moradin fueron creados para que "
"los enanos los empuñaran, pero ¿realmente crees que todavía eres un enano? "
"Tu armadura rúnica te permitió empuñarlo todo este tiempo, pero ahora que "
"está rota, no hay nada en ti que el Martillo reconozca como enano. Después "
"de todo, Argatyr, tal como te dijo mi hermano antes de morir, te has "
"convertido en un monstruo."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1227
msgid ""
"No... there's no way... (suddenly enraged) I only wanted to build a land "
"safe for our people and for you! But you, little ungrateful Sigdral, were "
"too arrogant to accept your place as my wife, you had to go and do as you "
"wished - and look at what you and your lenient brother have brought upon us "
"all!"
msgstr ""
"No... no puede ser... (de repente enfurecido) ¡Solo quería construir una "
"tierra segura para nuestro pueblo y para ti! Pero tú, pequeña desagradecida "
"Sigdral, fuiste demasiado arrogante para aceptar tu lugar como mi esposa, "
"tuviste que ir y hacer lo que quisiste, ¡y mira lo que tú y tu indulgente "
"hermano han traído sobre todos nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1231
msgid ""
"No, <i>you</i> were the one who could only have things your way, you were "
"the arrogant one who couldn't admit seeing other races as friends whom you "
"needed...You were the one who was too arrogant to admit that you needed "
"me... And now, Argatyr, you have lost all the power and honour that you so "
"cherished."
msgstr ""
"No, <i>tú</i> eras el que solo podía tener las cosas a tu manera, tú eras el "
"arrogante que no podía admitir ver a otras razas como amigos que "
"necesitabas... Tú eras el que era demasiado arrogante para admitir que me "
"necesitabas a mí... Y ahora, Argatyr, has perdido todo el poder y el honor "
"que tanto apreciabas."

#. [message], speaker=Argatyr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1235
msgid "(collapsing) Sig-gd-dral..."
msgstr "(derrumbándose) Sig-gd-dral..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1239
msgid ""
"As the ancient Hammer of Ymer fell heavily on the ground, releasing searing "
"sparks, the glimmering eyes of the once powerful Rune Lord blackened – but "
"it was only his damaged armour that reached the ground with a clang; his "
"decayed body, no longer sustained by dark and runic magic, had become ashes."
msgstr ""
"Cuando el antiguo Martillo de Ymer cayó pesadamente al suelo, liberando "
"chispas abrasadoras, los ojos brillantes del una vez poderoso Señor de las "
"Runas se oscurecieron; pero solo su armadura dañada llegó al suelo con un "
"estruendo; su cuerpo podrido, ya no sostenido por magia oscura y rúnica, se "
"había convertido en cenizas."

#. [message], speaker=Nordri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1251
msgid "That can't be... Lord Argatyr has fallen...?!"
msgstr "No puede ser... ¿Lord Argatyr ha caído...?"

#. [message], speaker=Esthri
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1255
msgid "There's nothing we can do now, we've... we've been defeated..."
msgstr "Ya no podemos hacer nada, hemos... hemos sido derrotados..."

#. [message], speaker=Gomatol
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1259
msgid ""
"Now can you see how foolish it was, to keep following such an unworthy lord? "
"Realise and regret your mistakes, my brothers, so that we may rejoin and "
"rebuild our nation."
msgstr ""
"¿Ahora pueden ver lo estúpido que fue seguir a un señor tan indigno? "
"Reconozcan y lamenten sus errores, hermanos míos, para que podamos unirnos y "
"reconstruir nuestra nación."

#. [message], speaker=Varag
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1263
msgid ""
"Forgive the surviving ones if you wish; I will even order my warriors to "
"spare those who surrender. But nobody will deny us the looting of the "
"Motsoghnir capital! We've bled and died, and now we must have our reward! "
"Go, warriors, go and take whatever you want from their city!"
msgstr ""
"Perdonen a los sobrevivientes si lo desean; incluso ordenaré a mis guerreros "
"que perdonen a los que se rindan. ¡Pero nadie nos negará el saqueo de la "
"capital de los Motsoghnir! Hemos sangrado y muerto, ¡y ahora debemos tener "
"nuestra recompensa! ¡Vayan, guerreros, vayan y tomen lo que quieran de su "
"ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1267
msgid ""
"Should we really let them do as they wish? Even if the Motsoghnir remain "
"quiet for now, they'll not forget this humiliation in a thousands years."
msgstr ""
"¿Realmente deberíamos dejarlos hacer lo que quieran? Aunque los Motsoghnir "
"permanezcan callados por ahora, no olvidarán esta humillación en mil años."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1271
msgid ""
"Probably they will have their revenge in the future, and another bloody war "
"will shake our continent, but this is not the time to be concerned about "
"that."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente se vengarán en el futuro, y otra guerra sangrienta sacudirá "
"nuestro continente, pero este no es el momento de preocuparse por eso."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1275
msgid ""
"(kicking Argatyr's armour) There you have it, Argatyr, son of Sigtyr. Your "
"capital ravaged by orcs, your people broken, my family gone, dwarfdom split, "
"and your power nothing but ashes. Wherever your soul is rotting, I hope "
"you're satisfied with your legacy..."
msgstr ""
"(pateando la armadura de Argatyr) Ahí lo tienes, Argatyr, hijo de Sigtyr. Tu "
"capital devastada por orcos, tu pueblo destrozado, mi familia desaparecida, "
"el reino enano dividido, y tu poder reducido a cenizas. Dondequiera que tu "
"alma se esté pudriendo, espero que estés satisfecho con tu legado..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1279
msgid ""
"Shh, Siggy, it's over, it's over, your people are saved and Netjer-Ta's "
"caves will know peace once again!"
msgstr ""
"Shh, Siggy, se acabó, se acabó, ¡tu pueblo está a salvo y las cuevas de "
"Netjer-Ta volverán a conocer la paz!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1283
msgid ""
"Then why don't I feel content in the slightest? Why do I feel like I haven't "
"won anything, only lost even more?!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces ¿por qué no me siento contenta en lo más mínimo? ¡¿Por qué siento "
"que no he ganado nada, solo he perdido aún más?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1287
msgid ""
"No fratricide is worth celebrating, but, as Nyx has said, it was "
"unfortunately necessary to prevent an even greater evil. Come on, friends, "
"let's rest and heal our wounds, for the worst is still to come..."
msgstr ""
"Ningún fratricidio merece celebrarse, pero, como dijo Nyx, lamentablemente "
"fue necesario para prevenir un mal aún mayor. Vamos, amigos, descansemos y "
"curemos nuestras heridas, porque lo peor todavía está por venir..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/31_Raging_Thunder.cfg:1328
msgid ""
"We're taking too long to defeat Argatyr! With Ymer's Hammer in his hands, "
"his strength is limitless, but our numbers are decreasing steadily!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estamos tardando demasiado en derrotar a Argatyr! Con el Martillo de Ymer "
"en sus manos, su fuerza es ilimitada, ¡pero nuestros números disminuyen "
"constantemente!"

#. [scenario], id=32_Light_Against_Light
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:4
msgid "Light Against Light"
msgstr "Luz Contra Luz"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:24
msgid "Defeat General Khamet"
msgstr "Derrotar al General Khamet"

#. [side], type=Aaneb
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:80
msgid "General Khamet"
msgstr "General Khamet"

#. [side], type=Aaneb
#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:85
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:79
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:105
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:134
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:155
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:176
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:135
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:161
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:186
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:82
msgid "Maat'Karian Loyalists"
msgstr "Leales Maat'Karianos"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:184
msgid ""
"Damn it, we've barely entered Maat'Karian territory and we're being attacked "
"already? We've been underground since we returned to Netjer-Ta, how could "
"Maat'Kare have known of our presence here?"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, apenas hemos entrado en territorio maat'kariano y ya nos están "
"atacando! Hemos estado bajo tierra desde que regresamos a Netjer-Ta, ¿cómo "
"podría Maat'Kare haber sabido de nuestra presencia aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Khamet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:188
msgid ""
"I see that you are that group who fought so distinctly in Skiron's invasion "
"before defecting to the traitors' side... I know that you've fought in that "
"battle where the Great Seer crushed Stygia's legion, so I can't understand "
"why you're asking such stupid question. Did you really think that you'd have "
"been able to sneak into our continent unnoticed by the Seer? Do you still "
"have any doubt of his power?"
msgstr ""
"Veo que son ese grupo que luchó tan destacadamente en la invasión de Skiron "
"antes de desertar al lado de los traidores... Sé que lucharon en esa batalla "
"donde el Gran Vidente aplastó la legión de Stygia, así que no entiendo por "
"qué hacen una pregunta tan estúpida. ¿Realmente pensaron que podrían "
"infiltrarse en nuestro continente sin que el Vidente lo notara? ¿Todavía "
"tienen alguna duda de su poder?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:192
msgid "Then that means he's already returned from Argea...?"
msgstr "¿Entonces eso significa que ya regresó de Argea...?"

#. [message], speaker=Khamet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:196
msgid ""
"Of course he has. With the sorry state he's left that accursed empire, he "
"can even afford to leave the front temporarily. Dealing with you ragtag "
"bunch of rebels is more of an issue now, you see..."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí. Con el lamentable estado en que dejó ese imperio "
"maldito, incluso puede permitirse dejar el frente temporalmente. Lidiar con "
"este grupo desharrapado de rebeldes es un problema mayor ahora, ¿ven...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:200
msgid ""
"Listen, general, I understand why you're following Master Menon's orders, "
"but I know him better than you do. Believe me, right now he's not the Master "
"we've always known and admired. He's being controlled by the malicious "
"spirit within the Sky Soul, and you can see that for yourself if you just "
"reflect on how he's been dealing with this rebellion and with Skiron..."
msgstr ""
"Escucha, general, entiendo por qué sigues las órdenes del Maestro Menon, "
"pero lo conozco mejor que tú. Créeme, ahora mismo no es el Maestro que "
"siempre hemos conocido y admirado. Está siendo controlado por el espíritu "
"malicioso dentro del Alma del Cielo, y puedes verlo por ti mismo si solo "
"reflexionas sobre cómo ha estado manejando esta rebelión y con Skiron..."

#. [message], speaker=Khamet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:204
msgid ""
"(laughing) Reflect on what? On how noble it is, that we're finally "
"destroying that evil empire? That Menon Hekare has held our civilisation "
"together throughout the worst storm to strike it in our entire history? "
"Honestly, your dedication to undermining our world escapes my comprehension, "
"but it only strengthens my resolve to destroy you traitors. Rest assured, "
"though, that I shall give you a quick death and a respectful funeral; you "
"were our heroes once."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¿Reflexionar sobre qué? ¿Sobre lo noble que es que finalmente "
"estemos destruyendo ese imperio malvado? ¿Que Menon Hekare ha mantenido "
"nuestra civilización unida durante la peor tormenta que la ha golpeado en "
"toda nuestra historia? Honestamente, tu dedicación para socavar nuestro "
"mundo escapa a mi comprensión, pero solo fortalece mi determinación para "
"destruirlos, traidores. Sin embargo, pueden estar tranquilos de que les daré "
"una muerte rápida y un funeral respetuoso; una vez fueron nuestros héroes."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:208
msgid "(sigh) I'm afraid we have no choice but to fight them..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Me temo que no tenemos otra opción más que luchar contra ellos..."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:212
msgid ""
"(serious) I'll make sure that they feel the least possible pain, if I'm "
"forced to kill them."
msgstr ""
"(seria) Me aseguraré de que sientan el menor dolor posible, si me veo "
"obligada a matarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:221
msgid "So will I."
msgstr "Yo también."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:245
msgid ""
"The last days have been so busy, we haven't had the chance to continue our "
"conversation, Branwyn. So you've come from an island in the middle of the "
"ocean, and your people descend of wildland Argeans?"
msgstr ""
"Los últimos días han estado tan ocupados que no hemos tenido oportunidad de "
"continuar nuestra conversación, Branwyn. Entonces vienes de una isla en "
"medio del océano, ¿y tu gente desciende de los argeanos de las tierras "
"salvajes?"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:249
msgid ""
"Well, I myself knew nothing of my ancestors' name, but yes, that's what "
"Mahyus tells me."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, yo misma no sabía nada del nombre de mis ancestros, pero sí, eso es "
"lo que me dice Mahyus."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:253
msgid ""
"Interesting indeed... You also told me that you're a singer and a poetess; I "
"hope you do love doing these things, because I'll ask you to show me your "
"talent many times. I love poetry and music, but in our culture we "
"unfortunately don't foster the arts very much. You could be very famous in "
"our lands, in fact; I wouldn't mind offering you my patronage when this war "
"is over."
msgstr ""
"Realmente interesante... También me dijiste que eres cantante y poetisa; "
"espero que realmente te guste hacer esas cosas, porque te pediré que me "
"muestres tu talento muchas veces. Me encanta la poesía y la música, pero en "
"nuestra cultura desafortunadamente no fomentamos mucho las artes. De hecho, "
"podrías ser muy famosa en nuestras tierras; no me importaría ofrecerte mi "
"patrocinio cuando termine esta guerra."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:257
msgid ""
"And I'd feel fortunate indeed, to sing my songs to such an interesting and "
"noble audience! (whispering to Mahyus) See, my love, she's actually quite "
"sweet, totally unlike the harsh general you described her..."
msgstr ""
"Y me sentiría realmente afortunada de cantar mis canciones para un público "
"tan interesante y noble. (susurrando a Mahyus) Mira, mi amor, en realidad es "
"bastante dulce, totalmente distinta a la general dura que me describiste..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:261
msgid "(looks offended)"
msgstr "(parece ofendida)"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:265
msgid "(embarrassed) Er, well, you see, Branwyn, I was only jesting..."
msgstr "(avergonzado) Eh, bueno, verás, Branwyn, solo estaba bromeando..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:269
msgid ""
"(stung) Well, I can't get angry at you for that, after all I too mistook you "
"for a glum, bitter, unfeeling Umbra mage, and there you are, all cuddly with "
"such a gorgeous, loving and talented woman..."
msgstr ""
"(ofendida) Bueno, no puedo enojarme contigo por eso, después de todo yo "
"también te tomé por un mago Umbra sombrío, amargado y sin sentimientos, y "
"ahí estás, todo cariñoso con una mujer tan hermosa, amorosa y talentosa..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:273
msgid "(blushing) Shut up, you...!"
msgstr "(sonrojándose) ¡Cállate...!"

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:314
msgid ""
"Apologies for my delay, General Khamet, I was opposed by Warglanders on the "
"way..."
msgstr ""
"Disculpas por mi retraso, General Khamet, me enfrenté a los Warglanders en "
"el camino..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:318
msgid "Romlur, please don't join this fight, I don't want to fight you too!"
msgstr ""
"Romlur, por favor no te unas a esta pelea, ¡no quiero luchar contra ti "
"también!"

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:322
msgid ""
"I tell you the same, Akhen Wadjet. I don't know why you and your friends are "
"doing this, but I know that I can't just sit down while my people's ancient "
"ally, which helped us so much during Skiron's invasion, is being attacked, "
"even if by your hands."
msgstr ""
"Te digo lo mismo, Akhen Wadjet. No sé por qué tú y tus amigos están haciendo "
"esto, pero sé que no puedo quedarme sentado mientras el antiguo aliado de mi "
"pueblo, que nos ayudó tanto durante la invasión de Skiron, está siendo "
"atacado, incluso si es por tus manos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:326
msgid ""
"(sigh) Be it then, Romlur; I just ask you not to personally partake of this "
"battle, I want you to live in order to see that I was..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Que así sea entonces, Romlur; solo te pido que no participes "
"personalmente en esta batalla, quiero que vivas para ver que yo estaba..."

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:363
msgid ""
"So there you are, Romlur! I hope you didn't think me so feeble that I'd give "
"up after that fight; I told you, I'm not resting until I have your pelt "
"adorning my haven!"
msgstr ""
"¡Así que ahí estás, Romlur! Espero que no me hayas creído tan débil como "
"para rendirme después de esa pelea; te dije que no descansaré hasta tener tu "
"pellejo adornando mi guarida!"

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:367
msgid ""
"(angry) You pesky <i>wolf</i>, I've had it with you! If you want to die so "
"much, then I'll happily fulfil your wish!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) ¡Lobo molesto, ya estoy harto de ti! Si tanto quieres morir, "
"¡entonces cumpliré tu deseo con gusto!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:371
msgid ""
"It would be good if we could count on him as an ally, but I doubt that he'll "
"accept siding with humans..."
msgstr ""
"Sería bueno poder contar con él como aliado, pero dudo que acepte ponerse "
"del lado de los humanos..."

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:375
msgid ""
"You can say that again, blood-sucker. Now, Warglanders, sharpen your claws, "
"that today we shall kill traitors!"
msgstr ""
"Puedes repetirlo, chupasangre. Ahora, Warglanders, afilen sus garras, "
"¡porque hoy mataremos traidores!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:390
msgid "Forgive me, friend..."
msgstr "Perdóname, amigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:405
msgid "Menon Hekare, you'll pay for making me do this to my own countrymen...!"
msgstr ""
"Menon Hekare, ¡pagarás por obligarme a hacer esto a mis propios "
"compatriotas...!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:420
msgid "Damn, this is just... wrong..."
msgstr "Maldición, esto simplemente está... mal..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:435
msgid "(tear-eyed) I'm sorry... I'm really sorry..."
msgstr "(con lágrimas en los ojos) Lo siento... Lo siento mucho..."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:447
msgid "Why... Why are you so bent on destroying your own homeland...?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué... por qué están tan empeñados en destruir su propia patria...?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:451
msgid ""
"We don't want to destroy it, Romlur, but to save it from the monster who has "
"taken over it through Master Menon. You will see what I'm talking about in "
"time; now, please go, I really don't want to kill you."
msgstr ""
"No queremos destruirla, Romlur, sino salvarla del monstruo que se ha "
"apoderado de ella a través del Maestro Menon. Verás de qué hablo con el "
"tiempo; ahora, por favor vete, realmente no quiero matarte."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:455
msgid ""
"I have been defeated, and so I must do as my conqueror wants. But I shall "
"follow your steps, Akhen Wadjet, and if I see that you're the actual "
"monster, you'll hear our howls once more..."
msgstr ""
"He sido derrotado, así que debo hacer lo que mi conquistador quiere. Pero "
"seguiré tus pasos, Akhen Wadjet, y si veo que tú eres el verdadero monstruo, "
"volverás a oír nuestros aullidos..."

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:470
msgid ""
"Arrrgghhh! Damn you, traitors! My only comfort is that I may now seek the "
"dirty Myra's spirit in the Ghost Realm, and rip her apart myself..."
msgstr ""
"¡Arrrgghhh! ¡Malditos traidores! Mi único consuelo es que ahora podré buscar "
"el espíritu de la sucia Myra en el Reino Fantasma y destrozarla yo mismo..."

#. [message], speaker=Khamet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:482
msgid ""
"Argh! Damn you, rebels... You've fought so hard for our homeland, why are "
"you trying to destroy it now...?"
msgstr ""
"¡Argh! ¡Malditos rebeldes...! Lucharon tan duro por nuestra patria, ¿por qué "
"intentan destruirla ahora...?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:486
msgid ""
"We've told you already, general, but you've chosen not to believe us. Rest "
"in peace, though, for we hold no grudge against you; you've just been "
"cheated by a monster who took advantage of your love for our homeland."
msgstr ""
"Ya te lo dijimos, general, pero elegiste no creernos. Descansa en paz, sin "
"embargo, porque no guardamos rencor contra ti; simplemente fuiste engañado "
"por un monstruo que se aprovechó de tu amor por nuestra patria."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:495
msgid "Curses, there's no way I can defeat them all on my own...!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, no hay forma de que pueda derrotarlos a todos yo solo...!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:499
msgid ""
"You may go if you wish, Romlur; I meant it when I said that I didn't want to "
"fight you. And, in time, you'll see that our motives are good."
msgstr ""
"Puedes irte si quieres, Romlur; lo dije en serio cuando afirmé que no quería "
"luchar contra ti. Y, con el tiempo, verás que nuestros motivos son buenos."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:503
msgid ""
"I have no more hope to win today, and dying here would be futile. I'll "
"withdraw now, Akhen Wadjet, but I shall follow your steps, and if I see that "
"you're the actual monster, you'll hear our howls once more!"
msgstr ""
"Ya no tengo esperanza de ganar hoy, y morir aquí sería inútil. Me retiraré "
"ahora, Akhen Wadjet, pero seguiré tus pasos, ¡y si veo que tú eres el "
"verdadero monstruo, volverás a oír nuestros aullidos!"

#. [message], speaker=Skorr
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:510
msgid "Come back, you shameless coward! I'm not done with you yet!"
msgstr "¡Regresa, cobarde desvergonzado! ¡Todavía no he terminado contigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:524
msgid ""
"(crying) T-this... T-this is j-just not r-right... T-they were our f-"
"friends, we w-were celeb-brating Stygia's d-defeat with t-them, we laughed a-"
"and drank with t-them..."
msgstr ""
"(llorando) E-esto... E-esto simplemente n-no está b-bien... E-ellos eran "
"nuestros a-amigos, e-estábamos celebrando la derrota de Stygia con e-ellos, "
"reíamos y bebíamos con e-ellos..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:528
msgid ""
"I know how you're feeling, we all know. But we had no choice; it was this or "
"let the Sky Dragon completely corrupt our land..."
msgstr ""
"Sé cómo te sientes, todos lo sabemos. Pero no teníamos opción; era esto o "
"dejar que el Dragón del Cielo corrompiera completamente nuestra tierra..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:532
msgid ""
"(angry) Listen, Merwe - and all of you, fellow Maat'Karians! We have just "
"butchered our brothers and sisters, all because of that cursed jewel! Make "
"no mistake; we will come across more of our own, but I say that we must not "
"falter, we must reach Master Menon and put an end to the Sky Dragon's threat "
"as soon as we can, or this fratricide will drag on for years to come!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Escucha, Merwe, ¡y todos ustedes, maat'karianos! Acabamos de "
"masacrar a nuestros hermanos y hermanas, ¡todo por culpa de esa joya "
"maldita! No se equivoquen; nos encontraremos con más de los nuestros, pero "
"digo que no debemos flaquear, debemos llegar al Maestro Menon y poner fin a "
"la amenaza del Dragón del Cielo lo antes posible, ¡o este fratricidio se "
"prolongará por años!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:536
msgid "(approving murmurs amongst soldiers)"
msgstr "(murmullos de aprobación entre los soldados)"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:540
msgid "Well spoken, Akhen."
msgstr "Bien dicho, Akhen."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:544
msgid ""
"Agreed. You heard Akhen, soldiers, so let us tend to our wounds quickly and "
"resume our march; the sooner we reach Maat'Kare, the sooner this war will "
"end!"
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo. Escucharon a Akhen, soldados, así que atendamos rápidamente "
"nuestras heridas y reanudemos la marcha; ¡cuanto antes lleguemos a "
"Maat'Kare, antes terminará esta guerra!"

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:562
msgid ""
"At last, my reinforcement troops have arrived! Apologies, Akhen Wadjet, but "
"this is the end for you and your companions."
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin llegaron mis tropas de refuerzo! Disculpas, Akhen Wadjet, pero este "
"es el fin para ti y tus compañeros."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/32_Light_Against_Light.cfg:566
msgid ""
"Oh, no, we're overwhelmed! There's no way we'll be able to outrun the "
"swifter Wargs...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, no, estamos abrumados! ¡No hay forma de que podamos escapar de los "
"Wargs más veloces...!"

#. [scenario], id=33_Fiery_Souls
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:4
msgid "Fiery Souls"
msgstr "Almas Ardientes"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:20
msgid "Defeat the Fire Empress Sadjet with Atenak"
msgstr "Derrotar a la Emperatriz del Fuego Sadjet con Atenak"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:146
msgid ""
"It's been a while, children. You've grown a lot since I last saw you, both "
"in size and in power..."
msgstr ""
"Ha pasado un tiempo, niños. Han crecido mucho desde la última vez que los "
"vi, tanto en tamaño como en poder..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:150
msgid "Master, I've never asked anything out of you, but..."
msgstr "Maestra, nunca te he pedido nada, pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:154
msgid ""
"Why do you call me master, rebel leader Atenak? I thought you had forsaken "
"everything when you chose to follow that fool of your uncle."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué me llamas maestra, líder rebelde Atenak? Pensé que habías "
"abandonado todo cuando elegiste seguir a ese tonto de tu tío."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:158
msgid ""
"Please, master, do not call my uncle that! And what makes you think that "
"I've forsaken my friends, my people? If I had, I wouldn't be here, fighting "
"for them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por favor, maestra, no llames así a mi tío! ¿Y qué te hace pensar que he "
"abandonado a mis amigos y a mi pueblo? Si lo hubiera hecho, ¡no estaría aquí "
"luchando por ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:162
msgid ""
"When you chose to rebel, Atenak Aracyne, you should've realised that you "
"were going to fight Maat'Karians and friends who stood by Master Menon, and "
"that you'd have to kill them, or else they’d kill you. I thought your "
"rebellion was inspired by a powerful motivation, but you haven't even "
"thought out the consequences of your acts... You have behaved like a fickle, "
"spoiled teenager who does as she feels like. And to think that such a youth "
"was my disciple..."
msgstr ""
"Cuando elegiste rebelarte, Atenak Aracyne, deberías haberte dado cuenta de "
"que ibas a luchar contra maat'karianos y amigos que se mantenían al lado del "
"Maestro Menon, y que tendrías que matarlos, o ellos te matarían a ti. Pensé "
"que tu rebelión estaba inspirada por una motivación poderosa, pero ni "
"siquiera has pensado en las consecuencias de tus actos... Te has comportado "
"como una adolescente caprichosa y consentida que hace lo que se le antoja. Y "
"pensar que una joven así fue mi discípula..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:166
msgid ""
"Well, Sadjet, now that we're expressing our opinions on each other, allow me "
"to say how disappointed we are, to see that our professors, whom we thought "
"so wise, have fallen so easily to the seduction of the power offered by the "
"Soul!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, Sadjet, ahora que estamos expresando nuestras opiniones sobre cada "
"uno, permíteme decir lo decepcionados que estamos de ver que nuestros "
"profesores, a quienes creíamos tan sabios, han caído tan fácilmente en la "
"seducción del poder ofrecido por el Alma!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:170
msgid ""
"What a baseless argument, if we were doing it for the Soul we'd have used it "
"a thousand times already! Frankly, I have to admit that I underestimated "
"Tewarin; I always thought him power-hungry, irresponsible and mediocre, but "
"he was truly a genius, to have twisted you all and made you follow him so "
"passionately!"
msgstr ""
"Qué argumento tan infundado, ¡si lo estuviéramos haciendo por el Alma ya lo "
"habríamos usado mil veces! Francamente, debo admitir que subestimé a "
"Tewarin; siempre lo creí ambicioso de poder, irresponsable y mediocre, ¡pero "
"realmente fue un genio al haberlos manipulado a todos y hacerlos seguirlo "
"con tanta pasión!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:174
msgid ""
"(enraged) I told you, please do not talk about my uncle like that! He wasn't "
"perfect, but he gave up his happiness and his life to fight an evil that "
"nobody else saw!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecida) ¡Te lo dije, por favor no hables así de mi tío! No era "
"perfecto, pero renunció a su felicidad y a su vida para luchar contra un mal "
"que nadie más veía!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:178
msgid ""
"Then show me what you see and I don't! Show me that you haven't betrayed us "
"all for nothing! Show me that you believe so much that you're on the right "
"side that you'd kill your loved ones for that!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces muéstrame qué ves tú y yo no! ¡Muéstrame que no nos han "
"traicionado a todos por nada! ¡Muéstrame que crees tanto que estás del lado "
"correcto que estarías dispuesta a matar a tus seres queridos por eso!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:185
msgid ""
"So be it, Sadjet Merewi. I will show you the strength of my beliefs, if "
"that's what you want."
msgstr ""
"Que así sea, Sadjet Merewi. Te mostraré la fuerza de mis convicciones, si "
"eso es lo que quieres."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:189
msgid ""
"(sigh) I kind of hoped that we wouldn't have to fight the Fire Empress out "
"of all people, but I suppose I was cheating myself..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Tenía la esperanza de que no tuviéramos que luchar contra la "
"Emperatriz del Fuego de entre todas las personas, pero supongo que me estaba "
"engañando a mí mismo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:193
msgid ""
"She is powerful, but so are we, and we have numbers whilst she is alone. "
"Nyx, be careful, these fire elementals can be specially dangerous to you. "
"And everyone... Leave Sadjet for Atenak. This is clearly their battle."
msgstr ""
"Ella es poderosa, pero nosotros también, y tenemos números mientras que ella "
"está sola. Nyx, ten cuidado, estos elementales de fuego pueden ser "
"especialmente peligrosos para ti. Y todos... Dejen a Sadjet para Atenak. "
"Claramente esta es su batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:215
msgid "Seriously, Atenak? Are you going to attack fire elementals with fire?"
msgstr "¿En serio, Atenak? ¿Vas a atacar elementales de fuego con fuego?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:219
msgid ""
"In a fight of fire against fire, very powerful flames can swallow the weaker "
"ones, causing them to vanish. You should know it, for you were the one who "
"taught me that."
msgstr ""
"En una pelea de fuego contra fuego, las llamas muy poderosas pueden tragarse "
"a las más débiles, haciendo que desaparezcan. Deberías saberlo, porque "
"fuiste tú quien me lo enseñó."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:223
msgid ""
"True, but I hope you're not planning on using this trick on me, for it shall "
"not work."
msgstr ""
"Cierto, pero espero que no estés planeando usar este truco conmigo, porque "
"no funcionará."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:227
msgid "We'll see about that."
msgstr "Ya veremos eso."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:267
msgid "(surprised) What..."
msgstr "(sorprendida) ¿Qué...?"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:271
msgid ""
"I warned you that fire would never work on me, girl, as bright and burning "
"as it may be, not even if it surpasses my own flames, if that's even "
"possible. Do you know why? Because they're my very life force: I can convert "
"any flame into energy that my body can take to replenish itself."
msgstr ""
"Te advertí que el fuego nunca funcionaría conmigo, niña, por brillante y "
"ardiente que sea, ni siquiera si supera mis propias llamas, si eso es "
"posible. ¿Sabes por qué? Porque son mi propia fuerza vital: puedo convertir "
"cualquier llama en energía que mi cuerpo pueda absorber para reponerse."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:275
msgid ""
"Incredible... I thought that I had understood the extent of her power when "
"we fought together, but I never thought she could do that. She's truly a "
"Fire Empress..."
msgstr ""
"Increíble... Pensé que había entendido el alcance de su poder cuando "
"luchamos juntas, pero nunca imaginé que pudiera hacer eso. Realmente es una "
"Emperatriz del Fuego..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:279
msgid ""
"I see... I admit that I underestimated you, Sadjet Merewi; seems like I'll "
"have to find another way to defeat you..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Admito que te subestimé, Sadjet Merewi; parece que tendré que "
"encontrar otra forma de derrotarte..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:283
msgid ""
"And how do you expect to achieve that, when fire magic is your only way of "
"attacking?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y cómo esperas lograrlo, cuando la magia de fuego es tu única forma de "
"atacar?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:287
msgid "I'll show you how soon enough..."
msgstr "Te mostraré cómo muy pronto..."

#. [effect], apply_to=new_attack, type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:300
msgid "explosive fists"
msgstr "puños explosivos"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:355
msgid "(shocked) What...!!!"
msgstr "(impactada) ¡¿Qué...?! "

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:359
msgid ""
"Think about a spear, master: the pole makes up most of it, but it only "
"serves to support the spearhead, which is what actually wounds the enemy. In "
"my attacks, the flames serve as spearheads, and thus I can't hope to harm "
"you. However, if I use my flames as a propelling pole, and my bare hands as "
"the spearhead..."
msgstr ""
"Piensa en una lanza, maestra: el asta compone la mayor parte, pero solo "
"sirve para sostener la punta, que es lo que realmente hiere al enemigo. En "
"mis ataques, las llamas sirven como puntas, y por eso no puedo esperar "
"herirte. Sin embargo, si uso mis llamas como asta propulsora y mis manos "
"desnudas como punta..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:379
msgid "So, professor, is my belief strong enough for you?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, profesora, ¿mis convicciones son lo suficientemente fuertes para "
"ti?"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:383
msgid ""
"(smirking) If it was capable of defeating even me... Thank the Gods I wasn't "
"wrong... (falls down)"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo burlonamente) Si fue capaz de derrotarme incluso a mí... Gracias "
"a los Dioses que no me equivoqué... (cae)"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:387
msgid "What do you mean... Can it be that..."
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir... Puede ser que..."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:391
msgid ""
"Atenak, did you really think me such a fool that I would forever blind "
"myself to what's going on? The Menon that we've always known can't be the "
"tyrant that has been ruling our land these last months; a tyrant who ordered "
"me to execute Smenkhare without even a trial, who executed Sage Imethep with "
"the accusation that he was 'subversive'... When Smenkhare told me about your "
"mission, Akhen, I decided to wait till you returned to act..."
msgstr ""
"Atenak, ¿realmente me creíste tan tonta como para cegarme para siempre a lo "
"que está pasando? El Menon que siempre hemos conocido no puede ser el tirano "
"que ha estado gobernando nuestra tierra estos últimos meses; un tirano que "
"me ordenó ejecutar a Smenkhare sin siquiera un juicio, que ejecutó al Sabio "
"Imethep con la acusación de que era «subversivo»... Cuando Smenkhare me "
"habló de tu misión, Akhen, decidí esperar hasta que regresaras para actuar..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:395
msgid "Then Smenkhare still lives?"
msgstr "¿Entonces Smenkhare todavía vive?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:399
msgid ""
"Wait just a minute, if you were on our side, why did you attack us like this?"
msgstr ""
"Espera un minuto, si estabas de nuestro lado, ¿por qué nos atacaste de esta "
"forma?"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:403
msgid ""
"Yes, he lives; I managed to smuggle him to a deep, abandoned northern cave, "
"where even Menon's clairvoyance can't reach him, and there he must be still. "
"As for the attack... It's just as I've said, I wanted to test your resolve; "
"if it was strong enough for you to even fight those you love, then it would "
"mean that it was worth fighting for. After all, people who truly fight for "
"the well of others never falter in their resolve."
msgstr ""
"Sí, vive; logré sacarlo de contrabando a una cueva profunda y abandonada en "
"el norte, donde ni siquiera la clarividencia de Menon puede alcanzarlo, y "
"allí debe seguir. En cuanto al ataque... Es justo como dije, quería probar "
"su determinación; si era lo suficientemente fuerte como para que incluso "
"lucharan contra aquellos a quienes aman, entonces significaría que valía la "
"pena luchar por ello. Después de todo, las personas que realmente luchan por "
"el bien de los demás nunca flaquean en su determinación."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:407
msgid "I... think I understand. So now will you join us?"
msgstr "Creo... que entiendo. ¿Entonces ahora te unirás a nosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:411
msgid ""
"I will, but as the ruler of Medewar. A keener observer can notice that the "
"civilians have been secretly growing unsatisfied with Menon's rule. No lord "
"has had the guts to follow his people's feelings and defy the central "
"government, but if I do that, I’m certain that others will follow. And you, "
"Akhen, can win us even more adepts; I know that people still hold you as a "
"hero for your exploits during Skiron’s invasion, and they don't believe that "
"the heir of their greatest heroine would have simply abandoned their land "
"for no good reason."
msgstr ""
"Lo haré, pero como gobernante de Medewar. Un observador más agudo puede "
"notar que los civiles han estado secretamente creciendo insatisfechos con el "
"gobierno de Menon. Ningún señor ha tenido el valor de seguir los "
"sentimientos de su pueblo y desafiar al gobierno central, pero si yo lo "
"hago, estoy segura de que otros seguirán. Y tú, Akhen, puedes ganarnos aún "
"más adeptos; sé que la gente todavía te considera un héroe por tus hazañas "
"durante la invasión de Skiron, y no creen que el heredero de su mayor "
"heroína simplemente haya abandonado su tierra sin una buena razón."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:415
msgid ""
"I see your point. Still, even if more Maat'Karians join us, many will remain "
"loyal to Menon. Judging from the general we fought recently, there are those "
"who actually like him for the way he's handling Skiron."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo tu punto. Aun así, aunque más maat'karianos se unan a nosotros, "
"muchos permanecerán leales a Menon. A juzgar por el general con quien "
"luchamos recientemente, hay quienes realmente lo aprecian por la forma en "
"que está manejando Skiron."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:419
msgid ""
"So we have no second to waste; we must rescue Smenkhare and retake Ineb-"
"Hedj, and from there we must send out word that Akhen has returned to free "
"our land from Menon's tyranny."
msgstr ""
"Entonces no tenemos ni un segundo que perder; debemos rescatar a Smenkhare y "
"retomar Ineb-Hedj, y desde allí debemos difundir la noticia de que Akhen ha "
"regresado para liberar nuestra tierra de la tiranía de Menon."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:423
msgid ""
"Have in mind that Menon will try to stop news of your return from spreading; "
"suppressing information is always an efficient way to control people. But "
"this may only serve to increase the civilians' dissatisfaction, and I shall "
"make sure that our side of the story is widely known. Now, go! Our fate in "
"this civil war lies on your shoulders!"
msgstr ""
"Ten en cuenta que Menon intentará impedir que la noticia de tu regreso se "
"difunda; suprimir información siempre es una forma eficiente de controlar a "
"la gente. Pero esto solo puede servir para aumentar la insatisfacción de los "
"civiles, y me aseguraré de que nuestra versión de la historia sea "
"ampliamente conocida. ¡Ahora, vayan! ¡Nuestro destino en esta guerra civil "
"está sobre sus hombros!"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:441
msgid ""
"(sigh) I expected you to be able to defeat me sooner than this... The sounds "
"of our fight have been heard in a nearby loyalist city, and they've sent "
"troops to help me. You have no way out not, rebels..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Esperaba que pudieran derrotarme antes que esto... Los sonidos de "
"nuestra pelea han sido escuchados en una ciudad leal cercana, y han enviado "
"tropas para ayudarme. Ya no tienen salida, rebeldes..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/33_Fiery_Souls.cfg:445
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:572
msgid "This is our end... We've been defeated...!"
msgstr "Este es nuestro fin... ¡Hemos sido derrotados...!"

#. [scenario], id=34_Fires_Of_Defiance
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:4
msgid "Fires of Defiance"
msgstr "Fuegos de la Rebeldía"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:24
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:316
msgid "Retake Ineb-Hedj by defeating General Ahmose"
msgstr "Retomar Ineb-Hedj derrotando al General Ahmose"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Move Smenkhare to Kun'lun's Tower (9,24) in order to get Ineb-Hedj's people "
"to rise"
msgstr ""
"Mueve a Smenkhare a la Torre de Kun'lun (9,24) para que el pueblo de Ineb-"
"Hedj se levante"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:56
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:348
msgid "Death of Smenkhare"
msgstr "Muerte de Smenkhare"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:92
msgid "Ineb-Hedj"
msgstr "Ineb-Hedj"

#. [side], type=Aaneb
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:100
msgid "General Ahmose"
msgstr "General Ahmose"

#. [label]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:177
msgid "Kun'lun's Tower"
msgstr "Torre de Kun'lun"

#. [message], speaker=Sebek
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:194
msgid ""
"What is this noise? Could it be that we're being attacked by vampires, or "
"worse, by Skironians?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué es este ruido? ¿Podría ser que nos estén atacando vampiros, o peor, "
"skironianos?"

#. [message], speaker=Ammun
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:198
msgid ""
"Commander, there's... There's an army of Maat'Karians coming from the hills "
"to the northwest!"
msgstr ""
"¡Comandante, hay... hay un ejército de maat'karianos viniendo desde las "
"colinas del noroeste!"

#. [message], speaker=Ahmose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:202
msgid ""
"So the rumours were true: the rebels are starting another uprising... I did "
"right in requesting reinforcements, I knew that the traitors would come for "
"Ineb-Hedj first, if they rose again. Men, grab your weapons! We must not let "
"this city fall into rebel hands again!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces los rumores eran ciertos: los rebeldes están iniciando otra "
"sublevación... Hice bien en pedir refuerzos, sabía que los traidores "
"vendrían por Ineb-Hedj primero si se levantaban de nuevo. ¡Hombres, tomen "
"sus armas! ¡No debemos permitir que esta ciudad caiga nuevamente en manos "
"rebeldes!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:206
msgid ""
"The city seems better protected than I had expected... Smenkhare, I hope "
"that the people are still on our side, or else we'll have to use all our "
"troops to defeat the government's troops."
msgstr ""
"La ciudad parece mejor protegida de lo que esperaba... Smenkhare, espero que "
"el pueblo todavía esté de nuestro lado, o tendremos que usar todas nuestras "
"tropas para derrotar a las tropas del gobierno."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:210
msgid ""
"Trust me, the citizens of Ineb-Hedj were defiant to the last; they only "
"stopped fighting because I ordered them so, for at the time we had no chance "
"of winning. Just let me reach Kun'lun's Tower, and I shall rally the people "
"of Ineb-Hedj from there."
msgstr ""
"Confía en mí, los ciudadanos de Ineb-Hedj fueron desafiantes hasta el final; "
"solo dejaron de luchar porque yo se lo ordené, porque en ese momento no "
"teníamos ninguna oportunidad de ganar. Solo déjenme llegar a la Torre de "
"Kun'lun, y desde allí reuniré al pueblo de Ineb-Hedj."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:232
msgid ""
"Your people's cities are quite a sight indeed, Mahyus. Just look at their "
"walls; the tallest Chomi building looks tiny next to them, and even so I can "
"see Ineb-Hedj's buildings over them... When this storm's over, I want you to "
"take me to every single one of the Maat'Karian cities, Mahyus."
msgstr ""
"Las ciudades de tu pueblo son realmente todo un espectáculo, Mahyus. Solo "
"mira sus murallas; el edificio más alto de Chomi parece diminuto al lado de "
"ellas, y aun así puedo ver los edificios de Ineb-Hedj por encima... Cuando "
"pase esta tormenta, quiero que me lleves a cada una de las ciudades "
"maat'karianas, Mahyus."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:236
msgid "(smiling) And I'll love showing you all of our land's wonders."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Y me encantará mostrarte todas las maravillas de nuestra tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:243
msgid ""
"Eh, Nyx would love to see the cities of the Maat'Karians too; she couldn't "
"go sightseeing before because people might be afraid of her, but if she's "
"accompanied by a native, she's certain there'll be no problem..."
msgstr ""
"Eh, Nyx también le encantaría ver las ciudades de los maat'karianos; antes "
"no podía ir de turismo porque la gente podría tenerle miedo, pero si va "
"acompañada por un nativo, está segura de que no habrá problema..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:250
msgid "...So? Don't you have anything to say about that?"
msgstr "...¿Entonces? ¿No tienes nada que decir al respecto?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:254
msgid "Oh, sorry, I wasn't listening, what did you say again?"
msgstr "Oh, lo siento, no estaba escuchando, ¿qué dijiste otra vez?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:258
msgid "(sigh) Never mind..."
msgstr "(suspiro) No importa..."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:272
msgid ""
"PEOPLE OF INEB-HEDJ! PEOPLE OF INEB-HEDJ, AWAKE! AWAKE, FOR THE HEIR OF MYRA "
"HAS RETURNED AS PROMISED, TO FREE US FROM MENON'S TYRANNY!"
msgstr ""
"¡PUEBLO DE INEB-HEDJ! ¡PUEBLO DE INEB-HEDJ, DESPIERTEN! ¡DESPIERTEN, PORQUE "
"EL HEREDERO DE MYRA HA REGRESADO COMO LO PROMETIÓ, PARA LIBERARNOS DE LA "
"TIRANÍA DE MENON!"

#. [message], speaker=Sebek
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:276
msgid "Look, it's... It's Lord Smenkhare! I thought he was dead...!"
msgstr "¡Miren, es... es Lord Smenkhare! ¡Pensé que estaba muerto...!"

#. [message], speaker=Balfre
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:280
msgid ""
"Well, clearly he isn't, and he's back to free us – and what's more, he says "
"Akhen Wadjet is back with his promised army!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, claramente no lo está, y ha regresado para liberarnos; ¡y además dice "
"que Akhen Wadjet ha vuelto con el ejército que prometió!"

#. [message], speaker=Sebek
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:284
msgid "This is it, folks! This is our chance to get our freedom back! Charge!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es, gente! ¡Esta es nuestra oportunidad de recuperar nuestra libertad! "
"¡Ataquen!"

#. [message], speaker=Ahmose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:306
msgid ""
"A thousand curses upon these traitors! I didn't want to stain Ineb-Hedj's "
"streets with more blood, but if they insist on turning their weapons against "
"our civilisation, then I have no choice but to stop them at all costs: kill "
"them until they give up, and if they don't, just kill them all!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mil maldiciones sobre estos traidores! No quería manchar las calles de Ineb-"
"Hedj con más sangre, pero si insisten en volver sus armas contra nuestra "
"civilización, entonces no tengo otra opción más que detenerlos a toda costa: "
"¡mátenlos hasta que se rindan, y si no lo hacen, simplemente mátenlos a "
"todos!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:310
msgid ""
"The people of Ineb-Hedj will help us, but they're not well suited to fight "
"the government's troops! We must take the brunt of the loyalist forces, or "
"the civilians will be slaughtered!"
msgstr ""
"El pueblo de Ineb-Hedj nos ayudará, ¡pero no están bien preparados para "
"luchar contra las tropas del gobierno! ¡Debemos soportar el peso de las "
"fuerzas leales, o los civiles serán masacrados!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:320
msgid "Ineb-Hedj's people must have fewer than $units_to_slay losses"
msgstr "El pueblo de Ineb-Hedj debe tener menos de $units_to_slay bajas"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:377
msgid ""
"We're winning the battle, but Ineb-Hedj's people have taken too many losses. "
"What is the point of such victory?"
msgstr ""
"Estamos ganando la batalla, pero el pueblo de Ineb-Hedj ha sufrido "
"demasiadas bajas. ¿Qué sentido tiene una victoria así?"

#. [print]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:386
msgid "Ineb-Hedj can only lose $units_to_slay more soldiers!"
msgstr "¡Ineb-Hedj solo puede perder $units_to_slay soldados más!"

#. [message], speaker=Ahmose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:405
msgid "Damn you, traitors...!"
msgstr "¡Malditos traidores...!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:409
msgid ""
"We're not the traitors here, general, we only want to save our land from the "
"monster that's leading it down a path of corruption. And I'm not referring "
"to Master Menon, but to the Sky Soul, which has managed to corrupt him."
msgstr ""
"No somos los traidores aquí, general, solo queremos salvar nuestra tierra "
"del monstruo que la está llevando por un camino de corrupción. Y no me "
"refiero al Maestro Menon, sino al Alma del Cielo, que ha logrado corromperlo."

#. [message], speaker=Ahmose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:413
msgid ""
"You rebels keep saying that, but the Great Seer has steered Maat'Kare better "
"than any other before him; he's saved us all, he's destroying Skiron, and "
"when he's done with it he will march against the vampires, the orcs, the "
"minotaurs... we'll finally get ridden of all those monsters who keep "
"plaguing us forever, and our people shall reign supreme on both Netjer-Ta "
"and Argea!"
msgstr ""
"Ustedes los rebeldes siguen diciendo eso, pero el Gran Vidente ha dirigido "
"Maat'Kare mejor que cualquier otro antes que él; nos ha salvado a todos, "
"está destruyendo Skiron, y cuando termine con eso marchará contra los "
"vampiros, los orcos, los minotauros... ¡finalmente nos libraremos de todos "
"esos monstruos que nos han plagado para siempre, y nuestro pueblo reinará "
"supremo tanto en Netjer-Ta como en Argea!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:417
msgid ""
"You idiot, can't you see that by slaughtering entire nations we'll be the "
"worst monsters of all?"
msgstr ""
"Idiota, ¿no ves que al masacrar naciones enteras nos convertiremos en los "
"peores monstruos de todos?"

#. [message], speaker=Ahmose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:421
msgid ""
"There's nothing wrong with exterminating those who are hostile to us! But I "
"see that nothing I say will make you realise your foolishness; enjoy well "
"your victory today, rebels, because you shall not last long; there's no way "
"that you can stand victorious for long when you're against the Immortal..."
msgstr ""
"¡No hay nada malo en exterminar a aquellos que son hostiles hacia nosotros! "
"Pero veo que nada de lo que diga les hará darse cuenta de su estupidez; "
"disfruten bien su victoria hoy, rebeldes, porque no durarán mucho; no hay "
"forma de que puedan mantenerse victoriosos por mucho tiempo cuando están "
"contra el Inmortal..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:433
msgid ""
"He's dead... Funny, I've always thought us Maat'Karians so much more "
"tolerant and kind than Skironians, orcs, even the dwarves; never had I "
"imagined our own land to be overtaken by such irrational hatred... "
msgstr ""
"Está muerto... Qué curioso, siempre pensé que nosotros los maat'karianos "
"éramos mucho más tolerantes y amables que los skironianos, los orcos, "
"incluso los enanos; nunca imaginé que nuestra propia tierra sería dominada "
"por un odio tan irracional..."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:437
msgid ""
"True, but let us not feel down; we must inform Sadjet that we've retaken "
"Ineb-Hedj, and not only her, but all other cities, towns and villages as "
"well. We must let the fires of defiance run wild through Maat'Karian lands, "
"until nothing is left of Menon's ambitions but ashes!"
msgstr ""
"Cierto, pero no nos desanimemos; debemos informar a Sadjet de que hemos "
"retomado Ineb-Hedj, y no solo a ella, sino también a todas las demás "
"ciudades, pueblos y aldeas. Debemos dejar que los fuegos de la rebeldía se "
"extiendan salvajemente por las tierras maat'karianas, ¡hasta que no quede "
"nada de las ambiciones de Menon más que cenizas!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:441
msgid "(thunderous roar)"
msgstr "(rugido atronador)"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:445
msgid "Akhen? Is something the matter?"
msgstr "¿Akhen? ¿Pasa algo?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:449
msgid ""
"No, I'm just tired, don't worry... *The bonfires have been lit, Master, and "
"our people's anger is the combustible; will you really let our nation burn "
"for the sake of the Sky Soul...?*"
msgstr ""
"No, solo estoy cansado, no te preocupes... *Las hogueras han sido "
"encendidas, Maestro, y la ira de nuestro pueblo es el combustible; "
"¿realmente dejarás que nuestra nación arda por el bien del Alma del Cielo...?"
"*"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:473
msgid "Ugh! I shouldn't have died now...!"
msgstr "¡Ugh! ¡No debería haber muerto ahora...!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:477
msgid ""
"He would've been invaluable for us to organize the counter-offensive against "
"Menon's troops! How could we let him die?"
msgstr ""
"¡Él habría sido invaluable para organizar la contraofensiva contra las "
"tropas de Menon! ¿Cómo pudimos dejarlo morir?"

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/34_Fires_Of_Defiance.cfg:488
msgid ""
"No...! Damn it, I see loyalist reinforcements coming from the south! We "
"cannot hope to retake Ineb-Hedj from so many foes at once, we're doomed!"
msgstr ""
"¡No...! Maldición, ¡veo refuerzos leales viniendo desde el sur! No podemos "
"esperar retomar Ineb-Hedj de tantos enemigos a la vez, ¡estamos condenados!"

#. [scenario], id=35_Crimson_Earth
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:4
msgid "Crimson Earth"
msgstr "Tierra Carmesí"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:24
msgid "Defeat Lord Suryen"
msgstr "Derrotar al Lord Suryen"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:29
msgid "Leave Masters Cnemhotep and/or Neferkent alive by the end of the battle"
msgstr ""
"Dejar vivos a los Maestros Cnemhotep y/o Neferkent al final de la batalla"

#. [unit], id=Cnemhotep, type=Mage of Storms
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:233
msgid "Master Cnemhotep"
msgstr "Maestro Cnemhotep"

#. [unit], id=Neferkent, type=Mage of Nature
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:245
msgid "Master Neferkent"
msgstr "Maestro Neferkent"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:297
msgid ""
"And at last the rebel leaders get off their pedestal to join the chaos "
"they've caused... Gods, thank you for giving me the chance to finish off the "
"traitors who brought this to our land with my own hands."
msgstr ""
"Y por fin los líderes rebeldes bajan de su pedestal para unirse al caos que "
"han causado... Dioses, gracias por darme la oportunidad de acabar con los "
"traidores que trajeron esto a nuestra tierra con mis propias manos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:301
msgid ""
"Open your eyes, Suryen! Can't you see the path that Master Menon is leading "
"Maat'Kare down? Can't you see that we're becoming the very monsters we've "
"fought just months ago?"
msgstr ""
"¡Abre los ojos, Suryen! ¿No ves el camino por el que el Maestro Menon está "
"llevando a Maat'Kare? ¿No ves que nos estamos convirtiendo en los mismos "
"monstruos contra los que luchamos hace solo meses?"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:305
msgid ""
"So what if we conquer the world? Maat'Kare is a centre of civilisation like "
"Irdya has never seen before; we value culture and the welfare of our people, "
"we don't destroy other nations out of greediness, we treat others fairly "
"regardless of cultural or ethnic differences, so how can expanding our "
"civilisation over the world be wrong? True, thousands would die in the "
"process, but in the end we'd have a better and unified human civilisation!"
msgstr ""
"¿Y qué si conquistamos el mundo? Maat'Kare es un centro de civilización como "
"Irdya nunca había visto antes; valoramos la cultura y el bienestar de "
"nuestro pueblo, no destruimos otras naciones por avaricia, tratamos a los "
"demás con justicia sin importar diferencias culturales o étnicas, entonces "
"¿cómo puede estar mal expandir nuestra civilización por el mundo? Cierto, "
"miles morirían en el proceso, pero al final tendríamos una civilización "
"humana mejor y unificada!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:309
msgid ""
"No truly better world can come out of a path paved with war and tyranny, "
"Suryen, for blood and violence only produce more blood and violence. "
"Besides, do you really think that the Sky Soul will allow this world to "
"become a better place? You're falling for the same lie that the dragons have "
"once fallen, Suryen; they too believed that the Sky Dragon would help them "
"build the world they wanted, and now they're nearly extinct. And this is the "
"fate that awaits our civilisation if we allow his influence to corrupt us "
"any further."
msgstr ""
"Ningún mundo verdaderamente mejor puede surgir de un camino pavimentado con "
"guerra y tiranía, Suryen, porque la sangre y la violencia solo producen más "
"sangre y violencia. Además, ¿realmente crees que el Alma del Cielo permitirá "
"que este mundo se convierta en un lugar mejor? Estás cayendo en la misma "
"mentira en la que una vez cayeron los dragones, Suryen; ellos también "
"creyeron que el Dragón del Cielo los ayudaría a construir el mundo que "
"querían, y ahora están casi extintos. Y este es el destino que espera a "
"nuestra civilización si permitimos que su influencia nos corrompa aún más."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:313
msgid ""
"I see, I heard you rebels were spreading rumours about Lord Menon being "
"controlled by that jewel... And I can't help but to laugh at your "
"foolishness for believing that the wisest master Maat'Kare has had in a "
"thousand years would let himself be cheated by it."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo, escuché que ustedes los rebeldes estaban difundiendo rumores de "
"que Lord Menon estaba controlado por esa joya... Y no puedo evitar reírme de "
"su estupidez por creer que el maestro más sabio que Maat'Kare ha tenido en "
"mil años se dejaría engañar por ella."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:317
msgid ""
"Akhen, I know what you're trying to do, but it's useless; he's determined to "
"uphold his beliefs, and nothing will make him see things differently."
msgstr ""
"Akhen, sé lo que estás tratando de hacer, pero es inútil; él está decidido a "
"mantener sus creencias, y nada lo hará ver las cosas de otra manera."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:321
msgid ""
"I doubt even he will stick to these beliefs when he hears the truth out of "
"Menon's own mouth. Do not kill Lord Suryen; instead, let's just capture and "
"arrest him."
msgstr ""
"Dudo que incluso él se mantenga en estas creencias cuando escuche la verdad "
"de la propia boca de Menon. No maten a Lord Suryen; en cambio, solo "
"capturémoslo y arrestémoslo."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:325
msgid ""
"That will be hard, though; you've only seen him in battle as a commander, "
"leading his soldiers from behind the lines, but I've already seen him in the "
"front lines, and I can tell you, he deserves the nickname he won in his days "
"as a soldier..."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, eso será difícil; solo lo han visto en batalla como comandante, "
"dirigiendo a sus soldados desde atrás de las líneas, pero yo ya lo he visto "
"en las líneas del frente, y puedo decirles que merece el apodo que ganó en "
"sus días como soldado..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:329
msgid ""
"...The Behemoth of Maat'Kare, I know. Still, we must try it; even if we "
"defeat Menon, we'll have other foes to defend against, and losing Suryen "
"would weaken us considerably."
msgstr ""
"...El Behemoth de Maat'Kare, lo sé. Aun así, debemos intentarlo; incluso si "
"derrotamos a Menon, tendremos otros enemigos contra los que defendernos, y "
"perder a Suryen nos debilitaría considerablemente."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:347
msgid ""
"Give up, Lord Suryen, you can't win now! Stop fighting and allow us to prove "
"that what we believe is right!"
msgstr ""
"Ríndete, Lord Suryen, ¡ya no puedes ganar! ¡Deja de luchar y permítenos "
"demostrar que lo que creemos es correcto!"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:351
msgid ""
"You think I'm going down with just this?! Foolish youths, you have no idea "
"who you're dealing with...!"
msgstr ""
"¿Creen que voy a caer solo con esto?! Jóvenes tontos, ¡no tienen idea con "
"quién se están metiendo...!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:355
msgid ""
"Lord Suryen, please stop this folly at once! Frankly, I can't believe that "
"you're so bent on fighting for a tyrant!"
msgstr ""
"Lord Suryen, ¡por favor detén esta locura de inmediato! Francamente, no "
"puedo creer que estés tan empeñado en luchar por un tirano!"

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:359
msgid "I fight... for MAAT'KARE!!!"
msgstr "¡Lucho... por MAAT'KARE!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Volturnus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:376
msgid ""
"By the First, how can he keep standing and fighting with all those "
"injuries...?"
msgstr ""
"Por el Primero, ¿cómo puede seguir de pie y luchando con todas esas "
"heridas...?"

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:382
msgid ""
"By the Moon Spirit, how can he keep standing and fighting with all those "
"injuries...?"
msgstr ""
"Por el Espíritu de la Luna, ¿cómo puede seguir de pie y luchando con todas "
"esas heridas...?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:389
msgid ""
"It's as I've told you, he truly deserves being compared to a Behemoth: a "
"beast whose fury can't be controlled or tamed once it's begun, and whose "
"rampage can only be stopped if..."
msgstr ""
"Es como les dije, realmente merece ser comparado con un Behemoth: una bestia "
"cuya furia no puede ser controlada ni domada una vez que comienza, y cuya "
"embestida solo puede detenerse si..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:396
msgid ""
"...Very well, then; if we have to kill him to continue, then we shall do "
"it... No, <i>I</i> shall do it; I've made you all fight your own countrymen "
"far too much already, I won't burden you with the guilt of killing a former "
"friend any more."
msgstr ""
"...Muy bien, entonces; si tenemos que matarlo para continuar, entonces lo "
"haremos... No, <i>yo</i> lo haré; ya los he hecho luchar contra sus propios "
"compatriotas demasiado, no los cargaré más con la culpa de matar a un "
"antiguo amigo."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:400
msgid ""
"We're not doing it only because of you, Akhen; my uncle too was responsible "
"for starting this war, and so I too have to take responsibility and do "
"whatever I ask of my soldiers to do."
msgstr ""
"No lo hacemos solo por ti, Akhen; mi tío también fue responsable de iniciar "
"esta guerra, y por eso yo también debo asumir responsabilidad y hacer lo que "
"pido a mis soldados que hagan."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Y-you... I've known your parents, boy; both Sahure and Amunet were worthy "
"Maat'Karians... And so I've always thought that their son would be like "
"them..."
msgstr ""
"T-tú... Conocí a tus padres, muchacho; tanto Sahure como Amunet eran dignos "
"maat'karianos... Y por eso siempre pensé que su hijo sería como ellos..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:416
msgid ""
"I will not claim that my words are the absolute truth, Suryen, but one thing "
"I can say: I always do what I find to be the best both for those I care "
"about and for our people, and that I don't even bother about dying if that "
"means giving everyone a chance to live happily and freely."
msgstr ""
"No afirmaré que mis palabras son la verdad absoluta, Suryen, pero una cosa "
"puedo decir: siempre hago lo que considero mejor tanto para aquellos que me "
"importan como para nuestro pueblo, y ni siquiera me molesta morir si eso "
"significa darles a todos una oportunidad de vivir felices y libres."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:420
msgid ""
"If that is so... then I hope that you truly are on the right side... and "
"also that I haven't committed a terrible mistake..."
msgstr ""
"Si es así... entonces espero que realmente estés del lado correcto... y "
"también que no haya cometido un terrible error..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:424
msgid ""
"Your only mistake was wishing to protect our people so much. Rest in peace, "
"Suryen Werses, for we shall not let your sacrifice to be in vain."
msgstr ""
"Tu único error fue desear proteger tanto a nuestro pueblo. Descansa en paz, "
"Suryen Werses, porque no dejaremos que tu sacrificio sea en vano."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:446
msgid ""
"And yet another bloody fratricidal battle takes place... By the Gods, I hope "
"it does end soon, I won't be able to continue this for long."
msgstr ""
"Y otra sangrienta batalla fratricida tiene lugar... Por los Dioses, espero "
"que termine pronto, no podré continuar con esto por mucho tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:450
msgid ""
"Be strong, friends, it will end soon; with Fortress Abhai down, nothing "
"stands between us and Maat'Kare."
msgstr ""
"Sean fuertes, amigos, terminará pronto; con la Fortaleza Abhai caída, nada "
"se interpone entre nosotros y Maat'Kare."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:454
msgid "That means that our next foe will be Menon Hekare himself..."
msgstr ""
"Eso significa que nuestro próximo enemigo será el propio Menon Hekare..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:458
msgid ""
"No, your foe will be the soldiers, elementals and undead that he'll unleash "
"upon us; Menon himself will be <i>my</i> foe."
msgstr ""
"No, su enemigo serán los soldados, elementales y no muertos que él desate "
"sobre nosotros; Menon mismo será <i>mi</i> enemigo."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:462
msgid ""
"I... understand. Let us heal our wounds then, we must be in our full health "
"for our next fight..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Entonces curemos nuestras heridas, debemos estar en plena salud "
"para nuestra próxima pelea..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:475
msgid ""
"Suryen's lieutenants still live, Atenak; do you have any plans for them?"
msgstr ""
"Los tenientes de Suryen todavía viven, Atenak; ¿tienes algún plan para ellos?"

#. [message], speaker=Cnemhotep
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:485
msgid ""
"Lady Aracyne, if I have the right to speak... then know that we deeply "
"regret that it all had to come down to this. I say that not out of fear of "
"punishment, for we shall accept any you may deem fit; we're fully capable of "
"seeing the signs of how the Great Seer's government has grown unfit and "
"nocive for our society's needs. Most importantly: the way you've tried to "
"spare Lord Suryen, here and today, has shown us that you're not the selfish "
"chaos-wreakers that some may have you. Please, accept our surrender, with "
"the promise that, one day, we shall make ourselves worthy of calling "
"ourselves Maat'Karians again."
msgstr ""
"Señora Aracyne, si tengo derecho a hablar... entonces sepan que lamentamos "
"profundamente que todo haya tenido que llegar a esto. Lo digo no por miedo "
"al castigo, porque aceptaremos cualquiera que consideres adecuado; somos "
"plenamente capaces de ver las señales de cómo el gobierno del Gran Vidente "
"se ha vuelto inadecuado y nocivo para las necesidades de nuestra sociedad. "
"Lo más importante: la forma en que intentaste salvar a Lord Suryen, aquí y "
"hoy, nos ha mostrado que no son los egoístas causantes de caos que algunos "
"pueden creer. Por favor, acepten nuestra rendición, con la promesa de que, "
"algún día, nos haremos dignos de llamarnos maat'karianos nuevamente."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:489
msgid ""
"Your words remind me of what Lady Sadjet Merewi has told me quite "
"recently... If this is how you truly feel, Master Cnemhotep, then let this "
"be your compensation: you shall join us in the oncoming confrontation with "
"Menon Hekare, and help us depose him. After all, the Gods know we shall need "
"every power we can rely on to face him."
msgstr ""
"Tus palabras me recuerdan lo que Lady Sadjet Merewi me dijo hace poco... Si "
"esto es lo que realmente sientes, Maestro Cnemhotep, entonces que esta sea "
"tu compensación: te unirás a nosotros en la confrontación que se avecina con "
"Menon Hekare, y nos ayudarás a derrocarlo. Después de todo, los Dioses saben "
"que necesitaremos todo el poder en el que podamos apoyarnos para enfrentarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Cnemhotep
#. [message], speaker=Neferkent
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:493
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:507
msgid ""
"(surprised) In that case, Lady Aracyne, I vow, on my own life, to help your "
"cause prevail, if that will serve to atone, even if but a little, for my "
"past mistakes."
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) En ese caso, Señora Aracyne, juro, por mi propia vida, ayudar "
"a que tu causa prevalezca, si eso sirve para expiar, aunque sea un poco, mis "
"errores pasados."

#. [message], speaker=Neferkent
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:499
msgid ""
"Lady Aracyne, if I have the right to speak... then know that we deeply "
"regret that it all had to come down to this. I say that not out of fear of "
"punishment, for we shall accept any you may deem fit; we're fully capable of "
"seeing the signs of how the Great Seer's government has grown unfit and "
"nocive for our society's needs. Most importantly: the way you've tried to "
"spare Lord Suryen, here and today, has shown us that you're not the selfish "
"chaos-wreakers that some may have you. Please, accept our surrender, with "
"the promise that, one day, we shall make ourselves worthy of calling "
"ourselves Maat'Karians."
msgstr ""
"Señora Aracyne, si tengo derecho a hablar... entonces sepan que lamentamos "
"profundamente que todo haya tenido que llegar a esto. Lo digo no por miedo "
"al castigo, porque aceptaremos cualquiera que consideres adecuado; somos "
"plenamente capaces de ver las señales de cómo el gobierno del Gran Vidente "
"se ha vuelto inadecuado y nocivo para las necesidades de nuestra sociedad. "
"Lo más importante: la forma en que intentaste salvar a Lord Suryen, aquí y "
"hoy, nos ha mostrado que no son los egoístas causantes de caos que algunos "
"pueden creer. Por favor, acepten nuestra rendición, con la promesa de que, "
"algún día, nos haremos dignos de llamarnos maat'karianos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:503
msgid ""
"(smiling) Your words remind me of what Lady Sadjet Merewi has told me quite "
"recently... If this is how you truly feel, Master Neferkent, then let this "
"be your compensation: you shall join us in the oncoming confrontation with "
"Menon Hekare, and help us depose him. After all, the Gods know we shall need "
"every power we can rely on to face him."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Tus palabras me recuerdan lo que Lady Sadjet Merewi me dijo hace "
"poco... Si esto es lo que realmente sientes, Maestro Neferkent, entonces que "
"esta sea tu compensación: te unirás a nosotros en la confrontación que se "
"avecina con Menon Hekare, y nos ayudarás a derrocarlo. Después de todo, los "
"Dioses saben que necesitaremos todo el poder en el que podamos apoyarnos "
"para enfrentarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:528
msgid "Akhen, if you don't mind, I'd like to speak with you, in private."
msgstr "Akhen, si no te molesta, me gustaría hablar contigo, en privado."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:532
msgid ""
"All right... Let's go to the main tower, there must be no one there right "
"now."
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo... Vamos a la torre principal, allí no debe haber nadie en este "
"momento."

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:556
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:702
msgid ""
"I now go join the ancestors in the Ghost Realm... Friends, make sure the "
"next generations find a better and safer Netjer-Ta to live..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora voy a unirme a los ancestros en el Reino Fantasma... Amigos, "
"asegúrense de que las próximas generaciones encuentren un Netjer-Ta mejor y "
"más seguro para vivir..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:560
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:706
msgid ""
"Rest in peace, noble Romlur, that we shall not allow the Sky Dragon to "
"destroy everything we've fought so hard for."
msgstr ""
"Descansa en paz, noble Romlur, porque no permitiremos que el Dragón del "
"Cielo destruya todo por lo que hemos luchado tan duro."

#. [message], speaker=Suryen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/35_Crimson_Earth.cfg:568
msgid ""
"I must acknowledge your valour, rebels, but this is the end of the line for "
"you: reinforcements, attack with everything you've got!"
msgstr ""
"Debo reconocer su valor, rebeldes, pero este es el final del camino para "
"ustedes: ¡refuerzos, ataquen con todo lo que tienen!"

#. [scenario], id=36_Master_Of_Four_Lights
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:4
msgid "The Master of Four Lights"
msgstr "El Maestro de las Cuatro Luces"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:24
msgid "Find a way to reach Menon Hekare"
msgstr "Encuentra una forma de llegar a Menon Hekare"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:28
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:617
msgid "Master Atseger must not be killed"
msgstr "No se debe matar al Maestro Atseger"

#. [unit], id=Sethi, type=Necromancer
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:255
msgid "Master Sethi"
msgstr "Maestro Sethi"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Maat'Karians, prepare yourselves, the traitors have finally come to storm "
"our city!"
msgstr ""
"Maat'karianos, prepárense, ¡los traidores finalmente han venido a asaltar "
"nuestra ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Headmistress, please stay out of this. The Academy has a tradition of never "
"getting involved in internal affairs, and so it should remain neutral, to "
"protect its students and knowledge."
msgstr ""
"Directora, por favor quédate fuera de esto. La Academia tiene una tradición "
"de nunca involucrarse en asuntos internos, y por eso debe permanecer "
"neutral, para proteger a sus estudiantes y su conocimiento."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:360
msgid ""
"There is no neutrality to be taken when our city is under attack, not even "
"by those once counted as friends, not when they seek to destroy everything "
"we've fought for!"
msgstr ""
"No hay neutralidad que tomar cuando nuestra ciudad está bajo ataque, ni "
"siquiera por aquellos que una vez contábamos como amigos, ¡no cuando buscan "
"destruir todo por lo que hemos luchado!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:364
msgid ""
"Leave them be, Atseger... There's nothing that we can say now to turn them "
"back to the light, they've been hopelessly corrupted already..."
msgstr ""
"Déjalos, Atseger... Ya no hay nada que podamos decir para hacerlos volver a "
"la luz, ya han sido corrompidos sin esperanza..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:368
msgid ""
"Beware, Menon's coming... But... His energy, it feels different from "
"before... not simply overwhelming, but also... full of hatred and violence..."
msgstr ""
"Cuidado, Menon se acerca... Pero... Su energía se siente diferente de "
"antes... no simplemente abrumadora, sino también... llena de odio y "
"violencia..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:381
msgid "Master...!"
msgstr "¡Maestro...!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:385
msgid ""
"(coldly) The bad son to home returns too... It's been a long while, Akhen; I "
"even thought that you had found yourself some beautiful foreign place to "
"settle and forgotten about your homeland, so long you stayed overseas. It "
"gladdens me to see that, at the very least, you've got the courage to face "
"the consequences of your actions."
msgstr ""
"(fríamente) El hijo malo también regresa a casa... Ha pasado mucho tiempo, "
"Akhen; incluso pensé que habías encontrado algún hermoso lugar extranjero "
"para establecerte y te habías olvidado de tu patria, tanto tiempo te "
"quedaste en el extranjero. Me alegra ver que, al menos, tienes el coraje "
"para enfrentar las consecuencias de tus acciones."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:389
msgid ""
"What has happened to him? It's as if that gentle Master Menon that we used "
"to know had never existed..."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué le ha pasado? Es como si ese amable Maestro Menon que conocíamos nunca "
"hubiera existido..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:393
msgid "Could it be... that I was too late...?"
msgstr "¿Podría ser... que llegué demasiado tarde...?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:397
msgid ""
"Menon Hekare, you've tyrannized us for far too long; you've killed those who "
"opposed you, thus violating that which we value the most: our freedom. As if "
"that wasn't enough, you gave no heed to the voice of the majority, and by "
"doing so you tore apart our nation, dragging it into a war infinitely worse "
"than Skiron's invasion! But we will not allow you to do as you wish; we "
"shall dethrone you, and you shall pay for all the deaths you've caused with "
"your lust for power!"
msgstr ""
"Menon Hekare, nos has tiranizado por demasiado tiempo; has matado a aquellos "
"que se opusieron a ti, violando así lo que más valoramos: nuestra libertad. "
"Como si eso no fuera suficiente, no prestaste atención a la voz de la "
"mayoría, y al hacerlo destrozaste nuestra nación, arrastrándola a una guerra "
"infinitamente peor que la invasión de Skiron! Pero no te permitiremos hacer "
"lo que quieras; te derrocaremos, ¡y pagarás por todas las muertes que has "
"causado con tu ambición de poder!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:401
msgid ""
"Opposing me is opposing Maat'Kare, and I shall not allow it to be hindered "
"any more! I shall make the City of the Sun shine supreme above all others, "
"even if that means crushing the fools who want to undermine it from within!"
msgstr ""
"Oponerse a mí es oponerse a Maat'Kare, ¡y no permitiré que sea obstaculizado "
"más! Haré que la Ciudad del Sol brille suprema por encima de todas las "
"demás, incluso si eso significa aplastar a los tontos que quieren socavarla "
"desde dentro!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:405
msgid ""
"Akhen, please, do not lose your heart now, or there's no way we'll be able "
"to win!"
msgstr ""
"Akhen, por favor, no pierdas el ánimo ahora, ¡o no habrá forma de que "
"podamos ganar!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:409
msgid ""
"I know... Sorry if my hesitation made you doubt me, friends, I promise I "
"won't let you down again. Now, everyone! This is what we've been preparing "
"for so many months, this is the promised battle that will decide the future "
"not only of Maat'Kare, but of the entire Irdya! Lose it, and you'll allow "
"the Sky Dragon to do as he wishes! Will you allow it to happen?"
msgstr ""
"Lo sé... Perdón si mi duda los hizo dudar de mí, amigos, prometo que no los "
"defraudaré de nuevo. ¡Ahora, todos! Esto es por lo que nos hemos estado "
"preparando durante tantos meses, esta es la batalla prometida que decidirá "
"el futuro no solo de Maat'Kare, ¡sino de toda Irdya! ¡Si la perdemos, "
"permitirán que el Dragón del Cielo haga lo que quiera! ¿Lo permitirán?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:413
msgid "NO!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Romlur
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:417
msgid "No!!!"
msgstr "¡No!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:421
msgid "Not in a thousands years!!!"
msgstr "¡Ni en mil años!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:425
msgid "Then TO BATTLE!!!"
msgstr "¡Entonces A LA BATALLA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Sethi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:429
msgid ""
"Let them come! Our living numbers are low, but the skeletons of our "
"ancestors and our fallen enemies alike shall rise to defend our city!"
msgstr ""
"¡Que vengan! Nuestros números vivos son bajos, ¡pero los esqueletos de "
"nuestros ancestros y de nuestros enemigos caídos por igual se levantarán "
"para defender nuestra ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:433
msgid ""
"Fear not the spawn of darkness, soldiers, for we have the power of light on "
"our side! Akhen, this is the time!"
msgstr ""
"No teman a la progenie de la oscuridad, soldados, ¡porque tenemos el poder "
"de la luz de nuestro lado! Akhen, ¡este es el momento!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:437
msgid "I see; (turning his face and hands skywards) Lumina Nume Ourania..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo; (volviendo su rostro y manos hacia el cielo) Lumina Nume Ourania..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:441
msgid "...OURANIA FULGURAS DESCENDIA!!!"
msgstr "...¡OURANIA FULGURAS DESCENDIA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:468
msgid "Argh! This light...!"
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡Esta luz...!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:472
msgid "Amazing! They specialized in this spell in such a short span...!"
msgstr "¡Increíble! Se especializaron en este hechizo en tan poco tiempo...!"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:476
msgid "The Gods of Light are on our side, soldiers! CHARGE!!!"
msgstr "¡Los Dioses de la Luz están de nuestro lado, soldados! ¡CARGUEN!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:492
msgid ""
"(enraged) No way... There's no way I will allow dirty traitors to bring down "
"this holy city..."
msgstr ""
"(enfurecido) De ninguna manera... No hay forma de que permita que sucios "
"traidores destruyan esta ciudad santa..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:499
msgid ""
"If my power alone isn't enough to stop them, then I have no choice but to "
"borrow some more from it..."
msgstr ""
"Si mi poder solo no es suficiente para detenerlos, entonces no tengo otra "
"opción más que tomar un poco más de él..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:504
msgid "Oh my Gods, please tell me he isn't..."
msgstr "Oh por los Dioses, por favor dime que no está..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:508
msgid ""
"Master, no!!! Remember what happened to Myra when she used it! Please, do "
"not let the Sky Soul control you completely!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maestro, no!!! ¡Recuerda lo que le pasó a Myra cuando lo usó! ¡Por favor, "
"no dejes que el Alma del Cielo te controle completamente!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:512
msgid ""
"Myra used the Soul to save her people; were it not for this jewel, she and "
"everyone else would have perished before the dragons, and we wouldn't even "
"be here today. This proves that even an evil can come for good..."
msgstr ""
"Myra usó el Alma para salvar a su pueblo; si no fuera por esta joya, ella y "
"todos los demás habrían perecido ante los dragones, y ni siquiera estaríamos "
"aquí hoy. Esto demuestra que incluso un mal puede servir para el bien..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:516
msgid "But not like this! Master, I beg you, don't...!"
msgstr "¡Pero no así! ¡Maestro, te lo suplico, no...!"

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:520
msgid "It's no good, Akhen, the jewel has started to glow!"
msgstr "No sirve de nada, Akhen, ¡la joya ha empezado a brillar!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:525
msgid ""
"<i>Akhen, Menon's mind is already taken by Svarballi! I'm going to enter it "
"as well, this should confuse him long enough for you to take the jewel away "
"from him, but it will also weaken me!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Akhen, ¡la mente de Menon ya está tomada por Svarballi! Voy a entrar en "
"ella también, esto debería confundirlo el tiempo suficiente para que le "
"quites la joya, ¡pero también me debilitará!</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:529
msgid "Do it then, and leave the rest to me!"
msgstr "¡Hazlo entonces, y déjame el resto a mí!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:572
msgid "AAARRGGHHHH!!! What... What is this... My mind...!"
msgstr "¡AAARRGGHHHH!!! ¿Qué... qué es esto... mi mente...!"

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:576
msgid "What's happening with him?"
msgstr "¿Qué le está pasando?"

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:580
msgid ""
"I don't know, but it's stopped him from using the Sky Soul. Charge, "
"everyone! We can't let this chance slip by!"
msgstr ""
"No lo sé, pero lo ha detenido de usar el Alma del Cielo. ¡Carguen, todos! "
"¡No podemos dejar pasar esta oportunidad!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:584
msgid "(in pain) Atseger, you... deal with them... I must... retreat now..."
msgstr ""
"(con dolor) Atseger, tú... encárgate de ellos... debo... retirarme ahora..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:597
msgid "As you wish, Master! Don't worry, I shall not let them defile our city!"
msgstr ""
"¡Como desees, Maestro! No te preocupes, ¡no permitiré que profanen nuestra "
"ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:601
msgid ""
"Damn it, I must reach Master as soon as possible, there's no guarantee that "
"he won't use the jewel again!"
msgstr ""
"Maldición, debo llegar al Maestro lo antes posible, ¡no hay garantía de que "
"no use la joya de nuevo!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:605
msgid "Focus on reaching the Foundation Square then, we shall cover you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Concéntrate entonces en llegar a la Plaza de la Fundación, nosotros te "
"cubriremos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:613
msgid "Lead Akhen to Maat'Kare's Foundation Square (Menon's keep)"
msgstr ""
"Lleva a Akhen a la Plaza de la Fundación de Maat'Kare (el torreón de Menon)"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:667
msgid "Now, Sky Dragon, you have nowhere to run..."
msgstr "Ahora, Dragón del Cielo, no tienes adónde huir..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:674
msgid "Damn you, traitors! I won't allow you to lay a finger on my Master!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos traidores! ¡No permitiré que pongan un dedo sobre mi Maestro!"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:678
msgid "And I won't allow you lay a finger on my Akhen!!!"
msgstr "¡Y yo no permitiré que pongas un dedo sobre mi Akhen!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Oh damn, she won't stand a chance against Atseger! Mahyus, we have to help "
"them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh maldición, ella no tendrá ninguna oportunidad contra Atseger! ¡Mahyus, "
"tenemos que ayudarlos!"

#. [message], speaker=Cnemhotep
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:718
msgid ""
"A fitting end for someone who betrayed the trust of the people... Please, "
"Lady Aracyne, make sure our nation survives this chaos..."
msgstr ""
"Un final apropiado para alguien que traicionó la confianza del pueblo... Por "
"favor, Señora Aracyne, asegúrate de que nuestra nación sobreviva a este "
"caos..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:722
msgid ""
"Rest in peace, Master Cnmehotep, for we shall not let Maat'Kare fall to ruin."
msgstr ""
"Descansa en paz, Maestro Cnemhotep, porque no dejaremos que Maat'Kare caiga "
"en la ruina."

#. [message], speaker=Neferkent
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:734
msgid ""
"A fitting end for someone who betrayed the ideals she swore to uphold... "
"Please, Lady Aracyne, make sure our nation survives this chaos..."
msgstr ""
"Un final apropiado para alguien que traicionó los ideales que juró "
"defender... Por favor, Señora Aracyne, asegúrate de que nuestra nación "
"sobreviva a este caos..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/36_Master_Of_Four_Lights.cfg:738
msgid ""
"Rest in peace, Master Neferkent, for we shall not let Maat'Kare's light fade."
msgstr ""
"Descansa en paz, Maestro Neferkent, porque no dejaremos que la luz de "
"Maat'Kare se apague."

#. [scenario], id=37_Forces_Of_Nature
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:4
msgid "Forces of Nature"
msgstr "Fuerzas de la Naturaleza"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:21
msgid "Defeat Menon Hekare"
msgstr "Derrotar a Menon Hekare"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:29
msgid "Akhen may recruit/recall from 9,11"
msgstr "Akhen puede reclutar/reincorporar desde 9,11"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Master, it's over. Your loyalists are suffering defeat after defeat all over "
"Tarkyn's Meadows, you’ve lost your best general, Maat’Kare is no longer in "
"your power and your forces have been depleted. It is time for you to face "
"your own soul, and free it from the Sky Dragon's control."
msgstr ""
"Maestro, se acabó. Tus leales están sufriendo derrota tras derrota por todo "
"los Prados de Tarkyn, has perdido a tu mejor general, Maat'Kare ya no está "
"bajo tu poder y tus fuerzas se han agotado. Es hora de que enfrentes tu "
"propia alma, y la liberes del control del Dragón del Cielo."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:237
msgid ""
"'My forces have been depleted'? 'Face my own soul'? I am disappointed, "
"Akhen; never would I have thought that you underestimated me so. Your little "
"trick may have forced me to withdraw, but my power is far from being "
"depleted! I was weak to resort to the Sky Soul, I don't need it to win, I "
"shall crush you all with my own strength!"
msgstr ""
"«¿Mis fuerzas se han agotado»? «¿Enfrentar mi propia alma»? Estoy "
"decepcionado, Akhen; nunca habría pensado que me subestimaras tanto. Tu "
"pequeño truco puede haberme obligado a retirarme, ¡pero mi poder está lejos "
"de estar agotado! Fui débil al recurrir al Alma del Cielo, no lo necesito "
"para ganar, ¡los aplastaré a todos con mi propia fuerza!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Friends, please don't interfere; we've fought together for all this time, "
"but this battle I must fight alone."
msgstr ""
"Amigos, por favor no interfieran; hemos luchado juntos todo este tiempo, "
"pero esta batalla debo librarla solo."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:256
msgid "Well then, Akhen, show your master what you have learned so far..."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien entonces, Akhen, muéstrale a tu maestro lo que has aprendido hasta "
"ahora..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:265
msgid ""
"Incredible... They were fighting so fiercely just now, summoning legions of "
"elementals, and they still have that much power and energy left..."
msgstr ""
"Increíble... Estaban luchando tan ferozmente hace un momento, invocando "
"legiones de elementales, y todavía les queda tanto poder y energía..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:269
msgid ""
"Do not be impressed, Mahyus Meritane. You're watching a force of nature in "
"the guise of a man; a man who was paramount amongst Maat’Kare’s mages for "
"seven centuries, who single-handedly defeated the Order of the Windsong, and "
"before whom even Skiron's Lich-Lords cower in fear. But I acknowledge "
"Akhen's worth for being able to withstand Master Menon's fury..."
msgstr ""
"No te impresiones, Mahyus Meritane. Estás viendo una fuerza de la naturaleza "
"con forma de hombre; un hombre que fue el principal entre los magos de "
"Maat'Kare durante siete siglos, que derrotó él solo a la Orden de las Hijas "
"del Viento, y ante quien incluso los Señores Liche de Skiron se acobardan de "
"miedo. Pero reconozco el mérito de Akhen por ser capaz de resistir la furia "
"del Maestro Menon..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:273
msgid ""
"Now it's you who shouldn't be impressed, Atseger. Akhen may not have Menon's "
"power, but his strength lies in his resolve; a resolve to protect his "
"friends, his people, his country, everything he holds dear. Such "
"determination is, too, like a force of nature, and so it cannot be easily "
"tamed."
msgstr ""
"Ahora eres tú quien no debería impresionarse, Atseger. Akhen puede no tener "
"el poder de Menon, pero su fuerza radica en su determinación; una "
"determinación de proteger a sus amigos, a su pueblo, a su país, todo lo que "
"le es querido. Tal determinación también es como una fuerza de la "
"naturaleza, y por eso no puede ser domada fácilmente."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:291
msgid "My power... has failed me...?"
msgstr "¿Mi poder... me ha fallado...?"

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:295
msgid "NO!!! Master is losing...?!"
msgstr "¡NO!!! ¿El Maestro está perdiendo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:299
msgid ""
"At long last, Akhen... You've realised and fulfilled your true potential... "
"How pathetic that I, of all people, was unable to realise... how strong you "
"had become..."
msgstr ""
"Por fin, Akhen... Has realizado y cumplido tu verdadero potencial... Qué "
"patético que yo, de entre todas las personas, no haya podido darme cuenta... "
"de lo fuerte que te habías vuelto..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:303
msgid ""
"You have won, Akhen Wadjet; your belief and determination were stronger than "
"mine, so now... please, destroy me once and for all..."
msgstr ""
"Has ganado, Akhen Wadjet; tu creencia y determinación fueron más fuertes que "
"las mías, así que ahora... por favor, destrúyeme de una vez por todas..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:307
msgid ""
"I would never do that, Master. You have just been corrupted by the Sky Soul, "
"but no longer; stand still, that I will chase away your..."
msgstr ""
"Nunca haría eso, Maestro. Acabas de ser corrompido por el Alma del Cielo, "
"pero ya no; quédate quieto, que yo alejaré tu..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:314
msgid "What's happening..."
msgstr "¿Qué está pasando...?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:318
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:380
msgid "AKHEN, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡AKHEN, NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:425
msgid "<i>You're alone...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Estás solo...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:429
msgid "<i>Well, it's not like you're not used to it already, right...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Bueno, no es como si no estuvieras acostumbrado ya, ¿verdad...?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:433
msgid ""
"<i>Your power has been both your virtue and your curse. It's allowed you to "
"accomplish much for your people, but it's also discouraged everyone from "
"getting near you. Your power has made you god-like, a being above common "
"humans, a being who would never be interested in such mundane things as joy, "
"friendship, love; a being who couldn't possibly be too weak as to need human "
"warmth, or a friendly hug...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Tu poder ha sido tanto tu virtud como tu maldición. Te ha permitido "
"lograr mucho por tu pueblo, pero también ha desanimado a todos a acercarse a "
"ti. Tu poder te ha hecho como un dios, un ser por encima de los humanos "
"comunes, un ser que nunca se interesaría en cosas mundanas como la alegría, "
"la amistad, el amor; un ser que no podría ser tan débil como para necesitar "
"calor humano, o un abrazo amistoso...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:437
msgid ""
"<i>You cloistered yourself in your studies and works, thinking that you "
"didn't need such trivial things after all, that all you needed was to see "
"your people well and happy...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Te encerraste en tus estudios y trabajos, pensando que después de todo no "
"necesitabas esas cosas triviales, que todo lo que necesitabas era ver a tu "
"pueblo bien y feliz...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:441
msgid "<i>You cheated yourself...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Te engañaste a ti mismo...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:445
msgid "<i>And, in your loneliness, you became an easy prey for me...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Y, en tu soledad, te convertiste en una presa fácil para mí...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:449
msgid ""
"<i>That is, until that little boy showed up. That little boy, son of your "
"once favourite student, and who unexpectedly became your responsibility. He "
"was all those suppressed dreams of being a father come true, wasn't he?</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Hasta que apareció ese niño pequeño. Ese niño pequeño, hijo de tu alumna "
"favorita de antes, y que inesperadamente se convirtió en tu responsabilidad. "
"Él era todos esos sueños reprimidos de ser padre hechos realidad, ¿verdad?</"
"i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:453
msgid ""
"<i>He was the son that you never had... He was the one who saw you as human, "
"and by doing so he made you feel human...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Él era el hijo que nunca tuviste... Era el que te veía como humano, y al "
"hacerlo te hacía sentir humano...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:457
msgid ""
"<i>And so, when he fled from you and disappeared from your sight, it was as "
"if your humanity had gone with him, wasn't it?</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Y así, cuando huyó de ti y desapareció de tu vista, fue como si tu "
"humanidad se hubiera ido con él, ¿verdad?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:461
msgid ""
"<i>And this left such a wound in your soul... After all, there's nothing "
"more painful than finding happiness only to have it brutally taken from "
"you...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Y esto dejó una herida tan grande en tu alma... Después de todo, no hay "
"nada más doloroso que encontrar la felicidad solo para que te la arrebaten "
"brutalmente...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:465
msgid ""
"<i>You were a good person, Menon Hekare; you dedicated yourself to your "
"people for longer than any human before you, and you did that from the "
"bottom of your heart. Indeed, not even un-death managed to corrupt you... "
"However...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Eras una buena persona, Menon Hekare; te dedicaste a tu pueblo por más "
"tiempo que cualquier humano antes que tú, y lo hiciste desde el fondo de tu "
"corazón. De hecho, ni siquiera la no-muerte logró corromperte... Sin "
"embargo...</i>"

#. [unit], id=Svarballi, type=Dream Avatar
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:471
msgid "Svarballi"
msgstr "Svarballi"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:484
msgid ""
"...You remained alone for far too long. The bonds between people are what "
"make their spirits strong; love for others is what makes them resist the "
"lure of darkness, regardless of how strong it may be."
msgstr ""
"...Permaneciste solo por demasiado tiempo. Los lazos entre las personas son "
"lo que hace fuertes a sus espíritus; el amor por los demás es lo que los "
"hace resistir el señuelo de la oscuridad, sin importar cuán fuerte sea."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:495
msgid ""
"You were too good and clever to let darkness take you, but what if I "
"corrupted you through your light? What if I controlled you using the very "
"best things about you, such as your commitment to your people and your "
"ideals? Having no confidant to serve as your moral compass, you were easily "
"convinced that destroying an arguably evil nation to expand your own "
"nation's virtuous culture was acceptable..."
msgstr ""
"Eras demasiado bueno e inteligente como para dejar que la oscuridad te "
"tomara, pero ¿y si te corrompía a través de tu luz? ¿Y si te controlaba "
"usando las mejores cosas de ti, como tu compromiso con tu pueblo y tus "
"ideales? Al no tener a nadie de confianza que sirviera como tu brújula "
"moral, te convencieron fácilmente de que destruir una nación posiblemente "
"malvada para expandir la virtuosa cultura de tu propia nación era "
"aceptable..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:499
msgid "I..."
msgstr "Yo…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:503
msgid ""
"But when you were abandoned by the only true friend you’ve ever had, I no "
"longer needed to be careful; you were more fragile than ever before, and you "
"no longer cared about light or darkness, you only wanted to fulfil your "
"plans, no matter the cost..."
msgstr ""
"Pero cuando fuiste abandonado por el único verdadero amigo que jamás "
"tuviste, ya no necesitaba ser cuidadoso; estabas más frágil que nunca, y ya "
"no te importaba la luz o la oscuridad, solo querías cumplir tus planes, sin "
"importar el costo..."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:507
msgid ""
"You were completely at my mercy, and I rejoiced, believing that nothing "
"stood between me and my own goals... I would make my wielder confront the "
"wielder of the Ruby, and in the fight that jewel would be shattered, thus "
"releasing the three dragons, who would therefore release me once again..."
msgstr ""
"Estabas completamente a mi merced, y me regocijé, creyendo que nada se "
"interponía entre mí y mis propios objetivos... Haría que mi portador "
"confrontara al portador del Rubí, y en la pelea esa joya se rompería, "
"liberando así a los tres dragones, quienes a su vez me liberarían una vez "
"más..."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:511
msgid ""
"And it was then that the heir of that pesky woman appeared, to thwart me "
"just like she had once done..."
msgstr ""
"Y fue entonces cuando apareció el heredero de esa mujer molesta, para "
"frustrarme igual que ella lo había hecho una vez..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:515
msgid ""
"You should have listened to what she told you, Svarballi; even if she was "
"dead, there would always be someone to stop you, until the day comes when "
"someone with the power and means to ultimately destroy you will be born."
msgstr ""
"Deberías haber escuchado lo que ella te dijo, Svarballi; incluso si ella "
"estaba muerta, siempre habría alguien para detenerte, hasta el día en que "
"nazca alguien con el poder y los medios para destruirte definitivamente."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:519
msgid ""
"I told her, and I tell you now: there’s no being left in the entire universe "
"that can destroy me. Let more foolish heroes and heroines rise and delay my "
"release, I will simply destroy them, as I did to Myra, and as I will do to "
"you!"
msgstr ""
"Se lo dije a ella, y te lo digo ahora: no queda ningún ser en todo el "
"universo que pueda destruirme. Deja que más héroes y heroínas tontos se "
"levanten y retrasen mi liberación, simplemente los destruiré, como hice con "
"Myra, ¡y como haré contigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:526
msgid ""
"Damn it, how can he summon so many beings at once? And where's everyone?"
msgstr ""
"Maldición, ¿cómo puede invocar a tantos seres a la vez? ¿Y dónde está todo "
"el mundo?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:530
msgid ""
"They're still in the Foundation Square, as do our bodies. Svarballi has "
"invaded your mind through my own; he's trying to destroy them both, and if "
"he does, we'll be effectively dead. I'm sorry, Akhen, this is all my..."
msgstr ""
"Todavía están en la Plaza de la Fundación, al igual que nuestros cuerpos. "
"Svarballi ha invadido tu mente a través de la mía; está tratando de destruir "
"ambas, y si lo logra, estaremos efectivamente muertos. Lo siento, Akhen, "
"todo esto es por mi..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:534
msgid ""
"It's all right, Master, I too committed a great mistake when I abandoned you "
"like that... But this is not the time to regret past things; come, we must "
"not allow Svarballi to have the last laugh!"
msgstr ""
"Está bien, Maestro, yo también cometí un gran error cuando te abandoné de "
"esa manera... Pero este no es el momento de lamentar cosas del pasado; ven, "
"¡no debemos permitir que Svarballi sea el que ría al final!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:538
msgid ""
"(smiling) You couldn't have spoken more wisely, Akhen; I'm proud for having "
"been your professor. Now, it is time to stop the Sky Dragon - together!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) No podrías haber hablado con más sabiduría, Akhen; estoy "
"orgulloso de haber sido tu profesor. Ahora, ¡es hora de detener al Dragón "
"del Cielo, juntos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:544
msgid "Destroy the Presence"
msgstr "Destruir la Presencia"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:548
msgid "Destruction of Akhen"
msgstr "Destrucción de Akhen"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:552
msgid "Destruction of Menon"
msgstr "Destrucción de Menon"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:572
msgid ""
"So much effort for nothing. I haven't been affected in the least, Menon's "
"still going to die, and all you've earned this world was a few more "
"generations."
msgstr ""
"Tanto esfuerzo para nada. No he sido afectado en lo más mínimo, Menon "
"todavía va a morir, y todo lo que le has ganado a este mundo son unas "
"cuantas generaciones más."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:576
msgid ""
"Dying matters nothing if that means thwarting you once more. Besides... by "
"dying I'll finally be free from your influence..."
msgstr ""
"Morir no importa nada si eso significa frustrarte una vez más. Además... al "
"morir finalmente estaré libre de tu influencia..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:767
msgid ""
"(crying in happiness) Akhen! Thank the Gods that you're back...! For a "
"moment, I thought I had lost you..."
msgstr ""
"(llorando de felicidad) ¡Akhen! ¡Gracias a los Dioses que estás de "
"vuelta...! Por un momento pensé que te había perdido..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:771
msgid ""
"(smiling) You see, I may not look like, but I'm actually quite hard to "
"break..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Verás, puede que no lo parezca, pero en realidad soy bastante "
"difícil de romper..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:775
msgid ""
"What happened? We only saw you about to give Menon the final blow, and then "
"you both fell unconscious, even your elementals disappeared..."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué pasó? Solo te vimos a punto de asestar el golpe final a Menon, y luego "
"ambos cayeron inconscientes, incluso tus elementales desaparecieron..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:779
msgid ""
"It was Svarballi... I told you, he was controlling Master Menon; after "
"realising that he was going to lose, he tried to destroy our minds, but... "
"It's over now..."
msgstr ""
"Fue Svarballi... Te lo dije, estaba controlando al Maestro Menon; después de "
"darse cuenta de que iba a perder, intentó destruir nuestras mentes, pero... "
"Ya se acabó..."

#. [message], speaker=Atseger
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:783
msgid "(shocked) Master, what... What is he saying...?"
msgstr "(impactada) Maestro, ¿qué... qué está diciendo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:787
msgid ""
"He speaks the truth, my dear... I was a weak fool, letting myself be "
"controlled by him like this... Nothing I say will change what I have done - "
"what I made you do..."
msgstr ""
"Dice la verdad, querida... Fui un tonto débil, dejándome controlar por él de "
"esta manera... Nada de lo que diga cambiará lo que hice, lo que te hice "
"hacer..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:791
msgid ""
"Master, do not blame yourself more than you should. You just loved your "
"people so much that you abdicated of your own needs for them. Besides... You "
"were just human, and humans do make mistakes."
msgstr ""
"Maestro, no te culpes más de lo que debes. Solo amaste tanto a tu pueblo que "
"renunciaste a tus propias necesidades por ellos. Además... Solo eras humano, "
"y los humanos cometen errores."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:795
msgid ""
"I see... At least I can say that I did one good thing: I raised <i>you</i>..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Al menos puedo decir que hice una cosa buena: te crié <i>a ti</"
"i>..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:799
msgid ""
"Thus fell the greatest mage Maat'Kare had seen in sixteen centuries: not "
"with a pompous funeral march, but on the dusty ground of his beloved city, "
"surrounded by the people he loved. And this, for him, was the best way he "
"could have ever hoped to die."
msgstr ""
"Así cayó el mayor mago que Maat'Kare había visto en dieciséis siglos: no con "
"una marcha fúnebre pomposa, sino sobre el suelo polvoriento de su amada "
"ciudad, rodeado por la gente que amaba. Y esto, para él, fue la mejor forma "
"en que jamás habría esperado morir."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:825
msgid "My mind...!"
msgstr "¡Mi mente...!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/37_Forces_Of_Nature.cfg:829
msgid "Master, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡Maestro, NO!!!"

#. [scenario], id=38_Winds_Of_Fate
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:4
msgid "Winds of Fate"
msgstr "Vientos del Destino"

#. [unit], id=Nekure, type=MaatKarian Elder Sage
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:124
msgid "Elder Nekure"
msgstr "Anciano Nekure"

#. [unit], id=Aneksi, type=Prophetess of Light
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:134
msgid "Master Aneksi"
msgstr "Maestro Aneksi"

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:155
msgid ""
"Wait a minute, Akhen, do you mean... Are you actually suggesting that..."
msgstr ""
"Espera un minuto, Akhen, ¿quieres decir... estás sugiriendo realmente que..."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:159
msgid ""
"But we can't simply abandon our cities, farms and fortresses, everything "
"we've built in the span of sixteen centuries, and move to the Silent Desert!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero no podemos simplemente abandonar nuestras ciudades, granjas y "
"fortalezas, todo lo que hemos construido en el lapso de dieciséis siglos, y "
"mudarnos al Desierto Silencioso!"

#. [message], speaker=Nekure
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:163
msgid ""
"Even if we did do that, how do you expect us to live in such an arid "
"environment? We may have lost nearly half our population with all the wars "
"of the last two years, but any farm that we manage to build on that desert "
"won't be enough to feed the thousands of Maat'Karian mouths that still live!"
msgstr ""
"Incluso si hiciéramos eso, ¿cómo esperas que vivamos en un ambiente tan "
"árido? Puede que hayamos perdido casi la mitad de nuestra población con "
"todas las guerras de los últimos dos años, ¡pero cualquier granja que "
"logremos construir en ese desierto no será suficiente para alimentar a las "
"miles de bocas maat'karianas que todavía viven!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:167
msgid ""
"Generals, I can tell you, and any mage can confirm it, that it is possible "
"to build huge perennial farms on a desert with the aid of the right spells; "
"I myself saw a huge Windsong Foundation thriving on the much harsher Blue "
"Realm just like that."
msgstr ""
"Generales, puedo decirles, y cualquier mago puede confirmarlo, que es "
"posible construir enormes granjas perennes en un desierto con la ayuda de "
"los hechizos adecuados; yo mismo vi una enorme Fundación de las Hijas del "
"Viento prosperando en el mucho más duro Reino Azul de esa misma forma."

#. [message], speaker=Aneksi
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:171
msgid ""
"Fine, but you haven't told us why you're suggesting that. Are you afraid "
"that we won't be able to defend so much territory if Skiron attacks us in "
"the years to come?"
msgstr ""
"Está bien, pero no nos has dicho por qué lo sugieres. ¿Temes que no podamos "
"defender tanto territorio si Skiron nos ataca en los años venideros?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:175
msgid ""
"It's much more than that. We all know that Aegaion will never give up on the "
"Sky Soul; and, if we could barely repel their sea attacks when we had our "
"full might, it's unlikely that we'll succeed with our current forces. In the "
"Silent Desert, however, we can better defend ourselves against their armies, "
"and any other known to us. And, most importantly, in the middle of the "
"desert we'll be hidden from any explorer that might stumble upon Netjer-Ta. "
"I doubt I've met even a tiny fraction of the civilizations thriving outside "
"Netjer-Ta and Argea; who knows, soon enough one of them may grow strong "
"enough to defy even us."
msgstr ""
"Es mucho más que eso. Todos sabemos que Aegaion nunca renunciará al Alma del "
"Cielo; y, si apenas pudimos repeler sus ataques marítimos cuando teníamos "
"todo nuestro poder, es poco probable que tengamos éxito con nuestras fuerzas "
"actuales. Sin embargo, en el Desierto Silencioso podemos defendernos mejor "
"contra sus ejércitos y cualquier otro que conozcamos. Y, lo más importante, "
"en medio del desierto estaremos ocultos de cualquier explorador que pueda "
"tropezar con Netjer-Ta. Dudo haber conocido siquiera una fracción mínima de "
"las civilizaciones que prosperan fuera de Netjer-Ta y Argea; quién sabe, "
"pronto alguna de ellas puede volverse lo suficientemente fuerte como para "
"desafiarnos incluso a nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:179
msgid ""
"I see your point; any seafaring people would have no trouble finding "
"Maat'Kare, with its towers that can be sighted even from Cape Atargatis..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo tu punto; cualquier pueblo marinero no tendría problemas para "
"encontrar Maat'Kare, con sus torres que se pueden avistar incluso desde el "
"Cabo Atargatis..."

#. [message], speaker=Smenkhare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:183
msgid ""
"Still, building an entire city - and it will be no small city - literally "
"out of nothing... and convincing everyone to move there..."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, construir una ciudad entera —y no será una ciudad pequeña— "
"literalmente de la nada... y convencer a todos de mudarse allí..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:187
msgid ""
"Of course, this would be an enterprise for the next few years at the very "
"least. We Aigathol are busy rebuilding our own country as well, but we could "
"spare some engineers to help you."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, esto sería una empresa para los próximos años como mínimo. "
"Nosotros los Aigathol también estamos ocupados reconstruyendo nuestro propio "
"país, pero podríamos prestar algunos ingenieros para ayudarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:191
msgid ""
"Furthermore, we could use undead and elementals, who feel no exhaustion, to "
"build the new Maat'Kare."
msgstr ""
"Además, podríamos usar no muertos y elementales, que no sienten agotamiento, "
"para construir el nuevo Maat'Kare."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:195
msgid ""
"And, in the meantime, we will prepare our people, psychologically and "
"logistically, for such great exodus."
msgstr ""
"Y, mientras tanto, prepararemos a nuestro pueblo, psicológica y "
"logísticamente, para tan gran éxodo."

#. [message], speaker=Sadjet
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:199
msgid ""
"Well, Akhen, your choices and decisions have saved our nation more than once "
"already, so I shall trust you in this as well. Who else is in favour?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, Akhen, tus elecciones y decisiones ya han salvado a nuestra nación "
"más de una vez, así que también confiaré en ti en esto. ¿Quién más está a "
"favor?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:203
msgid "Slowly, but surely, every other lord and sage raised their hands."
msgstr ""
"Lentamente, pero con seguridad, todos los demás señores y sabios levantaron "
"sus manos."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:207
msgid ""
"Thank you all for believing in me once more, my people. I promise that I "
"will not let you down."
msgstr ""
"Gracias a todos por creer en mí una vez más, mi pueblo. Prometo que no los "
"defraudaré."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:285
msgid ""
"At long last, this war is over... It may sound commonplace, but it does feel "
"like waking up from a long and turbulent nightmare..."
msgstr ""
"Por fin, esta guerra ha terminado... Puede sonar común, pero realmente se "
"siente como despertar de una larga y turbulenta pesadilla..."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:289
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, we still can't sit down and relax. Even if we do move to the "
"desert, until our new city is ready we'll have to stand on guard against any "
"attack by Skiron, the vampires or the minotaurs."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, todavía no podemos sentarnos y relajarnos. Incluso si nos "
"mudamos al desierto, hasta que nuestra nueva ciudad esté lista tendremos que "
"estar en guardia contra cualquier ataque de Skiron, los vampiros o los "
"minotauros."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Alas, I've just arrived at your marvellous country and you're moving "
"already; I won't be able to see your cities..."
msgstr ""
"Lamentablemente, acabo de llegar a su maravilloso país y ya se están "
"mudando; no podré ver sus ciudades..."

#. [message], speaker=Mahyus
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:297
msgid ""
"Well, it's not like they'll be dismantled; even after they're unoccupied, we "
"can still visit them."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no es como si las fueran a desmantelar; incluso después de que queden "
"desocupadas, todavía podremos visitarlas."

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:301
msgid ""
"Mmmm, to think that we'll have an entire and empty city to do whatever we "
"want, sounds interesting..."
msgstr ""
"Mmmm, pensar que tendremos una ciudad entera y vacía para hacer lo que "
"queramos, suena interesante..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:305
msgid ""
"(impatient) By the Gods of Light, can't you keep these naughty thoughts to "
"yourselves? I really don't care about them, you know!"
msgstr ""
"(impaciente) ¡Por los Dioses de la Luz, ¿no pueden guardarse esos "
"pensamientos traviesos para ustedes? ¡Realmente no me importan, saben!"

#. [message], speaker=Branwyn
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:309
msgid ""
"Well, I was thinking about running and playing in the streets without any "
"authority ordering us to stop, but maybe these 'naughty things' you've just "
"thought about can be fun too..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, estaba pensando en correr y jugar en las calles sin que ninguna "
"autoridad nos ordenara detenernos, pero tal vez esas «cosas traviesas» que "
"acabas de imaginar también pueden ser divertidas..."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:313
msgid ""
"My, my, you lambasted them for thinking indecent things when, in fact, you "
"were the one imagining them..."
msgstr ""
"Vaya, vaya, los reprendiste por pensar cosas indecentes cuando, en realidad, "
"tú eras la que las estaba imaginando..."

#. [message], speaker=Merwe
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:317
msgid "(blushing) Oh, shut up..."
msgstr "(sonrojándose) Oh, cállate..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:321
msgid "(laughing) Only you to make me laugh so much at a time like this..."
msgstr "(riendo) Solo tú para hacerme reír tanto en un momento como este..."

#. [message], speaker=Sigdral
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:325
msgid "(smirking) Well, that's what friends are for."
msgstr "(sonriendo burlonamente) Bueno, para eso están los amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Atenak
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:329
msgid ""
"Be strong, everyone, we'll manage to get over everything; sooner than we "
"expect, we'll be sitting on a veranda in New Maat'Kare, drinking dwarvish "
"beer and listening to Branwyn's ballads, and all the suffering of the last "
"months will be no more than bad memories."
msgstr ""
"Sean fuertes, todos, lograremos superar todo; más pronto de lo que "
"esperamos, estaremos sentados en una veranda en el Nuevo Maat'Kare, bebiendo "
"cerveza enana y escuchando las baladas de Branwyn, y todo el sufrimiento de "
"los últimos meses no será más que malos recuerdos."

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:333
msgid ""
"Branwyn's songs will probably be accompanied by a chorus of baby cries, "
"though..."
msgstr ""
"Las canciones de Branwyn probablemente irán acompañadas de un coro de "
"llantos de bebés, sin embargo..."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:337
msgid "You mean... Would you like to adopt children?"
msgstr "¿Quieres decir... que te gustaría adoptar niños?"

#. [message], speaker=Nyx
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:341
msgid ""
"(laughing) Don't sound so surprised, I did tell you once I'd have loved "
"having a bunch of babies with someone I loved. Besides... with all the lives "
"ended by this war, there'll be so many children in need of a home, a family."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) No suenes tan sorprendido, una vez te dije que me habría encantado "
"tener un montón de bebés con alguien que amara. Además... con todas las "
"vidas terminadas por esta guerra, habrá tantos niños que necesitarán un "
"hogar, una familia."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:345
msgid ""
"You're right... And after so much fighting, it'll be good to <i>care</i> for "
"people instead. *After all, we must make sure the next generations have "
"their own heroes and heroines too, right?*"
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón... Y después de tanta lucha, será bueno <i>cuidar</i> de las "
"personas en cambio. *Después de todo, debemos asegurarnos de que las "
"próximas generaciones también tengan sus propios héroes y heroínas, ¿verdad?*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/38_Winds_Of_Fate.cfg:350
msgid ""
"<i>Wise words, grandson. I'm so proud of you and your friends... Jevyan, "
"Ravyan, Alenya, Dvalin, Akashia, Maat and Abhai, be glad, that all of our "
"sacrifices were truly worthwhile...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Palabras sabias, nieto. Estoy tan orgullosa de ti y de tus amigos... "
"Jevyan, Ravyan, Alenya, Dvalin, Akashia, Maat y Abhai, estén contentos, "
"porque todos nuestros sacrificios realmente valieron la pena...</i>"

#. [scenario], id=WotJ_Epilogue
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Epilogue_WotJ.cfg:4
msgid "Epilogue"
msgstr "Epílogo"

#. [unit], id=Ankhmare, type=Celestial Master
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Epilogue_WotJ.cfg:85
msgid "Scion Ankhmare"
msgstr "Descendiente Ankhmare"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Epilogue_WotJ.cfg:111
msgid ""
"There's no mistaking it; only one thing would have caused such reaction in "
"the Trident, and that is... So, at long last you were born, Dragon-Slayer... "
"Or should I say, at long last you have returned... Myra..."
msgstr ""
"No hay error posible; solo una cosa habría causado tal reacción en el "
"Tridente, y esa es... Entonces, por fin has nacido, Matadragones... O "
"debería decir, por fin has regresado... Myra..."

#. [scenario], id=Prologue_Part_I
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:4
msgid "Prologue: Enlightening the Past - Part I"
msgstr "Prólogo: Iluminando el Pasado - Parte I"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:21
msgid "Find the Yawning Abyss"
msgstr "Encontrar el Abismo Bostezante"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:25
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:471
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:26
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:27
msgid "Death of Hashira"
msgstr "Muerte de Hashira"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:29
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:475
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:30
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:31
msgid "Death of Ayraton"
msgstr "Muerte de Ayraton"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:38
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:484
msgid ""
"This and the following two scenarios are merely part of the Prologue; thus, "
"there will be no gold carryover in them. Recruit at ease!"
msgstr ""
"Este y los dos escenarios siguientes son solamente parte del Prólogo; por lo "
"tanto, no habrá transferencia de oro en ellos. ¡Recluta con tranquilidad!"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:55
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:51
msgid "Hashira's Retinue"
msgstr "Comitiva de Hashira"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:76
msgid "Desert Ghosts"
msgstr "Fantasmas del Desierto"

#. [side], type=Gnoll Deadeye
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:98
msgid "Krarm"
msgstr "Krarm"

#. [side], type=Gnoll Deadeye
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:103
msgid "Gnolls"
msgstr "Gnolls"

#. [side], type=Minotaur Executioner
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:117
msgid "Mainos"
msgstr "Mainos"

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:164
msgid ""
"Another sandstorm is forming! Men, brace yourselves! (in private) Milady, it "
"is not my place to question your decisions, but are you sure you want to "
"insist on this enterprise?"
msgstr ""
"¡Otra tormenta de arena se está formando! ¡Hombres, prepárense! (en privado) "
"Señora, no me corresponde cuestionar sus decisiones, pero ¿está segura de "
"que quiere insistir en esta empresa?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:168
msgid ""
"I am, Djoser. If this expedition is successful - and I see no reason for it "
"not to be - our names shall be engraved on the History scrolls of Maat'Kare "
"forever. Will you let a petty sandstorm prevent you from achieving such "
"glory? Because I will not."
msgstr ""
"Lo estoy, Djoser. Si esta expedición tiene éxito —y no veo razón para que no "
"lo tenga— nuestros nombres quedarán grabados en los pergaminos de la "
"Historia de Maat'Kare para siempre. ¿Dejarás que una simple tormenta de "
"arena te impida alcanzar tal gloria? Porque yo no lo haré."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:172
msgid ""
"Neither will I, but I confess this sandstorm is enervating me. Why is it "
"happening, anyway? For what I've read, this desert has always been famed for "
"being a peaceful and calm environment."
msgstr ""
"Yo tampoco, pero confieso que esta tormenta de arena me está agotando. ¿Por "
"qué está ocurriendo, de todos modos? Por lo que he leído, este desierto "
"siempre ha sido famoso por ser un ambiente pacífico y tranquilo."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:176
msgid ""
"So it was, until the destruction of the Crystal Tower; I suspect that it was "
"the Celestials' power that kept this desert so calm."
msgstr ""
"Así era, hasta la destrucción de la Torre de Cristal; sospecho que fue el "
"poder de los Celestiales lo que mantenía este desierto tan calmado."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:180
msgid ""
"Speaking of which, wouldn't it be fun to find the ruins of the Crystal "
"Tower? I mean, we would be at the very site of the battle between Myra and "
"the Sky Dragon; who knows, we could even find her lost Trident there!"
msgstr ""
"Hablando de eso, ¿no sería divertido encontrar las ruinas de la Torre de "
"Cristal? Quiero decir, estaríamos en el mismo sitio de la batalla entre Myra "
"y el Dragón del Cielo; quién sabe, ¡incluso podríamos encontrar su Tridente "
"perdido allí!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:184
msgid "(smirking) Indeed we could..."
msgstr "(sonriendo burlonamente) En efecto podríamos..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:188
msgid "Wait, so is this our goal, to retrieve the Trident of the Seas?"
msgstr ""
"Espera, ¿entonces ese es nuestro objetivo, recuperar el Tridente de los "
"Mares?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:192
msgid "No, our goal is something far more important, but I won't tell it now."
msgstr ""
"No, nuestro objetivo es algo mucho más importante, pero no lo diré ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:196
msgid ""
"Maybe you should be more frank about this expedition's motives. I have been "
"quietly and obediently following you since Maat'Kare, and I'm well aware "
"that it was one of your conditions, but..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez deberías ser más franca sobre los motivos de esta expedición. He "
"estado siguiéndote en silencio y obedientemente desde Maat'Kare, y soy muy "
"consciente de que esa fue una de tus condiciones, pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:200
msgid ""
"But what? If you knew that I wasn't revealing this expedition's goal until "
"we reached it, then content yourself with the gold you're receiving for "
"every hour you're working for me. After all, it is no small amount."
msgstr ""
"¿Pero qué? Si sabías que no revelaría el objetivo de esta expedición hasta "
"que llegáramos a él, entonces conténtate con el oro que recibes por cada "
"hora que trabajas para mí. Después de todo, no es una cantidad pequeña."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:204
msgid "(rolls eyes) All right, milady Aelone..."
msgstr "(pone los ojos en blanco) Está bien, señora Aelone..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:208
msgid ""
"And no sarcasm, please; I have enough of it already from that pesky "
"Ithania..."
msgstr ""
"Y sin sarcasmo, por favor; ya tengo suficiente de eso de esa molesta "
"Ithania..."

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:212
msgid ""
"Milady, I was analyzing the maps, and according to them we are close to the "
"Yawning Abyss already. However, we're also close to the Gnoll Swamps; and "
"besides, we can't be certain that there are no orcs or minotaurs in this "
"desert."
msgstr ""
"Señora, estaba analizando los mapas, y según ellos ya estamos cerca del "
"Abismo Bostezante. Sin embargo, también estamos cerca de los Pantanos de los "
"Gnolls; y además, no podemos estar seguros de que no haya orcos o minotauros "
"en este desierto."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:216
msgid ""
"I know fully well the dangers that lurk in this region, but it does not sway "
"my resolve. Our men are well-trained, and if the situation requires, Ayraton "
"shall reanimate the corpses of our foes to fight for us. Now, onwards!"
msgstr ""
"Conozco muy bien los peligros que acechan en esta región, pero eso no hace "
"tambalear mi determinación. Nuestros hombres están bien entrenados, y si la "
"situación lo requiere, Ayraton reanimará los cadáveres de nuestros enemigos "
"para que luchen por nosotros. ¡Ahora, adelante!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:221
msgid ""
"If this is not your first time playing this campaign and you don't wish to "
"play the Prologue, you may skip straight to the first scenario. But, if this "
"is your first play, you're advised to follow the Prologue, else you will "
"miss some important bits of lore."
msgstr ""
"Si esta no es tu primera vez jugando esta campaña y no deseas jugar el "
"Prólogo, puedes saltar directamente al primer escenario. Pero, si esta es tu "
"primera partida, se te recomienda seguir el Prólogo, de lo contrario te "
"perderás algunos fragmentos importantes de la lore."

#. [option]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:223
msgid "Skip Prologue"
msgstr "Saltar Prólogo"

#. [option]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:235
msgid "Play Prologue"
msgstr "Jugar Prólogo"

#. [unit]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:262
msgid "Undead Slave"
msgstr "Esclavo No Muerto"

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:285
msgid ""
"So, dark mage, you want us to believe that you won't play with our bodies if "
"we die here, uh?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, mago oscuro, quieres que creamos que no jugarás con nuestros "
"cuerpos si morimos aquí, ¿eh?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:289
msgid ""
"You dumb soldier, I've told you already: we learn the Umbra Arts to better "
"understand it, not to employ it as Necromancy; at least, not unless we're "
"told to do so by our superiors! That incident of years ago was an exception, "
"and it is not a representative us Dark Adepts at all!"
msgstr ""
"Soldado tonto, ya te lo he dicho: aprendemos las Artes Umbra para "
"entenderlas mejor, no para emplearlas como Nigromancia; al menos, ¡no a "
"menos que nuestros superiores nos lo ordenen! Ese incidente de hace años fue "
"una excepción, ¡y no nos representa a nosotros los Adeptos Oscuros en "
"absoluto!"

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Right, right... So tell me, why did you accept following Lady Hashira so "
"easily? I mean, with conditions like those, any good person would be very "
"suspicious..."
msgstr ""
"Bien, bien... Entonces dime, ¿por qué aceptaste seguir a Lady Hashira tan "
"fácilmente? Quiero decir, con condiciones como esas, cualquier persona buena "
"estaría muy sospechosa..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:297
msgid ""
"Well, I simply believed her promise that, if the expedition was successful, "
"we'd all be famous like none other in this generation or the next. She is an "
"honourable member of the Aelones after all, am I right?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, simplemente creí en su promesa de que, si la expedición tenía éxito, "
"todos seríamos famosos como nadie en esta generación o en la siguiente. "
"Después de todo, ella es un miembro honorable de los Aelones, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:301
msgid ""
"Of course you are! Still, you must be eager for fame, to have accepted her "
"terms so quickly."
msgstr ""
"¡Por supuesto que sí! Aun así, debes estar ansioso por la fama, para haber "
"aceptado sus términos tan rápido."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:305
msgid ""
"Well... (annoyed) All right, actually I want to give some guy a lesson, are "
"you satisfied now?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno... (molesto) Está bien, en realidad quiero darle una lección a un "
"tipo, ¿estás satisfecho ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:309
msgid "Someone who bullied you at school, eh?"
msgstr "¿Alguien que te intimidaba en la escuela, eh?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:313
msgid ""
"Argh... No, he didn't bully me, he's just... intolerably arrogant and full "
"of himself. You must have heard of him: I’m talking about Menon Hekare..."
msgstr ""
"Argh... No, no me intimidaba, solo es... intolerablemente arrogante y lleno "
"de sí mismo. Debes haber oído de él: estoy hablando de Menon Hekare..."

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:317
msgid ""
"You mean that guy who became the first Master of Four Lights since Aldrik "
"the Pioneer, the son of Myra? Who has just helped General Rahotep win a "
"great victory against the orcs in the Sun Path? Who..."
msgstr ""
"¿Te refieres a ese tipo que se convirtió en el primer Maestro de las Cuatro "
"Luces desde Aldrik el Pionero, el hijo de Myra? ¿El que acaba de ayudar al "
"General Rahotep a ganar una gran victoria contra los orcos en el Camino del "
"Sol? ¿Quién..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:321
msgid "Yes, yes, this one, now enough with listing his feats, please!"
msgstr "Sí, sí, ese, ¡ahora basta de listar sus hazañas, por favor!"

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:325
msgid ""
"(laughing) Boy, I don't mean to dishearten you, but, unless Lady Hashira "
"finds a still-living Myra, I don't think you'll manage to surpass that young "
"man..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Muchacho, no quiero desanimarte, pero, a menos que Lady Hashira "
"encuentre a una Myra aún viva, no creo que logres superar a ese joven..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:339
msgid ""
"Look, it's a human! Can it be that there is another expedition searching for "
"the same place as us?"
msgstr ""
"¡Miren, es un humano! ¿Podría ser que haya otra expedición buscando el mismo "
"lugar que nosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:343
msgid ""
"Impossible, no one else could have discovered that! Still, that is "
"undoubtedly a human... Let us capture him; I want to ask him some questions."
msgstr ""
"Imposible, ¡nadie más podría haber descubierto eso! Aun así, ese es "
"indudablemente un humano... Capturémoslo; quiero hacerle algunas preguntas."

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:347
msgid "As you wish, milady."
msgstr "Como desee, mi señora."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Now, desert dweller, you will tell me who you are, what are you doing here, "
"and what is you affiliation? "
msgstr ""
"Ahora, habitante del desierto, me dirás quién eres, qué estás haciendo aquí "
"y cuál es tu afiliación."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:366
msgid ""
"It is I who should be asking you these questions! What are you doing in our "
"desert, what is your business here?"
msgstr ""
"¡Soy yo quien debería hacerte estas preguntas! ¿Qué están haciendo en "
"nuestro desierto, cuál es su negocio aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:370
msgid ""
"I am Hashira of the Aelones, Head of the Windsong Order, and my business "
"here is none of your concern, though I may tell you if you answer <i>my</i> "
"questions."
msgstr ""
"Soy Hashira de los Aelones, Jefa de la Orden de las Hijas del Viento, y mi "
"negocio aquí no es de tu incumbencia, aunque te lo diré si respondes <i>mis</"
"i> preguntas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:374
msgid ""
"Very well, then... I am a member of the Desert Ghosts; we are an "
"organization set up by Jevyan of Garet-Desh, Hero of the Exodus and Founder "
"of Maat'Kare, to watch over this desert after the Battle of the Crystal "
"Tower."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, entonces... Soy miembro de los Fantasmas del Desierto; somos una "
"organización creada por Jevyan de Garet-Desh, Héroe del Éxodo y Fundador de "
"Maat'Kare, para vigilar este desierto después de la Batalla de la Torre de "
"Cristal."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:378
msgid ""
"And why do you watch over this desert? There are many outposts over its "
"eastern borders already, to prevent orcs, gnolls or minotaurs from attacking "
"Maat'Kare through it."
msgstr ""
"¿Y por qué vigilan este desierto? Ya hay muchos puestos de avanzada en sus "
"fronteras orientales, para impedir que orcos, gnolls o minotauros ataquen "
"Maat'Kare a través de él."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:382
msgid ""
"That's not it; there's something else we protect, but I'm not allowed to "
"speak about it..."
msgstr ""
"No es eso; hay algo más que protegemos, pero no se me permite hablar de "
"ello..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:386
msgid ""
"I guess I know what you protect: it is an ancient jewel of great power, "
"isn't it?"
msgstr ""
"Supongo que sé qué protegen: es una antigua joya de gran poder, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:390
msgid "(shocked) But... how do you..."
msgstr "(impactado) Pero... ¿cómo tú..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:394
msgid ""
"Your faction may have been created by Jevyan, but I descend of Ravyan, and "
"he legated the truth about Myra's last battle to his heirs. Now, you have no "
"reason to be afraid: I'm not a bandit, I just want the Soul to protect and "
"study it. Don't you think it will be far safer in Hiera'Laksha than in the "
"middle of this wild desert?"
msgstr ""
"Tu facción puede haber sido creada por Jevyan, pero yo desciendo de Ravyan, "
"y él legó la verdad sobre la última batalla de Myra a sus herederos. Ahora, "
"no tienes razón para tener miedo: no soy una bandida, solo quiero el Alma "
"para protegerla y estudiarla. ¿No crees que estará mucho más segura en "
"Hiera'Laksha que en medio de este desierto salvaje?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:398
msgid "The last time the Soul was sent to Hiera'Laksha, a tragedy happened..."
msgstr ""
"La última vez que el Alma fue enviada a Hiera'Laksha, ocurrió una tragedia..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Yes, yes, Windsong can't handle a little bit of power, and everyone else is "
"best fit to wield said power, we've heard that story before. Now, will you "
"please facilitate our mission and tell us exactly where the Soul is?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, sí, las Hijas del Viento no pueden manejar un poco de poder, y todos los "
"demás son los más aptos para empuñar dicho poder, ya hemos oído esa historia "
"antes. Ahora, ¿podrías por favor facilitar nuestra misión y decirnos "
"exactamente dónde está el Alma?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:406
msgid "Never!"
msgstr "¡Jamás!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:410
msgid "Then you leave me no choice."
msgstr "Entonces no me dejas otra opción."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:414
msgid ""
"Um, Hashira, I don't mean to importune you, but are we really going to kill "
"humans to reach our goal?"
msgstr ""
"Um, Hashira, no quiero importunarte, pero ¿realmente vamos a matar humanos "
"para alcanzar nuestro objetivo?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:418
msgid ""
"Either that or we will be killed by them. Trust me, what we're searching is "
"worth that. It's not only for personal glory anymore; we need to retrieve "
"that before it falls in the wrong hands, if it hasn't already."
msgstr ""
"O eso o nos matarán ellos. Créeme, lo que estamos buscando vale la pena. Ya "
"no es solo por gloria personal; necesitamos recuperarlo antes de que caiga "
"en las manos equivocadas, si es que no ha caído ya."

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:430
msgid "And there he goes, playing with the dead..."
msgstr "Y ahí va él, jugando con los muertos..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:434
msgid "(annoyed) Tsc!"
msgstr "(molesto) ¡Tsc!"

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Wait, Windsong! I am Leivyan, leader of the Desert Ghosts, and I want to "
"know why are you so bent on finding the Soul? Aren't you aware of the danger "
"it poses not only to Maat'Kare, but to the whole world? Or do you want it "
"for your own purposes?"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen, Hijas del Viento! Soy Leivyan, líder de los Fantasmas del "
"Desierto, y quiero saber ¿por qué están tan empeñadas en encontrar el Alma? "
"¿No son conscientes del peligro que representa no solo para Maat'Kare, sino "
"para el mundo entero? ¿O la quieren para sus propios fines?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:453
msgid ""
"I only want to study and protect it. You may have been able to protect it so "
"far, but what will you do if, say, an orcish horde crosses this desert, "
"stumbles on the Yawning Abyss and decides to hide from a sandstorm inside "
"it? The Soul is said to corrupt even the most honest of people; I quake to "
"think of how it could be used by orcs, or worse, by vampires."
msgstr ""
"Solo quiero estudiarla y protegerla. Puede que hayan podido protegerla hasta "
"ahora, pero ¿qué harán si, por ejemplo, una horda orca cruza este desierto, "
"tropeza con el Abismo Bostezante y decide esconderse de una tormenta de "
"arena dentro de él? Se dice que el Alma corrompe incluso a las personas más "
"honestas; tiemblo solo de pensar cómo podría ser usada por orcos, o peor, "
"por vampiros."

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:457
msgid ""
"We have faced many orc armies already, Windsong; in fact, we are the reason "
"they seldom venture into this desert nowadays. Now, I will give you one last "
"chance to turn back to whence you came in peace, or we shall not refrain "
"from destroying you and your henchmen!"
msgstr ""
"Ya hemos enfrentado muchos ejércitos orcos, Hijas del Viento; de hecho, "
"somos la razón por la que rara vez se aventuran en este desierto hoy en día. "
"Ahora, les daré una última oportunidad de regresar por donde vinieron en "
"paz, ¡o no nos abstendremos de destruirlas a ustedes y a sus secuaces!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:461
msgid "So be it."
msgstr "Que así sea."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:467
msgid "Remove Leivyan and the Desert Ghosts who are standing on your way"
msgstr ""
"Elimina a Leivyan y a los Fantasmas del Desierto que estén en tu camino"

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:495
msgid "I can't die here... I must contact the other settlements..."
msgstr "No puedo morir aquí... Debo contactar a los otros asentamientos..."

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:510
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:516
msgid "Damn it, he escaped amidst the sandstorm!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, escapó en medio de la tormenta de arena!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:523
msgid ""
"Let him be; I really don't want to kill fellow humans, but they gave me no "
"choice... Now, nothing stands between us and the Soul..."
msgstr ""
"Déjenlo; realmente no quiero matar a humanos como nosotros, pero no me "
"dejaron opción... Ahora, nada se interpone entre nosotras y el Alma..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:527
msgid ""
"What makes you so sure that these Desert Ghosts haven't relocated this Soul, "
"or whatever it is?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué te hace estar tan segura de que estos Fantasmas del Desierto no han "
"reubicado esta Alma, o lo que sea?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:531
msgid ""
"I doubt any of them has ever come even ten steps close to it; they certainly "
"fear it, and with all due reason. Now, onwards to the Yawning Abyss..."
msgstr ""
"Dudo que alguno de ellos se haya acercado siquiera diez pasos a ella; "
"ciertamente le temen, y con toda razón. Ahora, ¡adelante hacia el Abismo "
"Bostezante...!"

#. [message], speaker=Djoser
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:549
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:377
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:846
msgid "Milady Aelone, I have failed you...!"
msgstr "¡Señora Aelone, te he fallado...!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:553
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:381
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:850
msgid ""
"Worry not, worthy Djoser, you have done your best. Rest in peace, for your "
"death shall not go unavenged!"
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, digno Djoser, hiciste lo mejor que pudiste. Descansa en "
"paz, porque tu muerte no quedará sin venganza."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_I.cfg:561
msgid ""
"Curses, we are taking too much time to reach the Abyss, and this sandstorm "
"is getting dangerously worse! As much as it pains me, we'll have to retreat "
"now; I fear that, with those Desert Ghosts now aware of our goals, we won't "
"be able to complete our mission..."
msgstr ""
"Maldición, estamos tardando demasiado en llegar al Abismo, ¡y esta tormenta "
"de arena se está poniendo peligrosamente peor! Por mucho que me duela, "
"tendremos que retirarnos ahora; temo que, con esos Fantasmas del Desierto "
"ahora conscientes de nuestros objetivos, no podremos completar nuestra "
"misión..."

#. [scenario], id=Prologue_Part_II
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:4
msgid "Prologue: Enlightening the Past - Part II"
msgstr "Prólogo: Iluminando el Pasado - Parte II"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:22
msgid "Find the Sky Soul and the Trident of the Seas with someone"
msgstr "Encuentra el Alma del Cielo y el Tridente de los Mares con alguien"

#. [objectives]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:39
msgid ""
"Hashira can recruit/recall in the hexes adjacent to where she starts the "
"scenario"
msgstr ""
"Hashira puede reclutar/reincorporar en los hexágonos adyacentes a donde "
"inicia el escenario"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:61
msgid "Elemental Guardians"
msgstr "Guardianes Elementales"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:99
msgid ""
"Ayraton, I have hired you to come with me till this place, but I'd like to "
"count with your skills a little further."
msgstr ""
"Ayraton, te contraté para que vinieras conmigo hasta este lugar, pero me "
"gustaría contar con tus habilidades un poco más."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:103
msgid "What do you wish from me?"
msgstr "¿Qué deseas de mí?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:107
msgid ""
"I don't want to present this jewel to anyone before I have a better "
"understanding of it. But I understand little of spirits that are not part of "
"the Raw; you, on the other hand, are the brightest student of the subject "
"Maat'Kare has seen in years, or so the Headmaster has told me. Thus, I want "
"your help to study the souls that dwell inside this gem: are they still "
"conscious? Can they communicate with those who peer into this gem? How "
"stable is the spell that binds them all inside it? I will pay you well, and "
"offer you my mansion in the town of Hatshep for you to live and work on your "
"research."
msgstr ""
"No quiero presentar esta joya a nadie antes de tener un mejor entendimiento "
"de ella. Pero entiendo poco de espíritus que no forman parte de lo Crudo; "
"tú, en cambio, eres el estudiante más brillante del tema que Maat'Kare ha "
"visto en años, o eso me dijo el Director. Por eso, quiero tu ayuda para "
"estudiar las almas que habitan dentro de esta gema: ¿todavía están "
"conscientes? ¿Pueden comunicarse con quienes miran dentro de esta gema? ¿Qué "
"tan estable es el hechizo que las ata a todas dentro de ella? Te pagaré bien "
"y te ofreceré mi mansión en la ciudad de Hatshep para que vivas y trabajes "
"en tu investigación."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:111
msgid ""
"Well, I- Of course I accept! Such a unique chance to study such formidable "
"artefact... I swear I will dedicate myself to the fullest of my abilities on "
"better understanding the Sky Soul."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, yo... ¡Por supuesto que acepto! Una oportunidad tan única para "
"estudiar un artefacto tan formidable... Juro que me dedicaré con todas mis "
"capacidades a entender mejor el Alma del Cielo."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:115
msgid ""
"I'm glad to hear that, but you must beware the time you expose yourself to "
"this gem; don't forget Akashia's fate. Now, let us leave this crater before "
"Leivyan and his Desert Ghosts find us."
msgstr ""
"Me alegra oír eso, pero debes tener cuidado con el tiempo que te expongas a "
"esta gema; no olvides el destino de Akashia. Ahora, salgamos de este cráter "
"antes de que Leivyan y sus Fantasmas del Desierto nos encuentren."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:132
msgid ""
"Incredible... The air here at the abyss' bottom almost crackles with magic "
"energy; an energy that must be lingering here since that legendary battle, "
"the power of Myra herself..."
msgstr ""
"Increíble... El aire aquí en el fondo del abismo casi crepita con energía "
"mágica; una energía que debe estar persistiendo aquí desde esa legendaria "
"batalla, el poder de la propia Myra..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:136
msgid ""
"But what amazes me is the size of this crater; to think that it was opened "
"by a single mage... With all my power and knowledge, I feel absolutely "
"humbled before this colossal testament of her strength."
msgstr ""
"Pero lo que me asombra es el tamaño de este cráter; pensar que fue abierto "
"por una sola maga... Con todo mi poder y conocimiento, me siento "
"absolutamente humillada ante este colosal testimonio de su fuerza."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:140
msgid "Indeed, but Lady Hashira, I think that now you should really tell me..."
msgstr "En efecto, pero Lady Hashira, creo que ahora sí deberías decirme..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:144
msgid ""
"(annoyed) All right, all right! Say, you certainly have heard of the Garnet "
"of the Cursed Souls, right?"
msgstr ""
"(molesta) ¡Está bien, está bien! Dime, seguramente has oído del Granate de "
"las Almas Malditas, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:148
msgid "Of course I have, it's probably one of our most famous folk tales."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí, es probablemente uno de nuestros cuentos populares más "
"famosos."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:152
msgid ""
"What if I told you that it's not a mere folk tale, but something based on a "
"real thing?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué tal si te digo que no es solo un cuento popular, sino algo basado en "
"algo real?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:161
msgid "And... what makes you think that..."
msgstr "Y... ¿qué te hace pensar que..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:165
msgid ""
"If you have studied the Dragon War and the Exodus with attention, you have "
"noticed that there are some strange, unexplained things about these events. "
"Firstly, no scroll tells precisely how the Sky Dragon, after being defeated "
"at Garet-Desh, re-emerged in the Crystal Tower."
msgstr ""
"Si has estudiado la Guerra de los Dragones y el Éxodo con atención, habrás "
"notado que hay cosas extrañas y sin explicación sobre estos eventos. "
"Primero, ningún pergamino cuenta con precisión cómo el Dragón del Cielo, "
"después de ser derrotado en Garet-Desh, reapareció en la Torre de Cristal."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:169
msgid ""
"It is told that, though his body had been destroyed at Garet-Desh, his "
"spirit remained on this world, and that he possessed the Celestial Lord "
"Grigorius when he was consumed by his own greediness..."
msgstr ""
"Se cuenta que, aunque su cuerpo fue destruido en Garet-Desh, su espíritu "
"permaneció en este mundo, y que poseyó al Lord Celestial Grigorius cuando "
"este fue consumido por su propia avaricia..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:173
msgid ""
"Which is a beautiful story to tell the peasants, but which makes little "
"sense for more learned people like you and me, right?"
msgstr ""
"Que es una hermosa historia para contar a los campesinos, pero que tiene "
"poco sentido para personas más instruidas como tú y yo, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:177
msgid "Well..."
msgstr "Bueno..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:181
msgid ""
"Another mystery that History doesn't explain is the Ughure Incident. Every "
"historian agrees that even Myra herself couldn't have destroyed an entire "
"dragon horde single-handedly; some versions claim that the lizards’ demise "
"was caused by the Garnet of the Cursed Souls, which is supposed to have been "
"an artefact created by the High Ascendant Maat. But, since no evidence of "
"its existence was ever found..."
msgstr ""
"Otro misterio que la Historia no explica es el Incidente de Ughure. Todos "
"los historiadores coinciden en que ni siquiera la propia Myra podría haber "
"destruido una horda completa de dragones ella sola; algunas versiones "
"afirman que la muerte de los lagartos fue causada por el Granate de las "
"Almas Malditas, que se supone fue un artefacto creado por el Alto Ascendente "
"Maat. Pero, como nunca se encontró ninguna evidencia de su existencia..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:185
msgid "I see, but how did you conclude that..."
msgstr "Entiendo, pero ¿cómo llegaste a la conclusión de que..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:189
msgid ""
"A few weeks ago, I discovered a journal written by my ancestor Ravyan, where "
"he describes a jewel of immense power, which contained within itself the "
"souls of four dragons, including the Sky Dragon himself, all locked in it by "
"Maat in the Battle of Garet-Desh. This jewel was called the Sky Soul."
msgstr ""
"Hace unas semanas, descubrí un diario escrito por mi ancestro Ravyan, donde "
"describe una joya de inmenso poder, que contenía dentro de sí las almas de "
"cuatro dragones, incluido el propio Dragón del Cielo, todos encerrados en "
"ella por Maat en la Batalla de Garet-Desh. Esta joya se llamaba el Alma del "
"Cielo."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:193
msgid ""
"According to Ravyan, Myra and her companions chose not to reveal the truth "
"about it to anyone, and so the Sky Soul remained a secret even after her "
"death; however, because the soldiers had already witnessed the jewel's "
"power, the Founders spread rumours of a mighty magical weapon created by "
"Maat. It was then that the story of the Garnet first appeared."
msgstr ""
"Según Ravyan, Myra y sus compañeros decidieron no revelar la verdad sobre "
"ella a nadie, y por eso el Alma del Cielo permaneció en secreto incluso "
"después de su muerte; sin embargo, como los soldados ya habían presenciado "
"el poder de la joya, los Fundadores difundieron rumores de un poderoso arma "
"mágica creada por Maat. Fue entonces cuando apareció por primera vez la "
"historia del Granate."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:197
msgid ""
"I now see what you meant with 'making a discovery that would shatter "
"Maat'Kare's established lore'..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora entiendo a qué te referías con «hacer un descubrimiento que haría "
"añicos la lore establecida de Maat'Kare»..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:201
msgid ""
"Furthermore, we may also find the Trident of the Seas, which, according to "
"the lore, contains the power of the Water Dragon within itself. So, let us "
"not waste any more time talking, and let us find these relics."
msgstr ""
"Además, también podríamos encontrar el Tridente de los Mares, que, según la "
"leyenda, contiene el poder del Dragón del Agua dentro de sí. Así que no "
"perdamos más tiempo hablando y busquemos estas reliquias."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:216
msgid ""
"By the Gods, it's getting better and better! These elementals can only be "
"the very same ones summoned by Myra centuries ago, kept 'alive' by the "
"energy that lingers in this abyss!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por los Dioses, cada vez se pone mejor! Estos elementales solo pueden ser "
"los mismos que Myra invocó hace siglos, mantenidos «vivos» por la energía "
"que persiste en este abismo."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:220
msgid ""
"Yes, I'm thrilled too, but I don't think these elementals will take kindly "
"to our presence here."
msgstr ""
"Sí, yo también estoy emocionado, pero no creo que estos elementales reciban "
"con agrado nuestra presencia aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:224
msgid ""
"Good; I've always wanted to measure my powers against Myra's elementals..."
msgstr ""
"Bien; siempre quise medir mis poderes contra los elementales de Myra..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:245
msgid "Hey, I think I found the Trident!"
msgstr "¡Oye, creo que encontré el Tridente!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:249
msgid ""
"Yes, it can only be the Trident of the Seas! Can you feel it, Ayraton? Can "
"you feel the power emanating from it?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, ¡solo puede ser el Tridente de los Mares! ¿Lo sientes, Ayraton? ¿Sientes "
"el poder que emana de él?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:253
msgid "Surely I can! Um, may I give it a closer look...?"
msgstr "¡Claro que sí! Um, ¿puedo darle un vistazo más de cerca...?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:257
msgid ""
"You may, but do not touch it. I’ve once read about a similarly mighty weapon "
"used by the kings of Garet-Desh which heavily injured any unworthy person "
"who touched it; I wouldn't be surprised if the Trident destroys any wielder "
"other than Myra herself."
msgstr ""
"Puedes, pero no lo toques. Una vez leí sobre un arma igualmente poderosa "
"usada por los reyes de Garet-Desh que hería gravemente a cualquier persona "
"indigna que la tocara; no me sorprendería que el Tridente destruya a "
"cualquier portador que no sea la propia Myra."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:270
msgid "We're making progress, but we still need to find the soul!"
msgstr "Estamos avanzando, ¡pero todavía necesitamos encontrar el alma!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:296
msgid ""
"Look, I've found a stone... Weird, suddenly I have begun to feel strange... "
"Like an overwhelming grief..."
msgstr ""
"Mira, encontré una piedra... Qué raro, de repente he empezado a sentirme "
"extraño... Como una pena abrumadora..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:300
msgid ""
"Get away from it! That must be the Sky Soul; according to Ravyan's journal, "
"it was impregnated with the Sky Dragon's malice, twisting the minds of "
"anyone who stood near it for long. Apparently, it was this jewel that caused "
"the death of Akashia, Hiera'Laksha's first Head..."
msgstr ""
"¡Aléjate de ella! Esa debe ser el Alma del Cielo; según el diario de Ravyan, "
"estaba impregnada con la malicia del Dragón del Cielo, torciendo las mentes "
"de cualquiera que permaneciera cerca de ella por mucho tiempo. "
"Aparentemente, fue esta joya la que causó la muerte de Akashia, la primera "
"Directora de Hiera'Laksha..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:307
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:344
msgid ""
"Yes... Yes, this is really the fabled jewel, the Garnet of the Cursed Souls, "
"created by High Ascendant Maat to imprison the soul of Irdya's most dreaded "
"foe to date!"
msgstr ""
"Sí... Sí, esta es realmente la joya legendaria, el Granate de las Almas "
"Malditas, creada por el Alto Ascendente Maat para aprisionar el alma del "
"enemigo más temido de Irdya hasta la fecha."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:311
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:348
msgid ""
"Fascinating... But, at the same time, terrible... No wonder not even Akashia "
"the Strong could resist its influence: I'm certain it could break even the "
"mentally strongest people."
msgstr ""
"Fascinante... Pero, al mismo tiempo, terrible... No es de extrañar que ni "
"siquiera Akashia la Fuerte pudiera resistir su influencia: estoy seguro de "
"que podría romper incluso a las personas mentalmente más fuertes."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:324
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:362
msgid "We're making progress, but we still need to find the trident!"
msgstr "Estamos avanzando, ¡pero todavía necesitamos encontrar el tridente!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_II.cfg:389
msgid ""
"We should have been quicker here, now we might be caught by Leivyan and his "
"Desert Ghosts!"
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos haber sido más rápidos aquí, ¡ahora podríamos ser atrapados por "
"Leivyan y sus Fantasmas del Desierto!"

#. [scenario], id=Prologue_Part_III
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:4
msgid "Prologue: Enlightening the Past - Part III"
msgstr "Prólogo: Iluminando el Pasado - Parte III"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:23
msgid "Hold off Menon Hekare's attack"
msgstr "Resistir el ataque de Menon Hekare"

#. [side]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:52
msgid "Hiera'Laksha"
msgstr "Hiera’Laksha"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:129
msgid ""
"Greetings, Lady Hashira. I am Menon Hekare, and I come here on behalf of the "
"Chamber of Sages..."
msgstr ""
"Saludos, Lady Hashira. Soy Menon Hekare, y vengo aquí en nombre de la Cámara "
"de los Sabios..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:133
msgid ""
"Say no more, for I now realise everything: our sister Ithania has told you "
"something about the nature of our experiments, and you have come to "
"investigate yourself, am I right?"
msgstr ""
"No digas más, porque ahora entiendo todo: nuestra hermana Ithania te ha "
"contado algo sobre la naturaleza de nuestros experimentos, y has venido a "
"investigar por ti mismo, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:137
msgid ""
"Yes, Lady Ithania has informed me about the experiments you are carrying on "
"in Hiera'Laksha, and..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, Lady Ithania me ha informado sobre los experimentos que están llevando a "
"cabo en Hiera'Laksha, y..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:141
msgid ""
"Then allow me to inform you, worthy Menon, that she could not have told you "
"anything short of a lie, for she was never allowed to see the object of our "
"studies..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces permíteme informarte, digno Menon, que no podría haberte dicho nada "
"que no fuera una mentira, porque nunca se le permitió ver el objeto de "
"nuestros estudios..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:145
msgid ""
"...Which I'm certain to be an obscure artefact known by our founders as the "
"Sky Soul, do you confirm this?"
msgstr ""
"...que estoy seguro es un artefacto oscuro conocido por nuestros fundadores "
"como el Alma del Cielo, ¿confirmas esto?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:154
msgid "I... H-how.."
msgstr "Yo... ¿C-cómo.."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:158
msgid ""
"Well, milady, you are not the only one who grew up interested in our History "
"and in the Garnet of the Cursed Souls. When I decided to study them some "
"months ago, I guessed that the Founders could have known the truth but chose "
"not to divulge it, and so I searched for every piece of written text they "
"had left with the aid of their heirs. The Wadjets didn't find anything from "
"Myra, Jevyan, Alenya or Dvalin, nor did the Aracynes find anything from "
"Ravyan. "
msgstr ""
"Bueno, señora, no eres la única que creció interesada en nuestra Historia y "
"en el Granate de las Almas Malditas. Cuando decidí estudiarlos hace algunos "
"meses, supuse que los Fundadores podrían haber conocido la verdad pero "
"eligieron no divulgarla, y por eso busqué cada pieza de texto escrito que "
"habían dejado con la ayuda de sus herederos. Los Wadjet no encontraron nada "
"de Myra, Jevyan, Alenya o Dvalin, ni los Aracyne encontraron nada de Ravyan."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:162
msgid ""
"Not willing to give up, I sought you out; I went to your mansion at Hatshep, "
"but I was informed that you had gone on a travel to the west; I visited "
"nearby caravanserais and outposts, hoping to find you, but all I found was "
"that you had been sighted going towards the Silent Desert..."
msgstr ""
"No dispuesto a rendirme, te busqué; fui a tu mansión en Hatshep, pero me "
"informaron que habías salido de viaje hacia el oeste; visité caravansares y "
"puestos cercanos, esperando encontrarte, pero todo lo que encontré fue que "
"te habían visto dirigiéndote hacia el Desierto Silencioso..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:166
msgid ""
"Right, I did go there, but how does my desert stroll provide any evidence of "
"ill intent by my part?"
msgstr ""
"Cierto, fui allí, pero ¿cómo mi paseo por el desierto proporciona alguna "
"evidencia de mala intención de mi parte?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:170
msgid ""
"Well, I naturally followed you into the desert, but I found none there - I "
"was the one to be found, by a desert wanderer who goes by the name Leivyan..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, naturalmente te seguí al desierto, pero no encontré a nadie allí - "
"fui yo quien fue encontrado, por un vagabundo del desierto que se llama "
"Leivyan..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:179
msgid ""
"...and he told me everything about the Sky Soul and about how you had "
"captured it. Afterwards, I tried to find you at Hatshep once again, and once "
"again I was unsuccessful; and yet again I was found, this time by Lady "
"Ithania, whose reports of some strange experiment being carried out by you "
"at Hiera'Laksha only confirmed all my suspicions."
msgstr ""
"...y me contó todo sobre el Alma del Cielo y cómo la habías capturado. "
"Después, intenté encontrarte en Hatshep una vez más, y una vez más no tuve "
"éxito; y una vez más fui encontrado, esta vez por Lady Ithania, cuyos "
"informes sobre un extraño experimento que estabas llevando a cabo en "
"Hiera'Laksha solo confirmaron todas mis sospechas."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:183
msgid ""
"I see... Well, you have caught me, Menon; I do have the Sky Soul in my "
"possession, and I am doing research on it with the help of a spirit mage, "
"but then I ask you, how does it concern you, or even Maat'Kare? We Windsong "
"are an independent faction, and so we need not explain our motives to anyone "
"else..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo... Bueno, me has atrapado, Menon; sí tengo el Alma del Cielo en mi "
"posesión, y estoy investigándola con la ayuda de un mago de espíritus, pero "
"entonces te pregunto, ¿cómo te concierne a ti, o incluso a Maat'Kare? "
"Nosotras las Hijas del Viento somos una facción independiente, y por eso no "
"necesitamos explicar nuestros motivos a nadie más..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:187
msgid ""
"...Unless it is something that involves the safety of the Maat'Karians. I "
"have shared my knowledge on the Sky Soul with the Chamber of Sages, and the "
"elders have agreed that we cannot let you go on playing with the being that "
"nearly destroyed this world thrice in the past. You know the story behind "
"Myra's last battle, and so you know what happens when the Soul is "
"irresponsibly dealt with."
msgstr ""
"...A menos que sea algo que involucre la seguridad de los maat'karianos. He "
"compartido mi conocimiento sobre el Alma del Cielo con la Cámara de los "
"Sabios, y los ancianos han acordado que no podemos permitir que sigas "
"jugando con el ser que casi destruyó este mundo tres veces en el pasado. "
"Conoces la historia detrás de la última batalla de Myra, y por eso sabes qué "
"pasa cuando el Alma se maneja de manera irresponsable."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:191
msgid ""
"You and the Chamber of Sages have noble intentions, but I believe we deserve "
"more trust than that. We are not power-hungry fools like that old Celestial "
"Lord, we just want to find a way to counter the Soul's danger."
msgstr ""
"Tú y la Cámara de los Sabios tienen intenciones nobles, pero creo que "
"merecemos más confianza que eso. No somos tontos hambrientos de poder como "
"ese viejo Lord Celestial, solo queremos encontrar una forma de contrarrestar "
"el peligro del Alma."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:195
msgid ""
"Lady Hashira, this is something you should tell the sages; I am here only to "
"take the Soul under Maat'Kare's custody."
msgstr ""
"Lady Hashira, esto es algo que deberías decirle a los sabios; yo estoy aquí "
"solo para tomar el Alma bajo la custodia de Maat'Kare."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:199
msgid ""
"So... So you want me to simply hand the Soul to you?! Why must it stay at "
"Maat'Kare? Have we Windsong become unreliable allies overnight?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces... ¿¡Quieres que simplemente te entregue el Alma!? ¿Por qué debe "
"quedarse en Maat'Kare? ¿Nosotras las Hijas del Viento nos hemos vuelto "
"aliadas poco confiables de la noche a la mañana?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:203
msgid "As I said, this is something you must treat with the sages, not me."
msgstr "Como dije, esto es algo que debes tratar con los sabios, no conmigo."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:207
msgid ""
"Then tell them that I am keeping the Soul at Hiera'Laksha, and that, if they "
"want it, they must come and take it by force!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces diles que estoy guardando el Alma en Hiera'Laksha, y que si la "
"quieren, deben venir y tomarla por la fuerza!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:211
msgid ""
"In fact, Lady Hashira, they have already given me permission to employ "
"violence if necessary..."
msgstr ""
"De hecho, Lady Hashira, ya me han dado permiso para emplear violencia si es "
"necesario..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:215
msgid ""
"Oh, really? And who is going to help you? Please do tell me, for I see none "
"beside you – other than the little viper, of course..."
msgstr ""
"¿Ah, sí? ¿Y quién va a ayudarte? Por favor dímelo, porque no veo a nadie a "
"tu lado, excepto la pequeña víbora, por supuesto..."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:219
msgid "(angry) You...!"
msgstr "(enojada) ¡Tú...!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:223
msgid "Worry not about me, for I alone am enough to retrieve the Soul."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes por mí, porque yo solo soy suficiente para recuperar el Alma."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:227
msgid ""
"You?! (laughs in disdain) You may be the first Master of Four Lights in "
"centuries, but you should know better than defying the Windsong, impudent "
"boy - and I shall presently teach you why!"
msgstr ""
"¿¡Tú!? (ríe con desdén) Puedes ser el primer Maestro de las Cuatro Luces en "
"siglos, pero deberías saber mejor que desafiar a las Hijas del Viento, "
"muchacho insolente, ¡y ahora mismo te enseñaré por qué!"

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:231
msgid ""
"My sisters, please heed me! Do not allow Hashira to lead you to your own "
"destruction! Do not let her turn you all against our precious Foundation!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hermanas mías, por favor escúchenme! ¡No permitan que Hashira las lleve a "
"su propia destrucción! ¡No dejen que las vuelva a todas contra nuestra "
"preciosa Fundación!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:235
msgid ""
"Never in our recorded History has the Windsong Order been so betrayed by one "
"of its own... Your name shall forever be engraved in our scrolls as the most "
"unworthy of all Windsong."
msgstr ""
"Nunca en nuestra Historia registrada la Orden de las Hijas del Viento ha "
"sido tan traicionada por una de las suyas... Tu nombre quedará grabado para "
"siempre en nuestros pergaminos como la más indigna de todas las Hijas del "
"Viento."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:239
msgid ""
"Worry not, Ithania, my elementals shall not kill your sisters; I will cast a "
"spell that will put to sleep every Windsong that is heavily injured."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, Ithania, mis elementales no matarán a tus hermanas; lanzaré "
"un hechizo que dormirá a toda Hija del Viento que esté gravemente herida."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:243
msgid "Thank you, Menon..."
msgstr "Gracias, Menon..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:259
msgid "(panting) Lady Hashira... I have... succeeded..."
msgstr "(jadeando) Lady Hashira... Lo he... logrado..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:263
msgid "Do you mean... Ayraton, did you manage to split the souls?"
msgstr "¿Quieres decir... Ayraton, lograste separar las almas?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:267
msgid ""
"(smiling) Look by yourself... (unwraps a purple gem) Do you recognize the "
"energy emanating from it?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Mira tú misma... (desenvuelve una gema púrpura) ¿Reconoces la "
"energía que emana de ella?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:271
msgid ""
"It's the Sky Soul, but its energy... it flows much more powerfully than "
"before...! But... Ayraton, how long have you exposed yourself to its evil "
"aura? And what about the other souls?"
msgstr ""
"Es el Alma del Cielo, pero su energía... ¡fluye mucho más poderosa que "
"antes...! Pero... Ayraton, ¿cuánto tiempo te expusiste a su aura maligna? ¿Y "
"qué pasó con las otras almas?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:275
msgid ""
"Worry not, milady, I haven't exposed myself to it for long; it's simply that "
"its aura is now just too intense for Windsong ciphers to contain. As for the "
"other souls, I have transferred them to another gem, as you have requested; "
"however, seeing your dear Foundation threatened by that pesky Menon, I have "
"taken the liberty of using it in a weapon of great might..."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, señora, no me expuse a ella por mucho tiempo; simplemente "
"su aura ahora es demasiado intensa para que los cifrados de las Hijas del "
"Viento la contengan. En cuanto a las otras almas, las he transferido a otra "
"gema, como me pediste; sin embargo, al ver tu querida Fundación amenazada "
"por ese molesto Menon, me tomé la libertad de usarla en un arma de gran "
"poder..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:279
msgid ""
"You have just accomplished an astonishing feat, Ayraton, one that I doubt "
"even Menon would have equalled; and you have dutifully served me and, "
"consequently, the Windsong Order. Thus, I shall trust whatever plan you have "
"in mind. Is this weapon ready?"
msgstr ""
"Acabas de lograr una hazaña asombrosa, Ayraton, una que dudo que incluso "
"Menon hubiera igualado; y me has servido fielmente y, por consiguiente, a la "
"Orden de las Hijas del Viento. Por eso, confiaré en cualquier plan que "
"tengas en mente. ¿Está lista esta arma?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:283
msgid "Apologies, milady, but it will take some time to be complete..."
msgstr "Disculpas, señora, pero tomará algo de tiempo completarla..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:287
msgid ""
"Then we shall hold off Menon's beasts until it is ready – or maybe we shall "
"crush him and the Viper before that; I am eager to test the unencumbered Sky "
"Soul..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces resistiremos a las bestias de Menon hasta que esté lista, o tal vez "
"lo aplastemos a él y a la Víbora antes; estoy ansiosa por probar el Alma del "
"Cielo sin restricciones..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:291
msgid ""
"And I shall return to my laboratory and hasten the weapon's building. Excuse "
"me..."
msgstr ""
"Y yo regresaré a mi laboratorio y aceleraré la construcción del arma. Con "
"permiso..."

#. [object]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:304
msgid "Sky Soul"
msgstr "Alma del Cielo"

#. [object]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:307
msgid "The 'purified' Sky Soul can now be used as a weapon of massive power"
msgstr ""
"El Alma del Cielo «purificada» ahora puede usarse como un arma de poder "
"masivo"

#. [effect], apply_to=new_attack, type=arcane, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:314
msgid "Sky Soul's Breath"
msgstr "Aliento del Alma del Cielo"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:352
msgid ""
"HA! So this is the power that destroyed an army of dragons at Ughure!? I now "
"understand why even Myra could not resist its lure... The lure of unlimited "
"power!"
msgstr ""
"¡JA! ¿¡Así que este es el poder que destruyó un ejército de dragones en "
"Ughure!? Ahora entiendo por qué ni siquiera Myra pudo resistir su señuelo... "
"¡El señuelo del poder ilimitado!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Hashira, are you insane?! Have you studied <i>nothing</i> about our History?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hashira, ¿estás loca?! ¡¿No has estudiado <i>nada</i> sobre nuestra "
"Historia!?"

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:360
msgid ""
"Give up, Menon, she's far too taken by her own power-hunger to give heed to "
"anyone now!"
msgstr ""
"Ríndete, Menon, ¡está demasiado consumida por su propia hambre de poder como "
"para prestar atención a alguien ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:364
msgid ""
"(in rage) I have had it with your impertinence, Ithania! Ayraton's weapon be "
"damned, I shall go there and destroy the two of you myself!"
msgstr ""
"(con rabia) ¡Ya estoy harta de tu impertinencia, Ithania! Al diablo con el "
"arma de Ayraton, ¡iré allí y los destruiré a los dos yo misma!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:368
msgid ""
"You leave me no choice but to use my full power against you, Head of the "
"Windsong..."
msgstr ""
"No me dejas otra opción más que usar todo mi poder contra ti, Jefa de las "
"Hijas del Viento..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:402
msgid "Argh! No... Please, wait...!"
msgstr "¡Argh! No... ¡Por favor, espera...!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:412
msgid "Milady, what is happening to you?"
msgstr "Señora, ¿qué te está pasando?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:416
msgid ""
"(frightened) The Raw... My guardian spirit... I... I don't feel them... "
"anymore!"
msgstr ""
"(asustada) Lo Crudo... Mi espíritu guardián... Yo... ya no los siento... "
"¡más!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:420
msgid "(appalled) But... How can this be? You're a Herald!"
msgstr "(horrorizado) Pero... ¿Cómo puede ser? ¡Eres una Heraldo!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:424
msgid ""
"I am certain that the Soul's evil aura has suppressed your affinity with the "
"Raw and its spirits; just as it suppressed Myra's affinity with the spirits "
"of nature when she first wielded it!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy seguro de que el aura maligna del Alma ha suprimido tu afinidad con lo "
"Crudo y sus espíritus; ¡igual que suprimió la afinidad de Myra con los "
"espíritus de la naturaleza cuando lo empuñó por primera vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:428
msgid ""
"(trembling) I-if my guardian spirit is too weak to coexist with the Sky "
"Soul, then I do not need it... nor the Raw itself!"
msgstr ""
"(temblando) S-si mi espíritu guardián es demasiado débil para coexistir con "
"el Alma del Cielo, entonces no lo necesito... ¡ni al propio Crudo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Disgusting... Will you still follow a sister who forsakes one of the pillars "
"of our Order, Windsong? Hashira has just given you the ultimate proof that "
"she is not fit to occupy the place that has already belonged to Maat, Myra "
"and Akashia!"
msgstr ""
"Asqueroso... ¿Todavía seguirán a una hermana que abandona uno de los pilares "
"de nuestra Orden, Hijas del Viento? ¡Hashira acaba de darles la prueba "
"definitiva de que no es apta para ocupar el lugar que ya perteneció a Maat, "
"Myra y Akashia!"

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:436
msgid "We... we will..."
msgstr "Nosotras... nosotras..."

#. [message]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:450
msgid ""
"Lady Hashira, I... We can no longer follow you who has turned your back to "
"what we hold as holiest. I am truly..."
msgstr ""
"Lady Hashira, yo... Ya no podemos seguirte a ti que le has dado la espalda a "
"lo que consideramos más sagrado. Realmente estoy..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:454
msgid ""
"(Mad in rage) Aahhh, I should have expected it from weak women such as you… "
"You too shame our Order by cowering in fear before the unknown! Begone from "
"my sight, I have no need of such useless sisters!"
msgstr ""
"(loca de rabia) Aahhh, debería haberlo esperado de mujeres débiles como "
"ustedes… ¡Ustedes también avergüenzan a nuestra Orden al acobardarse de "
"miedo ante lo desconocido! ¡Fuera de mi vista, no necesito hermanas tan "
"inútiles!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:469
msgid "To think that one so wise would fall so low..."
msgstr "Pensar que alguien tan sabia caería tan bajo..."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:473
msgid ""
"My sisters, run away from that mad woman, or she will destroy all of you!"
msgstr "¡Hermanas mías, huyan de esa mujer loca, o las destruirá a todas!"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:512
msgid "(laughing and panting) I have... finished the weapon... milady!"
msgstr "(riendo y jadeando) ¡He... terminado el arma... señora!"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:516
msgid ""
"I am ashamed for having failed to destroy Menon before you concluded your "
"toy, Ayraton... So be it, unleash it upon our enemies at once!"
msgstr ""
"Me avergüenzo por no haber logrado destruir a Menon antes de que terminaras "
"tu juguete, Ayraton... Que así sea, ¡desátalo sobre nuestros enemigos de "
"inmediato!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:520
msgid ""
"Ayraton, you were a great student of the Academy, one that I respected and "
"admired, and who was praised by the Headmaster himself! Why have you gone so "
"astray? Was it ambition only?"
msgstr ""
"Ayraton, eras un gran estudiante de la Academia, uno al que respetaba y "
"admiraba, y que el propio Director elogiaba! ¿Por qué te has desviado tanto? "
"¿Fue solo ambición?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:524
msgid ""
"Filthy Menon, now you claim to respect and admire me, but you never raised a "
"finger to defend me when those idiots of the Academy mocked me, calling me a "
"dreaming fool next to the 'great' Master of Four Lights! Yes, they all "
"laughed at my projects and ideas, but I will show them how wrong they were, "
"and how my ideas were right..."
msgstr ""
"Asqueroso Menon, ahora dices respetarme y admirarme, pero nunca levantaste "
"un dedo para defenderme cuando esos idiotas de la Academia se burlaban de "
"mí, llamándome un soñador tonto al lado del «gran» Maestro de las Cuatro "
"Luces! Sí, todos se reían de mis proyectos e ideas, pero les mostraré lo "
"equivocados que estaban, y cuán correctas eran mis ideas..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:528
msgid ""
"Ayraton, don't tell me... Those projects about the creation of artificial "
"life..."
msgstr ""
"Ayraton, no me digas... Esos proyectos sobre la creación de vida "
"artificial..."

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:532
msgid ""
"NETJER-TA, I GIVE THEE... THE KING OF BEASTS, THE ULTIMATE DRAGON, ISFET!"
msgstr ""
"¡NETJER-TA, TE ENTREGO... AL REY DE LAS BESTIAS, EL DRAGÓN SUPREMO, ISFET!"

#. [unit], id=Isfet, type=Ancient Feral Dragon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:546
msgid "Isfet"
msgstr "Isfet"

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:557
msgid "What on Irdya is that thing...?"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios es esa cosa...?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:561
msgid ""
"See, Menon, the result of my experiments and calculations: a perfectly "
"functioning and thinking life form, a child of alchemy and spirit magic, "
"modelled after the dreadful foes of our ancestors, but perfected and fuelled "
"by the soul power of three Fire Dragons!"
msgstr ""
"Mira, Menon, el resultado de mis experimentos y cálculos: una forma de vida "
"perfectamente funcional y pensante, un hijo de la alquimia y la magia "
"espiritual, modelado según los terribles enemigos de nuestros ancestros, "
"¡pero perfeccionado y alimentado por el poder de las almas de tres Dragones "
"de Fuego!"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:565
msgid ""
"Now, my creature, it's your time to act... Go forth and show those people I "
"told you about how perfect you are!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora, mi criatura, es tu momento de actuar... ¡Ve y muéstrales a esas "
"personas de las que te hablé lo perfecto que eres!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:569
msgid ""
"However, the newborn dragon did not seem to hear his creator. After the "
"first awkward steps, Isfet shook his head, roaring in pain; and, even though "
"his hard-skinned face could not show it, his gleaming eyes revealed the "
"intense conflict that raged on inside him…..."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, el dragón recién nacido no parecía escuchar a su creador. "
"Después de los primeros pasos torpes, Isfet sacudió la cabeza, rugiendo de "
"dolor; y, aunque su rostro de piel dura no podía mostrarlo, sus ojos "
"brillantes revelaban el intenso conflicto que rugía dentro de él…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:573
msgid "...but which did not last for long."
msgstr "...pero que no duró mucho."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:584
msgid "Ayraton!!!"
msgstr "¡Ayraton!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Ayraton
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:588
msgid "I-Isfet... w-wh..."
msgstr "I-Isfet... q-qué..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:598
msgid ""
"What a disappointment, my friend... After such a great success, you present "
"me this failure... But I shall solve it short- What... The Soul is "
"glowing...?"
msgstr ""
"Qué decepción, amigo mío... Después de un éxito tan grande, me presentas "
"este fracaso... Pero lo resolveré pronto... ¿Qué... el Alma está "
"brillando...?"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:612
msgid "AAAAARRRRR!!!"
msgstr "¡AAAAARRRRR!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:631
msgid "Oh no, the beast is fleeing! Quick, we must chase it!"
msgstr "¡Oh no, la bestia está huyendo! ¡Rápido, debemos perseguirla!"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:635
msgid ""
"No, let it be; something tells me he just wants a calm, deserted place to "
"hide. And besides, if he keeps going south, he will end up in Argea and "
"cease to be our problem. Now..."
msgstr ""
"No, déjenlo; algo me dice que solo quiere un lugar tranquilo y desierto para "
"esconderse. Además, si sigue hacia el sur, terminará en Argea y dejará de "
"ser nuestro problema. Ahora..."

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:653
msgid "Y-y-you... I-I'll not... (clutches the Soul)"
msgstr "T-t-tú... N-no voy a... (aprieta el Alma)"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:657
msgid ""
"(sad) So even now, as life abandons your ruined remains, all you think about "
"is wielding the power that has rejected and destroyed you? I will not "
"lecture you for a mistake that even Myra has committed, but I must not allow "
"you to keep it. (takes the gem from Hashira's burned hand)"
msgstr ""
"(triste) ¿Así que incluso ahora, mientras la vida abandona tus restos "
"arruinados, todo lo que piensas es en empuñar el poder que te ha rechazado y "
"destruido? No te daré una lección por un error que incluso Myra cometió, "
"pero no debo permitir que lo conserves. (toma la gema de la mano quemada de "
"Hashira)"

#. [message], speaker=Hashira
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:661
msgid "N-n-n-n..."
msgstr "N-n-n-n..."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:671
msgid ""
"Thus dies the most dishonourable of all Windsong... A great tragedy has "
"afflicted our Foundation today, but we shall recover from it, as we have "
"recovered from so many similar tragedies in our History..."
msgstr ""
"Así muere la más deshonrosa de todas las Hijas del Viento... Una gran "
"tragedia ha azotado a nuestra Fundación hoy, pero nos recuperaremos de ella, "
"como nos hemos recuperado de tantas tragedias similares en nuestra "
"Historia..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:675
msgid "I doubt not that you will recover, Ithania, but it shall not be here."
msgstr "No dudo que te recuperarás, Ithania, pero no será aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:679
msgid ""
"I don't understand, where do you suggest we should rebuild our Foundation?"
msgstr ""
"No entiendo, ¿dónde sugieres que deberíamos reconstruir nuestra Fundación?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:683
msgid ""
"Anywhere you wish to, as long as it is not on this continent; with the power "
"and authority granted me by the Chamber of Sages and the Chamber of Lords, I "
"henceforth banish the Windsong from Netjer-Ta."
msgstr ""
"Donde tú quieras, siempre y cuando no sea en este continente; con el poder y "
"la autoridad que me otorgaron la Cámara de los Sabios y la Cámara de los "
"Señores, a partir de ahora destierro a las Hijas del Viento de Netjer-Ta."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:692
msgid "M-Menon, what on Irdya are you saying...?"
msgstr "M-Menon, ¿qué demonios estás diciendo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:696
msgid ""
"This is the second time that the foolishness of the Windsong compromises the "
"safety of the humans and of the whole Netjer-Ta; I would not have it happen "
"a third time."
msgstr ""
"Esta es la segunda vez que la estupidez de las Hijas del Viento compromete "
"la seguridad de los humanos y de todo Netjer-Ta; no permitiré que ocurra una "
"tercera."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:700
msgid ""
"(shocked) You... You can't banish us from this continent... You have no such "
"authority..."
msgstr ""
"(impactada) Tú... No puedes desterrarnos de este continente... No tienes esa "
"autoridad..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:704
msgid ""
"Of course, you could go to Maat'Kare yourself and try to argue against my "
"decision, but I'm afraid that you shall not find much support amongst either "
"the Lords or the Sages. Hashira did manage to undermine much of their trust "
"in your Order with all her meddling in Maat'Karian affairs; when I report to "
"them what she had been doing with such an artefact..."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, podrías ir tú misma a Maat'Kare e intentar argumentar contra "
"mi decisión, pero me temo que no encontrarás mucho apoyo ni entre los "
"Señores ni entre los Sabios. Hashira logró socavar gran parte de su "
"confianza en tu Orden con toda su intromisión en los asuntos maat'karianos; "
"cuando les informe lo que ella había estado haciendo con un artefacto así..."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:708
msgid ""
"How... How can you do that to us?! You're sending us on an errand throughout "
"a world that we haven't explored in ages! What if we are caught by the "
"dragons again...?"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo... cómo puedes hacernos eso?! ¡Nos estás enviando a un viaje por un "
"mundo que no hemos explorado en siglos! ¿Qué pasa si nos atrapan los "
"dragones otra vez...?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:712
msgid ""
"I've risked myself by spending so much power to keep your sisters safely "
"asleep; accuse me of anything, but not of mercilessness. Whatever you do "
"outside of Netjer-Ta is none of my concern, but I'm certain that you, with "
"all your knowledge, will be able to find a new land for yourself."
msgstr ""
"Me arriesgué gastando tanto poder para mantener a tus hermanas dormidas y a "
"salvo; acúsame de cualquier cosa, pero no de falta de misericordia. Lo que "
"hagan fuera de Netjer-Ta no es de mi incumbencia, pero estoy seguro de que "
"tú, con todo tu conocimiento, podrás encontrar una nueva tierra para ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Ithania
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:716
msgid ""
"(trembling in fury) So be it, Menon Hekare... We shall leave this continent "
"forever, but know one thing: Maat'Kare is sending away one of the best "
"allies it could ever hope for. The day will come when the City of the Sun "
"will need our help, and when it does, all we shall say is: 'we may no longer "
"return to Netjer-Ta'."
msgstr ""
"(temblando de furia) Que así sea, Menon Hekare... Dejaremos este continente "
"para siempre, pero sepan una cosa: Maat'Kare está enviando lejos a uno de "
"los mejores aliados que jamás podría haber esperado. Llegará el día en que "
"la Ciudad del Sol necesite nuestra ayuda, y cuando eso suceda, todo lo que "
"diremos es: «ya no podemos regresar a Netjer-Ta»."

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:760
msgid ""
"By the Sacred Arrows, you did not exaggerate back then... What a formidable "
"mage you are, to single-handedly defeat the Order of the Windsong."
msgstr ""
"Por las Flechas Sagradas, no exagerabas entonces... Qué mago tan formidable "
"eres, para derrotar tú solo a la Orden de las Hijas del Viento."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:764
msgid ""
"I was lucky that they deserted their leader and that Ayraton's beast "
"intervened; had Hashira pressed on, with the Sky Soul in her hands and her "
"sisters at her back, I wouldn’t have stood a chance. I thank you for all the "
"help you have given me, Leivyan."
msgstr ""
"Tuve suerte de que abandonaran a su líder y de que la bestia de Ayraton "
"interviniera; si Hashira hubiera presionado, con el Alma del Cielo en sus "
"manos y sus hermanas a su espalda, no habría tenido ninguna oportunidad. Te "
"agradezco toda la ayuda que me has dado, Leivyan."

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:768
msgid ""
"As I thank you for helping me retrieve the Sky Soul. All I can give you in "
"return is the promise that we shall keep this gem in safety, away from ill-"
"intentioned hands."
msgstr ""
"Así como yo te agradezco por ayudarme a recuperar el Alma del Cielo. Todo lo "
"que puedo darte a cambio es la promesa de que mantendremos esta gema a "
"salvo, lejos de manos con malas intenciones."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:772
msgid "Will you? You've had this chance already, and you failed miserably."
msgstr "¿Lo harán? Ya tuvieron esta oportunidad y fallaron miserablemente."

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:776
msgid "Erm, excuse me?"
msgstr "Ejem, ¿disculpa?"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:780
msgid ""
"The Sky Soul was stolen from right under your nose by a small group of "
"Maat'Karian soldiers; what will you do if the remaining Windsong decide to "
"steal it again? After all, no one guarantees that they will really stay out "
"of Netjer-Ta; and, if Maat'Kare goes to your aid, many more people will know "
"of the Soul's existence. Thus, I deem it best if the Maat'Karians are the "
"ones..."
msgstr ""
"El Alma del Cielo fue robada justo bajo tus narices por un pequeño grupo de "
"soldados maat'karianos; ¿qué harán si las Hijas del Viento restantes deciden "
"robarla de nuevo? Después de todo, nadie garantiza que realmente se "
"mantengan fuera de Netjer-Ta; y, si Maat'Kare va en su ayuda, muchas más "
"personas conocerán la existencia del Alma. Por eso, considero que es mejor "
"que sean los maat'karianos los que..."

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:784
msgid "No, you won't!"
msgstr "¡No, no lo harás!"

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:792
msgid "AAARRRGHH!!! Curse you, traitor..."
msgstr "¡AAARRRGHH!!! Maldito traidor..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:796
msgid "...No, wait, I... I didn't mean to attack so powerfully..."
msgstr "...No, espera, yo... no quise atacar con tanta fuerza..."

#. [message], speaker=Leivyan
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:800
msgid ""
"(agonizing) I quake for you, young Menon... It seems like the Soul's malice "
"has started to take over your soul already..."
msgstr ""
"(agonizando) Temo por ti, joven Menon... Parece que la malicia del Alma ya "
"ha empezado a apoderarse de tu alma..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:804
msgid ""
"(angry) Stop saying nonsense, I was just defending myself...! Wait, I shall "
"heal you..."
msgstr ""
"(enojado) ¡Deja de decir tonterías, solo me estaba defendiendo...! Espera, "
"te sanaré..."

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:817
msgid "(appalled) *No... I... I have killed a human being...?*"
msgstr "(horrorizado) *No... Yo... ¿He matado a un ser humano...?*"

#. [message], speaker=Menon
#: War_of_the_Jewel/scenarios/Prologue_III.cfg:826
msgid ""
"<span size='large'>Wait... I can't falter now; I must make sure this gem "
"remains in safety first, only then will I have time for self-pity. Rest in "
"peace, poor Leivyan, for I shall take for myself the Desert Ghosts' "
"mission...*</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span size='large'>Espera... No puedo flaquear ahora; primero debo "
"asegurarme de que esta gema permanezca a salvo, solo entonces tendré tiempo "
"para compadecerme de mí mismo. Descansa en paz, pobre Leivyan, porque yo "
"asumiré la misión de los Fantasmas del Desierto...*</span>"

