#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Akhen.cfg:505
msgid "Akhen"
msgstr "Akhen"

#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Akhen.cfg:515
msgid ""
"Akhen Wadjet is the last remaining heir of the renowned Wadjet family, the "
"descendants of the Exodus heroes Myra, Jevyan, Dvalin and Alenya. His "
"parents were cousins: his father, Sahure Wadjet, was an Admiral Lord who "
"died in a shipwreck while searching for a rumoured new land across the "
"eastern ocean; and his mother, Amunet Wadjet, waa a Light Mage who "
"frequently visited the lands of Maat'Kare's allies as an ambassadress, until "
"her death by a mysterious disease. Orphaned at the age of seven, he was then "
"adopted by Menon Hekare, and moved to the Academy of Maat'Kare. For growing "
"up at such a culturally rich environment, and being Myra's heir, it was "
"believed that he would be a prodigy, but unfortunately Akhen didn't live up "
"to everyone's expectations, not in the least. Still, he won't be easily "
"disheartened by a few failures; after all, he does have a great inner "
"potential that may yet blossom."
msgstr ""
"Akhen Wadjet es el último heredero restante de la renombrada familia Wadjet, "
"los descendientes de los héroes del Éxodo Myra, Jevyan, Dvalin y Alenya. Sus "
"padres eran primos: su padre, Sahure Wadjet, era un Lord Almirante que murió "
"en un naufragio mientras buscaba una supuesta nueva tierra al otro lado del "
"océano oriental; y su madre, Amunet Wadjet, era una Maga de la Luz que "
"frecuentemente visitaba las tierras de los aliados de Maat'Kare como "
"embajadora, hasta su muerte por una misteriosa enfermedad. Huérfano a la "
"edad de siete años, fue adoptado por Menon Hekare y se mudó a la Academia de "
"Maat'Kare. Por haber crecido en un ambiente tan rico culturalmente y siendo "
"el heredero de Myra, se creía que sería un prodigio, pero lamentablemente "
"Akhen no cumplió con las expectativas de nadie, ni por asomo. Aun así, no se "
"desanimará fácilmente por unos pocos fracasos; después de todo, sí tiene un "
"gran potencial interno que aún puede florecer."

