"Filled with hatred and malice, these beings will destroy anything that is "
"foolish enough to stand in their way."
msgstr ""
"Llenos de odio y malicia, estos seres destruirán cualquier cosa que sea lo "
"suficientemente tonta como para interponerse en su camino."

#. [unit_type], id=Duelist Nyx, race=vampire, gender=female
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Duelist_Nyx.cfg:5
msgid "female^Duelist"
msgstr "Duelista"

#. [unit_type], id=Duelist Nyx, race=vampire, gender=female
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Duelist_Nyx.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Vampires have always had a somewhat upper-class manner. This transfers over "
"to their style of fighting too. The vampires without the family or "
"leadership to become lords make themselves useful to a lord that can ensure "
"they always have a fresh supply of blood. Those who do this are known as "
"duelists. Their masters use them as guards and assassins. The wear not "
"armor, but focus on rapid pinpoint fencing which they carry out with inhuman "
"accuracy."
msgstr ""
"Los vampiros siempre han tenido un aire algo aristocrático. Esto se traslada "
"también a su estilo de lucha. Los vampiros sin familia ni liderazgo para "
"convertirse en señores se hacen útiles para un señor que pueda asegurarles "
"un suministro constante de sangre fresca. Quienes hacen esto son conocidos "
"como duelistas. Sus amos los usan como guardias y asesinos. No llevan "
"armadura, sino que se centran en una esgrima rápida y precisa que ejecutan "
"con una precisión inhumana."

