msgstr "erupción"

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Fire_Empress_Sadjet.cfg:53
msgid "holy fire"
msgstr "fuego sagrado"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Fire_Empress_Sadjet.cfg:65
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Silver_Master_Atseger.cfg:46
msgid "blazing meteor shower"
msgstr "lluvia de meteoros ardientes"

#. [unit_type], id=Aaneb_Suryen, race=maatkarian, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Aaneb, race=maatkarian, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/MaatKarian_Aaneb_Suryen.cfg:5
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/maatkarians/MaatKarian_Aaneb.cfg:5
msgid "A'aneb"
msgstr "A'aneb"

#. [unit_type], id=Aaneb_Suryen, race=maatkarian, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Aaneb, race=maatkarian, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/MaatKarian_Aaneb_Suryen.cfg:30
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/maatkarians/MaatKarian_Aaneb.cfg:29
msgid ""
"A'anebs - or 'great lord' - are extremely seasoned commanders, and have led "
"their men to victory on many occasions; they know the best way to fight on "
"each kind of terrain and the best tactical formations, both offensie and "
"defensive; and they know how to grasp victory even when the situation seems "
"hopeless. In addition to their brilliant mind for strategies, they're "
"formidable warriors themselves; their mere presence can boost their "
"soldiers' morale. So formidable and respected they are, that they're often "
"given the title of Lords and entrusted with the government of entire towns."
msgstr ""
"Los A'aneb —o «gran señor»— son comandantes extremadamente experimentados y "
"han llevado a sus hombres a la victoria en muchas ocasiones; conocen la "
"mejor forma de luchar en cada tipo de terreno y las mejores formaciones "
"tácticas, tanto ofensivas como defensivas; y saben cómo arrebatar la "
"victoria incluso cuando la situación parece desesperada. Además de su "
"brillante mente para las estrategias, ellos mismos son guerreros "
"formidables; su mera presencia puede elevar la moral de sus soldados. Tan "
"formidables y respetados son que a menudo reciben el título de Señores y se "
"les confía el gobierno de ciudades enteras."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/MaatKarian_Aaneb_Suryen.cfg:50
