msgstr "Sanación rúnica"

#. [heals], id=rune_healing
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Sigdral.cfg:263
msgid ""
"Allows the unit to heal adjacent allied units at the beginning of our turn.\n"
"\n"
"A unit cared for by this healer may heal up to 8 HP per turn, or stop poison "
"from taking effect for that turn.\n"
"A poisoned unit cannot be cured of its poison by a healer, and must seek the "
"care of a village or a unit that can cure."
msgstr ""
"Permite a la unidad sanar a unidades aliadas adyacentes al comienzo de "
"nuestro turno.\n"
"\n"
"Una unidad atendida por este sanador puede sanarse hasta 8 PV por turno, o "
"detener el efecto del veneno durante ese turno.\n"
"Una unidad envenenada no puede ser curada de su veneno por un sanador y debe "
"buscar el cuidado de una aldea o de una unidad que pueda curar."

#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Sigdral.cfg:281
msgid "Master Othala, the Rune of Protection"
msgstr "Maestro Othala, la Runa de la Protección"

#. [resistance], id=runic_protection
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Sigdral.cfg:293
msgid "Runic protection"
msgstr "protección rúnica"

#. [resistance], id=runic_protection
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Sigdral.cfg:294
msgid ""
"Adjacent units of level 3 or below from this side receive a +20% bonus to "
"all resistances (up to a maximum of 50%)."
msgstr ""
"Las unidades adyacentes de nivel 3 o inferior de este bando reciben un bono "
"de +20 % a todas las resistencias (hasta un máximo de 50 %)."

#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Sigdral.cfg:320
msgid "Strengthen Sowilo, the Solar Rune"
msgstr "Fortalecer Sowilo, la Runa Solar"

#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Sigdral.cfg:335
msgid "Strengthen Uruz, the Rune of Strength"
msgstr "Fortalecer Uruz, la Runa de la Fuerza"

#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Sigdral.cfg:350
msgid "Runic Apprentice"
msgstr "Aprendiz Rúnico"

#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/Sigdral.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Dwarvish society is one that offers few paths of life to its females: "
"because they're so frail and rare, they're kept in safety by the male "
"dwarves, away from hazardous tasks - that is, nearly all of those done by "
"the dwarves -, perilous places and especially warfare. The only important "
"role that is safe enough for the females is that of a Rune Master; however, "
"this is a path that demands decades of full dedication to the study of the "
"runic mysteries, and since female dwarves are expected to bear as many "
"children as they can, they don't find enough time for narly anything else. "
"But this is not true of Sigdral: being raised by her more liberal brother "
"and by the Runemaster Anduril - who could never say 'no' to the apple of his "
"eyes -, she took great interest in the runic lore from an early age; and, "
"when told that she'd have to abandon that path when she married and had "
"children, she simply decided that she'd neither marry nor bear any children, "
"and passed to her brother the mission to continue the lineage of Dvalin and "
"Alenya.\n"
"\t\n"
"And she did improve herself as a Runic Apprentice regardless of all "
"criticism. However, when some more conservative Aigathol dwarves threatened "
"to request her to be cast out, Sigdral accepted to marry Argatyr, the King "
"of the Motsoghnir, who had promised to let her keep studying as a Runic "
"Apprentice. Their marriage was short-lived, though, for reasons that have "
"never been quite clear to anyone other than Sigdral herself. Back to her "
"homeland, she kept casting her runes and learning new ones, deaf to the "
"constant criticism of her detractors, and dreaming about breaking yet "
"another barrier: to be able to wander freely outside the caves."
msgstr ""
"La sociedad enana es una que ofrece pocos caminos de vida a sus hembras: "
"porque son tan frágiles y raras, son mantenidas a salvo por los enanos "
"machos, lejos de tareas peligrosas —es decir, casi todas las que realizan "
"los enanos—, lugares peligrosos y especialmente la guerra. El único rol "
"importante que es lo suficientemente seguro para las hembras es el de "
"Maestra de Runas; sin embargo, este es un camino que exige décadas de "
"dedicación total al estudio de los misterios rúnicos, y como se espera que "
"las enanas hembras tengan tantos hijos como puedan, no encuentran tiempo "
"suficiente para casi nada más. Pero esto no es cierto para Sigdral: al ser "
"criada por su hermano más liberal y por el Maestro de Runas Anduril —quien "
"nunca podía decir «no» a la niña de sus ojos—, tomó gran interés en el "
"conocimiento rúnico desde temprana edad; y, cuando le dijeron que tendría "
"que abandonar ese camino cuando se casara y tuviera hijos, simplemente "
"decidió que ni se casaría ni tendría hijos, y le pasó a su hermano la misión "
"de continuar el linaje de Dvalin y Alenya.\n"
"\t\n"
"Y sí se perfeccionó como Aprendiz Rúnico a pesar de todas las críticas. Sin "
"embargo, cuando algunos enanos Aigathol más conservadores amenazaron con "
"pedir que la expulsaran, Sigdral aceptó casarse con Argatyr, el Rey de los "
"Motsoghnir, quien había prometido dejarla seguir estudiando como Aprendiz "
"Rúnico. Su matrimonio fue corto, sin embargo, por razones que nunca han sido "
"del todo claras para nadie más que la propia Sigdral. De regreso a su "
"patria, siguió lanzando sus runas y aprendiendo nuevas, sorda a las "
"constantes críticas de sus detractores, y soñando con romper otra barrera "
"más: poder vagar libremente fuera de las cuevas."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee  # The idea here is that Siggy needs to stay close to the enemy to maximize the damage caused by this rune
