"practice target; in order not to break too easily, it's made so that it may "
"withstand many spells by lower-level mages."
msgstr ""
"Este gran orbe de cristal es usado por los aprendices de magia maat'karianos "
"como objetivo de práctica; para no romperse demasiado fácilmente, está hecho "
"de manera que pueda resistir muchos hechizos de magos de nivel inferior."

#. [unit_type], id=Transport Vessel, race=mechanical
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Transport_Vessel.cfg:5
msgid "Skironian Transport Vessel"
msgstr "Nave de Transporte Skironiana"

#. [unit_type], id=Transport Vessel, race=mechanical
#. [unit_type], id=War Vessel, race=mechanical
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Transport_Vessel.cfg:19
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/War_Vessel.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Skiron's ships are powerful juggernauts which rule the seas around both "
"Argea and Netjer-Ta; they're moved by undead crews which never tire, and so "
"they move more efficiently than most ships; on the other hand, they're "
"impregnated with dark energy, which makes them as vulnerable to arcane magic "
"as it is to fire."
msgstr ""
"Los barcos de Skiron son poderosos gigantes que dominan los mares alrededor "
"tanto de Argea como de Netjer-Ta; son impulsados por tripulaciones no "
"muertas que nunca se cansan, y por eso se mueven más eficientemente que la "
"mayoría de los barcos; por otro lado, están impregnados de energía oscura, "
"lo que los hace tan vulnerables a la magia arcana como al fuego."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/miscelanea/Transport_Vessel.cfg:38
