#. [unit_type], id=Stalker, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b1_Stalker.cfg:5
msgid "Stalker"
msgstr "Acechador"

#. [unit_type], id=Stalker, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b1_Stalker.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Stalkers are the smaller of the Warg bretheren and are known for their "
"darker fur. Because of their smaller size these Warg wield a spear in combat "
"instead of their claws. Stalkers use their heightened agility to great use "
"in combat to surround their foes."
msgstr ""
"Los acechadores son los más pequeños de los hermanos huargos y se "
"caracterizan por su pelaje más oscuro. Debido a su menor tamaño, estos "
"huargos usan una lanza en combate en lugar de sus garras. Los acechadores "
"aprovechan al máximo su mayor agilidad en combate para rodear a sus enemigos."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b1_Stalker.cfg:37
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b2_Shadow_Pelt.cfg:37
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b3_Night_Eye.cfg:39
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c2_Rabid_Wolf.cfg:43
msgid "tackle"
msgstr "placaje"

#. [unit_type], id=Shadow Pelt, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b2_Shadow_Pelt.cfg:5
msgid "Shadow Pelt"
msgstr "Pelaje Sombrío"

#. [unit_type], id=Shadow Pelt, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b2_Shadow_Pelt.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Many stalkers who have grown more experianced, will smear certain kinds of "
"dirt and dust on their fur to make themselves harder to see. This has lead "
"to the term shadow pelt, as it gives the impression of a permanent shadow "
"resting on them."
msgstr ""
"Muchos acechadores que han ganado experiencia se untan ciertos tipos de "
"tierra y polvo en el pelaje para hacerse más difíciles de ver. Esto ha dado "
"lugar al término «pelaje sombrío», ya que da la impresión de una sombra "
"permanente descansando sobre ellos."

#. [unit_type], id=Night Eye, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b3_Night_Eye.cfg:5
msgid "Night Eye"
msgstr "Ojo Nocturno"

#. [unit_type], id=Night Eye, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/b3_Night_Eye.cfg:19
msgid ""
"After a time as a shadow pelt something about the dirt bleeds into the fur. "
"This gives a very dark shade of black that hides very well in the darkest of "
"nights."
msgstr ""
"Tras un tiempo como pelaje sombrío, algo de la suciedad se filtra en el "
"pelaje. Esto da un tono muy oscuro de negro que se camufla muy bien en las "
"noches más oscuras."

#. [unit_type], id=Warrior Wolf, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c1_Warrior_Wolf.cfg:5
msgid "Warrior Wolf"
msgstr "Guerrero Lobo"

#. [unit_type], id=Warrior Wolf, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c1_Warrior_Wolf.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The low ranking warriors of the clan are know as wolves, only after proving "
"themselves are they allowed to call themselves warg."
msgstr ""
"Los guerreros de bajo rango del clan son conocidos como lobos; solo después "
"de probarse a sí mismos se les permite llamarse huargos."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c1_Warrior_Wolf.cfg:24
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c2_Rabid_Wolf.cfg:34
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/f1_Blackfur.cfg:23
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/f2_Black_Hunter.cfg:27
msgid "Claws"
msgstr "Garras"

#. [unit_type], id=Rabid Wolf, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c2_Rabid_Wolf.cfg:5
msgid "Rabid Wolf"
msgstr "Lobo Rabioso"

#. [unit_type], id=Rabid Wolf, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c2_Rabid_Wolf.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Some warrior wolves prefer to become more like wolves rather than choose to "
"take the name of warg. They never learn how to use weapons, but instead "
"adapt a style using their whole body, and move on all fours."
msgstr ""
"Algunos guerreros lobunos prefieren parecerse más a los lobos que adoptar el "
"nombre de huargo. Nunca aprenden a usar armas, sino que adaptan un estilo "
"usando todo su cuerpo y se mueven a cuatro patas."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c2_Rabid_Wolf.cfg:25
msgid "Fangs"
msgstr "Colmillos"

#. [unit_type], id=Warrior Warg, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c2_Warrior_Warg.cfg:5
msgid "Warrior Warg"
msgstr "Guerrero Huargo"

#. [unit_type], id=Warrior Warg, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c2_Warrior_Warg.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The Warg who have proven themselves worthy of the name are a force to be "
"reckoned with when defending their homeland."
msgstr ""
"Los huargos que han demostrado ser dignos del nombre son una fuerza a tener "
"en cuenta cuando defienden su patria."

#. [unit_type], id=Fenrir, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Fenrir.cfg:7
msgid "Fenrir"
msgstr "Fenrir"

#. [unit_type], id=Fenrir, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Fenrir.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Warg can fight quite well without weapons, as such many of their warriors "
"never become skilled with them. However the ones who do, are given the title "
"Fenrir, and are warriors to be feared."
msgstr ""
"Los huargos pueden luchar bastante bien sin armas, por lo que muchos de sus "
"guerreros nunca se vuelven expertos con ellas. Sin embargo, los que sí lo "
"hacen reciben el título de Fenrir y son guerreros temidos."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Fenrir.cfg:27
msgid "war axe"
msgstr "hacha de guerra"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Fenrir.cfg:36
msgid "war hammer"
msgstr "martillo de guerra"

#. [unit_type], id=Moon Blade, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Moon_Blade.cfg:5
msgid "Moon Blade"
msgstr "Hoja Lunar"

#. [unit_type], id=Moon Blade, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Moon_Blade.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The warg revere the moon, and sometimes the moon blesses devout warriors "
"with strange powers. These warg are marked with white fur, and wield swords "
"like slivers of the moon."
msgstr ""
"Los huargos reverencian la luna, y a veces la luna bendice a los guerreros "
"devotos con extraños poderes. Estos huargos se distinguen por su pelaje "
"blanco y empuñan espadas como astillas de luna."

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Moon_Blade.cfg:25
msgid "Moon Sword"
msgstr "Espada Lunar"

#. [unit_type], id=Pack Leader, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Pack_Leader.cfg:5
msgid "Pack Leader"
msgstr "Líder de Manada"

#. [unit_type], id=Pack Leader, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c3_Pack_Leader.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The individual packs, and clans each have a leader chosen from their "
"warriors, for his wisdom and prowess."
msgstr ""
"Cada manada y clan tiene un líder elegido entre sus guerreros por su "
"sabiduría y destreza."

#. [unit_type], id=Garou, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c4_Garou.cfg:5
msgid "Garou"
msgstr "Garou"

#. [unit_type], id=Garou, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/c4_Garou.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Most warg don't live to be very old. However the leaders that live to be "
"very old are revered by freinds, and feared by foes."
msgstr ""
"La mayoría de los huargos no viven hasta ser muy viejos. Sin embargo, los "
"líderes que llegan a una edad avanzada son reverenciados por los amigos y "
"temidos por los enemigos."

#. [unit_type], id=Wolf Cub, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d0_Wolf_Cub.cfg:5
msgid "Wolf Cub"
msgstr "Cachorro de lobo"

#. [unit_type], id=Wolf Cub, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d0_Wolf_Cub.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The warg can catch and train real wolves to aid them in war. They do it by "
"capturing wolf cubs, and starting the training while they are very young. "
"Wolves make good scouts as they can move even faster than the warg can."
msgstr ""
"Los huargos pueden capturar y entrenar lobos reales para ayudarlos en la "
"guerra. Lo hacen capturando cachorros de lobo y comenzando el entrenamiento "
"cuando aún son muy jóvenes. Los lobos son buenos exploradores porque pueden "
"moverse incluso más rápido que los huargos."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d0_Wolf_Cub.cfg:25
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d1_Wolf.cfg:25
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d2_Dire_Wolf.cfg:25
msgid "Bite"
msgstr "Mordisco"

#. [unit_type], id=EoM Wolf, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d1_Wolf.cfg:5
msgid "Wolf"
msgstr "Lobo"

#. [unit_type], id=EoM Wolf, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d1_Wolf.cfg:19
msgid "Full grown wolves are rather swift, and accurate with their jaws."
msgstr "Los lobos adultos son bastante rápidos y precisos con sus mandíbulas."

#. [unit_type], id=EoM Dire Wolf, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d2_Dire_Wolf.cfg:5
msgid "Dire Wolf"
msgstr "Lobo Terrible"

#. [unit_type], id=EoM Dire Wolf, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/d2_Dire_Wolf.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Something about the warg bleeds into the wolves they tame, causing them to "
"grow larger, and stronger. These wolves, known as dire wolves provide swift "
"sure firepower to the wargs arsenal."
msgstr ""
"Algo de los huargos se transmite a los lobos que domestican, haciendo que "
"crezcan más grandes y fuertes. Estos lobos, conocidos como lobos terribles, "
"proporcionan potencia de fuego rápida y segura al arsenal de los huargos."

#. [unit_type], id=Fire Sprite, race=dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e1_Fire_Sprite.cfg:5
msgid "Fire Sprite"
msgstr "Duende de Fuego"

#. [unit_type], id=Fire Sprite, race=dryad
#. [unit_type], id=Flame Sprite, race=dryad
#. [unit_type], id=Flame Spirit, race=dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e1_Fire_Sprite.cfg:18
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e2_Flame_Sprite.cfg:18
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e3_Flame_Spirit.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Fire Sprites are tiny faerie creatures who get their name from being able to "
"somewhat control the element of fire. Living in the forest, these creatures "
"use their powers primarily to prevent their homes from burning down. Sharing "
"a respect for the woods, they have become great allies with the Warg."
msgstr ""
"Los espíritus de llama son diminutas criaturas feéricas que reciben su "
"nombre por su capacidad para controlar en cierta medida el elemento del "
"fuego. Viviendo en el bosque, estas criaturas usan sus poderes "
"principalmente para evitar que sus hogares se quemen. Compartiendo el "
"respeto por los bosques, se han convertido en grandes aliados de los huargos."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e1_Fire_Sprite.cfg:25
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e2_Flame_Sprite.cfg:25
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e3_Flame_Spirit.cfg:26
msgid "sprite punch"
msgstr "puñetazo de duende"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e1_Fire_Sprite.cfg:34
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e2_Flame_Sprite.cfg:34
msgid "sapphire flame"
msgstr "llama de zafiro"

#. [unit_type], id=Flame Sprite, race=dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e2_Flame_Sprite.cfg:5
msgid "Flame Sprite"
msgstr "Duende de Llama"

#. [unit_type], id=Flame Spirit, race=dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e3_Flame_Spirit.cfg:5
msgid "Flame Spirit"
msgstr "Espíritu de Llama"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/e3_Flame_Spirit.cfg:35
msgid "spirit fire"
msgstr "fuego espiritual"

#. [unit_type], id=Blackfur, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/f1_Blackfur.cfg:5
msgid "Blackfur"
msgstr "Pelaje Negro"

#. [unit_type], id=Blackfur, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/f1_Blackfur.cfg:18
msgid ""
"There is a rare breed of warg with black fur and a slight build. Although "
"not as physicaly strong as the normal kind, foes have learned to fear the "
"sudden death that could await in any dark shadow."
msgstr ""
"Existe una rara estirpe de huargos con pelaje negro y complexión delgada. "
"Aunque no tan fuertes físicamente como los normales, los enemigos han "
"aprendido a temer la muerte repentina que puede acechar en cualquier sombra "
"oscura."

#. [unit_type], id=Black Hunter, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/f2_Black_Hunter.cfg:5
msgid "Black Hunter"
msgstr "Cazador Negro"

#. [unit_type], id=Black Hunter, race=warg
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/f2_Black_Hunter.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The blackfur hunt at night for the concealment it gives, and are quite adept "
"at hunting any kind of quarry."
msgstr ""
"Los de pelaje negro cazan de noche por el camuflaje que les proporciona, y "
"son bastante hábiles cazando cualquier tipo de presa."

#. [unit_type], id=Water Dryad, race=dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g1_Water_Dryad.cfg:5
msgid "Water Dryad"
msgstr "Dríada Acuática"

#. [unit_type], id=Water Dryad, race=dryad
#. [unit_type], id=Water Nymph, race=dryad
#. [unit_type], id=Water Shyde, race=dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g1_Water_Dryad.cfg:18
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g2_Water_Nymph.cfg:18
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g3_Water_Shyde.cfg:19
msgid ""
"In any wetland area you may find a Dryad calling the place her home. Dryads "
"are not combatitive in nature and instead will control surrounding plant "
"life to ensnare her enemies and slow them down until help arrives."
msgstr ""
"En cualquier zona pantanosa puedes encontrar una dríada que llama hogar a "
"ese lugar. Las dríadas no son combativas por naturaleza y en su lugar "
"controlan la vegetación circundante para atrapar a sus enemigos y "
"ralentizarlos hasta que llegue ayuda."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g1_Water_Dryad.cfg:23
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g2_Water_Nymph.cfg:23
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g3_Water_Shyde.cfg:24
msgid "Ensnare"
msgstr "Atrapar"

#. [unit_type], id=Water Nymph, race=dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g2_Water_Nymph.cfg:5
msgid "Water Nymph"
msgstr "Ninfa Acuática"

#. [unit_type], id=Water Shyde, race=dryad
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/wargs/g3_Water_Shyde.cfg:5
msgid "Water Shyde"
msgstr "Sílfide Acuática"

#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Champion, race=washraha
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Champion.cfg:4
msgid "Champion"
msgstr "Campeón"

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Champion.cfg:75
msgid "slash"
msgstr "corte"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Champion.cfg:84
msgid "pole"
msgstr "pértiga"

#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Huntress, race=washraha, gender=female
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Huntress.cfg:4
msgid "Huntress"
msgstr "Cazadora"

#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Jackal Warrior, race=washraha
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Jackal_Warrior.cfg:4
msgid "Jackal Warrior"
msgstr "Guerrero Chacal"

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Jackal_Warrior.cfg:84
msgid "sickle"
msgstr "hoz"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Jackal_Warrior.cfg:93
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Marksman.cfg:78
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:77
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Soldier.cfg:78
msgid "dash"
msgstr "embestida"

#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Lightning Striker, race=washraha, gender=female
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Lightning_Striker.cfg:4
msgid "Lightning Striker"
msgstr "Golpeadora de Relámpagos"

#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Seeker, race=washraha
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Seeker.cfg:4
msgid "Seeker"
msgstr "Buscadora"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=melee
#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Seeker.cfg:30
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Washraja.cfg:31
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Elfin.cfg:80
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Elfin.cfg:89
msgid "torch"
msgstr "antorcha"

#. [attack], type=blade, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Seeker.cfg:38
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Washraja.cfg:39
msgid "barbed axe"
msgstr "hacha dentada"

#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Smiter, race=washraha, gender=female
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Smiter.cfg:4
msgid "Smiter"
msgstr "Castigadora"

#. [unit_type], id=Washraha Warrior, race=washraha
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Warrior.cfg:4
msgid "Warrior"
msgstr "Guerrero"

#. [unit_type], id=Washraja, race=washraha
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Washraja.cfg:4
msgid "Washraja"
msgstr "Washraja"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/washraha/Washraha_Washraja.cfg:48
msgid "scorched axe"
msgstr "hacha abrasada"

#. [unit_type], id=Anuran Rider, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Anuran_Rider.cfg:5
msgid "Anuran Rider"
msgstr "Jinete Anuro"

#. [unit_type], id=Anuran Rider, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Anuran_Rider.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Once the amphibious creature has grown, the owner is able to mount it. The "
"amphibian or anuran can slap enemies with its tongue, stunning them in the "
"process. The stunning effect of the tongue combined with the elfin's "
"accuracy with javelins, makes these riders a force to be reckoned with."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que la criatura anfibia ha crecido, su dueño puede montarla. El "
"anfibio o anuro puede golpear a los enemigos con su lengua, aturdiéndolos en "
"el proceso. El efecto aturdidor de la lengua combinado con la precisión del "
"elfo con jabalinas hace que estos jinetes sean una fuerza a tener en cuenta."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Anuran_Rider.cfg:39
msgid "tongue"
msgstr "lengua"

#. [unit_type], id=Banebush, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Banebush.cfg:5
msgid "Banebush"
msgstr "Arbusto Mortal"

#. [unit_type], id=Banebush, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Banebush.cfg:20
msgid ""
"This monstrous shrub has been named the 'Banebush' by anyone who has managed "
"to survive an encounter with one. Having poisonous fangs and wrapping vines, "
"these plants are deadly when they are in groups."
msgstr ""
"Este arbusto monstruoso ha sido llamado el «Arbusto Mortal» por cualquiera "
"que haya logrado sobrevivir a un encuentro con uno. Teniendo colmillos "
"venenosos y enredaderas envolventes, estas plantas son mortales cuando están "
"en grupo."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Banebush.cfg:43
msgid "ensnare"
msgstr "atrapar"

#. [unit_type], id=Elfin, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Elfin.cfg:5
msgid "Elfin"
msgstr "Elfin"

#. [unit_type], id=Elfin, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Elfin.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Elfins are mischievous creatures found only in the deepest forests. They are "
"called such, by travelers, due to the crude resemblance to the elves they "
"exhibit. Nimble and armed with torches, these beings are hard to hit, but "
"can be injured severely due to their lack of armor. Every Elfins also "
"carries a young rodent along with him, until the rodent grows big enough to "
"be mounted."
msgstr ""
"Los elfins son criaturas traviesas que solo se encuentran en los bosques más "
"profundos. Los viajeros los llaman así debido al parecido crudo que exhiben "
"con los elfos. Ágiles y armados con antorchas, estos seres son difíciles de "
"alcanzar, pero pueden ser gravemente heridos debido a su falta de armadura. "
"Cada elfin también lleva consigo un roedor joven hasta que este crece lo "
"suficiente para ser montado."

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Captain, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Captain.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Captain"
msgstr "Capitán Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Captain, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Captain.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Fauns are sometimes chosen to lead their kind to battle. Such fauns forgo "
"their bows, take the sword and shield and can either slash enemies or bash "
"them. The presence of a captain in faun hunting or war parties inspires the "
"younger fauns to fight with more skill and dexterously."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos a veces son elegidos para liderar a los suyos en batalla. Tales "
"faunos renuncian a sus arcos, toman espada y escudo y pueden tanto cortar "
"como golpear a los enemigos. La presencia de un capitán en partidas de caza "
"o guerra faunas inspira a los faunos más jóvenes a luchar con más habilidad "
"y destreza."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Captain.cfg:109
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Lord.cfg:60
msgid "shield"
msgstr "escudazo"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Lord, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Lord.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Lord"
msgstr "Señor Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Lord, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Lord.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Fauns who have gained the title of 'Lord,' are truly born leaders. Leading "
"armies of forest dwellers, these commanders can give enemies a pain to "
"counteract the mastermind strategy devised. Improving on their sword and "
"shield combination, these warriors can take down most foes with ease."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos que han ganado el título de «Señor» son verdaderos líderes natos. "
"Liderando ejércitos de habitantes del bosque, estos comandantes pueden "
"causar dolor a los enemigos para contrarrestar la estrategia maestra ideada. "
"Mejorando su combinación de espada y escudo, estos guerreros pueden derribar "
"a la mayoría de los enemigos con facilidad."

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Marksman, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Marksman.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Marksman"
msgstr "Tirador Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Marksman, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Marksman.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Fauns, after lots and lots of practice and improve greatly in their bows. "
"Such skill allows them to accurately hit targets far away."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos, tras mucha práctica, mejoran enormemente en sus arcos. Tal "
"habilidad les permite acertar con precisión a objetivos lejanos."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Marksman.cfg:68
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:67
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Soldier.cfg:68
msgid "horns"
msgstr "cuernos"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Sharpshooter, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Sharpshooter"
msgstr "Francotirador Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Sharpshooter, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Fauns have tried to precede the elves in their archery skills, but they have "
"failed to do so. Instead they decide to use more weapons in their arsenal. "
"The result is a master archer with deadly arrows and a few darts containing "
"a mixture of the most venomous toxins the forest has to offer. This arsenal "
"of weapons and the ability of these fauns to move quickly throw the forest, "
"make them skilled assassins. If you ever encounter one of these master "
"killers, then run or prepare to take an arrow throw the heart."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos han intentado superar a los elfos en sus habilidades de arquería, "
"pero han fallado en hacerlo. En cambio decidieron usar más armas en su "
"arsenal. El resultado es un maestro arquero con flechas letales y algunos "
"dardos que contienen una mezcla de las toxinas más venenosas que el bosque "
"tiene para ofrecer. Este arsenal de armas y la capacidad de estos faunos "
"para moverse rápidamente a través del bosque los convierten en asesinos "
"hábiles. Si alguna vez te encuentras con uno de estos maestros asesinos, "
"entonces corre o prepárate para recibir una flecha en el corazón."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:103
msgid "blowgun"
msgstr "cerbatana"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Soldier, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Soldier.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Soldier"
msgstr "Soldado Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Soldier, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Faun_Soldier.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Fauns are mythical creatures, only seen by other forest dwellers. Having the "
"legs and horns of a goat, they can ram foes and move at a remarkable pace. "
"They are also very dexterous with their bows."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos son criaturas míticas, solo vistas por otros habitantes del "
"bosque. Teniendo las piernas y cuernos de una cabra, pueden embestir a los "
"enemigos y moverse a un ritmo notable. También son muy diestros con sus "
"arcos."

#. [unit_type], id=Golem, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Golem.cfg:5
msgid "Golem"
msgstr "Gólem"

#. [unit_type], id=Golem, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Golem.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Magical constructs of unknown origins, these monsters are almost impossible "
"to kill. They have an indefinite lifespan, the oldest of them have lived "
"entire eras. Completely made of solid rock, these creatures can punch any "
"determined foe to submission. Their only weakness is arcane magic - the "
"magic that created them."
msgstr ""
"Constructos mágicos de orígenes desconocidos, estos monstruos son casi "
"imposibles de matar. Tienen una vida indefinida, los más antiguos han vivido "
"eras enteras. Completamente hechos de roca sólida, estas criaturas pueden "
"golpear a cualquier enemigo determinado hasta someterlo. Su única debilidad "
"es la magia arcana, la magia que los creó."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Golem.cfg:72
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Guardian_Golem.cfg:35
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Sentinel_Golem.cfg:72
msgid "punch"
msgstr "puñetazo"

#. [unit_type], id=Guardian Golem, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Guardian_Golem.cfg:5
msgid "Guardian Golem"
msgstr "Gólem Guardián"

#. [unit_type], id=Guardian Golem, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Guardian_Golem.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The largest and most terrifying of these monsters should be avoided at all "
"costs. Their fists can finish of an adult troll in mere moments, while the "
"earthquakes it produces with its fists can knock almost any soldier of "
"balance. Most weapons are useless, but only arcane spells stand a chance in "
"defeating them."
msgstr ""
"Los más grandes y aterradores de estos monstruos deben evitarse a toda "
"costa. Sus puños pueden acabar con un trol adulto en meros momentos, "
"mientras que los terremotos que produce con sus puños pueden derribar a casi "
"cualquier soldado del equilibrio. La mayoría de las armas son inútiles, pero "
"solo los hechizos arcanos tienen una oportunidad de derrotarlos."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Guardian_Golem.cfg:45
msgid "earthquake"
msgstr "terremoto"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Knight, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Knight.cfg:5
msgid "Rodent Knight"
msgstr "Caballero Roedor"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Knight, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Knight.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Elfins who have earned the title of 'Knight,' are respected in the elfin "
"society for their courage and valor. They have incredibly fast mounts and "
"can dodge around the battlefield, piercing through flanks of the enemy. The "
"riders themselves have a good aim at throwing spears and finishing off "
"injured enemies."
msgstr ""
"Los elfins que han ganado el título de «Caballero» son respetados en la "
"sociedad elfin por su coraje y valor. Tienen monturas increíblemente rápidas "
"y pueden esquivar por el campo de batalla, atravesando los flancos del "
"enemigo. Los propios jinetes tienen buena puntería al lanzar lanzas y "
"rematar a enemigos heridos."

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Predator, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Predator.cfg:5
msgid "Rodent Predator"
msgstr "Depredador Roedor"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Predator, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Predator.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Some elfins undertake the task of riding the 'Shadow Rats'. These are "
"aggressive black rats raised in the wild and cannot be tamed easily. Elfins, "
"who have managed to tame them, ride these beasts with pride and are known to "
"strike in the night."
msgstr ""
"Algunos elfins emprenden la tarea de montar las «Ratas Sombra». Estas son "
"ratas negras agresivas criadas en la naturaleza y no pueden ser domesticadas "
"fácilmente. Los elfins que han logrado domarlas montan estas bestias con "
"orgullo y se les conoce por atacar en la noche."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Predator.cfg:52
msgid "shuriken"
msgstr "shuriken"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Rider, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Rider.cfg:5
msgid "Rodent Rider"
msgstr "Jinete Roedor"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Rider, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Rider.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Once the rodent has grown, the elfins mount and ride them. These large rat-"
"like beasts are very fast and quick to dodge enemies, and their riders have "
"an impressive accuracy in throwing spears."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que el roedor ha crecido, los elfins lo montan y cabalgan. Estas "
"grandes bestias parecidas a ratas son muy rápidas y ágiles para esquivar "
"enemigos, y sus jinetes tienen una precisión impresionante al lanzar lanzas."

#. [unit_type], id=Sentinel Golem, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Sentinel_Golem.cfg:5
msgid "Sentinel Golem"
msgstr "Gólem Centinela"

#. [unit_type], id=Sentinel Golem, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Sentinel_Golem.cfg:20
msgid ""
"With hard earthen fists, and near indestructible body, these magical "
"creatures are terrifying to behold. If you ever see one of these, then run."
msgstr ""
"Con puños de tierra dura y un cuerpo casi indestructible, estas criaturas "
"mágicas son aterradoras de ver. Si alguna vez ves una de estas, entonces "
"corre."

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Elfin, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Swamp_Elfin.cfg:5
msgid "Swamp Elfin"
msgstr "Elfin del Pantano"

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Elfin, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Swamp_Elfin.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The Swamp Elfins differ in a variety of ways from their dry land counter "
"parts. They are good swimmers and raise amphibious creatures instead of "
"rodents. They prefer to use a spear in melee and have a good aim at throwing "
"javelins as well."
msgstr ""
"Los elfins del pantano difieren de muchas maneras de sus contrapartes de "
"tierra firme. Son buenos nadadores y crían criaturas anfibias en lugar de "
"roedores. Prefieren usar una lanza en cuerpo a cuerpo y también tienen buena "
"puntería al lanzar jabalinas."

#. [unit_type], id=Toxic Plant, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Toxic_Plant.cfg:5
msgid "Toxic Plant"
msgstr "Planta Tóxica"

#. [unit_type], id=Toxic Plant, race=woodlander
#: War_of_the_Jewel/units/woodlanders/Toxic_Plant.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Toxic plants usually position themselves as a group around roads, in the "
"forests and attack any traveller that is foolish enough to enter their trap. "
"Compared to other plant creatures, these carnivorous beings have mobile "
"roots and secret a poison from their teeth. This makes them very dangerous."
msgstr ""
"Las plantas tóxicas usualmente se posicionan en grupo alrededor de caminos, "
"en los bosques y atacan a cualquier viajero que sea lo suficientemente tonto "
"como para entrar en su trampa. En comparación con otras criaturas vegetales, "
"estos seres carnívoros tienen raíces móviles y secretan veneno de sus "
"dientes. Esto los hace muy peligrosos."

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/character-utils.cfg:80
msgid "aura blast"
msgstr "explosión de aura"

