msgid "terror"
msgstr "terror"

#. [abilities]
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:264
msgid ""
"This unit can frighten enemy units that are next to it, making them fight "
"worse.\n"
"\n"
"Adjacent enemy units of lower level will do less damage in battle. When an "
"enemy unit of the same or lower level is adjacent and engages in combat, its "
"attacks do 15% less damage times the difference in their levels + 15%."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede asustar a las unidades enemigas que estén a su lado, "
"haciendo que luchen peor.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas adyacentes de nivel inferior infligirán menos daño en "
"batalla. Cuando una unidad enemiga del mismo nivel o inferior esté adyacente "
"y entre en combate, sus ataques infligen un 15 % menos de daño por cada "
"diferencia de nivel + 15 %."

#. [hides], id=mountain_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:276
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:278
msgid "mountain ambush"
msgstr "emboscada montañosa"

#. [hides], id=mountain_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:277
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:279
msgid "female^mountain ambush"
msgstr "emboscada montañosa"

#. [hides], id=mountain_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:280
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:283
msgid ""
"This unit can hide in mountainous terrain, and remain undetected by its "
"enemies.\n"
"\n"
"Enemy units cannot see this unit while it is on a mountain, except if they "
"have units next to it. Any enemy unit that first discovers this unit "
"immediately loses all its remaining movement."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede esconderse en terreno montañoso y permanecer indetectada "
"por sus enemigos.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas no pueden ver a esta unidad mientras esté en una "
"montaña, excepto si tienen unidades junto a ella. Cualquier unidad enemiga "
"que descubra primero a esta unidad pierde inmediatamente todo su movimiento "
"restante."

#. [hides], id=mountain_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:292
msgid ""
" On mountainous terrain, this unit's ambush skill renders it invisible to "
"enemies unless it is immediately adjacent or has revealed itself by "
"attacking."
msgstr ""
"En terreno montañoso, la habilidad de emboscada de esta unidad la vuelve "
"invisible para los enemigos a menos que esté inmediatamente adyacente o se "
"haya revelado al atacar."

#. [hides], id=forest_water_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:300
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:302
msgid "forest and water ambush"
msgstr "emboscada en bosque y agua"

#. [hides], id=forest_water_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:301
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:303
msgid "female^forest and water ambush"
msgstr "emboscada en bosque y agua"

#. [hides], id=forest_water_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:304
msgid ""
"This unit can hide in both forest and water, and remain undetected by its "
"enemies.\n"
"\n"
"Enemy units cannot see this unit while it is in either forest or water, "
"except if they have units next to it. Any enemy unit that first discovers "
"this unit immediately loses all its remaining movement."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede esconderse tanto en bosque como en agua y permanecer "
"indetectada por sus enemigos.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas no pueden ver a esta unidad mientras esté en bosque o "
"en agua, excepto si tienen unidades a su lado. Cualquier unidad enemiga que "
"descubra primero a esta unidad pierde inmediatamente todo su movimiento "
"restante."

#. [hides], id=forest_water_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:307
msgid ""
"This unit can hide in both forest and water, and remain undetected by its "
"enemies.\n"
"\n"
"Enemy units cannot see this unit while it is in forest, except if they have "
"units next to it. Any enemy unit that first discovers this unit immediately "
"loses all its remaining movement."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede esconderse tanto en bosque como en agua y permanecer "
"indetectada por sus enemigos.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas no pueden ver a esta unidad mientras esté en bosque, "
"excepto si tienen unidades a su lado. Cualquier unidad enemiga que descubra "
"primero a esta unidad pierde inmediatamente todo su movimiento restante."

#. [hides], id=forest_water_ambush
#: War_of_the_Jewel/utils/wotj-abilities.cfg:316
msgid ""
" On forested or aquatic terrain, this unit's ambush skill renders it "
"invisible to enemies unless it is immediately adjacent or has revealed "
"itself by attacking."
msgstr ""
"En terreno boscoso o acuático, la habilidad de emboscada de esta unidad la "
